NK115(re)001:1: // s+au r+ya ra smi n+aa ma gu na rat+na ko
NK115(re)001:2: sha s+ya t+ai g+ga r+b+h+aa r+tha b+h+aa sa ti bi
NK115(re)001:4: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi 'grel pa zab
NK115(re)001:5: don snang byed nyi ma'i 'od zer zhes bya ba
NK115(re)001:6: bzhugs so // dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:7: da ni lam gyi sbas don gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa ltar 'chad par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:9: khungs la yid ches nas don la spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir lo rgyus brjod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10: lo rgyus dang ldan pa'i chos de ji ltar 'chad pa'i thabs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11: bshad bya gzhung gi rang bzhin dngos bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12: dang po gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i chos kyi
NK115(re)001:13: rnam grangs ji ltar byung ba'i lo rgyus brjod pa
NK115(re)001:14: ni / skal ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis rdo
NK115(re)001:15: rje theg pa'i lta sgom spyod pa'i rnam bzhag thun
NK115(re)001:16: mong ma yin pa dag thos pa tsam gyis kyang
NK115(re)001:17: mos pa rgya chen po thob pa 'gyur bas the
NK115(re)001:19: skal ba dman pa rnams kyis ni /
NK115(re)001:20: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i skus dngos su ma gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21: 'phags pa'i yul kho na nas ma 'gyur ba tsam
NK115(re)001:22: la dpag nas yid mi ches pa 'byung srid pa'i
NK115(re)001:23: phyir na ji ltar byung ba'i lo rgyus brjod par
NK115(re)001:24: bya ste / ji skad du nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NK115(re)001:25: lo rgyus don gyis ma bshad na //
NK115(re)001:26: gsang chen nges pa'i bka' 'di la //
NK115(re)001:27: yid mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:29: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:30: rgyal ba rnams ni 'jig rten byon pa'i tshe //
NK115(re)001:31: de yis gsungs pa'i lung chen rnams la ni //
NK115(re)001:32: phyi rol rgol ba ngan pa 'byung srid kyis //
NK115(re)001:33: dang por srid pa chos kyi lo rgyus smos //
NK115(re)001:34: zhes gsungs pas nang rgyud yo ga gsum gtso bor
NK115(re)001:35: gyur pa'i rgyud sde rnams ji ltar byung ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:36: ni / spyir snga 'gyur rnying ma'i rgyud sde bka' ma thams cad brgyud pa gsum ldan dang /
NK115(re)001:37: gter ma rnams brgyud tshul drug dang bdun dang dgu rnams su nges pa las /
NK115(re)001:39: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK115(re)001:41: gang zag rna bar brgyud pa ste gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:43: de'i steng du mkha' 'gro gtad rgya'i brgyud pa /
NK115(re)001:44: smon lam dbang bskur gyi brgyud pa /
NK115(re)001:45: shog ser tshig gi brgyud pa ste drug go //
NK115(re)001:47: drug pa dor te bka' babs lung bstan gyi brgyud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:48: nyams len byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa gnyis bsnan pas bdun no //
NK115(re)001:50: de'i steng du snyan brgyud dmar khrid kyi brgyud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:51: phrin las phyag bzhes kyi brgyud pa ste dagu'o //
NK115(re)001:52: de dag las dang po'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:54: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK115(re)001:55: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK115(re)001:56: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK115(re)001:57: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyal ba rigs drug pa nas
NK115(re)001:58: da lta'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bar du
NK115(re)001:59: brgyud pa gsum gyi tshul du brgyud pa'i zam ma
NK115(re)001:60: chad cing / byin rlabs kyi dgongs bcud ma nyams pa zhig go //
NK115(re)001:61: de la dang po rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK115(re)001:62: gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa'i ston pa kun tu
NK115(re)001:63: bzang po nyid kyi thugs rje'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK115(re)001:65: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing khams dang /
NK115(re)001:69: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor sku lnga lhun grub
NK115(re)001:70: kyi rig 'dzin dang rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs bsam
NK115(re)001:71: gyis mi khyab pa rnams la chos thams cad tshig
NK115(re)001:72: dang brda'i sgo nas ma gsungs kyang /
NK115(re)001:73: thugs rje chen po rang rig pa ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:74: rang gdangs 'bad med lhun grub tu gsal ba nyid
NK115(re)001:75: las / ston pas mi gsung bar gsungs pa na /
NK115(re)001:76: 'khor rnams kyi don gyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma
NK115(re)001:77: log pa mngon du gyur te spangs rtogs kyi yon
NK115(re)001:78: tan dbyer med par gyur pa'o //
NK115(re)001:79: de ltar ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su med par
NK115(re)001:80: bzhugs pa de'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du gdul
NK115(re)001:81: bya'i khams su cho 'phrul chen po rnam pa gsum
NK115(re)001:83: de yang sku'i sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK115(re)001:86: sna tshogs sprul pa gsum gyi bkod pas gdul bya'i skal ba dang 'tshams par don mdzad cing /
NK115(re)001:87: gsung gi sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul yang /
NK115(re)001:88: ston pa nyid kyi gsang gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK115(re)001:89: dbyings las skye med mtshon pa'i yi ge a nyid
NK115(re)001:90: rang snang ba'i rnam par 'phrul pa +aa lii dang
NK115(re)001:91: k+aa li'i tshogs rnams las mtshon bya dang mtshon byed
NK115(re)001:92: tha mi dad bzhin don gyi dgongs pa mtshon byed
NK115(re)001:93: kyi yi ge'i tshogs su snang nas gdul bya'i don
NK115(re)001:95: de yang sgrar snang rung tsam ston pa rigs drug
NK115(re)001:96: pa'i dgongs pa'i klong na rang gsal ba rgyal ba
NK115(re)001:97: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i thugs su chud par mdzad
NK115(re)001:98: pa nyid / gsang bdag la sogs pa'i gzhan snang
NK115(re)001:99: gi ston pas sgrar grags pa'i sgo nas snang bar
NK115(re)001:100: pa nyid / mdzad pa de / blo gros thabs
NK115(re)001:101: ldan la sogs pas brdar gyur pa'i yi ge'i tshogs
NK115(re)001:102: su byas nas rim par brgyud de /
NK115(re)001:103: da lta yang yi ge'i phyi mo brdar gyur pa'i
NK115(re)001:104: tshul du yod pa sogs las 'chad pa po'i blo
NK115(re)001:105: la brjod bya'i don mtshon pa'i sgra spyi snang nas
NK115(re)001:106: sgrar grags pa'i tshul gyis bshad pas nyan pa po'i
NK115(re)001:107: blo la'ang de ltar snang ba ni de bzhin gshegs
NK115(re)001:108: pa'i gsung gi cho 'phrul yi ge'i 'khor lo'i mdzad
NK115(re)001:110: thugs kyi sprul pa ltar snang ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK115(re)001:111: yi ges mtshon par bya ba'i gnas lugs ma 'khrul pa'i ye shes de /
NK115(re)001:112: nyid kyi thugs la mnga' bzhin rang las mi gzhan
NK115(re)001:113: pa'i 'khor rnams kyi thugs su chud par byin gyis
NK115(re)001:114: brlabs nas / de ltar ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba
NK115(re)001:115: rnams kyi kun rtog gi rgyun chos nyid de bzhin
NK115(re)001:116: du ngal gso bar bya ba'i phyir gsang chen bla
NK115(re)001:117: na med pa'i theg pa rnams nyid kyi dgongs pa'i
NK115(re)001:118: klong nas nyid kyi thugs la mkhyen par mdzad nas
NK115(re)001:119: brlabs nas / / de nyid dngos su go rtogs
NK115(re)001:120: kyi skal pa dang mi ldan pa rnams la lam
NK115(re)001:121: stegs kyi theg pa sna tshogs par snang bas don
NK115(re)001:122: zab mo mtshon te ngo sprod par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:123: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK115(re)001:124: skal ba bzang po dang ldan pa'i lha dang mi
NK115(re)001:125: la sogs pa'i gdul bya rnams la rim gyis brgyud
NK115(re)001:126: pa ste / de yang rig 'dzin mi ma yin la brgyud pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:127: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas lha grags ldan phyogs skyong la bshad /
NK115(re)001:128: spyan ras gzigs kyis klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad /
NK115(re)001:129: phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad de /
NK115(re)001:130: rigs gsum sems dpas lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas so sor gsungs pa rnams rim gyis dar ro //
NK115(re)001:131: rig 'dzin mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa ni /
NK115(re)001:132: bskal pa bzang po'i dus 'dir ston pa rigs drug
NK115(re)001:133: pa nyid rnam 'dren stong gi rnam par 'phrul pa
NK115(re)001:134: las bzhi pa bdag cag gi ston pas sde snod
NK115(re)001:135: gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing shin tu
NK115(re)001:136: skal ba dang ldan pa'i gdul bya 'ga' zhig la
NK115(re)001:137: gsang ba sngags kyi chos kyi rnam grangs kyang bstan
NK115(re)001:138: mod kyi khyab brdal du ma grags par sku mya
NK115(re)001:139: ngan las 'da' bar nye ba'i tshe 'khor 'dus pa'i
NK115(re)001:140: nang nas rdzu 'phrul cher spyod la /
NK115(re)001:141: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na chos 'di bar
NK115(re)001:142: gtogs pa'i nga'i slob ma ji snyed yod pa rnams
NK115(re)001:143: sdus shig dang / nges par bzhag par bya ba dag yod do zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:144: rdzu 'phrul can des thams cad kyis go bar /
NK115(re)001:145: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur rigs drug gang su dag /
NK115(re)001:146: 'di bar nges shing phyogs pa kun nyon cig /
NK115(re)001:147: deng 'dir rgyal bas bdud rtsi gsum 'jog gis //
NK115(re)001:148: dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus shig /
NK115(re)001:149: ces bsgrags pas dam pa'i rigs can lnga ma gtogs pa thams cad 'dus par gyur to //
NK115(re)001:150: de la ston pas nga yongs su mya ngan las
NK115(re)001:151: 'da' bas su la the tshom ma chod pa yod
NK115(re)001:152: pa rnams dris shig ces bka' stsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:153: 'khor gyi nang nas rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po ku
NK115(re)001:154: dza ra zhes bya ba de rang gi stan las
NK115(re)001:155: langs te seng ge'i lta stangs kyis ston pa'i zhal
NK115(re)001:156: du bltas nas / khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK115(re)001:160: sa dang rnam thar la spyad pas //
NK115(re)001:161: byang chub thob par 'gyur ba yi //
NK115(re)001:162: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum las //
NK115(re)001:163: gang dag rim par bkod legs par //
NK115(re)001:164: mnyam pas blang dor med spyod cing //
NK115(re)001:165: byang chub gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK115(re)001:166: thabs chen dpag gis mi lang ba //
NK115(re)001:167: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK115(re)001:168: zhes pa la sogs pa zhus pa'i lan du /
NK115(re)001:170: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK115(re)001:171: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK115(re)001:172: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK115(re)001:173: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK115(re)001:174: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK115(re)001:175: mi las skal ldan rigs can te //
NK115(re)001:176: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK115(re)001:177: sngon ltas bzang pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:178: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rir //
NK115(re)001:179: grogs kyi sems can dman pa'i rigs //
NK115(re)001:180: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs par //
NK115(re)001:181: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:183: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po gnas skabs bcu gnyis su 'byung ste /
NK115(re)001:184: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:185: 'jig rten gyi sgron ma yongs su bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:186: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:187: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:188: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:189: gdul bya skabs la babs pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:190: byin gyis brlabs las snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:191: brgyud pa thabs kyis grags pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:192: gang gis ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:193: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:194: las rgyun yongs su gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:195: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:197: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK115(re)001:199: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK115(re)001:201: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde rnams ston pa gshegs nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK115(re)001:202: rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas bdun byung ste /
NK115(re)001:203: rang gi khang steng du rin po che gser gyi
NK115(re)001:204: glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas yi ger bris
NK115(re)001:205: pa'i gsang sngags rgyud sde'i pusti mang po dang /
NK115(re)001:206: phyag rdor gyi sku khru gang pa zhig babs pa rnyed de /
NK115(re)001:207: gsol ba btab pas rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u shes nas de dang /
NK115(re)001:208: phyag rdor gyi sku la brten te zla ba drug
NK115(re)001:209: tu bsgrubs pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mjal byin
NK115(re)001:210: gyis brlabs pas / glegs bam rnams kyi don ma
NK115(re)001:211: lus pa mkhyen te slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza
NK115(re)001:212: gyis brlabs pas / la gsungs / des seng ha r+aa dza la /
NK115(re)001:213: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK115(re)001:214: des sras mo go ma la gsungs pa ste de
NK115(re)001:215: yan chad tshom bu'i 'khor dang bcas te rig 'dzin
NK115(re)001:216: gyi sa la gshegs shing rig pa khyad pa can
NK115(re)001:217: gyi brgyud pa zam ma chad pas rig 'dzin rig
NK115(re)001:218: pa'i brgyud par 'dren pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:219: lung a nu yo ga'i byung tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:220: yang dus de'i tshe dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma
NK115(re)001:221: lngas ri ma la ya'i rtse mor phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK115(re)001:222: rgyas thams cad yid la byas te /
NK115(re)001:223: kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong //
NK115(re)001:224: ston pa gsal byed 'od nub na //
NK115(re)001:225: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK115(re)001:226: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyer gsum bton
NK115(re)001:227: pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsang ba'i
NK115(re)001:229: gsang bdag gis ri ma la ya'i rtser dam pa'i
NK115(re)001:230: rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la mdo dgongs pa 'dus
NK115(re)001:231: pa la sogs pa gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:232: de'i byin rlabs las lung a nu yo ga'i rgyud
NK115(re)001:233: sde rnams lang ka'i yul zhes grags pa sing ga
NK115(re)001:234: la'i nags tshal du babs pa rgyal po dzahns brgyud
NK115(re)001:235: pa'ang yod la / gzhan du nub phyogs o rgyan
NK115(re)001:236: gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling du lag na
NK115(re)001:237: pa'ang yod la / rdo rjes / sprul pa'i sku
NK115(re)001:238: dga' rab rdo rje la dpal gsang ba'i rgyud dang
NK115(re)001:239: pa'ang yod la / rdo rjes / man ngag dang / phur pa dang /
NK115(re)001:240: ma mo'i rgyud la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:241: de dag kyang o rgyan pad+ma thod phreng la bka' babs nas rim par dar ro //
NK115(re)001:242: man ngag a ti yo ga yang dang po lha'i yul du dar te /
NK115(re)001:243: de yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis dpal rdo rje
NK115(re)001:244: sems dpa' la bskul bas sh+r+ai badz+ra sa t+wa'i thugs
NK115(re)001:245: ka nas rin po che rang 'bar gyi 'khor lo
NK115(re)001:246: byung ste / sems dpa' rdo rje la gtad nas /
NK115(re)001:248: gnyis med ye shes gsang ba'i don //
NK115(re)001:249: byar med rtsol med ye sangs rgyas //
NK115(re)001:250: dbu ma chen po grags pa'i lam //
NK115(re)001:253: sems dpa' rdo rjes bshad par dam bcas pa /
NK115(re)001:255: tshig spyod yul ma yin pa la //
NK115(re)001:256: bdag gis sgrogs par shin tu dka' //
NK115(re)001:257: ma rtogs pa la tshig sgo nas //
NK115(re)001:258: mtshon pas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:259: ci rigs pa yi rnal 'byor sgrol //
NK115(re)001:260: zhes zhal gyis 'ches nas rigs lnga'i rgyal ba rnams
NK115(re)001:261: las rmad byung bstan pa'i snying po rtsol med rang
NK115(re)001:262: byung gi dgongs pa rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:263: a ti yo ga'i don rnams sgro 'dogs bcad cing
NK115(re)001:264: / rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i bcud blangs
NK115(re)001:265: nas sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas rnam par rgyal
NK115(re)001:266: ba'i khang bzang gi rtser lha de ba bzang skyong
NK115(re)001:267: gi bu sems lhag can zhes bya ba la /
NK115(re)001:268: rgyal thabs spyi blugs rdzogs pa'i dbang brda'i sgo nas bskur //
NK115(re)001:269: rgyud dang man ngag mang po dus matha'i skad cig
NK115(re)001:270: la rdzogs par bstan nas rgyal tshab dam par dbang
NK115(re)001:271: bskur te / rmad byung bstan pa'i snying po 'di //
NK115(re)001:272: lha gnas gsum du grags gyur nas //
NK115(re)001:273: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK115(re)001:274: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par shog /
NK115(re)001:276: bstan pa lha gnas gsum du rgyas par gyur to //
NK115(re)001:277: de nas mi yul du byung tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:278: rgya gar nub phyogs o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling du /
NK115(re)001:279: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza dang /
NK115(re)001:280: btsun mo snang gsal 'od ldan ma gnyis kyi sras
NK115(re)001:281: mo me tog gsal zhes bya ba dge slong ma'i
NK115(re)001:282: khrims rnam par dag pa dang ldan pa zhig dge
NK115(re)001:283: slong ma lnga brgya'i 'khor dang bcas nas gnas pa'i
NK115(re)001:284: tshe / phyag na rdo rje bya'i rgyal po ngang
NK115(re)001:285: pa zhig tu sprul nas lha'i bu sems lhag can
NK115(re)001:286: yi ge h'u du bsdus nas sras mo'i thugs kar
NK115(re)001:287: tshe / bstims pa na / de sbrum ma'i rnam
NK115(re)001:288: pa med par lo dus na thugs ka nas rdo
NK115(re)001:289: rje rtse dgu 'od 'bar ba zhig byung ste zhu
NK115(re)001:290: ba las khye'u chung mtshan dpes brgyan pa /
NK115(re)001:292: g.yon rin po che'i phyag shing thogs pa /
NK115(re)001:293: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:294: zhal 'don du mdzad pa zhig byung ba de la
NK115(re)001:295: thams cad dga' ba'i rab tu gyur cing phyag na
NK115(re)001:296: rdo rje bsnams pas dga' rab rdo rje zhes btags
NK115(re)001:297: / thams cad kun dgyes pas dgyes pa rdo rje /
NK115(re)001:298: bzhad pas bzhad pa rdo rjer btags la /
NK115(re)001:299: de nyid kyis rgyal srid bzung ba la phyag na
NK115(re)001:300: rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas rgyal thabs spyi
NK115(re)001:302: klong dgu bam po nyi khri la sogs pa rgyud
NK115(re)001:303: dang man ngag thams cad dus matha'i skad cig la
NK115(re)001:304: rdzogs par mdzad de bstan pa'i bdag por dbang bskur
NK115(re)001:305: zhing / dam can rnams la bstan pa'i srung mar gnyer gtad do //
NK115(re)001:306: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rjes slob dpon 'jam
NK115(re)001:307: dpal bshes gnyen la brda bstan pa tsam gyis skad
NK115(re)001:308: cig la rtogs / rgyud dang man ngag yongs su rdzogs pa gtad do //
NK115(re)001:309: des sh+r+ai sing ha la gnang nas rtogs pa mngon du gyur /
NK115(re)001:310: de nas o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa /
NK115(re)001:311: mkhas pa dz+ny+aa na s+au tra /
NK115(re)001:312: pan chen bi ma la mi tra rnams kyis zhus te /
NK115(re)001:313: de rnams kyang brda thabs bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs
NK115(re)001:314: pa klong du gyur te rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa
NK115(re)001:315: mchog la gnas par gyur pas rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud
NK115(re)001:316: pa zhes bya'o // gsum pa gang zag rna bar brgyud pa la /
NK115(re)001:317: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga rnams /
NK115(re)001:318: sras mo go ma sa las /
NK115(re)001:319: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma /
NK115(re)001:321: sangs rgyas gsang ba gsum la bshad /
NK115(re)001:322: phyi ma 'di gnyis kyis bi ma la mi tra la bshad nas rim bzhin dar zhing /
NK115(re)001:323: lung a nu yo ga rgyal po dzahns brgyud pa'i tshul 'di dang cung mi 'dra bar snang la /
NK115(re)001:324: bod du brgyud tshul yang gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye
NK115(re)001:325: shes rgya gar du byon te slob dpon gsal ba'i
NK115(re)001:326: rgyan las mdo'i dbang dang gdams ngag sogs zhus shing
NK115(re)001:327: / d+ha na rak+shi ta sogs las gtso bor gzhung
NK115(re)001:328: bshad sogs zhus te bod du byon nas gnubs yon
NK115(re)001:329: tan rgya mtsho la bshad de brgyud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:330: yang sru legs pa'i sgron me sogs nas rim gyis
NK115(re)001:331: zur gyi rigs la brgyud pa'i tshul ni rgyud dang
NK115(re)001:332: phal cher 'dra'o // de nas mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK115(re)001:333: pa thams cad bod du ji ltar dar ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:334: phal cher 'dra'o // ni / rgya gar gyi rgyal
NK115(re)001:335: po dmag brgya pa'i sras bod du 'ong ba rje
NK115(re)001:336: gnya' khri btsan po zhes grags pa byang chub sems
NK115(re)001:337: dpa' sgrib pa rnam sel gyi sprul pa de bod
NK115(re)001:338: kyi rgyal po thams cad kyi snga bar phebs pa
NK115(re)001:339: nas rgyal rabs mang zhig song ba'i tshe /
NK115(re)001:340: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i rnam 'phrul lha tho
NK115(re)001:341: tho ri snyan btsan gyi ring la dam pa chos
NK115(re)001:342: kyi dbu brnyes / de nas rgyal rabs lnga na
NK115(re)001:343: spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa srong btsan sgam po'i
NK115(re)001:344: ring la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che'i
NK115(re)001:345: kyi dbu brnyes / srol gtod / de nas rgyal
NK115(re)001:346: rabs lnga na 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa
NK115(re)001:347: khri srong lde'u btsan gyis 'phags yul gyi pan+di ta
NK115(re)001:348: brgya rtsa brgyad spyan drangs nas sprul pa'i lo pan
NK115(re)001:349: rnams kyis mdo sngags kyi chos thams cad bsgyur te
NK115(re)001:350: kyi dbu brnyes / srol gtod / / mkhan pos 'dul ba dang mdo sde'i srol bzung /
NK115(re)001:351: slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma la mi tras sngags
NK115(re)001:352: kyi srol btsugs nas rgyal ba'i mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK115(re)001:353: pa rin po che nyi ma shar ba bzhin dar
NK115(re)001:354: rgyas su mdzad pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:355: de'i dus su o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa dang /
NK115(re)001:356: pan chen bi ma la mi tra gnyis kyis thugs sras rje 'bangs grogs gsum /
NK115(re)001:357: nyang ban ting 'dzin bzang po la sogs pa snod
NK115(re)001:358: dang skal ba ldan pa rnams la shan 'byed la
NK115(re)001:359: bzla rang grol mngon sum du ston pa rdzogs chen
NK115(re)001:360: a ti yo ga la sogs pa nang rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:361: gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te rim bzhin
NK115(re)001:362: bdag cag gi bla ma rnams kyi bar du brgyud
NK115(re)001:363: pa yin la / khyad par du bstan bcos 'di
NK115(re)001:364: nyid mdzad pa po rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pa
NK115(re)001:365: pa yin la / ni / 'phags pa sems nyid
NK115(re)001:366: ngal gso dngos su dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi tshul
NK115(re)001:367: bzung nas pad+ma sam b+ha wa dang bi ma la
NK115(re)001:368: mi tra kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams la sogs
NK115(re)001:369: pa las dgongs brda' snyan brgyud kyi brgyud gsum chig
NK115(re)001:370: rdzogs su blangs te las dang skal bar ldan pa'i
NK115(re)001:371: gang zag rnams la bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi chos
NK115(re)001:372: kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK115(re)001:373: rgyas su bzhugs pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:375: lus ni gang zag lha mi yang //
NK115(re)001:376: dgongs pa dam pa sangs rgyas dngos //
NK115(re)001:378: de yang man ngag gi bstan bcos kyi gzhung 'di nyid dam pa de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:379: 'jigs med phrin las 'od zer gyis gsan zhing /
NK115(re)001:380: des rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas la gnang ste /
NK115(re)001:381: de las o rgyan 'jigs med chos kyi dbang pos gsan zhing /
NK115(re)001:382: de las bka' drin mtshungs pa med pa mtshan brjod
NK115(re)001:383: par dka' yang don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos
NK115(re)001:384: na7 o rgyan bstan 'dzin nor bus gsan te /
NK115(re)001:385: des thugs brtse ba chen pos bdag la rjes su stsal ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:386: gnyis pa lo rgyus dang ldan pa'i chos de ji ltar 'chad pa'i thabs bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:389: dpon slob gnyis kas 'chad nyan ji ltar bgyi ba'i tshul bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:390: dang po ni spyir bka' thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:391: bstan bcos thams cad rtsis mgo yan lag lnga'i sgo nas 'chad de sngar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:392: thun mong du ni spyi don gyis khog dbub /
NK115(re)001:394: tshig gi 'bru gnyer ba'i sgo nas 'chad cing der dgos pa shes par bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:395: tshig phan tshun mtshams sbyar ba dang /
NK115(re)001:396: mi 'thad par dogs pa la brgal ba'i lan ston pa dang /
NK115(re)001:397: rigs pa'i 'thad pa dang bcas pa'i sgo nas ma
NK115(re)001:398: rtogs log rtog the tshom gyi dri ma dang bral
NK115(re)001:399: bar nges pa'i shes pa yang dag pa bskyed pa'i
NK115(re)001:400: tshul du bshad par bya ba ni spyir btang ngo
NK115(re)001:401: // bye brag tu bshad pa la spyir 'jig rten
NK115(re)001:402: las 'das pa'i theg pa dam pa'i chos kyi sgo
NK115(re)001:403: thams cad theg pa rim pa dgur bsdus nas de
NK115(re)001:404: dag gi rim pa dang mthun par so so'i phun
NK115(re)001:405: sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa'i sgo nas de
NK115(re)001:406: dag re re'i lta sgom spyod 'bras kyi khyad par
NK115(re)001:408: phyi pa dang nang pa'i grub pa'i mtha' sna tshogs
NK115(re)001:409: pa so sor dbye zhing 'chad par bya ba yin
NK115(re)001:410: no // khyad par du gsang ba sngags kyi theg
NK115(re)001:411: pa mtha' drug dang tshul bzhis bcings pa'i don phyin
NK115(re)001:412: ci ma log par rang gis rtogs nas gzhan la
NK115(re)001:413: mos pa dang 'tshams par ston pa ste /
NK115(re)001:414: 'di dag ma h+aa yo ga'i 'chad thabs su gsungs
NK115(re)001:415: pa'i rgyan bdun las gsum pa dang bzhi pa yin
NK115(re)001:416: mod kyi / gsang sngags nang gi rgyud sde spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:417: der gtogs pa'i man ngag gi bstan bcos rnams kyang
NK115(re)001:418: tshul 'di dang mi 'gal bar 'chad dgos pa yin
NK115(re)001:419: no // de la mtha' drug ni gal po las /
NK115(re)001:420: rgyas bshad mtha' ni rnam pa drug /
NK115(re)001:421: drang don nges don dgongs pas bshad //
NK115(re)001:422: dgongs min sgra ni ji bzhin pa //
NK115(re)001:423: ji bzhin ma yin nyid du bshad //
NK115(re)001:425: don gyi mtha' la brten pa ni drang nges gnyis so //
NK115(re)001:426: tshig gi mtha' la brten pa ni dgongs dgongs min gnyis so //
NK115(re)001:427: gnyis ka'i mtha' la brten pa ni sgra ji bzhin yin min gnyis so //
NK115(re)001:428: de yang dang po gnyis ni rdo rje'i tshig gcig
NK115(re)001:429: gis gdul bya yang dag pa'i skal ba dngos su
NK115(re)001:430: med pa dang yod pa gnyis la don tha dad
NK115(re)001:432: bskyed rim yan lag dang bcas pa ston pa drang don dang /
NK115(re)001:433: rgyu rgyud dang rdzogs rim ston pa'i phyogs nges don te /
NK115(re)001:434: dper na rgyud kyi gzhung gcig la phyi nang gi bshad tshul tha dad du byung ba lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:436: rdo rje'i tshig tha dad pas bskyed rdzogs kyi don
NK115(re)001:437: gcig de dang 'gal ba'i tshig gi sbyor bas bcings
NK115(re)001:438: te brjod don dgongs gzhi la ltos nas go dgos
NK115(re)001:442: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK115(re)001:443: phyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du //
NK115(re)001:444: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NK115(re)001:445: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK115(re)001:446: zhes pa yum mkha' dang dga' bzhi la go dgos pa lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:447: rjod byed dngos bstan gyis brjod don dgongs gzhi la
NK115(re)001:448: ltos mi dgos par gsal bar go ba ni dgongs
NK115(re)001:449: pa can min pa'i bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:451: phyi dkyil sbyin sreg sogs cho ga rnams 'jig rten
NK115(re)001:452: dang bstan bcos la grags pa'i tshig gis gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:453: ni sgra ji bzhin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:454: thun mong ma yin pa'i spyod pa barlangasa po sogs
NK115(re)001:455: 'jig rten dang bstan bcos gzhan la ma grags pa'i
NK115(re)001:456: brdas bcings te gsungs pa ni sgra ji bzhin ma
NK115(re)001:457: yin pa ste / dper na sbyor sgrol la +aa li k+aa li zhes brjod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:458: dmar cha thabs kyis ldog pa la /
NK115(re)001:460: me tog bsdus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK115(re)001:461: bdag po'i zhal du thim par bshad //
NK115(re)001:465: tshig spyi sbas dang mthar thug yin //
NK115(re)001:466: zhes gsungs pa ltar bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:467: tshig gi don ni yi ge'i 'bru bsnon mtshams la
NK115(re)001:468: gzhal ba'i bshad pa sgra tshad kyi gzhung dang mthun
NK115(re)001:469: par 'chad pa'o // spyi'i don ni sngags lam bde zhing myur ba la ma zhugs par /
NK115(re)001:470: mdo lam bul zhing dka' thub kyi lam la zhugs
NK115(re)001:471: par 'gyod na de yang sngags kyi lam stegs yin
NK115(re)001:473: yang sngags lam gtsang sme med pa khyi phag lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:474: sbyor sgrol sogs 'tshe ba chos su smra bas mu
NK115(re)001:475: stegs kyi chos so snyam du 'gyod na mdo lam
NK115(re)001:476: du'ang gtsang smer zhen 'dzin ma spangs na mnyam pa
NK115(re)001:477: nyid kyi don mi mthong bar bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:478: dge ba'i sems kyis gang spyod kyang zhen 'dzin med
NK115(re)001:479: na bsod nams kyi tshogs su 'gyur bar gsungs te
NK115(re)001:480: ded dpon snying stobs can gyis mi nag mdung thung
NK115(re)001:481: can bsad pa la sogs pa bsod nams 'phel ba'i
NK115(re)001:482: rgyur song tshul du bshad pa ste mdo sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:483: bslab pa thun mong ba'i phyir spyi don no //
NK115(re)001:484: yang rten dang brten pa gzhal yas khang dang lhar
NK115(re)001:485: bsgom pa sogs ni bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i thun mong
NK115(re)001:486: gi bslab bya yin pa'i phyir spyi don no //
NK115(re)001:488: gzhan lus phyag rgya dang snyoms par 'jug pa'i cho ga dang /
NK115(re)001:489: rang lus rtsa rlung thig le'i byed bcings sogs sbas don du 'chad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:490: 'di spyi mthar gnyis kyi dbus su tshud pas snying
NK115(re)001:491: po lta bur gyur pa'i phyir sbas pa'o zhes kyang
NK115(re)001:492: gsungs so // mthar thug gi don ni /
NK115(re)001:493: don dam 'od gsal gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:494: bden gnyis zung 'jug gi gnas lugs rtogs pa lam
NK115(re)001:495: dang 'bras bu'i mthar thug yin tshul du 'chad pa
NK115(re)001:496: ste tshig de'i brjod bya lhag ma ma lus par
NK115(re)001:497: mur thug pas na mthar thug go //
NK115(re)001:498: de dag gang la bshad pa'i yul yang /
NK115(re)001:500: de dang thun mong ba'i dgongs min /
NK115(re)001:503: spyi'i don te bskyed rim 'khor bcas ni tshogs bshad yin la /
NK115(re)001:504: sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:508: mthar thug gi don rnams te rdzogs rim 'khor bcas ni slob bshad do //
NK115(re)001:509: thun mong ma yin pa'i dgongs min ni sbas mthar gnyis su 'dus pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:510: des na slob ma'i rgyud tshod dang bstun te 'chad tshul de lta bu'i sgo nas bshad dgos kyi /
NK115(re)001:511: gzhan du na de'i don du mi 'gyur zhing gsang
NK115(re)001:512: sgo 'chol bar 'gyur bas gar bab bab tu ci
NK115(re)001:514: gnyis pa slo mas nyan tshul la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:517: dang po kun slong la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:518: bsam pa rgya che ba byang chub sems kyi kun slong dang /
NK115(re)001:519: thabs rgya che ba gsang ba sngags kyi kun slong ngo //
NK115(re)001:520: dang po ni 'di ltar 'khor ba na rgyu ba'i
NK115(re)001:521: sems can 'di thams cad gdod nas ye sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:523: glo bur 'khrul rtog gis bsgribs nas sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyi mtha' la gcur ba 'di rnams /
NK115(re)001:524: rlabs chen po'i phrin las kyis 'khor ba ming med
NK115(re)001:525: par byas nas gdod ma'i sa la dgrol bar bya
NK115(re)001:526: ba'i phyir / myur lam zab mo gsang sngags rdo
NK115(re)001:527: rje theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas thos bsam gyis sgro
NK115(re)001:528: ba'i phyir / 'dogs bcad de / bskyed rdzogs zab
NK115(re)001:529: mo'i gnad la brten nas sngags kyi phyin drug la
NK115(re)001:530: bslab te bsgom pas nyams su blang bar bya'o snyam
NK115(re)001:531: du snying thag pa nas bsam par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:532: gnyis pa thabs rgya che ba gsang ba sngags kyii kun slong ni /
NK115(re)001:533: sngags kyi theg pa ni thabs mang zhing zab pa la sogs pa'i phyir myur ba'i lam ste /
NK115(re)001:534: de'i rtsa ba yang gnas tshul dang mthun par blo
NK115(re)001:535: zhugs nas 'dun pa bsgyur ba la thug pas na
NK115(re)001:536: / chos 'chad nyan byed pa'i gnas la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:537: ma dag pa'i snang ba 'di ltar mi lta bar
NK115(re)001:538: / / gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK115(re)001:539: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK115(re)001:540: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:541: rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud pa'i gshegs pa gshegs ma /
NK115(re)001:542: sems dpa' sems ma'i rang bzhin /
NK115(re)001:543: chos phun sum tshogs pa theg pa bla na med pa rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa /
NK115(re)001:544: dus phun sum tshogs pa rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor gsal gdab par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:545: de yang de ltar yin pa la yin par shes pa tsam las /
NK115(re)001:546: ma yin pa zhig yin par gzod gsal 'debs pa ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:547: bla ma ni sku gsum gyi bdag nyid mchog gsum rtsa ba gsum gyi ngo bor bzhugs pas /
NK115(re)001:548: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sprul pa /
NK115(re)001:549: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'byung khungs /
NK115(re)001:550: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rgyal tshab /
NK115(re)001:551: bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong gis kyang ma
NK115(re)001:552: thul ba'i snyigs ma'i sems can rnams rjes su 'dzin
NK115(re)001:553: pa'i thugs rje dang bka' drin gyi ngos nas sangs
NK115(re)001:555: yon tan gyi ngos nas sangs rgyas rnams dang mnyam pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:560: thabs de'i gdams ngag gis zin pas ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas su gdon mi za la /
NK115(re)001:561: gnas dus chos rnams kyang rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa ste /
NK115(re)001:563: phyogs bcu'i stong khams ye nas dben //
NK115(re)001:564: srid pa gsum ni sangs rgyas zhing //
NK115(re)001:565: snyigs ma nga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK115(re)001:566: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK115(re)001:567: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal //
NK115(re)001:570: sngar bshad bya'i yan lag gi skabs su bshad pa ltar spang blang ma 'dzol bar byas te /
NK115(re)001:572: rab tu dma' ba'i sa la 'dug /
NK115(re)001:573: dul ba'i dpal ni rnam par bskyed //
NK115(re)001:574: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis lta //
NK115(re)001:575: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK115(re)001:576: rab tu bsgrims te chos nyon cig /
NK115(re)001:577: ces pa la sogs pa ltar gus pa'i spyod lam dang bsam pas mnyan par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:578: gsum pa dpon slob de gnyis kas 'chad nyan ji ltar bgyi ba'i tshul ni //
NK115(re)001:579: rdo rje theg pa'i chos ni dbang thob cing rtsa
NK115(re)001:580: ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig la nyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:582: gal te byung yang phyir bcos pa'i thabs kyis dpon
NK115(re)001:583: slob gnyis ka'i rgyud rnams par dag pa zhig ma
NK115(re)001:584: byas na don dang ldan par mi 'gyur bas /
NK115(re)001:585: gzhung 'di nyid 'chad pa'i skabs su yang /
NK115(re)001:586: bla ma rnams kyi bka' srol la sngags kyi mgor
NK115(re)001:587: dri med bshags pa'i rgyud kyi le'u bcu drug pa
NK115(re)001:588: 'khor rnams kyis rjes su yi rang ba'i bshags pa
NK115(re)001:589: phul ba bde gshegs spyi bshags su grags pa de'i
NK115(re)001:590: don 'grel zhing nyin re bzhin bshags pa'i tshig de
NK115(re)001:591: dang / yi ge brgya pa ci nus su bzla
NK115(re)001:592: bar mdzad pas de bzhin du bya zhing rgyud dag
NK115(re)001:593: dang / par byas nas / sngar bshad pa'i chings
NK115(re)001:594: chen po lnga'am gsum gyis bcings te 'chad nyan bya
NK115(re)001:595: dang / par byas nas / zhing / de'i tshe
NK115(re)001:596: na'ang nyal ba dang rkang lag rkyong ba sogs lus
NK115(re)001:598: rtsed mo dang kyal ka dang ca co dang zhe sdang ba'i brgal lan dang /
NK115(re)001:599: ha cang rtog ger 'chel ba'i rtsod ngor thal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:602: ma smin pa'i skye bo'i thos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:604: 'gran sems te sgo gsum gyi skyon bcu gcig po
NK115(re)001:605: dpon slob gnyis kas spangs te bshad ma thag pa
NK115(re)001:606: ltar slob dpon smra ba'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:607: nas 'chad cing / nyan pa pos kyang bsam sbyor
NK115(re)001:608: phun sum tshogs pas legs par nyan la rjes su
NK115(re)001:610: dge ba bsngo ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK115(re)001:611: gsum pa bshad bya gzhung gi rang bzhin dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:612: mdo sngags lam gyi khyad par /
NK115(re)001:613: gsang sngags rgyud sde'i dbye ba /
NK115(re)001:614: bla na med pa'i theg pa bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:615: dang po mdo sngags lam gyi khyad par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:616: spyir rgyal bas sems can rnams kyi blo dang 'du
NK115(re)001:617: shes kyi rjes su 'gro ba'i theg pa'i rnam dbye
NK115(re)001:618: bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs pa mtha' dag
NK115(re)001:619: bsdu na gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:622: chen po la'ang rnam pa gnyis yod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:624: theg pa chen po rnam gnyis te //
NK115(re)001:625: pha rol phyin dang gsang sngags so //
NK115(re)001:627: de'i rgyu mtshan theg chen gyi gdul bya byang chub
NK115(re)001:628: semsa dapa'a de la'ang dbang po rnon po dang shin
NK115(re)001:629: tu rnon po'i rigs can gnyis yod pa'i gnyis ka'ang
NK115(re)001:630: snying rje chen po'i gzhan dbang gis bla med byang
NK115(re)001:631: chub bsgrub par mtshungs kyang sgrub tshul mtshan nyid theg
NK115(re)001:632: pa las bde gshegs snying po sa bon du yod
NK115(re)001:633: pa tsam tshogs gnyis kyi rkyen las gong 'phel du
NK115(re)001:634: song nas sangs rgyas thob par 'dod cing /
NK115(re)001:635: rgyu 'bras snga phyi 'brel bas rgyu'i theg pa zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:636: sngags su snying po de sems can thams cad la
NK115(re)001:637: rang chas su yod pa la yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:638: lhun gyis grub pa'i sbyang gzhi nyi ma lta bu
NK115(re)001:639: de nyid la / sbyang bya 'khor ba'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:640: tshogs brgyad kun gzhi dang bcas pa'i 'dus byas kyi
NK115(re)001:641: sems glo bur ba sprin dang 'dra bas bsgribs pa
NK115(re)001:642: de nyid la / nyid / sbyong byed dbang dang bskyed rdzogs kyis sbyangs pas /
NK115(re)001:643: sbyangs 'bras rang ngo'i yon tan ji bzhin pa mngon du 'gyur bar 'dod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:644: des na sngagsa kyi theg pa zhes pa'i don ni /
NK115(re)001:645: ma na yid dang tra ya skyob pa'i sgra bsdus pas man+t+ra zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:646: gang skyob na yid shes te /
NK115(re)001:647: de yang rig pa la brjod de /
NK115(re)001:649: rig pa'i ye shes la yid ces brjod pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:651: bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po'i //
NK115(re)001:653: gang las skyob na gzung 'dzin dang bcas pa'i tshogs brgyad las /
NK115(re)001:654: ji ltar skyob na bde myur gyi tshul du skyob pas na de skad ces bya'o //
NK115(re)001:655: de la 'bras bu'i theg pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK115(re)001:656: de'i don ni gzhi gtan la dbab pa'i dus su
NK115(re)001:657: mthar thug gi sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:658: kyi chos khams rgya mtsho lta bu sems nyid bde
NK115(re)001:659: gshegs snying po'i rang rtsal du rdzogs pas 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:660: gzhi la gnas par 'dod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:661: lam nyams su len pa'i dus su 'bras bu sku
NK115(re)001:662: dang ye shes kyi bzhugs tshul dang mthun pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:663: bsgoms pas 'bras bu lam du byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:664: 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'i dus su tshe lus
NK115(re)001:665: gcig gis 'bras bu mngon du byed pas 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:666: thus ka ste dper na sman thams cad kyi nus
NK115(re)001:667: pa phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa lta bu lam gyi
NK115(re)001:668: man ngag gi nus pa thams cad gcig tu 'dus
NK115(re)001:669: pa'i don gyis na de skad ces bya ba'am /
NK115(re)001:670: yang na ni mtshon byed dpe'i rdo rje dang rjes
NK115(re)001:671: su mthun pa'i chos nyid don dam pa'i rdo rje
NK115(re)001:672: bde gshegs snying po'i yin lugs bla mas ngo sprad
NK115(re)001:673: pa de nyid phar mtshan ma'i rnam rtog thams cad
NK115(re)001:674: 'joms pa la thogs pa med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:675: tshur mtshan ma'i rnam rtog thams cad kyis glags mi rnyed pas na rdo rje ste /
NK115(re)001:676: de nyid brjod bya'i gtso bor bstan pas na rdo rje'i theg pa zhes brjod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:677: yang sbyin pa lta bu spyod pa'i sgo re re
NK115(re)001:678: yang thabs du ma'i sgo nas sgrub pas thabs mang
NK115(re)001:679: ba dang / nyon mongs lnga yang lam du byed pas thabs mkhas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:680: 'dod yon lnga po spang mi dgos par lam du byed pas thabs bde ba dang /
NK115(re)001:681: skal ba dang ldan pa'i gang zag dbang po shin
NK115(re)001:682: tu rnon po zhig ma gtogs khong du mi chud
NK115(re)001:684: tshe gcig gis kyang 'bras bu 'grub pas thabs myur
NK115(re)001:685: ba'i phyir thabsa kyi theg pa zhes kyang bya la
NK115(re)001:686: / rig pa bde gshegs snying po'i chos nyid bla
NK115(re)001:687: mas ngo sprad pa de nyid mi 'bral bar 'dzin
NK115(re)001:688: pa'i rig 'dzin ni gsang sngags nyams su len pa'i
NK115(re)001:690: de dag gi nyams su blang bya'i sde snod yin
NK115(re)001:691: pas na rig pa 'dzina pa yi sde snod zhes
NK115(re)001:692: gragas shing / spyir sde snod ces pa'i don tshig
NK115(re)001:693: dang don gyi sde tshan du ma'i snod yin pas
NK115(re)001:694: de skad brjod pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:695: rgyu mtshan de rnams kyi phyir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:696: theg pa lasa khyad para du 'aphagas pa yin te
NK115(re)001:698: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK115(re)001:699: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK115(re)001:700: dbang po rnon pos dbang byas phyir //
NK115(re)001:701: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK115(re)001:703: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sgrub par don gcig na yang
NK115(re)001:704: bsgrub tshul la rmongs ma rmongs kyi khyad par yod
NK115(re)001:705: de mtshan nyid theg pa las /
NK115(re)001:706: phyi snang ba'i bden zhen ldog pa la sgyu mar
NK115(re)001:707: bsgom pa la sogs pas 'byung ba'i rig pa la
NK115(re)001:708: rmongs / nang phung po lhar ma shes pas gnas pa'i don la rmongs /
NK115(re)001:709: gsang ba rtog tshogs dang nyon mongs pa ye shes
NK115(re)001:710: su ma shes pas lam gyi rnam pa la rmongs
NK115(re)001:711: / thams cad dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med du
NK115(re)001:712: ma shes pas rtogs pa'i lta ba la rmongs pa
NK115(re)001:713: / nyid / sngags su phyi 'byung bar snang ba yum lnga /
NK115(re)001:714: nang phung por snang ba yab lnga /
NK115(re)001:715: gsang ba rtog tshogs kun byang chub sems dpa' sems ma ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK115(re)001:716: thams cad bden pa dbyer med dag mnyam chos sku chen por gtan la phab nas bsgom zhing /
NK115(re)001:717: blang dor dang 'dzin zhen med pa'i thabs mkhas kyi
NK115(re)001:718: spyod pa gong du bshad pa lta bu'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:719: 'bras bu la myur du sbyor ba'i dbang po shin
NK115(re)001:720: tu rnon po'i dbang du byas pa'i lam yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:721: phyir ro // yang rgyun chagas pa ste sems can
NK115(re)001:722: nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du yod pa'i don gyi
NK115(re)001:724: tan+t+ra zhes pa'i sgra las rgyud de /
NK115(re)001:725: de yang rgyud phyi ma las /
NK115(re)001:726: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK115(re)001:728: zhes pas rgyud ces pa ni rgyun chags pa'i don te /
NK115(re)001:729: gang zhig rtogs par bya ba gzhi'am rgyu'i rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:730: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:731: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud do //
NK115(re)001:732: de la dang po gzhi yi rgyud ni /
NK115(re)001:733: sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po gnas lugs
NK115(re)001:734: don dam pa'i ye shes rang rig pa byang chub
NK115(re)001:735: kyi sems lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod
NK115(re)001:736: yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'ching grol med par
NK115(re)001:737: sems can thams cad la ye nas gnas pa'i don
NK115(re)001:738: la bya ste / gsang snying las /
NK115(re)001:739: bcing med rnam pa grol med pa'i //
NK115(re)001:740: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK115(re)001:743: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:744: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK115(re)001:746: de la ci'i phyir gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK115(re)001:747: de nyid thabs kyi rkyen gyis ma zin na 'khor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:748: zin na myang 'das su snang bas de gnyis ka'i
NK115(re)001:749: 'byung gazhi'am rgyu lta bur gyur pas de skad ces
NK115(re)001:751: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK115(re)001:752: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:755: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK115(re)001:756: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:758: de yang tha snyad tsam du dbye na /
NK115(re)001:759: sems kyi chos nyid bde gshegs snying po ni sbyang
NK115(re)001:760: gzhi nor bu lta bu yin pas gnas lugs ngo
NK115(re)001:761: bo nyid kyi gzhi zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:762: log pa'i zhen snang yul dang bcas pa ni /
NK115(re)001:763: sbyang bya 'dam rdzab lta bu ste med snang glo
NK115(re)001:764: bur ba yin pas 'khrul pa brtags pa'i gzhi zhes
NK115(re)001:765: gsungs te / 'di 'bras bu'i nyer len gyi rgyu
NK115(re)001:766: rgyud mtshan nyid pa ma yin par shes dgos so
NK115(re)001:767: gsungs te / // gnyis pa lam gyi rgyud ni
NK115(re)001:768: gzhi de nyid glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral
NK115(re)001:769: bar byed pa'i thabs gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:771: rang bzhin yongs shes kyi don bsgom pa'i ting nge
NK115(re)001:772: 'dzin grogs spyod pa dang bcas pa la bya ste
NK115(re)001:774: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:775: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:776: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK115(re)001:777: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK115(re)001:779: de la ci'i phyir thabs sam lam gyi rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK115(re)001:780: thob bya 'bras rgyud nyid mngon du byed pa'i lhan cig byed rkyen yin pas thabs dang /
NK115(re)001:781: gang gis gang du bgrod pa'i rten yin pas lam ste /
NK115(re)001:783: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang //
NK115(re)001:784: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:785: de yang rnal 'byor bla na med pa khyad par
NK115(re)001:786: gyi lam 'di 'bras bu la nye ba'i lam rgyud
NK115(re)001:787: yin la / phyi rgyud rnams ni ring ba'i lam rgyud do //
NK115(re)001:788: lam de la rgyud ces smos pa'i don ni /
NK115(re)001:789: gzhi shes bya dang lam shes byed du dang /
NK115(re)001:790: 'bras bu thob bya dang lam thob byed du 'brel ba'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:791: lam dang po bsgrub pa nas 'bras bu'i bar du
NK115(re)001:792: bar ma chad par rgyun chags su 'byung bas na
NK115(re)001:795: gzhi'i gnas lugs la sgrib par byed pa'i dri ma
NK115(re)001:796: glo bur ba rnams lam gyis yang dag par sbyangs
NK115(re)001:797: nas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa
NK115(re)001:798: la bya ste / sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK115(re)001:800: lhun grub ji bzhin mngon byas pa'ang //
NK115(re)001:801: btags pa tsam ste gnyis pa med //
NK115(re)001:802: de phyir de la de brjod do //
NK115(re)001:804: de yang gnyis pa med ces pa /
NK115(re)001:805: gzhi 'bras ngo bo bdag gcig gis 'brel bas gzhi
NK115(re)001:806: las tha dad pa'i 'bras bu med pa'i don no
NK115(re)001:807: // de la ci'i phyir 'bras bu'i rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK115(re)001:808: bla na med pa mchog gi 'bras bu mthar thug
NK115(re)001:809: pa don du gnyer ba rnams kyi bsam pa yongs
NK115(re)001:811: nam yang rgyun mi 'chad pas rgyud du bzhag pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:812: des na spyir rgyud gsum gyi rnam gzhag de ltar
NK115(re)001:813: yin pa'i gnad kyis bye brag lam rgyud kyi dngos
NK115(re)001:814: po rnams kyang mtshan nyid theg pa las 'phags chos
NK115(re)001:815: du ma dang ldan pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:816: de la'ang nang gses kyi dbye ba byas na /
NK115(re)001:818: brjod bya don gyi rgyud gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:820: las phra mo sgrub pa'i dang /
NK115(re)001:821: thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i dang /
NK115(re)001:822: mchog dngos sgrub pa'i thabs ston pa'i sgo nas dbye ba dang /
NK115(re)001:823: rtsa ba'i rgyud dang yan lag gi rgyud kyi dbye ba dang /
NK115(re)001:824: phyi nang gi dbye ba sogs mang na yang bsdu na /
NK115(re)001:825: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi ye shes la dang /
NK115(re)001:826: gdul bya rnams kyi sems la snang ba sgrar snang ba'i dang /
NK115(re)001:827: sngar gsang ba'i bdag pos gsungs pa sogs nas smra
NK115(re)001:828: ba pos dngos su brjod pa sgrar grags pa'i dang
NK115(re)001:829: / blo gros thabs ldan gyis rgyud sde rnams yi ger btab pa sogs nas /
NK115(re)001:830: rgya bod sogs kyi yi ge'i gzugs su bkod de
NK115(re)001:831: glegs bam gyi bar du yod pa sogs la brdar
NK115(re)001:832: gyur pa'i rgyud ces brjod pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:833: phyi ma brjod bya don gyi rgyud sde la'ang dbye ba mang du snang mod /
NK115(re)001:834: don gyi snying po gzhi'i gnas lugs lta bas gtan
NK115(re)001:835: la 'bebs tshul gyis rgyu'i theg pa las khyad du
NK115(re)001:836: 'phags pa'i stobs kyis lam nyams su len tshul yang
NK115(re)001:837: spyir theg chen thams cad bsod nams dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:838: kyi tshogs gnyis la brten nas thabs shes zung 'brel
NK115(re)001:839: du bsgrub pa tsam du mtshungs na'ang /
NK115(re)001:840: gsang ba sngags kyi skabs su ni bsod nams kyi
NK115(re)001:841: tshogs bsags pa yang phung sogs kyi chos kun rdzob
NK115(re)001:842: pa rnams la ma dag pa'i mtshan mar bltas te
NK115(re)001:843: sbyin sogs la slob pa ma yin par rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:844: ye nas dag pa'i rnam pa lhar gsal ba'i bskyed
NK115(re)001:845: rima gyi ngang nas dkyil 'khor mchod pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:847: mtshan 'dzin sdom pa la sogs pa'i tshul khrims kyis
NK115(re)001:848: mtshon sngags kyi phyin drug gi spyod pa dang 'brel
NK115(re)001:849: ba'i sgo nas bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:850: ye shes kyi tshogs kyang rjes su dpag pa'i shes
NK115(re)001:851: rab kyis spros bral sogs su lta ba tsam ma
NK115(re)001:852: yin par bla ma'i man ngag gi thabs kyis ngo
NK115(re)001:853: sprad pa'i rang gnas kyi ye shes la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:854: 'jog pa'i rdzogs rima gyi sgo nas sgrub pa ste
NK115(re)001:855: / tshul de gnyis la brten nas thabas dang shesa
NK115(re)001:856: raba khyad par can zung du 'brel bas nyams su
NK115(re)001:857: / len pa la / mtshan nyid theg pa ltar
NK115(re)001:858: thabs la mi mkhas pas mgo dang yan lag gtong
NK115(re)001:859: ba sogs daka'a thuba kyi mthu yisa yun ring por
NK115(re)001:860: mi gdunga bar 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras thams cad gang
NK115(re)001:861: yang spang mi dgos par lam du byed cing /
NK115(re)001:862: mtshon rtul bos ma chod pa'i dngos po gang zhig
NK115(re)001:863: rnon pos yud tsam gyis gcod nus pa bzhin thabs
NK115(re)001:864: dman pa 'og ma'i lam gyis gdul ma nus pa'i
NK115(re)001:865: gang zag sdig pa dang sgrib pa stobs chen pos
NK115(re)001:866: non pa yang lam 'di ru 'juga tu yod pas
NK115(re)001:867: sgo yangsa shing / gang zag dabnga po shin tu
NK115(re)001:868: rnon po'i nyams su len pa'i dabnga du byas pa'i
NK115(re)001:869: lam yin pas shes rab zab mos sngags kyi lta
NK115(re)001:870: sgom spyod gsum ya ma bral bar sgra ji bzhin
NK115(re)001:871: par nyams su blang na de lta bu'i sdig pa
NK115(re)001:872: can zhig yin kyang mi gos par zung 'jug gi
NK115(re)001:873: 'bras bu mthar thug pa la tshe gcig la sogs
NK115(re)001:874: pa las mi 'gor bar sbyor bas na lam bgrod
NK115(re)001:875: pa'i brtul zhugsa te tshul gzhan las myur ba yin
NK115(re)001:876: sgo yangsa shing / no // gnyis pa gsang sngags rgyud sde'i dbye ba bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:877: spyir rgyud sde bzhir dbye ba /
NK115(re)001:878: de las phyi rgyud bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:880: dang po spyir rgyud sde bzhir dbye ba ni /
NK115(re)001:881: de yang 'di ltar gsang sngags kyi chos ni longs
NK115(re)001:882: sku'i bstan pa yin pas rgyal ba kun gyi spyi
NK115(re)001:883: gzugs rdo rje 'chang chen pos dus thog ma med
NK115(re)001:884: pa nas 'khor tshad med pa'i nang du gsungas pa'i
NK115(re)001:885: phyir sems can mtha' yas pa'i blo dang chos kyi
NK115(re)001:886: dbyings 'byams klas pa'i rjes su 'gro bas na /
NK115(re)001:887: gdul bya bye brag pa'i ngor snang ba'i sprul sku'i bstan pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:888: dus kyi thog matha'i tshad dang /
NK115(re)001:889: rgyud sde'i grangs la sogs pa mtha' gcig tu nges gzung bya rgyu med de /
NK115(re)001:890: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:891: gsang dang gsang chen shin tu gsang //
NK115(re)001:893: rjes su rnal 'byor chen po dang //
NK115(re)001:895: gsang dang gsang chen shin tu gsang //
NK115(re)001:896: rgyud rnams kun gyi spyi bo ste //
NK115(re)001:897: zhes pas shin tu rnal 'byor dang rjes su rnal 'byor la sogs pa gsal bar bstan la /
NK115(re)001:898: de bzhin du dpung bzang las /
NK115(re)001:899: lha dang lha min mi la phan gdags phyir //
NK115(re)001:900: gsang sngags rig sngags rnam pa sna tshogs dag /
NK115(re)001:901: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK115(re)001:902: rig 'dzin sde snod gsal bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK115(re)001:904: de dag kyang sde tshan du snang ba'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:905: rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyi rim pas
NK115(re)001:906: der 'bab pa'i khu rdul gnyis dang rlung gi 'du
NK115(re)001:907: ba las chos kyi rnam grangs de snyed cig gdul
NK115(re)001:908: bya'i blo la bde bar gshegs pa'i bdag rkyen las
NK115(re)001:910: bshad rgyud rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:911: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK115(re)001:912: khrag 'bab par ni shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:913: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK115(re)001:914: byang chub sems ni rab tu 'bab //
NK115(re)001:915: stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi ni //
NK115(re)001:916: rlung rgyu bar ni shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:917: zhes pa dang mthun par rgyud sde'i grangs /
NK115(re)001:918: klu sgrub zhabs kyi rim lnga'i 'grel pa las /
NK115(re)001:919: gsang sngags kyi dbye ba ni stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK115(re)001:921: de lta bu'i sngags kyi rgyud sde yod do cog thams cad /
NK115(re)001:922: 'dod yon dang nyon mongs lam du byed tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:923: gdul bya'i blo rim sogs kyis sgrub tshul gyi rnam
NK115(re)001:924: grangs dang sde tshan gyi grangs 'dzin sla ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:925: chings chen po bzhis bcings te ston pa ni /
NK115(re)001:927: gdul bya dus dang 'dul byed kyi //
NK115(re)001:928: skal pa can rnams don gyi phyir //
NK115(re)001:929: gsang sngags tshul chen rnam pa bzhi //
NK115(re)001:930: 'jig rten khams su bsgrags pa yin //
NK115(re)001:932: de yang dus dang rigs dang dbang po sogs la dgongs te gsungs pa'i dus la dgongas pa ni /
NK115(re)001:933: 'dzam bu'i gling pa rnams la sbyang gzhi 'dod chags kyi 'jug tshul bzhi rim gyis byung bas te /
NK115(re)001:934: tshe lo sa ya drug 'bum yan chad du nyon mongs mngon gyur med cing /
NK115(re)001:936: bdud rtsi'i zas te rnam pa bzhi po yod pa
NK115(re)001:937: rdzogas ldana te 'di'i dus na nyon mongs 'dod chags
NK115(re)001:938: cung zad langs kyang shas chung bas gcig la gcig
NK115(re)001:939: bltas pa tsam gyis tshim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:940: yon tan de dag las gcig nyams te gsuma ldana gyi dus na bgad pas tshim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:941: yang gcig nyams te gnyisa ldana gyi dus na phan
NK115(re)001:942: tshun reg pa dang lag pa bcangs tsam gyis tshim
NK115(re)001:944: yon tan thams cad nub ste phan tshun rtsod para
NK115(re)001:945: byed cing 'khyud sbyor gyi 'dod chags dang ldana pa
NK115(re)001:946: ste bzhi yi gnyen por gsungs pa yang /
NK115(re)001:948: rdzogs ldan dang po bya ba'i rgyud //
NK115(re)001:949: gsum ldan gnyis pa spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK115(re)001:950: gnyis ldan gsum par rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK115(re)001:951: rtsod ldan bzhi pa bla med do //
NK115(re)001:952: dus bzhi la ni dgongs nas kyang //
NK115(re)001:953: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK115(re)001:955: rigas la dgongas pa ni spyod pa'i sgo nas dbye
NK115(re)001:956: ste 'di ltar bram ze rnams gtsang sbra dang dka'
NK115(re)001:958: rje'u'i rigas rnams ni sgo gsum cha mnyam pa la gzo ba dang /
NK115(re)001:959: rgyal po'i rigs rnams rgya chen po la mos shing
NK115(re)001:960: sems kyi las gtso bor spyod pa dang ni damngas
NK115(re)001:961: rigs sama gdola pa rnams ni gtsang sbra chung zhing
NK115(re)001:962: nyon mongs pa'i brtul zhugs shas che bas de rnams
NK115(re)001:964: de ltar yang bde mchog rol pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:965: bya ba bram ze gtsang dang bstun //
NK115(re)001:966: spyod pa rje'u rigs de bas lhag /
NK115(re)001:968: gzhi rmongs gdod nas grol ba ste /
NK115(re)001:969: gzhan du su la'ang ma bstan par //
NK115(re)001:970: mdzes ma khyod la bstan pa yin //
NK115(re)001:972: dabnga po bzhir dgongsa pa ni /
NK115(re)001:973: dbang po rtul po rnams kyis sems kyi kun tu
NK115(re)001:974: brtsam pa chen po nyams 'og tu mi chud pas
NK115(re)001:975: lus ngag gi bya ba la che thang du mthong
NK115(re)001:976: ba dang / 'bring gis sems kyi brtsam pa chen
NK115(re)001:977: po yang rtogs su rung la lus ngag gi bya
NK115(re)001:978: ba dang sems kyi brtsam pa cha mnyam par blta
NK115(re)001:979: ba dang / ba dang / rnona pos sems kyi
NK115(re)001:980: brtsam pa gtso bor blta zhing lus ngag gi spyod
NK115(re)001:981: pa de'i grogs tsam du brten pa dang /
NK115(re)001:982: dbang po mchog gis sgo gsum gyi bya ba thams
NK115(re)001:983: cad la mtshan ma dang blang dor du mi blta
NK115(re)001:984: bar zung du tshud par shes pas de dag gi
NK115(re)001:985: phyir gsungs te / rdo rje gur las /
NK115(re)001:986: dman pa rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK115(re)001:987: bya min rnal 'byor de ltag la //
NK115(re)001:988: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK115(re)001:989: rnal 'byor bla med de ltag la'o //
NK115(re)001:991: de dag 'dul byed gsang sngags kyi chos ni rim
NK115(re)001:992: pa bzhin gdul bya de rnams dang mthun par ston
NK115(re)001:993: pa ste bya ba'i rgyud du 'dod chags lam du
NK115(re)001:994: byed pa'i thabs lha bri zhing bsgom pa'i tshul yang
NK115(re)001:995: / phyag na rdo rje mngon par dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:996: dbus su ni bcom ldan 'das spyan ras gzigs dbang bri /
NK115(re)001:997: de'i g.yon du na bza' dkar mo bcom ldan 'das la blta ba bri'o //
NK115(re)001:1000: dkyil 'khor gyi ni lha tshogs rnams //
NK115(re)001:1001: pho yang mo la blta ba dang //
NK115(re)001:1002: mo yang pho la blta ba bri //
NK115(re)001:1004: spyod pa yang khrus dang gtsang sbra dang /
NK115(re)001:1005: dkar gsum za ba dang gos gsum barje ba la sogs pa'i bya ba lhur len pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1006: sems kyi bsgom pa yang med pa min kyang gtso
NK115(re)001:1007: bo lus ngag gi bya ba la che thang du
NK115(re)001:1008: brtson no // spyod pa'i rgyud du chags pa lam
NK115(re)001:1009: du byed pa'i lha bri zhing bsgom pa'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:1010: brtson no // / rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK115(re)001:1011: rnam par snang mdzad rgyal po che //
NK115(re)001:1012: yid tsam 'dzum pa'i zhal du bri //
NK115(re)001:1014: de yi g.yas su lha mo ni //
NK115(re)001:1015: sangs rgyas spyan zhes bya ba ste //
NK115(re)001:1016: lha mo cung zad 'dzum pa'i zhal //
NK115(re)001:1017: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:1018: spyod pa yang sgo gsum gyi bya ba cha mnyam
NK115(re)001:1019: par byed la bsgom pa yang sems kyi brtsam pa
NK115(re)001:1020: chen po byed nus pas lus ngag gi kun spyod
NK115(re)001:1022: rnal 'byor rgyud du 'dod chags lam du byed pa'i thabs su lha bri zhing bsgom pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1024: dkyil 'khor gyi ni lha tshogs rnams /
NK115(re)001:1025: dpung pa yid tsam dam par bzhag /
NK115(re)001:1027: de yi logs la rdo rje che //
NK115(re)001:1028: mda' ni gsor ba la brtson pa //
NK115(re)001:1029: snyems pa'i phyag gis yongs 'khyud pa'i //
NK115(re)001:1030: chu srin rgyal mtshan sgreng dang bcas //
NK115(re)001:1031: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas lha thams cad phyag rgya sbrel bar 'byung ngo //
NK115(re)001:1032: spyod pa yang lus ngag gi bya ba grogs tsam du ston la /
NK115(re)001:1033: bsgom pa ni lha'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK115(re)001:1034: mtshan med pa'i don bsgom pa lhur len pas gtso bor byed do //
NK115(re)001:1035: bla na med pa'i rgyud sde rnams las ni /
NK115(re)001:1036: chags pa lam du byed pa'i thabs shes kyi lha rnams zung 'brel te /
NK115(re)001:1038: dbang po gnyis kyi sbyor ba yi //
NK115(re)001:1039: dngos po thams cad brtag par bya //
NK115(re)001:1042: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs te //
NK115(re)001:1045: spyod pa yang gtsang sme dang nyon mongs sogs la blang dor med par spyod cing /
NK115(re)001:1046: bsgom pa ni mnyam nyid blang dor dang bral zhing
NK115(re)001:1047: thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i don la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:1049: gzhan yang lha bzhi'i rjes su 'jug pa'i phyin ci log bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:1050: grub mtha' smra ba bzhi rjes su bzung ba'i phyir rgyud sde bzhir phye ba'ang /
NK115(re)001:1051: mdo sngags gnyis mthar thug dgongs pa gcig tu 'bab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1052: sangs rgyas rnams ni thabs la mkhas shing thugs rje
NK115(re)001:1053: dang ldan pas gdul byar ma gyur pa'ang med la
NK115(re)001:1054: / 'dul tshul yang rang rang gi mos pa dang mthun par ston pas mi 'thad pa med do //
NK115(re)001:1056: gti mug can tshangs pa gtsang sbra chos su smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1057: zhe sdang can khyab 'jug 'tshe ba chos su smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1058: nga rgyal can brgya byin rigs dang 'byor bas rgyags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1059: chags pa can dbang phyug 'dod chags chos su smra ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:1060: gnyis pa phyi rgyud sde gsum bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:1063: dang po spyir bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1064: de ltar gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde bzhi po de
NK115(re)001:1065: dag gi nang nas dang po bya spyod rnal 'byor
NK115(re)001:1066: gyi rgyud gsuma la ni gsang sngags phyi pa zhes
NK115(re)001:1067: bya ste / thub pa chags bral gyi rnam pasa
NK115(re)001:1068: dngosa su gsungas pa'i matshana nyid theg pa dang gatsanga
NK115(re)001:1070: nyes spyod sdoma pa'i tshul gyi kun tu spyod pa
NK115(re)001:1071: phala chera mtshungas pa'i phyir dka' thub rig byed kyi
NK115(re)001:1072: theg pa'am / thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK115(re)001:1073: des na 'di dag gi nyams len thabs shes gnyis
NK115(re)001:1074: ka'i sgo nas mtshan nyid theg pa las khyad par
NK115(re)001:1075: du 'phags na'ang spyir theg pa chen po'i mdo sngags
NK115(re)001:1076: kyi nyams su blang bya thams cad snying rje dang
NK115(re)001:1077: stong nyid zung du 'jug pa'i lam du gcig cing
NK115(re)001:1078: / nyon mongs dang kha na ma tho ba rang
NK115(re)001:1079: mtshan pas mi gos par byed pa la mtshungs pas
NK115(re)001:1080: thun mong gi theg pa'i nyams len dang sdom pas
NK115(re)001:1081: rgyud sbyang zhing byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems
NK115(re)001:1082: kyis gzhi bzung ba zhig med na rang gar sngags
NK115(re)001:1083: lam du zhugs pa tsam gyis lam gong ma'i khyad
NK115(re)001:1084: chos rgyud la mi 'byung bar ma zad rgyud chud
NK115(re)001:1086: sngags phyi pa 'di dag gis ni sngar bshad pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:1087: rtsoda pa'i dusa kyi dbang po gnyis sbyor dang 'agla
NK115(re)001:1088: ba'i bltas bgad lag bcangs kyis tshim pa'i 'doda chagsa
NK115(re)001:1089: kyi kun spyod lam du byed pas na lha yanga
NK115(re)001:1090: de dang mthun par bri ba dang bsgom pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:1091: ston gyi yab yum zung 'brela gyi tshul du ston
NK115(re)001:1092: pa mina la / dkar gsum gyi zas dang /
NK115(re)001:1093: ras gos la sogs pa'i gtsang zhing gsar par gyur
NK115(re)001:1094: pa'i gos dang longs spyod rnams bsten par bya ba
NK115(re)001:1095: la sha lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:1096: zhing lpags dang rus rgyan sogs la longas mi spyod do //
NK115(re)001:1097: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:1098: bya spyod kyi khyad par bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:1102: dang po bya spyod kyi khyad par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1103: de la spyir sngags kyi dbye ba byas na ni /
NK115(re)001:1109: gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo gsum du gnas pa'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:1110: dgongs pa grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:1111: gsang sngags kun gyi dbye ba ni //
NK115(re)001:1112: rnam pa gsum du shes bya ste //
NK115(re)001:1113: rig sngags thabs kyi ngo bo yin //
NK115(re)001:1114: gzugs sngags shes rab ngo bo yin //
NK115(re)001:1115: gsang sngags gnyis med ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:1116: zhes pas sngags phyii pa ni thabs shes rim can
NK115(re)001:1117: du bsgom pas bskyed rdzogs tsam po ba nyid yin
NK115(re)001:1118: la / 'di la 'ga' zhig gis thabs kyi rnal
NK115(re)001:1119: 'byor dang shes rab kyi rnal 'byor tsam las bskyed
NK115(re)001:1120: rdzogs kyi tha snyad mi btags gsungs /
NK115(re)001:1121: de'ang bya ba dang ni spyod pa'i rgyud du ni /
NK115(re)001:1122: thabs kyi cha lhar shar ba semas dapa'a dang /
NK115(re)001:1123: shes rab kyi cha lhar shar ba semas ma dang /
NK115(re)001:1124: shes rab dang ye shes 'brel ba'i ngo bo lhar shar ba riga sngagas kyi lha dang /
NK115(re)001:1125: shes rab dang dran pa 'brel ba'i ngo bo lhar shar ba gzungas sngagas kyi lha ste /
NK115(re)001:1126: de bsgrub pa'i tshul bya ba'i rgyud las lha ye
NK115(re)001:1127: shes pa rje bo dang bdag khola po'i tshul gyis
NK115(re)001:1128: dang / spyod rgyud pasa lha ye shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1129: bdag dam tshig pa gnyis mchog dman med par spuna
NK115(re)001:1130: dang grogas po'i tshul du bltas te sgrub par byed
NK115(re)001:1131: do // gnyis pa bya rgyud bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1132: de la bya ba'i rgyud kyi lam ni dpung bzang
NK115(re)001:1133: gi 'grel par spyod pa'i sgo bzhir bsdus te 'jug
NK115(re)001:1134: pa'i spyod pa dbang gis snod rung du byed pa
NK115(re)001:1135: / sbyor ba'i spyod pa rigs gsum gyi lha bsnyen pa /
NK115(re)001:1136: sgrub pa'i spyod pa rdzas dang cha rkyen 'dzom pas bzlas brjod la brtson pa /
NK115(re)001:1137: grub pa'i spyod pa lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i
NK115(re)001:1138: rig 'dzin nam mkha' spyod grub nas mthar 'bras la
NK115(re)001:1139: sbyor bar bshad pa'i spyod pa bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:1140: dang po 'jug pa'i spyod pa dbang ni 'og tu dbang gi skabs su 'chad par 'gyur la /
NK115(re)001:1141: gnyis pa sbyor ba'i spyod pa rigs gsum gyi lha bskyed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1142: bya bas rje bo dang khola po'i rnama para bsgrub
NK115(re)001:1143: pa yin par bshad pa de yin pas de la'ang
NK115(re)001:1144: / badga lhar bskyed pa meda para ranga nyid damna
NK115(re)001:1145: para bltas te tha mal ba'i tshul du bazhaga pa
NK115(re)001:1146: la ni bya rgyud tsam po ba'am rang rgyud pa
NK115(re)001:1147: / zhes bya la / bya rgyud la lara bdag
NK115(re)001:1148: lhar bskyed pa yoda de de la ni bya rgyud
NK115(re)001:1149: khyad par ba zhes zer zhing /
NK115(re)001:1150: 'on kyang gtso bora mduna bskyed byas nas de la dngos grub zhu ba'i tshul du ston to //
NK115(re)001:1152: bya ba'i rgyud la bdag bskyed med //
NK115(re)001:1153: bris sku bkod nas gsol ba 'debs //
NK115(re)001:1154: bdag bskyed sgrub thabs yod pa ni //
NK115(re)001:1156: de yi lugs su byas pa yin //
NK115(re)001:1158: thams cad kyis bya rgyud dngos gnas par bzhed pa /
NK115(re)001:1159: lag na rdo rje mngon par dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:1161: 'dug kyang rung lha'i snyems pa dang ma bral na dngos grub thob par 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:1163: bya rgyud 'ba' zhig tu 'dod pa gar mkhan mchog gi brtag pa phyi ma las /
NK115(re)001:1164: bdag nyid phyag rdor du bskyed par gsungs pas bya
NK115(re)001:1165: rgyud yin tshad la bdag bskyed med pa min no
NK115(re)001:1166: gsungs / des na bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa'i tshul ni de kho na nyid bzhi'i sgo nas te /
NK115(re)001:1167: de la dang po bdag gi de kho na nyid
NK115(re)001:1168: ni rgyud 'di'i lta ba'i ngang la 'jog pa ste
NK115(re)001:1169: / de yang chos nyid dag pa'i lha zhes /
NK115(re)001:1170: sems nyid don dam stong gsal gyi /
NK115(re)001:1171: ye shes yod med snang stong gi mtha' bzhi dang
NK115(re)001:1172: bral ba'i chos nyid du rtogs nas kun rdzob kyi
NK115(re)001:1173: chos thams cad lhar bsgom na stong nyid yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:1174: gnas kyis lcags khams la gser 'gyur gyi rtsis thebs
NK115(re)001:1175: pa bzhin rten 'brel gyi snang cha thams cad mthar
NK115(re)001:1176: thug sangs rgyas pa'i tshe lhar yongs su dag par
NK115(re)001:1177: 'dod do // gnyis pa lha'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK115(re)001:1179: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK115(re)001:1180: phyag rgya mtshan ma lha drug go //
NK115(re)001:1182: dang po stong pa'i lha ni lta ba ste bdag gi de kho na nyid bsgom pa'o /
NK115(re)001:1183: gnyis pa yi ge'i lha ni /
NK115(re)001:1184: stong nyid de kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1186: zla dkyil de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra sgrogs pa 'god pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1187: bzhi pa gzugs kyi lha ni /
NK115(re)001:1188: zla dkyil sngags phreng dang bcas pa las 'od zer
NK115(re)001:1189: spros bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub ste zla
NK115(re)001:1190: ba sngags phreng dang bcas pa yongs su gyur pa
NK115(re)001:1191: las rigs gsum gyi lha de dang de'i gzugs su
NK115(re)001:1192: sgom pa'o // lnga pa phyag rgya'i lha ni de
NK115(re)001:1193: la rigs gang yin gyi lha de'i dam rgyas 'debs
NK115(re)001:1194: sgom pa'o // pa'o // drug pa mtshan ma'i lha
NK115(re)001:1195: ni spyod lam kun tu lha de'i mtshan ma dang
NK115(re)001:1196: sgom pa'o // pa'o // mi 'bral ba'o // de
NK115(re)001:1197: nas rang gi mdun du yang dag smon lam gyi
NK115(re)001:1198: stobs las byung ba'i zhing khams pho brang dang bcas
NK115(re)001:1199: gsal btab pa'i nang du ye shes kyi lha spyan
NK115(re)001:1200: drangs pa bdag lhar bskyed pa la mi bstim par
NK115(re)001:1201: pho brang der bzhugs su gsol ba rje dang /
NK115(re)001:1202: de nyid lhar bskyed pa bran gyi tshul du bltas te mchod bstod dang rgyun bshags bya'o //
NK115(re)001:1203: rgyud sde la lar ye shes pa bstim par bshad
NK115(re)001:1204: de de'i dgongs pa klu sgrub kyis phyag stong spyan
NK115(re)001:1205: stong gi gzungs kyi sgrub thabs las bdag bskyed la
NK115(re)001:1206: ye shes pa gzhug pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1207: dbang bskur ba dang bcas pa gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:1208: gsum pa sgrub pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1209: de kho na nyid phyi ma gnyis po yin te /
NK115(re)001:1210: de yang gsum pa bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK115(re)001:1212: sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol //
NK115(re)001:1214: gzhi ni bdag mdun lhar bsam pa /
NK115(re)001:1215: sems ni de dag gi thugs kar zla dkyil bsam pa /
NK115(re)001:1216: sgra ni de'i steng du sngags phreng rang sgra sgrogs par bsam la bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya'o //
NK115(re)001:1217: bzhi pa bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK115(re)001:1219: gsang sngags mer gnas dngos grub ster //
NK115(re)001:1220: sgrar gnas rnal 'byor ster bar dran //
NK115(re)001:1221: sgras mthas thar pa ster bar byed //
NK115(re)001:1223: rang nyid lhar gsal ba'i snying gar me 'bar ba'i
NK115(re)001:1224: nang du zla ba la sngags phreng bkod nas srog
NK115(re)001:1225: bsdam pa'i sbyor bas bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1226: de ni las bzhi 'grub pa'i gazhi'o //
NK115(re)001:1227: sgrar gnas ni de las sngags kyi yi ge rnams rang sgra dril bu'i sgra ltar bsam pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1228: de ni rnal 'byor zhes pa zhi gnas skye ba'i rten yin no //
NK115(re)001:1229: sgra mthas thar pa ster ba ni /
NK115(re)001:1230: sgra yi rgyun je phrar song nas mi dmigs par 'jog pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1231: 'dis ni thar pa ster ba ste lhag mthong khyad par can rgyud la bskyed par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1232: de ltar nang gi sgom pa dang phyi yi bya
NK115(re)001:1233: ba khrusa dang gatsanga sbra la gtso bor brten pas
NK115(re)001:1234: bdag mdun mchoga damna gyi tshul du bsgrubsa pa ste
NK115(re)001:1235: / khrus dang gtsang sbra byed tshul yang khrus gsum byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1236: gos gsum barje bar gsungs te phyi'i khrus yan lag lnga khrus /
NK115(re)001:1237: nang gi khrus rtsa ltung dag par byed pa /
NK115(re)001:1238: gsang ba'i khrus mtshan rtog dag par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1239: phyi'i gos gsar pa gyon pa /
NK115(re)001:1240: nang gi gos sdom pa bsrung ba /
NK115(re)001:1241: gsang ba'i gos lha bsgom pa ste /
NK115(re)001:1242: de ltar na nang gi gtsang sbra ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:1243: gyi grogs su phyi'i dka' thub sogs 'gro ba'i thabs
NK115(re)001:1245: de ltar byed na smyung gnas med //
NK115(re)001:1246: bdag nyid lha ru bskyed pa la //
NK115(re)001:1247: mchod na bsod nams brnyas na sdig /
NK115(re)001:1248: gal te smyung gnas byed 'dod na //
NK115(re)001:1249: rang nyid tha mal nga rgyal gyis //
NK115(re)001:1251: rang gi bla ma rnams kyis lhar bskyed nas smyung gnas byed pa sogs dgag mi nus gsungs /
NK115(re)001:1252: de yang yin te don gyi gnas tshul las phyin
NK115(re)001:1253: ci log gi blos brnyas sems med na 'gal ba
NK115(re)001:1254: med de / gal te yod na bskyed rim pa'i
NK115(re)001:1255: lam pas sdig bshags sogs kyang byed par mi 'os
NK115(re)001:1256: med de / so // de yang bdag nyid chen
NK115(re)001:1257: po skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi gsung don dgongs
NK115(re)001:1259: mi 'thad pa'i phyogs su sems pa tsam yang mi phod mod /
NK115(re)001:1260: 'on kyang gsar rnying gi smyung gnas kyi cho ga
NK115(re)001:1261: du ma bdag bskyed can yin pas gzhan dag gi
NK115(re)001:1262: the tshom bsal ba'i phyir de ltar bris pa yin
NK115(re)001:1263: no // bzhi pa grub pa'i spyod pa ni mkha'
NK115(re)001:1264: spyod kyi rig 'dzin grub pa'i rten de la sngags
NK115(re)001:1265: kyi phyin drug gi spyod pa spyad nasa mthar thug
NK115(re)001:1266: gi 'bras bu mchog gi dngosa grub lha'i sku gsung
NK115(re)001:1267: thugs dang mnyam par sbyor bas rigs gsum rdo rje
NK115(re)001:1268: 'dzin pa'i go 'phang mngon du byed par 'doda pa
NK115(re)001:1269: no // ste / he ru ka gal po las /
NK115(re)001:1270: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas pa //
NK115(re)001:1273: de yang rig 'dzin grub pa'i tshes bskal ba rer gnas pas 'di'i mi tshe bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:1274: bya rgyud rang gzhung nas bshad pa'i bskal chen brgyad
NK115(re)001:1275: na 'bras bu thob par bshad pa sbyor shes par
NK115(re)001:1276: bya'o // gsum pa spyod rgyud bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1277: bya ba'i rgyud las bshad pa'i khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK115(re)001:1278: la sogs pa'i thabsa dang nanga gi lta ba dang
NK115(re)001:1279: sgom pa'i rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud ltar byas nas
NK115(re)001:1280: de gnyis la cha mnyam par spyod pasa spyod pa'i
NK115(re)001:1281: rgyud du gragsa pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:1283: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK115(re)001:1284: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK115(re)001:1285: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1286: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK115(re)001:1288: dka' ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK115(re)001:1289: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1290: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK115(re)001:1295: grub pa'i spyod pa gsum las /
NK115(re)001:1296: dang po 'jug pa'i spyod pa la phyi nang gnyis
NK115(re)001:1297: las phyi 'jug ni dbang gi snod rung du byed
NK115(re)001:1298: pa ste 'chad par 'gyur ba ltar la /
NK115(re)001:1299: nang 'jug la mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:1300: dang po mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor sgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1302: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK115(re)001:1303: de bzhin gzhi las gzhir gyur nyid //
NK115(re)001:1304: shin tu bsdams pa'i yid las ni //
NK115(re)001:1306: zhes pa ltar bdag gnas rnal 'byor bsrung ba sogs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK115(re)001:1307: yi ge dang po don dam byang chub kyi sems
NK115(re)001:1308: stong nyid kyi ngang las de'i snang cha zla dkyil
NK115(re)001:1310: yi ge gnyis pa de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra sgrogs pa /
NK115(re)001:1311: de thams cad yongs su gyur pa las gzhi dang
NK115(re)001:1312: po ranga nyida dam tshiga semsa dpa'i lhar bskyed pa
NK115(re)001:1313: la sngags rgya la sogs pas byin gyis brlab /
NK115(re)001:1314: de nas gzhi gnyis pa rang gi mduna du bskyed
NK115(re)001:1315: cing bzhugas pa'i ye shesa kyi lha'i thugs kar zla
NK115(re)001:1316: dkyil la sngags phreng bkod nas srog bsdam zhig rtse
NK115(re)001:1317: gcig pa'i sbyor bas ting nge 'dzin brtan par byed
NK115(re)001:1318: de / de yang bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK115(re)001:1319: la lta ba je bzang du song bas dam ye
NK115(re)001:1320: gnyis la dman mchog med par spun dang grogs ltara
NK115(re)001:1321: bltas te dngosa grub len par byed pa yin no
NK115(re)001:1322: de / // 'di la'ang ye shes pa 'jug pa yod med kyi phyogs gnyis yod do //
NK115(re)001:1323: gnyis pa mtshan ma med pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK115(re)001:1324: phung sogs kyi chos thams cad la rnam par dpyad pas skye med du rtogs pa 'jug pa'i sems /
NK115(re)001:1325: de mi rtog pa'i ngo bor mngon du gyur pa gnas pa'i sems /
NK115(re)001:1326: de ltar ma rtogs pa la snying rje chen pos rjes su 'jug pa ldang ba'i sems te /
NK115(re)001:1327: de ltar 'jug gnas ldang gsum gyis khyad par du
NK115(re)001:1328: byas pa'i don dam byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa'o
NK115(re)001:1329: // gnyis pa sbyor ba'i spyod pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:1330: phyi ni bzlas brjod yan lag bzhi ldan gyi sgo
NK115(re)001:1331: nas mtshan ma'am grangs kyi bsnyen pa byed pa yin
NK115(re)001:1333: bdag mdun lhar gsal ba yan lag dang po dang gnyis pa /
NK115(re)001:1334: ye shes pa'i thugs kar zla dkyil bsgom pa byang chub sems kyi yan lag /
NK115(re)001:1335: de la sngags phreng bkod pa sgra'i yan lag ste bzhi'o //
NK115(re)001:1337: rang nyid dam tshig sems dpa' lhar gsal ba'i thugs
NK115(re)001:1338: kar ting 'dzin sems dpa' zla ba khong stong gi
NK115(re)001:1339: nang du ye shes sems dpa' gsal ba'i thugs kar
NK115(re)001:1340: sngags phreng bkod de bzlas pa byed do //
NK115(re)001:1341: gsum pa grub pa'i spyod pa ni thun mong ba
NK115(re)001:1342: spyod pa mthar phyin nas rdzas sngags la brten pa'i
NK115(re)001:1344: thun mong ma yin pa 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor la
NK115(re)001:1345: brten nas rlung gi sbyor ba bsgoms pa las rdzu
NK115(re)001:1346: 'phrul dang mngon shes bsgrubs te rig pa 'dzin pa'i
NK115(re)001:1347: nang du 'gro ba sogs gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:1348: 'grub la / 'di'i rlung gi rnal 'byor bla med
NK115(re)001:1349: kyi rgyud nas bshad pa dang mi 'dra ste thun
NK115(re)001:1350: mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i rgyu tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:1351: rten de la brten nas sngags kyi spyod pa spyad
NK115(re)001:1352: pas mi tshe lnga'am ji ltar bul yang bskal pa
NK115(re)001:1353: gsum mam gcig gis rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK115(re)001:1354: sa mngon du byed par 'dod de /
NK115(re)001:1355: rigs bzhi ni sngar gyi sku gsung thugs kyi rigs gsum gyi steng rin chen rigs bsnan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:1356: de yang rigs gsum gyi tshe yon tan dang las ni rigs gsum po der bsdu zhing /
NK115(re)001:1357: 'dir yang las rigs yon tan du bsdus pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:1358: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kun la khyab
NK115(re)001:1359: byed yin pas logs su ma bgrangs pas bzhir 'dod
NK115(re)001:1360: de don la ni lnga ga yod par gsungs so
NK115(re)001:1361: // bzhi pa rnal 'byor rgyud bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1362: rnala 'byor gyi rgyud kyi 'jug sgo'i dbang ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ba ltar la /
NK115(re)001:1363: lta ba ni don dam par chos thams cad spros
NK115(re)001:1364: pa'i mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:1365: shes kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK115(re)001:1367: de yang chos thams cad mtshan ma dang bral ba'i
NK115(re)001:1368: sems kyi snang ba yin pas ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK115(re)001:1369: dbang bsgyur na ji ltar bsgom pa'i lha mngon du
NK115(re)001:1370: 'grub rung bas mthong lam thob pa'i tshe lha'i sku
NK115(re)001:1371: gsung thugs phrin las kyi ngo bor rang gi sgo
NK115(re)001:1372: gsum bya ba dang bcas pa dag par 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:1374: lam bsgom pas nyams su len tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:1375: thabs kyi rnal 'byor dang shes rab kyi rnal 'byor gnyis kyi sgo nas te /
NK115(re)001:1376: dang po la'ang rags pa lha la dmigs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1377: phra ba phyag mtshan la dmigs pa gnyis yod cing /
NK115(re)001:1378: lha'i rnal 'byor dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i skabs su gzhal
NK115(re)001:1379: yas khang gi gru chad man chad kyi khyams dang
NK115(re)001:1380: sgo nas phyi rol gyi srung ba'i bar phal cher
NK115(re)001:1381: la bkoda pa chena po rang snang longas spyod rdzogas
NK115(re)001:1382: pa'i zhing dang gzhal yas khang ltar bstan na yanga
NK115(re)001:1383: / nang gi lha yi gdan 'khor lo sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:1384: gzhal yas khang gi dbus phyur bu'i rnam pa dang
NK115(re)001:1385: rtse mo dang rgyan gyi rnam grangs rnams la mi
NK115(re)001:1386: 'dra ba'i khyad par du ma yod la /
NK115(re)001:1387: lha rnams kyang sngar bshad pa ltar yab yum zunga 'brela ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:1388: lha bskyed nas de la sems gtad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1389: rdzogas rim mi rtog pa bsgom pa'i thabas kyi rnal
NK115(re)001:1390: 'byor dang shesa raba kyi rnal 'byor gnyis rima cana
NK115(re)001:1391: du bsgom pas so so ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:1393: lhun grub mnyam par ma rtogs pas //
NK115(re)001:1394: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK115(re)001:1395: thabs shes rim can du bsgoms pas //
NK115(re)001:1396: bskyed rdzogs so so ba nyid de //
NK115(re)001:1398: lam bsgrub pa'i gang zag ni /
NK115(re)001:1399: byang chub kyi sems tshul bzhin rgyud la bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1400: the tshom dang yid gnyis med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1401: bde bar gshegs pa dang bla ma'i bka' las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1402: bla ma dang gsang sngags la dad pa shin tu
NK115(re)001:1403: brtan pa ste 'di dag ni rgyud sde gong 'og
NK115(re)001:1404: gang nyams su len na'ang med du mi rung ngo
NK115(re)001:1405: // de ltar yang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK115(re)001:1406: byang chub sems ni ma bskyed dang /
NK115(re)001:1407: the tshon ldan pa nyid dang ni //
NK115(re)001:1408: bka' bzhin du ni mi byed dang //
NK115(re)001:1411: gang zag des ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul yang nang gi rnala 'byor bsgom pa gtso bor spyod cing /
