NK115(re)001:1412: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs lusa ngaga gi bya ba rnams grogsa su ston pa yin la //
NK115(re)001:1413: de yang thabs kyi rnal 'byor ni mngon byang lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:1414: cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas bsgom ste /
NK115(re)001:1415: dang po mngon byang lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:1416: he ru ka gal po las /
NK115(re)001:1417: mi rtog zla ba rdo rje gzugs //
NK115(re)001:1418: spro bsdu bsgoms pas sku ru gsal //
NK115(re)001:1420: spyir lha'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa la srid pa bskyed
NK115(re)001:1421: pa'i rim pa kun nas nyon mongs pa'i phyogs dang
NK115(re)001:1422: bstun nas bsgom pa rgyud sde 'og ma gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:1423: lugs ma yin kyang rnam byang gi phyogs dang bstun
NK115(re)001:1424: nas mngon byang lnga yi rim pas bsgom pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:1425: / dang po rnam par mi rtog pa'i stong nyid bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1426: gnyis pa stong nyid kyi snang cha zla ba tshes pa lta bur bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1427: gsum pa de nyid nya ba lta bur bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1428: bzhi pa de'i steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag mtshan bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1429: lnga pa de las 'od zer spro bsdu byas te
NK115(re)001:1430: yongs su gyur pa las rigs kyi lha gang yin
NK115(re)001:1433: zhing dang gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'grub pa'i rgyu
NK115(re)001:1434: gdan pad zla la mngon par byang chub pa dang
NK115(re)001:1435: / chos phun sum tshogs pa 'grub pa'i rgyu gsung yig 'bru la mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1436: dus phun sum tshogs pa brtag pa bsam mi khyab
NK115(re)001:1437: par gnas pa'i rgyu thugs phyag mtshan la mngon par
NK115(re)001:1439: 'khor dang ston pa phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu sku
NK115(re)001:1440: yongs rdzogs dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:1441: la mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1442: sku'i ngo bo'am ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu
NK115(re)001:1443: lha ye shes sems dpa' la mngon par byang chub
NK115(re)001:1444: pa ste mngon byang lnga'i sgo nas bskyed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1445: gnyis pa cho 'phrul bzhi yang de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:1446: ting 'dzin byin rlabs dbang bskur mchod //
NK115(re)001:1447: ces pas ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul ni gtso 'khor yongs rdzogs bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1448: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK115(re)001:1449: lha de dag rang rang gi rigs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1450: dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni rang rigs kyi sku
NK115(re)001:1451: dang ye shes gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK115(re)001:1453: mchod pa'i cho 'phrul ni de dag la phyag dang mchod pa bstod pa rnams bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:1454: de ltar bdag lhar bskyed pa la dbyings nas ye
NK115(re)001:1455: shesa pa dguga cing bdag dang lha don la mnyam
NK115(re)001:1456: par shes pa'i nges shes kyis chu la chu bzhag
NK115(re)001:1457: pa bzhin dbyer med du bstimsa nas /
NK115(re)001:1458: sku yi rnam pa phyag rgya chen po /
NK115(re)001:1459: gsung gi rnam pa chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:1460: thugs kyi rnam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:1461: 'od zer 'phro 'du la sogs pas las bsgrub pa
NK115(re)001:1462: las kyi phyag rgya ste bzhi yisa rang gi sgo
NK115(re)001:1463: gsum bya ba dang bcas pa lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK115(re)001:1464: phrin las dang bcas pa'i ngo bor rgyas btab ste
NK115(re)001:1466: dama tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis ro gciga
NK115(re)001:1467: pa'i nganga nasa bzlas pa la brtson zhing dngos grub
NK115(re)001:1468: rnam pa gnyis len pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:1469: de ltar bsgrub cing dngosa grub blang ba'i bzlas brjod
NK115(re)001:1470: pa'i matha'a la gshegas gsola bya ba ste 'di'i cho
NK115(re)001:1471: ga la gzhi dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog dang /
NK115(re)001:1472: de la brten nas las rgyal mchog sgrub pa'i rim
NK115(re)001:1473: pas 'dod pa'i dngos grub ma grub kyi bar du
NK115(re)001:1474: ting nge 'dzin la rnal 'byor du bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:1475: phra ba phyag mtshan la dmigs pa ni rdo rje
NK115(re)001:1476: la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan shin tu phra ba sna
NK115(re)001:1477: rtse sogs su bsgoms nas mthar mi rtog par 'jog
NK115(re)001:1478: pa'o // gnyis pa shes rab kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK115(re)001:1479: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ye shes dang kun
NK115(re)001:1480: rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lha snang gnyis ka gnyis
NK115(re)001:1481: su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngang la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:1483: de ltar bsgoms shing bsgrubs pas 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub mkha' la spyod pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:1484: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub mi tshe gsum
NK115(re)001:1485: na sngar gyi rigs bzhi'i steng du las rigs bsnan
NK115(re)001:1486: pa'i rigs lnga stug po bkod par mngon byang lnga'i
NK115(re)001:1487: thabs kyis ye shes lnga'i ngo bor 'tshang rgya bar
NK115(re)001:1489: de skad du'ang kun byed las /
NK115(re)001:1490: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK115(re)001:1491: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK115(re)001:1493: gsum pa nang rgyud bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:1497: lta sgom spyod pa gsum po phyi rgyud las khyad
NK115(re)001:1498: par 'phags shing 'di dag gi gong na rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:1499: gzhan med pas bla na meda pa /
NK115(re)001:1500: thabs shes sam bskyed rdzogs dbyer med du nyams su
NK115(re)001:1501: len pa'i phyir gsang sngags nanga pa zhes bya la
NK115(re)001:1502: / nang rgyud sde gsum po 'dir ni bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:1503: gnyis med kyi lam ston yang gtso che chung tsam
NK115(re)001:1504: du bskyed pa'i rim pa rgya cher ston zhing lha'i
NK115(re)001:1505: rnam pa pho shas che la /
NK115(re)001:1506: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan mang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1507: rdzogsa pa'i rim pa tshang bar ston zhing /
NK115(re)001:1508: lha'i rnam pa mo shas che la gcer bu rus
NK115(re)001:1509: pa'i rgyan dang g.yang gzhi dang thal chen gyi byugs
NK115(re)001:1511: yang thabs shes zung du 'jug pa 'od gsal ba'i
NK115(re)001:1512: ye shes gsal bar ston pa ste de gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:1513: dbang lasa tha snyad kyi dbye ba pha rgyud dang
NK115(re)001:1514: ma rgyud dang gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum du rnam
NK115(re)001:1516: pha ma gnyis po'i 'jog mtshams de tsam du'ang ma nges te /
NK115(re)001:1517: gtso bo go 'pho la gtso mo mi 'pho ba thabs pha'i rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:1518: gtso mo go 'pho la gtso bo mi 'pho ba shes rab ma'i rgyud de /
NK115(re)001:1520: me tog gang la phog pa'i rigs de gtso bor
NK115(re)001:1521: byas na 'grub thag nye ba'i phyir rigs gang gtso
NK115(re)001:1522: bor byed dgos pa'i rigs kyi yab de'i gtso bo
NK115(re)001:1523: barje zhing yum rang gi go sa nas mi 'pho
NK115(re)001:1524: ba dang de las ldog pa'i khyad par ro //
NK115(re)001:1525: nang rgyud kyi lha thams cad ni thabs shes gnyis
NK115(re)001:1526: su med pa'i ye shes kyi rnam pa yab yum
NK115(re)001:1528: dama tshig gi rdzasa kyang 'og mas bsten du mi
NK115(re)001:1529: nus pa'i khyada para can sha lnga dang bdud rtsi
NK115(re)001:1530: lnga la sogs pa la longs spyod nus shing /
NK115(re)001:1531: de yang lta ba dag mnyam chen po rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:1532: gnad kyis gtsang btsoga sogs gnyis chos thams cad la
NK115(re)001:1533: bzang ngan gyi gnyis 'dzin med pas 'ga' zhig spong
NK115(re)001:1534: ba dang 'ga' zhig dang du lena pa med par
NK115(re)001:1535: ro mnyam du blta zhing spyod pa'i ranga bzhina can
NK115(re)001:1536: no // de la spyir mdo dang sngags kyi lta
NK115(re)001:1537: ba la khyad zhugs stobs kyis rgyud sde 'og ma
NK115(re)001:1538: bya rgyud pa'i lta spyod kyang dbu ma las khyad
NK115(re)001:1539: par du 'phags pa yin na'ang phyogs mthun pa tsam
NK115(re)001:1540: du grub mtha' smra ba bzhi po dang rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:1541: bzhi'i lta spyod rnams 'dra chos re yod cing gong
NK115(re)001:1542: 'og gi khyad kyang de ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:1543: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1544: de la bla na med pa'i rgyud sde 'dir 'khor
NK115(re)001:1545: ba'i rang bzhin sdug bsngal dang kun 'byung gi bden
NK115(re)001:1546: pa gnyis po dngos su rnam byang gi bden pa
NK115(re)001:1547: gnyis kyi ngo bor lam du byas nas sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:1548: gzugs kyi sku dang chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:1549: du da lta nas sgrub par byed pas de'i tshul
NK115(re)001:1550: la sems kyi spros pa rgya chen po'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:1551: sgom par byed pas rnal 'byor chena po pha yi
NK115(re)001:1552: rgyud de / 'dis ni thabas bde ba chen po'i
NK115(re)001:1553: ye shes kyi rang rtsal la gzung 'dzin glo bur
NK115(re)001:1554: ba'i rtog pa'i dbang gis phung sogs kyi chos snod
NK115(re)001:1555: bcud kyi rnam par snang zhing der sgro btags pa'i
NK115(re)001:1556: kun brtags kyi cha sbyang ba'i phyir rang bzhin yongs
NK115(re)001:1557: shes kyi lta ba'i ngang nas snod bcud thams cad
NK115(re)001:1558: zhing dang gzhal yas khang dang lha dang lha mor
NK115(re)001:1559: gsal ba'i lam bskyed pa'i rima pa gtso bor byas
NK115(re)001:1560: rgyud de / nas bsgom zhing / rdzogs rim ni
NK115(re)001:1561: gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes bskyed
NK115(re)001:1562: pa'i phyir 'byung ba'i dwangs ma'i rlunga lnga dbu ma'i
NK115(re)001:1563: dbyings su daga para byed pa la sogs pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:1564: nas dngos grub rnam pa gnyis sgrub par byed do
NK115(re)001:1565: rgyud de / nas bsgom zhing / // bskyed rim
NK115(re)001:1566: la goms pa brtan pa'i rjes su sgom par byed
NK115(re)001:1567: rgyud de / nas bsgom zhing / // pas sam
NK115(re)001:1568: / rjes chags kyi ye shes bskyed pa gtso bor
NK115(re)001:1569: 'don pa'i phyir rjesa su rnal 'byor ma rgyud de
NK115(re)001:1570: rgyud de / nas bsgom zhing / // pas sam
NK115(re)001:1571: / / 'dis ni rdo rje'i lus kyi rtsa rlung
NK115(re)001:1572: thig le la dngos su gnad du bsnun nas gzhan
NK115(re)001:1573: dbang gi ngo bo sems dang sems byung gi rtogs
NK115(re)001:1574: tshogs thams cad dbyings kyi rang bzhin shesa raba stong
NK115(re)001:1575: pa nyid kyi ngang du dag pa'i stobs kyis bde
NK115(re)001:1576: stong lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes dngos su bskyed
NK115(re)001:1577: pa'i lam rang lus thabs ldan sngon du song nas
NK115(re)001:1578: gzhan lus phyag rgya bsten pa'i rdzogas rima gtso bor
NK115(re)001:1579: byed cing khamas lasa su rung zhing zhu ba las
NK115(re)001:1580: dga' bzhi bde ba chen po'i ye shes bskyed pa
NK115(re)001:1581: sogs dngos grub rnam pa gnyis dmigs pa goms pa
NK115(re)001:1582: kho na la mi ltos par rtsa thig rlung gsum
NK115(re)001:1583: las su rung ba las sgrub par byed do //
NK115(re)001:1584: shin tu nyams su myong dka' ba'i rang gnas kyi
NK115(re)001:1585: ye shes ji bzhin pa rjen par bsgoms pas shin
NK115(re)001:1587: 'dis ni bskyed rdzogs sam thabs shes gnyis gtso che
NK115(re)001:1588: chung meda par yongs grub zung 'jug gi ye shesa
NK115(re)001:1589: mngon du byed pa'i lam la goms pas gcig dang
NK115(re)001:1590: du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba'i chos nyid 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:1591: lhun grub chena pora sbyor zhing phung po'i snyigs ma
NK115(re)001:1592: dwangs ma'i 'ja' 'od du dwangs par byed do //
NK115(re)001:1593: de dag gi rang bzhin rgyas par ni 'og tu
NK115(re)001:1594: ston na'ang 'di'i skabs su rang rang gi go don
NK115(re)001:1595: bsdus te 'dzin shes par bya dgos gsungs /
NK115(re)001:1596: rje bdag nyid chen po tsong kha bas ni /
NK115(re)001:1597: rnal 'byor pha ma zhes pa'i rnal 'byor gyi don
NK115(re)001:1598: thabs shes phyogs re ba min par thabs shes sbyar
NK115(re)001:1599: bar gsungs pa'i thabs ni lhan cig skyes pa'i bde
NK115(re)001:1601: shes rab ni bdag med stong pa nyid kyi de
NK115(re)001:1602: kho na nyid rtogs pa'i blo yin pas des dbang
NK115(re)001:1603: du byas na bla med kyi rgyud thams cad gnyis
NK115(re)001:1604: med kyi rgyud du gnas pas gnyis med kyi rgyud
NK115(re)001:1605: ni pha ma gnyis kyi dbye gzhir bya yi dbye
NK115(re)001:1606: ba'i ya gyal min zhes bzhed cing /
NK115(re)001:1607: thabs shes so so ba'i rgyud du 'jog byed kyi
NK115(re)001:1608: thabs shes ni dri med 'od las gsungs pa ltar
NK115(re)001:1609: / phung po dag pa las thabs su bzhag pa'i lha pho dang /
NK115(re)001:1610: khams dag pa las shes rab tu bzhag pa lha
NK115(re)001:1611: mo'i sgo nas pha ma so so'i rgyud so sor
NK115(re)001:1612: 'jog pa dang / yang rdo rje gur la sogs pa las gsungs pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:1613: gtso bor rdzogs rim gyi sgo nas rgyud gnyis so sor phye zhing /
NK115(re)001:1614: de ltar phye ba'i thabs shes yang /
NK115(re)001:1615: don dam bde ba chen po'i ye shes ni shes rab dang /
NK115(re)001:1616: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i sku ni thabs te /
NK115(re)001:1617: de'ang de kho na nyid stong pa nyid la phyag
NK115(re)001:1618: rgya chen po'i sbyor bas 'jug pa'i tshul ston pas
NK115(re)001:1619: gur la sogs pa ma rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:1620: 'od gsal 'char ba'i gnas snying gar rlung sdud rim las lugs 'byung gi stong pa bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:1621: phyir la ldang ba'i rim pas lugs ldog gi stong
NK115(re)001:1622: pa bzhi'i sgo nas stong pa'i ye shes skye tshul
NK115(re)001:1623: dang / 'od gsal gyi rlung 'od zer lnga pa
NK115(re)001:1624: las kun rdzob sgyu ma'i sku sgrub pa gtso bor
NK115(re)001:1625: ston pa ni pha rgyud do zhes bzhed pa yin
NK115(re)001:1626: dang / no // 'o na 'dir bskyed rdzogs zung
NK115(re)001:1627: 'jug gsum gyi dbye bas rgyud gsum du bzhag pa
NK115(re)001:1628: dang de gnyis mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK115(re)001:1630: rje nyid kyis rgyud sde thams cad kyi khyab byed
NK115(re)001:1631: du gsungs pa'i thabs shes gnyis kyi dbye gzhi byas
NK115(re)001:1632: te / pha ma gnyis su dbye tshul gnyis gsungs
NK115(re)001:1633: pa de'ang gtso che chung tsam las lha pho mo
NK115(re)001:1634: te / dang / bde chen ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:1635: sgyu ma'i sku de dag don dam pa'i thabs shes
NK115(re)001:1636: dbyer med las gzhan zhig min zhing de gnyis lam
NK115(re)001:1637: du byed dus rtags kyi phyag rgya lha pho mo
NK115(re)001:1638: dang bde ba'i ye shes dang sgyu ma'i sku'i rnam
NK115(re)001:1639: par sgrub tshul tsam gyis 'jog la /
NK115(re)001:1640: gnyis med kyi rgyud ya gyal ba med par gsungs pa'ang /
NK115(re)001:1641: 'od gsal gtso bor ston pa'i rgyud sde dus 'khor
NK115(re)001:1642: sogs nas kyang rgyud sde gnyis su 'jog byed kyi
NK115(re)001:1643: thabs shes dngos su bstan pa tsam la dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:1644: yin zhing / 'dir yang bskyed rim thabs kyi cha
NK115(re)001:1645: dang rdzogs rim shes rab kyi chas bzhag kyang don
NK115(re)001:1646: dam pa'i bde stong dbyer med lam du byed tshul
NK115(re)001:1647: la thabs shes de gnyis gtso che chung tsam ma
NK115(re)001:1648: gtogs sgrub gzhi thabs shes dbyer med de las gzhan
NK115(re)001:1649: na 'jog byed tha dad pa zhig yod par mi
NK115(re)001:1650: yin zhing / 'dod cing / gnyis med kyi rgyud
NK115(re)001:1651: ces gzhan du gsung par bzhag pa de'ang thabs shes
NK115(re)001:1652: de gnyis gtso che chung med par mnyam par sbyor
NK115(re)001:1653: ba'i ye shes rang gi ngo bo lam du byed
NK115(re)001:1654: tshul gtso bor ston pa'i rgyud la 'jog gi //
NK115(re)001:1655: de gnyis las tha dad pa zhig ni yod pa mi bzhed do //
NK115(re)001:1656: khyad par snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sde yo ga gong
NK115(re)001:1657: ma'i dgongs don bla na med pa rnams thabs shes
NK115(re)001:1658: phyogs re ba ma yin par zung 'jug gi ye
NK115(re)001:1659: shes nyag gcig gtso bor ston pa'i rgyud yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:1660: phyir pha ma gnyis las tha dad par bzhag pa
NK115(re)001:1661: ni ches 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1662: gsum pa bla na med pa'i rgyud sde bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:1663: lam gyi spyi chings mdor bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1664: nyams len gyi lam dngos rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1666: 'di ltar sems can thams cad ni bde gshegs snying
NK115(re)001:1667: po'i rang bzhin dri ma'i sbubs na gnas pa 'khor
NK115(re)001:1668: 'das thams cad kyi 'char gzhi can yin pas /
NK115(re)001:1669: de rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zab mos sbyang
NK115(re)001:1670: ba byas pas tshe gcig la sogs par mya ngan
NK115(re)001:1673: gang zhig 'khor ba'i rgyur gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:1674: de nyid sbyang ba byas pa las //
NK115(re)001:1675: dag pa de nyid mya ngan 'das //
NK115(re)001:1676: zhes pa ltar bla na med pa'i rgyu sde kun
NK115(re)001:1677: gyi nang nas bshad pa'i bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:1678: rim pas ganda du bsnuna pa'i gzhi ni gang yin
NK115(re)001:1679: zhe na / spyir khams gong ma rnams lta bu
NK115(re)001:1680: la'ang khams drug gam rtsa rlung thig le phra ba'i
NK115(re)001:1681: rang bzhin rdo rje gsum gyi bsgrub gzhi gtan nas
NK115(re)001:1683: dang po gsang sngags nyams su len par byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:1684: rten 'byung ba lnga rnam par shes pa dang bcas
NK115(re)001:1685: pa'i khamas drug po rags pa mngon gyur pa dang
NK115(re)001:1686: ldana pa'i lusa 'dod khams pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1687: khyad par du mi'i 'gro ba yin par bshad do //
NK115(re)001:1688: de ltar yin pa'i rgyu mtshan yang phunga po lnga
NK115(re)001:1689: dang khamas bco brgyad dang skye mcheda bcu gnyis po
NK115(re)001:1690: thams cad snang ba'i gzhi rags pa'i rtsa thiga rlung
NK115(re)001:1691: gsum dang ro gcig pa'i gnyug ma dri bcas kyi
NK115(re)001:1692: khams dang bcas pa rnams ni zung 'jug e wamhgyi
NK115(re)001:1693: rang bzhin stong pa bzhi dang snang ba bzhi'i ye
NK115(re)001:1694: shes dang gnyis su med pa'i sku gsung thugs rdo
NK115(re)001:1695: rje'i ngo bor ye nas gnas pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:1696: dam pa dang po'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:1697: thig le zla ba khu ba sku //
NK115(re)001:1698: rnam par gcad bya rdul nyi gsung //
NK115(re)001:1699: a yig mun can thugs rab brjod //
NK115(re)001:1700: mkha' khams e la rnam par gnas //
NK115(re)001:1702: des na rten la gnad du bsnun pas brten pa
NK115(re)001:1703: lasa su rung ba lasa bskyed rim gyis rtsa dag
NK115(re)001:1704: pa mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa'i sku dang
NK115(re)001:1705: / rdzogas rim gyis rlung dag pa yan lag drug cu dang ldan pa'i gsung dang /
NK115(re)001:1706: zung 'juga gi lam gyis thig le dag pa ye
NK115(re)001:1707: shes lnga'i rang bzhin thugs rdo rje gsuma gyi yona
NK115(re)001:1708: tan ma lus pa kuna myur du bskyed par byed
NK115(re)001:1709: pa ni rdo rje theg pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:1710: lam gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa yin no
NK115(re)001:1711: // gnyis pa nyams len gyi lam dngos rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:1712: kun gzhi rgyu rgyud du lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi nyams su blang ba /
NK115(re)001:1713: lam thabs rgyud du smin grol yan lag dang bcas pa nyams su len tshul bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:1714: dang po kun gzhi rgyu rgyud du lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi nyams su blang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:1715: 'di ltar rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zab mos
NK115(re)001:1716: nyams su blang bar bya ba'i ngo bo chos thams
NK115(re)001:1717: cad kyi rang bzhina sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK115(re)001:1718: snying po rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid
NK115(re)001:1719: sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor ye nas lhun
NK115(re)001:1720: gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khora chen po ru gnas pa
NK115(re)001:1721: nyid yin la / de'i rang bzhin mngon sum du rtogs shing nyams su myong ba ni /
NK115(re)001:1722: mos gus kyi pha phog thob pa'am /
NK115(re)001:1724: bskyed rdzogs kyi lam goms pa'i rten 'brel la brten nas 'byung ba las /
NK115(re)001:1725: sgra rtog gi yul du byas te bden gnyis sam /
NK115(re)001:1726: snang stong sogs kyi tha snyad la brten nas ji bzhin par mi rtogs na'ang /
NK115(re)001:1727: sngags bla med kyi lam du zhugs pa'i thos bsam
NK115(re)001:1728: pa dag gis gzhi'i rang bzhin nam gnas lugs de
NK115(re)001:1729: nyid dang po thos bsam gyi lta basa thaga bacada
NK115(re)001:1732: bsgom rgyu'i bskyed rdzogs de bla med du gtogs pa
NK115(re)001:1733: zhig yin pa tsam gyis der mi 'gyur bas na
NK115(re)001:1734: shi na tu gal che ste bla med kyi lam
NK115(re)001:1735: thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro zhing thun mong ma
NK115(re)001:1736: yin pa'i bslab pa thams cad kun de'i rjes su
NK115(re)001:1738: de lta bas na snang srid dag mnyam chen por
NK115(re)001:1739: nges pa'i blo lta ba thams cad kyi yang rtse
NK115(re)001:1740: grub mtha' thams cad kyi mthar thug /
NK115(re)001:1741: lam thams cad kyi skyel so bla na med pa'i
NK115(re)001:1742: lugs kyi lta ba ji ltar gtan la dbab pa'i
NK115(re)001:1743: tshul bla ma rnams kyi gsung la brten nas rang
NK115(re)001:1744: lugs ltar cung zad bshad na /
NK115(re)001:1745: 'di ltar tha snyad kyi yul can chos can lta ba'i lta ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1746: don dam pa'i yul can chos nyid lta ba'i lta ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1747: bden gnyis dbyer med par nges pa'i yul can rang
NK115(re)001:1748: rig lta ba'i lta ba ste gsum ni spyir lta
NK115(re)001:1749: ba thams cad kyi khyab byed yin na'ang /
NK115(re)001:1750: 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i lta bas gtan la 'bebs pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:1751: de gsum gyis chos thams cad lhag pa'i bden pa
NK115(re)001:1752: dbyer med chos sku chen po'i rang bzhin du gtan
NK115(re)001:1754: de yang chos can gyi lta bas lhag pa'i kun
NK115(re)001:1755: rdzob kyi bden pa snang ba thams cad sku dang
NK115(re)001:1756: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag par gtan la
NK115(re)001:1758: chos nyid kyi lta bas lhag pa'i don dam pa'i
NK115(re)001:1759: bden pa chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin de bzhin
NK115(re)001:1760: gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i mdzod khang 'bras
NK115(re)001:1761: chos lnga dang dbyings ye gnyis te dkor bdun ngo
NK115(re)001:1762: bo nyid med pa'i dbyings su mnyam par shes nas
NK115(re)001:1763: / rang rig gi lta bas lhag pa'i bden pa
NK115(re)001:1764: de gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa chen por yul med
NK115(re)001:1765: rang gsal gyi tshul du nyams su myong ba'o //
NK115(re)001:1766: de'i phyir mdo sngags kyi lta ba gzhal bya chos
NK115(re)001:1767: dbyings spros bral du gtan la 'bebs pa tsam la
NK115(re)001:1768: khyad med kyang / chos dbyings mthong tshul gyi yul
NK115(re)001:1769: can la khyad par yod pas lta ba ni yul
NK115(re)001:1770: can gyi ngos nas 'jog dgos pa'i phyir khyad shin
NK115(re)001:1771: khyad med kyang / tu che gsungs / de yang
NK115(re)001:1772: sngags kyi lam pas mnyam gzhag tu bden pa dbyer
NK115(re)001:1773: med kyi don la gsal snang thob tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:1774: rjes thob tu nges pa skye tshul gnyis ka mdo lam las 'phags shing /
NK115(re)001:1775: der ma zad sngags lam du dang por thos bsam
NK115(re)001:1776: gyis sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i dus nas kyang 'khor 'das
NK115(re)001:1777: kyi chos thams cad dag mnyam chen po'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:1778: du lta bas na lta ba la ma rmongs pa
NK115(re)001:1779: yin pa'i phyir kun 'byung lam bden dang sdug bsngal
NK115(re)001:1780: 'gog bden gyi ngo bor shar bas nyon mongs ye
NK115(re)001:1781: shes dang sdug bsngal bde ba chen por grol ba'i
NK115(re)001:1782: phyir rgyu 'bras dbyer med du ston pas 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:1783: theg pa dang rdo rje'i theg pa zhes pa'i mtshan
NK115(re)001:1784: yang don gyis thob pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:1785: de la dang po chos can lta ba'i lta bas
NK115(re)001:1786: chos thams cad dag par bsgrub pa'i dbang du byas
NK115(re)001:1787: na snang ba lha dang nyon mongs pa ye shes
NK115(re)001:1788: su dag par bsgrub pa yin par gsungs pas na
NK115(re)001:1789: // phyi don khas len pa rnams kyi ngor snang ba lhar bsgrub na /
NK115(re)001:1790: da lta ma dag par snang ba'i dngos po 'di
NK115(re)001:1791: thams cad gnas tshul la dag pa lha dang gzhal
NK115(re)001:1792: yas khang la sogs pa'i rang bzhin yin te /
NK115(re)001:1793: dper na chu gcig la yi dwags rnams kyis rnag khrag tu mthong ba nas /
NK115(re)001:1794: mi dang lha dang rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis mthong tshul phyi ma phyi ma rnams dag cing /
NK115(re)001:1795: bag nyal yongs su zad pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:1796: ji lta ba'i gzigs ngor dag ma dag gi spros
NK115(re)001:1797: pa thams cad zhi bas gang yang mi gzigs la
NK115(re)001:1798: / ji snyed pa'i gzigs ngor shin tu rnam par
NK115(re)001:1799: dag pa rang snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor tshad
NK115(re)001:1800: med par snang bas sgrib pa thams cad dag pa'i
NK115(re)001:1801: yul can de tshad ma mthar thug yin pas des
NK115(re)001:1802: ji ltar mthong ba de yul gyi gnas tshul dngos
NK115(re)001:1803: yin par grub pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:1804: des na snang ba thams cad chos can /
NK115(re)001:1805: gnas tshul la sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK115(re)001:1806: phyin ci log gi bslad pa dang bral ba'i 'phags pa rnams kyis dag par gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:1807: dper na mig skyon med pas dung dkar por mthong ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:1808: 'phags pas mthong ba rang snang yin pas da lta'i
NK115(re)001:1809: ma dag pa'i snang ba 'di ma yin no snyam
NK115(re)001:1810: na spyir blta bya thun mong ba zhig phyi don
NK115(re)001:1811: du grub pa med pas ma dag pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:1813: dag pa thams cad ye shes kyi rang snang yin
NK115(re)001:1814: na'ang rten 'brel gyi snang ba tsam la tha dad
NK115(re)001:1816: sh+aa ri'i bus sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di ma dag par mthong zhing /
NK115(re)001:1817: tshangs pa ral pa can gyis gzhan 'phrul dbang byed
NK115(re)001:1818: kyi gnas dang mtshungs pa tsam du dag par mthong
NK115(re)001:1819: ba'i tshe / bcom ldan 'das kyis dkyil 'khor rnams
NK115(re)001:1820: la sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di'i rang bzhin bstan par
NK115(re)001:1821: ba'i tshe / mdzad pas / thams cad kyis shar
NK115(re)001:1822: phyogs kyi sangs rgyas rin po che'i rgyan bkod pa'i
NK115(re)001:1823: zhing khams bzhin yongs su dag par mthong ba'i tshe
NK115(re)001:1824: bcom ldan 'das kyis nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di
NK115(re)001:1825: ni rtag tu 'di 'dra ste khyod rnams kyis mi
NK115(re)001:1826: mthong ngo zhes gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:1827: des na 'khrul ngor snang tshul la mkhris nad can
NK115(re)001:1828: gyis dung la ser por mthong ba bzhin ma dag
NK115(re)001:1829: par snang yang / gnas tshul la dung gi kha
NK115(re)001:1830: dog gi gnas tshul dkar po yin pa bzhin dag
NK115(re)001:1831: par snang yang / pa yin no // chos can
NK115(re)001:1832: gyi rigs pa 'dis chos thams cad mnyam par yang
NK115(re)001:1833: par snang yang / pa yin no // rtogs nus
NK115(re)001:1834: te / thams cad dag pa'i rang bzhin du mi
NK115(re)001:1835: mnyams pa gcig kyang med par shes pa'i phyir ro
NK115(re)001:1836: par snang yang / pa yin no // rtogs nus
NK115(re)001:1837: te / // yang don dam dpyod pa'i tshad mas
NK115(re)001:1838: kyang dag par sgrub nus te 'di ltar sdug kun
NK115(re)001:1839: gyis bsdus pa'i chos ma dag par snang ba 'di
NK115(re)001:1840: thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas rnam par dag
NK115(re)001:1841: par snang yang / pa yin no // rtogs nus
NK115(re)001:1842: te / // pa yin te / don dam par
NK115(re)001:1843: brtags na thams cad skye ba med pa'i phyir te
NK115(re)001:1844: par snang yang / pa yin no // rtogs nus
NK115(re)001:1845: te / // pa yin te / / stong pa
NK115(re)001:1846: dang dbyer med pa'i snang ba ni dag par grub
NK115(re)001:1847: ste stong pa'i rang bzhin la ma dag pa med
NK115(re)001:1848: par snang yang / pa yin no // rtogs nus
NK115(re)001:1849: te / // pa yin te / / pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:1850: ro // 'o na stong pa'i ngo bo la dag
NK115(re)001:1851: ma dag gnyis ka med pas snang ba dag par
NK115(re)001:1853: da dung rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid bden
NK115(re)001:1854: pa dbyer med kyi don bsgrub pas 'grub par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:1855: ro // yang blta bya thun mong pa'i phyi don
NK115(re)001:1856: mi 'dod par thams cad sems kyi snang ba tsam
NK115(re)001:1857: du khas len pa rnams kyi ngor nyon mongs ye
NK115(re)001:1858: shes su dag par bsgrub na /
NK115(re)001:1859: chos thams cad sems snang tsam yin pa 'di /
NK115(re)001:1860: sems can phal pa la ma dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1861: lam pa la dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1862: sangs rgyas la shin tu dag par snang bas sgrib
NK115(re)001:1863: pa dang bcas pa'i gnas skabs kyi nyon mongs dang
NK115(re)001:1864: des bskyed pa'i 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i sems snang
NK115(re)001:1865: thams cad ni 'khrul snang yin la /
NK115(re)001:1866: sgrib pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:1867: rang snang de ni sems kyi gshis lugs yin dgos
NK115(re)001:1868: pas sems dang nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin dag par
NK115(re)001:1869: grub bo // de yang dper na gser dang dngul
NK115(re)001:1870: chu 'dres pa'i gong bu mar gsar gyi kha dog
NK115(re)001:1871: lta bur snang ba de la mi shes pa rnams
NK115(re)001:1872: kyis mar gsar gyi gong bur 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:1873: de'i rang bzhin shes pa rnams kyis dkar por snang
NK115(re)001:1874: ba 'di dngul chu dang 'dres pas de'i kha dog
NK115(re)001:1875: tu snang gi don la gser yin no snyam du
NK115(re)001:1876: shes / de me la cung zad reg na zangs la sogs pa'i mdog tu snang /
NK115(re)001:1877: mes cher gdung bar byas na gser gyi mdog ji
NK115(re)001:1878: lta ba bzhin du snang ste de phan chad ni
NK115(re)001:1880: de bzhin du sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK115(re)001:1881: po'i khams 'di gzung 'dzin gyi sems kyis bslad pas
NK115(re)001:1882: ma dag par snang zhing mi shes pa dag gis
NK115(re)001:1883: ma dag pa de ltar grub par 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:1884: dag mnyam la nges pa rnyed pa rnams kyis sems
NK115(re)001:1885: kyis bslad pas 'di ltar snang gi don la dag
NK115(re)001:1887: sgrib pa cung zad dag pa'i lam pa rnams la snang ba de je dag tu 'gro /
NK115(re)001:1888: sgrib pa shin tu dag pa'i sangs rgyas la ye
NK115(re)001:1889: shes kyi rang snang sha na tu rnam par dag
NK115(re)001:1890: pa'i ngo bo ji lta ba bzhin snang bas de
NK115(re)001:1892: de ltar dag par bsgrub pa'i lha'i ngo bo ni
NK115(re)001:1893: chos nyid don gyi lha rang byung gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:1894: dang / chos can rtags kyi lha rten dang brten pa'i phyag rgyar shar ba'o //
NK115(re)001:1895: 'o na sangs rgyas kyi gzigs snang la ma dag pa yod pa min na /
NK115(re)001:1896: sems can gyi 'khrul snang ma dag pa 'di mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK115(re)001:1897: mkhyen na gzigs snang ma dag pa yod par 'gyur zhing /
NK115(re)001:1898: mi mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK115(re)001:1899: bden zhen can gyi ngor yul bden par snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:1900: yul can bden 'dzin 'di sangs rgyas kyis gzigs sam mi gzigs //
NK115(re)001:1901: gzigs na sangs rgyas la bden snang yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1902: bden grub kyi chos gzigs par thal la /
NK115(re)001:1903: mi gzigs na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par 'gyur ro zhes 'dri na lan ci yod /
NK115(re)001:1904: sangs rgyas kyis de ji lta ba bzhin gzigs kyang
NK115(re)001:1905: sangs rgyas rang la ni bden snang yang med la
NK115(re)001:1906: / sangs rgyas kyis bden par grub pa'i chos kyang
NK115(re)001:1907: ma gzigs te yul gyi gnas tshul la mi srid
NK115(re)001:1909: 'o na sangs rgyas kyis 'gro ba'i 'khrul snang ma
NK115(re)001:1910: dag pa 'di ji lta ba bzhin du yang gzigs
NK115(re)001:1911: shing / sangs rgyas rang la ma dag par snang ba yang med la /
NK115(re)001:1912: ma dag pa'i chos kyang ma gzigs te don la mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:1913: gnyis pa chos nyid lta ba'i lta bas chos thams cad mnyam pa chen por bsgrub pa la /
NK115(re)001:1914: gang zag cig char ba'i rigs rnams la ni man
NK115(re)001:1915: ngag gi thabs la sogs pas rtogs par 'gyur bas
NK115(re)001:1916: dpyad pa mang po mi dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:1917: mnyam pa nyid kyi don la nges pa rim gyis bskyed pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:1921: mnyam pa nyid bzhi po snga ma snga ma shes
NK115(re)001:1922: pa las phyi ma phyi ma 'byung bar 'gyur bas
NK115(re)001:1923: 'di ltar / gcig du bral la sogs pa dbu
NK115(re)001:1924: ma nas ji skad bshad pa'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:1925: phung sogs ma grub par dpyad pas ma grub pa'i
NK115(re)001:1926: rnam pa 'char ba stong pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1927: med pa nyid kyang ma grub pas stong bzhin du
NK115(re)001:1928: snang ba'i chu zla ltar shes pa zung 'jug dang
NK115(re)001:1929: / de gnyis brjod tshul tsam las ro gcig par
NK115(re)001:1930: nges pas dgag gzhi snang ba dang dgag bya gcad
NK115(re)001:1931: pa'i stong pa gnyis sbyor du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa
NK115(re)001:1932: rang sar zhig ste dgag sgrub med par 'jog nus
NK115(re)001:1934: de la goms nas chos can so so ba'i chos
NK115(re)001:1935: nyid 'dzin pa'i blo thams cad chos nyid gcig gi
NK115(re)001:1936: ngang du nub ste mnyam pa nyid du mthar phyin
NK115(re)001:1937: par 'gyur ro // de ltar chos nyid stong pa
NK115(re)001:1938: nyid kyi ngang du chos can thams cad mnyam pa
NK115(re)001:1939: nyid du bsgrub pa de yang /
NK115(re)001:1940: dbu ma'i skabs kyi dpyad pa dang tshul mthun par
NK115(re)001:1941: bstan pa ni gtan la dbab don spros bral du
NK115(re)001:1943: skabs 'dir ni snang ba thams cad dag pa rab
NK115(re)001:1944: 'byams lha'i 'khor lor bstan pa'i gnad kyis de'i snang
NK115(re)001:1945: gzhi don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun
NK115(re)001:1946: gyis grub pa'i rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa
NK115(re)001:1947: nyid kyi ngang du chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid
NK115(re)001:1948: du mthar phyin par gtan la phebs dgos par sems
NK115(re)001:1949: so // gsum pa rang rig lta ba'i lta bas
NK115(re)001:1950: de gnyis dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por
NK115(re)001:1951: bsgrubs nas mngon sum du mthong ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:1952: de ltar snang ngos nas dag par grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:1953: stong ngos nas mnyam par grub pa de gnyis po
NK115(re)001:1954: chos thams cad la dbyer med ro gcig pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:1955: gyis gnas pa ni snga ma gnyis po'i shugs las
NK115(re)001:1956: grub ste / gang snang ba de mtha' kun gyis stong /
NK115(re)001:1957: gang stong pa'i ngang du mnyam pa de dag pa
NK115(re)001:1958: sku dang ye shes su 'char bas de gnyis dbyer
NK115(re)001:1959: med pa chos sku thig le nyag gcig tu zlum
NK115(re)001:1960: pa ni so so rang gis rig par bya ba
NK115(re)001:1961: ste mngon sum pa'i spyod yul lo //
NK115(re)001:1962: de ltar dag mnyam dbyer med gsum po so sor bsgrubs nas /
NK115(re)001:1963: da ni chos thams cad sems dang ye shes rang
NK115(re)001:1964: snang bden pa dbyer med du ston pa rdo rje
NK115(re)001:1965: sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi
NK115(re)001:1966: dngos bstan rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis thun mong
NK115(re)001:1967: du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:1969: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:1970: byin gyis brlab dang mngon sum par /
NK115(re)001:1971: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK115(re)001:1972: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK115(re)001:1974: gzhal bya zhen snang nyid 'jal byed gtan tshigs rnams
NK115(re)001:1975: kyis gzhal bas rang rang gis gtan la phebs pa'i
NK115(re)001:1977: gzhal bya zhen snang nyid ces pa'i don ni rgyu
NK115(re)001:1978: gcig pa'i rtags kyis gzhal bya 'khor 'das gnyis yin
NK115(re)001:1979: zhes pa ste / de yang 'khor 'das kyi rang
NK115(re)001:1980: mtshan la gzhal du med de 'khor ba med snang
NK115(re)001:1981: yin pas gzhal bya'i yul du ma grub la /
NK115(re)001:1982: myang 'das blo yul las 'das pas gzhal bya'i yul du mi rung zhing /
NK115(re)001:1983: gzhal yang mi dgos te mi 'ching ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:1984: des na lam rnam bkod las /
NK115(re)001:1985: brtags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK115(re)001:1990: 'khor 'das zhes dag ma dag gnyis su blo la
NK115(re)001:1991: don spyi'i tshul du snang ba de gzhal byar byed
NK115(re)001:1992: pa yin pas 'di ltar gtan tshigs dang po ni
NK115(re)001:1993: / 'khor 'das gnyis su snang zhing zhen pa 'di chos can /
NK115(re)001:1994: ji ltar snang zhing zhen pa ltar ma grub par
NK115(re)001:1995: sems nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su rgyu gcig
NK115(re)001:1996: pa yin te / de ltar rtogs pa dang ma
NK115(re)001:1997: rtogs pa las 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:1998: pa yin te / // dper na rgyal bu dwa'u dmangs su 'dzin pa'i sgro 'dogs dang /
NK115(re)001:1999: rgyal bur nges pa'i tshad ma gnyis ngo bo rgyal bur gcig pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:2001: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig pas //
NK115(re)001:2002: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK115(re)001:2003: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK115(re)001:2005: grub mtha' ni rang bzhin skye med do //
NK115(re)001:2006: gtan tshigs phyi ma rnams kyi gzhal bya snga ma
NK115(re)001:2007: rnams kyis gtan la phab pa'i grub matha'i zhen cha
NK115(re)001:2009: rang bzhin skye med de chos can /
NK115(re)001:2010: ci yang med pa'i stong pa phyogs gcig pa ma
NK115(re)001:2011: yin par gdangs 'gag med las lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK115(re)001:2013: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid gnas dang
NK115(re)001:2014: byed pa la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis mtshon byed yi
NK115(re)001:2015: ge du mar ma 'gags pa'i snang bas mtshon nas
NK115(re)001:2016: rtogs pa'i phyir / dper na mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:2018: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yis //
NK115(re)001:2019: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK115(re)001:2020: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste //
NK115(re)001:2021: thabs dang ldan pas rgyas btab pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2023: grub mtha' ni rol pa 'gags med do //
NK115(re)001:2025: rol pa 'gag med de chos can /
NK115(re)001:2026: rang bzhin skye ba med pa dang dbyer med de /
NK115(re)001:2027: rol pa 'gag med du 'char rung gi byin rlabs
NK115(re)001:2028: sam stobs kyis rang bzhin skye med du grub cing
NK115(re)001:2029: / rang bzhin skye ba med pa yin pa'i byin
NK115(re)001:2030: rlabs sam stobs kyis rol pa 'gags pa med par
NK115(re)001:2031: / snang ba'i phyir / dper na chu zla bzhin no zhes pa'am /
NK115(re)001:2032: yang na rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gag
NK115(re)001:2033: med gnyis dngos su rtogs pa'i mthus de gnyis ngo
NK115(re)001:2034: bo dbyer med du rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs la
NK115(re)001:2036: lhag pa don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur
NK115(re)001:2037: lhun gyis grub pas de'i snang ldog snod bcud sku
NK115(re)001:2038: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:2039: phyir / dper na gser dang de'i kha dog bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:2041: de nyid dbyer med byin rlabs las //
NK115(re)001:2042: de nyid de yi byin rlabs te //
NK115(re)001:2043: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK115(re)001:2044: byin rlabs ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK115(re)001:2046: grub mtha' ni ngo bo dbyer med do //
NK115(re)001:2048: bden gnyis ngo bo dbyer med de chos can /
NK115(re)001:2049: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:2050: rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:2051: 'di'i rang rig zhes pa so so rang gi rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:2052: de nyid chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs yin te /
NK115(re)001:2053: 'phags pa rnams kyis de ltar gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:2054: dper na mig skyon med pas dung dkar por mthong ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:2056: rang byung rang shar sems 'di dag /
NK115(re)001:2057: gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK115(re)001:2058: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK115(re)001:2059: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK115(re)001:2061: grub mtha' ni mtshan nyid blo bral te mthar thug go //
NK115(re)001:2062: de ltar lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK115(re)001:2063: gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan la phab nas sngags lam
NK115(re)001:2064: nyams su len pa ni don dang ldan pa yin
NK115(re)001:2065: te / bden pa dbyer med kyi rang bzhin ji
NK115(re)001:2066: bzhin pa ni rtog dpyod kho nas rtogs pa ma
NK115(re)001:2067: te / yin kyang / rtog dpyod rjes dpag gi
NK115(re)001:2068: sgo nas nges shes rnam dag rnyed nas lam bsgom
NK115(re)001:2069: na yang dag pa'i gnas lugs mngon sum du rtogs
NK115(re)001:2070: te / yin kyang / par 'gyur ro // lta
NK115(re)001:2071: ba de lta bu'i ngang nas bsgom pasa nyamas su
NK115(re)001:2072: blang ba ni snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:2073: chos thams cad gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen
NK115(re)001:2074: por ye nas gnas par gsal 'debs shing bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:2075: te / yin kyang / par 'gyur ro // ste / sdom 'byung las /
NK115(re)001:2076: khams gsum gzhal yas khang bdag nyid //
NK115(re)001:2077: srog chags rnams ni dkyil 'khor ba //
NK115(re)001:2078: de dbus skad cig rnam pa yi //
NK115(re)001:2080: zhes pa ltar phyi don du 'dzin pa'i snang ba
NK115(re)001:2081: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams zhi ba dang khro bo'i
NK115(re)001:2082: dkyil 'khor gyi bkod pa sgo rgyan rta babs la
NK115(re)001:2083: sogs pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2084: nang phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga de bzhin
NK115(re)001:2085: gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po la sogs
NK115(re)001:2086: pa stang dpyal lnga'i ngo bo la /
NK115(re)001:2087: dbang yul dang rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs byang chub
NK115(re)001:2088: sems dpa' sems ma rnams dang sgo ba yab yum
NK115(re)001:2089: la sogs par bsgoms pas gzugs thams cad snang stong
NK115(re)001:2091: dran rtog thams cad rig stong sgyu ma'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:2092: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK115(re)001:2093: dkyil 'khor du gsal ba de yang snang ba'i cha
NK115(re)001:2094: nas bskyed pa / de rang bzhin med pa'i ting
NK115(re)001:2095: nge 'dzin gyi ngang du rdzogs pa'i cha nas rdzogs
NK115(re)001:2096: rim ste bden pa dbyer med chen por nyams su
NK115(re)001:2098: rgyas par ni 'og tu bskyed rdzogs kyi skabs su 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:2099: de ltar bsgom pas nyams su len pa de yi
NK115(re)001:2100: tshe grogs spyod pasa gzung 'dzin gyi la dora bar
NK115(re)001:2101: byed pa ni phyi nang gi snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2102: blo'i 'gro ldog bzang ngan thams cad la tha mal gyi snang bas mi dpyad cing /
NK115(re)001:2103: 'dod yon la rang dgar zhen pas dug lnga rang
NK115(re)001:2104: rgyud du shor ba ma yin par thabs kyis zin
NK115(re)001:2105: pa'i mnyam rdzogs chen pos rol pa ste dam tshig
NK115(re)001:2107: de dag gi gnad don rdzong 'phrang srog gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:2108: skyabs rje bla ma bka' drin can gyi gsung las /
NK115(re)001:2111: spyod pa'i srog mkhar tshugs pa zhig la sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:2112: de yang spyir mdo dang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha'
NK115(re)001:2113: dag gi dgongs don lta sgom spyod pa'i khongs su
NK115(re)001:2114: 'du ba la / ngos 'dzin ji ltar gnang na /
NK115(re)001:2115: lta ba ni stong nyid bco brgyad yin //
NK115(re)001:2116: the tshom dang bral ba'i rdzonga zhig dgos //
NK115(re)001:2117: sgom pa ni phyogs chos so bdun yin //
NK115(re)001:2118: bying rgod kyi 'phranga las 'da' ba dgos //
NK115(re)001:2119: spyod pa ni pha rol phyin drug yin //
NK115(re)001:2120: rang 'dod dang bral ba'i sroga tshugs dgos //
NK115(re)001:2121: zhes gong ma dag gis gsungs pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:2122: 'dir yang lta ba la yin pa med pa'i don
NK115(re)001:2123: chos can blos btags kyi tshogs pa chos nyid bsam
NK115(re)001:2124: gyis mi khyab pa'i klong du rang bzhin med par
NK115(re)001:2125: sangs tshe chos nyid blo 'das kyi rdzonga chen rnyed
NK115(re)001:2127: de ltar rtogs pa'i lta ba de'i ngang la rgyun
NK115(re)001:2128: du mnyam pa bzhag pa ni sgom pa zhes bya
NK115(re)001:2129: ste / bying rgod dang gsal 'grib kyi 'phranga las
NK115(re)001:2130: grol bas 'bad rtsol la ma ltos par bsgom med
NK115(re)001:2131: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor can la snang sems gnyis su
NK115(re)001:2132: ma grub pasa yul snang bsgom du shar ba'am /
NK115(re)001:2133: snang srid dpe char shar ba'i tshe sgom pa la min pa med pa'i tha snyad brjod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2134: de ltar lta sgom klong du gyur pa'i skabs tsam
NK115(re)001:2135: na spang blang rang grol du song bas yin min
NK115(re)001:2136: med pa'i spyod pa zhes mi bsrung ba'i bsrung ba
NK115(re)001:2137: chen po chos sku thig le nyag gcig gi srog
NK115(re)001:2138: makhara tshugsa pa ni spang thob zhig pa'i 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:2139: re dogs dang bral ba'i byang chub sems kyi yin
NK115(re)001:2141: rdzong 'phrang srog gsum 'di rnal 'byor pa gcig gis smin byed kyi dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:2142: grol byed kyi gdams pa thob pa nas sa lam
NK115(re)001:2143: mthar phyin pa'i bar gyi chings yin par shes dgos
NK115(re)001:2144: so zhes dang / gzhan yang bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du gsal thebs pa bskyed rim gyi rdzonga /
NK115(re)001:2145: snang stong zung du 'jug pa'i gnas lugs 'dus ma
NK115(re)001:2146: byas pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang la 'jog pa ni
NK115(re)001:2148: bying rgod dang dman pa'i sems sogs gnyis ka'i 'phranga
NK115(re)001:2149: rnams bsal ba la kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK115(re)001:2150: zhes bzhed do // zhes gsungs pa 'di dag gi
NK115(re)001:2151: don nges par byas nas lta sgom spyod gsum zung
NK115(re)001:2153: de ltar sngags bla med kyi lta sgom spyod gsum
NK115(re)001:2154: ya ma bral bar nyams su len pa'i byang chub
NK115(re)001:2155: sems dpa' rnams kyis don du gnyer bya ni gzhan
NK115(re)001:2156: don phun sum tshogs pa kho na yin na de
NK115(re)001:2157: rang don mthar phyin pa la rag las pas lta
NK115(re)001:2158: bas gtan la phab pa'i don rdzogs rim gyis 'bras
NK115(re)001:2159: bu rang don chos kyi sku mngon du byas nas
NK115(re)001:2160: bskyed rim mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu gzhan don gzugs
NK115(re)001:2161: sku'i bkod pa rtsol med du snang zhing /
NK115(re)001:2162: spyod pa mthar phyin pas 'khor ba ma stongs kyi
NK115(re)001:2163: bar du rtag khyab lhun grub chen po'i phrin las
NK115(re)001:2164: kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa ste de ltar dona
NK115(re)001:2165: gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'i yon tan thams cad myur
NK115(re)001:2166: du tshegs med par gruba pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:2167: de yang gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor lta bas gtan la phab ste /
NK115(re)001:2168: lam bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi don sgom pas nyams
NK115(re)001:2169: su blang zhing spyod pas grogs byas pas 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:2170: rgyud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mngon du
NK115(re)001:2171: snang bar 'gyur bas de gsum la yang dag par
NK115(re)001:2173: gnyis pa lam thabs rgyud du smin grol yan lag
NK115(re)001:2174: dang bcas pa nyams su len tshul la gnyis te
NK115(re)001:2177: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:2178: de lta bu'i gsang sngags kyi lam de la dbye na /
NK115(re)001:2179: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam tshig /
NK115(re)001:2180: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyis //
NK115(re)001:2181: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK115(re)001:2183: de kho na nyid lta ba /
NK115(re)001:2188: gnas su stob pa mchod pa /
NK115(re)001:2192: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2193: 'di dag la rgyud kyi dngos po bcu'am /
NK115(re)001:2194: sngags dang phyag rgya gnyis so sor bgrang na bcu gcig ces bya ste /
NK115(re)001:2195: shes bya'i gshis kyi bzhugs tshul ma nor bar rtogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2196: gsang sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i spyad bya
NK115(re)001:2197: la tshul bzhin du spyad pas gzung 'dzin gyi la
NK115(re)001:2198: dor ba dang / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:2199: kyi rang bzhin dang snang ba thams cad kyi bkod
NK115(re)001:2200: pa lha'i ngo bor rdzogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2201: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi thob bya'i chos go
NK115(re)001:2202: 'phang gi rim pa bgrod pa la dbang ba dang
NK115(re)001:2203: / bsrung bya khyad par can gyi mtshams las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2204: snang srid thams cad mchod pa'i phyag rgyar shar ba
NK115(re)001:2205: lha'i gnas dang chos nyid kyi ngo bor stob pa
NK115(re)001:2206: dang / yin pa gsum dang grub pa bzhi'i de
NK115(re)001:2207: nyid shes pas 'gyu ba'i rlung khams sngags su sgrub
NK115(re)001:2208: dang / pa dang / snang spyod thams cad la
NK115(re)001:2209: rig pa phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs las mi 'da' bar
NK115(re)001:2211: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i don las mi g.yo ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2212: lta dgongs dbyer med kyi rol pa tshad med bzhir
NK115(re)001:2213: shar ba'i las kyis rang gzhan la phan pa'i don
NK115(re)001:2214: 'byung ba dang / 'dod bya'i dngos grub ji lta
NK115(re)001:2215: ba bzhin sgrub pa rnams la go rim bzhin du
NK115(re)001:2216: 'byung ba dang / shes par bya'o // de dag
NK115(re)001:2217: kyang bsdu na 'di ltar 'jug pa'i sgo ni sku
NK115(re)001:2218: gsung thugs ye shes te rdo rje bzhi'i ngo bo
NK115(re)001:2219: rang nyid la nye len gyi rgyu'i tshul du yod
NK115(re)001:2220: kyang 'bras bu'i ngo bor mngon du ma smin pa
NK115(re)001:2221: de nyid mngon gyur du smin par bya ba'i lhan
NK115(re)001:2222: cig byed pa'i rkyen ni dabnga yin te /
NK115(re)001:2223: lam bzhi bsgom pa dang 'bras bu bzhi thob rung du byed pa'i nus pa 'jog pa ste /
NK115(re)001:2225: rno la ngar btags nus pa bzhin //
NK115(re)001:2226: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK115(re)001:2228: de ltar dbang thob pa tsam gyis mi 'ong ste /
NK115(re)001:2229: dbang dus su grol nus pa'i skal ba mchog dang ldan pa zhig yin na ma gtogs /
NK115(re)001:2230: rang la gnas pa'i ye shes kyi rang zhal sgrib
NK115(re)001:2231: par byed pa'i sgo gsum bag chags dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:2232: las grol bar byed pa'i thabs ni bskyed pa'i rim
NK115(re)001:2233: pa dang rdzogas pa'i rim pa rnam pa gnyis po
NK115(re)001:2234: yin pas yang yang bsgom dgos la /
NK115(re)001:2235: bskyed rdzogs bsgoms kyang dam tshig ma bsrung na dngos grub rnam pa gnyis mi 'grub pas /
NK115(re)001:2236: lam de dang tshul mthuna pa'i grogas su sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:2237: gzhung nas ji skad bshad pa'i dama tshiga gi rim
NK115(re)001:2238: pa yang dag par bsrung ba'i spyod pa dang gsuma
NK115(re)001:2239: po de tshang na gsang sngagsa kyi lam phar phyin
NK115(re)001:2240: theg pa'i lam las khyad par du 'phags pas mchoga
NK115(re)001:2241: ma nor ba yin pas rnal mara ngesa pa yin
NK115(re)001:2242: gyi de lasa gzhan du dbang ma thob bzhin bskyed
NK115(re)001:2244: bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa ltar snang yang dam tshig mi
NK115(re)001:2245: bsrung ba sogs ni sngags lam gyi gzugs brnyan tsam
NK115(re)001:2246: las mchog dang ma nor ba ni ma yin no
NK115(re)001:2247: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:2250: mthun pa'i grogs dam tshig rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2252: dbang thob dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK115(re)001:2253: slob dpon dang slob ma'i mtshan nyid /
NK115(re)001:2254: dbang bskur ba dngos bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2255: dang po dbang thob dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:2256: gsang sngags lam gyi 'jug sgo dang po dabnga bskura
NK115(re)001:2257: thob dgos pa yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir zhe
NK115(re)001:2258: na / dbang ma thoba bzhin sngags lam la ci
NK115(re)001:2259: tsam brtson kyang dngosa grub gang yang thob par mi
NK115(re)001:2260: 'gyur te rgyud smin pa meda pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:2261: dper na bye ma btsir ba'i bya ba la ji
NK115(re)001:2262: tsam 'bad kyang de lasa zhuna mara 'byung ba med
NK115(re)001:2263: pas 'doda pa'i don mi thob pa bzhina te /
NK115(re)001:2265: dbang med pa la dngos grub med //
NK115(re)001:2266: bye ma btsir las mar mi 'byung //
NK115(re)001:2267: mkha' la khu tshur gyis brdeg dang //
NK115(re)001:2268: smig rgyu'i chu ni 'thung dang mtshungs //
NK115(re)001:2270: dngos grub mi thob par ma zad gsang sngags kyi chos la dbang zos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2271: gsang sgrogs kyi nyes pas sngags kyi rgyud dang gdams ngag gzhan la 'achada pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2273: bskyed rdzogs kyi lam sgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2274: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa la brtson kyang phyi ma dmyala ba'i gnas su nges par 'gro ste /
NK115(re)001:2276: dbang bskur med par rgyud 'chad dang //
NK115(re)001:2277: zab mo'i de nyid sgom byed pa //
NK115(re)001:2278: de don legs par shes na yang //
NK115(re)001:2279: dmyal bar 'gyur gyi grol ba med //
NK115(re)001:2282: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK115(re)001:2283: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK115(re)001:2284: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa ni //
NK115(re)001:2287: dabnga thoba pa'i phan yon ni /
NK115(re)001:2288: dbang bskur ba'i sngon du dkyil 'khor du zhugs te phyi phan pa'i dbang tsam las ma bskur kyang /
NK115(re)001:2289: de'i sngon du rdo rje'i rnal 'byor du sems bskyed dgos pas /
NK115(re)001:2290: de ltar sems bskyed pa'i skyesa bu de dper na
NK115(re)001:2291: rgyal po'i bu thams cad kyi nang nas mtshan dang
NK115(re)001:2292: ldan pa de ni rgyal srid la mnga' gsol ba'i
NK115(re)001:2293: sras kyi mchog yin par shes pa de bzhin du
NK115(re)001:2294: byang sems phar phyin gyi theg pa ba rnams las
NK115(re)001:2295: kyang / rgyal ba rnams kyis nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyura te /
NK115(re)001:2297: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK115(re)001:2298: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK115(re)001:2299: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK115(re)001:2300: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2302: der ma zad dbang bskur dngos sbyin pa'i snod du
NK115(re)001:2303: ma gyur ba'i gang zag zhig yin kyang de la
NK115(re)001:2304: phan gdags pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa tsam
NK115(re)001:2305: byed rung bar gsungs pas de ltar byas pa na
NK115(re)001:2306: / dkyila 'khora mthonga ba tsam gyis kyang mtshams med
NK115(re)001:2307: pa lnga la sogs pa'i sdig pa lasa rnama para
NK115(re)001:2309: yo ga de nyid 'dus pa las /
NK115(re)001:2310: sdig pa bgyis par gyur ba gang //
NK115(re)001:2312: mthong bas byang bar 'gyur lags na //
NK115(re)001:2315: mtshams med lnga yi las can yang //
NK115(re)001:2316: tshon rtsi mthong bas grol bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2318: yang dkyil 'khor du bcug nas dbang bskur thob na
NK115(re)001:2319: lam la cher brtson ma nus kyang dam tshig tsam
NK115(re)001:2320: bsrungs na / gang du skyes kyang sdig pa dang
NK115(re)001:2321: phyin ci log gis ma bslad pa'i gtsang ma'i rigas
NK115(re)001:2322: su skyesa nas gsang sngags kyi chos dang 'phrad par
NK115(re)001:2323: bsrungs na / 'gyur te / de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:2324: dkyil 'khor bcug dang dbang bskur ba //
NK115(re)001:2325: gtsang ma'i rigs su skye bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2327: de lta bu'i gtsang ma'i skye ba brgyud pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:2328: yang yang dbang bskur thob pa'i yon tan gyis skye
NK115(re)001:2329: ba bduna phan mi 'gyang bar skye ba de daga
NK115(re)001:2330: gi tshe na lam goms pa'i mthus rtsol ba chen
NK115(re)001:2331: pos bsgrub ma dgos par bskyed rdzogs kyi yon tan
NK115(re)001:2332: ngesa para 'grub cing 'phags pa'i sa bcu po bgrod
NK115(re)001:2333: nas sangs rgyas kyi sa 'thoba para bashada de /
NK115(re)001:2335: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK115(re)001:2336: skye zhing skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2337: de yi skye ba bdun na ni //
NK115(re)001:2341: dbang bskur bas ni sa bcu non //
NK115(re)001:2343: de yang bum dbang gis las sgrib dang /
NK115(re)001:2344: gsang dbang gis nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa ste mthong spang dang /
NK115(re)001:2345: dbang gong ma gnyis kyis shes bya'i sgrib pa rags
NK115(re)001:2346: phra gnyis su phye ba'i sgom spang dag pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:2347: gyis sa bcu non pa ni spyir btang dang //
NK115(re)001:2348: dmigs bsal sngags lam gyis sa bcu bsgrod tshul dus myur ba sogs khyad par 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:2349: theg chen spyi'i lugs la dang po sems bskyed nas rgyal ba'i sras su ming thob cing /
NK115(re)001:2350: sa thob nas rgyud bla ma las /
NK115(re)001:2351: theg mchog la mos sa bon shes rab ni //
NK115(re)001:2352: sangs rgyas chos bskyed ma dang bsam gtan gyi //
NK115(re)001:2353: bde ba'i mngal gnas snying rje'i ma ma can //
NK115(re)001:2354: gang yin de ni thub pa'i rjes skyes sras //
NK115(re)001:2355: zhes rgyal ba'i sras por dngos su 'gyur bar gsungs
NK115(re)001:2356: la de yan chad du grangs med gnyis la sogs
NK115(re)001:2357: pa'i yun la sa bcu rim gyis bgrod dgos par
NK115(re)001:2358: bstan to // sngags su ni dbang gi sngon du
NK115(re)001:2359: rdo rje'i rnal 'byor du sems bskyed pa'i tshe rgyal
NK115(re)001:2360: sras kyi ming thob cing dbang gi dngos gzhi rnal
NK115(re)001:2361: ma thob nas rig pa 'dzin pa dngos kyi sa
NK115(re)001:2362: thob ste lta sgom gyi nus pa khyad par can
NK115(re)001:2363: thob pas yun ring por mi thogs par sa bcu'i
NK115(re)001:2364: yon tan mthar phyin par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:2365: de 'dra ba de dper na nya lcags kyus zin
NK115(re)001:2366: na gnas skabs chur gnas kyang myur du skam sar
NK115(re)001:2367: thon pa bzhin gnas skabs rnam smin gyi lus 'khor
NK115(re)001:2368: ba'i sas bsdus pa ltar snang yang rtogs pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:2369: tan la khyad par gyi sa'i yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:2370: lhun gyis grub par rdzogs te de'i stobs kyis myur
NK115(re)001:2371: du mthar 'bras la sbyor ba'i nus pa dang ldan
NK115(re)001:2372: pa ste / de dag gi don ni gsang snying las /
NK115(re)001:2374: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK115(re)001:2375: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:2376: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK115(re)001:2378: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang rkyen 'jug
NK115(re)001:2379: pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin gnyis rgyud la 'byor
NK115(re)001:2380: ba ni 'bras bu thob byed kyi thabs kyi nges
NK115(re)001:2381: pa mi gtong ba'i gzungs kyang yin la /
NK115(re)001:2382: 'bras bu smin par byed pa'i rgyu lta ba dang
NK115(re)001:2383: rkyen ting nge 'dzin gnyis po phar phyin theg pa'i
NK115(re)001:2384: lta sgom las khyad du 'phags pas de gnyis nus
NK115(re)001:2385: pa mthu can du gyur pa na rig pa 'dzin
NK115(re)001:2386: pa ming 'di zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:2387: nas rdo rje'i ming gi dbang thob cing lung yang
NK115(re)001:2388: ston pa sogs kyis sangs rgyas kyi zhing kun tu
NK115(re)001:2390: des na sa bcu po'i skabs kyi phar phyin bcu'i
NK115(re)001:2391: yon tan thams cad rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa de
NK115(re)001:2392: la cig car du rdzogs par 'gyur te chos thams
NK115(re)001:2393: cad la yongs su 'dzin pa med par shes nas
NK115(re)001:2394: bkag pa med pa ni sbyin pa /
NK115(re)001:2395: mnyam nyid du rig pas bsrung mtshams kyi 'du shes mi gnas pa ni tshul khrims /
NK115(re)001:2396: 'khrul pa med pas bzang ngan gyi bye brag mi phyed pa ni bzod pa /
NK115(re)001:2397: blang dor med pa dang spyod yul tshogs su gyur pa ni brtson 'grus /
NK115(re)001:2398: dbang po yul la 'jug kyang chags pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa ni bsam gtan /
NK115(re)001:2399: gshis kyi gnas lugs phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK115(re)001:2400: pas 'khor 'das kyi gnyis chos thams cad dbyings nas
NK115(re)001:2401: mya ngan las 'das pa ni shes rab /
NK115(re)001:2402: de las bdag dang gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa la mkhas pa ni thabs /
NK115(re)001:2403: zhing dang spyod yul yongs su dag par 'gyur ba ni smon lam /
NK115(re)001:2404: de la mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis bardzi bar mi nus pa'i brtul zhugs ni stobs /
NK115(re)001:2405: dpe dang tha snyad kyi rjes su dpag pa tsam
NK115(re)001:2406: ma yin par sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos sku'i bzhugs
NK115(re)001:2407: tshul ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs pa ni ye
NK115(re)001:2408: shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2409: de yang rdo rje'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK115(re)001:2410: sems stong pa nyid du mi g.yo na pha rol tu phyin pa drug 'dus so //
NK115(re)001:2412: de ltar sa dang pha rol tu phyin pa bcu'i
NK115(re)001:2413: yo na tan thams cad mthar phyin pas 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:2414: mi slob pa'i yon tan la ldog pas dbye ba'i
NK115(re)001:2415: sku gsum gyis mngon du 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:2416: de yang bcu gcig kun tu 'od sprul sku'i sa
NK115(re)001:2417: ste 'od zer kun tu bkye bas rnam par 'phrul
NK115(re)001:2418: pa'i sprul pa dang phrin las kyis 'gro ba 'dul
NK115(re)001:2421: 'od zer bkye bas gdul bya snod du rung bar byed pa'i phyir kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK115(re)001:2423: bcu gnyis pad+ma can longs sku'i sa ste sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:2424: med pa'i shes rab dang dmigs pa med pa'i thugs
NK115(re)001:2425: rje chen po zung du 'jug pa las lhun stug
NK115(re)001:2426: po bkod pa'i zhing chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par
NK115(re)001:2427: snang yang gzung 'dzin gyis gos pa med pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:2429: pad+ma can la longs spyod rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:2430: lhun grub ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:2432: bcu gsum 'khor lo tshogs chen chos sku'i sa ste
NK115(re)001:2433: gcig du ma dang bral ba'i rang byung ye shes
NK115(re)001:2434: chen po'i ngang na sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK115(re)001:2435: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i yon tan thams cad 'char rung
NK115(re)001:2436: gi gdangs 'gag pa med par gnas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:2438: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK115(re)001:2439: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK115(re)001:2440: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK115(re)001:2441: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK115(re)001:2444: kun tu 'od chos sku dang 'khor lo tshogs chen sprul sku'i sa yin te /
NK115(re)001:2446: dbyings la ye shes shar ba kun tu 'od //
NK115(re)001:2447: pad+ma'i spyan 'dra mi 'gag longs spyod rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:2448: yi ge 'khor lo'i gdul byar sprul pa 'gyed //
NK115(re)001:2449: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:2451: zhes bzhed kyang de gnyis 'gal ba med par sems te /
NK115(re)001:2452: rgyud kyi tshig ni shin tu barlinga bas mkhas pa
NK115(re)001:2453: rnams kyi rnam dpyod kyis dngos don dang mi 'gal
NK115(re)001:2454: bar gang ltar 'grel yang rung ste /
NK115(re)001:2455: 'khor lo tshogs chen chos sku'i sar 'jog pa ltar na /
NK115(re)001:2457: sprul pa tshad med pas kun tu 'od dang /
NK115(re)001:2458: snang ba tshad med pas pad+ma can dang /
NK115(re)001:2459: ye shes tshad med pas 'khor lo tshogs chen te /
NK115(re)001:2460: dbyings skye ba med pa na rang byung gi ye
NK115(re)001:2461: shes 'gag pa med pa yi ge'i sa bon ltar
NK115(re)001:2462: 'phro gzhir gnas pas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK115(re)001:2463: zhes bshad do // zhes gsungs pas 'di'i ltar na
NK115(re)001:2464: gong gi lung don yang dbyings dang ye shes zung
NK115(re)001:2465: du 'jug pa yi ge 'khor lo'i 'phro gzhir a'i
NK115(re)001:2466: rang bzhin skye med chos sku'i ye shes kyi gdangs
NK115(re)001:2467: 'gag pa med pa las gdul byar sprul pa 'gyed
NK115(re)001:2468: pa'i phyir chos sku'i sa'o zhes 'grel kyang rung ba'i
NK115(re)001:2469: zhes bshad do // phyir ro // de lta na'ang
NK115(re)001:2470: gsar rnying gi rgyud sde du ma nas lam bsgrod
NK115(re)001:2471: tshul rdo rje'i tshig gis bcings nas bstan pa la
NK115(re)001:2472: rgya bod kyi slob dpon rnams kyis dgongs pa len
NK115(re)001:2473: tshul yang tha dad pa du ma snang ste /
NK115(re)001:2474: gsang ba 'dus pa la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:2476: dang po las kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK115(re)001:2477: sa brgyud pa ni thob par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2478: snang ba gsum pa thob pa dag /
NK115(re)001:2479: sa bcu la ni rab tu gnas //
NK115(re)001:2481: de la kha cig ni mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam gyis sa bcu'i bar du bgrod de /
NK115(re)001:2482: de nas sngags la 'jug pa ste sa bcu pa
NK115(re)001:2483: la gnas pa srid pa tha ma bas bskyed rim
NK115(re)001:2484: nas brtsams te sems dben gyi bar bskyed mi dgos
NK115(re)001:2485: par / srod la gsang dbang bskur sgyu lus mngon du byas /
NK115(re)001:2486: nam phyed dbang gsum pa bskur 'od gsal mngon du byas /
NK115(re)001:2487: tho rangs bzhi pa bskur mi slob pa'i lam zung 'jug mngon du byas te 'tshang rgya bar 'dod /
NK115(re)001:2488: de'ang mtshan nyid theg pa rang lam gyis sa bcu'i
NK115(re)001:2489: bar du bgrod pa des bskyed rim nas brtsams te
NK115(re)001:2490: sems dben gyi bar rgyud la skye ba'i dod thub
NK115(re)001:2491: par 'dod pa la ni rigs pas gnod pa yod
NK115(re)001:2492: la / phyi 'gyur gyi chos skad nang mthun par smra ba dag kyang so skye'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK115(re)001:2493: 'phags pa sa mthon po'i rnal 'byor stobs nus che
NK115(re)001:2494: chung gi khyad par gnam sa lta bur khyad zhugs
NK115(re)001:2495: pa la dod thub byed pa ha cang thal lo
NK115(re)001:2496: zhes lung rigs rgya chen pos dgag cing /
NK115(re)001:2497: sngags la ma brten pa'i 'phags pa'i rtogs pa med par tshad mas grub pa'i shes byed du /
NK115(re)001:2499: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang 'das dang //
NK115(re)001:2500: de bzhin gang dag ma byin dang //
NK115(re)001:2501: da ltar byung ba'i mgon po rnams //
NK115(re)001:2502: 'gro la phan phyir bzhugs pa gang //
NK115(re)001:2503: de dag kun gyis gsang sngags kyi //
NK115(re)001:2504: cho ga zab mo 'di mkhyen nas //
NK115(re)001:2505: dpa' bos byang chub shing drung du //
NK115(re)001:2506: thams cad mkhyen pa tshad med brnyes //
NK115(re)001:2507: zhes pa 'di nges don du 'dod pa'i phyogs legs pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:2508: des na dbyig gi sgron ma las /
NK115(re)001:2509: khyod kyi mthar phyin kun tu 'od //
NK115(re)001:2510: thabs chen lam gyi bsti gnas sa //
NK115(re)001:2512: rgyu yis bgrod pa'i kun du 'od //
NK115(re)001:2513: thabs chen lam gyi chos sku ste //
NK115(re)001:2514: zhes pa la sogs rgyu'i sa lam thams cad sngags
NK115(re)001:2515: kyi lam stegs su bstan pa 'di'i dgongs pa ni
NK115(re)001:2516: / dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi yang dag par spong ba bzhi dang brgyad /
NK115(re)001:2517: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang po gsum dang bcu
NK115(re)001:2518: gcig gi bar la gdul bya drang ba'i phyir rab
NK115(re)001:2519: tu dga' ba la sogs pa'i sa bcu gcig tu
NK115(re)001:2520: btags pa de ni mtshan nyid theg pa rang lam
NK115(re)001:2522: de nas ni gdon mi za bar sngags kyi theg
NK115(re)001:2523: pa la 'jug pa'i mtshams ni rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang
NK115(re)001:2524: pa bzhi pa nas yin te /
NK115(re)001:2526: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i stobs chen ldan //
NK115(re)001:2527: de nyid dran pa chen po 'chang //
NK115(re)001:2528: dran pa bzhi po ting 'dzin rgyal //
NK115(re)001:2529: zhes mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam gyi rim pa dang mi 'dra ba'i sgras bstan cing /
NK115(re)001:2531: rang sangs rgyas mang po theg chen la zhugs nas
NK115(re)001:2532: 'ga' zhig gis sa brgyad pa thob nas phyir log
NK115(re)001:2533: par gsungs pa'i sa'i ngos 'dzin yang bshad ma thag
NK115(re)001:2534: pa de las gzhan 'phags pa'i sa brgyad pa dngos
NK115(re)001:2535: yin na shin tu mi 'thad do //
NK115(re)001:2536: des nas spyod bsdus kyi 'grel ba las kyang /
NK115(re)001:2538: gang tshe tha ma'i drod gyur nas //
NK115(re)001:2539: bzod pa chos mchog dbang du ni //
NK115(re)001:2540: rab 'bring sbyor ba bcu gnyis te //
NK115(re)001:2541: rab tu dga' ba bcu gsum pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2543: rab tu dga' nas chos kyi sprin //
NK115(re)001:2544: gang gi rjes la thob pa rnams //
NK115(re)001:2545: zung 'jug gis ni sbyong bar byed //
NK115(re)001:2546: ces sbyor lam bcu gnyis la sar btags pa gang zhig /
NK115(re)001:2547: rdor bzlas kyis brgyad pa bzod 'bring dang /
NK115(re)001:2548: sems dben gyis bcu pa dang bcu gcig pa chos mchog chung ngu'am 'bring dang /
NK115(re)001:2549: sgyu lus kyis bcu gnyis pa chos mchog chen po thob nas /
NK115(re)001:2550: 'od gsal gyis 'phags pa'i sa rab tu dga' ba
NK115(re)001:2551: sbyor lam gyi sa bcu gnyis la ltos nas bcu
NK115(re)001:2553: zung 'jug gis thob zin rnams sbyong bar gsungs pa dang tshul mthun no //
NK115(re)001:2554: gal te sa bcu pa thob kyi bar du sngags
NK115(re)001:2555: la 'jug pa'i nges pa med do zhes pa mi
NK115(re)001:2556: 'thad de / chos nyid mngon du gzigs pa'i 'phags pa sngags kyi snod ma yin par /
NK115(re)001:2557: so skye 'ching ba kun ldan sngags kyi snod yin pa rnam gzhag 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:2558: snod yin kyang sangs rgyas kyis de la sngags mi ston zhe na /
NK115(re)001:2559: sangs rgyas kyis snod dang 'tshams par chos ston par gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2560: sangs rgyas theg pa dman pas 'khrid mi mdzad /
NK115(re)001:2562: yang mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam thams cad sngags kyi lam stegs su 'gro dgos na /
NK115(re)001:2563: sngags kyi theg pa myur lam yin zhes pa ming tsam ste /
NK115(re)001:2564: thag ring por bgrod pa la rus sbal gyi nud
NK115(re)001:2565: 'gros kyis song ste sleb khar khyung gi lding stangs
NK115(re)001:2566: kyis song zer ba dang 'dra'o gsungs /
NK115(re)001:2567: des na dbang po'i khyad par gyis sngags la 'jug pa'i tshul mang yang /
NK115(re)001:2569: gzhi rigs gcig dang lam rigs bzhi //
NK115(re)001:2570: gsang chen bla med mi ldog brten //
NK115(re)001:2572: dbang rnon kha cig rgyu'i theg pa gsum po gang
NK115(re)001:2573: la yang ma zhugs par dang po nas sngags la
NK115(re)001:2575: nyan rang byang sems phyi rgyud kyi lam bzhi la
NK115(re)001:2576: bslab bzhin pa nas bla med du 'jug pa lam
NK115(re)001:2578: de dag las byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni tshogs
NK115(re)001:2579: lam du chos rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin dang po
NK115(re)001:2582: de tshe chos kyi rgyun las ni //
NK115(re)001:2583: sangs rgyas rnams la zhi gnas dang //
NK115(re)001:2584: ye shes yangs pa thob bya'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:2585: gdams ngag rgya chen rnyed par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:2587: bsam gtan las thob mngon par shes //
NK115(re)001:2588: mngon par bsgrub pa'i sgo nas ni //
NK115(re)001:2589: sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa la //
NK115(re)001:2590: mchod pa'i phyir dang mnyan pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:2592: zhes rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas las 'gyur ba med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:2593: blos dpag tu med pa'i ye shes thob pa 'i
NK115(re)001:2594: phyir 'jig rten gyi khams dpag tu med par song
NK115(re)001:2595: nas theg chen thun mong ma yin pa'i thabs la
NK115(re)001:2596: mkhas pa'i gdams ngag rgya chen po rnyed par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:2597: bar bshad pas ni don gyis sngags bla med bstan
NK115(re)001:2599: de ltar na rgyu'i theg chen dang phyi rgyud gsum
NK115(re)001:2600: nas lam dang 'bras bu kha tshang re bstan na'ang
NK115(re)001:2601: rang rang gi lam dngos bstan des 'bras bu de
NK115(re)001:2603: dper na sems tsam pa'i lta ba de dang ldan
NK115(re)001:2604: pas lam bsgrub kyang mthong lam tsam yang mi thob
NK115(re)001:2606: des na 'phags sa thob na grangs med gnyis la
NK115(re)001:2607: sogs par mgo dang yan lag la sogs pa gtong
NK115(re)001:2609: dang po sems bskyed pa rnams dus ring po dka'
NK115(re)001:2610: spyad de lta bu gzhan don du byed par dam
NK115(re)001:2611: bca' ba'i spobs pa bskyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:2612: sngags lam la zhugs na de thams cad mi dgos
NK115(re)001:2613: par bde myur gyi lam 'di 'dra'o snyam du brod
NK115(re)001:2614: pa bskyed pa'i phyir yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:2615: don la 'phags lam gyi ye shes dang sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:2616: ting nge 'dzin ngo bo gcig pa'i rnam par 'phrul
NK115(re)001:2617: pas gdul bya rnams la skad cig bskal par ston
NK115(re)001:2618: nus pas grangs med mang por tshogs bsags par ston
NK115(re)001:2619: pa dang / mgo sogs gtong bar ston pa yang
NK115(re)001:2620: ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par 'phrul pas de ltar
NK115(re)001:2621: bstan pa las rang mtshan pa med do //
NK115(re)001:2622: de bas na don gyi cha nas sngags kyi lam kho na nges don yin pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:2623: 'phags pa yab sras kyi rim lngar yang /
NK115(re)001:2624: bskyed rim med par rdzogs rim sgrub mi nus la /
NK115(re)001:2625: dben gsum med par kun rdzob kyi bden pa rtogs mi nus shing /
NK115(re)001:2626: de med par don dam pa'i 'od gsal rtogs par mi nus la /
NK115(re)001:2627: de med par zung 'jug sgrub mi nus par bshad pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:2628: de'i phyir lugs 'di la 'od gsal ni 'phags pa'i
NK115(re)001:2629: bden mthong gi lam dang zung 'jug ni mi slob
NK115(re)001:2630: pa'i lam mo // gnyis pa slob dpon dang slob ma'i mtshan nyid bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:2631: de la gsang sngags kyi dngos grub thams cad ni
NK115(re)001:2632: bla ma'i byin rlabs 'ba' zhig la rags las pas
NK115(re)001:2633: slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid shes pa'i tshul la gnyis
NK115(re)001:2635: de la dabnga bskur ba ni sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:2636: sa bon slob ma'i rgyud la 'jog pa yin na
NK115(re)001:2637: / slob dpona ngan pas de lta bu mi nus pas lam gyi gegs chen po yin te /
NK115(re)001:2638: de yang rang nyid kyis dbang ma thob par gsang
NK115(re)001:2639: sngags rang dgar len zhing brgyud pa gsum gang dang
NK115(re)001:2640: yang mi ldan pa'i bcos ma'i chos kyis dad ldan
NK115(re)001:2641: bslu ba'i blun po gzu lum can dang /
NK115(re)001:2642: lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gnyis kyi
NK115(re)001:2643: don khong du ma chud cing nyams len gyi gdenga
NK115(re)001:2644: dang brala bzhin rdul mtshon gyi las dang cho ga'i
NK115(re)001:2645: rim pa tsam shes pa la mkhas par rlom pa
NK115(re)001:2646: dang / rang gi che ba'am grags pa nyams su
NK115(re)001:2647: dogs nas gdams pa nod pa'i yul de bya bral
NK115(re)001:2648: ba'am ri khrod pa la sogs pa zhig yin na
NK115(re)001:2649: de rang gi bla ma yin par mi brjod par
NK115(re)001:2651: thob dang mnga' thang can zhig rang gi bla ma yin par sgrogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:2652: rgyud las phyi nang gi dbang ma bskur bar slob
NK115(re)001:2653: dpon byed pa ni dam tshig nyams pa'i spyod pa'o
NK115(re)001:2654: // mkhas pa la mi mkhas par sgro 'dogs pa yang dam tshig nyams pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2655: mi mkhas pa la mkhas par che ba 'byin par byed par yang dam tshig nyams pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2656: bka' nod pa'i slob dpon gyi khungs bsubs nas rang
NK115(re)001:2657: dad pa'i phyogs la khungs 'byin par byed pa yang
NK115(re)001:2658: dam tshig nyams pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2660: de bzhin du rigs rus dang cho 'brang sogs kyis rgyags nas rang gi bsti gansa te 'dug gnas /
NK115(re)001:2661: dgon sde dang grong khyim dang bla brang sogs kyi 'go 'dzin dang bya byed kyis g.yeng zhing /
NK115(re)001:2662: gtsug lag khang dang dge 'dun gyi dkora rdzas la byung rgyal du spyod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2663: sdom pa gsum gyi bsrung mtshams mi shes shing bslab
NK115(re)001:2664: pa la mi gus pas sgo gsum ma bsdamsa shing
NK115(re)001:2666: las 'bras la yid mi ches shing longs spyood la
NK115(re)001:2667: zhen chags che bas sbyin bdag sogs kyi khyima la
NK115(re)001:2668: chagas shing gson gshin gyi longs spyod sdud pa dang
NK115(re)001:2669: / nyon mongs dang gdug rtsub che bas byams pa dang snying rje chung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2670: rgyud dang sde snod kyi gnas la shes rab kyi
NK115(re)001:2671: mig zum pas ltar snang rtog ge zol mas zil
NK115(re)001:2672: gyis nona nas gang la yang phod pa che ba
NK115(re)001:2673: desa ni dabnga bskura bar byasa kyang /
NK115(re)001:2674: dper na be'u sbrela ma gcig g.yang du lhung na
NK115(re)001:2675: gcig shos kyang des drud nas lhung 'gro ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:2676: slob ma dad ldan zhig yin yang de'i skyon gyis
NK115(re)001:2677: skyon can du gyur te gnyis ka ngan song gi
NK115(re)001:2680: dkon mchog dkor la rngam sems can //
NK115(re)001:2681: khyim la chags nas nag chang brten //
NK115(re)001:2682: slob ma 'chal zhing las la brtson //
NK115(re)001:2683: tshong dang khe spogs lhu ru len //
NK115(re)001:2684: snying rje med cing srog chags gsod //
NK115(re)001:2686: de bsten dmyal bar 'phen par byed //
NK115(re)001:2689: dad ldan gcig bslus sems can brgya bsad pas //
NK115(re)001:2690: sdig pa shin tu che bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK115(re)001:2691: de phyir rang 'dod bslu ba'i chos mi bshad //
NK115(re)001:2694: thog mar gsang sngags kyi dbang bskur zhing lam ston pa'i bla ma de /
NK115(re)001:2695: 1lta 2sgom 3spyod pa'i mdzod dang ldan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2696: dbang bzhi chu bo yongs su rdzogs 4pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2697: blo rim dang 'tshams par slob ma rjes su 'dzin pa'i don gnyer dang ldan 5pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2698: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud don dang las bzhi'i phrin las sgrub pa la mkhas 6pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2699: lag len gyi man ngag shes 7pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2700: nyams myong gi drod dang ldan 8pa ste yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa zhig dgos par gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:2702: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:2703: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK115(re)001:2704: man ngag drod dang brgyad 'chang ba //
NK115(re)001:2707: brtan zhing dul la g.yo sgyu med //
NK115(re)001:2708: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor ba shes //
NK115(re)001:2709: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK115(re)001:2710: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK115(re)001:2711: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK115(re)001:2712: zhes pa'i de nyid bcu la phyi nang gsang gsum gyis dbye bas sum cu ste /
NK115(re)001:2713: de la phyi yi de nyid bcu ni /
NK115(re)001:2714: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:2718: slar bsdud 10pa yi rnam pa ni //
NK115(re)001:2719: phyi yi de nyid bcu yin no //
NK115(re)001:2720: zhes pa ltar phyi rgyud dang bstun pa'i dkyil 'khor bri ba la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2721: bskyed rdzogs kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2724: las bzhi la sogs pa'i 'dug stangs dang /
NK115(re)001:2725: snying po bzlas brjod byed pa'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:2726: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg gi rim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2727: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2728: bsnyen sgrub kyi mthar thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i las la sbyor ba'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:2729: bskyed pa'i lha thams cad bsdu rim gyis mi dmigs
NK115(re)001:2730: par 'jog pa slar sdud pa'i rnam pa ste bcu'o
NK115(re)001:2731: // nanga gi de nyid bcu ni /
NK115(re)001:2732: dkyil 'khor bri ba la sogs pa de dag nang rgyud dang bstan pa la zer ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:2733: gasnga ba'i de nyid bcu ni /
NK115(re)001:2739: drag shul sgrub pa'i cho ga 8dang //
NK115(re)001:2741: gsang ba'i de nyid bcu yin no //
NK115(re)001:2742: zhes pas rnam pa bcu ste /
NK115(re)001:2743: bla na med pa gsang ba'i rgyud 'dir 'jig rten
NK115(re)001:2744: pa dang grub mtha' phal cher gyi blo yul du
NK115(re)001:2745: mi chud pa'i las kyi rang bzhin shes na thabs
NK115(re)001:2747: khro bcu la sogs pa'i srung 'khor bsgoms nas bar chad phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2748: bris pa'i srung 'khor gyis phyir bzlog pa'i mngon spyod kyi las rnam pa gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:2749: ltar snang 'jig rten pa'i kun spyod dang mthun pas
NK115(re)001:2750: ma dad pa skye ba'i phyir shin tu gsang zhing
NK115(re)001:2751: sba ba'i gnas gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2752: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba gnyis la brten pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2753: de bzhin du kha sbyor 'byed pa'i cho ga ste sgrol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2754: gtor ma sbyang rtog sbar gsum gyis 'khor 'das kyi mgron la mchod pa sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:2755: 'byung 'jug gnas gsum dang bstun pa'i rdo rje'i bzlas pa bya ba sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:2756: las ma grub pas btsan thabs sam spogs pa'i cho gas lha la drag shul bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2757: rten dang dkyil 'khor la rab gnas byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2758: rdul tshon la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i cho
NK115(re)001:2759: ga yang 'khor ba dang rnam pa mthun pa srid
NK115(re)001:2760: pa skye ba'i rim pa dang sbyar nas 'dod pa
NK115(re)001:2761: bsten pa dang mngal 'byin la sogs pa'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:2763: tshul de rnams ji lta ba bzhin riga cinga khog
NK115(re)001:2764: du chud pa ni gsang sngags kyi dbang bskur byed
NK115(re)001:2765: nus pa'i rdo rje slob dpon yin la /
NK115(re)001:2766: de yang de tsam gyi gzugs brnyan shes pas mi chog ste /
NK115(re)001:2767: gsang sngags kyi lta ba rtogs shing sgom pas ranga
NK115(re)001:2768: nyid kyi rgyud grola ba zhig la bsten pa gces
NK115(re)001:2770: rang ma smin pas gzhan smin mi nus shing /
NK115(re)001:2771: rang ma grol bas gzhan grol bar mi nus pas so //
NK115(re)001:2772: de skad du sam+bu ta las /
NK115(re)001:2773: slob dpon smin pa'i las kyis ni //
NK115(re)001:2774: slob ma yongs su smin par bya //
NK115(re)001:2777: rang tha mal du bsdud pas gzhan smin par mi nus /
NK115(re)001:2780: rgyud la yon tan skye ba'i sa bon thebs nas
NK115(re)001:2781: chos dang bla ma la rkyen gang gis kyang mi
NK115(re)001:2783: dal 'byor rnyed dka' nas brtsams te lam gyi yon tan rnams bcos min du skyes nas /
NK115(re)001:2784: dbang po'i khyad par gyis nyin zhag gam /
NK115(re)001:2785: lo zla la sogs pa snga phyi'i blo la khyad par chen po thob pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:2786: de las gzhan du slob ma'i rgyud gong nas gong
NK115(re)001:2787: du dkri ba'i rgyu rang gi yon tan dbang don
NK115(re)001:2788: gyi ye shes rtogs pa lta ci smos /
NK115(re)001:2789: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK115(re)001:2790: sngags sdom gyi mtshan nyid tsam yang mi shes pas spang blang bgyid pa'i blo tsam yang med bzhin /
NK115(re)001:2791: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2792: sngags 'chang ngam grub thob kyi ming btags na rdo
NK115(re)001:2793: rje slob dpon gyi gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa rnams ku
NK115(re)001:2795: dar sna'i phur ma sogs rten dang yo byad kyi shom ra che ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2796: cho ga'i bshad sbyar dang lag len la byang ba tsam gyis gzhan rgyud smin par re ba ni /
NK115(re)001:2797: rdzing bu na ma mchis pa yur bar 'dren pa la re ba bzhin bzhad bgad kyi gnas so //
NK115(re)001:2798: des na gong du ji skad bshad pa de lta bu'i bla ma yisa /
NK115(re)001:2799: gang la dbang bskur ba'i slob ma'i mtshan nyid rgyas par sngar bstan pa bzhin la mdor bsdu na /
NK115(re)001:2800: dad pa med na bla ma'i thugs rje dang byin
