NK115(re)001:2801: rlabs 'jug pa'i go skabs med pas bla ma dang
NK115(re)001:2802: gsang sngags kyi chos la yid ches kyi dada pa
NK115(re)001:2803: dang mos gus yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2804: ngo tsha shes pa med na dbang dus su thob
NK115(re)001:2805: pa'i sdom pa dang dam tshig la nyes ltung gis
NK115(re)001:2806: sgribs te dngos grub kyi gegs su 'gyur zhing nyams
NK115(re)001:2807: pa gsor mi chud pas ngan song gi gting rdor
NK115(re)001:2808: 'gyur bas ngo tsha dang khrel yod shesa pa la
NK115(re)001:2809: sogs pa'i snod kyi yon tan sloba ma'i rgyud na
NK115(re)001:2810: ldan nam mi ldan brtag pa gal che ste /
NK115(re)001:2812: ji ltar rin chen brdar ba dang //
NK115(re)001:2813: gser ni bsreg dang bcad pas brtag /
NK115(re)001:2814: de bzhin du ni slob ma yang //
NK115(re)001:2815: lo ni bcu gnyis bar du brtag /
NK115(re)001:2816: de phyir phan tshun de lta bus //
NK115(re)001:2817: dus kun tu ni de ltar brtag /
NK115(re)001:2819: dngos grub 'joms shing sdug bsngal ster //
NK115(re)001:2821: gal te ma brtag par thug phrad du'am gsar nges
NK115(re)001:2822: kyis snod ngan la dbang bskur na slob ma'i don
NK115(re)001:2823: 'chor ba'i tshul sngar yang bshad la /
NK115(re)001:2824: slob dpon gyi dngos grub nyams shing ji ltar bsgos
NK115(re)001:2825: shing gnyer du gtang pa'i dam tshig rnams bsrung mi
NK115(re)001:2826: nus pas dngos grub kyi rtsa ba chad nas tshe
NK115(re)001:2827: 'dir phyi nang gi 'tshe ba dang tshe thung ba
NK115(re)001:2829: phyi mar ngan song du 'gro ba'i phyir na snod dang snod min legs par brtagsa la /
NK115(re)001:2830: dabnga bskura ba yang blo dang 'tshams par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:2831: dbang dngos gzhi bskur ba'i snod du mi rung ba
NK115(re)001:2832: la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa tsam byed pa dang
NK115(re)001:2833: / dad brtson dang ni ldan kyang zab dbang bskur
NK115(re)001:2834: ba'i snod du ni mi rung ba la bum dbang
NK115(re)001:2835: / tsam dang / yang zab mo'i dbang gi lam
NK115(re)001:2836: gyi brtul zhugs la slob nus pa rnams la dbang
NK115(re)001:2837: gong ma gsum dang bcas pa bskur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:2838: de ltar zab dbang gi snod du rung ba zhig
NK115(re)001:2839: yin na'ang thod rgal du bum dbang ma bskur ba'am
NK115(re)001:2840: go rim 'chol ba ma yin par dkyil 'khor du
NK115(re)001:2841: bcug ste bum dbang nas dbang bzhi po rima pa
NK115(re)001:2842: bzhin ma nor bas sbyin para bya dgos kyi /
NK115(re)001:2843: de ltar ma byas na slob bu dad can yin yang rgyud chud zos par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:2845: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK115(re)001:2846: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK115(re)001:2847: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK115(re)001:2848: snying rjes chud ma zos par zung //
NK115(re)001:2850: gsum pa dbang bskur dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:2851: dbang gi yan lag bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:2852: dbang gi dngos gzhi bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:2853: dbang thob pa'i phan yon bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2854: dang po dbang gi yan lag bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:2855: thog mar rdo rje slob dpon rang nyid kyi rgyud
NK115(re)001:2856: dag cing slob ma smin nus par bya ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:2857: bsnyen pa bya ba dang ni /
NK115(re)001:2858: bdag po'i gzhi la dbang mi za zhing sa dang
NK115(re)001:2859: sar 'dzin gyi rtog pa dbyings su mnyam par bya
NK115(re)001:2860: ba'i sa yi cho ga dang /
NK115(re)001:2861: dkyil 'khor dang slob ma'i las la thod rgal du
NK115(re)001:2862: mi 'jug pa sta gona gyi rim pa dang ni
NK115(re)001:2863: / sloba ma'i rgyud rim gyis dag cing smin par
NK115(re)001:2864: bya ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor du 'juga pa sngon du
NK115(re)001:2866: zhugs pa de la smin byed kyi dbang dngos bskur
NK115(re)001:2867: ba ste cho ga'i mngona rtogsa bzhi po de re
NK115(re)001:2869: yan lag bzhi re bzhi rer yongs su tshang zhing rdzogas dgos pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:2870: dang po bsnyen pa'i yan lag bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:2872: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK115(re)001:2873: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po'o //
NK115(re)001:2878: sgrub pa chen po bzhi yin la /
NK115(re)001:2879: de yang spyir lam rim las /
NK115(re)001:2880: 'di yang lam sgrub sbyor ba yis //
NK115(re)001:2884: sbyor dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ste rnam pa gsum gsungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:2885: dang po ni zag bcas lam gyi rnal 'byor lnga
NK115(re)001:2886: po mos sgom tsam ma yin par nges rdzogs kyi
NK115(re)001:2887: tshul du bsgom pa'i rim pa dang sbyar te stong
NK115(re)001:2889: snying rje 2sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor gnyis bsnyen pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2891: phyag rgya spros bcas 4gnyis nye bsnyen dang /
NK115(re)001:2892: tshom bu tshogs sgrub 5ni sgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2893: de'i 'bras bu mthong lam thob ma rag pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK115(re)001:2895: byang chub sems rtogs 'grus pa ni //
NK115(re)001:2896: bsnyen pa'i dam pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:2897: sems chas snying rje man chad do //
NK115(re)001:2898: phyag rgya gsal ba nye bsnyen pa //
NK115(re)001:2899: de phyir gcig dang spros pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2900: sgrub pa nyid ni bar chad med //
NK115(re)001:2901: dus kyi tshogs mthas sgrub chen len //
NK115(re)001:2903: sbyor dus kyi yan lag bzhi ni 'dir ma bshad cing /
NK115(re)001:2904: skabs 'dir ni sgrub dus kyi yan lag bzhi bshad par bya ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:2905: de yang lam rim las rnal 'byor lnga'i tshogs sgrub kyi dbang du byas nas gsungs pa yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:2906: 'dir slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i sngon du slob dpon gyis bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:2907: de la gzhi bsnyen dang las bsnyen gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:2909: grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa gsum gsungs pa las
NK115(re)001:2910: da lta phyi ma gnyis po gang rung dgos par
NK115(re)001:2911: bshad do // de la grangs bsnyen ni /
NK115(re)001:2912: bye ba yin par yang gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:2915: zhes gsungs pa la sogs pa'o /
NK115(re)001:2917: dus shin tu snyigs mar gyur pas de'i bzhi 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:2918: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa ni grub pa'i rtags mtshan thon pa'o //
NK115(re)001:2919: de ltar gzhi'i bsnyen pa ci tsam byed pa'i zhag
NK115(re)001:2920: grangs kyis bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi tshang ba yin
NK115(re)001:2921: te / zhag dang po sgrub rdzas dang yo byad
NK115(re)001:2922: sta gon byas nas cho ga tshar gcig gtong ba
NK115(re)001:2923: te / bsnyen pa / de nas sgrub pa ci
NK115(re)001:2924: tsam byed pa pa'i zhag grangs kyi phyed snga ma
NK115(re)001:2925: la 'od zer dkar po'i spro bsdus sdig sgrib sbyong
NK115(re)001:2926: ba'i dmigs pa gtso bor byed pa nye bsnyen /
NK115(re)001:2927: de phyin chad phyed phyi ma la 'od zer dmar
NK115(re)001:2928: po'i spro bsdus mchog thun mong gi dngos grub rang
NK115(re)001:2929: la bsdu ba'i dmigs pa gtso bor byed pa sgrub
NK115(re)001:2930: pa / zhag tha ma la 'od zer mthing ga
NK115(re)001:2931: tshur bsdu bas dngos grub len pa sgrub pa chen
NK115(re)001:2932: pa / po ste / lam rim las /
NK115(re)001:2933: zla phyed phyed gzhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK115(re)001:2935: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK115(re)001:2937: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK115(re)001:2938: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK115(re)001:2939: zhes gsungs pa dang phyogs mthun no //
NK115(re)001:2940: las bsnyen ni slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i dus su bsnyen pa kha gso ba'o //
NK115(re)001:2941: de gnyis ka la cho ga'i thun gcig dang sbyar
NK115(re)001:2942: te bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi tshang ba'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:2943: / phur pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:2944: spyir na gsang sngags nges pa la //
NK115(re)001:2945: ting 'dzin gsum bskyed bsnyen pa yin //
NK115(re)001:2946: bdag nyid lhar bskyed nye bsnyen te //
NK115(re)001:2947: yum bskyed sgrub par shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:2948: gzhan rnams sgrub pa chen po yin //
NK115(re)001:2950: ting 'dzin gsum bsgom pa yan chad bsnyen pa /
NK115(re)001:2951: rang lha gtso bor bsgom pa nye bsnyen /
NK115(re)001:2952: yum bsgoms te mkha' gsang brlabs pa dang 'khor gyi lha tshogs tshang bar sgom pa sgrub pa /
NK115(re)001:2953: dbang bskur rgyas gdab spyan 'dren sogs nas bzlas pa mchod bstod sogs sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK115(re)001:2954: gnyis pa sa chog gi yan lag bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:2955: de ltar slob dpon rang nyid kyis bsnyen pa sngon du grub nas gzhan la phan gdags pa la /
NK115(re)001:2956: dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub sogs kyi las rim ni /
NK115(re)001:2958: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshang thig dang //
NK115(re)001:2959: tshon dang bri ba rnam pa dang //
NK115(re)001:2960: rab gnas sbyin bsreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK115(re)001:2961: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK115(re)001:2962: zhes don rnam pa bcu gsungs pa las lhag ma rnams 'chad 'gyur ltar las //
NK115(re)001:2963: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa'i don ni /
NK115(re)001:2965: gzhi dang rang mtshan bslang dbang dang //
NK115(re)001:2966: sbyang byin bsrung dang gzung ba ni //
NK115(re)001:2967: dang po'i nying lag nyid du bshad //
NK115(re)001:2968: ces pa ltar rnam grangs bdun gsungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:2969: dang po sa der dkyil 'khor bya rung mi rung brtag pa ni /
NK115(re)001:2971: grong dang dur khrod tshong 'dus dang //
NK115(re)001:2972: tshal dang lha khang grong khyer gyi //
NK115(re)001:2973: shar dang byang gi sa gzhi shis //
NK115(re)001:2974: lho dang nub phyogs de lta min //
NK115(re)001:2976: de nas gzhal ba'i phyi rol gyi shar dang byang gi gzhi shis pa'i sar gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2977: spyi gnam sa bar gsum la dpyad de sa'i gzhi la brtag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:2978: bye brag sa rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag pa sogs mang du gsungs pas dpyad dka' yang /
NK115(re)001:2979: rnal 'byor pa'i yid la rang bzhin gyis bde ba ster ba la bkag pa med de /
NK115(re)001:2980: yang na yid ni gang dga' ba //
NK115(re)001:2981: de rnams su ni dkyil 'khor bri //
NK115(re)001:2984: phun sum tshogs pa kun bzang ba'i //
NK115(re)001:2985: tshogs pa dag ni rnyed par dka' //
NK115(re)001:2986: mdor na sa gzhi mnyam pa dang //
NK115(re)001:2987: mdangs snum shar du gzhol ba bzhed //
NK115(re)001:2988: chu mang ldan pa'i gnas dang ni //
NK115(re)001:2989: ljon shing bzang pos brgyan pa dang //
NK115(re)001:2990: bdag gi yid ni mgu ba dang //
NK115(re)001:2991: 'tshe med zug rngu spang ba ni //
NK115(re)001:2992: dkyil 'khor gnas su shis pa ste //
NK115(re)001:2993: mi yi dngos grub kun thob byed //
NK115(re)001:2995: gnyis pa sa bslang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:2996: brtags nas rung bar mthong na /
NK115(re)001:2997: sa de'i bdag po rgyal po la sogs pa la
NK115(re)001:2998: rin 'jal ba'am tshig gis bkrol nas sa gzhi de
NK115(re)001:2999: la rang dbang thob par bya ba snang ba mi
NK115(re)001:3001: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la 'dod don gsol zhing /
NK115(re)001:3002: sa'i lha mo sa bdag gzhi bdag gi 'khor dang
NK115(re)001:3003: bcas pa la gtor ma phul nas gnang ba zhu
NK115(re)001:3004: ba ni mi snang ba lha la bslang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3005: gsum pa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3006: zangs sam shing dmar po las byas pa'i phur bu
NK115(re)001:3007: pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i dbang mchog gi phur
NK115(re)001:3008: bu gdab pas dbang du bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3011: sbyang ba las me sngags phyag rgya //
NK115(re)001:3012: ting nge 'dzin gyis dag par bya //
NK115(re)001:3013: zhes pas rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3014: dang po las dang bya bas sbyang ba ni //
NK115(re)001:3015: sa gzhi thig gis grub bzhir bcad pa'i phyogs re
NK115(re)001:3016: rer zla ba gsum gsum gyi zhag grangs dang mthun
NK115(re)001:3017: pa'i re'u mig dgu bcu re phye la lto 'phye'i
NK115(re)001:3019: ston zla ra ba'i tshes gcig la dbang ldan gyi mtshams kyi re'u mig tu mgo bo dang /
NK115(re)001:3020: srin po'i phyogs kyi re'u mig tu mjug rtse bzhag
NK115(re)001:3021: nas nyal ba'i mtshan nyid kyis nyi zhag re la
NK115(re)001:3022: re'u mig rer gdong ngos nas bgrod pa'i g.yas skor
NK115(re)001:3023: gyi 'pho bas lo gcig la rdzogs par 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:3024: tshul shes pas lto ba'i thad nas sa brkos la
NK115(re)001:3025: chu dang sa'i sgo nas pra brtag cing gter bcug
NK115(re)001:3026: ste / stegs bu dbus bgas kyis mtho zhing shar
NK115(re)001:3027: dang byang yid tsam gzhol ba brtsigs pa la ba
NK115(re)001:3028: byung dang rdzas sum cus skyang nul bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3029: gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3030: mtshan ma ngan na zhi ba'i sbyin bsreg bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3031: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3033: ha na ha na kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK115(re)001:3035: lag pa tri sh+au la'i phyag rgya'am /
NK115(re)001:3036: rdo rje'i rang bzhin las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis sa gzhi rdo rjer byin gyis brlabs par bsam pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3037: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3038: sbyang bya sbyong byed kyi spros pa zhi ba'i chos
NK115(re)001:3039: nyid la mnyam par 'jog pa mtshan med stong pa
NK115(re)001:3041: de'i ngang las gzhi der gzhal yas khang gdan dang
NK115(re)001:3042: bcas pa bsgom pa mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:3043: te de gnyis kyi sgo nas sbyang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3044: 'di yan chad phal cher dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa gsar du bsgrub pa la dgongs pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:3045: dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa rnying par rdul tshon gyis bzhengs na /
NK115(re)001:3046: mi mngon pa la bslang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3047: rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3048: gzung ba ste byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3049: bsrung ba dang bzhi po bya la /
NK115(re)001:3050: ras bris yin na gzung ba byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3051: bsrung ba tsam gyis chog par gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:3052: lnga pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3053: slob dpon rdo rje'i 'gros kyis shar sgo nas zhugs
NK115(re)001:3054: te dbus su gnas pas bdag nyid gtso bo yab
NK115(re)001:3055: yum du bskyed pa'i sems sprin las 'khor rnams spro
NK115(re)001:3056: zhing / mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba rnams mchod nas /
NK115(re)001:3057: yum bzhi'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa'i phyogs bzhi'i slob ma
NK115(re)001:3058: bzhis slob dpon la mchod cing gsol ba btab rjes
NK115(re)001:3059: / slob dpon gyis rgyal ba rnams bskul zhing byin
NK115(re)001:3060: bsdus nas rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje'i snyems pas
NK115(re)001:3061: 'bar ba'i spyan dang rdo rje'i 'gros kyis sa gzhi
NK115(re)001:3062: rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3065: nam mkha' khyab pa'i rtsibs bcu la //
NK115(re)001:3066: nyi steng sum+b+hasa lha rnams mnan //
NK115(re)001:3067: khro bcu thugs las nges byung dgod //
NK115(re)001:3068: ces pa ltar bgegs kyi gtso bo phyogs skyong bcu bkug nas khro bcu'i phur bu gdab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3069: mtshon cha lnga'i rwa bas bsrung bar bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3071: lha sta gon dang gcig pas 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:3072: 'dir sa chog yan lag bzhir bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3073: dkyil 'khor khang pa rnyings par byed pa mang bas /
NK115(re)001:3075: sa bzung ba zhes pa skabs 'dir sa gzhi byin
NK115(re)001:3076: gyis brlabs pa la bshad pas de gnyis don gcig
NK115(re)001:3077: par song la / dbang du bya ba yang der 'du rung bas na /
NK115(re)001:3082: gsum pa sta gon la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3088: sa lha spyan drangs te gtor ma phul nas phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3089: sngar sa chog gi skabs su yod pas 'dir mi byed pa mang bas med kyang rung la /
NK115(re)001:3090: byas kyang lhag pa'i nyes pa med de /
NK115(re)001:3091: rdo rje phreng ba las de ltar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:3092: gnyis pa lha sta gon ni de ma byas na
NK115(re)001:3093: lha la dbang za zhing brnyas pa'i nyes pa yod
NK115(re)001:3094: pas snyan gsan dbab pa'i don du ste /
NK115(re)001:3095: 'di'i skabs su sngar rdo rje las rim nas bshad
NK115(re)001:3096: pa'i don bcu'i nang nas dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la
NK115(re)001:3097: sogs pa'ang bshad par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:3098: de la gnyis pa tshad ni /
NK115(re)001:3099: lha'i rigs kyi sgo nas bzhag na /
NK115(re)001:3104: don grub kyi rigs rnams la je cher spar ba'i tshul te /
NK115(re)001:3106: rdo rje can gyi khru gsum ste //
NK115(re)001:3107: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor khru bzhi pa //
NK115(re)001:3108: khru lnga pa ni snang byed la'o //
NK115(re)001:3109: gar gyi dbang phyug khru drug pa //
NK115(re)001:3110: rta yi rgyal po khru bdun pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3112: gnas khang yangs dogs la sogs pa'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK115(re)001:3114: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK115(re)001:3115: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK115(re)001:3116: zhes pa chung tshad gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:3117: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK115(re)001:3118: yang na khru ni bcu drug dang //
NK115(re)001:3120: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lngar bya //
NK115(re)001:3121: zhes pa che tshad gnyis te drug gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:3122: sbyin bdag gi 'byor ba'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK115(re)001:3124: 'dzam bu'i gling gi dbang phyug gam //
NK115(re)001:3125: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po yis //
NK115(re)001:3126: kun nas dpag tshad mtha' ru ni //
NK115(re)001:3127: dkyil 'khor rab tu bri bar bya //
NK115(re)001:3129: rgyal po la sogs pas yon sbyar na dpag tshad tsam yang ma bkag la /
NK115(re)001:3130: gdul bya'i khams dang 'byor ba'i dbang du lag mthil nyid du'ang bri bar gsungs ste /
NK115(re)001:3132: lag pa'i mthil du bris byas nas //
NK115(re)001:3133: zhes lag gis bri bar ma nus pa rnams yid kyis bri bar gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:3135: rgyu tshad kha dog la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid legs
NK115(re)001:3136: par tshang ba'i thig skud rab gnas kyis byin gyis
NK115(re)001:3137: brlabs pa'i dam thig ye thig gnyis byas la /
NK115(re)001:3138: thig g.yog rig ma dngos sam der mos pa la
NK115(re)001:3139: thig sna gtad de yab yum lhar gsal ba'i ngang
NK115(re)001:3140: nas dam thig sngon du btab ste sku gsung thugs
NK115(re)001:3142: de nas ye thig nam mkha' btab pas /
NK115(re)001:3143: dam tshig pa'i rang bzhin la ye shes lnga lngas rgyas 'debs pa'i tshul gyis sam /
NK115(re)001:3144: yang na ye thig sngon du btab pas ye shes
NK115(re)001:3145: kyi dkyil 'khor las sprul pa'i tshul du dam tshig
NK115(re)001:3146: gi dkyil 'khor 'char ba'i don du de nas dam
NK115(re)001:3147: thig gdab par bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:3148: gang ltar yang thig sna ma shor ba sogs gdab
NK115(re)001:3149: tshul gyi nyes pa thams cad spangs te gdab par
NK115(re)001:3150: bya ba sogs zhib par thig gi cho ga so
NK115(re)001:3152: de ltar las thig gi bya ba sngon du btang nas /
NK115(re)001:3154: thig gis mtshon pa'i lha'i gnas so sor dri bzang dang /
NK115(re)001:3155: bdud rtsi lngas gtso bo'i gnas su gru bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:3156: 'khor gyi gnas su zlum po byas la so so'i
NK115(re)001:3157: sngags brjod cing me tog gi tshom bu bkod nas
NK115(re)001:3158: rten du dmigs pa byas la /
NK115(re)001:3159: mthar mchod pas bskor nas byin gyis brlabs spro zhing
NK115(re)001:3160: nus na dam tshig gi 'khor lo ji lta ba
NK115(re)001:3161: bzhin bskyed nas ye shes pa gzhug cing goms pa
NK115(re)001:3162: brtan pas ni sa bon gyis bskyed pas kyang rung
NK115(re)001:3163: la / sngar sa chog gi skabs su bskyed nas
NK115(re)001:3164: nam mkhar bteg pa yin na de nyid phab pas
NK115(re)001:3165: la / kyang chog ste / he ru ka 'dus pa las /
NK115(re)001:3166: thig gdab cho ga ji bzhin bya //
NK115(re)001:3167: dri yi thig les mtshan ma dgod //
NK115(re)001:3168: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor phab cing mchod //
NK115(re)001:3170: de la lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i mchod pas mchod
NK115(re)001:3171: nas sta gon la gnas par gsol ba gdab pa'i
NK115(re)001:3172: mthar gzhi de nyid du thim par mos la tshom
NK115(re)001:3174: gsum pa bum pa sta gon ni /
NK115(re)001:3175: rgyu dbyibs tshad la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK115(re)001:3176: pa'i bum pa mgul chings kha rgyan dang ldan pa
NK115(re)001:3177: lha grangs sam / gtso bum tsam yin kyang rung ste /
NK115(re)001:3178: phyi rgyud dang thun mong gi rdzas nyer lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:3179: bla med thun min gyi rdzas bcu ste bcud so
NK115(re)001:3180: lngas gtams pa'i bum pa lha grangs yod na lha
NK115(re)001:3182: dgu yod na sgo mtshams brgyad dang dbus su dang /
NK115(re)001:3183: gcig las med na dbus su bzhag par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:3184: de lta bu'i bum pa'i dngos pos sprul sku /
NK115(re)001:3186: nang gi bsil ba'i ngo bor chos sku //
NK115(re)001:3187: lha bsgom pas ngo bo nyid sku rnams mtshon no //
NK115(re)001:3188: de nas bsang sbyangs byas te lha bskyed tshul yang de bzhin du grangs dang bstun la /
NK115(re)001:3189: rnam bum gcig pu las med na thams cad der bskyed par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3190: las bum shar sgo'i g.yon du 'god pa rgya gar ba'i lugs yin la /
NK115(re)001:3191: yang na rang gi mdun du'o //
NK115(re)001:3192: bzhi pa slob ma sta gon ni /
NK115(re)001:3193: sbyor ba ni slob ma khrus byas /
NK115(re)001:3194: man+dala phul nas 'dug pa la blo bcos nas /
NK115(re)001:3195: dngos gzhi ni nang dbang bskur nas sdom pa bzung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3196: ltas brtag pa phyi nang gnyis rnams las dang po
NK115(re)001:3197: nang dbang gi don po 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK115(re)001:3198: tshab tu dbang bskur ba la de'i rigs kyi bur
NK115(re)001:3199: bskrun pa zhig dgos pa dang 'dra bar /
NK115(re)001:3200: rdo rje slob dpon gyi chos srid la dbang bskur
NK115(re)001:3201: phyir slob ma nyid rdo rje'i bla ma'i sras su
NK115(re)001:3202: bsgrub dgos pas / slob ma'i rnam smin gyi phung
NK115(re)001:3203: po sbyangs nas rnam par shes pa sras su bskrun
NK115(re)001:3204: pa'i sbyor ba byas te dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor
NK115(re)001:3205: bzhag pa ni slob ma la bu zhes 'bod pa'i
NK115(re)001:3207: de nas slob mas gsol ba btab ste slob dpon gyis de la thun mong dang /
NK115(re)001:3208: thun mong ma yin pa'i sdom pa sbyin par bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:3209: skabs 'di dang dngos gzhi'i mgor 'bogs pa la khyad par med par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:3210: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags dang chus bsrung la /
NK115(re)001:3211: slob ma lhar bskyed pa'i sgo gsum rdo rje gsum
NK115(re)001:3212: du byin gyis brlabs pa sogs byas la 'dod yon
NK115(re)001:3213: lngas mchod cing 'dod yon la sred pa spangs te
NK115(re)001:3214: bsod nams kyi tshogs su gyis shig par basgo'o //
NK115(re)001:3215: de nas sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyong ba dang
NK115(re)001:3216: 'brel bar ltas brtag pa'i phyir dang po so shing
NK115(re)001:3217: dor ba ngag gi sgrib pa dag pa'i ched dang
NK115(re)001:3218: / khyor chu sbyin pa yid kyi sgrib pa dag pa'i ched dang /
NK115(re)001:3219: srung skud bcing ba lus kyi sgrib pa dag pa'i ched du ste de rnams ni phyi ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:3220: phyi ma 'di gnyis rmi lam gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3221: bar chad mi 'byung ba'i phyir yang bshad /
NK115(re)001:3222: de nas rmi ltas brtag pa ni grib gdon la
NK115(re)001:3223: sogs pas mi 'khrugs pa'i phyir ku sha'i sngas stan
NK115(re)001:3224: sbyin par bya ba ni nang ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:3225: de nas spro ba bskyed de dbugs dbyung bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3226: de ltar sta gon gyi chos rnams sngon du song nas /
NK115(re)001:3227: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor 'du bya ba'i
NK115(re)001:3228: phyir thig gi bya ba rnams legs par grub par
NK115(re)001:3229: byas nas / bzhi pa tshon ni /
NK115(re)001:3230: rgyu rab 'bring tha gsum gyi rang bzhin las byung
NK115(re)001:3231: ba'i tshon sna lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga byin gyis
NK115(re)001:3232: brlabs te tshon dgye tshul gyi spang blang rnams ma
NK115(re)001:3233: 'dzol bas dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus gang rung gi lugs
NK115(re)001:3234: bzhin bri bar bya ba ni gzhan las shes par
NK115(re)001:3235: bya'o // lnga pa bri ba yang tshon gyi khongs su song ngo //
NK115(re)001:3236: drug pa rnam pa dgos pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3237: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK115(re)001:3238: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK115(re)001:3239: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK115(re)001:3241: yang na rang mdog dang mtshungs pa'i thig le'i rnam pa dgod par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3242: de nas sngar lhag gnas byas pa'i bum pa rnams
NK115(re)001:3243: spos rol gyis sna drangs te dkyil 'khor la g.yas
NK115(re)001:3245: rnam rgyal gtso bo'i mdun nam /
NK115(re)001:3246: mdun gyi lha snam mam shar sgo'i phyi rol gyi g.yas logs ci bde bar dgod la /
NK115(re)001:3247: gzhan brgyad la sogs pa yod na des mtshon nas
NK115(re)001:3248: lha so so'i gnas kyi mdun nam sgo mtshams brgyad
NK115(re)001:3249: dam / nyung na shar sgo'i g.yon logs sam rdo
NK115(re)001:3250: rje'i rwa ba'i nang khongs su chud par bzhag ste
NK115(re)001:3252: rdo rje rwa ba'i phyi rol du //
NK115(re)001:3253: bgegs bskyed 'gyur bas mi dgod do //
NK115(re)001:3255: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bzhir mdo bzhi gdod par bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3256: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan sogs kyi bkod pa phun sum tshogs pas brgyan cing /
NK115(re)001:3257: phyi nang gi mchod pa dang yo byad kyi tshogs rgya chen pos bskor bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3259: spyir sku gsung thugs rten sogs dang dkyil 'khor la
NK115(re)001:3260: rab gnas byed tshul ni rab gnas kyi cho ga
NK115(re)001:3262: 'dir dkyil 'khor rab gnas dang dkyil 'khor sgrub pa
NK115(re)001:3263: don gcig ste rdul tshon la sogs pa'i lhag pa
NK115(re)001:3264: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:3265: la sogs pa'i stobs kyis rang snang ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:3266: dkyil 'khor dang ngo bo gcig par byin gyis brlabs
NK115(re)001:3267: nas rang dang slob ma rnams kyi rgyud la dngos
NK115(re)001:3268: grub 'byung ba'i gzhir 'gyur ba'i phyir te /
NK115(re)001:3270: sa la sogs las phyag rgyar byas //
NK115(re)001:3271: rnam grol rim pa thob 'gyur na //
NK115(re)001:3272: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK115(re)001:3273: smon ci dgos te 'di nyid yin //
NK115(re)001:3276: bdag mdun tha dad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3277: tha mi dad pa'i lugs gang ltar yang //
NK115(re)001:3279: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK115(re)001:3280: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs par //
NK115(re)001:3281: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis //
NK115(re)001:3282: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK115(re)001:3283: zhes pa ltar stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyangs nas /
NK115(re)001:3284: ting 'dzin rom mo mtha' yas mchog /
NK115(re)001:3285: ces pa la sogs pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:3286: rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis lhar bskyed la /
NK115(re)001:3287: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK115(re)001:3288: bskyed pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis rang
NK115(re)001:3289: snang gi ngo bor dbyer med pa'i dam tshig gi
NK115(re)001:3291: ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas dbyer med
NK115(re)001:3292: du bstim pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas bsgrub pa
NK115(re)001:3294: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK115(re)001:3295: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK115(re)001:3296: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK115(re)001:3297: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK115(re)001:3298: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK115(re)001:3299: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:3300: de ltar rab gnas ma byas pa'i dkyil 'khor la
NK115(re)001:3301: sogs pas ni tshogs rdzogs pa dang sdig sgrib bri
NK115(re)001:3302: zhing 'dag pa'i dgos pa myur du mi 'grub ste
NK115(re)001:3304: dkyil 'khor la sogs gang byas kyang //
NK115(re)001:3305: rab gnas ye shes mi ldan na //
NK115(re)001:3306: tshogs dang bri ba'i nus pa med //
NK115(re)001:3309: ye shes dag pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK115(re)001:3311: rgyal ba bzhugs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK115(re)001:3312: sgrib pa dag cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:3316: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK115(re)001:3317: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid do //
NK115(re)001:3318: zhes pas sa chog gi tshe mtshan ma ngan na zhi ba /
NK115(re)001:3319: rab gnas kyi tshe rgyas pa //
NK115(re)001:3320: dbang bskur ba'i gong du dbang /
NK115(re)001:3321: slob ma sta gon gyi tshe kun gyi rmi ltas
NK115(re)001:3322: ngan na drag po bya bar bshad pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:3323: pas mtshon / bsnyen pa'i kha skong sogs skabs su gang bab pa de byed pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:3328: lhag ma 11bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:3329: zhes pa ltar spyi dang bye brag gi sgos chos rnams shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3330: bzhi pa slob ma 'jug cing smin pa'i yan lag bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:3331: slob dpon rang nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3332: slob ma 'jug par gnang ba nod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3333: nod nas slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3334: zhugs pa la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3335: de la dang po gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:3336: rdo rje las rim gyis ston pa'i don //
NK115(re)001:3337: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3338: bcu pa zhugs pa'i phan yon gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:3339: dang po slob dpon rang nyid 'jug pa ni rtogs
NK115(re)001:3340: pa mchog dang ldan pa zhig yin na rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:3341: me tog dor ba tsam gyis 'jug pa'i go chod
NK115(re)001:3342: de / ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'bras chos lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:3343: dam tshig pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK115(re)001:3344: rnams dbyer med du rtogs pa bskyed pas 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:3346: 'di la so so ma yin par rig pa 'dun pa'i phyag dang /
NK115(re)001:3347: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la 'jug pa'i tshul zhes kyang bya'o //
NK115(re)001:3348: de lta ma yin pa'i so so skye bo'i slob dpon phal pa rnams ni /
NK115(re)001:3349: de tsam gyis 'jug pa'i go mi chod cing slob
NK115(re)001:3350: ma la'ang phan thogs dka' bas slob ma la ji
NK115(re)001:3351: ltar bskur ba bzhin du rang gis bdag 'jug blang
NK115(re)001:3352: bar bya ste / rim pa gsal ba las /
NK115(re)001:3353: slob ma 'jug pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK115(re)001:3354: dang po slob dpon 'jug par bya //
NK115(re)001:3356: de yang rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo bla ma
NK115(re)001:3357: dang tha mi dad pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor
NK115(re)001:3358: bzhugs pa la rnam smin bag chags kyi rten glo
NK115(re)001:3359: bur ba'i kun rtog cha dang bcas pa slob bu'i
NK115(re)001:3361: rgyu dbang thob pa'i bla mas las kyi slob dpon mdzad par mos kyang rung ste /
NK115(re)001:3363: rang nyid dbang len bla ma yis //
NK115(re)001:3364: las kyi slob dpon byed par bsam //
NK115(re)001:3366: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug par gnang ba nod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3367: slob dpon gyis thal mo sbyar la /
NK115(re)001:3368: rdo rje ye shes sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:3369: bden pa gang gis ye shes mchog /
NK115(re)001:3370: shes rab thabs dang dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK115(re)001:3371: bden pa de yis mgon po khyod //
NK115(re)001:3372: 'dod pa bdag la yongs rdzogs mdzod //
NK115(re)001:3373: ces pa la sogs pa lan gsum brjod pas gnang ba byin par bsam pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3374: gsum pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3382: zhes pa'i go rim ltar dang po slob ma rnams
NK115(re)001:3383: phyi rol du las thams cad pa'i chus khrus bya
NK115(re)001:3384: ba dang / gnyis pa gdong bcings te snyim pa me tog gis bkang la gsol ba gdab /
NK115(re)001:3385: gsum pa 'dod don dri lan byas nas slob dpon gyi drung du drang /
NK115(re)001:3386: bzhi pa dus gsum gyi rgyal ba la lus dbul /
NK115(re)001:3387: lnga pa slob bu'i tshe bsrung la bgegs bskrad /
NK115(re)001:3388: drug pa sgrib pa phral nas lhar bskyed de go bgo lus bsrung bya //
NK115(re)001:3389: bdun pa rdo rje gsum gyi dam tshig sbyin /
NK115(re)001:3390: brgyad pa dam tshig de nyid tshig gis dbab /
NK115(re)001:3391: dgu pa khe nyen gyi sgo nas chu nan bya //
NK115(re)001:3392: bcu pa skrag pa dang dogs pa med pa'i brtul
NK115(re)001:3393: zhugs kyis rmad du byung ba'i dam tshig gzhung bzhin
NK115(re)001:3395: bcu gcig pa lha dang las 'brel brtag pa'i phyir me tog dor /
NK115(re)001:3396: bcu gnyis pa me tog de spyi bor bcings la
NK115(re)001:3397: 'og min nas yi dam gyi lha bkug pa sngar
NK115(re)001:3398: chu nan gyi lha dang gnyis med du bstim pa
NK115(re)001:3399: ni phyi'i lha dbab pa ste phebs rtags byung ba
NK115(re)001:3401: nang gi lha dbab pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3402: gsang mtshan gdags shing lha'i sgom thabs ston pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3403: bcu gsum pa lha de bsgom pa la nan tan byed par gdams pa /
NK115(re)001:3404: bcu bzhi pa mig thur gyis gdong g.yogs phye nas mig dbye ba /
NK115(re)001:3405: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad cing
NK115(re)001:3406: lha ngo bstan pa rnams te me tog dor ba
NK115(re)001:3408: me tog spyi bor bcings nas lha dbab pa man chad nang 'jug go //
NK115(re)001:3409: de yan chad kyis 'jug pa'i chos so //
NK115(re)001:3410: de ltar zhugs pa'i phan yon ni /
NK115(re)001:3411: gnas skabs sgrib pa 'dag cing dngos grub la nye ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3412: mthar thug mthar lam pa 'og min du zhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam ste /
NK115(re)001:3414: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK115(re)001:3415: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yis //
NK115(re)001:3416: bsod nams brtan pa gang yin pa //
NK115(re)001:3417: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:3419: bzhi pa zhugs pa la dbang bskur ba ni 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:3420: de lta bu'i cho ga'i yan lag bcu drug po'i gang rung ma tshanga na /
NK115(re)001:3421: so so skye bo'i slob dpon la ni /
NK115(re)001:3422: cho ga'i yan lag phra mo nyamsa pasa kyang dngos
NK115(re)001:3423: grub dang byin rlabs kyi gnas la bsgrib par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:3424: bas / slob ma'i rgyud smin par nus pa ma
NK115(re)001:3425: yina pa'i phyir rtogs pa mchog dang ldan pa zhig
NK115(re)001:3426: yin yang slob ma'i dbang po dman mchog dang bstun
NK115(re)001:3428: so skye rnams kyis ni gzhan la dbang bskur byed pa la /
NK115(re)001:3429: rang gis bsnyen pa tshad dang ldan par gtong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3430: dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub sogs ci mi snyam du mi
NK115(re)001:3431: byed par bskyed rdzogs kyi gdeng med kyang de dag
NK115(re)001:3432: ni sla chos su ma song bar zhib cha byed
NK115(re)001:3433: dgos shing / dkyil 'khor yang ras bris tsam zhig ni med du mi rung ngo snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:3434: gnyis pa dbang ni dngos gzhi bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:3435: dbang spyi'i rnam bzhag mdor bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3436: dbang bzhi'i ngo bo rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3437: dang po dbang spyi'i rnam bzhag mdor bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:3438: rgyud sde bzhi'i dbang gi dbye ba bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:3439: dbang thob pa'i rgyu rkyen bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:3440: dbang gi grangs nges bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3441: dang po rgyud sde bzhi'i dbye ba bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3442: gong du ji skad bshad pa bzhin rgyud sde bzhi
NK115(re)001:3443: po gdul bya rnams kyi blo yi rim pa la
NK115(re)001:3444: dgongs te bstan pa yin pas so sora 'jug sgo
NK115(re)001:3445: dabnga gisa smin par bya ba'i tshul yang tha dad
NK115(re)001:3446: pa'i rigas kyi dbye ba mang du mchis la /
NK115(re)001:3448: bya ba'i rgyud la 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rigs gsum gang rung gi dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas /
NK115(re)001:3449: gzungs dang dbang sngags bzla bzhin par dbang bum gyi chu'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3450: rigs gang yin gyi dam tshig gi phyag rgyas coda
NK115(re)001:3451: pana gyi dbang gnyis kyis dbang gi dngos gzhi grub
NK115(re)001:3454: bkra shis rdzas brgyad sbyin pa rnams kyang byed do //
NK115(re)001:3455: spyod pa'i rgyud la gnyis po de yi steng du
NK115(re)001:3456: rdo rje minga gi dbang bsnan pa dngos bstan yin
NK115(re)001:3463: chos 'chad kyi rjes gnang sogs kyi dbang 'khor bcas
NK115(re)001:3464: bskur bar bshad pa ste rjes gnang sogs kyi mang
NK115(re)001:3465: nyung rgyud dang slob dpon so so'i gzhung gi khyad
NK115(re)001:3466: par yod do // rnal 'byora gyi rgyud la rigs rkyang dang /
NK115(re)001:3467: rigs bsdus che chung gang yin kyang /
NK115(re)001:3468: dkyil 'khor du zhugs la dam tshig dang sdom pa bzung /
NK115(re)001:3470: me tog dor bas lhag pa'i lha nges par byas nas /
NK115(re)001:3471: slob ma'i dbang gtso bor gyur pa riga pa'i dabnga lnga bskur bar bya ste /
NK115(re)001:3472: de yang gang bum gyi khrus sngon du 'gro bas /
NK115(re)001:3474: rnam rgyal sogs lha bum gyi chu'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3475: rigs gang yin gyi cod pan dang /
NK115(re)001:3477: de rnams kyiis mtshan pa'i dril bu dang /
NK115(re)001:3478: lhag pa'i lha dang mthun pa'i ming dbang rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:3479: de nas slob dpon gyi dbang /
NK115(re)001:3480: phyir mi ldog pa'i dam tshig gsum gzung ba /
NK115(re)001:3481: gsang dkyil du gsang ba'i 'jug pas zhugs shing mthong ba /
NK115(re)001:3482: lha dang dkyil 'khor gyi de kho na nyid ston pa /
NK115(re)001:3483: bka'a yi dabnga zhes yo ga rang gi thun mong ma yin pa'i chos 'chad rjes gnang dang /
NK115(re)001:3484: lung bstan dbugs dbyung gzengs bstod de slob dpon gyi
NK115(re)001:3485: dbang drug dang bcas bcu gcig po matha'a rten dang
NK115(re)001:3486: bcas pa rdzogas par bskur bar byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3487: de ltar yang ye shes thig le las /
NK115(re)001:3488: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /
NK115(re)001:3489: bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK115(re)001:3490: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK115(re)001:3491: spyod pa'i rgyud la rab tu gsal //
NK115(re)001:3492: phyir mi ldog pa yi ni dbang //
NK115(re)001:3493: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK115(re)001:3494: de ni drug pa'i bye brag dbang //
NK115(re)001:3495: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:3497: rnal 'byor bla na meda pa'i dbang ni /
NK115(re)001:3498: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK115(re)001:3499: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK115(re)001:3500: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK115(re)001:3501: rnam rtog dri ma dag bya'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:3502: dbang bskur rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK115(re)001:3503: zhes pa ltar rig pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:3504: drug pa rdo rje 'chang gi dbang ste slob ma'i dbang drug gi steng /
NK115(re)001:3505: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang bcas pas buma dbang dngos gzhi la bdun /
NK115(re)001:3509: gzengs bstod de bcu gcig dang /
NK115(re)001:3511: sbyor ba shesa raba ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3512: don dam tshiga gi dabnga bzhi po nang gses kyi dbye bas bcu bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3514: dang po'i dbang ni gtso bor ste //
NK115(re)001:3515: gnyis pa gsang ba'i ming can no //
NK115(re)001:3516: gsum pa kun nas sbyor ba ste //
NK115(re)001:3517: bzhi pa don ni dam pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3518: gtso bo'i dbye ba bcu gcig ste //
NK115(re)001:3519: bcu gnyis pa ni gsang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3520: bcu gsum pa ni yang dag sbyor //
NK115(re)001:3521: bcu bzhi pa ni don dam ste //
NK115(re)001:3522: dbang bskur re re sa re'o //
NK115(re)001:3523: rnam pa gsum ni rgyu yi dbang //
NK115(re)001:3524: bzhi pa 'bras bur shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:3526: de ltar na rnal 'byor rgyud kyi dbang rnams spyi
NK115(re)001:3527: tsam du bla med kyi bum dbang gi phyogs dang
NK115(re)001:3528: mthun kyang bla med la thun min gyi chos du
NK115(re)001:3529: ma yod pas khyad par 'phags so //
NK115(re)001:3530: de ltar phyi nang gi rgyud kyi thun mong ba
NK115(re)001:3531: bum dbang gi steng du bla med rang gi thun
NK115(re)001:3532: mong ma yin pa mchog dbang gong ma gsum bsnon
NK115(re)001:3533: ma'i tshul du byas pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3534: ye shes thig le'i rgyud sngar drangs pa'i 'phror /
NK115(re)001:3535: rnal 'byor bla ma yi ni mtshan //
NK115(re)001:3536: gsang ba yi ni dbang rgyal bshad //
NK115(re)001:3537: shes rab ye shes bla na med //
NK115(re)001:3538: bzhi pa de yang de bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:3540: de la spyir rgyud sde dang sgrub sde so so'i
NK115(re)001:3541: dbang gi grangs ni ma nges pa sna tshogs pa
NK115(re)001:3543: byis pa 'jug pa 'i dbang bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:3544: gong ma la 'jig rten pa gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:3545: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzhi pa ste bcu gcig tu gsungs pa sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:3546: snga 'gyur bla med kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs la /
NK115(re)001:3547: rgyud lugs man ngag sgrub sde bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:3548: rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ltar na /
NK115(re)001:3550: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK115(re)001:3551: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK115(re)001:3552: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK115(re)001:3553: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK115(re)001:3557: rang don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan dbang dang sgom dbang gnyis /
NK115(re)001:3558: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la 'chad dbang dang phrin dbang gnyis /
NK115(re)001:3559: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ste lnga'o //
NK115(re)001:3561: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum ste gsang sher bde ba chen po'i dbang ste gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:3564: lung a nu yo ga la kun 'dus rig pa'i mdor /
NK115(re)001:3565: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bcu /
NK115(re)001:3567: rtags kyi mtshan ma rdo rje sogs /
NK115(re)001:3572: rin chen pad+ma seng ge'i khri sogs /
NK115(re)001:3577: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig /
NK115(re)001:3578: nyan pa dang slob ma'i dbang rdzas glegs bam /
NK115(re)001:3579: phrin dbang sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK115(re)001:3581: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang rdo rje rtse dgu /
NK115(re)001:3583: thun min gyi rin chen bdun /
NK115(re)001:3584: phyag rgya'i dbang lha tsaka yongs rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:3586: sku gsung thugs kyi lha tsaka /
NK115(re)001:3590: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bcu gsum /
NK115(re)001:3591: shes rab rig pa'i dbang sgron me /
NK115(re)001:3592: snying rje rtags kyi dbang nyi zla /
NK115(re)001:3593: h'u las byung ba'i thong gshol /
NK115(re)001:3594: dug gsum dkrugs pa'i dung dmar /
NK115(re)001:3595: srid gsum sgrol ba'i mtshon cha /
NK115(re)001:3597: las bzhi rdzogs pa'i bam dbyug /
NK115(re)001:3599: gsang ba sbyor ba'i rig ma /
NK115(re)001:3601: sgrub dbang zhi khro'i gtso tsaka /
NK115(re)001:3602: sgrub rdzas phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK115(re)001:3605: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:3606: bdud rtsi'am gsang dkyil mtshon byed chos 'byung /
NK115(re)001:3607: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang ngo //
NK115(re)001:3609: sum cu rtsa drug gi dbye ba sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:3610: thega pa'i rtse mo man ngag a ti yo ga'i dbang gi rima pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3611: gsum pa'i dpe'i ye shes la ltos mi dgos par
NK115(re)001:3612: thog ma nas don dam byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK115(re)001:3613: 'khor du 'jug rung ba'i skal ldan la rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:3615: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis /
NK115(re)001:3616: zab pa don gyi dbang mchog ni //
NK115(re)001:3617: rig pa'i rtsal dbang thob pa ste //
NK115(re)001:3618: chos nyid rtogs pas dbang zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:3619: ye shes dbang bskur cod pan can //
NK115(re)001:3621: khyad par man ngag sde'i lugs ltar na dbang bzhi pa la bye brag tu dbye ba byas pa /
NK115(re)001:3622: spros bcas bum pa'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3624: shin tu spros med shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK115(re)001:3625: rab tu sprosa meda tshig gi dbang ste bzhi po
NK115(re)001:3626: la dag bya dag byed sogs kyis dbye bas shin
NK115(re)001:3628: mdor bsdu na lus ngag yid gsum dang shes bya la rmongs pa'i dri ma sbyong /
NK115(re)001:3629: sku gsung thugs dang rang byung 'od gsal gyi nus pa 'jug /
NK115(re)001:3630: thun mong ma yin pa a ti'i lam gyi bskyed rim dang /
NK115(re)001:3632: bde stong zung 'jug bsgom zhing ka dag gi ye shes rtogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3633: mngon sum lhun grub kyi don nyams su len pa bzhi la dbang /
NK115(re)001:3634: slob pa'i lam bzhi rdzogs pa'i rten byed cing /
NK115(re)001:3635: mthar 'bras mgon po rdo rje 'chang gi sku gsung
NK115(re)001:3636: thugs ye shes mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK115(re)001:3637: yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa ste 'di'i
NK115(re)001:3638: dbang bzhi po'i grangs bla med thun mong gi dbang
NK115(re)001:3639: dang 'dra yang don mi 'dra ba shes dgos so
NK115(re)001:3640: // yang sgrub sde la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:3642: gdul bya zhe sdang can sgrol ba lam du 'khyer
NK115(re)001:3643: ba'i phyir bum pa sogs phyi nang gi rdzas brgya
NK115(re)001:3644: rtsa brgyad la brten nas phyi dbang bskur ba /
NK115(re)001:3645: nga rgyal can lha lam du 'khyer ba'i phyir nang dbang lus la brten nas bskur ba /
NK115(re)001:3646: 'dod chags can sbyor ba lam du 'a khyer ba'i phyir gsang dbang yum la brten nas bskur ba /
NK115(re)001:3647: gti mug can rnam rtog lam du khyer ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:3648: de kho na nyid kyi dbang sems la brten nas
NK115(re)001:3650: sgrub sde'i dgos bka' yang phur sogs la thun mong
NK115(re)001:3651: ba bla med spyi bka' ltar dbang bzhi bskur ba
NK115(re)001:3652: dang / zab khyad sgrub dbang gi lugs su bskur
NK115(re)001:3653: ba sogs spyir na bla med kyi rgyud sde dang
NK115(re)001:3654: sgrub sde so so'i dag bya dang dag byed sbyor
NK115(re)001:3655: tshul sogs kyi dbang gi dbye bsdu matha'a yasa pa
NK115(re)001:3657: de dag gi tshul jo bo'i dam tshig bsdus pa las /
NK115(re)001:3658: bla ma'i zhal las byung ba'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3659: yi dam gyi lhas byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3660: rdo rje mkha' 'gro mas lung bstan pa'i dbang dang /
NK115(re)001:3661: rang gi sems nyid kyi rtsal las thob pa'i dbang dang bzhi'o zhes pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:3662: dang po ni dbang gi cho ga sgra ji bzhin par ltos pa dag dang /
NK115(re)001:3663: gnyis pa ni rgyal po dza'i khang steng du glegs bam babs pa lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:3664: gsum pa ni slob dpon klu sgrub dang /
NK115(re)001:3665: 'gro bzang gis o rgyan d+harma gany+dzo nas brtag gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:3666: ma h+aa m+aa y+aa gnyis ma byin blang bas bdag
NK115(re)001:3667: gir byas pa na mkha' 'gro mas bsnyags te rjes
NK115(re)001:3668: la zin pa'i tshe chos de'i bdag po gyis la
NK115(re)001:3669: shod ces rjes su gdams pa lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:3670: bzhi pa ni chos nyid kyi lta bas thob pa
NK115(re)001:3671: rig pa'i rtsal dbang ste de la brten nas bskur
NK115(re)001:3672: bya'i slob mas dngos grub thob pa ni dbang gi
NK115(re)001:3673: 'bras bu yin pas tha snyad phyogs gcig pa la
NK115(re)001:3674: zhen nas / dbang gi grangs dang /
NK115(re)001:3676: thob tshul tha dad pa dag la mi 'thad par
NK115(re)001:3677: mi sems te kun la dag snang byed pa gal
NK115(re)001:3678: che'o // des na bla med kyi dbang gi rnam
NK115(re)001:3679: grangs ji snyed cig yod pa thams cad gang las
NK115(re)001:3680: dbye ba dang gang du bsdu ba'i gzhir gyur pa'i
NK115(re)001:3681: grangs nges pa'i sa zin gyi 'jog mtshams ni 'chad
NK115(re)001:3682: 'gyur ltar dag bya dag byed dag 'bras sogs kyi
NK115(re)001:3683: dbang gis bum gsang shes rab tshig dbang ste rnama
NK115(re)001:3684: pa bzhi pora 'du zhing der nges pa yina no
NK115(re)001:3685: che'o // // gnyis pa dbang thob pa'i rgyu rkyen bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3686: de la sngags kyi theg pa bla na med pa'i
NK115(re)001:3687: dbang du ni gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK115(re)001:3688: dkyil 'khor chen po phung po khams dang skye mched
NK115(re)001:3689: thams cad kyi 'char gzhi bde gshegs snying po'i rang
NK115(re)001:3690: bzhin gnyug ma'i sgo gsum ye shes dang bzhi bum
NK115(re)001:3691: dbang la sogs pa'i dbang gi ngo bor ye nas
NK115(re)001:3692: gnas pa ni gzhi'i dbang bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:3693: de nyid dbang bzhi bskur ba'i thabs la brten nas smin pa'i nus rung du byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3694: lam dbang gis bogs 'don par byed pa ni lam gyi dbang bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:3695: 'bras bu sku bzhi'i ngo bor mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i dabnga bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3696: de dag kyang gnas skabs gsum du bzhag pa tsam
NK115(re)001:3697: las rang bzhin chos nyid gcig gi ngo bor dbyer
NK115(re)001:3698: med pa ru sems can thams cad la gdoda ma
NK115(re)001:3700: dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:3701: dbang mchog rang la med gyur na //
NK115(re)001:3702: bskur bas thob par ga la 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:3703: bra sran 'bras bu dbang bskur yang //
NK115(re)001:3704: de la 'bras kyi dngos snang med //
NK115(re)001:3706: 'o na dbang gi snod du mi rung ba'i sems can gang yang med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK115(re)001:3707: sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:3708: can yin pas mthar thug 'tshang rgya bar mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:3709: ba'i sems can de ni 'ga' yang med cing gsang
NK115(re)001:3710: sngags la ma brten par yang sangs mi rgya bas
NK115(re)001:3711: mthar thug ni thams cad sngags kyi snod rung yin
NK115(re)001:3712: par lung rigs gnyis kas grub pa yin mod /
NK115(re)001:3713: 'on kyang gnas skabs dbang gi rten du rung ba'i bum dbang gi rten rtsa dang /
NK115(re)001:3714: gsang dbang gi rten rlung dang /
NK115(re)001:3715: sher dbang gi rten khams lnga rdzas kyi thig le'i rang bzhin khams dkar dmar dang /
NK115(re)001:3716: dbang bzhi pa'i rten 'khrul pa ma rig pa'i thiga
NK115(re)001:3717: le'i ngo bo sems rtog rags pa ste rten de
NK115(re)001:3718: rnams mngon gyur du yod pa'i khams drug ldan kho
NK115(re)001:3719: na yin te / gzhan yid kyi lus can gzugs med dang /
NK115(re)001:3720: 'dod sred rags pa bcom pa'i gzugs khams pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3721: khams gcig nas lnga'i bar las drug ka mi ldan
NK115(re)001:3722: pa'i 'gro ba yod par bshad pa rnams ni rten
NK115(re)001:3723: ma yin te / brtag gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:3724: gzugs med pa yi rten rnams la //
NK115(re)001:3725: dbang rnams bskur ba'i brten med de //
NK115(re)001:3726: rtsa rlung rtog pa mi dmigs pas //
NK115(re)001:3727: ye shes dbang bskur ga la nus //
NK115(re)001:3728: gzugs khams rtsa dang rlung yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:3729: khams kyi zas dang bral bas min //
NK115(re)001:3730: des na 'dod khams gnas rigs ni //
NK115(re)001:3731: dbang rnams bskur ba'i rten yin te //
NK115(re)001:3732: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK115(re)001:3733: nga rgyal khong khro phrag dog gis //
NK115(re)001:3735: dbang gi snod du rung ba yin //
NK115(re)001:3737: gzhan yang lha min lha sgra mi snyan gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:3738: ngan song gi 'gro ba ni 'bras bu la spyod pas rgyud dman pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:3739: gling gsum du skyes pa'i khams drug ldan ni khyad par ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3740: de las kyang 'dzam bu'i gling pa ni las kyi sa par grags pas mchog tu gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:3741: de lta na'ang dam pa'i rigs can bzhi la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:3742: nyan rang dgra bcom lhag med du zhugs pa 'ga'
NK115(re)001:3743: zhig yid lus kyi sngags lam la 'jug pa yod
NK115(re)001:3744: pa ni bsam pa'i rten khyad par can yin pas
NK115(re)001:3745: ma nges so // des na rten khams drug dang //
NK115(re)001:3746: brten pa bde gshegs snying po gnyis ka ranga chasa
NK115(re)001:3747: su yod pa nyid de ni mtshungsa para ldana pa'i
NK115(re)001:3748: rgyu yin te / brtag gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:3749: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK115(re)001:3750: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spang //
NK115(re)001:3751: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK115(re)001:3752: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3755: gnas rten rtsa dang thig le la //
NK115(re)001:3756: bcu dbang lnga gsum dbang rnams ldan //
NK115(re)001:3758: de ltar slob ma'i rgyud mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu dang
NK115(re)001:3759: ldan pa de smin par 'gyur ba'i lhana cig byed
NK115(re)001:3760: pa'i rgyu ni rdo rje slob dpon gyis lha sngags
NK115(re)001:3761: ting nge 'dzin gyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang rdzas
NK115(re)001:3762: dang rig ma rnams te rgyu rnama pa gnyis yin
NK115(re)001:3763: la / de'i steng du dad pa la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:3764: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i dbang gi snod du runga
NK115(re)001:3765: ba'i slob bu ni rgyu yi rkyen yin te mtshan
NK115(re)001:3766: nyid dang mi ldan na sa bon rul ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:3767: smin mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:3768: lta ba rtogs shing bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:3769: lha'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:3770: gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:3771: bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:3772: 'phro 'du'i de kho na nyid de sngags kyi yan
NK115(re)001:3773: lag lnga'i dgongas pa dang ldana pa'i rdo rje sloba
NK115(re)001:3774: dpona ni badga po'i rkyen yin te /
NK115(re)001:3775: lta dgongs dang mi ldan na rlan dang bral ba'i
NK115(re)001:3776: rdo yis sa bon skye ba la mi phan pa
NK115(re)001:3777: bzhin byin rlabs 'jug tu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:3778: man ngag ji lta ba bzhin slob ma'i rgyud smin
NK115(re)001:3779: nus pa'i cho ga ste lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:3780: gyi bya ba thams cad ma nor bar mkhyen pa
NK115(re)001:3782: de dang mi ldan na byis pa'i rtsed mo bzhin
NK115(re)001:3783: dbang rdzas gnas su gtugs pa tsam gyis mi thob
NK115(re)001:3784: pa'i phyir ro // dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas bum dbang bskur te /
NK115(re)001:3785: de la gsang dbang bskur ba sogs snga ma snga
NK115(re)001:3786: ma'i rten cing 'brela 'byung gis go phye nas phyi
NK115(re)001:3787: ma phyi ma rnams rgyud la thob pa ni de
NK115(re)001:3788: ma thaga pa'i rkyen yin te /
NK115(re)001:3789: snga ma ma thob par phyi ma mi 'byung ste rmang ma bting ba la gyang dang /
NK115(re)001:3790: gyang med pa la ri mo bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:3791: 'on kyang tshe sngon dbang snga mas rgyud smin nas
NK115(re)001:3792: da lta gong ma la mos shing thob par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:3793: ba dang / dbang rnon cig char ba'i rigs la
NK115(re)001:3794: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang kho na dang po nas
NK115(re)001:3795: bskur te rtogs pa rgyud la skye ba yod pa
NK115(re)001:3796: sogs la ni ma nges so //
NK115(re)001:3797: de lta bu'i rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi ste drug
NK115(re)001:3798: po tshogas pa lasa slob bu'i rgyud la dngos grub
NK115(re)001:3799: thob rung gi nus pa smin nas lam dang 'bras
NK115(re)001:3800: bu'i chos mtha' dag pa'i yon tan bskyed pa'i dabnga
NK115(re)001:3803: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag bsnyed //
NK115(re)001:3804: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK115(re)001:3805: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK115(re)001:3807: gzhan du de dag las gang yang rung ba ma tshang na smin pa'i don mi 'grub ste /
NK115(re)001:3808: dper na yi ge 'bru gcig tsam zhig 'bri dgos
NK115(re)001:3809: na yang de la shog bu snag tsha smyug gu
NK115(re)001:3810: skyes bu' lag pa des de 'bri shes pa sogs
NK115(re)001:3811: mang po las gcig tsam zhig ma tshang na yig
NK115(re)001:3812: 'bru de yod mi rung ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:3813: gsum pa dbang gi grangs nges bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3814: de la gnyen po mchog gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK115(re)001:3815: pa'i lam gyis ma dag 'khor ba'i chos su snang
NK115(re)001:3816: ba thams cad dag pa ye shes chen po'i ngo
NK115(re)001:3817: bor dag par byed pa la dag byed kyi thabs
NK115(re)001:3818: tshul dpag tu med pa yod kyang grangas ngesa pa'i
NK115(re)001:3819: sgo nasa bsdus te rnam par bazhaga pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3820: spyir 'gro ba rnams rang rang gi las dang 'khrul
NK115(re)001:3821: pa'i dbang gis gnas rigs drug tu 'khor ba las
NK115(re)001:3822: / khyad par mtho ris kyi rten khams drug ldan rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:3823: bye brag mi'i 'gro ba mngal nas skyes pa rnams
NK115(re)001:3824: thog mar lte ba'i rtsa mdud nas rim pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:3825: lus chags shing / de ltar lus su snang ba'i bag chags de'i dbang gis phyi'i lus snod dang /
NK115(re)001:3826: bar gyi lus 'gro ba gzhan gyi lus rnams kyang
NK115(re)001:3827: snang ba yin pas lusa kyi dag bya'i gtso bora
NK115(re)001:3828: gyur pa ni rtsa yina te /
NK115(re)001:3829: des na de dag byed kyi gnyen po ni sku
NK115(re)001:3830: rdo rje bum pa'i dbang bskur nas de'i lam phyi
NK115(re)001:3831: nang bar gsum gyi lus su snang ba thams cad
NK115(re)001:3832: lha'i rang bzhin du bsgom pa'i bskyed rim rnams nyams
NK115(re)001:3834: rtsa yi rnama pa dag bya dang dag byed kyi
NK115(re)001:3835: yi ge du ma'i gzugsa su gansa pa de la
NK115(re)001:3836: g.yo byed kyi rlung brten nas da lta 'khrul pa'i
NK115(re)001:3837: gnas skabs su byed las sna tshogs su shar zhing
NK115(re)001:3838: 'khor ba'i sgra tshig rang rgyud par snang ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:3839: ngag gi dag bya'i gtso bor rlung yin pas /
NK115(re)001:3840: de dag byed kyi gnyen po gsung rdo rje gsang ba'i dbang bskur nas /
NK115(re)001:3841: de'i lam ngag bskyed byed rlung gi byed bcings la
NK115(re)001:3842: gtso bor bslab pa'i rang lus thabs ldan gyi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:3843: rim bstan la / rlung de yis ni rtsa khams
NK115(re)001:3844: thams cad la khyab par bkod pa byang chub kyi
NK115(re)001:3845: sems khamsa dkar dmar dwangs ma chen po rnamas 'gro
NK115(re)001:3846: 'ong can du khrid cing gnas pa'i sgo nas brtena
NK115(re)001:3847: pa de'i sems kyi rten byed pas /
NK115(re)001:3848: sems dag pa la rtsa ba khams la gnad du bsnun dgos pas /
NK115(re)001:3849: de dag byed kyi gnyen po thugs rdo rje shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur nas /
NK115(re)001:3850: de'i lam sems kyi rten khams las su rung bar
NK115(re)001:3851: byed pa gzhan lus thabs ldan gyi rdzogs rim bstan
NK115(re)001:3852: pa dang / khamas de la sems kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:3853: nam chos nyid dam dona dama byang chub kyi semsa
NK115(re)001:3854: pa dang / sam / dri bcas ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:3855: khams brten pa'i tshul du yod pas de mngon du
NK115(re)001:3856: 'gyur ba la sems kyi bag chags sgrib byed kyi
NK115(re)001:3857: rnam par yod pa nyid dag dgos pas /
NK115(re)001:3858: de dag byed kyi gnyen po ye shes rdo rje tshig gi dbang bskur nas /
NK115(re)001:3859: de'i lam sems kyi sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i zung
NK115(re)001:3860: 'jug gi rdzogs rim 'od gsal ba'i ye shes bsgom
NK115(re)001:3861: par bstan pas dbang bzhi po lam dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:3862: de rnams su gsang sngags kyi nyams len thams cad
NK115(re)001:3864: gnyis pa dbang bzhi'i ngo bo bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3865: dbang bzhi'i ngo bo dngos bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:3866: dbang gi sgra don bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:3867: rgyu lam 'bras bu'i dbang bstan pa /
NK115(re)001:3868: sdom pa'i thob mtshams bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:3869: dang po dbang bzhi'i ngo bo dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:3872: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3873: gsang sngags ni nyon mongs dang 'dod yon lam du
NK115(re)001:3874: byed pa'i thabs mkhas can yin pas 'doda pa'i khamas
NK115(re)001:3875: kyi ganga zaga 'phags pa'i sprul pa lta bu ma
NK115(re)001:3876: yin pa'i ranga rgyud pa kuna la 'doda chagsa rang
NK115(re)001:3877: mtshan pa sogs nyon mongs rnams yod pa dang des
NK115(re)001:3878: bskyed pa'i las rnams kyis srid pa'i gnas su 'ching
NK115(re)001:3879: bar byed cing / 'ching ba thams cad kyi rtsa
NK115(re)001:3880: ba ni sred pa yin pas de la nang gses
NK115(re)001:3881: kyi dbye ba bltas dgod lag bcangs gnyis sbyor gyi
NK115(re)001:3882: 'dod chags rnama pa bzhira gansa pa sogas daga bya
NK115(re)001:3883: bar byed cing / dang / daga byeda bum pa
NK115(re)001:3884: la sogs pa dbang bzhi po lam dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:3885: la brten nas grangs ngesa pa can du 'jog pa
NK115(re)001:3886: bar byed cing / dang / yanga yin no // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:3891: dang po bum pa'i dbang bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3892: dbang re re la'ang 'dod chags kyi 'jug tshul bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:3893: gang gi gnyen por che ba /
NK115(re)001:3898: lam gang bsgom pa la dbang ba /
NK115(re)001:3900: 'da' ka ma'i man ngag gang yin pa /
NK115(re)001:3901: 'bras bu gang thob pa ste dgu rer yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:3902: dbang dang po 'di la gang gi gnyen por che ba ni /
NK115(re)001:3903: pho mo phan tshun gcig gis gcig la 'dod pa'i
NK115(re)001:3904: sems kyis bltas pa tsam gyis tshima para 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:3905: 'doda chagas ni lha gazhana 'phrul dabnga byed pa la
NK115(re)001:3906: gansa pa ste de'i gnyen po byed pa yin la
NK115(re)001:3907: / 'khyud sbyor gyi 'dod chags can la ni snga
NK115(re)001:3908: ma gsum po de tsam gyis tshim par mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:3909: yang gnas pa nyid yin te /
NK115(re)001:3910: chags sems kyis blta ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3912: lag pa la sogs pas reg par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:3913: dkyil 'khor gang la brten pa ni /
NK115(re)001:3914: spyi rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhir gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:3915: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:3916: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:3917: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:3918: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK115(re)001:3919: dang po ni slob dpon rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK115(re)001:3920: slob ma mthar phyin pa'i lam pa la /
NK115(re)001:3921: ye shes kyi snang ba las grub pa'i rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:3922: ye shes kyi lha mo la brten nas dbang bskur bar mdzad pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:3924: rgyal ba kun gyi spyi gzugs des //
NK115(re)001:3925: 'khor tshogs ye shes rgya mtsho la //
NK115(re)001:3926: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor lhan cig tu //
NK115(re)001:3927: ye shes lha mo la brten nas //
NK115(re)001:3928: ye shes chen pos dbang bskur bas //
NK115(re)001:3929: gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang chen gyur //
NK115(re)001:3931: gnyis pa ni slob dpon mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la nye ba des /
NK115(re)001:3932: slob ma mthong sgom gnyis la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin la /
NK115(re)001:3933: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin dang rig pa'i lha mo la brten nas dbang bskur bar mdzad de /
NK115(re)001:3935: dang po nas bzung bcu pa'i bar //
NK115(re)001:3937: rig pa'i lha mo la brten nas //
NK115(re)001:3938: ting 'dzin chu bos dbang bskur bas //
NK115(re)001:3939: sa dang ye shes zhing khams dang //
NK115(re)001:3942: sngon slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mtsho ma pham
NK115(re)001:3943: la thig btab nas rdo rjee dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:3944: bstan te / dbas many+dzu sh+r+ai sogs la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:3945: slob dpon chen po pad+mas stag tshang seng phug tu
NK115(re)001:3946: mtsho rgyal la phur pa'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha' dang
NK115(re)001:3947: mnyam pa bstan nas dbang bskur ba lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:3948: dkyil 'khor de la sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:3949: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan zhes kyang gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:3951: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam gnas pas //
NK115(re)001:3952: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gsum 'phro zhing //
NK115(re)001:3953: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor sogs //
NK115(re)001:3954: rdo rje'i thig tshad dor tsam gyis //
NK115(re)001:3955: rgyang grags la sogs mtshan ma yi //
NK115(re)001:3956: dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gsal ldan pa //
NK115(re)001:3957: ting 'dzin lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan yin //
NK115(re)001:3959: gsum pa ni slob dpon mthong lam pas slob ma
NK115(re)001:3960: phyag rgya gcig spros las su rung ba'i sbyor lam
NK115(re)001:3961: pa la / rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK115(re)001:3962: rig pa rtsal gyi gzungs ma la brten nas dbang bskur te /
NK115(re)001:3964: mthong lam rdo rje'i sku thob pas //
NK115(re)001:3966: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK115(re)001:3967: rig pa rtsal gyi gzungs brten nas //
NK115(re)001:3968: zag med rdo rje'i sku la sbyor //
NK115(re)001:3970: 'di gsum gyis dkyil 'khor de rnams la brten nas dbang thams cad bskur ba las /
NK115(re)001:3971: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la brten mi dgos te slob ma'i dbang gis so //
NK115(re)001:3972: bzhi pa ni ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob
NK115(re)001:3973: pa'i slob dpon gyis skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob
NK115(re)001:3974: ma la lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang
NK115(re)001:3975: / las rgya mtshan ldan la brten nas dbang bskur ba ste /
NK115(re)001:3977: rig pa brtan thob rnal 'byor pas //
NK115(re)001:3978: las dang skal ldan rnal 'byor la //
NK115(re)001:3979: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor du //
NK115(re)001:3980: rig ma phyag rgya mdzes ma la //
NK115(re)001:3981: dbang bskur byin rlobs brtan byas nas //
NK115(re)001:3982: cho ga thabs kyis dbang bskur zhing //
NK115(re)001:3983: brgyud pa dbang gi man ngag gis //
NK115(re)001:3984: sbyor ba nyams ldan rnal 'byor thob //
NK115(re)001:3986: de dag las skabs 'dir ni slob dpon skye 'phags ci yin kyang //
NK115(re)001:3987: slob ma dkyil 'khor snga ma gsum la 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:3988: nus pa med pa'i so skyes kyi dbang du btang
NK115(re)001:3989: nas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:3990: phyag rgya la bsten par gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:3991: de yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdul tshon kho na'i nges pa yang med de /
NK115(re)001:3992: las dang po pa yin kyang dbang po'i khyad par
NK115(re)001:3993: gyis mchog dang rab 'bring tha gsum las mchog tu
NK115(re)001:3994: gyur pas ni / rdo rje slob dpon gyi lus
NK115(re)001:3995: kyi dkyil 'khor la mos pa brtan pas der thog
NK115(re)001:3997: lus la dkyil 'khor du 'du shes pa'i mkhas pa
NK115(re)001:3998: des phyi dkyil la brten dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan med
NK115(re)001:3999: de / slob dpon dril bu pas /
NK115(re)001:4000: bcos ma gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor gang //
NK115(re)001:4001: de ni gdul bya'i dbang las 'dod //
NK115(re)001:4002: mkhas pas bsgrub bya de ma yin //
NK115(re)001:4004: yang de tsam min yang dbang po rab tshom bu'i
NK115(re)001:4005: dkyil 'khor tsam la brten rung bar yang gsungs te
NK115(re)001:4006: / bde 'dus dbang gi rtsa ba las /
NK115(re)001:4007: dkyil 'khor gang du dbang bskur na //
NK115(re)001:4008: rab 'bring tha mar gsungs pa yis //
NK115(re)001:4009: me tog bris sku rdul tshon gsum //
NK115(re)001:4010: dkyil 'khor gsum du dbang bskur ro //
NK115(re)001:4012: 'bring ras bris la brten par yang //
NK115(re)001:4013: bi ma la'i thig gi pin+d+air+thara /
NK115(re)001:4014: brtan zhing ngos 'jam khang bu dang //
NK115(re)001:4015: ras sam gro ga'am shing shun nam //
NK115(re)001:4016: ta la'i lo ma'am dur khrod ras //
NK115(re)001:4017: zhing chen ras la sogs pa la //
NK115(re)001:4018: phyag rgya mnyam rdzogs bris pa ni //
NK115(re)001:4019: mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten yin no //
NK115(re)001:4020: zhes khang bu'i ldebs ris dang /
NK115(re)001:4021: ras bris la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4022: khyad par a ts+aar+ya rgyal ba'i sdes //
NK115(re)001:4023: rdul tshon bri bar ma nus na //
NK115(re)001:4024: dkyil 'khor dang mnyam ras la ni //
NK115(re)001:4025: nges par bcom ldan he ru ka /
NK115(re)001:4026: phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan bcas pa bri //
NK115(re)001:4028: 'on kyang dbang po tha ma rnams ni nges par rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la brten dgos te /
NK115(re)001:4029: rgyud sde du ma nas gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:4030: sngon phyis kyi mkhas grub mang pos phyag len la de ltar mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:4031: des na rgyu mtshan ci yang mi shes bzhin //
NK115(re)001:4032: dbang po'i rno rtul sogs gang la yang mi sems
NK115(re)001:4033: par thams cad spros med sla chos sogs ci bab
NK115(re)001:4034: bab tu byas pas ni don ci yang mi 'grub
NK115(re)001:4035: par ma zad sngags la dbang zos pa'i nyes pa
NK115(re)001:4037: des na 'dir dkyil 'khor gang la brten na rdul tshona gyi dkyil 'khora la brten nas /
NK115(re)001:4039: 'di'i dngos gzhi kun gyi rjes su bum chu'i bya
NK115(re)001:4040: ba 'gro dgos pas bum pa'i dabnga zhes bya la
NK115(re)001:4041: de nyid bskur bar byed pa ste /
NK115(re)001:4042: de yang slob ma rnams 'khrus nas byung ba sogs
NK115(re)001:4043: sngon du 'gro ba rnams dbang chog so so'i lugs
NK115(re)001:4044: bzhin byas la dbang don du gsol ba gdab /
NK115(re)001:4045: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su dbang stegs la dngos su bzhag pa'am /
NK115(re)001:4046: ma bde na mos pas dkyil 'khor la mngon du phyogs par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:4047: de nas dbang bskur ba dngos ni sku rdo rje
NK115(re)001:4048: sprul sku'i ngo bo bla ma dang gnyis su med
NK115(re)001:4049: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhas bum dbang bskur ba'i dgongs
NK115(re)001:4050: pa gtad nas thugs ka la sogs pa nas rigs
NK115(re)001:4051: lnga so so'i ngo bo nyid kyi dbang rdzas rnams
NK115(re)001:4052: byung bar mos shing slob ma yang lhag pa'i lha
NK115(re)001:4053: gang yin du gsal nas bskur ba'am /
NK115(re)001:4054: spro zhing nus na slob ma la sngar ltar nang
NK115(re)001:4055: dbang bskur ba'i dmigs pas rdo rje'i lam nas brgyud
NK115(re)001:4056: rig pa'i pad+mara bzhag pa mi dmigs pa'i ngang las
NK115(re)001:4057: cho ga gsum gyis dbang rdzas dang mthun pa'i lhar
NK115(re)001:4058: bskyed nas / dbang bskur ba'i don du slob dpon
NK115(re)001:4059: gyis dbang lha la gsol ba gdab cing snying ga'i
NK115(re)001:4060: 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras
NK115(re)001:4061: dang bcas pa thams cad gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil
NK115(re)001:4062: 'khor gyi rnam pa steng gi nam mkha' la gsar
NK115(re)001:4063: du spyan drangs pas dbang gi bya ba byed par
NK115(re)001:4064: mos pa'i phyogs gnyis yod pas /
NK115(re)001:4066: gshegs pa rnams kyis dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa mdzad //
NK115(re)001:4067: rig pa'i lha mo rnams kyis ni bzhengs nas bum pa yo bar bzung ste dbang bskur /
NK115(re)001:4068: sems dpa' sems ma rnams kyis ni bkra shis pa'i tshig gis me tog gtor zhing shis pa brjod /
NK115(re)001:4069: khro bo dang khro mo rnams kyis ni bgegs bskrad
NK115(re)001:4070: de lha tshogs thams cad dbang gi bya ba la
NK115(re)001:4071: dgyes pa'i sgo nas dbang bskur te so so'i mjug
NK115(re)001:4072: tu dbang lha yang slob ma la bstim pa yin
NK115(re)001:4073: no // de ltar spyan drangs pa'i dbang lha la rnam pa dang grangs ma nges te /
NK115(re)001:4074: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:4075: til gyi gang bu bzhin gang ba'i //
NK115(re)001:4076: rgyal bas bum pa bzung nas ni //
NK115(re)001:4077: zhes gsungs pa la sogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:4078: 'o na dbang lha gsar du spyan drangs pa las
NK115(re)001:4079: dbang thob pa ltar na rdul tshon la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:4080: dkyil 'khor las dbang thob par cis 'gyur snyam na
NK115(re)001:4081: / de dang gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje slob
NK115(re)001:4082: dpon gyis dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa gtad pas dbang
NK115(re)001:4083: ni de las thob pa kho na ste /
NK115(re)001:4085: bcom ldan 'das zab mo snang ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pas /
NK115(re)001:4086: sh+aa ri'i bus dris te spyan ras gzigs kyis shes rab snying po bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:4087: don 'di khong du chud na chos thams cad rgyal ba'i dgongs rgyud gcig tu gnas pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:4088: sgron ma rnam par bkod pa las /
NK115(re)001:4089: dgongs pa brda' dang snyan brgyud nas //
NK115(re)001:4090: gsang sngags don gyi tshad ma 'byung //
NK115(re)001:4092: de yang dang po mi bskyod pa chu'i dbang la
NK115(re)001:4093: sogs pa rig pa'i dbang lnga bskur bar bya ste
NK115(re)001:4094: / de la ci'i phyir rig pa'i dbang zhes bya zhe na /
NK115(re)001:4095: ma rig pa'i rang bzhin phung po lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:4096: dug lnga la sogs pa'i 'khor ba'i chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:4097: kyi ngo bo rig pa'i chos nyid sangs rgyas lnga
NK115(re)001:4098: dang / ye shes lnga la sogs pa mya ngan
NK115(re)001:4099: las 'das pa'i dbyings su dag cing sad par byed
NK115(re)001:4100: pas na de skad ces bya ste /
NK115(re)001:4102: sangs rgyas lngar ni rnam dag pa'i //
NK115(re)001:4103: dbang skur lnga thob rgyu las ni //
NK115(re)001:4104: ma rig pa dang bral bas na //
NK115(re)001:4105: ye shes lnga ni thob par 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:4108: slob ma me tog gang la phog pa'i lhar bskyed
NK115(re)001:4109: nas rang rigs kyi chus dbang bskur ba nas rang
NK115(re)001:4110: rigs kyi ming 'dogs pa la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4111: slob ma des kyang rang gi babs pa'i lha gang
NK115(re)001:4112: yin pa de'i rigs kyi dam tshig gtso bor bsrung
NK115(re)001:4113: ba la sogs pa'i tshul yang shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:4114: de ltar dag bya dang dag 'bras su gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:4115: de'ang dri ma'i dngos po rang mtshan pa zhig dag
NK115(re)001:4116: nas 'bras bu gsar du thob pa yang min la
NK115(re)001:4117: / phung sogs 'di 'bras bu de'i ngo bor gnas 'gyur ba yang ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:4118: phung sogs 'khor ba'i chos 'di thams cad kyi snang
NK115(re)001:4119: tshul ma dag pa ltar snang ba 'di yod ma
NK115(re)001:4120: myong ba'i snang ba glo bur ba zhig yin pas
NK115(re)001:4121: na dri ma glo bur ba de thams cad dbyings
NK115(re)001:4122: su sangs nas dag bya dag byed kyi sems rtog
NK115(re)001:4123: thams cad zad pa na rang rigs kyi yon tan
NK115(re)001:4125: da lta ni rigs sad rung gi nus pa tsam
NK115(re)001:4126: bzhag nas lam la bslab pa'i rten 'brel gyis rigs
NK115(re)001:4127: kyi yon tan thob pa'i rkyen du 'gyur ba ste
NK115(re)001:4128: gnas skabs kun rdzob pa'i chos tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:4129: de ltar rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du dri bcas
NK115(re)001:4130: ye shes kyi khams rdo rje sems dpa'i de kho
NK115(re)001:4131: na nyid du sbyang ba'i phyir tha mal gyi spyod
NK115(re)001:4132: pa brtul nas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshul la 'jug
NK115(re)001:4133: pa rdo rje brtul zhugs kyi dbang thun mong ba
NK115(re)001:4134: dang / khyad par spyod pa'i brtul zhugs d+aa ma
NK115(re)001:4135: ru dang kha t+w+aam la sogs pa yod pa'i phyogs
NK115(re)001:4136: la de yang bskur bar bya ste slob ma'i dbang
NK115(re)001:4137: dang / drug go // thabs de las byung ba ni rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ste /
NK115(re)001:4138: slob dpon du 'os pa gang zhig la sngar lhag
NK115(re)001:4139: gnas kyi skabs su slob dpon gyi sdom pa byin
NK115(re)001:4141: min na gnas skabs 'dir bya ste gzhan don la
NK115(re)001:4142: mthu bskyed pa'i phyir bum pa bya ba gtso bor
NK115(re)001:4143: bya zhing / de'i rjes 'brel du lha dbang yang bskur bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:4144: dam tshig gsum 'dzin pa gtso bor bya ba ste gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:4145: phyi ma 'di la phyir mi ldog pa'i dbang zhes
NK115(re)001:4146: kyang bya ste dper na mdo lam du sbyor lam
NK115(re)001:4147: thob pa na phyir mi ldog par bshad pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:4148: no // de skad du'ang brtag gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:4149: shes rab bcu drug lon pa la //
NK115(re)001:4150: lag pa dag gis yang dag 'khyud //
NK115(re)001:4151: rdo rje dril bu mnyam sbyor bas //
NK115(re)001:4152: slob dpon dbang du rab tu brjod //
NK115(re)001:4154: 'di ni rig dbang lnga lta bu'i rigs nyi tshe
NK115(re)001:4155: ba tsam ma yin par rigs thams cad kyi khyab
NK115(re)001:4156: byed drug pa rdo rje 'chang gi dbang ste dbang
NK115(re)001:4157: stegs la bzhag nas rnal 'byor chen po'i lha lus
NK115(re)001:4158: la bkod de dam tshig gsum bzung la /
NK115(re)001:4159: ye shes pa drangs nas bstim ste rigs bdag gis rgyas btab /
NK115(re)001:4161: lha dang gzhal yas khang dang slob dpon gyi de
NK115(re)001:4162: kho na nyid bstan pa sogs te bum dbang gi
NK115(re)001:4163: dngos bzhi bdun yan lag dang bcas pa bskur bas
NK115(re)001:4165: gtso bora srog gcod pa la sogs pa lusa kyi sngar bsags pa'i sgrib pa 'adga cing /
NK115(re)001:4166: bum dbang gi dam tshig las mi 'da' zhing lus
NK115(re)001:4167: tha mal du blta ba'i 'dzin pa dor nas lha
NK115(re)001:4168: bsgom pa la sogs pa byas pas phyin chad kyi
NK115(re)001:4169: las rgyun gcod / las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4170: gnas skabs bzhi las sad pa'i gnas skabs snang ba rags pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4171: lus kyi thig le'i sgrib pa 'dag /
NK115(re)001:4173: lam gang bsgom pa la dbang na snang ba snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK115(re)001:4174: srid pa bcuda kyi sems can te rten gyi rang bzhin brtan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4175: brten pa'i rang bzhin g.yo bar snang bas bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:4176: phung po lnga dang khamas lnga gshegs pa gshegs ma'i
NK115(re)001:4177: gdan dang / phyi nang gi skye mcheda kun sems dpa' dang sems ma'i gdan /
NK115(re)001:4178: yan lag gam lus kyi dbang yul la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:4179: khro bo dang khro mo'i gdan te gadna gsuma tshanga
NK115(re)001:4180: ba'i dkyil 'khora gcig tu shes nas rang rgyud du
NK115(re)001:4181: blta ba las grol te rgyud sde so so'i gzhung
NK115(re)001:4182: nas byung ba'i dag bya dag 'bras kyi lha'i 'khor
NK115(re)001:4183: lo dbyibs kyi lam bsgoms pas /
NK115(re)001:4186: sems thams cad rig stong zung 'jug sgyu ma'i rnam
NK115(re)001:4187: rol du shara ba'i bskyed pa'i rim pa bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:4189: lta ba gang rtogs na ngo bo nyid gsum rtogs te /
NK115(re)001:4190: de'ang snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba snanga ba'i ngo bo nyid bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4191: de'i rang bzhin stong nyid du shes pas ma zhen
NK115(re)001:4192: pa stong pa'i ngo bo nyid rdzogs pa'i rim pa
NK115(re)001:4193: dang / de gnyis la ched du rtsol mi dgos
NK115(re)001:4194: par lhun gyis grub cing zung du 'jug pa zunga
NK115(re)001:4195: 'juga gi ngo bo nyid de bskyed rim rang gi
NK115(re)001:4196: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gsuma gyi rang bzhin du rtogs
NK115(re)001:4197: dang / pa ste / dang po gnyis rgyu dus kyi lta ba dug can dang /
NK115(re)001:4198: phyi ma 'bras dus kyi lta ba dug med do //
NK115(re)001:4199: dug yod med kyi don ni /
NK115(re)001:4200: snga ma gnyis kyi dus su snang phyogs dang stong phyogs la zhen pa yod la /
NK115(re)001:4201: phyi ma la de med pa'i don no //
NK115(re)001:4202: 'on kyang rdzogs rim gyi lta ba la ltos na gsum ka dug can no //
NK115(re)001:4203: bskyed rim gyi dus nas rim pa gsum gyi zlas
NK115(re)001:4204: phyes pa'i rdzogs rim dang zung 'jug gi lta ba
NK115(re)001:4205: skyes na ni lam phyi ma ched du ma bsgom
NK115(re)001:4206: yang bskyed rim gyi dus kyi lta ba de dug
NK115(re)001:4207: med do // de yang mi slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK115(re)001:4208: mngon du ma gyur gyi bar du zhen pa'i dug
NK115(re)001:4209: gtan nas med pa ni ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:4210: tshul des dbang gong ma dag gi lta ba la dug yod med kyang shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:4211: grub matha'a gang snyogs na 'khora ba dang mya ngan
NK115(re)001:4212: las 'adsa pa'i chos thams cad dag pa dang skye
NK115(re)001:4213: ba med pa'i rang bzhin du gnyis su meda par
NK115(re)001:4214: mnyam pa nyid chena po'i ngang du rtogs pa yin
NK115(re)001:4215: la / de yang skabs 'di dag tu grub mtha'
NK115(re)001:4216: snyogs zhes pa ni rang rang gi lta ba mngon
NK115(re)001:4217: sum du rtogs pa yin pas sa thob pa'am rig
NK115(re)001:4219: 'ad'a ka ma'i man ngag gang yin na snang ba
NK115(re)001:4220: bsgyur ba'i 'pho ba zhes sngar gyi bskyed rim de
NK115(re)001:4221: nyid gsal btab nas de'i ngang la 'pho ba dang
NK115(re)001:4222: / rnam shes 'od kyi thig ler dmigs nas 'pho ba 'oda kyi gonga busa 'pho ba dang /
NK115(re)001:4223: phata dang hi ka la sogs pa'i sgra yisa 'pho ba ste /
NK115(re)001:4224: 'pho ba de dag la brten nas dag pa'i zhing ngam /
NK115(re)001:4225: sngags la spyod pa'i rten can du skyes nas lam gyi 'phro mthud pa'o //
NK115(re)001:4226: de yang tshe 'dir grub mtha' ma snyogs na bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:4227: snyogs na ni mi dgos so //
NK115(re)001:4229: de ltar bskyed rim gyi lam de nyid rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:4230: zab mo'i ye shes dang 'brel te goms pa mthar
NK115(re)001:4231: phyin pas ma dag pa'i snang ba phra rags thams
NK115(re)001:4232: cad kyi snang gzhir gyur pa rtsa yi ma dag
NK115(re)001:4233: pa'i 'grosa bar ma chad par yod pa de nyid
NK115(re)001:4234: dag pa ye shes kyi ngang du thima pa ste
NK115(re)001:4235: dag nas / bskyed rima gyis 'bras bu gzugs kyi
NK115(re)001:4236: sku ji ltar lam du byas shing goms pa de
NK115(re)001:4237: bzhin sprul pa'i sku yi rnam rol nam mkha' khyab
NK115(re)001:4238: par snang yang sku yi ngo bo rdo rje ltar
NK115(re)001:4239: 'pho 'gyur med cing rang bzhin nam mkha' ltar 'dusa
NK115(re)001:4240: ma byas pa de mngon du 'gyur ba'o //
NK115(re)001:4241: de ltar yang glang po rab 'bogs las /
NK115(re)001:4242: rtsa yi 'gros thim dbyibs kyi lam dag pa /
NK115(re)001:4243: lus kyi sgrib byang bskyed rim sprul pa'i sku //
NK115(re)001:4246: dkyil 'khor gang la brten na bla ma'i yum shes
NK115(re)001:4247: rab ma'i rtsa yi ge b+ha ga'i dkyila 'khora la
NK115(re)001:4248: brten nas te / klong gsal las /
NK115(re)001:4249: yum mkha' sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK115(re)001:4250: gsang ba zab mo'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK115(re)001:4251: ye shes bzhi yi rang bzhin du //
NK115(re)001:4252: gnyis su med par dbang bskur ro //
NK115(re)001:4254: dbang gang bskur na skal med rnams kyis mthong du
NK115(re)001:4255: mi rung bar ma zad thos pa tsam yang mi
NK115(re)001:4256: rung bas gasnga ba'i dabnga zhes bya la de nyid
NK115(re)001:4257: bskur ba ste / de yang dkyil 'khor gyi lho
NK115(re)001:4258: sgor phyag rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa bla ma
NK115(re)001:4259: la phul nas mig dar dang bcas gsol ba btab
NK115(re)001:4260: bskur ba ste / / gsung rdo rje longs spyod
NK115(re)001:4261: rdzogs sku'i ngo bo bla ma yab yum 'du shes
NK115(re)001:4263: phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par zhugs te phung khams skye
NK115(re)001:4264: mched gdod nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa ting
NK115(re)001:4265: nge 'dzin gyis gsal btab nas sangs rgyas thams cad
NK115(re)001:4266: spyan drangs la bstim ste rjes chags kyi mes zhu
NK115(re)001:4267: ba gsang dkyil du babs pa de yab kyi gsang
NK115(re)001:4268: rtse nas len pa thabs kyi gsang dbang dang /
