NK115(re)001:4269: yum gyi pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru nas len pa shes rab kyi dang /
NK115(re)001:4270: gnyis ka'i mkha' gsang nas len pa thabs shes gnyis med kyi gsang dbang zhes bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:4271: yang na me long yu ba can la sogs pas
NK115(re)001:4272: blang ba bdud rtsi dang bsres nas slob ma'i lcer
NK115(re)001:4273: bzhag pa snying gar bstim ste /
NK115(re)001:4274: rlung gi khams dang bsre bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:4275: da lta ni yongs grags la dgag bya dang dgos
NK115(re)001:4276: pa'i dbang gis dmigs pa de lta bu'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:4277: bdud rtsi'i rdzas tsam la brten te bskur ba yin
NK115(re)001:4278: no // gang gi gnyen por che ba ni /
NK115(re)001:4279: dgod pa tsam gyis tshim pa ltar lha 'phrul dag'a ba'i 'dod chagsa kyi gnyen po byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4281: rdzun la sogs pa ngaga gi las sngar bsags kyi sgrib pa thams cad sbyang zhing /
NK115(re)001:4282: rang gi dam tshig ngag 'phel byed kyi rtsa ba rlung gi byed bcings dang /
NK115(re)001:4283: gtum mo bsgom zhing bzlas brjod sogs la brtson pas phyin chad kyi las rgyun gcod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4284: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4285: gnas skabs bzhi las rmi lam dang /
NK115(re)001:4286: de'i snang ba phra ba dang bcas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4287: brjod 'dod kyi rtsa ba ngag gi thig le'i sgrib pa 'dag /
NK115(re)001:4289: lam gang bsgom pa la dbang na /
NK115(re)001:4290: thabs la mkhas pa'i man ngag la brten nas badga
NK115(re)001:4291: nyid kyi rtsol bas rtsa thig rlung gsum las su
NK115(re)001:4292: rung zhing ye shes khyad par can gyi ngo bor
NK115(re)001:4293: sgo gsum byin gyis rloba par byed pa'i lam kun
NK115(re)001:4294: rdzob sgyu ma'i rdzogs rim bsgom pa la dbang ba
NK115(re)001:4295: ste / de yang rnam shes 'gro 'ong gi nus
NK115(re)001:4296: pa can ma yin pa de rlung gi las kyis
NK115(re)001:4297: sna tshogs su 'phro bar 'gyur bas lus dang rtsa'i
NK115(re)001:4298: gnad la brten nas rlung zin na rnam par shes
NK115(re)001:4299: pa yang zin par 'gyur ba'i phyir rlung zin pa
NK115(re)001:4301: rlung la rnam grangs mang du gsungs kyang 'dir gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4304: 'jug pa ste bzhi po'i byed las tsam bshad na
NK115(re)001:4305: thog mar skye srid 'dzin pa'i dus na rnam par
NK115(re)001:4306: shes pa rlung la zhon te mngal du zhugs pa
NK115(re)001:4307: gang zhig khu khrag la brten nas gnas par gyur
NK115(re)001:4308: bas rnam par shes pa yang brgyal lo //
NK115(re)001:4309: de'i tshe ye shes kyi rlung gi bdag nyid du gnas pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:4310: de nas srog gi rlung nas brtsams te rlung bcu rim gyis skyes pas lus rgyas par byed la /
NK115(re)001:4311: rgyas pa de rgyu ba'i rlung gis ji srid gson
NK115(re)001:4312: pa'i bar du rul myags su mi 'gyur ba'i bya
NK115(re)001:4313: ba byed do // de yang ldang ba dang 'jug
NK115(re)001:4314: pa'i sgos dran bsam dang tshor ba sna tshogs su
NK115(re)001:4315: bskyed par byed pas lam dus su rnal 'byor gyi
NK115(re)001:4316: las kyang des byed pa yin la 'chi ba'i dus
NK115(re)001:4317: su ni rlung de dag 'gags pas srid pa de
NK115(re)001:4319: spyi rlung bcu po rang rang gi gnas nas rang
NK115(re)001:4320: rang gi bya ba byed pa dag kyang rlung rgyu
NK115(re)001:4321: ba'i rang bzhin yin mod kyang /
NK115(re)001:4322: re zhig srog rtsol rgyu ba'i dbye bas /
NK115(re)001:4325: ldang rgyu'i sbyor ba rnam pa gsum gyi dbye bas bzhag pa ni /
NK115(re)001:4327: gsum nyid sbyor ba rnam pa gsum //
NK115(re)001:4328: rnam gsum dbye bas rnam par bzhag /
NK115(re)001:4330: de la srog gi rgyu ba ni sna sgo kho na yin la /
NK115(re)001:4331: rnam shes kyi rlung ni ye shes kyi rlung gi
NK115(re)001:4332: bdag nyid de mthar thug de la rgyu ba med
NK115(re)001:4333: pa'i cha nas gnas pa nyid du bshad kyang /
NK115(re)001:4335: dbugs phyed bcas so gnyis kyi mtshams su rgyu bar bstan pa bzhin /
NK115(re)001:4336: rdo rje phreng ba las kyang thun bzhi'i mtshams su rgyu bar bshad do //
NK115(re)001:4337: nam mkha'i rlung ni da lta khyab pa'i tshul gyis rgyu zhing /
NK115(re)001:4338: dngos su rgyu ba ni 'chi ba'i gnas skabs kho na ste dengs pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK115(re)001:4339: de yang ye rlung a thung la gnas pa de
NK115(re)001:4340: gzung 'dzin gyi rtsa gnyis kyi dbang las srog dang
NK115(re)001:4341: rtsol ba gnyis su byung zhing /
NK115(re)001:4342: de las 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa 'dab rnams su nang gi yul nyer bzhi 'byung zhing /
NK115(re)001:4343: de'i rten 'brel gyis phyi rol du'ang gnas yul gyi bkod pa sogs snang ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:4344: nang gi rlung rgyu tshul gyis /
NK115(re)001:4346: nyin tshes khyim zhag gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:4347: chu tshod la sogs pa de dang mthun par snang ba yin pas /
NK115(re)001:4348: ji srid rlung sems kyi rgyu ba ma dag pa
NK115(re)001:4349: de srid du de'i dbang gis snang ba'i srid pa'i
NK115(re)001:4350: 'khrul 'khor mtha' yas pa 'di yang rgyun 'chad par
NK115(re)001:4351: mi 'gyur bas rang la ni theg pa gong 'og
NK115(re)001:4352: gang gi'ang nyams len gyi skal ba chad nas 'dug
NK115(re)001:4353: kyang / 'di nyid las dang po ba gzhan rnams la phan pa'i blos bris par rlom pas na /
NK115(re)001:4354: da lta mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs rim zab mo'i khrid
NK115(re)001:4355: rgyun phyogs so so na re zung tsam las med
NK115(re)001:4356: pa la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis 'di la nyams len
NK115(re)001:4358: phyi nang gi rten 'brel mtshungs pa'i tshul mdor bsdus
NK115(re)001:4359: pa 'di dag 'grel par yod pa 'dir bris na
NK115(re)001:4362: mtshan nyid theg par srid pa'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin la bshad pa de yang /
NK115(re)001:4363: rtsa ba las rlung gi rgyu ba la thug cing
NK115(re)001:4364: rlung sems byed pa gcig pas mnyam du dag dgos
NK115(re)001:4365: pa'i phyir sngags la ma brten par 'khrul snang phra
NK115(re)001:4366: ba rtsad nas ldog par mi 'gyur bar bshad pa'i
NK115(re)001:4368: rlung sems kyi rgyu ba 'gog pa'i thabs kyang brgyud
NK115(re)001:4369: nas 'gag pa'i thabs su 'gro ba dang dngos su
NK115(re)001:4370: byed pa bcings te btsan thabs su 'gog pa dang
NK115(re)001:4371: / de 'dra'i rtsa ba la ltos mi dgos par
NK115(re)001:4372: man ngag mchog gi lam gyis rang dwangs su 'gro
NK115(re)001:4373: ba de thams cad mthar thug pa'i don du gnad
NK115(re)001:4375: dbu ma'i dpyad rigs rnon po lta bu zhig med
NK115(re)001:4376: na lhag mthong yang dag pa skye mi srid pas
NK115(re)001:4377: lam rnam dag min snyam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4378: yang dngos su rtsa rlung gi byed pa bcings pa'i
NK115(re)001:4379: thabs la ma brten na las rlung gi rgyu ba
NK115(re)001:4380: 'gag pa'i thabs gzhan med pas 'di kho na las
NK115(re)001:4381: gzhan la dgos pa chung snyam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4382: yang rtsol med rang gzhag gi nyams len 'di ma
NK115(re)001:4383: gtogs rtsol bcas kyi lam thams cad ni tha chad
NK115(re)001:4384: pa'o snyam pa la sogs pa rang gang la mos
NK115(re)001:4385: pa'i lam de la zhen zhing mchog tu gzung nas
NK115(re)001:4386: gzhan dag dman par lta ba de ni lam gyi
NK115(re)001:4387: gegs chen po zhig yin par 'dug pas /
NK115(re)001:4388: de ltar mi sems par rang nyid gang la mos
NK115(re)001:4389: pa yod cing rgyud la phan pa de nyams su
NK115(re)001:4391: man ngag gi nyams len gzhan thams cad kyang rang
NK115(re)001:4392: gi nyasama su len rgyu de'i nang du dngos brgyud
NK115(re)001:4393: gang rung gis 'du zhing mthun pa'i tshul shes pa
NK115(re)001:4394: la 'bad cing / gal te nyams su ma lon
NK115(re)001:4395: na'ang bu ram thams cad mngar ba'i ror gcig pa
NK115(re)001:4396: la 'bad cing / ltar / bstan pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:4397: rnam grol gyi lam du gcig par shes pas kun
NK115(re)001:4398: la gus pa bskyed pa 'di ni gnad gal po
NK115(re)001:4399: che yin pas kun gyi thugs la zhog cig /
NK115(re)001:4400: nyams len snying po'i stong pa'i kha bshad kyi //
NK115(re)001:4401: ldir sgras gzhan la phan du re ba 'di //
NK115(re)001:4402: mdo shor bdag gi rang gshis yin mod kyang //
NK115(re)001:4403: dam pa'i zhal rgyun yin rlom 'dir bris so //
NK115(re)001:4404: des na 'dir gtum mo bsgom thabs kyi man ngag gis rtsa rlung gi byed pa bcings pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4405: bar 'dzag gi dmigs pa sogs la brten nas gzung
NK115(re)001:4406: 'dzina gyi rlung ro rkyang gi lam brgyud nas dbu
NK115(re)001:4407: mara 'dzuda pa'i thabs rgyud dang man ngag so so
NK115(re)001:4408: nas ji ltar bstan pa'i tshul la bslab cing /
NK115(re)001:4409: so so'i 'khrul 'khor gyi lag len rnams kyang byas na /
NK115(re)001:4410: rlung la brten nas rtsa mdud grol /
NK115(re)001:4411: gtum mo la brten nas byang sems zhu //
NK115(re)001:4412: 'khrul 'khor la brten nas rtsa gnas thams cad la
NK115(re)001:4413: byang sems kyis khyab pas gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK115(re)001:4414: 'gag / zad par la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo mang po thob /
NK115(re)001:4415: phrin las bzhi la mnga' dbang 'byor ba sogs lam
NK115(re)001:4416: rtags kyi yon tan du ma dbyar gyi chu bo
NK115(re)001:4418: lta ba gang rtogs na ranga byung gi ye shesa rtogs te /
NK115(re)001:4420: dang po snying ga'i nyon mongs pa'i rtsa 'khor du
NK115(re)001:4421: rlung sems 'dus pas nyon mongs pa sngar bas rags
NK115(re)001:4422: pa ltar gyur pa nyon mongs rang byung ye shes
NK115(re)001:4423: / de nas ro rkyang rnam rtog gi rtsa la
NK115(re)001:4424: rlung sems 'dus pas rnam rtog sngar bas rags pa
NK115(re)001:4425: ltar gyur pa rnam rtog rang byung ye shes /
NK115(re)001:4426: de nas dbu ma'i rtsa 'phred bstan 'ga' zhig tu
NK115(re)001:4427: rlung sems 'dus pas shes pa sngar bas rmongs pa
NK115(re)001:4428: ltar gyur pa s+n+rel gzhi rang byung ye shes /
NK115(re)001:4429: de nas dbu mar rlung sems 'dus nas rig pa
NK115(re)001:4430: gsal dwangs sngar bas khyad par du 'phags pa rgyud
NK115(re)001:4431: la skyes pa gsal zhing yangs pa rang byung ye
NK115(re)001:4432: shes so // snga ma gsum lta ba dug can dang phyi ma dug med do //
NK115(re)001:4434: ngag dag pa +aa li k+aa li la rang dbang
NK115(re)001:4435: thob pas 'gro drug gi sgra skad che chung bzang
NK115(re)001:4436: ngan thams cad ma 'dresa par sangs rgyas kyi gsung
NK115(re)001:4437: rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin du yongs su rdzogas
NK115(re)001:4438: shing rtogs pa'o // 'ad'a ka ma'i man ngag gang yin na /
NK115(re)001:4439: tshe 'dir grub mtha' de ma snyogs na 'chi kha'i
NK115(re)001:4440: sdud rim gyi rkyen gyis rlung thams cad dbu mar
NK115(re)001:4441: thim pa la phyogs pa na sngar gyi lta ba
NK115(re)001:4442: de'i ngang ma shor bar mi rtog pa'i ting nge
NK115(re)001:4443: 'dzin dpe yi 'oda gsal chena po'i nganga du 'pho
NK115(re)001:4444: ba'o // 'bras bu gang thob pa ni /
NK115(re)001:4445: rtsa khams kyi yi ge rlung gis bskyod nas rnam
NK115(re)001:4446: rtog yi ge'i rnam par skye zhing brjod pa'i sgrar
NK115(re)001:4447: snang ba dang grags pa'i ma dag pa'i 'grosa 'dus
NK115(re)001:4448: byas pa thams cad skye ba med pa'i dbyings su
NK115(re)001:4449: thima nas 'dus ma byas pa'i rang gdangs 'gag pa
NK115(re)001:4450: med pa langas spyod rdzagas pa'i sku dang /
NK115(re)001:4451: gsung dbyangs kyi yan lag druga cu la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:4452: gsung gi yon tan thams cad rig pa'i ngo bor
NK115(re)001:4453: lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogas pa'i gsunga rdo
NK115(re)001:4454: rje mngon du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:4455: de ltar yang glang po rab 'bogs las /
NK115(re)001:4456: yi ge'i 'gros thim sngags kyi lam dag pa //
NK115(re)001:4457: ngag gi sgrib byang rdzogs rim longs spyod rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:4460: // gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK115(re)001:4462: phung khams la sogs pa gadna gsuma lha yi rang
NK115(re)001:4463: bzhin du gdod nas grub cing ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK115(re)001:4464: kyang byin gyis brlabs te lha'i mngona rtogsa ji lta
NK115(re)001:4465: ba bzhin ngoma zhing rgyud nas gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid
NK115(re)001:4466: dang ldan pa'i mdzesa ma yi gasnga ba b+ha ga'i
NK115(re)001:4467: dkyila 'khor la brten pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:4468: dper na dngul chu bzhu btul gyi sbyor ba med na gser 'gyur mi 'grub pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:4469: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes mngon
NK115(re)001:4470: du byed pa la zhu bde bsgrub dgos shing de
NK115(re)001:4471: rjes chags la brten dgos te /
NK115(re)001:4473: e ma bde ba skyes tsam gyi //
NK115(re)001:4474: byang chub mchog ni thob byed pa'i //
NK115(re)001:4475: byed po bud med dang sbyor las //
NK115(re)001:4476: gzhan du nam yang ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:4477: sgyu ma'i de nyid thams cad las //
NK115(re)001:4478: bud med sgyu ma'i de nyid basngagasa //
NK115(re)001:4480: 'di la brten nas dbang gsum pa sgra ji bzhin
NK115(re)001:4481: par zhu ba'i gang zag ni rang lus thabs ldan
NK115(re)001:4482: sngon du song nas rtsa drang rlung byang thig le
NK115(re)001:4484: dbang dang po gnyis kyi lta ba la goms pas
NK115(re)001:4485: 'dzag bde la mi zhen par lta sgom khyad par
NK115(re)001:4486: can gyis lam du byed nus pa zhig dgos par
NK115(re)001:4487: gsungs la / des na de 'dra ba'i nus pa
NK115(re)001:4488: med pa'i las dang po pa'i gang zag rnams ni
NK115(re)001:4489: sngags la kha g.yar nas chags pa rang mtshan par
NK115(re)001:4490: spyad na ngan song gi rgyu las mi 'da' ba'i
NK115(re)001:4491: rang la rab byung gi sdom khrims zhu ba dang
NK115(re)001:4492: bsrung ba'i skal ba med kyang las 'bras la yid
NK115(re)001:4493: ches dang dkon mchog la dad pa re ci nus
NK115(re)001:4494: su e 'ong bltas nas rang tshod kyi nyams len
NK115(re)001:4496: de ltar mi byed par da dung sngags par rlom
NK115(re)001:4497: nas mchog 'dzin gyis rnyed grags sogs bsgrub pa ni
NK115(re)001:4498: log pa'i nga rgyal can zhes bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:4499: des 'tsho ba bsgrub pa'ang log pa'i 'tsho ba 'ba'
NK115(re)001:4500: zhig tu zad pas chos zab mo la brten nas
NK115(re)001:4501: rang gzhan phung la sbyor ba de lta bu las
NK115(re)001:4502: ni / dge sdig la blang dor nus tshod re
NK115(re)001:4503: byas nas nyam chung du 'dug pa'i khyim pa phal
NK115(re)001:4504: pa rnams dga' bar sems so //
NK115(re)001:4505: yang 'dul ba nas bshad pa'i sor sdom tsam tshul
NK115(re)001:4506: bzhin dbang po'i sgo bsdom pa la sogs pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:4507: nas bsrung nus na'ang sngags lam gyi thabs mkhas pa
NK115(re)001:4508: ji bzhin spyod pa'i nus pa med pa rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:4509: kyang / gsang sngags la dad mos kyis grol lam
NK115(re)001:4510: gtso bor gyur pa'i nyams len la brtson pa las
NK115(re)001:4511: thabs lam la dngos bstan ltar bslab na tshul khrims
NK115(re)001:4512: 'chal ba la sogs pa lam gyi gegs su 'gyur
NK115(re)001:4513: bas de lta bu la dgongs te /
NK115(re)001:4515: gsang ba shes rab dbang bskur ni //
NK115(re)001:4516: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyud chen las //
NK115(re)001:4517: rab tu 'bad pas bkag pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:4518: tshangs par spyod pas blang mi bya //
NK115(re)001:4520: 'on kyang ji skad bshad pa'i thabs mkhas la brten
NK115(re)001:4521: nus pa'i rigs la ni dbang gsum pa'i lam gyi
NK115(re)001:4522: phyag rgya bsten pa la sogs pa bkag pa ni
NK115(re)001:4523: med de / rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rten mchog ni
NK115(re)001:4524: tshangs par spyod pa'i rab byung yin par basngagasa pa'i
NK115(re)001:4525: med de / phyir te / phur pa'i rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:4526: dus kyi 'khor lo gnyis mthun par /
NK115(re)001:4527: gsum las dge slong mchog yin 'bring /
NK115(re)001:4528: dge tshul zhes bya de las gzhan /
NK115(re)001:4529: khyim na gnas pa tha ma'o //
NK115(re)001:4532: dge slong lus la phyag rgya bsten //
NK115(re)001:4533: lho nub srin po'i kha gnon mdzad //
NK115(re)001:4534: pad+ma k+aa ra zhes bya ba'i //
NK115(re)001:4535: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:4537: dge tshul lus la gdol pa'i rigs //
NK115(re)001:4538: phyag rgya ma dang dngos grub brnyes //
NK115(re)001:4539: ku ku r+ai pa zhes bya ba'i //
NK115(re)001:4540: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:4542: rgya bod kyi grub thob phal mo che lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:4543: gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams la snying nas
NK115(re)001:4545: rang nyid kyang tshe rabs phyi ma rnams su theg
NK115(re)001:4546: pa 'og ma'i bstan don tsam kho na la gcig
NK115(re)001:4547: tu zhen zhing mngon par rlom par mi byed par
NK115(re)001:4548: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos theg pa chen po spyi
NK115(re)001:4549: dang / khyad par rdo rje theg pa'i dgongs spyod rmad du byung ba nyams 'og tu tshud nas /
NK115(re)001:4550: snang ba bden med du shes pas 'khor 'das ro mnyam du rtogs te /
NK115(re)001:4551: nyon mongs ye shes su 'char ba'i thabs mkhas la tshul bzhin du spyod nus pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4552: phung sogs su snang ba'i chos thams cad gdod nas dag pa lha'i 'khor lor mthong zhing /
NK115(re)001:4553: khyad par shes rab kyi rang bzhin phyag rgya ma
NK115(re)001:4554: ni sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon sum du ston
NK115(re)001:4555: pa'i grogs yin pas gus pas dang du blang ste
NK115(re)001:4556: bsten nus pa zhig 'ong na ci ma rung snyam
NK115(re)001:4557: du smon par byed pa las /
NK115(re)001:4558: dman par bltas na smod pa la sogs pa ni
NK115(re)001:4559: lam 'di dang ches 'gal ba yin pas mi rung
NK115(re)001:4561: shes rab kyi rang bzhin phyag rgya la brten nas
NK115(re)001:4562: lhan skyes bde ba chen po'i ye shes la dbang
NK115(re)001:4563: bar byed pas na shera dabnga zhes bya ste de
NK115(re)001:4565: de yang rig ma brtag 'gugs sogs byas te sdom pas rgyud sbyangs shing /
NK115(re)001:4566: dbang dang man ngag gis smin par byas nas /
NK115(re)001:4567: dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su rdo rje slob dpon
NK115(re)001:4568: yab yum thugs rdo rje chos kyi sku'i ngo bor
NK115(re)001:4569: bzhugs pa la / man+dala phul nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK115(re)001:4570: mtshan ldan gyi phyag rgya slob bu la gtad pa na /
NK115(re)001:4571: slob bu yab yum gyis thabs shes gnyis ka lha'i 'du shes /
NK115(re)001:4572: gsang bar phyag mtshan dang yig 'bru bkod pa la sngags sam yi ge'i 'du shes //
NK115(re)001:4573: thabs mchog tu gyur pa 'di la brten nas sems
NK115(re)001:4574: can thams cad kyi don du bde chen lhan cig
NK115(re)001:4575: skyes pa'i ye shes mngon du bya'o snyam pa'i sems
NK115(re)001:4576: bskyed pa chos kyi 'du shes te de lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:4577: ngang nas snyoms par zhugs pa la phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK115(re)001:4578: rgyas thams cad spyan drangs te bstim pa rjes chags
NK115(re)001:4579: kyi mes byang chub kyi sems dang ro gcig tu
NK115(re)001:4580: zhu ba'i rgyun yas babs dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis phyin
NK115(re)001:4581: pa rdo rje nor bu'i bum par 'dzag med du
NK115(re)001:4582: bzung nas zhu bde nyams su myong ba'i rkyen las
NK115(re)001:4583: snang mched thob gsum gyi rim pas lhan cig skyes
NK115(re)001:4584: pa'i 'od gsal la bde ba chen po'i ngo bo
NK115(re)001:4585: shar bas yid byin gyis brlabs te thugs rdo rje
NK115(re)001:4586: spangs rtogs kyi nus pa khyad par can thob pa'o
NK115(re)001:4587: // de yang dbang gsum pa'i ye shes 'di mthong
NK115(re)001:4588: lam gyi ye shes min gyi don la 'phags yul
NK115(re)001:4589: gyi grub chen dag kyang dgag gzhag mdzad mod /
NK115(re)001:4590: spyi gang zag gi sbyang pa dang dbang po'i rim
NK115(re)001:4591: pas dbang thob lugs du ma yod de gsum pa'i
NK115(re)001:4592: dus nas don gyi ye shes ngo 'phrod pa'i gang
NK115(re)001:4594: de ni mthong lam gyi ye shes las mi 'da' la /
NK115(re)001:4595: yang dpe'i ye shes tsam skyes na'ang de la mchog dman du ma yod pas /
NK115(re)001:4596: de la brten nas don gyi 'od gsal ngo 'phrod mi 'phrod mtha' gcig tu ma nges shing /
NK115(re)001:4597: yang dbang po shin tu rtul pos thabs lam zab
NK115(re)001:4598: mo'i cho ga la brten nas bde ba dang bcas
NK115(re)001:4599: pa'i mi rtog pa yud tsam re nyams su myong
NK115(re)001:4600: ba yod kyang 'dod chags bde chen ye shes su
NK115(re)001:4601: 'char ma nus pas gshis kyi gnas tshul dang 'gal
NK115(re)001:4602: bas dpe'i 'od gsal tsam yang nyams su myong ba
NK115(re)001:4603: med pas mtha' gcig tu ma nges na'ang /
NK115(re)001:4604: spyi tsam du gang zag rim gyis pa rnams la
NK115(re)001:4605: dbang la brten nas ye shes skye tshul gyi rim
NK115(re)001:4606: pa ni gsum pa'i lam du dpe'i ye shes zhes
NK115(re)001:4607: bya ba bsam du med pa'i de kho na nyid
NK115(re)001:4608: kyi gzugs brnyan bde bas thabs byas pa'i lhan cig
NK115(re)001:4609: skyes dag'i shes rab la goms par byas pa las
NK115(re)001:4610: / bzhi pa'i dus na rang bzhin ci yin pa
NK115(re)001:4611: mthong ba'i thabs byung 'bras bu'i lhan skyes mngon sum
NK115(re)001:4613: rdo rje khros pa'i rtsa rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:4614: de yi shes rab ye shes kyi //
NK115(re)001:4615: dbang gi rdo rje thugs nyid dang //
NK115(re)001:4616: rdo rje sems dpa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK115(re)001:4617: sems nyid mkha' dang mtshungs par mthong //
NK115(re)001:4619: de ltar dbang gsum pa bskur thob sgra ji bzhin
NK115(re)001:4620: pa thams cad la yongs grags su shin tu dka'
NK115(re)001:4621: bas da lta rig tsaka sogs la brten nas dmigs
NK115(re)001:4622: pa 'bogs par byed pa 'dis kyang slob ma dbang
NK115(re)001:4623: po rno zhing dad mos can la ni skal ba
NK115(re)001:4625: gang ltar yang gsum pa'i nyams myong dang rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:4626: gyi ye shes de bde ba dang stong pa dbyer
NK115(re)001:4627: med pa tsam du bzhed pa la 'dra yang /
NK115(re)001:4628: rang lugs la thabs las skyes pa'i tshor ba de
NK115(re)001:4629: sems dang mtshungs ldan du yod pa la dpyad rig
NK115(re)001:4630: rnon pos stong pa'i nges shes kyis rgyas 'debs pa
NK115(re)001:4631: lta bu ma yin par lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:4632: shes spros pa'i rtog pa thams cad dbyings su zhi
NK115(re)001:4633: ba'i gshis kyi bzhugs tshul ji bzhin pa'am de dang
NK115(re)001:4634: rjes su mthun pa zhig la ngos 'dzin mdzad par
NK115(re)001:4635: 'dug snyam mo // gang gi gnyen por che ba ni /
NK115(re)001:4636: de ltar gsum pa'i dbang gisa smin par byas pas /
NK115(re)001:4637: pho mo phan tshun chags pas lag pa bcangsa pa
NK115(re)001:4638: sogs reg pa dang bzung ba tsam gyis tshima para
NK115(re)001:4639: 'gyur ba'i lha dag'a ldana pa la yod pa'i 'doda
NK115(re)001:4642: brnab sems la sogs pa sngar bsags pa'i yida kyi sgriba pa sbyanga zhing /
NK115(re)001:4643: rang gi dam tshig sems bde stong gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:4644: la goms par byas pas phyin chad kyi las rgyun
NK115(re)001:4645: gcod / ye shesa kyi sgrib pa zhes shes sgrib rags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4646: gnas skabs bzhi las tshogs drug snang ba dang bcas pa 'gags pa'i gnyid 'thug gi gnas skabs dang /
NK115(re)001:4649: lam gang bsgom pa la dbang na gzhan lus sna
NK115(re)001:4650: tshogs gzugs can ma'am pho nya'i lam la brten nas
NK115(re)001:4651: byang sems yas babs dang mas brtan gyis mthar thabs
NK115(re)001:4653: shes rab mcheda pa'i ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:4654: zung 'jug nyer thob kyi ye shes gsuma gyis drangs
NK115(re)001:4655: pa'i 'od gsal lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes bsgom
NK115(re)001:4657: lta ba gang rtogs na bde stong dag'a ba bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:4658: ye shesa khamas kun rdzob byang chub sems kya zhu
NK115(re)001:4659: bad'i thabs la brten nas 'gruba pa yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:4660: de yang dang po gsum dug can dang /
NK115(re)001:4662: snang ba gsum dang dga' ba bzhi po 'di dag
NK115(re)001:4663: gi don ni rdzogs rim gyi skabs su 'chad par
NK115(re)001:4664: 'gyur ro // gruba matha'a gang snyogs na bde stong
NK115(re)001:4665: dbyer med pa'i lta ba de yi ngang la phyag
NK115(re)001:4666: rgya ma bsten pa'i tshe na'ang rtag tu gnas shing
NK115(re)001:4669: kun+da chu ltar dwangs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4670: lus la skra dkar dang gnyer ma mi 'byung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:4671: kha zas dang gos mi dgos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4672: ri brag zang thal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:4673: phyi nang gi gnas yul dang /
NK115(re)001:4674: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro ma rnams dbang du 'du ba la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:4675: 'ad'a ka ma'i man ngag gang yin na /
NK115(re)001:4677: 'chi kha'i sdud rim gyis rkyen byas nas don dam
NK115(re)001:4678: byang chub sems kyi rten khams kyi thig le kun
NK115(re)001:4679: rdzob pa rnams lhan cig tu tshogs shing dbu mar
NK115(re)001:4680: cung zad zhugs pas gnas skabs dera snanga la ma
NK115(re)001:4681: grub pa'i ye shes rdo rje stong pa dang semsa
NK115(re)001:4682: bde ba ste / bde stong rdo rje sems dpa'
NK115(re)001:4683: gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal ngo 'phrod nas grol ba
NK115(re)001:4684: ste de yang snying ga'i rtsa mduda grol ba'i stobs
NK115(re)001:4685: kyis dpe'i ye shesa shar ba de nyid gzhi'i 'od
NK115(re)001:4686: gsal dang ma bu 'dres nas grol ba yin no
NK115(re)001:4687: bde ba ste / // 'bras bu gang thob na
NK115(re)001:4688: mthar thug grol ba'i tshe rtsa khams kyi dwangs ma'i
NK115(re)001:4689: thig le rlung gis 'pho ba'i 'gros dbyings dang ye
NK115(re)001:4690: shes zung du 'jug pa'i ngang du thim ste chos
NK115(re)001:4691: kyi dbyings dang nam mkha'i mthar khyaba pa ste tshad
NK115(re)001:4692: bde ba ste / // las 'das shing / bsam
NK115(re)001:4693: gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes zung 'jug thugas kyi
NK115(re)001:4694: rdo rje sems byung gi rnyog pa zhi ba'i dwangas
NK115(re)001:4695: ma'i ye shes chos kyi sku mngon du 'gyur ro
NK115(re)001:4696: bde ba ste / // las 'das shing / // de ltar yang glang po rab 'bogs las /
NK115(re)001:4697: bdud rtsi khams kyi 'gros thim bcud kyi lam //
NK115(re)001:4698: sems kyi sgrib sbyangs dwangs ma chos kyi sku //
NK115(re)001:4700: bzhi pa dbang gi mchog tshig dbang rin po che bshad pa la /
NK115(re)001:4701: dkyil 'khor gang la brten pa ni /
NK115(re)001:4702: sngar sna tshogs gzugs can ma las brnyed pa'i dpe'i
NK115(re)001:4703: 'od gsal de ni don dam byang chuba semas kyi
NK115(re)001:4704: myu gu lta bu yin te de nyid don gyi
NK115(re)001:4705: 'od gsal du ngo sprad pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:4707: mdo sde chos mngon thams cad nas //
NK115(re)001:4708: bud med rnams ni smod mdzad pa //
NK115(re)001:4709: sna tshogs slob ma'i snod phyir bshad //
NK115(re)001:4710: de kho na nyid sbas nas gsungs //
NK115(re)001:4711: phung po lnga dang rnam bral ba'i //
NK115(re)001:4712: mya ngan 'das pa blta bar bya //
NK115(re)001:4713: zhes phar phyin man chad du de kho na nyid
NK115(re)001:4714: zab mo rjes dpag tsam las ston par ma nus
NK115(re)001:4715: pa sngags lam du thabs la brten nas sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:4716: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa glo bur du bcom
NK115(re)001:4717: nas snang ba gsum gyis drangs pa'i 'od gsal lhan
NK115(re)001:4718: cig skyes pa'i ye shes ji bzhi'i pa'i ngo bo
NK115(re)001:4719: mngon du mthong zhing de la goms pas mtha' gang
NK115(re)001:4720: du'ang ma reg pa'i gshis kyi gnas lugs rnam thar
NK115(re)001:4721: bzhi ldan gyi ye shes sam /
NK115(re)001:4722: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i de kho na nyid du
NK115(re)001:4723: mthar phyin te phung po'i snyigs ma thams cad dwangs
NK115(re)001:4724: ma mi shigs pa'i thig le'i ngo bor dengs nas
NK115(re)001:4725: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin du mngon
NK115(re)001:4727: de lta bu'i dpe'i lhan skyes 'od gsal ba'i ye
NK115(re)001:4728: shes de'i ngang la slob bu mnyam par gzhag pa
NK115(re)001:4729: na ye shes de la dkyil 'khora zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:4731: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK115(re)001:4732: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK115(re)001:4733: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor bas //
NK115(re)001:4736: de la brten nas dbang gang bskur na /
NK115(re)001:4737: bla ma ngo bo nyid kyi sku ye shes rdo rje'i ngo bor bzhugs te /
NK115(re)001:4738: slob bu'i dbang gsuma pa'i dus kyi yas babs kyi
NK115(re)001:4739: dga' bzhi rdzogs nas thabs kyi ldog pa las mas
NK115(re)001:4740: brtan gyi dga' bzhi'i mthar nyamsa su myong ba'i bde
NK115(re)001:4741: stong dbyer med kyi ye shes kyi ngang la mnyam
NK115(re)001:4742: par gzhag pa na de dang rang sems lhan cig
NK115(re)001:4743: skyes pa'i ye shes ro gcig tu ngo sprad pa
NK115(re)001:4745: bde ba'i ngang de nyid gang du'ang ma grub pa'i
NK115(re)001:4746: rang bzhin spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK115(re)001:4747: rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bor slob dpon gyis tshiga
NK115(re)001:4748: gisa mtshona pa'i sgo nas ngo sprad pa bde ba
NK115(re)001:4749: chen po'i dbang dam tshig gi bzhi pa yin la
NK115(re)001:4750: / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:4751: de kho na nyid sku dang ye shes zung du
NK115(re)001:4752: 'jug pa dbyer med bde ba chen po mchog gi
NK115(re)001:4753: ting nge 'dzin rgyud la skyes pa don gyi bzhi
NK115(re)001:4754: / pa / ye shes ngos ma zin na las
NK115(re)001:4755: rgya la brten nas nyams myong 'dres pa rten can
NK115(re)001:4756: / pa / gyi bzhi pa / de las lam goms par byed pa lam gyi bzhi pa /
NK115(re)001:4757: dga' bzhi'i 'gros re re la'ang dga' chung bzhi bzhir phye ba'i bcu drug gi //
NK115(re)001:4759: de nas re res sbyor mthong dang /
NK115(re)001:4761: tha ma bcu drug pa mi slob pa'i lam ste /
NK115(re)001:4762: yas babs rgyu dang mas brtan 'bras bu'i sa lam dang sbyar te /
NK115(re)001:4763: mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu drug pa'i mthar khu
NK115(re)001:4764: rdul steng 'og tu thim pa'i skad cig la rlung
NK115(re)001:4765: 'gags pas / de gsum gyi 'gyur ba myong ba'i
NK115(re)001:4766: shes rig kyang rgyun chad de sku bzhi mngon du
NK115(re)001:4767: byed pa ni 'bras bu'i bzhi pa'o //
NK115(re)001:4768: de ltar yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK115(re)001:4769: gnas ni ye shes bcu drug po //
NK115(re)001:4770: tshogs sbyor la sogs dang po nas //
NK115(re)001:4771: mthar phyin sangs rgyas sa nyid de //
NK115(re)001:4772: gnas bzhi de bzhin dbye ba las //
NK115(re)001:4773: gnyis pa'i gnyis pa rab dga' sogs //
NK115(re)001:4774: pha rol phyin dang sa mtshan nyid //
NK115(re)001:4775: mtshungs phyir rdzogs par bshad pa yin //
NK115(re)001:4777: gang gi gnyen por che ba ni /
NK115(re)001:4778: lha 'athaba brala mana chada kyi 'dod khams pa rnams
NK115(re)001:4779: la yod pa'i 'khyud sbyor gyi 'doda chagas kyi gnyen
NK115(re)001:4782: sgo gsuma phra ba'i sgrib pa daga ste de yang
NK115(re)001:4783: sgo gsum tha dada du 'dzina pa'i sems kyi dri
NK115(re)001:4784: ma shin tu phra ba cha mnyam par sbyong zhing
NK115(re)001:4785: rgyun gcod / shes sgrib ches phra ba 'pho ba'i bag chags cha dang bcas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:4786: gnas skabs bzhi las snyoms 'jug gi gnas skabs te /
NK115(re)001:4787: de yang 'dzag ba de'i sred pa yin pas khu
NK115(re)001:4788: rdul rlung gsum las 'khor ba'i lus ngag yid gsum
NK115(re)001:4789: dang / bde sdug btang snyoms gsum 'char bas khu
NK115(re)001:4790: rdul rlung gsum la cha mnyam du 'jug pa'i rtog
NK115(re)001:4791: dang / pa dang / sgo gsum phra ba'i bag chags 'dzin pa'i thig le'i sgrib pa rnams dag /
NK115(re)001:4794: ngo bo spros pa dang bral ba'i stong pa'i thiga
NK115(re)001:4795: le rang bzhin gsal ba riga pa'i gdangs ma 'gags
NK115(re)001:4796: pa las thugs rje'i rol pa sku dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:4797: su 'char ba'i snying po can rnam thar sgo gsum
NK115(re)001:4798: gyi rang bzhin rig stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK115(re)001:4799: don rtogs / lam gang bsgom pa la dbang na /
NK115(re)001:4801: rig stong rdzogs pa chen po bsgom pa la dbang /
NK115(re)001:4802: de yang nang rgyud thun mong ba'i dbang bzhi pa thob pas ni /
NK115(re)001:4803: rang rang gi skabs kyi zung 'jug gi rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:4804: bsgom pa'i skal ba can du byas pa yin la
NK115(re)001:4805: / theg rtse'i bzhi pa bye brag pa thob na ka dag khregs chod dang /
NK115(re)001:4806: lhun grub thod rgal gyi lam thun mong ma yin par sgom pa la dbang ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:4807: grub matha'a gang snyogs na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK115(re)001:4808: ye shesa bde stong phyag rgya chen po rtogs pa
NK115(re)001:4809: yin te 'khor 'das thams cad blang dor dang spang
NK115(re)001:4813: gasnga chena phyag rgya chena po sngar gyi lta ba de'i ngang la 'pho bar byed pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:4816: las la sbyar ba gsum ste 'da' ka'i man ngag
NK115(re)001:4817: thams cad mtshungs par da ltar yang yang goms cha
NK115(re)001:4819: 'chi bar nges pa'i tshe las la sbyar te gsal 'debs byed mkhan gzhan yod na de'i tshe dang /
NK115(re)001:4820: med kyang rang nyid kyis sdig ltung thams cad snying nas bshags te /
NK115(re)001:4821: bla ma la mos gus drag po dang bcas /
NK115(re)001:4822: da lta'i 'chi ba 'di la brten nas sems can
NK115(re)001:4823: thams cad kyi don du rang sems sangs rgyas su
NK115(re)001:4824: ngo 'phrod pa zhig bya dgos snyam du nyams len
NK115(re)001:4825: gyi ngang bskyangs te 'pho bar byed dgos gsungs //
NK115(re)001:4826: 'brasa bu gang thob na snying po ye shes rlung
NK115(re)001:4827: gi 'gros thim zhes ye shes kyi rlung las rlung
NK115(re)001:4828: gis bslad pa'i cha shin tu phra ba dang bcas
NK115(re)001:4829: pa thams cad dag nas mngon du gyur te ye
NK115(re)001:4830: shes rdo rje mkha'a khyab dbyings kyi rang bzhin dang
NK115(re)001:4831: zung du 'jug pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob
NK115(re)001:4832: pa'o // de ltar yang glang po rab 'bogs las /
NK115(re)001:4833: rlung gi 'gros thim mi shigs rdo rje'i sku //
NK115(re)001:4834: lus ngag yid dag ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK115(re)001:4836: skabs 'di dag gi lta ba rnams kyi nyams myong ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:4837: mtshan nyid theg par thos bsam gyis gtan la dbab pa'i lta ba bshad pa dang mi 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:4838: rtsa'i 'gros thim sogs ni ma dag pa'i rtsa rlung
NK115(re)001:4839: thig le rnams dag pa ye shes kyi ngang du
NK115(re)001:4840: thim pa'o // mthar thug gi 'bras bu rnams thob
NK115(re)001:4841: rung gi sa bon rgyud la bzhag pa tsam yin
NK115(re)001:4842: gyi dbang de dag thob pa tsam gyis dngos su
NK115(re)001:4843: thob pa ni ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:4844: de yang bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa las dbang legs pa thob kyang /
NK115(re)001:4845: dam tshig tsam yang ma bsrungs na shi ma thag
NK115(re)001:4846: ngan song du skye bar 'gyur na'ang ha cang yun
NK115(re)001:4847: ring por mi thogs par gsang sngags kyi chos dang
NK115(re)001:4848: 'phrad nas lam bsgom pa'i skal ba yod par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:4849: la / gal te dam tshig gi rim pa bsrung
NK115(re)001:4850: yang tshe 'dir bskyed rdzogs la goms par ma byas
NK115(re)001:4851: na rigs gtsang ma rnams su skye ba bdun la
NK115(re)001:4852: sogs par brgyud de lam mthar phyin nas grol bar
NK115(re)001:4853: la / gsungs shing / dbang thob cing dam tshig
NK115(re)001:4854: la gnas nas lam la 'bad na gong du ji
NK115(re)001:4855: skad bshad pa'i 'bras bu sku bzhi'i yon tan thams
NK115(re)001:4856: cad tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha'am bar do gang rung du
NK115(re)001:4858: de'ang dbang rang rang gi skabs su bshad pa'i 'bras
NK115(re)001:4859: bu de dag lam gzhan rnams dang ma 'brel bar
NK115(re)001:4860: rang rang gi lam rkyang pas thob mi nus pas
NK115(re)001:4861: zung 'brel du bsgoms pas sku bzhi'i yon tan de
NK115(re)001:4862: rim can du thob pa ma yin par cig car
NK115(re)001:4864: dper na mtshan nyid theg par tshogs gnyis kyi rgyu las sku gnyis 'grub par bshad kyang /
NK115(re)001:4865: bsod nams kyi tshogs de ye shes dang ma 'brel
NK115(re)001:4866: bar de rkyang pas gzugs sku mi thob pas tshogs
NK115(re)001:4867: gnyis zung 'brel du bsags pas sangs rgyas pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:4868: sku gnyis cig car du thob par bzhed pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:4869: no // grub mtha' yang lam de bsgoms pas da bzod grub pa'o //
NK115(re)001:4870: gnyis pa dbang gi sgra don ni /
NK115(re)001:4871: dbang zhes pa'i skad dod kyi sgra don dang sbyar
NK115(re)001:4872: na dri ma 'khrud pa dang nus pa 'jog pa
NK115(re)001:4873: gnyis la 'jug ste 'di ltar a b+hi shiny+tsa zhes
NK115(re)001:4874: pa'i sgrasa glo bura gyi dri ma gtor ba'i don
NK115(re)001:4875: ston te // de yang gong du bshad pa'i dbang
NK115(re)001:4876: bzhi rang rang gi dag bya rnams rang gnas kyi
NK115(re)001:4877: ye shes la sgrib par byed pa'i dri ma yin
NK115(re)001:4878: zhing chos nyid kyi gshis la ma zhugs pas glo
NK115(re)001:4879: ston te // bur ba ste / de nyid dbang
NK115(re)001:4880: thob pa tsam gyis skal ba mchog dang ldan pa
NK115(re)001:4881: rnams ma gtogs mi spong yang dbang rang rang gi
NK115(re)001:4882: lam gyis ni dngos su spong bas dbang thob pa'i
NK115(re)001:4883: dus nas 'dag rung du byas pas gtor ba dang
NK115(re)001:4884: she ka ta zhes pa'i sgras skala ba blugas pa
NK115(re)001:4885: ston te // bur ba ste / ste / chos
NK115(re)001:4886: nyid la sku bzhi'i yon tan rang chas su yod
NK115(re)001:4887: pa de dbang rang rang gi lam gyis sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:4888: bsal ba'i stobs kyis dngos su mngon du 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:4889: phyir dbang thob pa'i dus nas lam sgom rung dang
NK115(re)001:4890: ston te // bur ba ste / ste / / yon tan skye rung du song ba'i phyir te /
NK115(re)001:4891: mdor na sgrib pa mtha' dag spang ba la dbang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:4892: yon tan mtha' dag thob pa la dbang ba rnama
NK115(re)001:4893: pa gnyis su 'jug pas dbang gi nges tshig grub
NK115(re)001:4894: pa yin no // gsum pa rgyu lam 'bras bu'i dbang bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:4895: dabnga bzhi'i ngo bo mchoga gi yon tan sku gsung
NK115(re)001:4896: thugs ye shes rdo rje bzhi'i rang bzhin ranga la
NK115(re)001:4897: lhan skyes su sman gyi ro dang nus pa dang
NK115(re)001:4898: / dri dang zhu rjes ltar gansa pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:4899: de yang khamas druga gi nang nas sems ni ming bzhi'i phung po can ye shes kyi rten dang /
NK115(re)001:4900: phung po'i rten ni 'byung ba lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:4902: rtsa'i brten pa srog gi rlung dang /
NK115(re)001:4903: rlung gi brten pa byang chub kyi sems yin pas
NK115(re)001:4904: dbang bzhi'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu rtsa rlung thig le
NK115(re)001:4905: sems dang bcas pa mngon gyur du ldan zhing de
NK115(re)001:4906: thams cad kyi rang bzhin bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK115(re)001:4907: po la dbang bzhi'i yon tan 'byor pa de ni
NK115(re)001:4908: rgyu'am gzhi yi dabnga zhes bya ba yina te /
NK115(re)001:4910: sems ni ming bzhi'i phung po ste //
NK115(re)001:4911: phung po'i rten ni 'byung ba lnga //
NK115(re)001:4912: 'byung ba'i rten ni rtsa rnams so //
NK115(re)001:4913: rtsa rnams brten pa srog gi rlung //
NK115(re)001:4914: srog rlung brten pa byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:4916: rdo rje phur pa'i bshad rgyud las //
NK115(re)001:4917: sems nyid rtogs na dbang yin te //
NK115(re)001:4918: thams cad rang rig phur bu mchog /
NK115(re)001:4920: de ltar rgyu dbang rang la gnas pa mngon du
NK115(re)001:4921: byed pa thabs su rdo rje slob dpona mtshan nyid
NK115(re)001:4922: dang ldan pa nyid kyisa cho ga sbyor dngos rjes
NK115(re)001:4923: gsum tshang zhing rnam par dag pas bskur ba dang
NK115(re)001:4924: / de las gzhan pa bdag 'jug dang /
NK115(re)001:4925: rnal 'byor zab mo'i dbang bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:4926: byin rlabs 'pho ba'i rgyun la ranga gi dmigas pasa
NK115(re)001:4927: yang yang 'drisa shing goms par byed pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:4929: rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa'i skabs su slob lam mthar
NK115(re)001:4930: phyin nas sa bcu'i rgyun matha'i dusa su 'oda zera
NK115(re)001:4931: chena po'i dabnga thob par bshad pa bzhina du ranga
NK115(re)001:4932: gi semas nyid la ldan pa'i dbang gi de kho
NK115(re)001:4933: na nyid nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lta bu de 'khor
NK115(re)001:4934: ba'i rang bzhin kun gzhi tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:4935: dri ma glo bur ba sprin sbubs lta bus bsgribs
NK115(re)001:4936: te mi mngon par gyur ba de nyid lam dus
NK115(re)001:4937: kyi dbang dang / mngon rtogs bskyed rdzogs rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:4938: byed las rlung lta bu des dri ma glo bur
NK115(re)001:4939: ba bsal ba'i mod la gzhi na yod pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:4940: tan sku bzhi'i ngo bor smina pa ste mngon du
NK115(re)001:4942: de'i tshul mthar lam pa la sangs rgyas longs spyod
NK115(re)001:4943: rdzogs pa'i sku ye shes sgyu ma'i rnam rol du
NK115(re)001:4944: snang bas zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas snang gsum
NK115(re)001:4945: 'pho ba'i bag chags phra ba dag nas ston 'khor
NK115(re)001:4946: dgongs pa dbyer med du 'gyur bar yang bshad la
NK115(re)001:4947: / don du rang rig gi ngo bo la sgrib
NK115(re)001:4948: byed kyi dri ma mtha' dag dag nas nam sangs
NK115(re)001:4949: rgyas pa de'i tshe 'bras bu'i chos thams cad la
NK115(re)001:4950: mnga' dbang 'byor bas 'brasa bu'i dabnga zhes bya'o /
NK115(re)001:4951: de yang phar phyin theg pa ltar rgyu 'bras snga
NK115(re)001:4952: phyi can ma yin yang gnas skabs tsam du rgyu
NK115(re)001:4953: lam 'bras bu'i dbang gi tha snyad btags pa yin
NK115(re)001:4954: no // de dag kyang bsdu na rnam pa gnyis su 'du ste /
NK115(re)001:4955: dbang snga ma gsum 'dus byas kun rdzob pa'i cha
NK115(re)001:4956: yin te ngo sprod tshul dang lam nyams su len
NK115(re)001:4957: tshul gnyis ka sems dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:4958: phyi ma ni 'dus ma byas don dam pa'i bden pa'i rang bzhin yin te /
NK115(re)001:4959: ngo sprod tshul dang nyams su len tshul gnyis ka sems las 'das pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:4961: gsum po 'jig rten kun rdzob ste //
NK115(re)001:4962: bzhi pa don gyi dam pa yin //
NK115(re)001:4964: bzhi pa sdom pa'i thob mtshams bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:4965: de ltar dabnga bzhi po mtha' rten dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:4966: rdzogas pa'i tshe na riga 'dzina gyi sdoma pa'ang thoba
NK115(re)001:4967: pa yin te / de'ang slob bu'i sgo gsum rdo
NK115(re)001:4968: rje gsum du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus nas brtsams
NK115(re)001:4969: te rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la rang lugs kyi
NK115(re)001:4970: dngos gzhi rdzogs nas slob dpon gyi dbang bskur ba'i
NK115(re)001:4971: pa yin te / mtha' dang / bla med la
NK115(re)001:4972: bum dbang gi mthar bskyed rim gyi sngags sdom dngos
NK115(re)001:4973: pa yin te / mtha' dang / bstan dang /
NK115(re)001:4974: dbang gong ma gsum la de dang ngo bo gcig
NK115(re)001:4975: pa'i rdzogs rim gyi sdom pa ste so so'i mtshams
NK115(re)001:4976: su gsar du thob pa na 'og ma'i ngo bo
NK115(re)001:4977: je bzang du song zhing ldog pa tha dad par
NK115(re)001:4978: yod pas rang rang la ltos pa'i yon tan dang
NK115(re)001:4979: pa yin te / mtha' dang / bstan dang /
NK115(re)001:4980: / rtsa ltung gnyis ka bskyed pa'i rten du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:4981: pa yin te / mtha' dang / bstan dang /
NK115(re)001:4982: / ba yin no // de nas dam tshig bsrung
NK115(re)001:4983: bar dam bcas nas yon dbul bar bya ste /
NK115(re)001:4985: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK115(re)001:4986: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK115(re)001:4989: de ltar phul ba'i phan yon yang /
NK115(re)001:4991: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK115(re)001:4992: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin /
NK115(re)001:4993: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK115(re)001:4996: gsum pa dbang thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK115(re)001:4997: de ltar mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon gyis /
NK115(re)001:4998: dad mos can gyi slob ma cho ga phun sum
NK115(re)001:4999: tshogs pa la brten nas dbang bskur ba na rab
NK115(re)001:5000: dbang don gyi ye shes khyad par can rgyud la
NK115(re)001:5001: skye / 'bring nyams myong gi sne zin /
NK115(re)001:5002: tha ma go bas ngo 'phrod pa gang yang rung bas dabnga rnal ma zhig thoba na /
NK115(re)001:5003: skyesa bu de'i rgyud ni dper na gshol gyis rmo
NK115(re)001:5004: ba la sogs pa'i sgo nas tha ba'i skyon legs
NK115(re)001:5005: par sbyangas ba'i zhing sa gshin po der nas la
NK115(re)001:5006: sogs pa'i sa bona bazhaga pa ste btab na de
NK115(re)001:5007: chu lud drod gsher gyi rkyen dang 'dzom pas skad
NK115(re)001:5008: cig re re bzhin myu gu'i dngos po cher 'phel
NK115(re)001:5009: nas 'bras bu yongs su rdzogs par smin pa mthar
NK115(re)001:5010: thug par 'gyur ba ji lta ba bzhina du /
NK115(re)001:5011: sngar yon tan skyer mi rung ba'i tha ba lta
NK115(re)001:5012: bu de dbang gis legs par sbyangs nas sku bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:5013: sa bon bzhag pas smin rung du byas pa de
NK115(re)001:5014: dbang so so'i lam bskyed rdzogs la gzhol ba'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:5015: dang 'dzom na skad cig re re bzhin /
NK115(re)001:5016: sgo gsum dang tha dad du 'dzin pa ste bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:5017: las dang nyon mongs shes bya bag chags kyi sgriba pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5018: gnas skabs bzhi'i sgrib pa sogs rim gyis daga ste
NK115(re)001:5019: slob lam bzhi'i ngo bor gyur pa'i byang chub phyogs
NK115(re)001:5020: kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:5021: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK115(re)001:5022: tshogs gnyis kyi yon tan thams cad bskyed pa dang
NK115(re)001:5023: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gnyis kyi sgo nas bgrod cing
NK115(re)001:5024: gong nas gong du 'phel te sku gsung thugs ye
NK115(re)001:5029: ngo bo nyid sku ste sku bzhi la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:5030: bzhi la gnas pa'i rang bzhin sgrib pa bral stobs
NK115(re)001:5031: kyis 'bras bu'i chos su rnam par bzhag pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:5032: tan ji snyed pa thams cad mngona du byed pa
NK115(re)001:5033: yin no // de ltar yang 'dus pa las /
NK115(re)001:5034: 'di ni bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK115(re)001:5035: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK115(re)001:5036: ye shes rgya mtsho'i rnam par brgyan //
NK115(re)001:5040: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK115(re)001:5041: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK115(re)001:5042: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK115(re)001:5043: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:5045: ma thob pa'i nyes dmigs ni //
NK115(re)001:5047: dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs dang /
NK115(re)001:5048: dam tshig rnams ni spangs pa dang //
NK115(re)001:5049: gsang ba'i de nyid mi shes pas //
NK115(re)001:5050: bsgrubs kyang ci yang mi 'grub bo //
NK115(re)001:5053: dper na bu tsha med pa'i khyim //
NK115(re)001:5054: shi ba tsam gyis stongs pa yin //
NK115(re)001:5055: de bzhin dbang dang bral ba'i dus //
NK115(re)001:5056: ye shes kun gyis stongs pa yin //
NK115(re)001:5057: dper na pi wam sbyor sogs kun //
NK115(re)001:5058: rgyud dang bral na brdung mi nus //
NK115(re)001:5059: de bzhin dbang dang bral na ni //
NK115(re)001:5062: des na byang sngags kyi sdom pa 'di ni sor
NK115(re)001:5063: sdom lta bu lan cig las zhu rgyu med pa
NK115(re)001:5064: ma yin par / lan grangs mang por zhus na
NK115(re)001:5065: yon tan gyi tshogs gong du 'phel zhing nyams len
NK115(re)001:5067: nyes pa'i tshogs thams cad dag par 'gyur ba yin pas yang yang len pa la 'bad par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5068: khyad par du dbang ni gsang sngags kyi lam bsgrub
NK115(re)001:5069: pa la med du mi rung zhing shin tu gal
NK115(re)001:5070: che ba'i tshul / spyi don 'od gsal snying po las /
NK115(re)001:5071: mdor na rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi thog ma'i
NK115(re)001:5072: 'jug sgo gcig pur gyur pa dbang zhes bya ba
NK115(re)001:5074: 'bras bu thob pa la dbang bar byed pa'i thabs khyad par can yin pas na /
NK115(re)001:5075: 'di la brten nas sngags kyi lta ba rgyud la skye ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5076: de'i don bzhin bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5077: spyod pa la nus pa thob pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5078: sgrub pa dang mchod pa phrin las sngags dang phyag rgya rnams don yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5079: dam tshig thob par byed pas na dbang ni kun gyi 'byung gnas lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:5080: go 'phang gi rim pa thob par byed pa la
NK115(re)001:5081: rgyal po lta bu yin pas na thams cad 'di
NK115(re)001:5082: la brten par gyur cing mthar thug gi don la
NK115(re)001:5083: bskur thob med par ye nas chos sku chen por
NK115(re)001:5084: rdzogs pa'i don mthong na rang rig pa rtsal gyi
NK115(re)001:5085: dbang thob pa ste rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul nyid
NK115(re)001:5086: du ni dbang thams cad mthar phyin pa yin no
NK115(re)001:5088: gnyis pa grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi lam bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:5092: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5093: de ltar dbang gis rgyud legs par smin par byas nas /
NK115(re)001:5094: gnyis pa rang bzhin ye nas dag pa'i chos nyid
NK115(re)001:5095: la glo bur du kun rtog mthu brtas pa'i dbang
NK115(re)001:5096: gis 'khrul ba'i 'khor lor 'phyan pa nyid de bzhin
NK115(re)001:5097: gshegs pa rnams kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba bsam
NK115(re)001:5098: gyis mi khyab pa'i dbyings su grol bar byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:5099: lam gzhan las chos khyad par du 'phags pa gsang
NK115(re)001:5100: sngags nang rgyud gsum gyi nyams len la rnam grangs
NK115(re)001:5101: dpag tu ma mchis pa zhig yod kyang mdor bsdu
NK115(re)001:5102: na theg pa chen po'i lam gyi mdo chings thabs
NK115(re)001:5103: shes gnyis sam tshogs gnyis po lta dgongs zab mo
NK115(re)001:5104: dang thabs la mkhas pa'i sgo nas ma dag pa'i
NK115(re)001:5105: snang zhen sbyong phyir gdan gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK115(re)001:5106: bsgom pa bskyed pa'i rim pa khyad chos bzhi dang
NK115(re)001:5107: ldan pa dang / sgo gsum gyi snyigs ma gcod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5108: snying po'i don la 'jug pa'i phyir lhan cig skyes
NK115(re)001:5109: pa'i ye shes la goms su 'jug pa rdzogas pa'i
NK115(re)001:5110: rim pa khyad chos gsum dang ldan pa ste rnama
NK115(re)001:5112: bskyed rim gyi khyad chos bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:5113: cho ga'i khyad par rgyud nas gsungs pa'i bskyed chog tshang ba /
NK115(re)001:5114: rang 'bras kyi khyad par sngags kyi mthu bskyed nus pa /
NK115(re)001:5115: ngo bo'i khyad par zhu bde dang stong nyid kyi rang bzhin /
NK115(re)001:5116: byed las kyi khyad par rdzogs rim gyi smin byed du 'gro ba'o //
NK115(re)001:5117: rdzogs rim gyi khyad par gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:5118: rgyu'i khyad par rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa /
NK115(re)001:5119: byed las kyi khyad par rtsa rlung thig le dbu mar dag par byed pa /
NK115(re)001:5120: rnam pa'i khyad par lhan skyes kyi bde ba stong
NK115(re)001:5121: gzugs dang ngo bo gcig tu gyur pa'i bde stong
NK115(re)001:5122: zung 'jug go // de lta bu'i bskyed rdzogs gnyis
NK115(re)001:5123: po 'di dbang rnon gyis ni dang po nas zung
NK115(re)001:5125: de ltar mi nus pa rnams kyis dang po bskyed
NK115(re)001:5126: rim la brtan pa thob nas gzod rdzogs rim la
NK115(re)001:5127: bslab dgos te / klu sgrub kyis /
NK115(re)001:5128: bskyed pa'i rim la legs gnas shing //
NK115(re)001:5129: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod rnams la //
NK115(re)001:5130: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK115(re)001:5131: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur gsungs //
NK115(re)001:5133: lam 'di dag mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam las khyad
NK115(re)001:5134: par du 'phags pa'i tshul mdor bsdu na spang rtogs
NK115(re)001:5135: kyi yon tan bskyed pa'i tshul gyis te /
NK115(re)001:5136: de la spang bya spong ba'i tshul yang sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:5137: gnyis las gtso bor bskyed rim gyis lha'i nga rgyal
NK115(re)001:5138: brtan pa dang / 'dod yon dang chos kyi phyag rgya la rol bar blta ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5139: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa skyong ba sogs nyon
NK115(re)001:5140: mongs pa lam du byed cing de thams cad chos
NK115(re)001:5141: nyid kyi lta bas zin par byed pas shes sgrib
NK115(re)001:5142: kyang mi spong ba ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:5143: sdug kun gnyis las kun 'byung ni nyon mongs lam
NK115(re)001:5144: du byed pa de nyid kyis srid par 'phen byed
NK115(re)001:5145: kyi las thams cad yang dag pa'i lam du bsgyur
NK115(re)001:5146: bar byed la / sdug bsngal bden pa'i gtso bo
NK115(re)001:5147: skye shi gnyis las skye ba lam du byed do
NK115(re)001:5148: bar byed la / // rdzogs rim gyis ni gzung
NK115(re)001:5149: 'dzin gyi rtog pa phra rags thams cad cig car
NK115(re)001:5150: du dbyings su dengs par byed pas gtso bo shes
NK115(re)001:5151: sgrib kyi gnyen po byed la /
NK115(re)001:5152: mtshan bcas rdzogs rim gyi skabs su phyag rgya la
NK115(re)001:5153: sogs pa'i thabs la brten nas chags pa'i ro dga'
NK115(re)001:5154: ba bzhi'i ye shes sogs su lam du byed pas
NK115(re)001:5155: nyon sgrib kyi gnyen por yang 'gyur bas kun 'byung
NK115(re)001:5156: spong la sdug bden skye shi gnyis las 'chi ba
NK115(re)001:5157: lam du byed pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:5158: lam la ltos na bskyed rim gyis bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK115(re)001:5159: rdzogs rim gyis ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'i sgo nas lam lnga mthar phyin par byed cing /
NK115(re)001:5160: 'bras bu la ltos na bskyed rim gyis gzugs sku dang /
NK115(re)001:5161: rdzogs rim gyis chos sku lam du byas nas myur du de gnyis mngon du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:5162: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:5168: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5169: de ltar lam rim pa gnyis su yod pa de
NK115(re)001:5170: las dang po thabs gtso che ba bskyed pa'i rima
NK115(re)001:5171: pa ni / skye ba lam du byed pa'i thabs
NK115(re)001:5172: yin pas rigs drug gi sems can 'di thams cad
NK115(re)001:5173: 'khor bar skye ba len pa ni skye gansa rnama
NK115(re)001:5174: pa bzhi po gang yang rung ba la brten nas
NK115(re)001:5175: pa ni / skye ste / spyir mi dang dud 'gro la skye gnas bzhi ga srid cing /
NK115(re)001:5176: zhing dag pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK115(re)001:5179: bar do'i 'gro ba rnams bardzusa nas skyes la /
NK115(re)001:5180: yi dwags ni mngal skyes kyang srid la /
NK115(re)001:5181: phal mo che bardzusa skyes so //
NK115(re)001:5182: mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags bdun dang gnod sbyin
NK115(re)001:5183: dang srin po sogs 'ga' zhig ni sgo nga las
NK115(re)001:5184: skye'o // sa rdo chu shing las skye ba ni drod gsher skyes so //
NK115(re)001:5185: de ltar skyes pa de'i tshe yang snga ma'i las
NK115(re)001:5186: kyis 'phangs pa'i gnas don lus kyi snang ba rgya
NK115(re)001:5187: chen po dang / phyi mar 'phen par byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:5188: las kyang sna tshogs pa gsog par byed pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:5189: de lta bu'i baga chagas de dag sbyong ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:5190: skye gnas bzhi po de dang tshul mthuna para rgyas
NK115(re)001:5191: pa chen po'i bskyed rim sogs rnam pa bzhi ston
NK115(re)001:5192: chen po dang / pa yin no // 'di lta
NK115(re)001:5193: bu'i zab mo'i lam 'di la sngon sbyangs can dang
NK115(re)001:5194: chen po dang / pa yin no // / dbang
NK115(re)001:5195: po shin tu rnon po cig char ba'i rigs lta
NK115(re)001:5196: bu skal ba bzang po dang ldan pa rnams ma
NK115(re)001:5197: chen po dang / pa yin no // / gtogs
NK115(re)001:5198: / gang zag rim gyis pa rnams kyis thun mong
NK115(re)001:5199: theg pa'i lam gyis rgyud legs par ma sbyang bar
NK115(re)001:5200: 'jug snga byas na rang rgyud chud zos su 'gyur
NK115(re)001:5202: lam gnad thams cad mdor bsdu na theg dman gyi
NK115(re)001:5203: lam la brten nas 'khor ba las yid 'byung ba
NK115(re)001:5204: dang / theg chen thun mong ba'i lam la brten
NK115(re)001:5205: nas gzhan phan gyi blo gting nas skyes pa'i gnyis
NK115(re)001:5206: po de la lam gyi gzhung shing thams cad tshang
NK115(re)001:5207: ba yin pas lam gyi yan lag gzhan thams cad
NK115(re)001:5209: des na de 'dra ba'i gang zag des mtshan nyid
NK115(re)001:5210: dang ldan pa'i bla ma bsten nas sngags la zhugs
NK115(re)001:5211: na sngags lam pa rnal ma zhig 'ong gis /
NK115(re)001:5212: de lta ma yin par 'khor ba spyi dang tshe 'di'i snang shes las blo ma log cing /
NK115(re)001:5213: gzhan la phan 'dod kyi bsam pa bzang po gang
NK115(re)001:5214: yang med bzhi na sngags la zhugs te dbang dang
NK115(re)001:5215: bskyed rdzogs sogs la bslab par byed pa de ni
NK115(re)001:5218: lag len ji tsam mkhas kyang rung /
NK115(re)001:5219: der ma zad thun mong gi dngos grub bya ltar nam mkha' la 'phur /
NK115(re)001:5220: ri brag la zang thal du 'gro nus pa sogs
NK115(re)001:5221: byung yang lam gyi gnad 'phyugs zin pas srid pa'i
NK115(re)001:5222: rgyu las mi 'da' bas lam gnad ma 'phyugs pa
NK115(re)001:5224: 'jam dbyangs sa pan gyi zhal nas /
NK115(re)001:5225: gnad rnams min pa'i chos gzhan 'ga' //
NK115(re)001:5226: ma tshang ba dang lhag pa dang //
NK115(re)001:5228: nyes pa chen po bskyed mi nus //
NK115(re)001:5229: chos kyi gnad rnams bcos gyur na //
NK115(re)001:5230: chos gzhan bzang yang 'tshang mi rgya //
NK115(re)001:5231: dper na 'gro ba'i srog rtsa dang //
NK115(re)001:5232: ljon shing rnams kyi rtsa ba dang //
NK115(re)001:5233: sa bon gyi ni skye sa dang //
NK115(re)001:5234: thags rnams kyi ni srog shing dang //
NK115(re)001:5235: bcud rnams len gyi rtsa ba dang //
NK115(re)001:5236: dbang po rnams kyi gnad rnams ni //
NK115(re)001:5237: 'phyugs na bsgrub tu mi rung bzhin //
NK115(re)001:5238: de bzhin chos kyi gnad 'phyugs na //
NK115(re)001:5240: des na la la 'khrul yang sla //
NK115(re)001:5241: gnad rnams 'khrul med dpyad dgos so //
NK115(re)001:5243: rgyu mtshan de lta bu la dgongs nas snyigs ma'i
NK115(re)001:5244: sngags btsun rnams kyis lam gnad mi 'phyugs pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:5245: // rigs 'dzin chen po pad+ma badz+ra gyi zhal snga
NK115(re)001:5246: nas kyang bskyed rim gyi lam gnad bcu gsungs pa'i
NK115(re)001:5247: // thog mar / ma rig las dang nyon mongs kyis bskyed pa'i //
NK115(re)001:5248: khams gsum 'bar ba'i me 'obs ltar mthong nas //
NK115(re)001:5249: nges 'byung bsam pas so thar gang rung blang //
NK115(re)001:5250: yon tan gzhi rten lam gnad dang po yin //
NK115(re)001:5251: thog med dus na skye 'chi'i 'khor lo 'dir //
NK115(re)001:5252: 'khyams pa'i tshe na pha mar ma gyur med //
NK115(re)001:5253: lus can 'di kun srid las 'don pa'i blos //
NK115(re)001:5254: byang chub sems bskyed lam gnad gnyis pa yin //
NK115(re)001:5255: tshe lus gcig gis sangs rgyas sgrub pa la //
NK115(re)001:5256: nye lam mthar thug rdo rjee theg pa ste //
NK115(re)001:5257: bla mar mi bsten de 'grub thabs gzhan med //
NK115(re)001:5258: tshul bzhin bsten pa lam gnad gsum pa yin //
NK115(re)001:5259: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:5260: de'ang bzhi pa dbang thob par bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5261: lnga pa dam tshig bsrung ba /
NK115(re)001:5262: drug pa nyams len la rang rkya thub phyir lta sgom la sgro 'dogs gcod pa /
NK115(re)001:5263: bdun pa dben par sgrub pa la dam bca' ba /
NK115(re)001:5264: brgyad pa stong nyid dang snying rje zung du 'jug pa /
NK115(re)001:5265: dgu pa ting nge 'dzin skyon med du sgrub pa /
NK115(re)001:5266: bcu pa mtshan rtog sdom pa'i bskyed rim rnam dag bsgom pa'i tshul rnams tshang dgos par gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:5267: de ltar bsam pa dag cing dbang thob la dam
NK115(re)001:5268: tshig dang ldan pa des cho ga rnam par dag
NK115(re)001:5269: pa zhig la brten nas bskyed pa'i rim pa rnams
NK115(re)001:5270: bsgoms te bsnyen sgrub byed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5271: dkyil 'khor gyi las dang sgrub rdzas dang mchod rdzas
NK115(re)001:5272: sogs sngar bshad pa bzhin ma tshang ba med par
NK115(re)001:5273: 'du byas la / rgyud sde bka' ma'i cho ga sgyu 'phrul zhi ba lta bu la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:5274: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes kyi rim pa gsum las /
NK115(re)001:5275: dang po sngon 'gro la bdun te /
NK115(re)001:5276: dang po gral phyag dang tshul phyag bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5277: gnyis pa yan lag brgyad pas rgyud sbyang ba /
NK115(re)001:5278: gsum pa mtshon cha dam tshig las rgyal po lnga'i phyag rgyas mtshams gcod pa /
NK115(re)001:5279: bzhi pa brjod med kyi bshags pa bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5280: lnga pa pun+da r+ai ka'i rgyud las gsungs pa ltar dam bca' nyi shu pa bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5281: drug pa babs drug 'das bzhi'i dgongs pas bdag gnas yo byad rnams la byin dbab pa /
NK115(re)001:5282: bdun pa phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams byin gyis rlobs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5283: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la khyad par gyi sbyor ba
NK115(re)001:5284: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i sems rnam pa gnyis
NK115(re)001:5285: bskyed nas / ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:5286: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK115(re)001:5287: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK115(re)001:5288: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK115(re)001:5289: dang po ni snang ba'i zhen pa sbyong phyir stong chen /
NK115(re)001:5290: stong ba'i zhen pa sbyong phyir snying rje sgyu ma /
NK115(re)001:5291: snang stong so sor zhen pa sbyong phyir rgyu'i ting
NK115(re)001:5292: 'dzin bsgom zhing brtan pa'i yan lag tu yi ge'i
NK115(re)001:5293: spro bsdu la sems sbyong ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:5294: gnyis pa la 'byung lnga'i zhen rtog sbyong phyir yum
NK115(re)001:5295: lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin gzhi
NK115(re)001:5296: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK115(re)001:5297: ma dag pa'i snod bcud kyi snang zhen sbyong phyir b+h+r+aum las rten gzhal yas khang /
NK115(re)001:5298: yi ge zhe gnyis las cho ga gsum gyis brteen pa lha'i dkyil 'khor rnams bskyed de /
NK115(re)001:5299: rigs mthun gyi las la dbang bsgyur ba'i zhen pa sbyong phyir dbang bskur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5300: sgo gsum stobs 'phel ba'i zhen rtog sbyong phyir byin gyis brlabs pa rnams bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5301: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la drug las /
NK115(re)001:5302: dang po 'khor 'das tha dad kyi zhen pa sbyong
NK115(re)001:5303: phyir ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la snyan gsan dbab
NK115(re)001:5304: cing spyan drangs pa la rig pa'i me tog dor
NK115(re)001:5305: nas dbyer med du bstim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5306: gnyis pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i phyir phyag dang mchod pa bcu gsum 'bul ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5307: gsum pa rgyud dag phyir bshags pa bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5308: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba /
NK115(re)001:5310: drug pa 'dzab kha phye nas dam ye 'phro 'du
NK115(re)001:5311: gsum gsal bas ngag gi zhen pa sbyong ba dang
NK115(re)001:5312: / lha'i thugs dam bskul ba'i phyir 'dzab bzla zhing skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:5313: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la lnga ste /
NK115(re)001:5314: dang po bsod nams spel phyir tshogs kyi mchod sbyin /
NK115(re)001:5315: gnyis pa las 'chol phyir bstan ma skyong ba /
NK115(re)001:5316: gsum pa rtag chad kyi mtha' bsal phyir dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing thun mtshams kyi lhar ldang ba /
NK115(re)001:5317: bzhi pa bar chad kyi rgyun gcod phyir go bgo lus bsrung bya ba /
NK115(re)001:5318: lnga pa spyod pa rnam par dag pa'i phyir spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bskyang ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:5319: de dag gis spyi'i 'gros tsam zhig shes par byas nas /
NK115(re)001:5320: gzhan sgyu 'phrul khro bo lta bu la khro bo rang gi sgos chos dmigs bsal rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:5321: cho ga gzhan la'ang rgyas bsdus sogs mi 'dra ba ci rigs pa yod pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5322: yang gter ma'i cho ga rnams la'ang rgyas bsdus sogs mi 'dra ba mang du yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:5323: spyi tsam du sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK115(re)001:5324: sbyor ba la bdun las thog mar rang nyid gnyug
NK115(re)001:5325: ma'i lhar gsal bzhin pa'i snying ga'i srog mi shigs
NK115(re)001:5326: pa'i thig le nyid sngar dbang dus su dam tshig
NK115(re)001:5327: gi chu rdo rje sems dpar byin gyis brlabs pa
NK115(re)001:5328: dang dbyer med du byas nas byin 'bebs kyis dam
NK115(re)001:5329: ye gnyis su med par brtan par bgyis pa de
NK115(re)001:5330: h'u yig gi ngo bor gsal ba las 'od zer
NK115(re)001:5331: 'phros pas / rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba
NK115(re)001:5332: chos sku'i dbyings nas bla ma dang gnyis su med
NK115(re)001:5333: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad gzugs sku ye
NK115(re)001:5334: shes sgyu ma'i rnam rol du thugs rje'i dbang gis
NK115(re)001:5335: bzhengs te gang sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i
NK115(re)001:5336: rnam par bzhugs par bsams la /
NK115(re)001:5337: bdag cag gi ston pas slob pa lam gyi gnas
NK115(re)001:5338: skabs na dang po mchog gsum la skyabs su song
NK115(re)001:5339: zhing / byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:5340: rang rig gi ngo bo mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:5341: yin pas don la skyabs su 'gro bya dang 'gro
NK115(re)001:5342: byed med par shes pa'i ngang nas tha snyad tsam
NK115(re)001:5343: du bla ma dang yi dam la sangs rgyas /
NK115(re)001:5344: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong la dge 'dun /
NK115(re)001:5345: bskyed rdzogs zab mo la chos su shes nas skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5346: gnyis pa mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK115(re)001:5347: don du bsgrub bya zung 'jug rdo rje 'chang gi
NK115(re)001:5348: go 'phang dang / dus kyi khyad par tshe 'di nyid la /
NK115(re)001:5349: thabs kyi khyad par rim gnyis kyi rnal 'byor la
NK115(re)001:5350: brten nas bsgrub par bya snyam du sems bskyed pa
NK115(re)001:5351: dang / gsum pa ston pa bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK115(re)001:5352: bar du tshogs gnyis zung 'jug gi lam la bslab
NK115(re)001:5353: pa ltar bsod nams mtha' yas pa bsdud pa'i ting
NK115(re)001:5354: nge 'dzin bden gnyis zab mo'i don las mi 'da'
NK115(re)001:5355: ba'i sgo nas yan lag bdun pas rgyud sbyang zhing
NK115(re)001:5356: tshogs bsags te rgyud dngos grub kyi snod du rung
NK115(re)001:5358: bzhi pa sngon ston pa tho rangs 'tshang rgya ba'i snga logs su srod la bdud btul ba bzhin /
NK115(re)001:5359: ma rig gnyis 'dzin las byung ba'i log par 'dren
NK115(re)001:5360: pa'i tshogs rnams chos nyid ngang gis khros pa'i rig
NK115(re)001:5361: pa he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas khro
NK115(re)001:5362: bo dang mtshon cha 'chol ba'i tshogs dpag tu med
NK115(re)001:5363: pa 'phros nas phyir bskrad pas gzhi med rtsa bral
NK115(re)001:5364: gyi ngang du dengs bar bsam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5365: lnga pa phyi rol kun tu khro mtshon me dpung
NK115(re)001:5366: gi rwa gur yangs shing rgya che bas gtams te
NK115(re)001:5367: rnam rtog 'khrul pa'i gdon bgegs thams cad rig pa
NK115(re)001:5368: sku gsum gyi ngang du mtshams bcad pa ste /
NK115(re)001:5369: de ltar bgegs bskrad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5370: mtshams gcod pa 'dis kyang snang srid dag mnyam gyi lta ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5371: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las dang /
NK115(re)001:5372: mtshan rtog sdom pa'i rnam pa sogs sngags kyi khyad chos du ma zhig ston to //
NK115(re)001:5374: dam tshig gtsang zhing sgrub pa la gzhol ba'i bdag sgrub pa po dang /
NK115(re)001:5375: bkra shis shing byin chags pa'i gnas dang /
NK115(re)001:5376: grangs tshogs shing rnam par dag pa'i mchod rdzas dang
NK115(re)001:5377: sgrub rdzas sogs yod byad rnams la byin dbab pa
NK115(re)001:5378: ste / de yang de dag thams cad gdod nas
NK115(re)001:5379: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du grub zin
NK115(re)001:5380: kyang gnyis snang 'khrul pa'i bag chags kyis bslad de
NK115(re)001:5381: ma dag par snang ba 'di dag la /
NK115(re)001:5382: brgyud gsum gyi bla ma yi dam zhi khro'i dkyil
NK115(re)001:5383: 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK115(re)001:5384: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor los byin phab cing rang
NK115(re)001:5385: snang ye shes kyi 'khor lo dang ro gcig tu
NK115(re)001:5386: byed pa dang / bdun pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5387: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas rnams snang srid rang
NK115(re)001:5388: byung gi mchod pa'i gsang ba chen por ye nas
NK115(re)001:5390: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin gyi byin gyis
NK115(re)001:5391: brlabs nas sku gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams zag med
NK115(re)001:5392: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i rdzas su mngon du
NK115(re)001:5395: sngon ston pa bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i gdan la
NK115(re)001:5396: bzhugs te mkha' khyab kyi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam
NK115(re)001:5397: par bzhag nas mngon par sangs rgyas te 'jin rten
NK115(re)001:5398: gsum gyi mchod gnas su gyur nas chos kyi 'khor
NK115(re)001:5399: lo bskor te gdul bya'i don mdzad pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:5400: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi khog dbub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5401: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5402: spyan 'dren zhing phyag dang mchod pa sogs 'bul ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5403: bzlas pa bya ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:5404: dang po ni dus gsum gyi rtog pas mi shigs
NK115(re)001:5405: pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin de bzhin
NK115(re)001:5406: nyid kyi ngang la mnyam par gzhag nas de ltar
NK115(re)001:5407: ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams la 'dzin med snying
NK115(re)001:5408: rje chen po mkha' khyab tu bsgom pa sgyu ma
NK115(re)001:5409: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin nam kun snang gi ting
NK115(re)001:5411: de gnyis zung du 'jug pa'i ngang las rgyu'i ting
NK115(re)001:5412: nge 'dzin rang rig gi ngo bo h'u yig la
NK115(re)001:5414: gnyis pa rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5415: nang rgyud sde gsum po'i skabs 'dir bdag mdun dbyer med du sgrub pa yin pas /
NK115(re)001:5416: phyi rgyud ltar bdag mdun gnyis la mchog dman dang
NK115(re)001:5417: tha dad du mi blta bas bsgrub gzhi ni rang
NK115(re)001:5418: rig gam gnyug ma'i sgo gsum yin pa la khyad
NK115(re)001:5419: par med la / bsgrub tshul bdag mdun gyi bskyed
NK115(re)001:5420: chog so sor yod pa'i cho ga la de bzhin
NK115(re)001:5421: du bskyed cing dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bdag mdun
NK115(re)001:5422: gnyis po la ye shes pa bstim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5423: yang bdag mdun so sor mi bskyed pa ltar na
NK115(re)001:5424: bsgrub rten dkyil 'khor dang rang gnyis dbyer med pa'i
NK115(re)001:5425: ngo bo dam tshig pa'i 'khor lor bskyed nas ye
NK115(re)001:5426: shes pa bstim la bzlas pa'i tshe dam ye so
NK115(re)001:5428: gang ltar yang rgyu'i sa bon las 'byung ba rim brtsegs /
NK115(re)001:5429: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed nas brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5430: cho ga rang rang bskyed tshul bzhi po gang gi
NK115(re)001:5431: lugs ltar yin pa de bzhin du bskyed par bya
NK115(re)001:5432: ste gzhung du rgyas par 'chad par 'gyur ba ltar
NK115(re)001:5433: shes par bya'o // gsum pa spyan 'dren pa sogs ni /
NK115(re)001:5434: gdod nas dam ye dbyer med kyi don la nges
NK115(re)001:5435: pa brtan po yod na spyan 'dren dang bzhugs gsol
NK115(re)001:5436: ched du ma byas kyang rung mod /
NK115(re)001:5437: lha dang rang rgyud tha dad du lta ba yod
NK115(re)001:5438: na de gzhom pa'i phyir de gnyis byas te dam
NK115(re)001:5439: ye dbyer med par nges shes brtan par bya dgos
NK115(re)001:5440: gsungs / phyag mchod bstod pa rnams ni mchod pa'i rnam grangs yin la /
NK115(re)001:5441: byed pa'i tshul yang rang gi thugs ka nas sprul
NK115(re)001:5442: pa'i lha mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung nas
NK115(re)001:5443: / de dag gis phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i
NK115(re)001:5444: sprin chen po spros te rang la mchod pas mnyes
NK115(re)001:5445: par byed pa 'phrul dag'i lha rnams kyis 'dod yon
NK115(re)001:5446: la longs spyod pa'i tshul lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:5447: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na yod pa'i 'dod yon thams
NK115(re)001:5448: cad gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs pa'i phyi nang
NK115(re)001:5449: gsang ba'i lha mo'i rang bzhin du 'phrul ba rnams
NK115(re)001:5450: kyis rang rang gi byed las dang mthun pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:5451: nas mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:5452: gyi rnam par rol pas mchod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5453: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas rang gi rig pa'i ngo
NK115(re)001:5454: bo las kyi sems dpa'i rnam par thon nas dkyil
NK115(re)001:5455: 'khor gyi shar sgor 'khod de mchod pa'i sprin rab
NK115(re)001:5456: 'byams spros pas mnyes par byed pa gsum las rang
NK115(re)001:5457: blor gang 'tshams byed pa las khyad med gsungs /
NK115(re)001:5458: gang ltar yang kun rdzob tu sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:5459: ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod pa dang rol pa'i bya
NK115(re)001:5460: byed lha la lha rol pa'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:5461: don dam par bya byed las 'das pa chos nyid
NK115(re)001:5462: la chos nyid rol pa'am thim pa'i tshul gyis tshogs
NK115(re)001:5463: gnyis zung 'brel du rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5465: khyad par nam mkha'i dbyings las bstod pa'i glu dbyangs rang grag tu byung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5466: 'khor rnams kyis gtso bo la bstod cing /
NK115(re)001:5467: gtso bos 'khor rnams la basngagasa pa brjod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5468: rdo rje'i lha mo rnams kyis bro gar dang sbyar
NK115(re)001:5469: te bstod pa'i tshul ji ltar byas kyang 'gal ba
NK115(re)001:5470: med do // bzhi pa bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK115(re)001:5471: thugs kar sa bon gyi mthar sngags phreng gsal ba
NK115(re)001:5472: las spro bsdu'i sbyor bas snod bcud sku dang ye
NK115(re)001:5473: shes kyi rol par blta zhing sgra grag thams cad
NK115(re)001:5474: sngags kyi rang sgrar shes pas bzlas pa spyi'i lugs
NK115(re)001:5479: ngag bzlas rnams rim gyis byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5483: spyi dril gyi sngags rnams la bzlas pa'i grangs 'gro tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:5484: sham bu gdags tshul sogs rang rang gi gzhung las shes par bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:5485: bzlas pa'i mjug tu mchod cing bstod nas /
NK115(re)001:5486: bsnyen rkyang la mi dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:5487: bsgrub pa la sogs pa'i dus su 'dzab kha phyes nas yod na dam ye dbyer med du bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5488: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa ni bsod nams spel
NK115(re)001:5489: ba'i phyir tshogs dang lhag ma'i mchod sbyin bya ba
NK115(re)001:5490: dang / bar chad bsrung zhing mthun rkyen bsgrub phyir chad tho bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:5491: bstan ma skyong la bro brdung bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5492: gtang rag tu mchod cing bstod la dngos grub len pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5493: lhag chad la sogs pa'i skyon 'dag phyir bzod gsol bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5494: rtag chad kyi mtha' bsal phyir bsdu rim bya zhing rjes thob kyi lhar ldang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5495: tshogs gnyis kyi 'bras bu ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin mngon du 'gyur phyir dge ba bsngo ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5496: gnas skabs dang mthar thug thams cad du dge legs
NK115(re)001:5497: kyi snang ba rgyun mi 'chad pa'i phyir shis pa
NK115(re)001:5499: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:5500: dag rdzogs smin gsum gyi go ba spyir bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:5501: skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong tshul bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:5502: bskyed gzhi ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:5503: sa lam rim par bgrod tshul bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5504: dang po dag rdzogs smin gsum gyi go ba spyir bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5505: gong du ji skad bshad pa bzhin sngags kyi lta
NK115(re)001:5506: ba la yid ches shing nges pa rnyed nas bsgom
NK115(re)001:5507: dgos te / klong chen rab 'byams kyis /
NK115(re)001:5508: de la dang po gnas lugs shes pa gces //
NK115(re)001:5509: theg pa'i dbang gis rnam pa mang na yang //
NK115(re)001:5510: nges pa'i snying po bden pa dbyer med de //
NK115(re)001:5511: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsang ba'i mdzod khang yin //
NK115(re)001:5513: de yang rgyal ba'i bka' dri ma med pa'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK115(re)001:5514: mkhas pas nyams su blangs shing grol ba'i dbang po yod pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK115(re)001:5515: gnyis ka dang rjes su mthun pa'i rigs pa tshad
NK115(re)001:5516: ma ste gsum gyis gtan la phebs pa zhig dgos
NK115(re)001:5517: te / rdo rje me long las /
NK115(re)001:5518: lung dang rigs pa man ngag gi //
NK115(re)001:5519: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal bas //
NK115(re)001:5520: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:5522: de ltar nges par byas nas lta ba dang zung
NK115(re)001:5523: du 'brel ba'i bsgom pas ji ltar bskyed pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:5524: / 'chi srid dang mtshungs pa'i stong nyid /
NK115(re)001:5525: bar srid dang mtshungs pa'i snying rje /
NK115(re)001:5526: dri za nye bar len pa'i shes pa dang mtshungs
NK115(re)001:5527: pa'i sa bon dbang po yongs su rdzogs nas skye
NK115(re)001:5528: ba la sogs pa dang mtshungs pa'i lha yongs rdzogs
NK115(re)001:5529: bsgom pa dang / de yang skye gnas bzhi po
NK115(re)001:5530: rang rang rig skye tshul dang mtshungs par rang rang
NK115(re)001:5531: sbyong byed kyi gnyen po bsgom pa sogs 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:5533: skye gnas bzhi la sogs pa'i rnama pa dang mthuna par bsgom pasa /
NK115(re)001:5534: bskyed tshul bzhi po re re yang sgo gsum 'jug
NK115(re)001:5535: pa gcig pa'i snang zhen dang rigs drug gi skye
NK115(re)001:5536: gnas kyi bag chags kun kyi sbyong byed du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:5537: bas / lus snang ba 'dod pa'i srid pa /
NK115(re)001:5538: ngag phyed snang gzugs kyi srid pa /
NK115(re)001:5539: yid mi snang ba gzugs med pa'i srid pa ste sgo gsum po'i bag chags bcas dang /
NK115(re)001:5540: phyi rol du snang ba'i khams gsuma po ma lusa
NK115(re)001:5541: pa'i snang zhen thams cad sbyong zhing 'adga par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:5542: ba dang / yang mya ngana las 'adsa pa dang bzhugas tshul mthuna pa yi /
NK115(re)001:5543: ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum po sku gsum dang 'dra ba lam du byas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5544: zhing dang gzhal yas khang dang mtshan dang dpe byad
NK115(re)001:5545: dang 'od zer la sogs pa'i lha yi rnama pa
NK115(re)001:5546: lam du byas shing bsgoms pasa 'brasa bu sku gsum
NK115(re)001:5547: gyi yon tan thams cad gzhi la ye nas gnas
NK115(re)001:5549: mngon du sad rung gi nus pa khyad par can la gsos thebs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5550: de ltar dag rdzogs gnyisa ka tshang ba de'ang rdo
NK115(re)001:5551: rje'i lus kyi rtsa thig rlung gsum la brgyud nas
NK115(re)001:5552: gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs yin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5553: sems kyi chos nyid bde gshegs snying po'i gnas lugs
NK115(re)001:5554: dang rjes su mthun par bsgom pa yin pas de
NK115(re)001:5555: lta bu'i bskyed rim brtan nas rdzogas pa'i rima pa
NK115(re)001:5556: rnams bsgom na de'i ye shes dpe dang don gyi
NK115(re)001:5557: 'od gsal skye ma rag par 'gyur bas rim pa
NK115(re)001:5558: gnyis pa'i smina byed du 'gro ba'i phyir na daga
NK115(re)001:5559: rdzogas smina gsuma po 'di nang rgyud kyi bskyed rim
NK115(re)001:5560: spyi la gcesa pa'i chings gal po che yin pas
NK115(re)001:5561: tshul bzhin du shes par bya dgos so //
NK115(re)001:5562: gnyis pa skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong tshul bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:5565: dang po rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:5570: dang po sgong skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:5573: dang po rgyas pa ltar bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5574: de la 'khor ba'i rnam pa grub tshul ji ltar
NK115(re)001:5575: na spros pa can sgonga skyes rnams ni thog mar
NK115(re)001:5576: bya la sogs pa las sgo nga dang /
NK115(re)001:5577: sgong nga de las gzugs su smin pa ste lana gnyis su skye ba ltara /
NK115(re)001:5579: sras dang btsun mor bcas pa ni //
NK115(re)001:5580: 'khor ba'i chos las skyes pa ste //
NK115(re)001:5581: sems can gyi ni sras su bya //
NK115(re)001:5583: ji ltar sangs rgyas mthu las byung //
NK115(re)001:5584: lhun gyis grub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK115(re)001:5585: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs pa las //
NK115(re)001:5586: mkhas pa sangs rgyas sras yin no //
NK115(re)001:5587: zhes gzhan srasa te rnama pa gnyis su gsungs pa'i
NK115(re)001:5588: bskyed tshul rgyas pa ni las dang po ba rnams
NK115(re)001:5589: la basngagasa shing / las dang po ba'i tshad ni
NK115(re)001:5590: dkyil 'khor rags pa yud tsam gyis mngon du byed
NK115(re)001:5591: nus pa tshun chad la bshad cing /
NK115(re)001:5592: bskyed rdzogs so so'i cha nas bskyed rim gyi gnas skabs thams cad las dang po pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5593: rdzogs rim ni de las ldog par rim lnga dang spyod bsdus las bshad do //
NK115(re)001:5594: bskyed tshul 'di la sgrub sde'i lugs dang /
NK115(re)001:5595: rgyud sde'i lugs gnyis yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:5596: dang po sgrub sde'i lugs rig 'dzin chen po pad+ma
NK115(re)001:5597: sam+b+ha wa'i dgongs pa rgyal po'i bla dpe bka' brgyad
NK115(re)001:5599: bdag sras dang gzhan sras gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:5600: dang po badga gi srasa su gazhana bya ba zhes
NK115(re)001:5601: pa'i go don rang gi sems nyid bde bar gshegs
NK115(re)001:5602: pa'i snying po ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:5603: kyi 'char gzhir gnas pas na rig pa'i ngo bo
NK115(re)001:5604: de gtso bo yab yum du bskyed nas des sras
NK115(re)001:5605: su gzhan de bzhin gshegs pa rnams bskrun te 'khor
NK115(re)001:5606: du bkod pa'i don gyis yin te /
NK115(re)001:5607: 'di la lnga rang gi rnam smin gyi lus la
NK115(re)001:5608: sogs pa chos thams cad stong pa nyid du sbyang
NK115(re)001:5609: ba sogs bsam gtan gsum gyi man ngag la brten
NK115(re)001:5610: nas rang rig gi ngo bo sa bona yig 'bru'i
NK115(re)001:5611: rnam par bsgom pa las 'byung ba'i sa bon rnams
NK115(re)001:5612: spros te 'byung ba rim brtsegs bsgom /
NK115(re)001:5613: b+h+r+aum yig kha dog lnga ldan 'phros pa las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bsgoms nas /
NK115(re)001:5614: dbus kyi gdan steng du bar snang nas sa bon
NK115(re)001:5615: gyi yi ge babs pa yongs su gyur pa lasa
NK115(re)001:5616: ni gtso bo rgyu'i he ru ka zhal gcig phyag
NK115(re)001:5617: gnyis sku mdog smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba zhig
NK115(re)001:5619: yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i bde ba chen po'i
NK115(re)001:5620: 'od zer gyis phyogsa bcu'i sangsa rgyasa thams cad bkuga
NK115(re)001:5621: nasa yab kyi spyi bo nas zhugs te yum gyi
NK115(re)001:5623: yang 'od zer 'phros te semas can thams cad bkuga
NK115(re)001:5624: nasa sgrib pa sbyong zhing mkhar bstim par bya ba
NK115(re)001:5625: dang / de nas 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi dpal
NK115(re)001:5626: chen po ni nga'o zhes 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK115(re)001:5627: pa'i bdag nyid chen po la che ba'i nga rgyal
NK115(re)001:5628: dang / bskyed pa dang / lha tshogs thams cad
NK115(re)001:5629: mkha'a gsang nasa btona nasa so so'i gadna la 'goda
NK115(re)001:5630: dang / bskyed pa dang / par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5631: gnyis pa gazhana gyi srasa su badga bya ba zhes
NK115(re)001:5632: pa'i don bdag sras kyi skabs su gzhan de bzhin
