NK115(re)001:5633: gshegs pa thams cad rang la bstim nas mngal 'byin
NK115(re)001:5634: gyi sgo nas sras kyi rnam par 'khor du bkod
NK115(re)001:5635: pa de rnams gtso bo'i thugs su gyur nas bdag
NK115(re)001:5636: gi rtog tshogs yi ge'i rnam par yod pa mkha'
NK115(re)001:5637: ru phab ste sras su bskrun nas 'khor du bkod
NK115(re)001:5638: pa'i don te 'di la rnam pa brgyad yod de
NK115(re)001:5639: dang / bskyed pa dang / par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5640: / dper na sgong skyes rnams dang po sgo nga
NK115(re)001:5642: de nas sgong khyim brdol nas dbang po dang yan
NK115(re)001:5643: lag yongs su rdzogs pa phyir smin pa dera 'gyur
NK115(re)001:5644: ba bzhina du / gtso bo yab yum 'oda du
NK115(re)001:5645: zhu nas thig le mthing nag gi gong bu sa
NK115(re)001:5646: bona phyag mtshan gyis mtshan par gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5647: de nyid yongs su gyur pa lasa 'bras bu'i he
NK115(re)001:5648: ru ka yaba yuma sku mdog mthing nag dbu dgu
NK115(re)001:5649: phyag bco brgyad zhabs brgyad pa skye mcheda thams cad
NK115(re)001:5650: yongs su rdzogas pa zhig tu bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5651: de'i tshe yaba kya rtog pa thams cad ya ga'i
NK115(re)001:5652: ngo bar gyura nas sras 'dod kyi nus pa med
NK115(re)001:5654: yuma lasa 'oda zer 'phrasa pas bskul te 'khor gyi
NK115(re)001:5655: lha tshogs rnams la sras bskyed pa'i don du gasla
NK115(re)001:5657: de nas 'khor gyi lha tshogs kuna kyang dgyes pa
NK115(re)001:5658: chen po'i ngang nas 'od du zhu ste ranga nyid
NK115(re)001:5659: gtso bor yod pa de'i thugs kar bstim ste thugs
NK115(re)001:5660: su gyur nas dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag ye
NK115(re)001:5661: shes chen po'i bdag nyid nga'o zhes nga rgyal bzunga
NK115(re)001:5662: ba dang / de nas mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs
NK115(re)001:5663: te phyag rgya bzhis snyomsa para zhugsa nasa yum mkha'a
NK115(re)001:5664: ru byang chub sems kyi 'od zer lan gsum phab
NK115(re)001:5666: gnyis pas rten gyi dkyila 'khora gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyeda /
NK115(re)001:5667: gsum pas rtog pa zhe gnyis yi ge'i ngo bor
NK115(re)001:5668: yod pa rnams yongs su gyur pa las gtso 'khor
NK115(re)001:5669: gyi lha tshogs yongs su rdzogs par gsal te yum
NK115(re)001:5670: mkha' nas phyir gdona pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5671: phyag rgya'i lha mo bzhi spros te lcags kyu mas
NK115(re)001:5672: dbyings nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rten la
NK115(re)001:5674: zhags pa mas gnas nas bskyod la spyan drangs nas /
NK115(re)001:5675: lcags sgrog mas dam tshig pa'i dkyil 'khor der gnyis med du bstim la /
NK115(re)001:5676: dril bu mas dgyes pa bskyed pa yi sgo nas
NK115(re)001:5677: dam ye dbyer med du brtan pa bcingsa pa dang
NK115(re)001:5678: / gnas gsum rdo rje gsum gyis rgyas gadba par byas te 'khor rnams so so'i gdan du 'khod /
NK115(re)001:5679: gtso bo 'bras bu'i he ru ka la bstim /
NK115(re)001:5680: gzhal yas khang gzhal yas khang dang /
NK115(re)001:5681: gdan rnams gdan so so la bstim pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5682: gnyis pa rgyud sde'i lugs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5683: spyir rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba lta
NK115(re)001:5684: bu la mtshon na dkyil 'khor bskyed tshul gyi cho
NK115(re)001:5685: ga la sngon gyi slob dpon rnams dgongs pa mi
NK115(re)001:5686: mthun te / 'grel pa nyi seng mar cho ga lnga bskyed dang /
NK115(re)001:5687: d+r+wa ba che chung la brten te bdag sras gzhan sras dang /
NK115(re)001:5688: cho ga gsum bskyed kyi tshul rnams yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:5689: dang po'i lugs cho ga lnga bskyed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5690: thog mar sems bskyed de yud tsam gyis kun tu bzang por bsgoms nas /
NK115(re)001:5691: 'og gi phyogs su ye shes kyis gzhi nas bzung
NK115(re)001:5692: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed tshar ba
NK115(re)001:5693: dang / nyi zla'i gdan la sems dkyil gyis 'dug par mos te /
NK115(re)001:5694: byang chub kyi sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i don
NK115(re)001:5695: gyis stong pa nyid kyi ye shes te cho ga
NK115(re)001:5696: dang po'o // de'i ngang las rang sems a'i ngo bor bsgoms nas 'phro 'dus bya bas /
NK115(re)001:5697: a las zla dkyil gyi dbus su mtshan gyi sa bon +aa li dang /
NK115(re)001:5698: +aa ring las nyi dkyil gyi dbus su dpe byad kyi sa bon k+aa li ste /
NK115(re)001:5699: gnyis gnyis rim du bskor ba'i rang bzhin cho ga
NK115(re)001:5700: gnyis pa ste me long lta bu'i ye shes so
NK115(re)001:5701: // de dag 'od kyi gong bu gcig tu 'dril ba ni /
NK115(re)001:5702: cho ga gsum pa ste mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:5703: 'od kyi gong bu las h'u du gyur nas de'i
NK115(re)001:5704: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu rdo rjer byin gyis rlobs
NK115(re)001:5705: pa cho ga bzhi pa ste so sor rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:5706: ye shes so // de yongs su gyur pa las
NK115(re)001:5707: kun tu bzang po'i skur bskyed pa ni cho ga
NK115(re)001:5708: lnga ba ste bya grub ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:5709: de nas yum bskyed de sems sprin las so so'i
NK115(re)001:5710: skur bskyed pa rang rang gi sngags kyis phyir phyung
NK115(re)001:5711: nas dkyil 'khor du 'god par mdzad do //
NK115(re)001:5712: rje rong zom dang kun mkhyen chen po cho ga lnga'i bskyed tshul de dang 'dra ba las /
NK115(re)001:5713: khyad par ting 'dzin rnam gsum sngon du 'gro bas /
NK115(re)001:5714: ting 'dzin dang po gnyis stong nyid ye shes te cho ga dang po dang /
NK115(re)001:5715: rgyu'i a yig las nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga gnyis pa bskyed par mdzad nas /
NK115(re)001:5716: ji srid cho ga lnga pas skur bskyed pa rdzogs pa dang gzhal yas khang bskyed /
NK115(re)001:5717: de nas bdag sras gzhan sras kyi cho ga la 'jug par mdzad de 'di ltar /
NK115(re)001:5718: e ma mtshar lngas sems bskyed nas /
NK115(re)001:5719: de ting dang kun snang sngon du song nas /
NK115(re)001:5720: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin a dkar po las a'i 'phro 'du byas te /
NK115(re)001:5721: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du mtshan
NK115(re)001:5722: bzang po'i sa bon sgra yig gam dbyangs yig bcu
NK115(re)001:5723: drug gi phreng ba rim pa gnyis su skor ba
NK115(re)001:5725: de nas a de las ming gi yi ge rnams 'phros shing 'dus pas /
NK115(re)001:5726: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i steng na dpe
NK115(re)001:5727: byad bzang po'i sa bon du gyur pa ming gi
NK115(re)001:5728: yi ge sum cu rtsa bzhi phreng ba'i rim pa
NK115(re)001:5730: nang rim a bcu gnyis kyi phreng ba can snying po yi ge'i k+sha'o //
NK115(re)001:5731: kun mkhyen chen pos gsal byed so bzhi'i steng ya
NK115(re)001:5732: ra la wa sogs drug bsnan pa'i nyis rim du
NK115(re)001:5733: gsungs // de nas de thams cad 'od kyi gong
NK115(re)001:5734: bu gcig tu 'dril ba las h+aum gis mtshan pa'i
NK115(re)001:5735: gsungs // rdo rjer gyur / de yongs su gyur
NK115(re)001:5736: pa las rang bzhin gzhi'i kun tu bzang po mthing
NK115(re)001:5737: ga rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i sku
NK115(re)001:5738: 'od zer gyi phung po 'bar ba las nam mkha'i
NK115(re)001:5739: dbyings thams cad khyab par bsgom mo //
NK115(re)001:5740: de'ang mngon byang dang po de bzhin nyid dang kun
NK115(re)001:5741: tu snang ba ni stong ba nyid kyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:5742: kyi bdag nyid dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so
NK115(re)001:5743: // gnyis pa nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor ni me long lta bu'i ye shes dang rdo rje'i rigs so //
NK115(re)001:5744: gsum pa 'od kyi gong bu ni mnyam pa nyid dang rin po che'i rigs so //
NK115(re)001:5745: bzhi pa rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa ni so sor rtog pa dang pad+ma'i rigs so //
NK115(re)001:5746: lnga pa sku ni bya ba grub pa dang las
NK115(re)001:5747: kyi rigs te sangs rgyas kyi chos kun yongs su
NK115(re)001:5748: rdzogs par bsgom pa nyid do //
NK115(re)001:5749: 'di ltar rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:5750: sangs rgyas kyi sa bcu gnyis gsungs pa yang /
NK115(re)001:5751: rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga dang thabs dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid du gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:5752: de la dbyangs dang gsal byed kyi yi ge mtshan
NK115(re)001:5753: dang dpe byad kyi sa bon du ji ltar rung
NK115(re)001:5754: ba'i tshul ni spyir yi ge ni ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:5756: mtshan dpe yang ye shes kyi yon tan yin pa'i phyir de'i rigs dang sa bon du rung la /
NK115(re)001:5757: de yang dbyangs yig mtshan dang /
NK115(re)001:5758: gsal byed dpe byad du sbyor ba ni rigs mthun pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:5759: dbyangs yig gzhi ma la gsal byed 'bras bur gnas
NK115(re)001:5760: pa de bzhin du mtshan gyi me tog la dpe
NK115(re)001:5761: byad kyi 'bras bu gnas pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:5763: snod kyi rim pa byung tshul gyis //
NK115(re)001:5764: rim brtsegs gzhal yas gzhung bzhin bskyed //
NK115(re)001:5766: snod kyi 'jig rten gyi bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:5767: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed kyang rung ma bskyed
NK115(re)001:5768: kyang rung ste / ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed do //
NK115(re)001:5769: de nas bshad rgyud rgya mtsho las /
NK115(re)001:5770: rang byung dngos dang mi 'gal zhing //
NK115(re)001:5771: 'bras bu nyid las ma shes pas //
NK115(re)001:5772: ma lus dkyil 'khor thig le rnams //
NK115(re)001:5773: bdag gi sras su bsgom par bya //
NK115(re)001:5775: bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir bdag gi
NK115(re)001:5776: sras su de bzhin gshegs pa rnams bya ba ste
NK115(re)001:5777: / de yang bdag ces bya ba ni byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin te /
NK115(re)001:5778: de ni thog ma dang tha ma med pa'i sangs
NK115(re)001:5779: rgyas yin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas thams cad de las
NK115(re)001:5780: sprul par bya ba bdag sras kyi tshul la 'jug
NK115(re)001:5781: pa ste / rang nyid kun tu bzang po'i g.yon
NK115(re)001:5782: phyog su yi ge a las kun tu bzang mo
NK115(re)001:5783: skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed de yab
NK115(re)001:5784: yum thabs shes su tshogs pa'i sbyor mtshams nas byang
NK115(re)001:5785: chub sems kyi sprin yi ge'i rang bzhin du spros
NK115(re)001:5786: nas ngo mtshar sras kyi dkyil 'khor du gyur nas
NK115(re)001:5787: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te slar 'dus nas
NK115(re)001:5788: dkyil 'khor chen por zhugs par bsam zhing mi bskyod
NK115(re)001:5789: pa ni kun bzang yab yum la thim par gyur
NK115(re)001:5790: pa ste / to // kun mkhyen yab sras ni
NK115(re)001:5791: gtso bo rnam snang du bzhed pas rnam snang kun
NK115(re)001:5793: de nas bshad rgyud rgya mtsho las /
NK115(re)001:5794: gang gis gang la gsol btab pas //
NK115(re)001:5795: thugs rjes byin rlabs sbyangs byas nas //
NK115(re)001:5796: thugs zhugs 'dres par dbyer med na //
NK115(re)001:5797: sras gyur dgongs pa ci la gnas //
NK115(re)001:5799: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:5800: yin kyang dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi byin gyis ma
NK115(re)001:5801: brlabs shing / rang rig pa'i ye shes can du
NK115(re)001:5802: ma gyur na sangs rgyas nyid du snang bar mi
NK115(re)001:5803: 'gyur bas rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par
NK115(re)001:5804: bya ba'i phyir gzhan sras kyi tshul la 'jug par
NK115(re)001:5805: brlabs shing / bya ba ni / dang po dngos
NK115(re)001:5806: por zhen pa snang ba'i bag chags sbyor ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:5807: brlabs shing / bya ba ni / // gtso bo'i
NK115(re)001:5808: thugs ka nas kun tu bzang po byang chub sems
NK115(re)001:5809: kyi bdag nyid rnam smin gyi lus 'dzin pa sems
NK115(re)001:5810: dpa'i rgyan dang ldan pa zhig byung nas dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:5811: gyi lha rnams la bskor ba byas te dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:5812: gyi nub sgor rkang pa'i long bu sprad cing thal
NK115(re)001:5813: mo sbyar te gsol ba btab pas /
NK115(re)001:5814: lha rnams kyis gnang ste thabs dang shes rab kyi
NK115(re)001:5815: 'od zer bdag la 'phros pas sems kyi rtog pa
NK115(re)001:5816: dang / de las gyur pa'i lus ngag rnams sbyangs
NK115(re)001:5817: te gnyis su med pa'i ye shes gzung 'dzin dang
NK115(re)001:5818: bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od kyi gong bu gcig tu
NK115(re)001:5819: dang / gyur par bya'o // de ltar dri ma
NK115(re)001:5820: dag par byas nas yon tan gyi tshogs bsgrub cing
NK115(re)001:5821: byin gyis brlabs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:5822: yang lha rnams las 'od zer yig 'bru gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:5823: rnam par 'phros te phog pas rdo rje gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:5824: rang bzhin +aahmh'u gsum du gyur pa rim bzhin h'u
NK115(re)001:5825: du bsdus te / h'u yig zla dkyil la gnas
NK115(re)001:5826: pa rlung gis bteg ste gtso bo'i thugs kar thim
NK115(re)001:5827: pa'i rkyen gyis yab yum bde ba'i rol mos tshim
NK115(re)001:5828: nas byang chub kyi sems dang gnyis su med pa'i
NK115(re)001:5829: gong bur gyur pa yum gyi mkha' la gnas pa
NK115(re)001:5830: du bsdus te / la / lha tshogs thams cad
NK115(re)001:5831: rang rang gi gsang sngags kyi sgra dang bcas nas
NK115(re)001:5832: thim par gyur pas gtso bo yab yum kyang rjes
NK115(re)001:5833: chags chen po'i bde ba'i ngo bor zhu ste thams
NK115(re)001:5834: cad gcig tu 'dres pa'i gong bur bsam mo //
NK115(re)001:5835: de nas chad pa'i mtha' la zhen pa stong pa'i bag chags sbyong phyir /
NK115(re)001:5836: 'od gong de nyid thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis
NK115(re)001:5837: bskyood nas h'u dang m+aum du gyur te 'phro 'dus
NK115(re)001:5838: yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje dang dril bur
NK115(re)001:5839: gyur pa las mi bskyod pa'am /
NK115(re)001:5840: kun mkhyen yab sras ltar na rnam snang yab yum
NK115(re)001:5841: du gsal la dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab par
NK115(re)001:5842: bya'o // de nas gtso bo yab yum gyi mkha'
NK115(re)001:5843: gsang byin gyis brlabs nas snyoms par zhugs nas byang
NK115(re)001:5844: chub sems kyi sprin yum mkhar spros te gzhal yas
NK115(re)001:5845: khang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i nang na /
NK115(re)001:5846: lha rnams kyi snying po h'u dang la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:5847: so so'i sa bon rnams gsal btab la lha so
NK115(re)001:5848: so'i gsang sngags brjod pa tsam gyis so so'i skur
NK115(re)001:5849: bskyed la / dzahzhesa yum mkha' nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bton te /
NK115(re)001:5850: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs /
NK115(re)001:5851: 'od zer spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs
NK115(re)001:5852: ste rang rang gi gnas su bzhugs par bsam zhing
NK115(re)001:5853: / kun bzang yab yum ni gtso bo'i thugs kar dang /
NK115(re)001:5854: thub drug ni khyams la bzhugs par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5855: de nas spyan 'dren sogs spyii 'gro ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:5856: yang d+r+wa ba che chung la brten pa'i bdag sras
NK115(re)001:5857: gzhan sras kyi bskyed tshul bka' sde zur pa rnams
NK115(re)001:5859: bdag sras kyi dus su yang cho ga gsum gyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bskyed la /
NK115(re)001:5860: de nas gzhan sras kyi cho ga snga ma dang phyogs 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:5861: yang cho ga gsum bskyed kyi lugs ltar na bdag
NK115(re)001:5862: sras gzhan sras la mi sbyor bar yi ge zhe
NK115(re)001:5863: gnyis las phyag mtshan zhe gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:5864: de las lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po bsgom ste /
NK115(re)001:5865: dbang bskur ba sogs gzhung bzhin bya'o //
NK115(re)001:5866: gnyis pa bsdus pa ltar bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:5867: de ltar sgong skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim gyi khyad
NK115(re)001:5868: par ni lan gnyis su skye ba dang mthun pa
NK115(re)001:5869: kho nar sbyor te sbyong ba yin pas na spros
NK115(re)001:5870: pa chung ngu'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:5871: 'di ltar mdor bsdu na thoga mara ranga nyid gnyug
NK115(re)001:5872: ma'i lhara gasla ba'i mduna gyi nam makhara gang bsgom
NK115(re)001:5873: pa'i dkyil 'khora gyi lha gasla gadba pa dang /
NK115(re)001:5874: rang gi thugs ka nas dkyil 'khor spro ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5875: dbyings nas spyan drangs shing mdun mkhar bzhugs par dmigs
NK115(re)001:5876: pa ste gsum du yod pa gang ltar yang de
NK115(re)001:5877: ltar byas nas / de'i mdun du rgyun bashagas yan
NK115(re)001:5878: lag bdun pa'am brgyad pa'am bcu pa rnams gang rung
NK115(re)001:5879: ltar byas nas / byas mthar / bdag dang tshogs
NK115(re)001:5880: zhing gnyis ka mi dmigas pa'i nganga nasa slar yang
NK115(re)001:5881: lha so so'i dkyila 'khora gyi mngona rtogsa skye gnas
NK115(re)001:5882: gang sbyong ba'i cho ga yin kyang de ji lta
NK115(re)001:5883: ba bzhina sgoma par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:5884: de yang rdo rje'i cho ga gsum bskyed sogs ston
NK115(re)001:5885: pa'i cho ga phal che bar tshogs zhing gsal nas
NK115(re)001:5886: tshogs bsags kyi rim pa rnams song nas rang la
NK115(re)001:5887: bsdu ba dang / de nas bgegs bskrad /
NK115(re)001:5890: mchod pa byin rlabs rnams byas te /
NK115(re)001:5891: bdag la sogs pa'i chos thams cad mi dmigs pa
NK115(re)001:5892: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa nas
NK115(re)001:5893: rim bzhin lha bskyed pas tshul de lta bu la
NK115(re)001:5894: yang zer ro // sgong skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed tshul
NK115(re)001:5895: rgyas bsdus gnyis po 'di dag gi skabs su dag
NK115(re)001:5896: rdzogs smin gsum bye brag tu sbyar nas gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:5897: yang zer ro // mi dran yang / mdor bsdu
NK115(re)001:5898: na 'di gnyis po gang yin kyang snang stong gi
NK115(re)001:5899: zhen pa sbyong ba'i phyir yang yin pas /
NK115(re)001:5900: rgyas pa'i dus su bdag sras kyi gtso 'khor thams cad 'od zhu bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:5901: bsdus pa'i tshe gnyis ka mi dmigs pa'i ngang la
NK115(re)001:5902: 'jog pa gnyis kas phyi nang gi snang ba dang
NK115(re)001:5903: rtog tshogs thams cad re zhig 'gags pa'i 'chi srid
NK115(re)001:5904: dag / bag chags mtha' dag dbyings su dag pa'i chos sku gzhi la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:5905: gnyis snang gi spros pa 'gags pa'i ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:5906: ngang la gnas pa'i 'od gsal ba'i rdzogs rim gyi
NK115(re)001:5908: yang rgyas pa'i tshe slar yang gzhan sras kyi gtso
NK115(re)001:5909: bo dang 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad gsal ba
NK115(re)001:5910: dang bsdus pa'i dus rang rang gi gzhung gi mngon
NK115(re)001:5911: rtogs bsgoms pas / 'chi srid kyi rjes su slar
NK115(re)001:5912: yang rlung sems rim gyis mched nas bar srid dang
NK115(re)001:5913: rtogs bsgoms pas / / de nas skye srid kyi
NK115(re)001:5914: snang ba rgya chen por 'byams pa mtha' dag dag
NK115(re)001:5915: rtogs bsgoms pas / / / mi slob pa'i zung
NK115(re)001:5916: 'jug gi lha sku chos sku'i ngang las gzugs sku'i
NK115(re)001:5917: bkod pa chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par 'byams klas
NK115(re)001:5919: rdzogs rim pa'i rnal 'byor pa 'od gsal las slob
NK115(re)001:5920: pa'i zung 'jug gi lha skur ldang nus pa'i smin
NK115(re)001:5921: byed du 'gro zhes sbyar na khyab che zhing /
NK115(re)001:5922: nang gses sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi skabs thams cad
NK115(re)001:5923: kyi dag rdzogs smin gsum po yang de'i khongs su
NK115(re)001:5924: ma 'dus pa'ang med la so sor bye brag tu
NK115(re)001:5925: sbyar yang chog gam snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:5926: yang dag rdzogs smin gsum gyi go ba sbyir bshad
NK115(re)001:5927: pa de tsam gyis go ba legs po zhig lon
NK115(re)001:5928: na bskyed tshul bzhi po so sor sbyar yang rung
NK115(re)001:5929: la ma sbyar yang rung ste /
NK115(re)001:5931: so sor sbyor na ni bskyed tshul dngos gzhi tsam
NK115(re)001:5932: du ma zad las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:5933: sogs la'ang sbyar du yod par mngon no //
NK115(re)001:5934: gnyis pa mngal skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:5936: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum bskyed /
NK115(re)001:5938: dang po mngon byang bzhi bskyed ni /
NK115(re)001:5939: spyir bskyed tshul gcig gis kyang skye gnas bzhi ka'i
NK115(re)001:5940: bag chags sbyong ba yin mod gtso cher skye gnas
NK115(re)001:5941: rang rang gi skye tshul gyi rnam pa dang dngos
NK115(re)001:5942: su mthun par bsgom pa'i tshul gyis de dang de'i
NK115(re)001:5943: bag chags gtso bor sbyong bas na mangla skyes kyi
NK115(re)001:5944: bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir de dang rnam pa mthun
NK115(re)001:5945: par mngona byang bzhi'i sgo nas bskyed pa'am /
NK115(re)001:5946: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum gyi sgo nas sam /
NK115(re)001:5947: mngon byang lnga'i sgo nas bskyed pa rnam pa gsum po las /
NK115(re)001:5948: dang po mngon byang bzhi bskyed kyi tshul 'di ni /
NK115(re)001:5949: rgyud khraga 'thung gal po'i dgongas pa ltar bshad pa ste /
NK115(re)001:5950: he ru ka gal po'i rgyud de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:5951: dang po stong pa byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:5952: gnyis pa sa bon bsdu ba ste //
NK115(re)001:5953: gsum pa la ni gzugs rdzogs pa //
NK115(re)001:5954: bzhi pa la ni yi ge 'god //
NK115(re)001:5956: sbyor ba'i rim pa rnams song nas /
NK115(re)001:5957: dngos gzhi'i dus su mngon byang dang po ni /
NK115(re)001:5958: sbyang bya'am dag bya rang bzhin brgyad cu'i rtog tshogs
NK115(re)001:5959: thams cad 'khrul stobs kyis nub pa'i 'chi srida dang
NK115(re)001:5960: / slar yang las rlung mched pa'i stobs kyis bar
NK115(re)001:5961: dora snang ba yad yud du 'byung ba dang bacasa
NK115(re)001:5963: rim pa bzhin rnam par rtog pa'i spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:5964: bral ba'i stong pa nyid chen po'i ngang la mnyam
NK115(re)001:5965: par gzhag nas de las de ltar ma rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:5966: sems can rnams la zhen med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:5967: snying rje byang chub kyi semas gnyis bsgoms pas chos
NK115(re)001:5968: sku dang longs sku gnyis gzhi la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:5969: 'od gsal dang sgyu lus gnyis kyis smin byed du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:5971: dri za nye bar lena pa bar do'i rnama par
NK115(re)001:5972: shesa pa de pha ma'i khu khrag gi dbus su
NK115(re)001:5974: ngo bo stong nyid dang snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes /
NK115(re)001:5975: rnam pa bskyed bya'i lha yi sa bona h'u la sogs par lam gyisa gsal bas sbyong zhing dag /
NK115(re)001:5977: dpe'i 'od gsal las sgyu lus kyi lha skur ldang ba'i smin byed du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:5979: sbyang bya'am dag bya rnam shes khu khrag dang 'dres
NK115(re)001:5980: pa de rlung bcus rim gyis bskyed nas gzugs kyi
NK115(re)001:5981: rnam pa rdzogs pa'i bar der /
NK115(re)001:5983: srog 'dzin sogs rtsa ba'i rlung lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:5985: yan lag gi rlung rgyu ba mig /
NK115(re)001:5986: rab tu rgyu ba rna ba /
NK115(re)001:5989: nges par rgyu ba lce ste dbang po lnga byed
NK115(re)001:5990: las dang bcas pa bskyed par byed pa'i rlung lnga
NK115(re)001:5991: dang bcu'o // de'ang nang gses kyi dbang du rlung
NK115(re)001:5992: bcu po'i 'du 'phrod kyis 'gyur ba'i gnas skabs lnga
NK115(re)001:5993: nyams su myong ba rdo rje'i cho ga bzhis sbyong
NK115(re)001:5994: dang bcu'o // ba'i tshul ni / gsung rdo rje
NK115(re)001:5995: sa bon gyis sbyong tshul ni mngon byang gnyis par
NK115(re)001:5996: dang bcu'o // ba'i tshul ni / song nas /
NK115(re)001:5997: rnam shes de nyid kyang khu ba dang rdul te
NK115(re)001:5998: khrag dang rlunga gsum dang 'dresa pa'i cha de rlung
NK115(re)001:5999: gi byed las kyis mera mera dang nur nur gyi
NK115(re)001:6000: gnas skabs su gyur ba de /
NK115(re)001:6001: sa bona gyi yi ge nyid lasa thugs rdo rje
NK115(re)001:6002: phyag matshana gyi rnam pa rdo rje la sogs par
NK115(re)001:6004: de nas ltara ltar dang mkhranga gyur du song ba'i gnas skabs ni /
NK115(re)001:6005: ye shes rdo rje phyag matshana de 'oda gonga du gyur pas sbyong zhing /
NK115(re)001:6006: de nas rim gyis brtas te khyab 'jug nya dang rusa sbala gyi rnam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6007: mig la sogs pa'i dabnga po dang yan lag yongs su rdzogas pa'i gnas skabs ni /
NK115(re)001:6008: sku rdo rje lha yi rnama pa zhal phyag sogs yongs su rdzogs par gyur bas sbyor ba'o //
NK115(re)001:6009: de ltar bsgoms pas zung 'jug ngo bo nyid kyi sku gzhi la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:6010: don gyi 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi lha skur ldang ba'i smin byed du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:6012: sbyang bya btsas nas dbang po yul la sad de
NK115(re)001:6013: sna tshogs pa'i dngos po la longs spyod pa'i zhen
NK115(re)001:6014: pa dag / sbyong byed lha mngal 'byin gyi sa bon spro ba'am /
NK115(re)001:6015: gnas gsum la sogs par yi ge bkod de rgyas gdab pa la'ang sbyar du rung bar gsungs pas /
NK115(re)001:6016: 'dis lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las gzhi la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:6017: rdzogs rim pa slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha skur
NK115(re)001:6018: ldang nas 'dod yon gyi snang ba la zhen med
NK115(re)001:6019: du rol bas rig pa'i rgyan du 'char ba'i smin
NK115(re)001:6021: de nas 'khor gyi lha tshogs spro ba sogs dngos
NK115(re)001:6022: gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa lhag ma rnams
NK115(re)001:6023: dang rjes kyi rim pa rnams rang rang gi gzhung
NK115(re)001:6024: ltar ro // gnyis pa rdo rje'i cho ga gsum bskyed ni /
NK115(re)001:6025: de la lha sku phyaga rgya chen po gsal ba ni /
NK115(re)001:6026: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku rdo rje'i ngo bo yin la /
NK115(re)001:6027: sa bon gyi yiga 'bru bsgom pa ni gsunga rdo rje dang /
NK115(re)001:6028: thugas rdo rje'i ngo bo nyid ni phyaga matshana yig
NK115(re)001:6029: 'brus matshana pa nyid du sbyor ba la bshad pa
NK115(re)001:6030: yin no // 'di'i sgom tshul gyi go rim ni /
NK115(re)001:6031: ting 'dzin rnam gsum yan chad sngon du song nas /
NK115(re)001:6032: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK115(re)001:6033: bo nyid rdo rje rtse lnga pa la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:6034: phyag mtshan gyi rnam par bsgoms pas /
NK115(re)001:6035: mngal du khams dkar dmar tshogs pa la dri za'i rnam shes zhugs pa sbyong /
NK115(re)001:6036: de nas phyag mtshan de nyid yi ger gnas gyur ba'am /
NK115(re)001:6037: gsung gi rang bzhin +aahdang h+aum la sogs pas mtshan
NK115(re)001:6038: par bsgoms pas khu khrag sems gsum 'dres pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:6039: skabs lnga nyams su myong ba sbyong /
NK115(re)001:6040: de las 'od zer gyi spro bsdus don gnyis byas
NK115(re)001:6041: te sku'i ngo bo lha'i rnam pa thams cad rdzogs
NK115(re)001:6042: par bsgoms pas dbang po dang yan lag la sogs
NK115(re)001:6043: pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i gnas skabs rnams
NK115(re)001:6045: 'di la cho ga phal che bar yig 'bru dang
NK115(re)001:6046: po bsgoms nas phyag mtshan du 'gyur bar gsungs kyang
NK115(re)001:6047: / 'dir bshad pa ltar na gong gi sbyang bya'i go rim dang /
NK115(re)001:6048: spyir sbyang bya srid pa'i mched tshul yang sems rtog
NK115(re)001:6049: phra ba las ngag dang lus sems snang ba rags
NK115(re)001:6051: sbyangs 'bras kyang thugs chos sku'i ngang las /
NK115(re)001:6052: gsung dang sku'i rang bzhin longs sku dang sprul skur
NK115(re)001:6053: snang ba sogs dang bstun na ches mchog tu gyur
NK115(re)001:6054: pa'i lam gnad cig ston par 'dug snyam du sems
NK115(re)001:6055: so // 'di'i dag rdzogs smin gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:6056: ji skad bshad pa'i sbyang bya de dag dang sgo gsum gyi snang zhen thams cad dag /
NK115(re)001:6057: 'bras bu rdo rje gsum gyi yon tan thams cad gzhi la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:6058: dben gsum gyi smin byed du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:6059: de ni lha bskyed tshul gyi dngos gzhi bye brag
NK115(re)001:6060: pa ste lhag ma rnams ni rang rang gi gzhung
NK115(re)001:6062: 'di la rdo rje'i cho ga gsuma bskyed do zhesa
NK115(re)001:6063: yongs su grags pa ste pha rgyud spyi'i lugas so
NK115(re)001:6064: // gsum pa mngon byang lnga bskyed bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:6065: gzhi 'bras lto sbyar te spyir bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:6066: lam gyi mngon byang lnga bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:6067: dang po gzhi 'bras lto sbyar te spyir bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:6068: 'di la spyir sbyang gzhi 'khor ba'i ngo bor gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6069: sbyong byed lam gyi byed rtsol la brten nas rgyud la bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6070: sbyangs 'bras mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du gyur
NK115(re)001:6071: pa'i gnas skabs gsum gyis dbye bas gzhi'i mngon byang
NK115(re)001:6074: don du stong bzhi'i 'od gsal zung 'jug dang bcas
NK115(re)001:6075: pa'i lnga po nyid yin pas gsang sngags kyi lam
NK115(re)001:6076: thams cad kyi don po yin gsungs /
NK115(re)001:6077: de yang lus ngag yid gsum tshogs pa dang bcas pa'am /
NK115(re)001:6078: dkar dmar rlung sems tshogs pa dang bcas pa ye
NK115(re)001:6079: nas ye shes lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pa ni
NK115(re)001:6081: tshogs sbyor du dpe'i ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:6082: mthong sgom du don gyi 'od gsal mngon du byas
NK115(re)001:6083: pa'i stong bzhi zung 'jug dang bcas pa lam gyi
NK115(re)001:6085: de rgyud la bskyed byed bskyed rim du zla nyi sogs lnga bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6086: rdzogs rim du dkar dmar rlung sems cha dang bcas
NK115(re)001:6087: pa la gnad du bsnun pa'i ye shes lnga po
NK115(re)001:6088: dang bcas pa'ang lam gyi mngon byang /
NK115(re)001:6090: ye shes lnga la sogs pa mi slob pa'i zung
NK115(re)001:6091: 'jug gi yon tan thams cad ni 'bras bu'i mngon
NK115(re)001:6092: byang yin no // des na mthar 'bras la sgrib byed kyi sbyang gzhi shin tu phra ba /
NK115(re)001:6093: sgo gsum phra ba'i bag chags sam /
NK115(re)001:6094: dkar dmar rlung sems kyi rgyu ba phra ba ni
NK115(re)001:6095: rdo rje theg pa'i lam ma gtogs gzhan gyis sbyong
NK115(re)001:6096: mi nus pas na gsang sngags bgrod pa gcig pu'i
NK115(re)001:6097: lam yin pa'i rgyu mtshan yang de yin pas 'di
NK115(re)001:6098: dag gi sbyang gzhi dang sbyong byed sbyangs 'bras rnams
NK115(re)001:6099: lto sbyar nas legs par shes na rdo rje theg
NK115(re)001:6100: pa'i lam gnad thun mong ma yin pa rig par
NK115(re)001:6101: 'gyur ro gsungs / de la mngal zhugs kyi rim
NK115(re)001:6102: pa dang lam dang 'bras bu'i chos mthun pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:6104: chos sku'i 'od gsal lugs ldog tu mched ba'i yid
NK115(re)001:6105: lus bar do longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur ldang mi
NK115(re)001:6106: nus pa'am nus kyang gzhan don du skye ba sprul
NK115(re)001:6107: sku'i lam 'khyer la 'jug pa dag gis bar ma
NK115(re)001:6108: do nasa sems bskyed dang ldan pas lusa 'tshola ba
NK115(re)001:6110: chos ldan gyi lus rten thob pa'i mngal sgo 'dams
NK115(re)001:6111: nas ma'i mangla du rnam shesa h'u yig la sogs
NK115(re)001:6112: pas rnam pas 'juga pa sbyor ba'i lam ste /
NK115(re)001:6113: lhumas su zhugsa dus kyi khu 1ba /
NK115(re)001:6117: 'dres pa'i cha 5ste byang chub lnga po mer nur
NK115(re)001:6118: la sogs pa'i gnas skabs lnga'i rim pas rgyas par
NK115(re)001:6119: byed pa'i byed las rang rgyud pa rnams sbyong ba
NK115(re)001:6121: de'i tshe'i zla ba bcu'i yun ni slob pa'i sa
NK115(re)001:6122: bcu dang raba tu sbyar nasa batsa'a ba na lhag
NK115(re)001:6123: pa'i lha gang yin pa'i skur bzhengs pa mi sloba
NK115(re)001:6124: pa'i lam du gyur nas zung 'jug skye ba sprul
NK115(re)001:6127: mngal zhugs byang chub rnam lnga ste //
NK115(re)001:6128: zla ba bcu ni sa bcu'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:6129: skye ba rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku //
NK115(re)001:6130: lhun grub sku gsum bdag nyid do //
NK115(re)001:6132: de ltar mi nus pa'i phal pa zhig yin na
NK115(re)001:6133: yang rim pa de dag ni lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:6134: chos de rnams dang rang bzhin gyis tshul mthun par
NK115(re)001:6135: yod de gzhi 'bras ngo bo gcig pa'i rten 'brel
NK115(re)001:6137: de yang bar dor lus rten tshol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:6138: tshogs lam du thos bsam gyis lam yang dag tshol ba gnyis mtshungs shing /
NK115(re)001:6139: de bzhin du rnam shes mngal du zhugs nas phyir mi ldog pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6140: sbyor lam du rigs nges thob pa /
NK115(re)001:6141: rnam shes khu khrag sogs dang 'dres nas ming gzugs kyi tshogs pa tshang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:6142: mthong lam du bdag med pa'i rtogs pa tshang bar rnyed pa /
NK115(re)001:6143: mer nur sogs gnas skabs lnga'i rim pas zla ba bcur gong du 'phel ba dang /
NK115(re)001:6144: sgom lam du rtogs pa de gong du 'phel ba'i rim pas sa bcu bgrod pa /
NK115(re)001:6145: lus yongs su rdzogs shing phyir btsas nas dbang po
NK115(re)001:6146: yul la sad de tshogs drug gi yul so so
NK115(re)001:6148: mi slob pa'i lam du rtogs pa yongs su rdzogs
NK115(re)001:6149: pa mthar phyin nas shes bya thams cad la mkhyen
NK115(re)001:6150: pa'i ye shes sad de gdul bya'i 'gro ba drug
NK115(re)001:6151: gi don so so la mnga' dbang 'byor pa rnams
NK115(re)001:6153: gnyis pa lam gyi mngon byang lnga bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:6154: rgyud sde spyi khyab dang bstun pa ste /
NK115(re)001:6155: de yang sbyor rjes la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:6156: gyi rim pa gzhan rnams rang gzhung gis bstan pa
NK115(re)001:6157: ltar la / dngos gzhi'i dus su lam byed bzhi
NK115(re)001:6158: la brten nas bsgom pa'i sbyang bya dang sbyong byed
NK115(re)001:6160: sbyong byed mngona byang dang po /
NK115(re)001:6161: rnam snang gi ngo bo +aa li las byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:6162: zla ba'i dkyila 'khora du bsgom pa ni rnam pa
NK115(re)001:6163: lam byed / de'i ngo bo chos thams cad me
NK115(re)001:6164: long gi gzugs brnyan ltar snang bas me long lta
NK115(re)001:6165: bu'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa lam
NK115(re)001:6166: lam byed / byed / de'ang chos sku'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:6167: sgrib med du gsal ba ni 'bras bu lam byed
NK115(re)001:6168: lam byed / byed / / lam byed gsum la
NK115(re)001:6169: brten nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i rten 'brel du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:6170: ba'i byin rlabs lam byed ces bya ste /
NK115(re)001:6171: lam byed phyi ma 'di ni 'og ma rnams la'ang 'agre'o //
NK115(re)001:6178: mangla skyes kyi pha'i khu ba droda gshera skyes kyi gshera te rlan gyi cha /
NK115(re)001:6179: sgonga skyes kyi pha'i cha dang rdzusa skyes kyi stonga pa'i cha rnams sbyong ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:6180: de bzhina du sbyong byed mngon byang gnyis pa rin
NK115(re)001:6181: 'byung gi ngo bo k+aa li las byung ba'i nyi
NK115(re)001:6182: ma'i dkyila 'khora bsgom pa yanga rnam pa lam byed
NK115(re)001:6183: / mngon byang dang po 'di gnyis kyi skabs su mtshan gyi sa bon +aa li dang /
NK115(re)001:6184: dpe byad kyi sa bon k+aa li'i phreng ba nyis
NK115(re)001:6185: rim re zla nyi so so'i khong seng du sgom
NK115(re)001:6186: par yang gsungs / nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor de'i ngo
NK115(re)001:6187: bo chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:6188: ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa lam byed
NK115(re)001:6189: par yang gsungs / / de'ang sangs rgyas dang sems
NK115(re)001:6190: can gyi rang bzhin dngos po gcig par thugs su
NK115(re)001:6191: chud pa'i ye shes sgrib med du gsal ba ni
NK115(re)001:6199: mangla skyes kyi ma'i rdula dang /
NK115(re)001:6201: sgo skyes kyi ma'i cha dang /
NK115(re)001:6202: rdzusa skyes kyi gasla ba'i cha rnams sbyong ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:6203: yang sbyong byed mngon byanga gsum pa 'od dpag med
NK115(re)001:6204: kyi ngo bo sa bona phyag matshana dang bacasa pa'i
NK115(re)001:6205: rnam par bsgom pa ni rnam pa lam byed /
NK115(re)001:6206: de'i ngo bo chos thams cad ma 'dres par rtogs
NK115(re)001:6207: pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa lam
NK115(re)001:6208: byed // de yang chos thams cad ma bsgribs par
NK115(re)001:6209: gsal zhing mkhyen pa'i ye shes so sor rtog pa
NK115(re)001:6216: mngal skyes kyi khu rdul gnyis kyi bar du bar do'i rnama shesa zhugas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6217: des mtshon nas skye gansa gzhan gsum dang bcas bzhi
NK115(re)001:6218: po'i bar do'i rnama shesa skye gnas so sor zhugs
NK115(re)001:6219: pa rnams sbyong ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:6220: de bzhin du sbyong byed mngona byang bzhi pa don grub kyi ngo bo /
NK115(re)001:6223: phyag mtshan sa bon gyi mtshan pa ste rnama pa
NK115(re)001:6224: gsuma po ro gciga tu 'dresa pa'i thig le gong
NK115(re)001:6225: bu'i rnam pa can du bsgom pa ni rnam pa
NK115(re)001:6226: lam byed / de'i ngo bo sangs rgyas thams cad
NK115(re)001:6227: kyi mdzad pa ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:6228: su mos pa ni mos pa lam byed /
NK115(re)001:6229: de'ang sems can gyi bya ba thams cad grub pa'i ye shes ni 'bras bu lam byed do //
NK115(re)001:6236: mngal skyes dang sgong skyes gnyis la mtshon na khu
NK115(re)001:6237: rdula semas gsuma ro gciga tu 'dresa pa'i cha dang
NK115(re)001:6238: / droda gshera skyesa kyi droda gsher gnyis dang rnama shesa 'dres pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6239: rdzusa skyesa kyi gasla la stonga pa'i cha tsam dang
NK115(re)001:6240: bar do'i srida pa ste rnam shes 'dresa pa'i cha
NK115(re)001:6242: yang sbyong byed mngona byang lnga pa mi bskyod pa'i
NK115(re)001:6243: ngo bo rgyu'i he ru ka yab yum gyi sku
NK115(re)001:6244: ru bskyed cing gruba pa ni rnam pa lam byed
NK115(re)001:6245: / de nyid 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad dbyings
NK115(re)001:6246: su rdzogs pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos
NK115(re)001:6247: / pa lam byed / de'i ngo bo chos kyi
NK115(re)001:6248: dbyings kyi ye shes dang ro gcig pa ni 'bras
NK115(re)001:6251: zla ba me long ye shes te //
NK115(re)001:6252: bdun gyi bdun pa mnyam pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:6253: rang lha'i sa bon phyag mtshan ni //
NK115(re)001:6254: so sor rtog par brjod par bya //
NK115(re)001:6255: thams cad gcig gyur nan tan nyid //
NK115(re)001:6256: rdzogs pa chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK115(re)001:6259: rnam shes kyi phung po dang /
NK115(re)001:6261: sgo gsum cha mnyam pa'i bag chags dang /
NK115(re)001:6262: tshogs brgyad kyi chos nyid du 'dzin pa'i cha dang /
NK115(re)001:6264: skye gansa bzhi po'i rang rang gi yan lag dang
NK115(re)001:6265: nying lag dang skye mcheda kyi cha thams cad yongas
NK115(re)001:6266: su rdzogas nasa phyir btsas te rega pa'i yula gzugs
NK115(re)001:6267: la sogs pa la mig la sogs pa'i dabnga po
NK115(re)001:6268: mngon sum du sada de longs spyod pa yi 'khora
NK115(re)001:6269: ba'i 'khrul snang gi rnam par bya byed kyi cha
NK115(re)001:6270: dang bcas pa mtha' dag sbyong bar byed pa yin
NK115(re)001:6271: no // de ltar bskyed pa de yi rang 'bras sngags kyi yon tan bskyed pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:6272: ji skad bshad pa ltar skye srid bzhi'i bag chags dang /
NK115(re)001:6275: rnama para shesa pa'i tshogas brgyad dang /
NK115(re)001:6276: nyon mongs pa lnga dang bcas pa'i cha thams cad
NK115(re)001:6277: mngon byang lnga'i sbyong byed kyis sbyangs shing gansa su
NK115(re)001:6278: daga pa'i gadna gsuma tshanga ba'i lha ru rdzogs pa
NK115(re)001:6279: ni mtshan dang dpe byad kyi rang bzhin gzhan la
NK115(re)001:6280: phan pa brgya chen po 'grub pa'i mya ngana las
NK115(re)001:6281: 'adsa pa yon tan dang ye shes thams cad mthar
NK115(re)001:6282: phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dang bzhugas tshula mthuna
NK115(re)001:6283: par lam du byed pa ste /
NK115(re)001:6284: de'i tshul ni rgyu'i rdo rje 'dzin pa yab yum
NK115(re)001:6285: 'od du zhu nas thig ler gyur pa lasa 'khor
NK115(re)001:6286: gyi lha mos zhu ba glus bskul gyi sgra'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:6287: gyis 'brasa bu'i he ru ka'i skur bzhengs pa dang
NK115(re)001:6288: don gnyis sgrub pa'i phrin las la 'jug pa la
NK115(re)001:6290: de ltar yang nges brjod bla ma las /
NK115(re)001:6291: mngal skyes glu yi sbyor ba yis //
NK115(re)001:6292: bsgoms pa rnams ni yongs su brtag /
NK115(re)001:6293: sgong skyes glu ni med pa ste //
NK115(re)001:6296: 'gro ba'i lus rten khyad par can la khams kyi
NK115(re)001:6297: sbyang gzhi rtsa thig rlung sems rags pa'i cha mngon
NK115(re)001:6298: gyur du yod pa thabs kyis zin pas grol bar
NK115(re)001:6299: 'gyur te dang po dbang gis smin par byas te
NK115(re)001:6300: / rtog bcas kyi lam bskyed rim gyi dus su
NK115(re)001:6301: mngon byang lnga bsgom pa'i tshe na'ang gnad du bsnun
NK115(re)001:6302: bya'i gtso bo ni dkar dmar sems gsum yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:6303: phyir 'khor ba dang mthun pa'i rnam pa lam byed
NK115(re)001:6304: kyis ni sbyang bya srid pa'i rang bzhin khu rdula
NK115(re)001:6305: rlunga gsuma semas dang bcas pa'i cha thams cad rnama
NK115(re)001:6306: / para daga / rgyal ba'i bzhugs tshul dang mthun
NK115(re)001:6307: pa'i mos pa lam byed pa bsgomas pasa 'bras chos
NK115(re)001:6308: lnga dang ye shes lnga'i yon tan thams cad gzhi
NK115(re)001:6309: / para daga / la rdzogs / de gnyis ka snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:6313: zug 'jug la sogs pa'i rdzogas rim gyi smina byed
NK115(re)001:6314: du 'gyur ba'i 'bras bu lam byed kyis mtshan dpe
NK115(re)001:6315: la sogs pa'i bdag nyid du smin par byed pa
NK115(re)001:6316: yin no // 'di'i bskyed tshul gyi rim pa go
NK115(re)001:6317: bde bar cho ga'i 'gros dang sbyar nas mdor bsdus
NK115(re)001:6319: kyee rdor lta bu la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:6320: skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed nas /
NK115(re)001:6321: rdor sems he ru ka'i bsgom bzlas byas rjes /
NK115(re)001:6322: rang nyid skad cig gis gtso bo'i skur gsal ba'i
NK115(re)001:6323: thugs ka'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas dkyil
NK115(re)001:6324: 'khor gyi lha tshogs spyan drangs la mchod cing /
NK115(re)001:6325: tshogs bsags sdom bzung rnams byas nas tshad med pa bzhi bsgom la /
NK115(re)001:6326: sh+au nya t+aas stong par sbyangs nas /
NK115(re)001:6327: pad nyi'i steng du sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK115(re)001:6328: h'u yig gnas pa'i 'od zer gyis steng 'og phyogs
NK115(re)001:6329: mtshams thams cad rdo rjes gtams pa'i phyi rol du
NK115(re)001:6330: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba dang /
NK115(re)001:6331: yang sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar pad nyi'i steng
NK115(re)001:6332: b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo rtsibs bcu par gyur pa'i dbus
NK115(re)001:6333: kyi nyi steng gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba ser
NK115(re)001:6335: rtsib bcur khro bcu gsal ba sogs kyis gnod byed brlagsa shing mtshams bcad de /
NK115(re)001:6336: gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba zhu ba las chos
NK115(re)001:6337: 'byung gi nang du rlung me chu sa'i dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:6339: de'i steng 'bru gsum hohganyisa kyis mtha' brten pa'i bar do'i rnam shes /
NK115(re)001:6340: de rnams 'byung bzhi 'khor lo dang bcas pa la
NK115(re)001:6341: thim ste thams cad ro gcig tu 'dres pa las
NK115(re)001:6342: gzhal yas khang phyi rol du dur khrod brgyad kyis
NK115(re)001:6343: bskor bar gsal ba'i dbus kyi gdan steng mtshan bzang
NK115(re)001:6344: gi ngo bo +aa li dkar po phrag gnyis zhu
NK115(re)001:6345: ba las byung ba'i zla dkyil /
NK115(re)001:6346: de'i steng du dpe byad kyi ngo bo gsal byed so bzhi'i steng du /
NK115(re)001:6347: ya ra la wa da d+ha bsnan pa'i yi ge
NK115(re)001:6348: dmar po bzhi bcu po phrag gnyis zhu ba las
NK115(re)001:6350: de gnyis kyi bar phyag mtshan sa bon gyis mtshan pa /
NK115(re)001:6351: de thams cad zhu ba'i thig le dmar skya las
NK115(re)001:6352: rgyu'i rdo rje 'dzin pa yab yum gsal nas mkha'
NK115(re)001:6353: gsang byin gyis brlabs te snyoms par zhugs pa'i mkha'
NK115(re)001:6354: gsang nas ha si la sogs pa'i bde ba chen
NK115(re)001:6355: po'i sgras de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad spyan drangs
NK115(re)001:6356: yab kyi zhal du zhugs sku'i dbyibs brgyud rdo rje'i
NK115(re)001:6357: lam nas yum mkhar thig le brgyad du gyur pa
NK115(re)001:6358: las sa bon brgyad du gyur pa 'od zhu'i lha
NK115(re)001:6359: mo brgyad du gyur pas gdan so sor bkod /
NK115(re)001:6360: slar yang yab yum snyoms par zhugs pas bar snang
NK115(re)001:6361: nas 'bru gsum hohganyisa kyis mtha' brten pa'i bar do'i
NK115(re)001:6362: rnam shes yab kyi zhal nas zhugs pa yum gyi
NK115(re)001:6363: mkhar slebs pa'i rkyen gyis yab yum 'od kyi thig
NK115(re)001:6364: ler gyur pa la rang gi shes pa mtshams bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:6365: lha mo bzhir 'phos te glus bskul ba'i rkyen gyis
NK115(re)001:6366: thig le sa bon du gyur pa zhu ba las
NK115(re)001:6367: 'bras bu'i rdo rje 'dzin par bzhengs te gtso 'khor
NK115(re)001:6368: thams cad kyi dbang po'i sgo so sor lha'i phyag
NK115(re)001:6369: rgyas rgyas btab la ye shes pa spyan drangs nas
NK115(re)001:6370: dam ye dbyer med du bsres te /
NK115(re)001:6371: slar yang dbang lha spyan drangs pas dbang bskur /
NK115(re)001:6372: de nas bdud rtsi brlabs te myong /
NK115(re)001:6373: rang gi thugs ka nas sprul pa'i lha mo rnams kyis mchod cing bstod nas /
NK115(re)001:6374: dag pa dran par byas la /
NK115(re)001:6376: de nas 'dod don gsol te nyer bsdu bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:6377: shis brjod dang smon lam sogs kyis mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:6378: gsum pa drod gsher skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:6379: dbang po rno zhing blo las su rung ba rnams
NK115(re)001:6380: kyis dang po nas bsgom du med pa'ang ma yin
NK115(re)001:6381: mod / spyir bskyed rim spros pa can gnyis la
NK115(re)001:6382: goms pa cher thob pa rnams kyis ni drod gsher
NK115(re)001:6383: skyes sbyong ba a nu yo ga'i bskyed rim gtso
NK115(re)001:6385: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde'u mig las /
NK115(re)001:6386: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni //
NK115(re)001:6387: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas pas //
NK115(re)001:6388: ma skyes rdzogs pa'i lha ru bsgom //
NK115(re)001:6390: droda gshera las skyes pa rnams ni gnyisa po lhan
NK115(re)001:6391: du 'dusa pa la rnama par shesa pa zhugas pa'i
NK115(re)001:6392: moda la mngal skyes ltar yun ring por smin mi
NK115(re)001:6393: dgos par gzugas kyi dngos po yongs su rdzogs par
NK115(re)001:6395: dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa'i lta ba'i
NK115(re)001:6396: ngang las snying rje chen po'i rtsal snang gi 'phen
NK115(re)001:6397: pa gtad tsam gyis mngon byang lnga la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:6398: rnam pa dang tshig gi spros pa la ma brten
NK115(re)001:6399: par gnas lus la sred pa dang len pa'i bag
NK115(re)001:6400: chags sbyang phyir / gang bskyed par bya ba'i lha
NK115(re)001:6401: yi snying po brjod pas matshana dang mngona rtogsa kyi
NK115(re)001:6402: rnam pa drana tsam lasa shes rab kyi dbyings stong
NK115(re)001:6403: pa nyid kun tu bzang mo'i klong las kun rdzob
NK115(re)001:6404: bden pa'i cha rten dang brten pa'i lha'i phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:6405: yongs su rdzogas pa'i bskyeda rima tshang bar bsgoma pa
NK115(re)001:6406: ni bde stong dbyer med kyi bskyed rim chen po
NK115(re)001:6407: chags sbyang phyir / ste / rang shar las /
NK115(re)001:6408: rim gyis 'jug pa gang zhe na /
NK115(re)001:6409: dbyings dang ye shes rim gyis zhugs nas ni //
NK115(re)001:6411: des na 'di la yul snang bden med du shes pa sgyu ma'i bskyed rim zhes kyang bya'o //
NK115(re)001:6412: bzhi pa rdzus skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:6413: 'di ltar sems can bardzusa te skye ba rnams ni /
NK115(re)001:6414: gsal stong gi cha la rnam shes zhugs pa tsam
NK115(re)001:6415: gis lus yongs su rdzogs par grub pa ni drod
NK115(re)001:6416: gsher las skye ba las kyang myur ba ltar skada
NK115(re)001:6417: ciga gis lta ba goms pa'i ngang las snying po
NK115(re)001:6418: tsam drana pa'i mod la dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK115(re)001:6419: yongs su rdzogas te minga ngam snying po brjod pa
NK115(re)001:6420: dang lha'i gzugas kyi rnam pa la rim gyi sems
NK115(re)001:6421: gtad pa sogs kyi spros pa la ma brten par
NK115(re)001:6422: chu las nya 'phar ba bzhin rten dang brten pa
NK115(re)001:6423: thams cad wala gyis gasla ba ste /
NK115(re)001:6425: cig char 'jug pa gang zhe na /
NK115(re)001:6426: lha rnams ma bskyed snying po dran pas rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:6429: skad cig tsam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK115(re)001:6430: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa ni //
NK115(re)001:6431: khams gsum gzhal yas khang bdag nyid //
NK115(re)001:6432: srog chags rnams ni dkyil 'khor ba //
NK115(re)001:6433: de dbus skad cig rnam pa yi //
NK115(re)001:6434: dkyil 'a khor bdag po rnal 'byor pa'o //
NK115(re)001:6436: skad cig dran rdzogs 'di la bskyed rim gyi yan
NK115(re)001:6437: lag ma tshang bas rgyal ba'i bka' las gzhan du
NK115(re)001:6439: mngon brjod bla ma'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:6440: cig char 'jug pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK115(re)001:6441: bdag gi lus ni rnam par bsam //
NK115(re)001:6443: gsang ba mchog ni bla na med //
NK115(re)001:6444: skad cig gis ni bdag bsgom pa //
NK115(re)001:6445: he ru ka dpal gzugs su bya //
NK115(re)001:6448: dbang po rnon pos skad cig gis //
NK115(re)001:6449: rnam pas sems tsam dkyil 'khor bsam //
NK115(re)001:6452: sems can bardzusa te skye ba bzhin //
NK115(re)001:6453: sa bon med par rnam par bsgom //
NK115(re)001:6454: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas rnam pa thams
NK115(re)001:6455: cad du spros pa dang bcas pa'i bskyed rim gyi
NK115(re)001:6456: yan lag tshang bar yod dgos pa ma yin no
NK115(re)001:6457: // spyir bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gsum po re re
NK115(re)001:6458: la'ang bskyed rim gyi bskyed rim nas zung 'jug gi
NK115(re)001:6459: zung 'jug gi bar gsum re yod par gsungs pas
NK115(re)001:6460: lha'i rnam pa zhig gsal ba thams cad bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:6461: gnyis kyi zlas phye ba'i bskyed rim yin mi dgos
NK115(re)001:6462: // so // des na rim pa gnyis su phye
NK115(re)001:6463: ba'i bskyed rim ni rim pa gnyis pa'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:6464: rgyud la ma skyes pa'i gang zag gis de'i smin
NK115(re)001:6465: byed du dang po bsgom pa ste sngags kyi lta
NK115(re)001:6466: ba la nges pa rnyed nas rtog pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK115(re)001:6467: lha'i rnam par shar ba la goms su 'jug pa
NK115(re)001:6468: // so // yin la / rdzogs rim gyi rtogs
NK115(re)001:6469: pa khyad par can skyes nas ye shes kyi rtsal
NK115(re)001:6470: snang lha'i rnam par shar ba yin pas slob pa'i
NK115(re)001:6472: rgyu mtshan de lta bas na las dang po pas
NK115(re)001:6473: bskyed rim bsgom pa rnam rtog gi gzugs brnyan tsam
NK115(re)001:6474: zhig yin yang lta ba'i gdeng gis zin nas ye
NK115(re)001:6475: shes dngos dang rjes su mthun pa zhig med na
NK115(re)001:6476: de'i rgyu dang smin byed du mi 'gyur bas na
NK115(re)001:6477: de ting dang dgongs pa'i gzer gal che ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:6479: des na nyams su len rgyu'i chos rim pa gnyis
NK115(re)001:6480: po gzhung dang cho gar bstan pa de tsam gyis
NK115(re)001:6481: de dang de kho nar mi 'gyur te las dang
NK115(re)001:6482: po pas rdzogs rim gyi ye shes la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:6483: bzhag na'ang sems kyi dmigs pa las mi 'da' la
NK115(re)001:6484: / rtogs pa mchog ldan gyis bskyed rim gyi spros
NK115(re)001:6485: pa bsgoms kyang ye shes kyi rang rtsal yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:6486: / phyir ro // rdzogs rim gyi ye shes ma
NK115(re)001:6487: skyes pa'i gang zag gis rtsa rlung dang gtum mo
NK115(re)001:6488: sogs kyi skabs su lha'i rnam pa gsal ba ni
NK115(re)001:6489: dngos su lhan skyes ye shes 'char byed yin pas
NK115(re)001:6490: rtog pa'i gzugs brnyan yin yang rdzogs rim gyi lha
NK115(re)001:6491: / phyir ro // skur bsdu'o // lta dgongs mthon
NK115(re)001:6492: por gyur pa rnams kyis bskyed rim gyi spros pa
NK115(re)001:6493: chen po dag bsgom pa ni gdul bya'i dbang dang
NK115(re)001:6494: / phyir ro // skur bsdu'o // / khyad par
NK115(re)001:6495: dkyil 'khor de dang der slob ma 'jug cing smin
NK115(re)001:6496: pa'i rten 'brel khyad du mi gsod pas yin gyi
NK115(re)001:6497: rang la ched du dgos nas ni ma yin no
NK115(re)001:6499: 'dir 'phros don cung zad bshad pa 'di yang bla
NK115(re)001:6500: ma'i zhal rgyun yin snang shar yang don zab pas
NK115(re)001:6501: ji bzhin mi nges pa'i phyir blo gsal rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:6502: / phyir ro // skur bsdu'o // / // dpyad par bya'o // gnyis pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:6503: dper na gang zag gcig la'ang byis pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6505: rgan po'i gnas skabs gsum yod pa bzhin /
NK115(re)001:6506: bskyed rim gyi bsgoma tshula skye gnas bzhi sbyong byed
NK115(re)001:6507: du bstan pa bzhi po de'nga dang po'i lasa cana
NK115(re)001:6508: gsar du bskyed rim la goms su 'jug pa rnams
NK115(re)001:6509: kyis sganga skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rima gatsa bora bsgama
NK115(re)001:6510: zhing / de nas rama pa bazhin gamas pa cung zad brtan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6511: brtana pa chena po thob pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6512: shina tu brtana pa'i gnas skabs kyi blo'i mthu dang
NK115(re)001:6513: mthuna para sloba pa ste rags pa'i dkyil 'khor yud
NK115(re)001:6514: tsam gyis mngon du byed mi nus pa'i bar mngal
NK115(re)001:6515: skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim dang /
NK115(re)001:6516: phra ba de'i spyan gyi dkar nag tshun chod la gsal snang thob pa'i bar drod gsher skyes dang /
NK115(re)001:6517: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo yud tsam la rdzogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:6518: tshe bardzusa skyes ltar bsgom pa ste de ltar bzhi
NK115(re)001:6519: po'i snga ma gnyis byis pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6520: de nas gnyis dar babs dang /
NK115(re)001:6521: rgan po'i gnas skabs lta bu ting nge 'dzin la
NK115(re)001:6522: goms cha ma song ba dang song ba'i bye brag
NK115(re)001:6523: gis so // de skad du'ang sdom 'byung las /
NK115(re)001:6524: bskyed pa'i rim pas dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK115(re)001:6525: rtul 'bring dag gis bsam par bya //
NK115(re)001:6526: rnal 'byor skad cig rnam pa yi //
NK115(re)001:6527: sems tsam nyid kyi dkyil 'khor te //
NK115(re)001:6528: skad cig rnam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK115(re)001:6529: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom par bya //
NK115(re)001:6531: gsum pa bskyed gzhi ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum sgom pa'i tshul bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:6532: de lta bu'i bskyed rim yang snang ba'i phyogs thabs
NK115(re)001:6533: su byas pa'i cha tsam las don la bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:6534: ya ma bral bar nyams su len pa'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:6535: / sngags bla med kyi bskyed rim bsgom pa rnams
NK115(re)001:6536: thog mar spros pa can gyi bskyed rim dang po
NK115(re)001:6537: gnyis nas rim par 'jug dgos pas de gnyis kyi
NK115(re)001:6538: sngon du 'gro ba ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum po
NK115(re)001:6539: yin pa ni snga 'gyur rnying ma'i thun mong ma
NK115(re)001:6541: de yang skye srid phyi ma gnyis sbyong byed kyi
NK115(re)001:6542: bskyed rim gnyis la ni sngon du ting 'dzin gsum
NK115(re)001:6543: po rim can du ma bsgom yang goms pa' stobs
NK115(re)001:6544: kyis stong nyid dang snying rje ngang gis zung 'jug
NK115(re)001:6545: tu yod do // des na gsang sngags nang pa'i
NK115(re)001:6546: bskyed rim kuna kyanga ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:6547: ngang las shar ba zhig dgos pas /
NK115(re)001:6548: dang po de bzhina nyid kyi ting nge 'dzina ni /
NK115(re)001:6549: zab mo stong pa nyid kyi gnas lugs sprosa pa'i
NK115(re)001:6550: mtha' kun dang brala ba'i rang bzhin shes pa'i shesa
NK115(re)001:6551: raba kyi don la mnyam par 'jog pa yin pas
NK115(re)001:6552: / thog mar gzhi rang bzhin lhun grub kyi gnas
NK115(re)001:6553: lugs de dbang dus su bla ma'i byin rlabs 'pho
NK115(re)001:6554: ba la sogs pa'i stobs kyis shes na smos ci
NK115(re)001:6555: dgos kyang gzhan du thos bsam la brten nas nges
NK115(re)001:6556: pa rnyed dgos pas de'i tshul sngar yang bshad la
NK115(re)001:6557: / / 'dir mdor bsdus te smos na gsang ba snying po las /
NK115(re)001:6558: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs /
NK115(re)001:6559: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang bsgyur //
NK115(re)001:6560: ngo mtshar sku gsum yon tan zhing khams las //
NK115(re)001:6561: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK115(re)001:6563: gdod ma'i sems nyid de ni stong pa chos sku'i
NK115(re)001:6564: snying po can yin pas nam mkha' ltar go phyed
NK115(re)001:6565: pa / gsal ba longs sku'i rang bzhin can yin pas nyi zla ltar rang 'od gsal ba /
NK115(re)001:6566: 'char tshul sprul sku'i bdag nyid can yin pas yid
NK115(re)001:6567: bzhin gyi nor bu ltar 'dod dgu lhun gyis grub
NK115(re)001:6568: pas bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po can nam rgyal
NK115(re)001:6569: ba'i sku gsum gyi 'char gzhir ye nas rang chas
NK115(re)001:6571: de'i ngang las sems can 'khrul tshul yang /
NK115(re)001:6573: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK115(re)001:6574: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK115(re)001:6575: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK115(re)001:6576: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK115(re)001:6577: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK115(re)001:6579: de ltar 'khrul dus nas sems kyi rang bzhin la nyams pa med pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:6581: srid gsum ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK115(re)001:6582: bdag tu rtog pa srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs kyis //
NK115(re)001:6583: yun ring dus nas 'khyams pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK115(re)001:6584: mi mthun bde sdug gnas rnams so sor bzung //
NK115(re)001:6585: log rtog goms pa'i dbang gis kun brtags kyang //
NK115(re)001:6586: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa rdul tsam med //
NK115(re)001:6588: de ltar gtan la phab pa'i don de la mnyam
NK115(re)001:6589: par 'jog pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:6590: ni so so skye bo'i sa la rjes dpag tsam
NK115(re)001:6591: yin pas / chos thams cad bsam du med pa'i
NK115(re)001:6592: de kho na nyid kyi gzugs brnyan tsam du snang
NK115(re)001:6593: ba'i ting nge 'dzin ltar gyur pa de bzhin nyid
NK115(re)001:6594: de'i gadngas kuna snang snying rje chen por shar ba'i
NK115(re)001:6595: 'phena pasa gdan gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa'i
NK115(re)001:6596: bskyed rima skyon med du shara ba ni theg pa
NK115(re)001:6597: chen po'i thabas kyi lam thams cad kyi nang nas
NK115(re)001:6598: mchoga tu gyur pa'i sngags kyi thabs ma nora ba
NK115(re)001:6599: yin pas / yin zhing / de ltar bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:6600: de ni mar ma dag 'khor ba'i dus na yang
NK115(re)001:6601: skye gnas gang du 'phen byed kyi las de sred
NK115(re)001:6602: len gyis gsos ma btab na mngal du 'jug mi
NK115(re)001:6603: nus pas sred len gyis gsos btab nas 'jug pa
NK115(re)001:6604: ltar snying rje'i 'phen pas gsos btab nas 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:6605: stong nyid kyi ngang las dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i skye
NK115(re)001:6606: ba 'dzin pas sbyang bya dang mthun /
NK115(re)001:6607: mthar thug 'bras bu'i gnas skabs na yang rtog pa
NK115(re)001:6608: bral ba'i thugs rje chen po chos sku'i ngang las
NK115(re)001:6609: gzugs skur bzhengs nas nam mkha' mthar khyab kyi 'gro
NK115(re)001:6610: don mdzad pa dang chos mthun no //
NK115(re)001:6611: 'di lta bu'i ting 'dzin gsum po yang lam nges
NK115(re)001:6612: rdzogs ltar bsgom na dang po dbang dang dam tshig
NK115(re)001:6613: la gnas pas shes bya lta ba'i de nyid ngo
NK115(re)001:6614: sprod dang / gtan tshigs la brten nas yid ches
NK115(re)001:6615: par byas te mthong ba'i rjes la 'jog pa dang
NK115(re)001:6616: sprod dang / / rig pa spyi blugs su 'jog
NK115(re)001:6617: pa'i bzhag thabs gnyis po gang rung gis sems ma
NK115(re)001:6618: bcos spros bral rang babs su lhod kyis glod pa
NK115(re)001:6619: dran rtog gi 'gyu ba'i spun thag bcad de bying
NK115(re)001:6620: rgod kyi skyon dang bral bar bzhag cing de nyid
NK115(re)001:6621: goms pas rlung sems dbu mar 'dus te rtags bcu'i
NK115(re)001:6622: mthong snang rdzogs shing rab kyis snang gsum la brten
NK115(re)001:6623: pa'i dpe'i ye shes kyang bskyed nus la /
NK115(re)001:6624: de ltar min kyang stong nyid spros pa dang bral
NK115(re)001:6625: ba'i go yul dang ldan pa'i sems gnas la brtan
NK115(re)001:6626: pa thob tshe med bzhin du snang ba'i 'khor ba
NK115(re)001:6627: la bltas nas 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying
NK115(re)001:6628: rje mkha' khyab tu bsgom pa la blo sbyang /
NK115(re)001:6629: de nyid goms pas stong nyid la blo bzhag tshe
NK115(re)001:6630: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can med snang 'khrul
NK115(re)001:6631: pas bslus pa la snying rje rtsol med du skye
NK115(re)001:6632: zhing / snying rje goms kyang bdag gzhan a 'thas
NK115(re)001:6633: su mi gol zhing rten 'byung sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:6634: snang ba las don du rang bzhin ma grub pa'i
NK115(re)001:6635: stong nyid kyi nges shes skyes pa na stong nyid
NK115(re)001:6636: snying rje'i snying po can zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:6637: de la goms par bya ba ni 'dir de ting
NK115(re)001:6638: dang kun snang gnyis ka'i don yin pas lam 'di
NK115(re)001:6639: gnyis re re dang bral bas kyang rdzogs pa'i byang
NK115(re)001:6640: chub bsgrub mi nus na gnyis ka dang bral bas
NK115(re)001:6643: snying rje dang bral stong pa nyid lta ba //
NK115(re)001:6644: des ni lam mchog rnyed pa ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:6645: gal te snying rje 'ba' zhig bsgom na yang //
NK115(re)001:6646: 'khor ba 'dir gnas thar pa yod dam ci //
NK115(re)001:6648: des na mos sgom du byed pa'i tshe na yang /
NK115(re)001:6649: thun thams cad kyi 'gor tshig tsam gyis chog shes
NK115(re)001:6650: mi bya bar cho ga'i yan lag rnams rdzogs pa
NK115(re)001:6651: dang blo lhod kyis glod la de ting dang kun
NK115(re)001:6652: snang la sems zin gyi bar du mnyam par bzhag
NK115(re)001:6653: / de nas rgyu ting sogs rim pa ltar bsgom
NK115(re)001:6654: zhing nyams len gyi gtso bo stong nyid snying rje
NK115(re)001:6655: gnyis dang ma bral ba'i bskyed rim ma brtan gyi
NK115(re)001:6656: bar du bzlas pa dang spro bsdu sogs la do
NK115(re)001:6657: / gal mi bya'o // de ltar mos sgom dang
NK115(re)001:6658: nges rdzogs gang ltar bsgom yang bskyed rim gyi skabs
NK115(re)001:6659: thams cad du ting 'dzin gsum ya ma bral bar
NK115(re)001:6660: bsgom pa las res 'jog lta bus mi 'thus la
NK115(re)001:6661: / gal mi bya'o // / de yang dper na
NK115(re)001:6662: rtsig ngor ri mo byed pa'i tshe rtsig pa ni
NK115(re)001:6663: gzhi yin pas de med na ri mo gang la
NK115(re)001:6664: / gal mi bya'o // / byed / rtsig pa
NK115(re)001:6665: yod kyang zhal ba med na rtsig ngor ri mo
NK115(re)001:6666: 'dri mi nus pas zhal ba ni ri mo dang
NK115(re)001:6667: rtsig pa lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen yin /
NK115(re)001:6668: ri mo bris zin pa'i gnas skabs na yang rtsig
NK115(re)001:6669: pa dang ri mo zhal ba dang bcas pa gsum
NK115(re)001:6670: po tshogs nas yod pa ltar rgyu ting las dkyil
NK115(re)001:6671: 'khor gyi 'khor lo rdzogs par bsgom pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:6672: na'ang stod nyid snying rje'i rtsal snang lhar shar bas
NK115(re)001:6673: gsum ga ya ma bral bar yod dgos te tha
NK115(re)001:6674: mal gyi snang ba stong pa nyid du ma dag
NK115(re)001:6675: na dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo gang du bsgom /
NK115(re)001:6676: des na chos thams cad stong pa nyid yin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6677: 'khor 'das dbyer med yin pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis sku
NK115(re)001:6678: gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgoms nas mngon du byed
NK115(re)001:6679: nus pa yin zhing stong nyid ni bskyed rim gyi
NK115(re)001:6680: gzhi yin te / gang la stong pa nyid rung ba //
NK115(re)001:6681: de la thams cad rung bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:6683: gal te chos thams cad stong pa nyid ma yin
NK115(re)001:6684: zhing tha mal gyi snang ba bden par grub na
NK115(re)001:6685: ni bskyed rim bsgom pa don med de /
NK115(re)001:6686: bra sran 'bras bu dbang bskur yang //
NK115(re)001:6687: de la 'bras kyi dngos snang med //
NK115(re)001:6689: de ltar chos thams cad stong pa nyid du shes kyang /
NK115(re)001:6690: snying rje chen po'i 'phen pa dang bral na ni
NK115(re)001:6691: gzhan don du gzugs kyi skur bzhengs mi nus te
NK115(re)001:6692: nyan rang 'gog par zhugs pa la gzugs sku'i 'gro
NK115(re)001:6693: don mdzad pa mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:6694: 'o na de gnyis kho na chog gi bskyed rim bsgoms pas ci bya snyam na /
NK115(re)001:6695: rten 'brel gyi snang cha sgyu ma lta bu 'di
NK115(re)001:6696: gdod ma nas rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK115(re)001:6697: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor dag pa myur du mngon
NK115(re)001:6698: du byed pa'i thabs gsang sngags kyi lam yin pas
NK115(re)001:6699: de gnyis kyis zin pa'i bskyed rim ni thabs rmad
NK115(re)001:6700: du byung ba'o // de ltar na stong nyid dang
NK115(re)001:6701: snying rje gnyis po ni theg pa chen po'i lam
NK115(re)001:6702: gyi gzhung shing yin pas mdo sngags gang gi lam
NK115(re)001:6703: nyams su len par byed na yang med du mi
NK115(re)001:6705: da lta snyigs dus kyi sngags lam pa phal cher
NK115(re)001:6706: gyis rgyu mtshan de lta bu mi shes par sngags
NK115(re)001:6707: kyi lam zhes stong nyid dang snying rje gang yang
NK115(re)001:6708: mi dgos par rang la gces par bzung nas lha
NK115(re)001:6709: bsgom pa dang / sngags bzla ba la sogs pas rang phyogs la phan pa bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6710: gzhan phyogs la sdang sems kyis mthu dang ngan sngags sogs byed cing /
NK115(re)001:6711: des rang nyid mchog tu rlom par byed pa de
NK115(re)001:6712: ni sngags log bdud kyi bstan pa yin pa la
NK115(re)001:6713: dgongs nas bla ma dam pa rnams kyis kyang khyad
NK115(re)001:6714: par sngags kyi gzhung rnams la bshad pa mdzad pa'i
NK115(re)001:6715: tshe na dngos gzhi bskyed rdzogs gnyis po bas /
NK115(re)001:6716: 'di gnyis rtsal du bton te nan cher yang yang
NK115(re)001:6717: gsungs 'dug pa ni kho bos kyang ma brjed par
NK115(re)001:6718: yod pa dang / bskyed rim gyi dka' 'grel sogs
NK115(re)001:6719: gsung chos rnams na'ang snang ba 'dir bris pa yin
NK115(re)001:6720: pas rang sde sngags su zhugs pa'i las dang po
NK115(re)001:6721: ba kun gyis thugs nyams su bzhes shig /
NK115(re)001:6722: de ltar de bzhin nyid bsgom pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:6723: snying rje bsgom pa sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:6724: de gnyis kyi ngang nas lha gang yang rung ba'i
NK115(re)001:6725: bskyed rim gyi rgyu'i sa bon bsgom pa dpa' bar
NK115(re)001:6726: 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin te ting 'dzin gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:6727: gzhi byas pa'i bskyed rim thams cad sgo gsum bya
NK115(re)001:6728: ba dang bcas pa de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:6729: gsang ba gsum phrin las dang bcas pa'i ngang du
NK115(re)001:6730: sdom par byed pa'i srog sdom gzer bzhi'i man ngag
NK115(re)001:6731: la brten te nyams su blang zhing dang po nyid
NK115(re)001:6732: nas bsnyen sgrub dang 'brel bar mos bsgom byed pa
NK115(re)001:6733: rnams kyang / byas pa'i chos la grub pa'i mtha'
NK115(re)001:6734: dgos zhes pa ltar blo tshod dang bstun pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:6735: tan ci rigs pa zhig rgyud la 'byung dgos pas
NK115(re)001:6736: rnams kyang / na / chos rje bla ma bka' drin can gyi gsung /
NK115(re)001:6738: go bde la chod che ba /
NK115(re)001:6739: byin rlabs che bas snang ba sgyur nus pa /
NK115(re)001:6740: dman pa tha shal ba bdag lta bus kyang dad
NK115(re)001:6741: pas bag phab ste mjal bar byas na dngos por
NK115(re)001:6742: zhen pa dang nyon mongs pas rtag tu gdung ba'ang
NK115(re)001:6743: re zhig thugs rjes byin gyis brlabs pa'i gsung gi
NK115(re)001:6744: bsil zer gyis ngal bso'i dbugs 'byin thob tu yod
NK115(re)001:6745: na skal ba dang ldan pa gzhan dag ni lta
NK115(re)001:6747: srog sdom gzer bzhi'i gnad nyung ngur dril ba'i man
NK115(re)001:6748: ngag skabs 'di dag tu dngos shugs gang yang rung
NK115(re)001:6749: bas phal cher dgod par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:6750: 'di ltar lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:6751: dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'am chos nyid kyi gzer dang por bshad kyang chog mod /
NK115(re)001:6752: sku gsung thugs phrin las bzhi'i dbang du na /
NK115(re)001:6753: lha sngags chos nyid phrin las kyi gzer rnam pa bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:6754: dang po ting 'dzin lha'i gzer ni /
NK115(re)001:6755: skye gnas bzhi gang rung gi bag chags sbyong ba
NK115(re)001:6756: dang 'brel bar phyi snod gzhal yas khang dang nang
NK115(re)001:6757: bcud lha dang lha mo rang lus lha sku sgyu
NK115(re)001:6758: ma lta bur gsal te snang cha nas dbus kyi
NK115(re)001:6759: gtso bo nas matha'i me ri'i bar thams cad so
NK115(re)001:6760: sor ma 'dres par na baza'i ri mo yan chad
NK115(re)001:6761: yongs su rdzogs par gsal yang snang dusa de nyid
NK115(re)001:6762: nasa ranga bzhina gyis ma gruba pa'i zung 'jug chen
NK115(re)001:6763: por lam gyis gsal btab la /
NK115(re)001:6764: ye shes lngas dbang bskur zhing sku gsung thugs kyis
NK115(re)001:6765: rgyas gdab pa sogs yan lag tshang bar byed pa
NK115(re)001:6766: yin te / de yang zhi ba yin na tshul dgu dang /
NK115(re)001:6767: khro bo yin na gar gyi nyams dgu dang ldan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:6769: sku dang zhal phyag sogs gyong khengs kyi rnam pa
NK115(re)001:6770: shing la sogs pa lta bu ma yin pas mnyen
NK115(re)001:6771: pa / phra sbom sogs rim par skabs phyed pas lcug pa /
NK115(re)001:6772: sku sha lhod por ma gyur pas 'khril bag chags pa /
NK115(re)001:6773: tshigs mtshams sogs 'phrul ldem dang ldan pas ldem pa /
NK115(re)001:6774: sku sha rgyas shing pags pa srab pas gzhon tshul can /
NK115(re)001:6775: kha dog ma 'dres pas gsal bas gsal ba /
NK115(re)001:6776: de dag kyang mu med pa'i 'od zer 'phro ba dang ldan pas 'tsher ba /
NK115(re)001:6777: sku skyes bu chen po'i mtshan dang ldan pa'i brjid bag gis mdzes pas lhun sdug pa /
NK115(re)001:6778: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi byin dang ldan pa ste dagu'o //
NK115(re)001:6782: rmongs nyams kyis mi sdug pa ste sku'i nyams gsum /
NK115(re)001:6783: bzhad pa'i gad mo 'byin pas dgod pa /
NK115(re)001:6784: bsdig pa'i nga ro sgrogs pas gshe ba /
NK115(re)001:6785: sgra gdangs che zhing bzod par dka' bas drag shul te gsung gi nyams gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:6786: rmongs pa'i 'gro khams rjes su 'dzin pa'i snying rje /
NK115(re)001:6787: ma rungs pa'i sems can khro bas 'dul ba'i rngam pa /
NK115(re)001:6788: thams cad chos nyid du ro mnyam pa'i zhi ba ste thugs kyi nyams gsum dang bcas dagu'o //
NK115(re)001:6789: de lta bu'i lha de rnams zhi ba la longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rgyan chas /
NK115(re)001:6793: dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs /
NK115(re)001:6794: tshigs gus smad dkris te dar gyi chas gos lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:6802: zhabs gdub ste rgyan brgyad dang bcas pa'i bcu gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:6803: sprul sku'i rnam pa can la chos gos rnam pa gsum la sogs pas brgyan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6804: khro bo rnams la bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK115(re)001:6806: byugs pa'i rtsi gsum ste dur khrod kyi chas brgyad du grags pa la sogs pas brgyan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:6807: de yang dang po gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:6810: stag lpags kyi sham thabs rnams so //
NK115(re)001:6812: thod pa sbrul gyi rgyan gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:6813: thod pa skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan /
NK115(re)001:6814: rnyid pa'i se ral kha zhes pa'ang 'ga' zhig na snang /
NK115(re)001:6815: rlon pa khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu'i do shal /
NK115(re)001:6817: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu sogs so //
NK115(re)001:6818: klu rgyal rigs dkar po'i skra ching /
NK115(re)001:6819: rje rigs ser po'i snyan cha /
NK115(re)001:6820: bram ze'i rigs dmar po'i mgul chu /
NK115(re)001:6821: dmangs rigs ljang gu'i phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu /
NK115(re)001:6822: gdol pa'i rigs nag po'i do shal te thams cad gdug pa sbrul gyi rnam pa can no //
NK115(re)001:6826: zhag gi zo ris rnams so //
NK115(re)001:6827: gzhan yang gzhal yas khang gi steng rgyan dang logs
NK115(re)001:6828: rgyan la sogs pa'i bkod pa'i rnam pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:6829: dang bcas pa gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan
NK115(re)001:6831: de la gsal ba'i tshad bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:6832: spyan gyi dkar nag tshun chad ma 'dres par gsal bas sal le /
NK115(re)001:6833: rig pa'i gsal ngar dang bral ba'i bying nyams can
NK115(re)001:6834: ma yin par gsal stong seng bag dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:6835: rig pa'i ngar dang ldan pas seng nge /
NK115(re)001:6836: sems med bem po'i rnam pa 'ja' tshon lta bu
NK115(re)001:6837: ma yin par ba spu'i khong bu dang dbu skra'i
NK115(re)001:6838: nyag ma tshun chad rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK115(re)001:6839: ye shes kyis zin pas dbang shes dwangs pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:6840: tan brgya phrag tu 'char zhing bkra hrig ger bzhugs
NK115(re)001:6841: pas lhag ge // de lta bu'i lha sku de
NK115(re)001:6842: yang de ltar yin no dang yod do tsam gyi
NK115(re)001:6843: rjes dpag gi blo rtog ma yin par yid ngor
NK115(re)001:6844: mngon sum lta bur 'char bas lhang nge ba ste
NK115(re)001:6845: pas lhag ge // bzhi'o // brtan pa'i tshad bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:6846: le lo dang brjed nges sogs kyis mi g.yo /
NK115(re)001:6847: rab rib dang mog mog por gyur pa sogs kyis mi 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:6848: yun ring du mnyam par bzhag kyang rnam rtog phra mos kyang mi barji bas mngon par mi 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:6849: sku mdog dang zhal phyag dang /
NK115(re)001:6850: byon bzhugs dang 'od zer gyi spro bsdu sogs ji ltar bsgom yang de ltar 'byung ba ste bzhi'o //
NK115(re)001:6851: de dag la rnam pa gsal ba zhes kyang bshad do //
NK115(re)001:6852: de ltar yang yang goms pas nyams lnga mthar phyin
NK115(re)001:6853: te yul gsum gyad du gyur pa na grub pa
NK115(re)001:6854: yin no // de la yul gsum gyad du gyur pa gang zhe na /
NK115(re)001:6856: ye shes lha yi phyag rgya kun //
NK115(re)001:6857: dang po yid kyi yul du gsal //
NK115(re)001:6858: sems nyid shin tu sbyangs pa'i mthar //
NK115(re)001:6859: rang bzhin dbang po'i yul du gsal //
NK115(re)001:6860: mthar ni bden gnyis dbyer med kyi //
NK115(re)001:6861: lus sems shin sbyang thob pa'i lha //
NK115(re)001:6862: lus kyi yul du mngon sum gsal //
NK115(re)001:6864: dang po lhar snang la goms pa ma skyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:6865: gnas skabs na bsam pa'i blo rtog gam yid kyis
NK115(re)001:6866: brjod pa tsam gyis bdag lha yin no lha yang
NK115(re)001:6867: de dang de lta bu yin no snyam du rtog
NK115(re)001:6868: dpyod kyi blo ngor gsal bas na bsam pa'i yul
NK115(re)001:6869: du gsal ba'am yid kyi yul du gsal ba zhes
NK115(re)001:6870: bya / de ltar goms pas lhar snang la brtan
NK115(re)001:6871: pa thob nas 'di ltar yin no ba'i rtog dpyod
NK115(re)001:6872: kyi rgyas gdab mi dgos par mig gi dbang po
NK115(re)001:6873: skyon med kyi yul la bltas pa ltar rtog med
NK115(re)001:6874: gzhi gnas kyi rtsi dang ma bral ba'i ngang nas
NK115(re)001:6875: ma 'dres par gsal ba ni mthong ba'i yul du
NK115(re)001:6876: gsal ba'am dbang po'i yul du gsal ba zhes bya'o
NK115(re)001:6877: bya / // mthar bskyed rim gyad du gyur te
NK115(re)001:6878: rnam smin rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'i dus su snang
NK115(re)001:6879: cha lha'i dkyil 'khor dang 'dres nas rang ngor tha
NK115(re)001:6880: mal ma dag pa'i snang ba gtan du mi 'char
NK115(re)001:6881: zhing sgyu lus sam zung 'jug gi lha sku mngon
NK115(re)001:6882: du gyur pa'i gnas skabs ni lus kyi yul du
NK115(re)001:6883: gsal ba'am reg pa'i yul du gsal ba zhes bya'o
NK115(re)001:6884: bya / // // de ltar dang po yid kyi
NK115(re)001:6885: yul du gsal ba'i gnas skabs na rnam dag dran
NK115(re)001:6886: bya / // // pa ni / rten zhing khams
NK115(re)001:6887: dang gzhal yas khang rnams bem po rang rgyud pa
NK115(re)001:6889: pa lha rnams gang zag rang rgyud par mi blta
NK115(re)001:6891: / thams cad ye shes nyag gcig gi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:6892: mtshan ma rtags kyi phyag rgyar shar ba'i tshul la
NK115(re)001:6893: blta bar bya ba ni gzhal yas khang gi 'og
NK115(re)001:6894: gzhi'i 'khor lo ye shes lngas nyon mongs pa gcod
NK115(re)001:6895: pa'i rtags su shar ba nas rdo rje rin po
NK115(re)001:6896: che'i tog gi bar gyi dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6897: nang gi lha gtso bo zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi lta bu la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:6898: rnam thar sgo gsum mam sku gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:6899: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug gam pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
NK115(re)001:6900: tshad med pa bzhi'am rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi
NK115(re)001:6901: rnams kyi rtags su shar ba sogs nas gtso 'khor
NK115(re)001:6902: thams cad kyi zhal phyag dang bzhugs tshul /
NK115(re)001:6903: rgyan dang cha lugs la sogs pa'i dag pa dran pa'o //
NK115(re)001:6905: bskyed pa'i lha gang yin yang bdag lha min gyi
NK115(re)001:6906: bdag gis lha de bsgom pa yin no snyam pa
NK115(re)001:6907: dang / lha de dngos ma yin gyi lha de'i
NK115(re)001:6908: rnam pa tsam zhig bdag gi yid yul du byas
NK115(re)001:6909: pa yin no snyam pa lta bu ma yin par
NK115(re)001:6910: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid
NK115(re)001:6911: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes dang
NK115(re)001:6912: ro gcig pa de ye nas chos nyid don gyi
NK115(re)001:6913: lha yin zhing de'i rang rtsal 'gag pa med pa
NK115(re)001:6914: rten dang brten pa'i 'khor lor shar ba yin snyam
NK115(re)001:6915: pa'i ngang la dran pa nye bar 'jog pa'o //
NK115(re)001:6916: rnam dag dran pa dang nga rgyal brtan pa 'di
NK115(re)001:6917: gnyis bskyed rim shin tu brtan par gyur pa na
NK115(re)001:6918: rtog dpyod kyis ched du bsam mi dgos par mngon
NK115(re)001:6919: no // de ltar ting 'dzin lha'i gzer des ni
NK115(re)001:6920: mar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na skye gnas bzhi'i lus
NK115(re)001:6921: kyi bag chags sbyong zhing dag par byed /
NK115(re)001:6922: yar sangs rgyas kyi gnas skabs na sku'i gsang ba
NK115(re)001:6923: bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhal phyag mtshan ma las
NK115(re)001:6924: 'das pa dang / sku rnam pa thams cad pa
NK115(re)001:6925: gang la gang 'dul du snang ba'i 'bras bu gzhi
NK115(re)001:6926: 'das pa dang / la rdzogs / bar lam gyi
NK115(re)001:6927: gnas skabs na rtsa yi d+r+wa ba thams cad dag
NK115(re)001:6928: pa lha ru sbyangs pas rdo rje'i lus la gnad
NK115(re)001:6929: du bsnun pa'i rdzogs rim gyi smin byed du 'gro
NK115(re)001:6930: 'das pa dang / la rdzogs / ba yin no // gnyis pa snying po sngags kyi gzer ni /
NK115(re)001:6931: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung gi gsang
NK115(re)001:6932: ba zaba mo snying po sngags kyi bzlas pa la
NK115(re)001:6933: brten nas sgra ru grag pa thams cad sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:6934: rang bzhin du snang zhing snanga ba'i dus nyid nas
NK115(re)001:6935: brjod bral stong pa'i gshis su grol bar byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:6937: de ni lha tshogs thams cad kyi thugs kar rang
NK115(re)001:6938: 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs
NK115(re)001:6939: pa re re'i thugs kar ting 'dzin sems dpa'i thugs
NK115(re)001:6940: srog yi ge'i rnam par gnas pa'i mtha' skor du
NK115(re)001:6941: mdun nas brtsams te sngags phreng gis bskor ba la
NK115(re)001:6942: sems rtse gcig tu gtad de ngag bzlas grangs dus
NK115(re)001:6944: khyad par 'byin 'jug gnas gsum sngags su shes pas
NK115(re)001:6945: rdo rje'i bzlas pa la brtson par byed pa yin
NK115(re)001:6946: te / des ni mar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na
NK115(re)001:6947: brjod pa sgra'i rang bzhin 'gro ba'i ngag gi bag
NK115(re)001:6949: yar dag pa sangs rgyas kyi dus na gsung gi
NK115(re)001:6950: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa sgra tshig brjod
NK115(re)001:6952: gsung rnam pa thams cad pa theg pa bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:6953: mi khyab par 'char ba'i 'bras bu gzhi la rdzogs
NK115(re)001:6954: / bar du lam nyams su len pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:6955: na ngag rlung gi rang bzhin snying po sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:6956: rol par sbyangs pas rlung la brten pa'i rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:6957: thams cad kyi smin byed du 'gro ba yin no
NK115(re)001:6958: / // gsum pa dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'i gzer ni /
NK115(re)001:6959: thabas kyi cha snang grag thams cad lha dang sngags
NK115(re)001:6960: kyi rang bzhin du gsal ba de'ang shesa rab khyad
NK115(re)001:6961: par can chos nyid kyi lta ba'i rtsis zin pa
NK115(re)001:6962: la bya ste / de ltar snang grags snod bcud
NK115(re)001:6963: thams cad lha sngags gzhal yas su lhun gyis grub
NK115(re)001:6964: par gsal ba de yang 'dus byas blos sprul gyi
NK115(re)001:6965: bkod pa min par don dam pa'i chos nyid dag
NK115(re)001:6966: mnyam stong pa chen po'i rang rtsal snang srid bzhir
NK115(re)001:6967: bzhengs kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas pa la bdag gzhan
NK115(re)001:6968: la bya ste / dang dam ye / bsgrub bya dang sgrub byed /
NK115(re)001:6969: dag pa dang ma dag pa la sogs pa'i gnyis
NK115(re)001:6970: chos su 'dzin pa cung zad kyang med par gnyis
NK115(re)001:6971: med mnyam pa chen po'i klong du 'khor 'das ye
NK115(re)001:6972: sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor na bdag dang lha zhes
NK115(re)001:6973: tha dad du 'dzin pa med de /
NK115(re)001:6974: bdag gi chos nyid rnam par dag pa lha'i rang
NK115(re)001:6975: bzhin du dbyer med par gnas pa'i don mnyam nyid
NK115(re)001:6976: rdo rje'i dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa ste
NK115(re)001:6977: 'di'i tshul tshigs su bcad de gsungs pa /
NK115(re)001:6978: gang gi rang bzhin gnyis med bde ba che //
NK115(re)001:6979: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' lta bu'i klong //
NK115(re)001:6980: nam mkhas mi mtshon mtshon pa tha snyad tsam //
NK115(re)001:6981: don 'di rtogs na 'khor 'das gnyis med de //
NK115(re)001:6982: ye nas sangs rgyas srid pa ming tsam lus //
NK115(re)001:6983: skye med klong na rgyal kun thugs rdo rje //
NK115(re)001:6984: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid dbyings dag pa //
NK115(re)001:6985: snang ba lha yin lha las snang mi dmigs //
NK115(re)001:6986: grag pa sngags yin sngags las sgra med do //
NK115(re)001:6987: lha sngags ma grub dag mnyam chos sku'i ngang //
NK115(re)001:6988: bdag dang gzhan du 'dzin pa yod min te //
NK115(re)001:6989: stong dang mi stong 'di la ci zhig yod //
NK115(re)001:6990: blo las 'das so theg pa'i rgyal po'i lam //
NK115(re)001:6991: 'di dang rnam pa kun tu 'bral mi bya //
NK115(re)001:6992: 'di 'bral bskyed pa'i lha de 'ching ba'i rgyu //
NK115(re)001:6994: 'dis mar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na sems kyi bag chags gsal tsam pa'i ngo bor gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:6995: de las 'phros pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad dag par byed /
NK115(re)001:6996: yar sangs rgyas kyi dus na thugs kyi gsang ba
NK115(re)001:6997: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dmigs bsam spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:6998: bral ba'i chos nyid dang thugs rnam pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:6999: pa mngon shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:7000: gzhi la rdzogs / bar lam nyams su len pa'i
NK115(re)001:7001: gnas skabs na snang stong gnyis su med pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:7002: nyid la goms pas kun rdzob dang don dam byang
NK115(re)001:7003: chub kyi sems la brten pa'i bde gsal stong pa
NK115(re)001:7004: nyid kyi rdzogs rim bsgom pa'i smin byed du 'gro
NK115(re)001:7005: gzhi la rdzogs / ba yin no // bzhi pa 'phro 'du phrin las kyi gzer ni /
NK115(re)001:7006: lha sngags chos nyid gsum po de dang 'brela ba'i
