NK115(re)001:7007: sgo nas mchog thun gyi phrin las sgrub pa'i bye
NK115(re)001:7009: snod bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba thams cad
NK115(re)001:7010: thugs chos nyid kyi dgongs pa las g.yo 'gul med
NK115(re)001:7011: pa / gsung snying po sngags kyi sgra gdangs gzhom med yan lag drug cu'i dbyings su bsgyur zhing /
NK115(re)001:7012: sku zhi ba tshul dgu dang khro bo gar dgu'i rnam rol du bzhugs pa'i sku'i cha dang /
NK115(re)001:7013: thugs ka'i sngags phreng las 'od dang 'od zer gyi phung po dkar la 'tsher ba /
NK115(re)001:7017: mthing la gsal ba dpag tu med pa 'phros /
NK115(re)001:7018: dus gsum dang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas
NK115(re)001:7019: pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i rnam par gnas pa
NK115(re)001:7020: la mchod bya dang mchod byed tha dad du med
NK115(re)001:7021: pa 'phrul dag'i rnam rol du mchod pas bde stong
NK115(re)001:7022: ye shes chen po'i ros tshim /
NK115(re)001:7023: rang snang ye shes kyi snang char 'khor ba ming tsam yang mi dmigs kyang /
NK115(re)001:7024: gzhan snang sems kyi snang bar yul don lus su
NK115(re)001:7025: a 'thas pa'i med snang sgyu ma'i 'gro khams rigs
NK115(re)001:7026: drug gi gnas ris bsam gyis mi khyab pa ji
NK115(re)001:7027: snyed yod pa kun tu thabs la mkhas pa'i 'od
NK115(re)001:7028: zer des reg pas 'khrul 'dzin ma rig pa'i cha
NK115(re)001:7029: thams cad skad cig la sangs te /
NK115(re)001:7032: yid thams cad chos sku'i dgongs pa 'pho 'gyur med
NK115(re)001:7033: par sangs rgyas pa ste srid pa zhes bya ba'i
NK115(re)001:7034: ming yang med par shes pa ni mchog gi dngos
NK115(re)001:7035: grub gtso bor byed pa don gnyis lhun gyis grub
NK115(re)001:7037: yang 'od zer de dag gi byed pa gnas skabs su dkar pos zhi ba /
NK115(re)001:7040: ljang gus drag po'i phrin las sgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7041: dmigs pa'i spro bsdu dang phrin las kyi mde kha
NK115(re)001:7042: bsgyur bas thun mong gi grub pa brgyad la sogs
NK115(re)001:7043: pa bsgrub pa ste 'dis mar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:7044: na lus ngag yid kyi bya ba'i cha thams cad
NK115(re)001:7045: sbyong zhing dag / yar dag pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK115(re)001:7046: gnas skabs na sku gsung thugs rnam pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:7047: pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:7048: sbyong zhing dag / gzhi la rdzogs / bar lam
NK115(re)001:7049: nyams su len pa'i gnas skabs na don gnyis lhun
NK115(re)001:7051: byed rtsol dag pa'i lam la bslabs pas rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:7052: gyi gnas skabs na lus ngag yid kyi byed las
NK115(re)001:7053: la ltos pa'i dmigs bcas thun mong gi lam dang
NK115(re)001:7054: / dmigs med ye shes kyi dgongs pa mngon sum
NK115(re)001:7055: 'od gsal gyi rnal 'byor snang srid 'od skur sbyong
NK115(re)001:7056: ba'i smin byed du 'gro ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:7058: tha dad ma yin gzhi lam 'bras //
NK115(re)001:7059: zung du 'jug pa sangs rgyas lam //
NK115(re)001:7060: dang po nyid nas du mar med //
NK115(re)001:7061: ro gcig nyid du 'bras bu rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:7063: lta ba dgongs pa mi 'gyur gzhi ste sgom pa lam //
NK115(re)001:7064: lha dang sngags yin spyod pa shugs yin te //
NK115(re)001:7065: phrin las mchog thun 'bras bu gang gnas pa //
NK115(re)001:7066: dang po nyid nas zung 'jug lam zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:7068: 'di ltar dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'i gzer ni lta ba yin pas na gzhi /
NK115(re)001:7069: ting 'dzin lha'i gzer ni sgom pa /
NK115(re)001:7070: snying po sngags kyi gzer ni sgom pa yang yin
NK115(re)001:7071: la shugs kyis spyod pa yin pas de gnyis lam
NK115(re)001:7072: / 'phro 'du dmigs pa'i gzer ni mchog thun gyi
NK115(re)001:7073: dngos grub sgrub cing sangs rgyas kyi phrin las da
NK115(re)001:7074: lta nas byed pa'i 'bras bu yin te /
NK115(re)001:7075: de ltar srog sdom gzer bzhi'am /
NK115(re)001:7077: gzhi lam 'bras bu gang yin pa de dag kyang
NK115(re)001:7078: tha dad dam ya bral lam res 'jog can nam
NK115(re)001:7079: rim pa can du mi blta ste /
NK115(re)001:7080: dang po nyid nas gcig dang du ma med par dbyer med zung 'jug tu shes dgos te /
NK115(re)001:7081: 'di ltar dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba chos nyid dag
NK115(re)001:7082: mnyam chen po'i dbyings su ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK115(re)001:7083: rang rtsal kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:7084: du rang shar ba'i bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:7085: ngang nas grag stong sngags kyi rang sgra cir yang
NK115(re)001:7086: bsgyur zhing 'phro 'du phrin las kyi rol pa la
NK115(re)001:7087: slob ste / sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku gsung thugs
NK115(re)001:7088: ye shes chen po byed rtsol spros pa dang bral
NK115(re)001:7089: bzhin don gnyis lhun gyis grub par bzhugs pa'i 'bras
NK115(re)001:7090: bu da lta nas lam du byed pa'i rdo rje'i
NK115(re)001:7091: theg pa'am 'bras bu'i theg pa zhes smos pa yin
NK115(re)001:7092: slob ste / la / de yang gzhi lta ba
NK115(re)001:7093: ye shes kyi 'khor lo 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du
NK115(re)001:7094: rtogs pas srid zhi gnyis ka'i srog la dbang bsgyur
NK115(re)001:7095: slob ste / la / / lam bsgom pa lha
NK115(re)001:7096: sngags kyi 'khor lo thabs shes zung du 'jug pas
NK115(re)001:7097: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i srog la rang dbang /
NK115(re)001:7098: 'bras bu rtsol med chos nyid kyi 'khor lo don
NK115(re)001:7099: gnyis lhun grub kyi spyod pas thabs chen bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:7100: mi khyab pa'i srog la rang dbang ba ste /
NK115(re)001:7101: dper na sgra gcan gyi khas nam mkha'i zla ba
NK115(re)001:7102: bzung bas chu nang gi zla ba ji snyed pa
NK115(re)001:7103: thams cad rang zin pa ltar srog sdom gzer bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:7104: man ngag gcig shes pas mdo rgyud bsam gyis mi
NK115(re)001:7105: khyab pa'i dgongs gnad dus gcig la nyams su longs
NK115(re)001:7106: pas na re re'ang gnad kyi khyad par du ma
NK115(re)001:7108: dang po dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'i gzer gyis /
NK115(re)001:7109: 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du shes pas spang blang gzhi las dag pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7110: ro mnyam stong pa nyid du shes pas dngos 'dzin bden zhen 'jig pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7111: snang stong zung 'jug tu shes pas tshogs gnyis mnyam du rdzogs pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7112: lta ba'i rtsis zin pas bskyed rdzogs ya bral du mi 'gyur ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7113: dgongs pa'i ngang las mi g.yo bas lta thog tu sgom pa 'khyol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7114: gya nom lhar zhen las grol bas bskyed rim gyi gol sa spong ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7115: snang srid gzhir bzhengs su rdzogs pas bdag gzhan gyi gnyis 'dzin med pa'i gnad //
NK115(re)001:7116: ye grol gzhi rdzogs su rtogs pas dug lnga'i gol sa med pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7117: chos sku'i dgongs pa brnyes pas sku gsum rang la rdzogs pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7118: gzhi 'bras ro gcig tu shes pas lam gyi rtsol sgrub mi dgos pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7119: sgom pa 'bras bur 'khyol bas sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7120: 'bras bu gzhi la 'khyil bas thob bya'i zhen 'dzin grol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7121: chos nyid klong du gcig pas dam ye'i 'dzin pa dag pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7122: rigs brgya'i khyab bdag rtogs pas lha gcig bsgrubs pas thams cad 'grub pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7123: mchog gi dngos grub brnyes pas don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7124: bzang ngan spang blang las 'das pas gtsang sbra'i kun spyod la ma ltos pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7125: byar med ye zin du shes pas cho ga'i khrigs rim mi dgos pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7126: grub matha'i 'dzin pa dag pas theg pa'i rtse mor
NK115(re)001:7127: phyin pa'i gnad de gnad chen po bco brgyad dang
NK115(re)001:7128: da dung yang du ma dang ldan pas 'di ni
NK115(re)001:7129: srog gi srog ste srog gzhan gsum gyi srog kyang
NK115(re)001:7130: 'dis sdom pas med thabs med pa nyid du dang
NK115(re)001:7131: por bzhag la / gnyis pa bskyed rim lha'i gzer gyis /
NK115(re)001:7132: snang cha lha ru gsal bas stong pa phyogs gcig tu mi gol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7133: kun rdzob lam du byed pas bden gnyis zung du 'jug pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7134: dngos po'i a 'thas sbyor bas tha mal gyi bden zhen spong ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7135: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs pas bsod nams kyi tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7136: sku'i rnam pa gsal bas gzugs sku'i nye rgyur gyur pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7137: 'bras bu'i bzhugs tshul dang mthun pas sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i gnad de drug dang /
NK115(re)001:7138: gsum pa snying po sngags kyi gzer la'ang /
NK115(re)001:7139: gsung rdo rje lam du byed pas ngag gi sgrib pa sbyong ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7140: sems dpa' sum brtsegs su bsgoms pas sgo gsum mnyam du grol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7141: dmigs pa sngags phreng la gtad pas tha mal gyi rtog pa spong ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7142: zla ba skar phreng ltar bzlas pas rang babs kyi ting 'dzin la gnas pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7143: mgal me'i 'khor lo ltar bzlas pas bde stong gi ye shes bskyed pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7144: bung ba tshang zhig ltar bzlas pas sgra grag sngags su grol ba'i gnad //
NK115(re)001:7145: snying po'i srog nas bgrangs pas lha'i byin gyis rlobs pa'i gnad //
NK115(re)001:7146: ngag gi nus pa 'phel bas ci smras gzhan don du 'gyur ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7147: rig sngags kyi bden tshig grub pas smon lam gang btab 'grub pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7148: rgyal ba'i gsung la dbang bas snang srid lha 'dres bka' bzhin sgrub pa'i gnad de bcu dang /
NK115(re)001:7149: bzhi pa 'phro 'du phrin las kyi gzer gyis mchog
NK115(re)001:7150: gi dngos grub 'grub pas thun mong shugs kyis 'byung
NK115(re)001:7151: ba'i gnad / dmigs pa'i mde kha bsgyur bas las tshogs gzhan la mi ltos pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7152: phrin las mtha' ru phyin pas gzhan don 'bad med du 'byung ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7153: 'gro don lhun gyis grub pas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa 'grub pa'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7154: sems bskyed kyi 'phen pas 'phangs pas theg pa dman par mi gol ba'i gnad /
NK115(re)001:7155: gdul bya smin cing grol bas gdung brgyud 'dzin pa'i gnad de drug dang ldan pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:7156: de ltar rtsa ba bzhi la gnad kyi khyad chos bzhi bcu dang ldan pas na /
NK115(re)001:7157: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i lam gnad ma lus pa 'dir 'du zhing /
NK115(re)001:7158: 'di dang mi ldan pa'i lam ni shi ba'i ro
NK115(re)001:7159: dang 'dra bar nges pas na srog sdom gzer bzhi
NK115(re)001:7160: zhes bya ste / gnyis 'dzin gyi cha thams cad
NK115(re)001:7161: gnyis med ye shes chen por gcig tu sdom pa'i
NK115(re)001:7163: des na de lta bu'i srog sdom gzer bzhi'i man
NK115(re)001:7164: ngag dang ldan pa'i bskyed rim ni sngags kyi lam
NK115(re)001:7165: rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:7166: de lasa ldog ste sbyang gzhi sbyong byed kyi rten
NK115(re)001:7167: 'brel mi shes shing man ngag dang mi ldan pas
NK115(re)001:7168: zhen med kyi lta ba dang snying rje'i sems dang
NK115(re)001:7169: mi ldan pa ni theg pa chen po dang 'agla
NK115(re)001:7170: ba'i phyir gsang sngags kyi lam min par ma zad
NK115(re)001:7171: rnam grol gyi lam tsam du'ang 'gyur dka' bas de
NK115(re)001:7172: 'dra ba'i lam snang phyogs kyi dmigas pa la zhen
NK115(re)001:7173: pa dang bacasa pa'i bskyed rima ni mu stegsa byed
NK115(re)001:7174: dag la'ang yod de rang rang gis 'dod pa'i lha
NK115(re)001:7175: bsgrub cing 'grub pas rang phyogs la gnas skabs kyi
NK115(re)001:7176: phan pa sgrub pa dang gzhan phyogs la gnod pa
NK115(re)001:7177: skyel ba du ma yod par bshad pa'i phyir dang
NK115(re)001:7178: / yang zhi ba'i lha'i rnam pa la goms kyang
NK115(re)001:7179: zhen par gyur na gzugs khams su gol bar bshad
NK115(re)001:7180: / pa dang / yang bsgom zhing bsgrub rgyu de
NK115(re)001:7181: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lha dpal chen po lta
NK115(re)001:7182: bu zhig yin yang bsgrub tshul snying rje byang chub
NK115(re)001:7183: kyi sems dang ma 'brel bar lha rang rgyud par
NK115(re)001:7184: bzung nas lha snang goms pa dang drag sngags bzla
NK115(re)001:7185: ba sogs gzhan la gnod pa'i bsam sbyor dang bcas
NK115(re)001:7187: gdona gyi rigas mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags mthu
NK115(re)001:7188: bo che gzhan gyi srog lus la 'tshe bar byed
NK115(re)001:7189: pa dag tu 'gyur zhing de'i tshe na'nga de sngags
NK115(re)001:7190: pa nus ldan rnams kyis snying rje ma gtogs bskyed
NK115(re)001:7191: rim dang drag las sogs kyis 'dul mi nus par
NK115(re)001:7192: kho rang yang de 'dra ba'i drag po'i nga rgyal
NK115(re)001:7193: gyi gnas thub pa yoda par bshad pas te /
NK115(re)001:7195: dgongs pa mi 'gyur gzer med na //
NK115(re)001:7196: dpal chen 'grub kyang thun mong las //
NK115(re)001:7197: mchog mi 'grub cing r+au trar gol //
NK115(re)001:7199: des na stong nyid kyi go yul yod pa /
NK115(re)001:7200: bskyed rim gyi gsal snang thon pa /
NK115(re)001:7201: bzlas pa'i grangs 'khyol ba du ma rgyal 'gong du skyes pa ni yod la /
NK115(re)001:7202: snying rje chen po'i rtsi dang ma bral ba'i gdug 'dre ni gang na'ang yod par ma thos so //
NK115(re)001:7203: bzhi pa sa lam bgrod tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:7204: de la theg pa chen po'i rigs can gyi gang
NK115(re)001:7205: zag rnam pa gnyis te dbang rtul sngags kyi lta
NK115(re)001:7206: spyod zab mo la dang po nas 'jug mi nus
NK115(re)001:7207: pa dang / dbang rnon dang po nas 'jug nus pa gnyis yod la /
NK115(re)001:7208: de'ang dbang rtul sngags la 'jug pa'i mtshams kyang gzhung
NK115(re)001:7209: 'di'i dgongs pa ni tshogs lam chen po nas yin
NK115(re)001:7210: par bshad zin pa ltar la /
NK115(re)001:7211: snga 'gyur ba 'ga' zhig gis 'phags lam nas nges
NK115(re)001:7212: par 'jug par bshad pas de'i lugs ltar na de
NK115(re)001:7213: gnyis ka'i rgyud la mthong lam gyi ye shes ma
NK115(re)001:7214: skyes kyi bar du mdo sngags so so'i lam gyis
NK115(re)001:7215: rang rang gi rigs kyi nus pa gsos nas lam
NK115(re)001:7216: sbyangs pa las / nam zhig mthong lam thob pa
NK115(re)001:7217: na de gnyis kyi rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK115(re)001:7218: bo la khyad par med par gsungs pas na sngagas
NK115(re)001:7219: su zhugs pa'i gang zag de'i /
NK115(re)001:7220: byanga chuba semsa dpa'i lam mtshan nyid theg pa las
NK115(re)001:7221: bshad pa'i mthonga lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:7222: shes de la phyag rgya chena po mchoga gi dngosa
NK115(re)001:7223: gruba cesa bya bar gsar rnying gi rgyud thams cad
NK115(re)001:7224: du shina tu gragas pa de nyid myur du mngona
NK115(re)001:7225: du byeda pa'i thabas gsang sngags kyi lam ni thabs
NK115(re)001:7226: phyogs re ba tsam yang ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:7227: spang gnyen gnyis su byed pa'i dka' thub kyis yun
NK115(re)001:7228: ring por gdung yang mi dgos par thabs shes khyad
NK115(re)001:7229: par can gyi sgo nas tshogs gnyis myur du rdzogs
NK115(re)001:7230: par 'gyur te / de yang lhag pa'i lha'i bskyed rim gang bsgom yang /
NK115(re)001:7231: pho brang rnam par snang mdzad /
NK115(re)001:7236: bdud rtsi myong ba 'od dpag med de yan lag drug rdzogs su bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7237: bskyed rim rgyas pa gnyis la phyag rgya bzhis bcing ba dang /
NK115(re)001:7238: dbang bskur ba dang rgyas gdab pa gsum las /
NK115(re)001:7239: dang po ni phyag rgya bzhis ye shes pa dgug
NK115(re)001:7240: cing dam tshig par gzhug la dbyer med du byas
NK115(re)001:7241: nas dgyes pa bskyed pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7242: 'di la sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin nam snyoms 'jug gi tha snyad kyang thob la /
NK115(re)001:7243: 'khor gyi lha rnams rdzogs par bskyed pa la dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog dang /
NK115(re)001:7244: mchod bstod phrin las la sogs pa la las rgyal
NK115(re)001:7245: mchog ste ting nge 'dzin gsum du bshad cing sku
NK115(re)001:7246: gsum lam du byed par gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7248: dbang lha spyan drangs nas dbang bzhi ka bskur bar bshad pa'ang yod la /
NK115(re)001:7249: phal cher byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang
NK115(re)001:7250: bskur nas bag chags 'khrud pa la sogs pa byed
NK115(re)001:7251: do // gsum pa ni rigs bdag gis rgyas 'debs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7252: 'di ni rdo rje theg pa'i gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi mtshon don te /
NK115(re)001:7253: de la thugs rigs kyis rigs gzhan bzhi la rgyas
NK115(re)001:7254: 'debs pa ni phung po gzhan bzhi sems kyi rang
NK115(re)001:7255: bzhin du shes pa'i don de rang bzhin la rang
NK115(re)001:7256: bzhin gyi rgya zhes kyang bya'o //
NK115(re)001:7257: dbye na gtso bo yab yum rang sems su shes
NK115(re)001:7258: pa la yid kyi ngo bo mi bskyod pas rgyas
NK115(re)001:7259: 'debs pa ni ngo bo la ngo bo nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:7260: rgya dang / lus kyi ngo bo rnam snang la
NK115(re)001:7261: sems rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pas
NK115(re)001:7262: rgyas 'debs pa lus la sems kyi rgya dang /
NK115(re)001:7263: yid dag pa mi bskyod pa la lus dag pa
NK115(re)001:7264: rnam snang gis rgyas 'debs pa sems la lus kyi
NK115(re)001:7265: rgya dang / rgyu 'dod chags dag pa 'od dpag
NK115(re)001:7266: med la 'bras bu ser sna dag pa'i rin 'byung
NK115(re)001:7267: gis rgyas 'debs pa rgyu la 'bras bu'i rgya dang
NK115(re)001:7268: rgya dang / / 'bras bu phrag dog dag pa
NK115(re)001:7269: don grub la rgyu 'dod chags dag pa snang mthas
NK115(re)001:7270: rgyas 'debs pa 'bras bu la rgyu'i rgya'o //
NK115(re)001:7271: tshul de rnams ni snang shes dang /
NK115(re)001:7273: rgyu 'bras dag la so sor zhen pa sbyong ba'i
NK115(re)001:7274: phyir gtso bor bstan te des mtshon na rin 'byung
NK115(re)001:7275: la'ang rgyas 'debs tshul yod par sems so //
NK115(re)001:7276: spyir ma dag pa'i phung sogs lhar bsgom pa kun brtags la gzhan dbang gi rgya dang /
NK115(re)001:7277: lha rnams kyi spyi bor so so'i rigs bdag gis
NK115(re)001:7278: rgyas 'debs pa gzhan dbang la gzhan dbang gi rgya
NK115(re)001:7279: dang / rigs bdag de rnams kyi spyi bor rang
NK115(re)001:7280: rang gi rigs kyi phyag mtshan gyis rgyas gdab pa
NK115(re)001:7281: gzhan dbang la yongs grub kyi rgya'o /
NK115(re)001:7282: de bzhin du skye mched rnams la rgyas 'debs tshul
NK115(re)001:7283: yang so sor gsungs mod dkyil 'khor gyi lha gang
NK115(re)001:7284: yin yang gtso 'khor thams cad rigs gang yin so
NK115(re)001:7285: sor shes par byas nas rang rig kyis rgyas 'debs
NK115(re)001:7287: de lta bu'i thabs kyis snang cha thams cad lha
NK115(re)001:7288: skur gasla ba'i sgo nas gzugs sku phrin las dang
NK115(re)001:7289: bcas pa lam du byas pas bsod namas kyi tshogas
NK115(re)001:7290: rdzogs shing / de thams cad la rang bzhin yongs
NK115(re)001:7291: shes kyi shes rab kyis zin te ranga bzhina ma
NK115(re)001:7292: gruba par shes pa'i sgo nas chos sku lam du
NK115(re)001:7293: byas pas ye shesa kyi tshogs rdzogs pa yin te
NK115(re)001:7294: rdzogs shing / / de yang thabs la mkhas pas
NK115(re)001:7295: 'bras bu la myur du sbyor bar byed pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:7296: yin pa'i phyir na spyir gsang sngags thams cad nye
NK115(re)001:7297: ba'i rgyu yin zhing de las kyang nang rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:7298: gsum gyi lam thams cad shin tu nye ba tshe
NK115(re)001:7299: 'di nyid la zung 'jug gi 'bras bu mngon du
NK115(re)001:7300: byed pa'i lam khyad par can yin pas /
NK115(re)001:7301: grol lam bskyed rim la brten nas rdzogs rim gyi
NK115(re)001:7302: ye shes la sbyor ba'i phyira tshogas gnyisa nye ba'i
NK115(re)001:7303: rgyur bsten pa'i sgo nas sam /
NK115(re)001:7304: dbang po rnon po thabs lam pa daga las rgya
NK115(re)001:7305: la brten nas rdzogs rim gyi rtogs pa mthar phyin
NK115(re)001:7306: pa'i bar gyi lam lnga po bgrod par byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:7307: tshul dag ni mtshan nyid theg par yun ring mo
NK115(re)001:7308: zhig nas lam lnga dang sa bcu'i yon tan thams
NK115(re)001:7309: cad rim gyis thob par bshad pa de sngags lam
NK115(re)001:7310: gyis myur du bgrod par 'gyur ba'i khyad par tsam
NK115(re)001:7311: las / lam gyi go rim dang yon tan gyi
NK115(re)001:7312: rnam grangs thams cad ni mtshungs par yod pas na
NK115(re)001:7313: 'dir sngags kyis lam ji ltar bgrod pa'i tshul cung
NK115(re)001:7314: zad cig bshad par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:7315: de la lam gyi ngo bo'i cha nas bskyed rim
NK115(re)001:7316: zhes smos pa de nyams su len tshul gyi cha
NK115(re)001:7317: nas shes rab kyis rnam par grol ba'i lam zhes
NK115(re)001:7318: bya ste / grol lam pa de'i thos bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:7319: sngags kyi lta ba la nges pa rnyed nas lam
NK115(re)001:7320: bsgom pa na bskyed rim rkyang pa'i lam gyis 'jig
NK115(re)001:7321: rten pa'i dngos grub 'dod pa'i rig 'dzin dang gzugs
NK115(re)001:7322: kyi rigs 'dzin gnyis grub ste 'dod pa'i lha dang
NK115(re)001:7323: bya ste / / gzugs kyi lha 'og min gyi
NK115(re)001:7324: bar dag dang skal pa mnyam par 'gyur zhing de
NK115(re)001:7325: nas rdzogs rim dang 'brel ba'i thabs kyis grol ba
NK115(re)001:7326: yod kyis bskyed rim de kho nas 'das lam mngon
NK115(re)001:7328: 'on kyang skal ba dang ldan pa'i dbang rab kha
NK115(re)001:7329: cig dang po nas dbang dang man ngag bstan pa
NK115(re)001:7330: tsam gyis bskyed rdzogs zung du tshud de rtogs goms
NK115(re)001:7331: chig chod du gyur nas grol ba yod de /
NK115(re)001:7332: de la ni grol lam cig car ba zhes bya
NK115(re)001:7333: ste sa lam gyi yon tan cig car du skye
NK115(re)001:7334: bas so // grol lam rim gyis pa ni /
NK115(re)001:7335: dag mnyam gyi lta ba dang mthun pa'i lam zag
NK115(re)001:7336: bcas kyi rnal 'byor lnga'i ting 'dzin la rtsal sbyang
NK115(re)001:7337: ba'i mnyam rjes kyi rnal 'byor la brten nas dper
NK115(re)001:7338: na rin po che kostu b+ha dang lhan cig bzhag
NK115(re)001:7339: pa'i rdo'i khams rim gyis gser du 'gyur ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:7340: tha mal 'khrul pa'i rtog pa rnams rim gyis rang
NK115(re)001:7342: de grol na de dang dbyer med par 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:7343: rlung khams kyi 'pho ba yang ye shes kyi dbyings
NK115(re)001:7344: su grol bar mi 'gyur ba'i gnas med de srog
NK115(re)001:7345: gi dbang po 'gags na dbang po gzhan thams cad
NK115(re)001:7347: de ltar gzung 'dzin 'khrul snang gi kun rtog rkyen
NK115(re)001:7348: dang bcas pa chab rom chur zhu ba bzhin rang
NK115(re)001:7349: zhi rang grol du song nas gnas lugs don dam
NK115(re)001:7350: pa'i bden pa mthong lam gyi ye shes mngon du
NK115(re)001:7351: byas te mi slob pa'i 'bras bu la sbyor bar
NK115(re)001:7353: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK115(re)001:7354: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK115(re)001:7355: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK115(re)001:7356: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK115(re)001:7358: yang lam gyi ngo bo rdzogs rim nyams su len
NK115(re)001:7359: pa'i cha nas thabs kyis nges pa'i lam zhes bya
NK115(re)001:7360: ste / gtso bor thabs kyi spyod pa rmad du
NK115(re)001:7361: byung ba'i sgo nas rang gnas kyi ye shes btsan
NK115(re)001:7362: thabs su 'char bar byed pa ste dper na mak+shi
NK115(re)001:7363: ka'i sbyor bas lcags khams yud tsam gyis gser du
NK115(re)001:7365: de la yang thabs lam rim gyis pa steng sgo
NK115(re)001:7366: la bslab pa ste 'khor lo drug sogs la brten
NK115(re)001:7367: nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor bas bde ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:7368: bskyed pa dang / thabs lam cig char ba 'og
NK115(re)001:7369: sgo la brten nas dbab bzung ldog khyab kyi sbyor
NK115(re)001:7370: bas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mngon du byed
NK115(re)001:7371: bskyed pa dang / pa ste / de yang brtson
NK115(re)001:7372: 'grus can thabs kyi sgo nas spros bral blo 'das
NK115(re)001:7373: kyi don mnyam gzhag tu ci rigs par myong ba'i
NK115(re)001:7374: stobs las rjes thob tu snang srid dag mnyam chen
NK115(re)001:7375: po'i tshul la nges pa shugs kyis 'drongs shing rnam
NK115(re)001:7376: rtog gi bzhon par gyur ba'i rlung dang rkyen du
NK115(re)001:7377: gyur pa'i khams phra rags rnams rtsa yi gnad la
NK115(re)001:7378: brten te bcings pas g.yo byed kyi rlung 'ching ba
NK115(re)001:7379: na yid kyang rang bzhin gyis 'ching ba ni dper
NK115(re)001:7380: na rkang pa bcings na lus 'gro ba med pa
NK115(re)001:7381: bzhin yin pas kun rtog bzhon pa dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:7382: dbu ma'i dbyings su thim pas khams dang rtsa'i 'gro
NK115(re)001:7383: sa dag nas rang la rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i
NK115(re)001:7384: ye shes kyi snang ba rim gyis 'phel te mthar
NK115(re)001:7385: 'pho ba'i bag chags shin tu phra ba'ang dag nas
NK115(re)001:7386: bde ba chen po'i sku 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:7388: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:7389: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:7390: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK115(re)001:7391: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK115(re)001:7393: de lta bu'i thabs kyi lam steng 'og gi sgo
NK115(re)001:7394: gnyis la brten pa'i tshul rgyas par ni 'og tu
NK115(re)001:7396: skabs 'dir ni sa lam rim gyis bgrod par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:7397: ba de bskyed rdzogs sam thabs grol gnyis po'i thun
NK115(re)001:7398: mong gi byed las yin pas gnyis ka gang la
NK115(re)001:7399: bslab pa de'i sa lam thams cad mthar phyin par
NK115(re)001:7400: byed pa'i phyir de go ba'i don du smos pa
NK115(re)001:7401: yin no // de ltar grol lam dang thabs lam
NK115(re)001:7402: gnyis po bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i lam nyams su len
NK115(re)001:7403: tshul yin par bshad pa de'ang thabs shes kyi byed
NK115(re)001:7404: pa gtso che chung gi sgo nas bzhag gi gcig
NK115(re)001:7405: la gcig med pa ni ma yin te bskyed rim
NK115(re)001:7406: la'ang rtsa rlung thig le thams cad ngang gis dag
NK115(re)001:7407: ste rdzogs rim gyi ye shes 'dren pa'i thabs yod
NK115(re)001:7408: yin no // la / rdzogs rim la'ang thabs kyi
NK115(re)001:7409: sgo nas shes rab khyad par can gyi lta ba
NK115(re)001:7410: dang rtog tshogs thams cad lhar 'char ba yod pa'i
NK115(re)001:7411: phyir rim pa gnyis po gang gi ltar yang gnyis
NK115(re)001:7412: ka zung 'jug tu med pa ni lam bgrod du
NK115(re)001:7413: med pas zung 'jug gi lam yin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7414: gnas lugs kyi don mthong ba la khyad par med par shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:7415: thabs de dag la brten nas lam bgrod tshul gyi
NK115(re)001:7416: rim pa dngos ni spyir rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:7417: gyi spyi don / dang po dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub
NK115(re)001:7418: nas mthar mi slob pa'i lam gyi bar thams cad
NK115(re)001:7419: phyag rgya bzhi'i chings kyis bcings nas bshad pa'ang yod
NK115(re)001:7420: gyi spyi don / de / sgrub gzhi las kyi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:7421: sgrub byed dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:7422: bsgrub bya chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:7425: dkyil 'khor gyi las rim rnams chos bya ba mo yum gyi mkha' klong dang 'brel ba'o //
NK115(re)001:7426: gnyis pa ni de thams cad yid byed pa po dam tshig sdom pa'i kun spyod dang 'brel ba'o //
NK115(re)001:7427: gsum pa ni pha rol tu phyin pa drug la
NK115(re)001:7428: brten pa rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i chos nyid dang
NK115(re)001:7429: 'brel ba'o // bzhi pa ni sku gsum yan lag
NK115(re)001:7430: bdun ldan gyi rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po'i go
NK115(re)001:7432: yang bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i khongs su rigs 'dzin
NK115(re)001:7433: rnam pa bzhi'i sa lam bgrod tshul dang sbyar ba'ang
NK115(re)001:7434: yod de / de'ang zag bcas kyi rnal 'byor lnga
NK115(re)001:7435: po dang sbyar te lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan
NK115(re)001:7436: lag bzhi lam rim ltar bshad pa ni sngar ltar
NK115(re)001:7437: yod de / yin la / 'dir ni tshogs lam
NK115(re)001:7438: nas mthar lam gyi bar thams cad yan lag bzhi
NK115(re)001:7439: po 'di'i khongs su bsdu ba'i tshul te /
NK115(re)001:7440: de yang tshogs lam du dbang bskur gyi lha ngo
NK115(re)001:7441: bstan nas rigs gtad de dam tshig dang mi 'gal
NK115(re)001:7442: bar yi dam gyi lha dang rang rgyud dbyer med
NK115(re)001:7443: du bsnyen te tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:7444: nas / sbyor lam du spyod pa'i bogs 'don la
NK115(re)001:7445: brten nas drod rtse bzod gsum gyi lam stegs mngon
NK115(re)001:7446: du byas nas chos mchog chen por rnam smin rigs
NK115(re)001:7447: 'dzin mngon du byas pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK115(re)001:7448: mthong lam du thog mar slob pa'i zung 'jug gi
NK115(re)001:7449: sku mngon du gyur te skye 'chi med pa tshe
NK115(re)001:7450: dbang rigs 'dzin bsnyes pa ni yi dam gyi lha
NK115(re)001:7451: dang sngar bas nye bar nye bsnyen /
NK115(re)001:7452: sgom lam du yi dam gyi lha dang rnam pa
NK115(re)001:7453: 'dra ba'i phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'dzin mngon du
NK115(re)001:7454: byas te rang gzhan gyi don gnyis mnyam du bsgrub
NK115(re)001:7455: pas sgrub pa / mthar lam du rang don lam
NK115(re)001:7456: gyi rtsol ba chad de rjes thob de bzhin gshegs
NK115(re)001:7457: pa dang mnyam pa'i phrin las kyis 'gro don mdzad
NK115(re)001:7458: pa ni sgrub pa chen po yin par gsungs so
NK115(re)001:7459: pas sgrub pa / // yang de dag gi tshe
NK115(re)001:7460: lha snang gong du 'phel nas lam lnga mthar phyin
NK115(re)001:7462: sems nyid yi ge a'i rang bzhin skye ba med
NK115(re)001:7463: par gnas pa las rtsa gnas 'khor lor yi ge'i
NK115(re)001:7464: sprin chags te gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor du grub
NK115(re)001:7465: pa las 'gro ba'i sgra skad kun 'byung zhing /
NK115(re)001:7466: yi ge phyag mtshan du gyur pa las sku sgyu ma lta bu dang 'gro ba'i lus 'byung zhing /
NK115(re)001:7467: yi ge'i ngo bo skye ba med pa las thugs
NK115(re)001:7468: chos kyi sku mi phyed rdo rje dang 'gro ba'i
NK115(re)001:7469: yid rtog med dang rtog bcas thams cad 'byung ba
NK115(re)001:7470: yin pa'i phyir rdo rje gsum gyi sgrub gzhi yi
NK115(re)001:7473: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK115(re)001:7474: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK115(re)001:7477: a zhes bya ba ni ma skyes pa'i phyir chos thams cad kyi sgo'o zhes so //
NK115(re)001:7478: yi ge de la'ang gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:7479: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi yi ge 'od gsal ba'i sems nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:7480: lus gnas rtsa yi yi ge dbyangs gsal lha'i sa bon dang /
NK115(re)001:7481: sgra don rtags kyi yi ge sgra spyi dang don spyi'i rnam pa yi ger btags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7482: de'i phyi mo bris pa lany+tsa dang na ga ra dang bod kyi yi ge la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7483: des na skye med kyi gdangs las 'gag med kyi
NK115(re)001:7484: yi ge la bslab pa nas rim par lha tshogs
NK115(re)001:7485: yongs rdzogs 'od zer gyi spro bsdu dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:7486: bsgom pa dkyil 'khor dang po'i ting nge 'dzin te
NK115(re)001:7488: de nas gzhal yas khang gi dbus phyur bu dang /
NK115(re)001:7489: shar lho nub gsum gyi sgo'i steng bzhir rnam snang
NK115(re)001:7490: la sogs pa rigs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor spros te bsgoms
NK115(re)001:7491: pas sbyor lam bzhi bgrod nas byang sgo'i steng don
NK115(re)001:7492: grub kyi dkyil 'khor bsgoms pas mthong lam thob ste
NK115(re)001:7493: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis la mnga' dbang 'byor
NK115(re)001:7494: / de lta ba'i dkyil 'khor stong phrag bcu gnyis rdzogs pas sa gnyis pa nas /
NK115(re)001:7495: mthar grangs med kyis bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs nas sa bcu pa non te /
NK115(re)001:7496: rdo rje 'chang kun tu bzang po he ru ka'i
NK115(re)001:7497: dbang phyug rnams kyis dbang bskur te khams gsum chos
NK115(re)001:7498: kyi rgyal por mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'o zhes gsungs so
NK115(re)001:7499: // yang de dag gi tshe gsang sngags gsar rnying
NK115(re)001:7500: gung mthun par 'khor lo bzhi'i rlung sems rim pa
NK115(re)001:7501: bzhin las su rung ba las slob lam bzhi'i yon
NK115(re)001:7502: tan mdo lam nas bshad pa'i byang phyogs so bdun
NK115(re)001:7503: gyi rnam par 'char zhing dbu ma la ro rkyang
NK115(re)001:7504: gnyis kyi mdud pa nyi shu rtsa gcig yod pa'i
NK115(re)001:7505: gnyis gnyis grol te sa bcu'i yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:7507: de yang rlung sems las su rung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:7509: der tshud dus las su rung ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:7510: 'byongs pa ni de dag gi rtsa bran dang bcas pa'i mdun pa grol dgos so //
NK115(re)001:7511: de la dang po lte ba skyed byed kyi rtsa
NK115(re)001:7512: 'khor du rlung sems las su rung ba'i tshe tshogs
NK115(re)001:7513: lam gsum gyi yon tan sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku'i
NK115(re)001:7515: 'di rnams kyi dus su mngon rtogs sgom tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:7516: rang gzhan gyi lus la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK115(re)001:7517: 'khor lor ye nas dag pa bzhin du bsgom zhing
NK115(re)001:7518: / de yang stong nyid spros bral mnyam pa chen
NK115(re)001:7519: po dang zung du 'jug pa'i tshul la blo gzhag
NK115(re)001:7520: pa ni lus dran pa nye bar bzhag pa /
NK115(re)001:7521: byung tshor gyi rtog pa thams cad bde ba chen
NK115(re)001:7522: po'i ye shes su bsgyur ba tshor ba dran pa
NK115(re)001:7524: sems sems byung gi spros pa ma lus pa 'od
NK115(re)001:7525: gsal gnyug ma'i dbyings su sdom pa sems dran pa
NK115(re)001:7526: nyer bzhag / 'khor 'das snang btags kyi chos thams
NK115(re)001:7527: cad dag mnyam blang dor dang bral bar spyod pa
NK115(re)001:7528: chos dran pa nyer bzhag ste tshogs lam chung ngu'i
NK115(re)001:7529: nyer bzhag / dus dang / de gong du 'phel
NK115(re)001:7530: te dge sdig spang blang las 'das pa'i tshul gyis
NK115(re)001:7531: yang dag spong bzhi'i rang bzhin can gyi tshogs lam
NK115(re)001:7532: nyer bzhag / dus dang / 'bring po dang /
NK115(re)001:7533: de nyid stobs su gyur nas bskyed rdzogs kyi don
NK115(re)001:7534: la rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK115(re)001:7535: rkang pa bzhi'i rang bzhin can gyi tshog lam chen
NK115(re)001:7536: nyer bzhag / dus dang / 'bring po dang /
NK115(re)001:7537: po rnams so // chos kyi 'khor lo'i rlung sems
NK115(re)001:7538: las su rung bas sbyor lam bzhi'i yon tan 'char
NK115(re)001:7539: nyer bzhag / dus dang / 'bring po dang /
NK115(re)001:7540: po rnams so // te / 'di dag gi dus
NK115(re)001:7541: su bskyed rdzogs kyi don la sgom pa'i nyams myong
NK115(re)001:7542: lhag par 'phel te mtshon bya don gyi gnas lugs
NK115(re)001:7543: don spyi'i tshul du bsgoms pas mthong lam gyi ye
NK115(re)001:7544: shes me lta bu 'byung ba'i snga ltas su mtshon
NK115(re)001:7545: byed dpe'i ye shes rgyud la dang por skyes pa
NK115(re)001:7547: dag mnyam gyi gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shes rab dang
NK115(re)001:7548: de'i grogs dad sogs dang bcas pa'i dbang po lnga
NK115(re)001:7549: yod la / de gong du 'phel bas dge rtsa
NK115(re)001:7550: g.yo ba'i nang nas rtse mor gyur pa rtse mo'i
NK115(re)001:7551: yod la / rtogs pa skye'o // de nas dad
NK115(re)001:7552: sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis barji mi nus pa'i
NK115(re)001:7553: stobs lnga'i rang bzhin can bzod pa skye zhing /
NK115(re)001:7554: de yang stobs su gyur nas don gyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:7555: mthong lam gyi dngos rgyu dpe'i ye shes mthar thug
NK115(re)001:7556: pa skyes pa chos mchog ste de rnams kyi ye
NK115(re)001:7561: nyer thob kyi ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:7562: de la sbyor lam yin min gyi mtshams dpe'i ye
NK115(re)001:7563: shes rgyud la skyes ma skyes kyi sgo nas 'dzin
NK115(re)001:7564: dgos kyi / bskyed rim tshogs lam dang /
NK115(re)001:7565: rdor bzlas sogs rdzogs rim sbyor lam nas nyams su len par bshad pa'ang /
NK115(re)001:7566: rim gyis pa la de ltar 'ong ba yod kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK115(re)001:7567: dbang dus su ye shes ngo 'phrod pa sogs rtogs goms cig car ba srid pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:7568: dang po nas bskyed rdzogs zug 'brel du nyams su len pa yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:7569: bskyed rim zab mo'i dpe'i ye shes 'dren pa srid pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:7570: rdzogs rim gyi rnal 'byor bsgom yang dpe'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:7571: tsam yang skye mi nus pa srid pa'i phyir na
NK115(re)001:7572: rgyud sde so sor bstan pa'i bskyed rdzogs gang nyams
NK115(re)001:7573: su blangs kyang dpe'i ye shes rgyud la na ma
NK115(re)001:7574: skyes pa de la sngags kyi sbyor lam zhes ngos
NK115(re)001:7575: 'dzin dgos shing / de'ang sbyor lam snga ma gnyis
NK115(re)001:7576: su ri mor bris pa'i zla ba lta bu rjes
NK115(re)001:7577: 'dzin dgos shing / mthun pa dang / phyi ma
NK115(re)001:7578: gnyis su chu nang gi zla ba lta bu mtshan
NK115(re)001:7579: nyid pa gnyis su yod do zhes chos rje mi
NK115(re)001:7580: 'dzin dgos shing / mthun pa dang / pham pas
NK115(re)001:7581: gsungs / de nas longs spyod 'khor lo'i rlung sems
NK115(re)001:7582: las su rung zhing dbu ma'i mar snar ro rkyang
NK115(re)001:7583: gi mdud pa gnyis grol bas mtshon bya don gyi
NK115(re)001:7584: ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bo rang
NK115(re)001:7585: mtshan pa gnam zla dngos lta bu mngon sum du
NK115(re)001:7586: mthong ba'i mthong lam thob ste chos nyid kyi don
NK115(re)001:7587: rnam par 'byed pa'i shes rab sogs byang chub kyi
NK115(re)001:7588: yan lag bdun gyi mngon rtogs dang ldan no //
NK115(re)001:7589: de nas bde chen 'khor lo'i rlung sems las su
NK115(re)001:7590: rung ba'i tshe mas rim nas dbu ma'i mdud pa
NK115(re)001:7591: gnyis gnyis grol te sgom lam sa dgu'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:7592: rim gyis 'char zhing snang srid dag mnyam chen po
NK115(re)001:7593: mngon sum du gzigs pa'i ye shes stobs su gyur
NK115(re)001:7594: pa'i yang dag pa'i lta ba sogs 'phags pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:7595: yan lag brgyad kyi yon tan rnams gong du 'phel
NK115(re)001:7596: bar 'gyur ro // de ltar sgom lam sa dgu'i
NK115(re)001:7597: gnas skabs su mi slob pa'i zung 'jug la sgrib
NK115(re)001:7598: par byed pa'i dri ma rnams rim gyis dag ste
NK115(re)001:7599: rtsa mdud tha ma grol bas gtsug tor rtse mo'i
NK115(re)001:7601: de ltar gnas lugs mthong tshul gyis lam lngar bzhag pa na /
NK115(re)001:7602: de dang de'i gnas skabs kyi chos nyid mthong ba'i
NK115(re)001:7603: ye shes la 'od gsal gyi tha snyad 'jog par
NK115(re)001:7604: gsungs te / tshogs lam na go yul tsam gyi 'od gsal dang /
NK115(re)001:7605: sbyor lam na dpe'i 'od gsal dang /
NK115(re)001:7606: mthong lam na don gyi 'od gsal dang /
NK115(re)001:7607: sgom lam na slob pa'i 'od gsal dang /
NK115(re)001:7608: mi slob pa'i lam na mthar thug gi 'od gsal rnams yod cing /
NK115(re)001:7609: de ltar chos nyid mnyam pa chen po'i don la
NK115(re)001:7610: gsal snang gi 'od gsal je bzang du song ba
NK115(re)001:7611: de bzhin dag pa'i snang ba yang gong du 'phel
NK115(re)001:7612: te tshogs lam na mos pa'i lha sku /
NK115(re)001:7613: sbyor lam na rlung sems kyi lha sku /
NK115(re)001:7614: mthong lam na 'od gsal gyi lha sku /
NK115(re)001:7615: sgom lam na slob pa'i zug 'jug gi lha sku /
NK115(re)001:7616: sangs rgyas kyi sa na mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku rnams yod par shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:7617: de ltar lam lnga po der 'brela ba riga 'dzina
NK115(re)001:7618: rnama pa bzhi'i skabs kyi dag mnyam rtogs pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:7619: tan gong nas gong du them skasa bgrod pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:7620: 'phel ba nyid du gyur pa lasa gnas ngesa pa
NK115(re)001:7621: sogs le'u bcu gsum par 'chad 'gyur ltar nges pa
NK115(re)001:7622: lnga ldana sogas sku lnga'i yon tan thams cad mthar
NK115(re)001:7623: phyin pa'i 'og min gyi zhing du ring por mi
NK115(re)001:7624: thogs par thabs shes khyad par can gyi stobs kyis
NK115(re)001:7625: miga 'phrula lta bur 'gro ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:7626: rig 'dzin bzhi po des lam gang bsdus pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:7627: kun mkhyen chen pos lam lnga ga rig 'dzin bzhis bsdus par bzhed de /
NK115(re)001:7628: de yang dang po bskyed rim la brtan pa thob
NK115(re)001:7629: nas sems nyid lhar smin yang 'byung ba'i snyigs ma
NK115(re)001:7630: nye rgyu'i spyod pas sbyong bar ma nus pa rnams
NK115(re)001:7631: la ni tshogs sbyor gyi lam la gnas pa rnam
NK115(re)001:7632: par smin pa'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:7633: des sbyor lam chos mchog ma thob par rnam smin
NK115(re)001:7634: gyi lus rten zhig na srid pa phyi ma la
NK115(re)001:7635: nying mtshams sbyor mi dgos par bar dor phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:7637: sems lha sku sgyu ma'i stong gzugs tsam du smin
NK115(re)001:7638: zin pas rnam smin gyi lus dor ma thag mthong
NK115(re)001:7640: rten des chos mchog thob na ni tshe la dbang
NK115(re)001:7641: bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin gyi dam pa 'grub pa zhes
NK115(re)001:7642: bya ste / lus rten de nyid kyang dwangs ma'i
NK115(re)001:7643: lus rdo rje lta bur 'gyur zhing sems kyang mthong
NK115(re)001:7645: de lta bu'i rten gyi tshe bcu drug mthud pa'i mthar sangs rgyas par gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:7647: don mthong 'jug pa'i mthar phyin pa'i //
NK115(re)001:7648: tshogs spyod sgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK115(re)001:7649: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK115(re)001:7650: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rig /
NK115(re)001:7651: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'da' //
NK115(re)001:7652: lus ma bor bar rgyal ba'i sa //
NK115(re)001:7656: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yi //
NK115(re)001:7657: brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK115(re)001:7658: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas so //
NK115(re)001:7659: zag gsum zag pa de la med //
NK115(re)001:7662: lus rang dbang med par 'dor ba dang na tsha
NK115(re)001:7663: la sogs pa rang dbang med par 'byung ba lus
NK115(re)001:7665: bsam gtan gyi sems grub nas bsam bzhin du 'dod
NK115(re)001:7666: khams su skye ba 'dzin mi nus pa khams kyi
NK115(re)001:7667: zag pa dang / skye gnas bzhi gang rung du
NK115(re)001:7668: rang dbang med par 'jug pa skye gnas kyi zag
NK115(re)001:7669: zag pa dang / pa'o // mthong lam gyi 'od
NK115(re)001:7670: gsal de las langs pa'i slob pa'i zung 'jug sa
NK115(re)001:7671: gnyis pa dri ma med pa la sogs pa'i lhag
NK115(re)001:7672: ma dgu ni zug 'jug ye shes sgyu ma'i sku
NK115(re)001:7673: can phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin te /
NK115(re)001:7675: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK115(re)001:7676: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK115(re)001:7677: mtshan dang dpe byad mngon shes ldan //
NK115(re)001:7678: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grags //
NK115(re)001:7680: rig 'dzin des bsdus pa'i sgom lam du rigs kyi
NK115(re)001:7681: 'khor los sgyur ba dang mtshungs par bgrod pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:7683: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK115(re)001:7684: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK115(re)001:7685: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dpe ldan //
NK115(re)001:7686: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK115(re)001:7687: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK115(re)001:7690: 'di la sgyu 'phrul pa'i bshad sgros su sa gnyis
NK115(re)001:7691: pa nas lnga pa'i bar la rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:7692: rdo rje lta bus rang sa'i sgrib pa bcom pa'i
NK115(re)001:7694: drug pa sher phyin gtso bor ston pa'i chos 'khor bskor la /
NK115(re)001:7695: bdun par yang thabs la mkhas pa 'khor lo ltar gyur pas de gnyis la 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:7696: brgyad par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la dbang bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:7697: dgu par chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis sbyong zhing gzhan don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:7698: bcu par phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems can
NK115(re)001:7699: gyi don byed pas ral gri'i rig 'dzin zhes bya'o
NK115(re)001:7700: // de nas rgyun matha'i ye shes rnam grol dang /
NK115(re)001:7701: khyad par gyi lam ni sku lnga lhun grub rdo
NK115(re)001:7702: rje 'chang gi cha lugs 'dzin pas lhun grub rig
NK115(re)001:7704: spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas kyis ni lhun grub rig 'dzin dngos yin te /
NK115(re)001:7706: snga ma'i rigs las mthu rdzogs pas //
NK115(re)001:7707: bshad pa bzhin du dri ma sbyangs //
NK115(re)001:7708: sangs rgyas sa yi shes rab gsum //
NK115(re)001:7709: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK115(re)001:7711: bka' sde zur ba rnams kyis ni rig 'dzin bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:7712: mthong sgom mthar lam gsum ste 'phags pa slob pa'i
NK115(re)001:7713: sa bcu bsdus pa bzhed de /
NK115(re)001:7714: de yang rig 'dzin snga ma gnyis mthong lam ste /
NK115(re)001:7715: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:7716: mes rnam smin gyi lus sbyong ma nus pa rnam
NK115(re)001:7718: sbyor bar nus nas dwangs ma'i sku skye shi med par gyur pa tshe dbang rig 'dzin te /
NK115(re)001:7720: nus pa thob dang ma thob las //
NK115(re)001:7721: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK115(re)001:7723: des na lam mthar chags kyi skabs su'ang gang zag
NK115(re)001:7724: gcig gis rig 'dzin snga ma gnyis po gang rung
NK115(re)001:7725: las gnyis ka thob pa med par bzhed cing /
NK115(re)001:7726: sgom lam phyag chen rig 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:7727: mthar lam pa lhun grub rig 'dzin du bzhed do //
NK115(re)001:7728: bzhed pa de gnyis kyang tshogs sbyor la rig 'dzin
NK115(re)001:7729: dang po'i tha snyad btags ma btags tsam las don
NK115(re)001:7730: la mthun te / snga ma'i lugs la'ang tshogs sbyor
NK115(re)001:7731: gyi rten de la sbyor lam bzhi pa ma thob
NK115(re)001:7732: na rten de'i tshe la dbang bsgyur mi nus pas
NK115(re)001:7733: bar dor mthong lam thob nas phyag rgya chen po'i
NK115(re)001:7734: tha snyad gdags pas mdzad la /
NK115(re)001:7735: de yang rung ste mthong lam yan chad slob pa'i
NK115(re)001:7736: lam thams cad las 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi cha
NK115(re)001:7738: skye shi med pa'i cha nas tshe dbang du btags
NK115(re)001:7739: pa yin zhes kun mkhyen nyid kyis gsungs pas mthong
NK115(re)001:7740: sgom so sor phye nas rnam pa thams cad du
NK115(re)001:7741: tshe dbang ba yin na mthong lam dang /
NK115(re)001:7742: phyag chen pa yin na sgom lam pa kho na yin mi dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:7744: lam chung gi lung don ji bzhin 'dren nus la /
NK115(re)001:7745: bzhed pa phyi mas kyang rnam smin gyi lus sbyong
NK115(re)001:7746: ma nus pa'i rten de'i mthong lam gyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:7747: bskyed nus kyi dpe'i 'od gsal grub nas /
NK115(re)001:7748: rten de bor ma thag mthong lam dngos skye ba
NK115(re)001:7749: la dgongs nas de ltar bshad rung ba'i phyir te
NK115(re)001:7750: / sher phyin rgyan du sa bcu pa la sangs
NK115(re)001:7751: rgyas kyi sa zhes btags pa lta bu'o snyam mo
NK115(re)001:7752: / // gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:7756: gnyis pa shes rab gtso che ba rdzogas pa'i rima pa nyida bshad pa la'ang /
NK115(re)001:7757: spyir rdzogs rim gyi ngo bo ni rnam rtog gi
NK115(re)001:7758: rang bzhin shes nas de nyid mi rtog pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:7759: du dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i thabs la brten pa'am
NK115(re)001:7760: / dmigs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis 'gog pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7762: rnam rtog rang bzhin shes pa na //
NK115(re)001:7763: mi rtog pa la 'jug par bya //
NK115(re)001:7765: de'ang dbye na thabs pha yi rgyud /
NK115(re)001:7767: gshin rje'i gshed la sogs pa rnal 'byor chen po'i
NK115(re)001:7768: rgyud rnamas lasa ni 'byunga ba lnga yi rlunga dbu
NK115(re)001:7769: mar zhugs te rnama para daga pa las zab gsal
NK115(re)001:7770: lam gasla stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shesa
NK115(re)001:7772: de la 'dus pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:7774: ye shes zhabs kyi lugs gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:7775: dang po'i lugs la rim lnga las /
NK115(re)001:7776: bdag byin brlabs pa'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK115(re)001:7777: de bzhin 'od gsal ba yi gnas //
NK115(re)001:7778: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i khyad par gyis //
NK115(re)001:7779: bden pa gnyis su bstan pa yin //
NK115(re)001:7780: zhes pa ltar sngon du sgyu lus kun rdzob kyi
NK115(re)001:7781: bden pa bsgrub nas 'od gsal don dam pa'i bden
NK115(re)001:7782: pa la 'jug pa ste bden pa gnyis kyi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:7783: rim dang / rlung 'jug gnas ldang gsum +aahmh'u gsum
NK115(re)001:7784: du mos pas gnas pa rgyun bsring zhing bum pa
NK115(re)001:7785: can du bsgom pa rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7786: snying gar yi ge'am phyag mtshan phra mo la sems
NK115(re)001:7787: rtse gcig tu 'dzin pa sems la dmigs pa dang
NK115(re)001:7788: / snang ba thams cad sgyu ma'i lha dang gzhal
NK115(re)001:7789: yas khang du gsal 'debs pa dag byin gyis brlab
NK115(re)001:7790: pa ste dben pa gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:7791: de nas rim gyis stong par bcug nas snang ba
NK115(re)001:7792: gsum du stong pa chen po'i 'od gsal bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:7793: 'od gsal / de las slar yang snang stong gnyis
NK115(re)001:7794: su med pa'i lha'i skur bzhengs pa ni zung 'jug
NK115(re)001:7795: ste rim pa lnga'i rdzogs rim bsgom tshul gsungs shing
NK115(re)001:7797: he ru ka galpo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:7798: rdo rje'i bzlas dang sems la dmigs //
NK115(re)001:7799: bdag byin brlabs dang 'od gsal dang //
NK115(re)001:7801: zhes dbu mar zhugs gnas thim gsum gyi stong bzhi
NK115(re)001:7802: dang dga' bzhi bskyed nas sad rmi'i bsre ba gsum
NK115(re)001:7803: gsum dang bdag byin gyis rlobs pa'i rim pa rlung
NK115(re)001:7804: sems tsam las grub pa'i sgyu ma'i lha sku dag
NK115(re)001:7805: pa'i sgyu lus bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7806: las rgya la brten nas de nyid 'od gsal du
NK115(re)001:7807: dag ste bar chad med lam mngon du gyur te
NK115(re)001:7808: zung 'jug gi skur ldang ba'i tshul rdo rje'i tshig
NK115(re)001:7810: gnyis pa sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyi bzhed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:7811: sgyu ma lta bu'i lha sku phyag rgya chen po gsal ba'i bdag nyid can dang /
NK115(re)001:7812: de kho na nyid la zhugs pa'i thugs zab cing
NK115(re)001:7813: ting dpag dka' ba gnyis dbyer med du sbyor ba
NK115(re)001:7814: zab gsal gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:7815: rim ste / grol ba'i thig le las /
NK115(re)001:7816: des na zab gsal byang chub ni //
NK115(re)001:7817: gnyis med rtogs pas de grol lo //
NK115(re)001:7818: zab mo kho na rtogs pas min //
NK115(re)001:7819: gsal ba dag kyang de bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:7821: yang bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs las kyang /
NK115(re)001:7822: sngags sems sgyu lus 'od gsal dang //
NK115(re)001:7824: zhes rim pa lnga gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:7825: sgrub sde bde gshegs 'dus pa las kyang /
NK115(re)001:7826: bsgom tshul gyi rnam pa cung mi 'dra yang rim pa lngar gsungs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7827: yang shes rab ma'i rgyud yang phur dang /
NK115(re)001:7830: dgyes rdor la sogs pa rjes su rnal 'byor gyi
NK115(re)001:7831: rgyud rnamas lasa ni khamas byang chub kyi sems thig
NK115(re)001:7832: le la gtso bor gnad du bsnun te zhu bde
NK115(re)001:7833: yi ye shesa bskyed pa'i phyir du gtum mo 'bar
NK115(re)001:7834: 'dzag gi sbyor ba la sogs pa'i thabs kyis gzhan
NK115(re)001:7835: rkyen la mi ltos par bde stong gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:7836: bskyed pa ranga lusa thabs ldana dang /
NK115(re)001:7837: gazhana lusa phyag rgya la brten nas dag'a ba bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:7838: ye shesa bskyed par byed pa gzhan lus thabs ldan
NK115(re)001:7840: de yang phyag rgya bzhir bsdu ba'i tshul ltar na /
NK115(re)001:7841: rlung la dbang thob pas pad+ma can sogs phyi las kyi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:7842: nang dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK115(re)001:7844: snang ba chos kyi phyag rgya sgyu lus /
NK115(re)001:7845: phyag rgya chen po 'od gsal ba dang lhan cig skyes sbyor ro //
NK115(re)001:7846: chos drug gi dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:7847: rmi lam sgyu lus kyi yan lag /
NK115(re)001:7848: 'pho ba bar do gnyis phyi ma'i mtshams sbyor te yan lag gsum /
NK115(re)001:7852: zung 'jug ni 'bras bu yin pas ma bgrangs so //
NK115(re)001:7853: gzhan yang bdag byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK115(re)001:7854: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rim pa /
NK115(re)001:7857: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rim pa lnga las /
NK115(re)001:7858: dang po ni snying ga'i thig le la dmigs nas
NK115(re)001:7859: 'byung ba lnga'i kha dog dang sbyar ba'i rlung 'byung
NK115(re)001:7860: 'jug gis sgrib pa sbyangs shing dngos grub bsdu ba'o
NK115(re)001:7861: // gnyis pa ni 'khor lo lnga'i dbus su rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan la dmigs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7862: gsum pa ni rol pa chen po'i ngang nas rtsa 'khor bzhir dga' bzhi'i ye shes ngos 'dzin pa'o /
NK115(re)001:7863: bzhi pa ni rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan skur gyur pa
NK115(re)001:7864: las bdud rtsi'i 'bebs shing gtum mo'i man ngag dang
NK115(re)001:7865: bsre ba'o // lnga pa ni snying ga nas 'od
NK115(re)001:7866: zer spros nas brtan g.yo 'od zhu'i rdzogs rim mo
NK115(re)001:7867: bsre ba'o // // khyad par du dgyes rdor gyi
NK115(re)001:7868: dgongs pa snang gsum dang rgyud gsum gyi dkri tshul
NK115(re)001:7869: lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7870: de yang nyams su len tshul gyis snang gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:7871: gnas tshul gyis rgyud gsum zhes bzhag par gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:7872: man ngag gi khrid yig las ni snang gsum lam 'bras kyi sngon 'gro dang /
NK115(re)001:7873: rgyud gsum dngos gzhir gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:7874: de dag gi don glang po che rab 'bogs kyi bkol rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:7875: ma mo'i rgyud lung rnams las kyang gsal bar bstan cing /
NK115(re)001:7876: he ru ka galpo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:7880: de yang 'khor 'das thun mong gi gzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:7881: gzhi 'bras mtshams sbyor ba'i lam dang /
NK115(re)001:7882: 'das pa 'bras bu ste snang ba gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:7883: 'jig rten pa dang zhes gzhi lam gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:7884: 'khor lo bskor zhes rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang 'bras bu ste rgyud gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:7885: yang 'khor 'das thun mong lam bshad na /
NK115(re)001:7886: snang ba gsum du bstan pa'i lam //
NK115(re)001:7887: kun gzhi lus dang phyag rgya che //
NK115(re)001:7888: rgyu rgyud thabs dang 'bras bu'i rgyud /
NK115(re)001:7890: kun gzhi zhes pas gzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:7891: lus zhes pas lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i lam ston pa'am /
NK115(re)001:7893: 'dus dang zhes snang bas gzhi 'bras gnyis ka 'dus pa ste bsdoms nas lam du byed pas lam /
NK115(re)001:7894: phyag rgya che zhes pa zung 'jug phyag rgya chen
NK115(re)001:7895: po 'bras bu ste snang ba gsum dang tshig rkang
NK115(re)001:7896: phyi mas rgyud gsum bstan te go sla'o //
NK115(re)001:7897: de dag ni gsung rgyun yin snang shar nas bris
NK115(re)001:7898: pa yin kyang log bshad du song e yod mi
NK115(re)001:7899: shes pas / mkhas pa rnams la 'dri ba dang /
NK115(re)001:7900: rgyud 'di'i 'grel ba sogs la blta ba las yid rton du mi rung ngo //
NK115(re)001:7901: gnyisa su med pa'i rgyud rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK115(re)001:7903: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor la sogs pa lasa zhu bdes drangs pa'i /
NK115(re)001:7904: gsal ba dang mi rtog pa dang bsam gyis mi
NK115(re)001:7905: khyab pa'i ye shes gciga dang du bral gyi thiga
NK115(re)001:7906: le chena po'i 'oda gasla gtso bor bsgom par byed
NK115(re)001:7907: pa ste / de yang bde ba'i 'od gsal ni
NK115(re)001:7908: dbu mar dwangs ma babs te khams las su rung
NK115(re)001:7909: ba las zag med kyi bde ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:7910: pa ste / skye'o / gsal ba'i 'od gsal ni
NK115(re)001:7911: rlung lnga'i dwangs ma stobs su gyur te dbu mar
NK115(re)001:7912: chud pa las nang du dwangs gsal sgrib pa med
NK115(re)001:7914: phyi rol du sna sgor rlung lnga'i kha dog mngon pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7915: ye shes lnga'i 'od gdangs sku dang thig le'i rang bzhin du 'char te /
NK115(re)001:7917: ye shes snang ba lam me ba //
NK115(re)001:7918: 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron //
NK115(re)001:7919: gzi brjid chen po 'od gsal ba //
NK115(re)001:7922: bde ba dang gsal ba gang gi yang ngo bor mi rtog par 'dzin med du gnas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7923: de yang rang bzhin gshis kyi gnas lugs bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:7924: mi khyab pa'i 'od gsal chen po'i ngang du grol
NK115(re)001:7925: bar 'gyur te / sgyu 'phrul rngam glog las /
NK115(re)001:7926: dngos po thams cad rnam bral ba'i //
NK115(re)001:7927: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK115(re)001:7928: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK115(re)001:7929: chos bdag med pa mnyam nyid pas //
NK115(re)001:7930: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK115(re)001:7931: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:7933: de bzhin du dus 'khor rtsa rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:7934: gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK115(re)001:7935: so sor sdud dang bsam gtan dang //
NK115(re)001:7936: srog rtsol de bzhin 'dzin pa dang //
NK115(re)001:7937: rjes su dran dang ting nge 'dzin //
NK115(re)001:7938: sbyor ba yan lag drug tu 'dod //
NK115(re)001:7941: sbyor ba yan lag drug gis bsnyen //
NK115(re)001:7943: nyin mo'i rnal 'byor nam mkha' dang /
NK115(re)001:7944: mtshan mo'i rnal 'byor mun khang la brten nas dbang
NK115(re)001:7945: po lnga yul la mi g.yeng bar bsgom pa sor
NK115(re)001:7946: sdud / de las rtags bcu'i stong gzugs mngon du
NK115(re)001:7947: gyur nas yul sems gnyis su med pa'i mnyam bzhag
NK115(re)001:7949: 'di gnyis kyis ma grub pa bsgrub cing grub zin brtan par bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:7950: de'ang du ba la sogs pa'i stong gzugs ni mthar mtshan dpes spras pa'i skur 'gyur la /
NK115(re)001:7951: stong gzugs kyi rnam pa de nyid kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7952: rang bzhin med pa don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7953: de nas g.yas g.yon dang steng 'og gi rlung gcig tu 'dres pa srog rtsol dang /
NK115(re)001:7954: 'khor lo bzhi'i rlung sems las su rung ste gzung 'dzin dbu mar thim pa 'dzin pa ste /
NK115(re)001:7955: 'di gnyis kyis ngag gi rtsa ba rlung la dbang thob par byas nas rgyal ba'i gsung bsgrub pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7956: de nas las dang ye shes phyag rgya chen po
NK115(re)001:7957: gsum gang rung la brten nas bde stong lhan cig
NK115(re)001:7958: skyes pa'i ye shes skyes pa'i ye shes skyes pa
NK115(re)001:7959: rjes dran dang / mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK115(re)001:7960: po'i ye shes mngon du byas pa ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:7961: te snga ma nye rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:7962: phyi ma ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo yin te rgyal ba'i thugs sgrub par byed do //
NK115(re)001:7964: rgyud kyi le'u lnga pa las /
NK115(re)001:7965: lus ni dwang zhing rdul phran nyams pa nam mkha'
NK115(re)001:7966: dang mtshungs mtshan la sogs pa rnams kyis rab rdzogs
NK115(re)001:7967: 'gyur // sna tshogs 'jig rten gsum po nyid ni
NK115(re)001:7968: dwang zhing sgrib pa rnam par bral ba rmi lam
NK115(re)001:7969: 'gyur // bzhin du snang // skad ni kun nas
NK115(re)001:7970: chad pa med cing du ma'i skad gzhan dag gis
NK115(re)001:7971: du ma'i snying la 'jug pa ste //
NK115(re)001:7972: sems ni dam pa'i bde bas gang zhig mi g.yo
NK115(re)001:7973: thams cad dus su lhan cig skyes pas 'khyud pa'o
NK115(re)001:7975: de ltar pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud las bstan pa'i rdzogs rim gsum lasa /
NK115(re)001:7976: snga ma rlung dang thig le'i rdzogs rim gtso bor
NK115(re)001:7977: ston pa gnyisa ni snang bacasa te dmigas rnam dang
NK115(re)001:7979: phyi ma zung 'jug gi ye shes gtso bor 'jug
NK115(re)001:7980: gi ye shes gtso bor ston pa'i rdzogs rim gciga
NK115(re)001:7981: ni yul dang yul can gyi snanga ba gnyis su
NK115(re)001:7982: meda pa 'oda gasla ba'i rdzogs rim te de gnyis
NK115(re)001:7983: la mtshan bcas dang mtshan med kyi rdzogs rim kyang
NK115(re)001:7984: zer te rdzogs rim gyi rnam grangs thams cad de
NK115(re)001:7986: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:7987: snang bcas kyi rdzogs rim dang /
NK115(re)001:7988: snang med kyi rdzogs rim bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7989: dang po snang bcas kyi rdzogs rim bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:7990: rdo rje'i lus kyi gnas lugs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7992: dang po rdo rje'i lus kyi gnas lugs bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:7993: rgyud sde spyi'i lugs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:7994: sgyu 'phrul gsang thig gi lugs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:7995: dang po rgyud sde spyi'i lugs bshad pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:8000: de la dang po snang ba dang bcas pa'i rdzogs
NK115(re)001:8001: rim ni rtsa rlung thig le la gnad du bsnun
NK115(re)001:8002: pa'i sgo nas ye shes bskyed dgos pas de'i phyogsa
NK115(re)001:8003: nyams su len pa la de dag gi gnas tshul
NK115(re)001:8004: shes pa gal che bas na /
NK115(re)001:8005: 'di ltar rnam par gyur pa'i lha'i bdag nyid du
NK115(re)001:8006: g.yo ba med par gnas pas na gansa pa rtsa
NK115(re)001:8008: he ru ka la sogs pa'i lha //
NK115(re)001:8009: rtsa gzugs mdzes par yang dag byung //
NK115(re)001:8011: de la rtsa'i gtso mo gsum dang 'khor lo lnga /
NK115(re)001:8012: byed las kyi sgo nas ni tha dad du bzhag
NK115(re)001:8013: pa'i rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis su yod
NK115(re)001:8014: de / sangs rgyas thod pa las /
NK115(re)001:8015: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK115(re)001:8016: rtsa rnams kyi ni 'gros bshad do //
NK115(re)001:8018: de'i nang nas kyang gnad du bsnun bya'i gtso bo
NK115(re)001:8019: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba ster zhing lus can
NK115(re)001:8020: kun gyi srog tu gyur pa ni a wa d+h+au
NK115(re)001:8021: t+ai'o // de lta bu'i rtsa rnams dang rten dang brten pa'i tshul du 'brel zhing /
NK115(re)001:8022: phra ba dang bskyod pa'i byed las can rnams par shes pa'i bzhon par gyur pa /
NK115(re)001:8023: khams gsum thams cad kyang 'du byed pas na g.yo ba rlung zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:8024: de gnyis ka'i brten pa lta bur gyur zhing rlung
NK115(re)001:8025: gis gang du bkod pa'i gnas su 'gro 'ong byed
NK115(re)001:8027: rang bzhin dri ma dang bral zhing yon tan lhun gyis grub pas byanga chuba kyi semas te /
NK115(re)001:8028: dbye na rtsa ba spros bral gyi thig le rig pa'i ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:8029: 'khrul pa ma rig pa'i thig le sems dang /
NK115(re)001:8030: khams lnga rdzas kyi thig le khams dkar dmar rnams so //
NK115(re)001:8031: de yang sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po'i
NK115(re)001:8032: rang bzhin can yin pas gnyug ma'i sgo gsum dang
NK115(re)001:8034: gnas skabs su khams gong lta bu khams drug rags
NK115(re)001:8035: pa med pa rnams sngags lam gyi dang po'i rten
NK115(re)001:8036: du dman pas na rtsa rlung thig le rags pa'i
NK115(re)001:8037: rnam pa gsuma du gansa pa ni rten khyad par
NK115(re)001:8038: can te de la rdo rje zhes bya ba ni
NK115(re)001:8039: mi phyed pa'i don te sku gsung thugs gsum mam
NK115(re)001:8040: sku gsum gyi rang bzhin dang dbyer mi phyed pa'o
NK115(re)001:8041: // phunga po ni du ma spungs pa'i don te
NK115(re)001:8042: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i rtsal snang gzugs la
NK115(re)001:8043: sogs pa 'dus pa'i bdag nyid can no //
NK115(re)001:8044: de dag rang byung rig pa'i ye shes kyi bzhugs gnas yin pas grong zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:8045: des na rten de dag la gnad du bsnun na
NK115(re)001:8046: brten pa sku gsum gyi dgongs pa tshe 'di nyid
NK115(re)001:8047: la mngon du 'gyur bas thabs rmad du byung ba'o
NK115(re)001:8048: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:8051: bkod pa byang chub kyi sems bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8052: dang po gnas pa rtsa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:8053: rtsa gtso mo gsum bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:8054: rtsa 'khor gyi rnam grangs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8055: dang po rtsa gtso mo gsum bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8056: de la kun gzhi'i rten srog rlung dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:8057: bar srid kyi rnam par shes pa khams gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:8058: skye bar sbyor ba na gling gsum du skyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:8059: mi yi lus rten thob pa rnams bar do'i rnam
NK115(re)001:8060: shes de mangla gansa su khu khrag gi dbus su
NK115(re)001:8061: zhugs te de nyid rten du 'dzina pa'i thoga ma
NK115(re)001:8062: ru rtsa khamsa grub pa'i tshul miga gnyis dang ni
NK115(re)001:8063: lte ba'i rtsa mduda de gsum po sgrog mdo ltar
NK115(re)001:8064: chagas shing / de lasa snod kyi 'jig rte chags
NK115(re)001:8065: pa'i dus dwangs ma rnams dbus su ri rgyal lhun
NK115(re)001:8066: por song ba nas rim gyis gser ri dang /
NK115(re)001:8067: snyigs ma rnams gling dang khor yug sogs su gyur
NK115(re)001:8068: pa dang tshul mthun bar rim pa bzhin lusa bskyed
NK115(re)001:8069: pa'i tshul ni khams gyi dwangas mara gyura pa yi
NK115(re)001:8070: rtsa dbu rkyang ro gsuma lus kyi dbus na ka
NK115(re)001:8071: ba lta bura gansa pa'i nanga na /
NK115(re)001:8072: phyi ru lusa ngaga yid gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:8073: nanga du nyona mongas dug gsuma dang /
NK115(re)001:8074: gasnga bar sku gsunga thugas gsum gnas pa dang snang
NK115(re)001:8075: ba sogs kyi rten byed pa'i yi ge gsuma gtso
NK115(re)001:8077: de yang so sor gnas pa'i tshul rgyud dang man
NK115(re)001:8078: ngag rang gis mthong ba rnams na'ang mi 'dra bar
NK115(re)001:8079: snang yang / rtsa gsum po'i byed las kyis mtshon na ro mar /
NK115(re)001:8080: rkyang mar +aah dbu mar h'u yig rnams gnas par bshad kyang chog par snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:8081: de la dbu ma zhes pa'i don gnas tshul gyi
NK115(re)001:8082: dbang du byas na de gnyis kyi dbus na yod
NK115(re)001:8083: pa'i phyir dang / chos nyid kyi dbang du byas
NK115(re)001:8084: na yod med gnyis ka'i mtha' dang bral ba'i bde
NK115(re)001:8085: stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo yin pas de
NK115(re)001:8087: rtsa de'i yara sna na pha las thob pa'i thig
NK115(re)001:8088: le dkar cha thabs kyi rang bzhin ham yig gi
NK115(re)001:8090: mara sna na ma las thob pa'i thig le dmar
NK115(re)001:8091: cha shes rab kyi rang bzhin a thung gi rnam
NK115(re)001:8092: par gnas pa gnyis po rim pa bzhin spyi bo
NK115(re)001:8093: tshangsa pa'i sgo dang lte 'og gasnga ba'i gansa gnyisa
NK115(re)001:8094: la zuga pa'i bar na gnyis med kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:8095: kun gzhi'i rten srog rlung gi rnam par gnas te
NK115(re)001:8097: de'i gayasa dang g.yona na rim bzhin ro ma zhes
NK115(re)001:8098: rang bzhin du bzhag na don byed mi nus pas
NK115(re)001:8099: ro dang 'dra zhing gnad du bsnun na bde ba'i
NK115(re)001:8100: ro myong bar byed pa'i rtsa dang /
NK115(re)001:8101: rkyang ma zhes rang bzhin du bzhag na gzhan dang mi 'brel bar reng bu ltar gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8102: gcud pa'i man ngag las chos nyid rtog bral gyi
NK115(re)001:8103: nyams skye bas rtog pa'i yan lag dang mi ldan
NK115(re)001:8104: par byed pa'i rtsa gnyis gnas pa'i kha dog ni
NK115(re)001:8105: rim par dkar ba dang dmar ba nyid do //
NK115(re)001:8106: bud meda nyid la thabs shes kyi rten 'brel las
NK115(re)001:8107: de gnyis go ldog tu gnas pasa rkyang ma gayasa
NK115(re)001:8108: su yod do // de gsum ni rtsa thams cad kyi phyi mo yin pas ma sgra zhugs so //
NK115(re)001:8109: byed las kyi sgo nas gzhal na ro ma nas
NK115(re)001:8110: khrag dang chu ser dang byang sems rgyu bas thig
NK115(re)001:8111: le'i las la mkhas na lus kyi las zad par
NK115(re)001:8112: byed / zas kyi zhen pa chod cing bsam gtan gyi zas kyis 'tsho //
NK115(re)001:8113: rkyang ma las 'byung ba'i dwangs ma dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:8114: kyi rlung rgyu bas rtsa'i gnad la mkhas na ngag
NK115(re)001:8115: gi las dang / gos kyi zhen pa chod /
NK115(re)001:8116: gnad du bsnun pa'i ngo bo don dam gyi dbu
NK115(re)001:8117: ma ni stong pa zang thal 'od kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:8118: can yin pas rlung gi gnad la mkhas na sems
NK115(re)001:8119: kyi las sbyong / skom gyi zhen pa dag /
NK115(re)001:8121: mthar thug mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i chos nyid 'od gsal gyi don la sbyor bar byed do //
NK115(re)001:8122: dbu ma'i mdog ni sngo skya yin la /
NK115(re)001:8123: der ro rkyang gnyis posa lte ba nas gyes te
NK115(re)001:8124: mkhal mar gcer ba sogs spyi bo'i bar luga rgyud
NK115(re)001:8125: du phan tshun bsnol zhing gcu ba'i tshul gyis mduda
NK115(re)001:8126: pa nyi shu rtsa gciga gi tshul du byas pa
NK115(re)001:8127: ni dus 'khor ye shes kyi le'ura /
NK115(re)001:8128: lu gu rgyud du bcings pa'i rtsa //
NK115(re)001:8129: srog dang thur sel gyi lam gsum //
NK115(re)001:8131: de la thur sel gyi lam gsum lcags sgrog ltar
NK115(re)001:8132: bcings pa'i rtsa las gyes pa'i rtsa chen nyer bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:8133: sna zug pa'i rtsa mdud yig 'bru'i rnam par yod
NK115(re)001:8134: pa la sku gsung thugs kyi bye brag gis gnas
NK115(re)001:8136: de rnams las byung ba'i khams nyi shu rtsa bzhi
NK115(re)001:8137: po dang bcas pa spyi bo na dz+aa lan+d+ha ra
NK115(re)001:8138: sogs nang gi yul nyer bzhi he ru ka'i gnas
NK115(re)001:8139: bcu'i bye brag tu gnas pa la sogs pa'i gnad
NK115(re)001:8140: kyis thabs khyad par can la brten nas gnad du
NK115(re)001:8141: bsnun na mthar gyis rtsa thams cad chos nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:8142: dbu mar gyur nas dwangs ma ye shes kyi sku
NK115(re)001:8143: 'grub cing phyi nang gi gnas yul thams cad rang
NK115(re)001:8144: snang gi ngo bor tha dad med par rang dbang
NK115(re)001:8145: bsgyur bar byed pa la sogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:8146: de yang rgyud sde gsar rnying 'gros mthun par yul
NK115(re)001:8147: nyer bzhi po he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang sbyar
NK115(re)001:8148: nas sa lam bgrod pa'i rim pa dang bstun na
NK115(re)001:8150: gnas dang nye ba'i gnas dang ni //
NK115(re)001:8151: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing nyid dang //
NK115(re)001:8155: dur khrod nye ba'i dur khrod nyid //
NK115(re)001:8156: 'di rnams sa ni bcu gsum yin //
NK115(re)001:8157: zhes tha ma gnyis bsnan te bcu gnyis gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:8158: de yang 'thung gcod rnam gnyis las gzhan pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:8159: dang nye gnas la bzhi bzhi dang lhag ma brgyad
NK115(re)001:8160: la gnyis gnyis sbyar bas yul nyer bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:8161: sa bcu'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:8163: gnas ni rab tu dga' ba'i sa //
NK115(re)001:8165: nye ba'i dur khrod chos kyi sprin //
NK115(re)001:8166: pha rol phyin bcu'i sa rnams la //
NK115(re)001:8168: bcu gsum pa'i tshe 'thung gcod gnyis po ye shes dang sbyor ba'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:8170: 'thung gcod dpe med ye shes te //
NK115(re)001:8171: nye ba'i 'thung gcod ye shes che //
NK115(re)001:8173: yang tha ma dur khrod gnyis po ma smos par
NK115(re)001:8174: gnas bcur byas te legs blo chos sprin gnyis 'thung
NK115(re)001:8176: ye shes gnyis gnas dang ma sbyar bar gsungs pa yang snang /
NK115(re)001:8177: de la sbas pa'i rtsa lnga snying gar gnas pa
NK115(re)001:8178: sgrib bral du gyur pas bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin
NK115(re)001:8179: pa'i sa ste 'di ltar dwangs ma rnams kyis 'khor
NK115(re)001:8180: lo so so gang ba'i 'gros kyis mthar gtsug tor
NK115(re)001:8181: mchog grub ste / der brtan pa'i skad cig tha
NK115(re)001:8182: ma la mtshan dpe'i me tog rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:8183: su mngon par byang chub pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:8184: gnyis pa rtsa 'khor gyi rnam grangs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8185: de la 'khor lo rnams brten pa'i srog shing lta bu ni dbu ma yin pas /
NK115(re)001:8186: de nyid dngos po'i gnas tshul la gtan nas med pa'ang ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:8187: gzhan du na de la gnad du bsnun pas yon tan 'byung ba yang mi rigs so //
NK115(re)001:8189: rgyungs pa kho na'ang ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:8190: de dag rags pa'i rtsa yin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8191: srog rtsar rlung zhugs pas smyo 'bogs sogs 'byung bar
NK115(re)001:8192: bshad pas dbu ma'i mtshan nyid dang 'gal ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:8193: ro // de gnyis la ma ltos pa'am ma brten pa'i dbu ma zhes pa zhig kyang med de /
NK115(re)001:8195: rlung dang shes pa rtsar brten phyir na srog pa rtsar //
NK115(re)001:8196: gcud na tha mal shes pa ngang gis 'gag pa 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:8199: thabs kyi dbu ma ni a wa d+hu t+ai zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:8200: tha mal pa rnams rgyungs pa zhes zer /
NK115(re)001:8201: shes rab kyi dbu ma ni kun 'dar ma zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:8202: tha mal du ming srog rtsa zhes zer /
NK115(re)001:8203: thabs shes dbyer med kyi dbu ma ni sgal tshigs
NK115(re)001:8204: kyi mdun srog rtsa'i rgyab na zug pa khrag dang
NK115(re)001:8205: chu ser med pa'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:8206: des na gnas pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK115(re)001:8207: chos nyid kyi dbu ma dang /
NK115(re)001:8208: don dam pa'i dbu ma gsum las /
NK115(re)001:8209: dang po ni gnas tshul gyi ngos nas srog 'dzin pa'i rtsa yin la /
NK115(re)001:8210: gnyis pa ni mtshan nyid kyi rtsa mtshan nyid bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK115(re)001:8211: 'od gsal ba'i rang bzhin thogs reg dang bral ba'i
NK115(re)001:8212: srid du lus sems dbugs gsum gyi tshogs pa yod
NK115(re)001:8213: pa de srid du yod pas med pa'ang min la
NK115(re)001:8214: / de gsum so sor gyes pa'i tshe de yang
NK115(re)001:8215: mi snang bar 'gyur bas yod pa'ang min te dper
NK115(re)001:8216: na rkyen tshogs pa de srid du 'ja' tshon snang
NK115(re)001:8217: yang tshogs pa gyes pa na mi snang ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:8218: / no // sgom dus srog rtsa'i dbus su ste /
NK115(re)001:8219: de'i rgyu mtshan kun gzhi srog rlung dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:8220: de la brten pas thams cad chos nyid du ro
NK115(re)001:8222: gsum pa ni 'bras bu'i ngo bo nyid de ngo bo med pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8223: de ltar gnas pa srog gi dbyug gu dang bcas
NK115(re)001:8224: pa'i rtsa dbu ma ro rkyang gi yan lag can
NK115(re)001:8225: la / rima pa bzhina sbyang bya dug gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:8226: sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8227: sbyangs 'bras sku gsunga thugas gsum gyi yon tan mngon du byed pa'i phyir sbyong byed lte ba /
NK115(re)001:8229: snying ga'i 'khor lo gsum bsgom par gsungs pa'i grangs sama /
NK115(re)001:8230: de bzhin du sbyang bya sgo gsum bya ba dang bcas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8232: sku gsung thugs phrin las dang bcas pa thob pa'i
NK115(re)001:8233: phyir sbyong byed de'i steng du spyi bo'i 'khor lo
NK115(re)001:8235: yang sbyang bya phung lnga dang dug lnga sbyangs nas /
NK115(re)001:8236: sbyangs 'bras sku lnga dang ye shes lnga thob phyir
NK115(re)001:8237: de'i steng gsang gnas kyi 'khor lo bsnan pa dang
NK115(re)001:8238: / yang sbyang bya dug lnga ser sna dang bcas drug dang /
NK115(re)001:8239: phung po lnga bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs nas
NK115(re)001:8240: sbyangs 'bras ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:8241: dang drug gam / phyana druga gam /
NK115(re)001:8242: sku lnga bde pa chen po'i sku dang drug thob
NK115(re)001:8243: pa'i phyir sbyong byed snga ma lnga po'i steng du
NK115(re)001:8244: gtsug tor gyi 'khor lo bsnan te drug gi grangas
NK115(re)001:8245: kyi 'khora lo so so'i rtsa 'adba rnamas phri ste
NK115(re)001:8246: gsum du byas pa nas drug gi bar du bsnana
NK115(re)001:8247: par gyura pa dang de la yi ge 'god pa
NK115(re)001:8248: la sogs pa'i rnam grangs la rgyud sde so so'i
NK115(re)001:8249: lugs mi mthun pa ni sbyang gzhi sems can gyi
NK115(re)001:8252: dbang po la sogs pa tha dad pas de sbyong
NK115(re)001:8253: byeda kyi man ngag bsgom pa'i tshula tha dad kyang
NK115(re)001:8254: / de ltar bsgoms pas rtsa 'khor de dang de'i
NK115(re)001:8255: dbus su rlung thig gi dwangs ma thim pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:8256: 'bras bu la khyad par med de lam tha dad
NK115(re)001:8257: nas gnas gcig tu sleb pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:8258: 'khor lo de rnams so so'i ming gi tha snyad
NK115(re)001:8259: 'dogs pa'i rgyu mtshan dang rtsa 'dab kyi grangs ni
NK115(re)001:8260: / lte ba'i 'khor lo ni dang po lus chags pa'i tshe de las gyes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8261: der rlung sems zhugs na sku dang zhing khams kyi
NK115(re)001:8262: snang ba tshad med pa 'char bas sprul pa'i 'khor
NK115(re)001:8264: der ni rtsa 'dab druga cu rtsa bzhi yod la /
NK115(re)001:8265: mgrina pa'i 'khor lo'i man ngag gis 'dod yon gyi
NK115(re)001:8266: snang ba ma 'gags par longs spyod pas longs spyod
NK115(re)001:8267: kyi 'khor lo zhes bya ste de la brgyad tshan
NK115(re)001:8268: gnyisa te rtsa 'dab bcu drug yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8269: snying gara rlung sems kyi dwangs ma zhugs pas bsam
NK115(re)001:8270: gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid mngon du byed pas
NK115(re)001:8271: chos kyi 'khor lo zhes bya ste de la rtsa
NK115(re)001:8272: 'adba brgyada dang / spyi bora ham yig gnas pa
NK115(re)001:8273: bde ba'i 'byung gnas yin pas bde chen gyi 'khor
NK115(re)001:8274: lo zhes bya ste rtsa 'dab suma cu rtsa gnyis
NK115(re)001:8275: 'adba brgyada dang / so // gsang gnas ni /
NK115(re)001:8276: lhan skyes kyi bde ba skyong ba'i rkyen gyi gnas
NK115(re)001:8277: yin pas bde skyong gi 'khor lo zhes te de
NK115(re)001:8278: na rtsa 'dab bduna cu rtsa gnyis yod do //
NK115(re)001:8279: de bzhina du gtsuga tor la ni rlung sems thig
NK115(re)001:8280: le dang bcas pa thim pa'i tshe snyigs ma thams
NK115(re)001:8281: cad nam mkha' ltar dwang ba'am /
NK115(re)001:8282: rags pa'i rtsa ma yin pas rtsa 'dab kyi grangs
NK115(re)001:8283: med pas nama mkha'i khamas kyi 'khora lo zhesa bya
NK115(re)001:8284: ba rnams su gragas pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:8285: gtsug tor gyi 'khor lo 'di la 'ga' zhig rtsa 'dab bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:8286: la la gsang gnas dang grangs mtshungs par smra ba'ang yod do //
NK115(re)001:8287: gzhan yang rtsa 'khora lo drug po re re'i lte ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8288: so so'i bar matshamas rnams su rlung gi 'pho ba
NK115(re)001:8289: bcu gnyis kyis rtsa gnas rnams su dkar dmar gyi
NK115(re)001:8290: dwangs ma khrid cing bkod pa'i rten 'brel las phyi
NK115(re)001:8291: rol du go la'i rlunga gi steng du nyi zla
NK115(re)001:8292: gnyis rang 'gros kyis bgrod pa'i gnas dus sbyor te
NK115(re)001:8294: de bzhina du nang gi sems can rnams las nyon
NK115(re)001:8295: gyis 'khor bar bgrod cing 'khor ba na'ang rten cinga
NK115(re)001:8296: 'brela bar 'byunga ba bcu gnyis kha brgyud de 'khor
NK115(re)001:8297: bar snang ba'i gazhi'am rtsa bar gyur pas na gnas
NK115(re)001:8298: zhes bya'o // des na rnal 'byor pas rtsa rlung
NK115(re)001:8299: gi byed pa bcings nas khamas la gnad du bsnun
NK115(re)001:8300: te ma dag pa'i rtsa gnas su 'pho ba de
NK115(re)001:8301: spangas pa'i thabs kyis ro rkyang gi lam brgyud de
NK115(re)001:8302: dbu ma'i mar sna nas bcud pa'i mas nas yar
NK115(re)001:8303: lugas ldoga gi 'grosa kyis gasnga gansa ye shesa kyi
NK115(re)001:8304: 'khora lora phyin pa dang mnyam du rlunga gi 'pho
NK115(re)001:8305: ba gciga dang rten 'brel gciga 'aggas nasa dang po'i
NK115(re)001:8306: sa yi rtogsa pa dang yon tan rnams 'achara zhing
NK115(re)001:8307: zhes bya'o // // de ltar rima pa bzhina du
NK115(re)001:8308: gtsug tor nama mkha'i khamas kyi 'khora lo'i bar du
NK115(re)001:8309: 'khor lo re dang bar mtshams rer rlung gi 'pho
NK115(re)001:8310: ba dang rten 'brela re re'i cha ldoga pasa sa
NK115(re)001:8311: ni gnyis pa sogs bcu gnyisa rab tu rdzogas pa'i
NK115(re)001:8312: mathara rlung sems thiga le dang bcas pa nama mkha'i
NK115(re)001:8313: khamsa dang 'dresa pa'i tshe 'khor ba'i rten 'brel phyi
NK115(re)001:8314: dang nang du snang ba thams cad rgyun chad nas
NK115(re)001:8315: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'i mngona para rdzogs
NK115(re)001:8316: par 'atshanga rgya bar 'gyur ba ni dang po'i sangsa
NK115(re)001:8317: rgyas dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo'i lugas so //
NK115(re)001:8318: de ltar yang dbang mdor bstan las /
NK115(re)001:8319: rten dang brten pa'i 'brel pa ni //
NK115(re)001:8321: sems kyi mi 'gyur nyid thob na //
NK115(re)001:8322: rten dang brten pa'i 'brel ba med //
NK115(re)001:8324: de yang rtsa 'khor lo drug gi rang bzhin don
NK115(re)001:8325: spyi la dmigs pa rgyud sde tha dad pa'i rdzogs
NK115(re)001:8326: rim gyi don shes pa'i phyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i
NK115(re)001:8328: rnam pa thams cad du rdzogs pa'i rim pa gang bsgom na'ang mos gus dang ldan zhing /
NK115(re)001:8329: bskyed rim gyis smin par byas shing tshogs gnyis kyis rgyud sbyangs nas rlung sems las su rung bas /
NK115(re)001:8330: gong du bshad pa de dang rnama pa'i grangas drug tu mthuna pa'i rtsa 'adba la /
NK115(re)001:8331: lam gyis sbyanga ba'i gazhir gansa shing so so'i bag
NK115(re)001:8332: chags 'dzin pa'i rigas druga gi sa bona ma rig
NK115(re)001:8333: pa gnyis las byung ba'i ma dag pa'i rlung thig
NK115(re)001:8334: dang yig 'bru'i rnam par gnas pa rnamas /
NK115(re)001:8335: sbyong byed riga pa'i rang bzhin dag pa ye shes
NK115(re)001:8336: kyi rlung dang thig le la gnad du bsnun pas
NK115(re)001:8337: rigs drug gi bag chags thams cad thul bas thub
NK115(re)001:8338: pa'am skyes bu rnama pa druga gis sbyong ste /
NK115(re)001:8340: sa bon zung gsum de bde ba //
NK115(re)001:8341: nges skyes rang rig gyur pa yis //
NK115(re)001:8342: gnyis byung 'dul bas thub par gsungs //
NK115(re)001:8344: der gnad du bsnun pas ser sna la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:8345: dag cing phyin drug gi yon tan rang bzhin gyis
NK115(re)001:8346: rdzogs par 'gyur bas 'khor lo drug gi dag pa'i
NK115(re)001:8347: rlung thig dang de bsgom pa'i man ngag rnams la
NK115(re)001:8348: pha rola tu phyin pa druga ces bya ste sbyong
NK115(re)001:8349: byed de dag gisa sbyangsa par byas pa lasa /
NK115(re)001:8350: sbyangs 'bras me long lta bu la sogs pa tha dada pa yi ye shesa rnama pa lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:8351: de thams cad kyi rang bzhin bsam gyisa mi khyab
NK115(re)001:8352: pa rang byung gi ye shes gciga dang druga 'thoba
NK115(re)001:8353: bo zhes sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:8355: de la sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi rang lugs
NK115(re)001:8356: ni 'di bzhina te snying ga na rang byung gi
NK115(re)001:8357: ye shes ye shes lnga'i rang rtsal 'gag pa med
NK115(re)001:8358: pa las rtog tshogs thams cad lhar dag pa'i rten
NK115(re)001:8359: gyi rtsa dang thig le gnas pas zhi ba'i 'khora
NK115(re)001:8360: lo dang / spyi gtsuga na zhi ba'i gting mdangs
NK115(re)001:8361: 'char ba'i gzhi'i rtsa thig gnas pas khro bo'i 'khora
NK115(re)001:8362: lo dang / lo ste / rnama pa gnyis po
NK115(re)001:8363: de la zhi khro'i lha dang rnama grangas mnyam pa'i
NK115(re)001:8364: snying gar rtsa 'adba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:8365: dung khang na lnga bcu rtsa brgyad de dam pa rigs brgya'i grangs dang mnyam par gnas so //
NK115(re)001:8366: phra ba ni bsam gyis mi khyab kyang khams dang
NK115(re)001:8367: rlung 'bab pa'i rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis
