NK115(re)001:8368: ni / 'bum lnga dang sangs rgyas thod pa la sogs pa spyi dang mthun par yod de /
NK115(re)001:8370: ro ma rkyang ma kun 'dar ma //
NK115(re)001:8371: 'khor lo so so'i dkyil dag na //
NK115(re)001:8372: ka ba'i tshul du gnas pa la //
NK115(re)001:8374: khams dang rlung ni 'bab pa yi //
NK115(re)001:8375: ye shes rtsa ni stong phrag gcig /
NK115(re)001:8376: bdun cu rtsa gnyis bsgres pa yi //
NK115(re)001:8377: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i rlung //
NK115(re)001:8380: de yang rgyud gdams ngag ltar bshad pa'i dbang du
NK115(re)001:8381: byas na rtsa rgyud le'u bzhi pa nas nyer gcig
NK115(re)001:8382: pa yan chad kyis bstan pa'i thabas lam dang grola
NK115(re)001:8383: lam gnyis bsgom pa'i man ngag bkral ba ni grol
NK115(re)001:8384: lam bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa zhi
NK115(re)001:8385: khro so so'i sgrub thabs ltar yin la /
NK115(re)001:8386: thabs lam la stenga sgo rnam grol gyi lam dang /
NK115(re)001:8387: 'oga sgo khams gsum rol pa'i lam gyi sgo gnyis
NK115(re)001:8388: su yod pa las dang po steng sgo la'ang 'khor
NK115(re)001:8389: lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor ba
NK115(re)001:8391: man ngag bzhi la bslab tshul gnyis su yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:8392: dang po ni sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las /
NK115(re)001:8393: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK115(re)001:8394: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK115(re)001:8395: gzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK115(re)001:8396: zhes spyi mgrin snying ga lte ba'i 'khor lo bzhi
NK115(re)001:8397: gsal btab nas byed pa bcings pas sgrom mdo rlung
NK115(re)001:8399: sum mdo me'i 'khor lo'i sbar te dbu mar gyen
NK115(re)001:8400: du song bas 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le zhu ba
NK115(re)001:8401: las byung ba'i thabs kyis so so'i dwangs ma zin
NK115(re)001:8402: cing dga' bzhi dang 'brel ba'i ye shes rgyud la
NK115(re)001:8403: skyes pa la thun mong gi lam zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:8404: man ngag bzhi la bslab pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8405: kun tu bzang po'i man ngag snying la /
NK115(re)001:8406: bde chen thig le'i man ngag lte bar /
NK115(re)001:8407: sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag mgrin par /
NK115(re)001:8408: khyab gdal chen po'i man ngag spyi bo'i 'khor lor
NK115(re)001:8409: bsgom pa'i tshul rtsa rgyud le'u bcu gsum par bstan
NK115(re)001:8410: pa ltar bsgoms pas 'khor lo bzhi'i lte ba'i dwangs
NK115(re)001:8411: ma g.yo byed dang bral ba'i 'od gsal la dwangs
NK115(re)001:8412: ma'i dwangs ma rnams thim pas mchog tu mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:8413: ba'i 'od gsal sku bzhi'i dgongs pa ji bzhin pa
NK115(re)001:8414: 'char ba'o // 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:8415: la nam mkha'i rdo rje'i lam zhes kyang bya ste
NK115(re)001:8416: 'char ba'o // / dang po ltar na gsang ba'i
NK115(re)001:8417: yul dbang shes pa'i khams gsum la brten nas rtog
NK115(re)001:8418: tshogs thams cad rang grol te bde ba chen po'i
NK115(re)001:8419: ye shes la rol pa'i phyir de skad smos la
NK115(re)001:8422: rdo rje ni thabs te thabs shes gnyis med phyag
NK115(re)001:8423: rgya bzhis rol pas rnam smin gyi lus la lhan
NK115(re)001:8424: cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyis rgyas thebs pas tha
NK115(re)001:8425: mal gyi 'dod chags su rtog pa'i bdud bcom /
NK115(re)001:8426: bde ba'i ye shes kyi rtsi rgyas /
NK115(re)001:8428: khams 'dzag med kyis 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo bcom /
NK115(re)001:8429: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su gyur pas mya ngan las 'da' ba'o //
NK115(re)001:8430: de ltar gnyis su med pa zung 'jug gi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:8431: rim zab mo'i thabs la brten nas phyogs bcu'i bde
NK115(re)001:8432: bar gshegs pa rnams kyi 'bras chos lnga'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:8433: 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa dus gcig la mngon du
NK115(re)001:8434: gyur par 'doda pa'i rgyud thams cad kyi 'phro gzhir
NK115(re)001:8435: gyur zhing man ngag thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:8436: rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrula d+r+wa ba'i
NK115(re)001:8438: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK115(re)001:8439: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK115(re)001:8440: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong zhing //
NK115(re)001:8441: dbang bsgyur mchog nyid dam pa yin //
NK115(re)001:8443: gnyis pa g.yo ba rlung bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:8447: dang po phyi'i rlung bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8448: g.yo ba rlung gi rang bzhin ji ltar rgyu ba'i tshul la /
NK115(re)001:8449: 'byung ba sa chu me rlung gi rlung che ba
NK115(re)001:8450: dang chunga ba gnyis su rgyu ba las che ba
NK115(re)001:8451: ni rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis po gsum
NK115(re)001:8452: du bsgres pa'i 'gyur 'byung ba bzhi so so'i rlung
NK115(re)001:8453: la lnga stong bzhi brgya po'i 'gyur tshad bsdoms pas
NK115(re)001:8454: skyes bu dar la babs pa nad kyi skyon dang
NK115(re)001:8455: bral ba zhig la nyin zhaga phrugas gciga daga la
NK115(re)001:8456: ni nyi khri chiga stonga drug brgya'i grangas su 'gyu
NK115(re)001:8458: rtsa la brten pa'i rlung dag ni //
NK115(re)001:8459: nyi khri dang ni stong phrag gcig /
NK115(re)001:8460: drug brgya dag tu 'gyu ba ni //
NK115(re)001:8463: de la rgas pa rnams la ni 'byung ba'i gral
NK115(re)001:8464: nyams pas lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyis ma tshang la
NK115(re)001:8465: / 'byung ba ma rgyas pa'i gzhon nu rnams la ni sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis ma tshang ngo //
NK115(re)001:8466: 'byung ba chunga ba'i rlung ni kuna tu rtog pa
NK115(re)001:8467: can gtso che ba'i nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi
NK115(re)001:8468: stong gi grangas dang manyama pa'i rtog pa de dag
NK115(re)001:8469: gi bzhona pa lta bura rgyun mi 'chad par gansa
NK115(re)001:8471: gzhan ni bzhi stong brgyad khri'o //
NK115(re)001:8473: de yang kha sna nas 'gyu ba ma gtogs rtsa'i
NK115(re)001:8474: nang na rtog pa dang ye shes kyi rten du
NK115(re)001:8475: 'gyu ba'i rlung longs spyod 'khor lo las gyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:8476: 'phar rtsa nas 'gyu ba rnams bsdoms pas chig 'bum
NK115(re)001:8477: nyi khri drug stong drug brgya nang du 'gyu bar
NK115(re)001:8478: gsungs so // 'byung ba che chung gi rlung thams
NK115(re)001:8479: cad kyi rtsa bar gyur ba'i rlunga ni sroga 'dzina
NK115(re)001:8480: gsungs so // gyi rlung dang / me mnyam gyi rlung dang /
NK115(re)001:8483: thura sela gyi rlung dang lngara gansa pa'i /
NK115(re)001:8484: byed lasa ni rima pa bzhina du srog 'dzin ni
NK115(re)001:8485: snying ga na gnas te sroga brten par byed do
NK115(re)001:8486: // me mnyam ni lto ba na gnas te droda bskyed par byed do //
NK115(re)001:8487: khyab byed ni lus byings na gnas te lusa nyamsa brtasa par byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8488: gyen rgyus dbugsa kyi 'gro 'onga gi bya ba byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8489: thur sel gyis ni 'gro 'dug dang bashanga gci sdom pa dang 'phena pa'i bya ba byed la /
NK115(re)001:8490: de'ang pho rlunga gyena rgyu ni stoda na gansa la /
NK115(re)001:8491: mo rlunga thura sela ni smada na gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8492: ma ninga gi rlung gzhan gsum ni stod smad mnyam par gnas pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:8493: sna nas rgyu ba'i gnas skabs na /
NK115(re)001:8496: mnyam par ma ning gi rlung rgyu ba yin zhing de dag ni phyi'i rlung ste rags pa'i cha'o //
NK115(re)001:8497: gnyis pa nang gi rlung bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8498: snga ma de dag las phra zhing nanga gi byed
NK115(re)001:8499: pa gtso che ba'i rlunga ni sa rlung ser po
NK115(re)001:8503: nam mkha'i rlung mthing ga ste 'byunga ba lnga'i rang
NK115(re)001:8504: bzhin kha doga kyang 'byung ba so so dang mthun
NK115(re)001:8506: bsgom tshul gyi dbang du byas na dbyibs kyang rim pa bzhin gru bzhi /
NK115(re)001:8511: gnas ni snying ga'i rtsa 'khor na gnas par bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8512: rtsa 'khor lnga ga'i dbus na yod par bshad pa sogs tha dad do //
NK115(re)001:8513: byed las ni nang gi phung po khamas dang skye
NK115(re)001:8514: mched thams cad rlung de dag las rlung gi rang
NK115(re)001:8515: bzhin du gnas shing ma thim pa de srid du
NK115(re)001:8516: snang zhing gansa pa'i rten byed la /
NK115(re)001:8517: 'chi srid sogs kyi dus de dag thim pas phung
NK115(re)001:8518: sogs re zhig mi snang bar 'gyur yang ye rlung
NK115(re)001:8519: gi ngo bo gtan du ma dag pas slar yang
NK115(re)001:8520: rlung de dag langs pas rim gyis bar srid dang
NK115(re)001:8521: phyi ma'i skye srid kyis bsdus pa'i phung sogs phyi
NK115(re)001:8522: nang gi chos thams cad snang bar 'gyur bas na
NK115(re)001:8523: 'khor ba ji srid du 'khrul snang gi rten byed
NK115(re)001:8524: do // sems dang ye shes kyi rten byed tshul
NK115(re)001:8525: bye brag tu bshad na 'di ltar ma dag pa
NK115(re)001:8526: sems kyi gnas skabs na rlung lnga po de'i nyon
NK115(re)001:8527: mongs pa duga lnga rang rang gi rkyen nye bar
NK115(re)001:8528: gnas pa'i tshe rtsol ba med par mched par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:8530: dag pa ye shes kyi dus su ji lta ba
NK115(re)001:8531: dang ji snyed pa'i shes bya thams cad la mngon
NK115(re)001:8532: sum pa'i ye shesa rnama pa lnga po snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:8533: gzhi yin pas na rlung lnga rgyu lta bu las
NK115(re)001:8534: sems dang ye shes 'brasa bu lta bur mcheda pa'i
NK115(re)001:8535: rten byeda do zhes brjod kyang ngo bo tha dad
NK115(re)001:8536: pa med de shel las 'ja' tshon bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:8537: de dag rgyu tshul gyi dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:8541: dpyid sa'i rlung rgyu bas de'i gnyen po go ldog nas bsgom pa'am /
NK115(re)001:8542: yang na kun la shes pa nam mkha'i rlung 'ba' zhig gam /
NK115(re)001:8543: nad khams dang bstun nas gang 'phrod bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8544: de dag sna nas rgyu tshul gyis gsum du bsdu ba sngar dang 'dra zhing /
NK115(re)001:8545: gsum po 'byung lnga'i rlung gi nges pas dus bzhi'i 'pho dus la sbyar te /
NK115(re)001:8547: bud med kyis pho rlung dang /
NK115(re)001:8548: gnyis kas ma ning gi rlung la gtso bor sbyangs
NK115(re)001:8549: na gsang ba ye shes kyi rlung lnga 'byongs bar
NK115(re)001:8552: mnyam gnas gsum gyi gnad las /
NK115(re)001:8555: bar rlung bskyil ba gsum gyi gnad la mkhas par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:8556: gzhan yang mda' ltar 'phang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8558: bum pa can du bskyil ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8559: chu srin chings su bsdam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8560: ri bo ltar mnan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8561: sbubs chu ltar bsdu ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8562: rtsa gnas su dgram pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8563: rang gnas su gzhil ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8564: nam mkha' ltar chos nyid du khyab par gdal ba'i gnad dgu la mkhas par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:8565: de'ang rlung gi rang bzhin ni gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:8566: las dang ye shes kyi rlung ngo //
NK115(re)001:8567: gnyis po de shes pa'i gdangs dang rtsa nas 'gyu ba'i rlung tsam du gcig kyang /
NK115(re)001:8568: gnad du bsnun pa dang ma bsnun pa dang lam
NK115(re)001:8569: du song ma song gi ngos nas ye shes dang
NK115(re)001:8571: des na rlung gi sbyor ba la bslab par byas
NK115(re)001:8572: na spyir khams las su rung ba la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:8573: yon tan dang / khyad para du 'byung ba dwangas
NK115(re)001:8574: ma'i rlung lnga po rlung sems kyi byed pa gcig
NK115(re)001:8575: tu bcings pa'i thabs kyis d+h+au t+ai ste dbu mar
NK115(re)001:8576: chud pa na rlung lnga las su rung ba'i rtags
NK115(re)001:8578: g.yas rlung dbu mar chud pas du ba lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:8579: g.yon rlung chud pas smig rgyu /
NK115(re)001:8581: chu rlung las sprin dang mthongs khong gi zla 'od lta bu /
NK115(re)001:8582: sa rlung las gser gyi kha dog lta bu dang glog lta bu /
NK115(re)001:8583: nam mkha'i rlung las dang po mthing ga dang de nas 'od lnga'i thig le /
NK115(re)001:8584: thams cad dbu mar las su rung ba las 'od lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:8587: lha sku la sogs pa du ma 'char zhing /
NK115(re)001:8588: khyad par du zada para sa chu me rlunga nama
NK115(re)001:8589: mkha'a yi tinga nge 'dzina grub nas dngos po thams
NK115(re)001:8590: cad sa la sogs par bsgyur ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK115(re)001:8591: bkod pa ston nus pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8592: nyon mongs lnga dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8594: zhing khams lngar bgrod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:8595: ye shes lnga mngon du 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:8596: yon tana dang rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs pa 'gruba par
NK115(re)001:8598: rlung lnga'i dwangs ma stobs gyur na //
NK115(re)001:8599: 'od lnga nang gi ye shes lnga //
NK115(re)001:8600: sku lnga bgrod pa'i zhing khams lnga //
NK115(re)001:8603: gsum pa gsang ba'i rlung bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8604: shin tu phra zhing rtogs dka' ba'i gasnga ba'i rlunga
NK115(re)001:8605: ni chos nyid don gyi ye shesa rnama pa lnga
NK115(re)001:8606: yi rang bzhin can yin pa'i phyir dbyibs dang kha
NK115(re)001:8607: dog la sogs pa'i ragas pa'i chosa dang rnama pa
NK115(re)001:8609: gong du bshad pa'i nang gi rlung lnga dbu mar
NK115(re)001:8610: zhugs te phyi nang gsang ba'i rlung thams cad dbyer
NK115(re)001:8613: ngo bo spros pa dang bral /
NK115(re)001:8614: 'gyu dran ye shes su dengs pa'i tshe lhag mthong
NK115(re)001:8615: rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin chos nyid 'od
NK115(re)001:8616: gsal ba'i dgongs pa mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:8617: gsum pa bkod pa byang chub kyi sems bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8618: de la gsuma pa rnam par shes pa'i rten du
NK115(re)001:8619: gyur pa'i khams dwangs ma chen po khu rdul gnyis
NK115(re)001:8621: de yang rlung gis rtsa gnas rnams su bkoda pa'i
NK115(re)001:8622: byanga chuba semas kyi khamas ji ltar 'babs pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:8623: ni ro ma'i yar sna lasa ni spyi bo'i ham
NK115(re)001:8624: yig gi rgyun zla ba'i bduda rtsi ste khams dkar
NK115(re)001:8625: cha 'bab cing de las lus kyi cha thams cad
NK115(re)001:8627: rkyang ma'i mar sna lasa ni gsang gnas kyi a
NK115(re)001:8628: shad las nyi ma'i rdula te khams dmar cha mched
NK115(re)001:8629: de rtsa gnas thams cad du 'abba cinga khyab par
NK115(re)001:8630: 'gyur la / thabs shes kyi rten 'brel gyis pho yi shes rab kyi rtsa rkyanga ma dang /
NK115(re)001:8631: mo yi thabs kyi rtsa ro ma'i sna gnyis po
NK115(re)001:8632: mduda para gyur pasa pho rnams la khamas dmar po
NK115(re)001:8633: dang / mo rnams la dkar po gnyis po phyir 'adzaga pa bsrung ste mi 'apho'o //
NK115(re)001:8634: ro rkyang du rgyu ba de lasa gazhana du de
NK115(re)001:8635: gnyis po lasa mcheda para gyur ba'i 'khor lo so
NK115(re)001:8636: so'i rtsa 'dab sogs rtsa mduda yi ge'i rnam par
NK115(re)001:8637: yod pa'i yul nyer bzhi'i rang bzhin du brjod pa
NK115(re)001:8638: la sogs pa kuna na khams kyi dwangsa ma dakara
NK115(re)001:8639: cha thabs dang damra cha shes rab kyi ngo bor
NK115(re)001:8640: gnas pa gnyisa dapa'a bo yab dang ni rnala 'byor
NK115(re)001:8641: ma de'i yum gyi tshula du zhes snang stong gnyis
NK115(re)001:8642: su med pa'i sems kyi rtsal mdangs thabs shes dbyer
NK115(re)001:8643: med kyi ngo bor bzhugs nas 'khrila zhing sbyor basa
NK115(re)001:8644: zhu bde'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK115(re)001:8645: las bde stong gnyis su med pa'i mchoda pa len
NK115(re)001:8646: pas tshogs gnyis myur du rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:8648: khu ba'i rnam pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK115(re)001:8649: de yi bde ba 'dod mar brjod //
NK115(re)001:8653: kha sbyor gnyis su med pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:8655: de yang 'khor ba'i rtsa ba 'dzag bde yin pas
NK115(re)001:8656: de'i rang bzhin 'pho med du 'ching ba'i bsam pas
NK115(re)001:8657: yid nang du chud pa las so so rang rig
NK115(re)001:8658: pa'i ye shes kyis zhu bde'i mtshan nyid la rgyas
NK115(re)001:8659: thebs nas 'khor gsum yongs dag gi tshogs su sbyor
NK115(re)001:8660: ba ni de kho na nyid kyi mchod pas mnyes
NK115(re)001:8663: ji bzhin shes rab snyoms zhugs pa'i //
NK115(re)001:8664: yang dag sbyor dang ldan pa yis //
NK115(re)001:8665: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor dkar //
NK115(re)001:8666: yid nang chud pa de yis spyad //
NK115(re)001:8667: mchog tu dga' ba spro ba yi //
NK115(re)001:8668: gnas skabs su ni mnyes par bya //
NK115(re)001:8670: gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:8671: de dag gi gnas tshul dang de la gnad du bsnun pa'i tshul mdora bsdusa te brjod na /
NK115(re)001:8672: rtsa gnad du 'gro ba la lus gnad /
NK115(re)001:8674: thig le gnad du 'gro ba la rtsol ba gal che ba ni spyir gces la /
NK115(re)001:8675: bye brag tu lus kyi rten gansa pa rtsa ni
NK115(re)001:8676: zhing sar chu 'khrid pa'i lam yura ba dang 'dra
NK115(re)001:8677: ste rlung rgyu ba'i lam yin pas srog rtsol la
NK115(re)001:8678: brten nas rtsa lam sbyang bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:8679: ngag gi rten g.yo ba rlunga ni 'khor 'das gnyis
NK115(re)001:8680: kar 'gro ba dang 'onga ba'i kha lo ba lta
NK115(re)001:8681: bu yin pas 'khor ba'i byed pa bcing ba'i thabs
NK115(re)001:8683: yid kyi rten byanga chuba semsa kyi thig le ni
NK115(re)001:8684: rlung gi gnad la brten na chu dang 'dra bar
NK115(re)001:8685: khrida sara 'du zhing don dam byang chub sems kyi
NK115(re)001:8686: rten yang yin pas rnam pas 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK115(re)001:8687: ye shes kyi rlung dang lhan cig gtsug tor gyi
NK115(re)001:8689: ji ltar na lus bsrangs pas rtsa drang //
NK115(re)001:8691: de las chos nyid mthong bar 'gyur bas /
NK115(re)001:8692: lus kyi gnad rnam snang chos bdun nam /
NK115(re)001:8693: rtsa rlung bsgom pa'i man ngag rnams nas gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:8694: bzhin lus kyi gnad legs par bcos te ma 'phyug
NK115(re)001:8695: na rlung dang rnam rtog g.yo med du gyur nas
NK115(re)001:8697: de nas rtsa gsum 'khor lo dang bcas pa gsal gdab par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:8698: de yang 'khora lo druga po steng 'og tu brtsegas pa'i srog shing lta bu dbu ma ste /
NK115(re)001:8699: de la chos nyid kyi dbu ma ni yod la rdzas su ma grub pas sgra gcan te /
NK115(re)001:8700: phyi snang ba'i sgra gcan gyi gdong mjug gnyis kyis nyi zla za ba ltar /
NK115(re)001:8701: nang du dkar dmar gyi rang bzhin a ham gnyis
NK115(re)001:8702: dbu ma'i yas mar gyi sna rtser gnas pa'i 'bar
NK115(re)001:8703: 'dzag gi ting 'dzin goms pa las dbu mar rlung
NK115(re)001:8704: zhugs gnas thim gsum gyi bya ba byed cing /
NK115(re)001:8705: nyi ma dang zla ba'i rang bzhin khams dkar dmar
NK115(re)001:8706: gnyis rgyun mi 'chad du dbu ma'i dbyings su 'bab
NK115(re)001:8707: par bsgom pa'i byed bcing la nus pa thob na
NK115(re)001:8708: phyi rol tu nyi zla gzas 'dzin par mi nus
NK115(re)001:8709: shing / gtod la gnon pa sogs nus pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8710: de ji ltar bsgom pa'i man ngag la mang yang 'dir gtum mo ye shes kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK115(re)001:8711: bde chen chos nyid kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK115(re)001:8712: rtsa sbyong bogs 'byin 'khor lo gsum du dbye ba ltar na /
NK115(re)001:8714: rta gdong gi mes rgya mtsho za ba ltar /
NK115(re)001:8715: a shad las byung ba'i mes phung khams ma lus
NK115(re)001:8716: za bar byed pas na gtum mo zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:8717: / de'i man ngag gi dbu ma sgra gacana gyi
NK115(re)001:8718: dbyingas su sroga ces pa rlung dang rtsola ba ni
NK115(re)001:8719: / sems te / de gnyis dbyer med du bcing
NK115(re)001:8720: ba'i shinga rtas'khor lo so so'i gnas na rgyu ba'i
NK115(re)001:8721: rlung rim gyis drangas pa lasa a shad las me
NK115(re)001:8722: 'bar te spyi bo'i ham yig thur bstan la reg
NK115(re)001:8723: pas bdud rtsi babs te dbu ma'i nang thams cad
NK115(re)001:8724: gang nas bde ba skyes pa'i ngang la dar cig
NK115(re)001:8725: / sems te / glod / de nas dbu ma'i
NK115(re)001:8726: yas mar gyi sna gnyis nas dkar dmar gnyis zhugs
NK115(re)001:8727: pa snying gar 'dres pa'i e wam zung 'jug bde
NK115(re)001:8728: gsal gnyis su med pa'i ngang bskyang /
NK115(re)001:8729: de nas 'od lnga'i thig le shin tu phra ba
NK115(re)001:8730: la sems gtad nas mthar mi rtog pa'i ngang la
NK115(re)001:8733: rtag tu snying la gang gnas pa'i //
NK115(re)001:8734: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK115(re)001:8735: de bsgom byed pa'i skyes bu la //
NK115(re)001:8736: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:8738: gnyis pa ni gtum mo 'bar tshul 'dra ba las /
NK115(re)001:8740: spyi bo'i bam yig 'dres pa'i gong bu sran ma
NK115(re)001:8741: tsam la sems bzung nas mthar mi dmigs par bsgom
NK115(re)001:8742: mo // gsum pa ni chags bral rnams rlung khams
NK115(re)001:8743: gnyis dus mnyam par zung du 'jug pas lte bar
NK115(re)001:8744: me rlung e'i rnam pas ham yig zhu nas dbu
NK115(re)001:8745: ma dang 'khor lo thams cad khyab pa'i rlung sems
NK115(re)001:8746: kyi thig le dkar po thur du babs pa dang
NK115(re)001:8747: dmar po gyen 'gro gnyis snying gar 'dres pa'i gnyug
NK115(re)001:8748: ma lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes spros bral du
NK115(re)001:8749: 'char ba'i ngang la glod pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:8750: chags ldan rnams yab yum sbyor ba'i dga' bzhi'i mthar spros bral du 'jog pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8751: thabs der grub pa'i 'bras bu ni bde gsal mi
NK115(re)001:8752: rtog pa'i nyams las 'das pa'i rang bzhin spros pa
NK115(re)001:8753: dang bral ba'i 'od gsal ba'i ye shes te /
NK115(re)001:8755: bsgom pa med pa sgom pa'i dngos //
NK115(re)001:8756: bsgom pa nyid ni sgom pa min //
NK115(re)001:8757: de ltar dngos dang dngos med pas //
NK115(re)001:8758: bsgom pa dmigs su med pa'o //
NK115(re)001:8760: de yang spyir rtsa rlung thig le la gnad du bsnun nas goms pa'i stobs dang /
NK115(re)001:8761: tshogs gnyis rlabs po che gong du 'phel ba'i mthu dang /
NK115(re)001:8762: 'chi ba'i dus gsum por dbu mar rlung zhugs te
NK115(re)001:8763: snang mched thob gsum gyi mthar 'od gsal 'char bar
NK115(re)001:8764: 'gyur ba las / de lta bu'i man ngag bsgoms
NK115(re)001:8765: pa'i stobs kyis 'khor lo so so'i rlung sems las
NK115(re)001:8766: su rung bas tshogs sbyor gyi lam mthar phyin te
NK115(re)001:8767: rim gyis 'phags pa'i sa la sbyor par 'gyur te
NK115(re)001:8768: sprul pa'i 'khor lor rlung sems las su rung bas
NK115(re)001:8770: ting nge 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul thob pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:8771: pa'i tshogs lam gyi yon tan mngon du 'gyur zhing
NK115(re)001:8772: / snang ba lhar 'char bas lus dran pa nyer bzhag dang /
NK115(re)001:8773: tshor ba bde chen du grol bas tshor ba dran nye dang /
NK115(re)001:8774: sems dang sems byung rags pa zhi bas sems dran nye dang /
NK115(re)001:8775: snang btags kyi chos thams cad rang bzhin med par
NK115(re)001:8776: shes pas chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa ste
NK115(re)001:8777: tshogs lam chung ngu'i rtogs pa'i yon tan 'byung bas
NK115(re)001:8778: mtshon byang chos so bdun gyi yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:8779: lam rang rang gi skabs su skye ba'i tshul shes
NK115(re)001:8780: par bya la / rlung sems 'byongs nas rim gyis dbu ma'i mduda pa gnyis gnyisa grola ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8781: rlung dang khamsa kyi dwangsa ma rnama pa gnyis re
NK115(re)001:8782: sgra gacana gyi ltor zhugas pa dang mnyam du dang
NK115(re)001:8783: po'i sa yi rtogs pa dang yon tan thams cad
NK115(re)001:8784: mngon du 'gyur pa nasa bzunga sa bcu'i yona tan
NK115(re)001:8785: thams cad gong nas gonga du 'phel te thams cad
NK115(re)001:8786: kyi tha ma rtsa mdud nyer gcig pa grol ba'i
NK115(re)001:8787: tshe rlung sems kyi dwangs ma thig le dang bcas
NK115(re)001:8788: pa gtsug tora du 'gro zhing rdo rje 'chang 'grub
NK115(re)001:8789: pa'i tshul / nges brjod rtse mo las /
NK115(re)001:8790: ro ma rkyang ma kun 'dar ma //
NK115(re)001:8791: mdud pa grol ba'i 'khrul snang ste //
NK115(re)001:8792: grol bas ye shes mya ngan 'das //
NK115(re)001:8794: gnyis pa sgyu 'phrul gsang thig gi lugs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:8795: de ltar sngags rgyud 'gyur snga phyi'i rdzogs rim rnams spyir bshad nas /
NK115(re)001:8796: khyad para du snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sde thams cad
NK115(re)001:8797: kyi rtsa ba rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrula d+r+wa
NK115(re)001:8798: ba'i don slob dpon chen po bi ma la'i gasnga
NK115(re)001:8799: thiga gis bkral ba'i lugas mdo tsam bstan pa'i don
NK115(re)001:8800: ni / phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang po rlung la brten nas chu chags /
NK115(re)001:8802: sa las drod 'byung zhing shing dang lcags la sogs
NK115(re)001:8803: pa me'i rgyur song ba las 'byung bzhi'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:8805: rlung sems dwangs mar 'dus pa khrag gi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:8806: chus gcig tu bsdus pa las sems can gyi lus
NK115(re)001:8807: su chags te de yang sa'i rang bzhin sha /
NK115(re)001:8808: de las me'i rang bzhin lus kyi drod skyes nas dbang po dang /
NK115(re)001:8810: mes rlung bskyed pas dbugs dang bkrag mdangs rgyas par byed cing /
NK115(re)001:8811: phyi nang gi 'byung ba de dag bag la nyal
NK115(re)001:8812: dang kun nas ldang ba'i las kyis brtan g.yo chags
NK115(re)001:8813: gnas 'jig stongs byed pa dang mthun par nang lus
NK115(re)001:8814: sems kyi tshogs pa'ang 'byung ba so so'i byed las
NK115(re)001:8815: kyis skye rga na 'chi byed pas snod bcud kyi
NK115(re)001:8816: rang bzhin ni ranga gi lus sems la rdzogas pa
NK115(re)001:8817: yin la / dus kyi 'khor lo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:8820: gzhan chos nyid kyi dbyings zhes rten 'grel gnad mtshungs par sbyor bas na /
NK115(re)001:8821: lus la brten nas 'byung ba la gnad du bsnun
NK115(re)001:8822: pa'i rten 'brel gyis sems chos skur grol bar byed
NK115(re)001:8823: pa ni rdzogs rim gyi thabs mkhas yin pas /
NK115(re)001:8824: rgyud sde 'di'i man ngag ni 'di ltar phyi rol
NK115(re)001:8825: du bskal ba bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis
NK115(re)001:8826: 'dzam bu'i gling gi yul dbus ma ga d+ha'am rdo
NK115(re)001:8827: rje'i gdan du mngon par sangs rgyas shing rgya bar
NK115(re)001:8828: 'gyur ba bzhin / rdo rje phunga po'i grong khyer
NK115(re)001:8829: gyi dbus ni rang bzhin rnam par dag pa chos
NK115(re)001:8832: 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da lta ba'i
NK115(re)001:8833: dusa gsuma car du lunga du ma bstan pa'i sems
NK115(re)001:8834: kyi chos nyid ni bde gshegas snying po ste /
NK115(re)001:8836: sems la ni dus med do //
NK115(re)001:8837: dus gsum dang bral ba gang yin pa de ni ngo bo nyid kyi mtshan ma dang bral ba'o //
NK115(re)001:8839: ye shes kyi snang ba chen po rang gsal bas mi g.yo ba'i dus te zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:8841: 'od srung sems dang chos kyi de bzhin nyid ni
NK115(re)001:8842: gang nas kyang ma 'ong gang du yang ma song
NK115(re)001:8843: / gar yang mi gnas pas na ma nges pa ste bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK115(re)001:8846: dus gsum dus med rtogs pa po //
NK115(re)001:8848: de lta bu'i sems kyi rang bzhin bde bar gshegs
NK115(re)001:8849: pa'i snying po'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin mngon
NK115(re)001:8850: du gyur pa kho nas dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:8851: matha'a daga mngona par rdzogs par sangs rgyas shing /
NK115(re)001:8853: de nyid mngon du byed pa'i thabs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK115(re)001:8854: ba chen po'i lugs 'dir 'khor 'das skyed sdud kyi
NK115(re)001:8855: sa bon snying ga na gnas pa la gnad du
NK115(re)001:8857: de yang mi phyed pa'am mi 'gyur ba'i don gyis rdo rje'i gadna dang /
NK115(re)001:8858: dbyings zab pas snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la dapala gyi be'u zhes smos nas /
NK115(re)001:8859: de'i khongas senga na 'khrul snang dang /
NK115(re)001:8860: ye shes skyed byed rtsa yi dwangas ma brgyad du
NK115(re)001:8861: gansa pa'i dbus na sbyang gzhi sbyong byed ltar gnas
NK115(re)001:8862: pa'i sa bon la gnad du bsnun pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:8863: slob dpon bi ma la'i gsang thig las /
NK115(re)001:8864: gang la yod pa rnam pa brgyad du shes //
NK115(re)001:8867: gang la yod na snying khong stong gi dkyil na
NK115(re)001:8868: rtsa'i dwangs ma rtsa phran rgyus pa bldad pa 'dra
NK115(re)001:8873: gcig yon tan gyi rtsa ste de ltar brgyad du shes par bya'o zhes so //
NK115(re)001:8874: de dag lasa dbus ma gsuma ni sku gsuma dang chosa nyid mi 'gyur ba'i rten yin la /
NK115(re)001:8875: de'i mduna ma na yod pa'i rtsa gciga ni ye
NK115(re)001:8876: shesa gzhi 'achara bar 'gyur ba'i rten gyi rtsa yin
NK115(re)001:8877: zhing / rgyab na ni yona tan gyi rtsa gnas
NK115(re)001:8878: pa lasa zhing khamas dang gzhal yas khang la sogs
NK115(re)001:8879: pa dag pa'i snang ba mu med par 'char ro
NK115(re)001:8880: zhing / // g.yona na ranga rgyud pa'i rtsa gsum
NK115(re)001:8881: dug gsum dang khams gsum rang mtshan pa'i 'khrula snanga
NK115(re)001:8882: mtha' dag 'char ba'i rtena te de ltar gnas tshul
NK115(re)001:8883: la brgyad yod kyang byed las ni bzhi po nyid
NK115(re)001:8884: zhing / // de / snga ma las kyang /
NK115(re)001:8885: rnam bzhi bye brag drug dang brgyad dkyil na //
NK115(re)001:8887: rtsa bzhi po so so'i dbus na 'khora ba dang
NK115(re)001:8888: mya ngan las 'adsa pa'i yiga 'bru dang rnam shes
NK115(re)001:8889: tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa ni sbyang gzhi dang sbyonga
NK115(re)001:8890: byeda kyi tshula du gansa pa yin te 'di ltar
NK115(re)001:8891: chos nyid kyi rtsa 'od snang ser la zlum pa'i
NK115(re)001:8892: rnam pa can gyi dkyil na lha min dang byol
NK115(re)001:8893: song gi sa bon su dang tri'i steng du sku
NK115(re)001:8894: rdo rje'i snying po rang 'od za 'og gi gur
NK115(re)001:8895: khang lta bur gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8896: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa gnas so //
NK115(re)001:8897: ye shes kyi rtsa mthing ga gru bzhi pa'i sbubs
NK115(re)001:8898: na lha dang mi'i sa bon a dang n+ri dkar
NK115(re)001:8899: dmar gyi steng na thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin h'u
NK115(re)001:8900: mthing ga dang / yid kyi shes pa gnas so //
NK115(re)001:8901: rang rgyud pa'i rtsa dmar po zla gam gyi dkyil
NK115(re)001:8902: na dmyal ba dang yi dwags kyi sa bon pre
NK115(re)001:8903: dang du'i steng na gsung rdo rje'i rang bzhin +aahyiga
NK115(re)001:8904: pad+ma r+aa ga ltar 'tsher ba dang /
NK115(re)001:8905: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gnas so //
NK115(re)001:8906: yon tan gyi rtsa dmar nag gru gsum gyi dbus na sgo lnga'i shes pa gnas so //
NK115(re)001:8907: de ltar gnas pa'i dwangs ma rgyu tshul ni 'od
NK115(re)001:8908: ser po rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar gyi skud pa
NK115(re)001:8910: mthing ga dbugs kyi dwangs ma la'o //
NK115(re)001:8911: dmar po khrag gi dwangs ma la'o //
NK115(re)001:8912: dmar nag sgo lnga'i rtsa'i dwangs ma la rgyu ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:8913: rigs drug gi sa bon rnams kyang rang rang gnas
NK115(re)001:8914: pa'i 'od gang la rgyu ba de'i snyigs ma la
NK115(re)001:8915: rgyu'o // des na 'khor ba'i gnas ris drug por
NK115(re)001:8916: 'phen pa'i las kyi bag chags ni sbyang bya'i yig
NK115(re)001:8917: 'bru drug po rang rang gi steng du bsogs nas
NK115(re)001:8918: de dang de'i 'khrul pa'i snang ba bskyed la /
NK115(re)001:8919: thar pa'i 'bras bu thob byed sgo gsum gyi dge ba spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:8920: bye brag rdo rje gsum gyi lam byed rnams ni
NK115(re)001:8921: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge'i steng du bzhag nas
NK115(re)001:8922: lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan snang bar 'gyur zhing
NK115(re)001:8923: / khyad par sbyang gzhi dang sbyong byed kyi yig
NK115(re)001:8924: 'bru rnams dngos su gsal btab nas de la gnad
NK115(re)001:8925: du bsnun pa'i rdzogs rim dang 'bru gsum gyi bzlas
NK115(re)001:8926: pa sogs byas pas sku gsunga thugas kyi yi ge
NK115(re)001:8927: rnams stobs 'phel bas 'khor ba'i sa bon gyi yi
NK115(re)001:8928: / ge dang / des bzung ba'i bag chags thams
NK115(re)001:8929: cad dag ste rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub thob
NK115(re)001:8930: / ge dang / par byed do // snying ga'i
NK115(re)001:8931: rtsa 'dab kuna gyi dbus na dwangs ma lnga 'dus
NK115(re)001:8933: rtsa brgyad po'i dbus ma ni rgyud sde gzhan ltar na yang dag pa'i dbu ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:8934: dbu ma'i rlung gi dwangs ma yang ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:8935: rtsa la 'jug dgos pas dwangsa ma'i 'od rtsa dakara
NK115(re)001:8936: po shel dkar gyi skud pa lta bu phra ba'i
NK115(re)001:8937: cha nas rta rnga'i bcu cha tsam du phra ba'i
NK115(re)001:8938: nanga na rdula te khrag dang dbugas kyi dwangas ma
NK115(re)001:8939: 'dresa pa la brten pa'i rlung sems shin tu phra
NK115(re)001:8940: ba'i snang cha ma 'gags pa'i gdangs 'od kyi thig
NK115(re)001:8941: le ye shes kyi rang 'od kha doga lnga ldana
NK115(re)001:8942: shina tu phra ba nyid yod la /
NK115(re)001:8943: de yang 'byung ba lnga ka'i dwangs ma yin te
NK115(re)001:8944: sa'i dwangs ma ni dar dkar gyi skud pa lta
NK115(re)001:8945: bu'o // chu'i dwangs ma ni khrag gi rang bzhin rgya mtshal gyi khu ba lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:8946: me'i dwangs ma ni me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad lta bu'i drod do //
NK115(re)001:8947: rlung gi dwangs ma ni gser sa 'og na yod pa'i rlangs lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:8948: nam mkha'i dwangs ma ni go 'byed pa'i cha tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:8949: de rnams ni rnam par shes pa'i chos nyid ranga
NK115(re)001:8950: bzhina gyis 'oda gasla zhing 'dus ma byas pa'i byanga
NK115(re)001:8951: chuba semsa kyi rten yin te /
NK115(re)001:8952: bshad rgyud rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:8953: snying ga'i pad+mo'i sbubs mkha' la //
NK115(re)001:8954: ye shes rdo rje rtag tu bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:8955: gtso bo chen po mi bskyod pa'i //
NK115(re)001:8956: 'jig rten khams ni de nyid do //
NK115(re)001:8958: rgyu mtshan de bas na snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK115(re)001:8959: rig pa'i ye shes snang stong gnyis su med pa kuna bazanga yab yum dang /
NK115(re)001:8960: de'i gdangs ye shes lnga'i ngo bor ma 'gags pa
NK115(re)001:8961: ni rigas lnga ste bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:8962: nyid de la rang gi ngo bo'i rten dang brten
NK115(re)001:8963: pa med na'ang tha snyad du de la brten pa
NK115(re)001:8964: ltar yod pas bzhugas pa'i gazhala meda khanga zhes bya
NK115(re)001:8965: la / snying ga'i 'khor lo'i dbus ganga du rdzogs
NK115(re)001:8966: rim gyi thabs zab mo la brten nas rlunga semas
NK115(re)001:8967: kyi dwangs ma rnams 'dusa pa'i tshe na mya ngana
NK115(re)001:8968: las 'adsa pa'i ye shes kyi rang gdangs zhing dang
NK115(re)001:8969: gzhal yas khang dang sku dang 'od zer dang /
NK115(re)001:8970: ye shes dang yon tan gyi snang ba matha'a daga lam dus su'ang 'char la /
NK115(re)001:8971: mthar thug snang cha'i 'oda lnga po'i rtsal las rlung
NK115(re)001:8972: gis bslad de phung khams skye mched ma dag pa'i
NK115(re)001:8973: chos su snang pa'i cha thams cad dang bral ba
NK115(re)001:8974: na rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i stong pa
NK115(re)001:8975: nyid kyi cha'i chosa kyi sku mngon du gyur te
NK115(re)001:8976: / de gnyis don la dbyer med pas gcig tu
NK115(re)001:8977: 'dre ba med kyang 'khrul ba'i snang ba bag chags
NK115(re)001:8978: dang bcas pa thams cad dbyings su ldog nas snang
NK115(re)001:8979: stong ro gciga tu 'dresa pasa lam gyi tshogas gnyis
NK115(re)001:8981: chos sku skye med kyi dbyings su mngon par sangs
NK115(re)001:8982: rgyas nas chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par sku dang
NK115(re)001:8983: ye shes kyi snang ba 'byams klas par snang ba
NK115(re)001:8984: yin pas na / rgyas pa las /
NK115(re)001:8985: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK115(re)001:8986: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK115(re)001:8987: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK115(re)001:8988: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK115(re)001:8990: sangs rgyas rnams mngon par 'tshang rgya ba'i gnas 'oga
NK115(re)001:8991: mina rnama par daga pa tshad dang bkod pa mtha'
NK115(re)001:8992: yas pas brgyan pa'i zhing khams stug po bkoda pa
NK115(re)001:8993: zhesa bya ba de khams gsum gyi gnas 'di las
NK115(re)001:8994: sam rang gi sems nyid las gazhana du gnas rang
NK115(re)001:8995: mtshan pa zhig mi gansa te /
NK115(re)001:8996: dbyings la sgriba para byed pa ni dri ma rlung
NK115(re)001:8997: sems ma dag pa'i cha matha'a daga ba nama zhiga
NK115(re)001:8998: spangas par gyur pa'i dusa der ye shes kyi rang
NK115(re)001:8999: snang du lhuna gyisa gruba par 'gyur ba yin no
NK115(re)001:9000: // de yi phyira na lusa 'di ni rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:9001: ye shesa 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:9002: thams cad kyi chos nyid khyab gdal chena po'i rten
NK115(re)001:9003: yin pas 'di la gnad du bsnun na mya ngan
NK115(re)001:9004: las 'das pa 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rang gi
NK115(re)001:9006: ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams ni de'i ngang du 'khor bar 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:9008: 'di dag ni bdag med pa yin mod kyi /
NK115(re)001:9009: 'on kyang byis pa so so'i skye bo bdag tu 'dzin pa la zhen pa dag ni /
NK115(re)001:9010: bdag gi phung po rnams la bdag yod do zhes
NK115(re)001:9011: mngon par zhen pas de kho na nyid khong du
NK115(re)001:9012: mi chud do // khong du ma chud pas mgal
NK115(re)001:9013: me'i 'khor lo ltar 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyam mo
NK115(re)001:9014: mi chud do // zhes so // de ltar 'khora
NK115(re)001:9015: zhing 'khrul ba'i dus nyid na'ang sems nyid rang gi
NK115(re)001:9016: ngo bo'i bzhugas tshula rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK115(re)001:9017: cing sku dang ye shes kyi chos thams cad ma
NK115(re)001:9018: tshang ba med par lhun gyis grub pa la nyamsa
NK115(re)001:9019: te grangs nyung bar gyur nas 'bras bu'i chos ma
NK115(re)001:9020: mi chud do // zhes so // tshang ba dang
NK115(re)001:9021: / damna de rang bzhin zhan para gyura pa gnyis
NK115(re)001:9022: ka med de dper na dngul chu thal ba'i gseb
NK115(re)001:9023: tu lhung yang de dang mi 'dre ba bzhin no
NK115(re)001:9024: mi chud do // zhes so // tshang ba dang / // de skad du'ang gsang 'dus las /
NK115(re)001:9025: rin chen sems las phyir gyur ba'i //
NK115(re)001:9026: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK115(re)001:9029: sems kyi dam pa 'od gsal ba //
NK115(re)001:9030: kun tu dang po'i sangs rgyas te //
NK115(re)001:9031: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ba //
NK115(re)001:9032: ye nas nyid ni gnas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9034: de'i rang bzhin ting nge 'dzin la brten nas mngon du 'gyur ba'i tshul yang /
NK115(re)001:9035: stug po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:9036: ji ltar shin tu bzang po'i gser //
NK115(re)001:9037: gser gyi dbyibs la mi snang ste //
NK115(re)001:9038: btsal nas shin tu zhib btags nas //
NK115(re)001:9039: yongs su sbyangs na snang bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:9040: de bzhin kun gzhi'i rnam par shes //
NK115(re)001:9041: rnam shes bdun dang bcas pa yang //
NK115(re)001:9042: ting nge 'dzin gyis yongs sbyangs pa'i //
NK115(re)001:9043: rnal 'byor can gyis rtag tu mthong //
NK115(re)001:9045: de'i rang bzhin thos bsam gyis rjes su dpag ste yid ches pa tsam las /
NK115(re)001:9046: ji bzhin par shes pa ni /
NK115(re)001:9047: dad pa dang bsgom pa'i rkyen la rag las te /
NK115(re)001:9049: sh+aa ri'i bu don dam pa ni dad pas rtogs pa kho na yin no //
NK115(re)001:9050: zhes pa la sog pa gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9051: de lta bu'i 'gyur ba meda pa'i chos nyid dona
NK115(re)001:9052: dama byang chuba kyi semsa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK115(re)001:9053: po de ni 'jag ma'i srin bu yan chad sems
NK115(re)001:9054: rgyud kyis bsdus so cog thams cad la ma khyab
NK115(re)001:9055: pa med de / dper na til yin no cog
NK115(re)001:9056: thams cad la mara gyisa khyab pa ji lta ba
NK115(re)001:9057: pa med de / bzhina no // tshul de ni /
NK115(re)001:9058: sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:9059: nges don gyi mdo sde dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa rnams las gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:9062: yun ring dus nas rmongs pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK115(re)001:9063: ye nas don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK115(re)001:9064: rmongs pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyams //
NK115(re)001:9065: log rtog nyid nas dngos med byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:9066: 'khrul 'khor nyid kyang mi zad rgyan du che //
NK115(re)001:9067: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas su gsal //
NK115(re)001:9068: phung po lnga nyid mngon par rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK115(re)001:9069: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs byang chub snying por gsal //
NK115(re)001:9070: phyi nang snod bcud yab yum ngang du gsal //
NK115(re)001:9073: gang zhig bdag dang sangs rgyas rnams //
NK115(re)001:9074: rang bzhin mnyam par rab gnas shing //
NK115(re)001:9075: mi gnas len pa med pa de //
NK115(re)001:9076: de dag de bzhin gshegs par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:9079: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK115(re)001:9080: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:9081: zhes pa la sogs pa dpag tu med do //
NK115(re)001:9082: des na zab mo'i don nyams su len par 'dod
NK115(re)001:9083: pa rnams kyis ni tshul 'di la som nyi za
NK115(re)001:9084: bar mi bya'o // gnyis pa rdzogs rim dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:9087: dang po rang lus thabs ldan ni /
NK115(re)001:9088: de ltar rten rdo rje'i lusa kyi rtsa rlung thig le la sogs pa'i gansa lugas dang /
NK115(re)001:9089: brten pa sems kyi rang bzhin gdoda ma nas gnas
NK115(re)001:9090: pa'i chos nyid gzhi yi bzhugas tshula dag shesa par
NK115(re)001:9091: byasa nasa rdzogs rim zab mo'i man ngag la brten
NK115(re)001:9092: te / rten la gnad du bsnun pas brten pa'i
NK115(re)001:9093: ye shes myur du mngon du 'gyur par 'dod pas
NK115(re)001:9094: gsar rnying gi rgyud sde rnams nas ji snyed cig
NK115(re)001:9095: bstan pa'i rdzogs rim gyi man ngag thams cad chos
NK115(re)001:9096: drug po 'dir ma 'dus pa med pas 'di rnams
NK115(re)001:9097: shes par byas nas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9099: rdzogs rim gyi lam thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni gtum mo yin te /
NK115(re)001:9100: thabs kyi cha snang ba thams cad shes rab skye ba med pa'i ngang du dag dgos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9101: de'i thabs zab mo ni thabs shes kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:9102: dkar dmar gyi 'du 'phrod las phung khams skye mched
NK115(re)001:9103: kyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos thams cad bde stong
NK115(re)001:9104: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngang du dag
NK115(re)001:9105: par byed pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9106: lam gyi gzhi ma ni sgyu lusa yin te dag
NK115(re)001:9107: bdag gi chos thams cad rang bzhin med par shes
NK115(re)001:9108: pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin ma goms
NK115(re)001:9109: na dngos po zhen pa dang bcas pa'i lam gyis
NK115(re)001:9110: grol mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9111: lam gyi drod tshad ni nying 'khrul rmi lam gyi lam la sbyang ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:9114: bar do la sogs par grol nus mi nus kyi
NK115(re)001:9115: tshad ni rmi lam 'od gsal du bsdu ba dang
NK115(re)001:9116: / sgyu mar sbyong ba la sogs pa nus mi
NK115(re)001:9117: nus kyis shes pas de la bslab dgos pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:9118: / ro // lam gyi snying po ni 'oda gasla
NK115(re)001:9119: yin te bsgom par bya ba dang don du gnyer
NK115(re)001:9120: bar bya ba'i don po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9121: lam gyi sun ma ni bar do yin te lam
NK115(re)001:9122: gyi nyams len 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i mtshams sbyor
NK115(re)001:9123: gyi rkyen yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9124: lam gyi blo chod ni 'pho ba yin te tshe
NK115(re)001:9125: 'dir le lo la sogs pas lam mthar ma phyin
NK115(re)001:9126: pa'am / glo bur du 'chi rkyen byung ba la
NK115(re)001:9127: sogs pa'i tshe man ngag gi thabs kyis btsan thabs
NK115(re)001:9128: su rnam shes dag pa'i zhing la sogs par 'pho
NK115(re)001:9129: bar byas nas lam gyi 'phro mthud dgos pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:9130: pa'am / ro // des na de dag tu 'dus pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:9131: rnama pa druga po de ni skyesa bu gang gis
NK115(re)001:9132: lam bsgom pa'i rtsola ba dang bcas pasa rang gi
NK115(re)001:9133: lus kyi rtsa rlung thig le sems dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:9134: la gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs kho nas 'grub kyis
NK115(re)001:9135: gazhana phyag rgya'i lus kyi rkyen la raga ma lusa
NK115(re)001:9136: pa'i phyir ranga lus thabas ldan nam steng sgo rnam
NK115(re)001:9137: par grol byed kyi lam zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9138: de la dang po lam gyi rtsa ba gtum mo la /
NK115(re)001:9142: dang po las kyi gtum mo ni /
NK115(re)001:9143: lus kyi byed pa bcings te chos bdun g.yo med du byed pa /
NK115(re)001:9144: ngag gi byed pa bcings te rlung kha sbyor du 'ching ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9145: sems kyi byed pa bcings te gtum mo 'bar 'dzag bsgom pa sogs so //
NK115(re)001:9146: nyams kyi gtum mo ni de ltar bsgoms pas rlung
NK115(re)001:9147: sems dbu mar 'dus pa'i rtags su du ba smig
NK115(re)001:9148: rgyu me khyer la sogs pa snang zhing sems bde
NK115(re)001:9151: rlung sems 'du tshul las snang ba gsum gyis drangs
NK115(re)001:9152: pa'i 'od gsal mngon du gyur nas rnam par mi
NK115(re)001:9153: rtog pa mchog gi gtum mo rgyud la skye ba'o
NK115(re)001:9154: // gnyis pa lam gyi gzhi ma sgyu lus la'ang /
NK115(re)001:9157: sbas don rlung sems kyi sgyu lus so //
NK115(re)001:9158: dang po ma dag sgyu lus ni /
NK115(re)001:9159: phyi nang gi snang ba thams cad sgyu ma dang rmi lam ltar bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9160: dag pa'i sgyu lus ni snang ba thams cad lha sku sgyu ma ltar bsgom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9161: sbas don rlung sems kyi sgyu lus ni /
NK115(re)001:9162: de ltar snang ba lhar bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9163: de nyid 'od gsal du 'jug pa'i bsdu rim gnyis
NK115(re)001:9164: ka spel nas goms pas bsdu rim gyi tshe tha
NK115(re)001:9165: mal gyi lus rags pa'i 'dzin pa dang bral nas
NK115(re)001:9166: / rlung sems tsam las grub pa'i sgyu ma lta
NK115(re)001:9167: bu'i lha skur langs pa de nyid rang ngo la
NK115(re)001:9168: rtag par snang zhing gzhan snang du sngar gyi lus
NK115(re)001:9169: rags pa de nyid mi snang ba ste de'i tshe
NK115(re)001:9170: sgyu lus grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9171: gsum pa lam gyi drod tshad rmi lam ni /
NK115(re)001:9172: sgyu lus kyi yan lag ste /
NK115(re)001:9173: dang po 'dun stobs dang rlung stobs gang rung gis
NK115(re)001:9174: rmi lam bzung nas rmi lam la rmi lam du
NK115(re)001:9176: de nas rmi lam gyi snang ba sprul bsgyur byed
NK115(re)001:9177: pa dang rmi lam bzung nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK115(re)001:9178: dang sems can gyi gnas la sogs pa nyul ba
NK115(re)001:9179: dang / 'jigs skrag gi gnas me dang chu dang
NK115(re)001:9180: g.yang sa la sogs pa la thog bardzisa bya ba
NK115(re)001:9181: dang / dang / mthar rmi lam gyi snang ba
NK115(re)001:9182: thams cad lha dang gzhal yas khang gi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:9183: du bltas nas sgyu mar sbyong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9184: mthar sgyu ma'i lha sku yang bsdu rim gyis bsdus
NK115(re)001:9185: nas 'od gsal du 'jug pa ste mthar rmi lam
NK115(re)001:9186: dbyings su nub pa'i thabs la slob pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9187: bzhi pa lam gyi snying po 'od gsal ni /
NK115(re)001:9188: sngar sgyu lus kyi skabs kyi sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:9189: lha sku de yang bsdu rim gyis 'od gsal du
NK115(re)001:9190: bsdu ba dang / gtum mo rang lus dang gzhan
NK115(re)001:9191: lus phyag rgya'i lam gang rung la brten nas dga'
NK115(re)001:9192: bzhi lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes sogs la goms
NK115(re)001:9193: bsdu ba dang / pa las / stong pa bzhi'am
NK115(re)001:9194: dga' ba bzhis drangs pa'i 'od gsal rgyud la skye
NK115(re)001:9195: bsdu ba dang / pa las / ba'o // de yang stong pa bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:9196: dang po rnam shes snang ba la thim pa'i skabs su zhe sdang gi rtog pa so gsum 'gags /
NK115(re)001:9197: phyi rtags su ston gnam zla 'od kyis bslad pa ltar dkar lam pa'i snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9198: nang rtags su gsal ba'i nyams mtha' dbus med par 'char te stong pa zhes bya /
NK115(re)001:9199: de nas snang ba mched pa la thim pas 'dod chags kyi rtog pa bzhi bcu 'gags /
NK115(re)001:9200: phyi rtags su ston gnam nyi 'od kyis bslad pa lta bu'i dmar lam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9201: nang rtags su bde ba mu mtha' med par 'char te stong pa chen po zhes bya /
NK115(re)001:9202: de nas mched pa nyer thob la thim pas gti mug gi rtog pa bdun 'gags //
NK115(re)001:9203: phyi rtags su ston gnam smag gis bslad pa lta bu'i nag lam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9204: nang rtags su rnam par mi rtog pa'i nyams mtha'
NK115(re)001:9205: dbus med par 'char te shin tu stong pa zhes
NK115(re)001:9206: bya / de nas nye thob 'od gsal la thim pa zhes zer yang /
NK115(re)001:9207: don du sngar nyer thob kyi skabs kyi mi rtog
NK115(re)001:9208: pa de nyid cung zad sangs nas rang bzhin gzhir
NK115(re)001:9209: gnas kyi 'od gsal don dam lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:9210: ye shes bcos min du shar ba ni ston gyi
NK115(re)001:9211: dus su tho rangs kyi nam mkha' bslad byed kyi
NK115(re)001:9212: rkyen gsum dang bral ba lta bu ste thams cad
NK115(re)001:9214: de dag gi skabs su bshad pa'i zhe sdang gi rtog pa so gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:9215: yul mi 'dod pa'i rnam pa can la shas chung ngu 'dod chags dang bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9216: 'bring 'dod chags dang bral ba bar ma dang /
NK115(re)001:9217: chen po shin tu 'dod chags dang bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9218: nang gi yul la tshur 'jug pa gang yid kyi 'ong dag dang /
NK115(re)001:9219: phyi'i yul la phar 'gro ba yid kyi 'gro ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9220: yul gyi rjes su song ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9221: yul yid du 'ong ba dang bral ba'i sems kyis gdung ba chung ngu mya ngan dang /
NK115(re)001:9223: chen po shin tu mya ngan dang /
NK115(re)001:9224: sems zhi bar gnas pa'am yang na sems rnal du 'dug pas dal ba zhi ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9225: rgod par gnas pa'am yang na sems rtsing par rtog pa /
NK115(re)001:9227: yul yid du mi 'ong ba dang phrad nas sems skrag pa chung ngu 'jig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9229: chen po shin tu 'jigs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9230: yul la zhen pa tha ma sred pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9232: rab shin tu sred pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9233: 'dod yon gyi yul rnams la kun tu 'dzin pa nye bar len pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9234: dge ba'i las la yid gnyis za ba'am yang na rang gi sems mi gsod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9238: bde sdug btang snyoms gsum la yul gyi sgo nas chung ngu tshor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9240: chen po shin tu tshor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9245: rig bya'i las te de gsum la rtog pa gsum du gsungs pa ltar na /
NK115(re)001:9246: gong gi song ba zhes pa mi bgrangs /
NK115(re)001:9248: rig pa dang rig bya gnyis la rtog pa gnyis su byas nas song ba bgrangs pa yin nam /
NK115(re)001:9250: rigs pa dang mi rigs pa dpyod pa /
NK115(re)001:9252: rang ngam chos rgyu mtshan du byas nas kha na ma tho ba la 'dzem pa /
NK115(re)001:9254: sdug bsngal dang bral bar 'dod pa /
NK115(re)001:9256: dmigs bya yongs su bsrung ba dang sdug pa dang phrad par 'dod pa ste gsum la /
NK115(re)001:9259: yid 'phrig pa'i sems nges par mi gnas pa dogs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9260: yo byad sdud pa'i sems sdud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9261: 'di la bsags pa zhes pa'ang snang ste 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:9262: yo byad kun tu 'dzin pa'i sems ser sna rnams so //
NK115(re)001:9263: 'di la phrag dog ces 'byung ba ltar na gzhan gyi phun tshogs la sems 'khrug pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9264: 'dod chags kyi rtog pa bzhi bcu ni /
NK115(re)001:9265: 'di la zhen pa zhes thob pa'i yul la yid chags par gsungs pa 'dod chags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9266: ma thob pa'i yul la yid chags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9267: yid du 'ong ba mthong nas sems dga' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9270: chen po shin tu dga' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9271: 'dod don 'grub pas bde ba'i sems pa rangs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9272: de'i rnam pa sems kyis yang dang yang du myong ba rab tu mgu ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9273: gtam sna tshogs pas ci 'di yin nam min snyam du the tshom za ba'am /
NK115(re)001:9274: yang na sngar ma byung ba'i don la sems pa mtho ba ngo mtshar ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9275: yid du 'ong ba mthong nas sems g.yeng ba rgod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9276: bde ba'i rnam pa myong ba'am yang na yul des ngoms pa'i rtog pa tshim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9280: ste de rnams bya bar 'dod pa'i sems gsum /
NK115(re)001:9281: rgyud mi 'gyur ba'i sems brtan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9282: dge ba la gzhol ba brtson pa dang mtho bar sems pa khengs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9283: bya ba rdzogs par byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9287: dge ba'i lam la goms par byed pa'i sems spro ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9288: dregs pa'i dbang gis mi dge ba spyod pa'am yang
NK115(re)001:9289: na yul la 'bad pas sbyong ba chung ngu tsham
NK115(re)001:9291: 'bring tsham tshom med pa bar ma dang /
NK115(re)001:9292: chen po shin tu tsham tshom med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9293: rgyu med par yang dam pa rnams dang rtsod 'dod pa dregs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9294: yid 'ong mthong bas 'gying ba'am rtse bar 'dod pa rnam par sgeg pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9295: 'khon du 'dzin pa'i sems zhe 'gras pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9296: dge ba'i las la rtsol bar 'dod pa dge ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9297: gzhan gyis go bar smra 'dod pa tshigs gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9298: 'du shes ma bsgyur bar smra 'dod pa bden pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9299: 'du shes bsgyur te smra 'dod pa mi bden pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9300: yid dam shin tu brtan pa nges pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9301: yul yongs su 'dzin par mi 'dod pa nye bar mi len pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9302: bdog pa gtor bar 'dod pa sbyin pa po nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:9303: gzhan le lo can skul bar 'dod pa brtul ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9304: nyon mongs sogs kyi dgra las rgyal bar 'dod pa dpa' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9305: bdag gam chos kyi dbang du byas nas mi 'dzem par mi dge ba bcu la 'jug pa /
NK115(re)001:9307: bcos mas gzhan bslu ba g.yo can dang /
NK115(re)001:9309: lta ba ngan pa la byang ba gdug pa can dang /
NK115(re)001:9310: gzhan la mtho 'tsham pa mi srun pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9311: rgyud mi drang ba gya gyu che ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:9312: gti mug gi rtog pa bdun ni /
NK115(re)001:9313: don du gnyer bya'i ngo bo ji bzhin du mi shes pa 'dod chags bar ma dang /
NK115(re)001:9314: dran pa nyams pa brjed nges dang /
NK115(re)001:9315: smig rgyu la chur 'dzin pa sogs 'khrul ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9316: smra snying mi 'dod pa mi smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9317: yid sun pa skyo ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9318: dge ba la mi spro ba le lo dang /
NK115(re)001:9319: bden pa rnams la yid gnyis za ba'am /
NK115(re)001:9320: yang na las 'bras dang chos nyid la yid gnyis za ba /
NK115(re)001:9324: yang na dga' ba bzhis drangs pa'i 'od gsal gang
NK115(re)001:9325: yin kyang 'dra ste de la 'od gsal tsam du
NK115(re)001:9326: 'dra yang / dpe don gyi 'od gsal du ma dang /
NK115(re)001:9327: dpe'i 'od gsal la yang mchog dman gyi rim pa du ma yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:9328: des na mthong lam ma skyes tshun chad du dpe'i 'od gsal yin la /
NK115(re)001:9329: mthong lam gyi bden pa mthong ba ni don gyi 'od gsal yin te /
NK115(re)001:9330: de yan chad don gyi 'od gsal la 'gyur ba med do //
NK115(re)001:9331: 'chi dus kyi thim rim rdzogs pa'i mtha' dang /
NK115(re)001:9332: gnyid dus sogs su 'od gsal shar ba ni gzhi'i 'od gsal yin la /
NK115(re)001:9333: rnal 'byor pas lam goms pa'i stobs kyis de nyid
NK115(re)001:9334: ngo shes par byas nas dpe don gyi 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:9336: lnga pa lam gyi sun ma bar do ni /
NK115(re)001:9337: rab 'byung 'khrug 'chi kha'i bar do la snang gsum
NK115(re)001:9338: gyis drangs pa'i gzhi'i 'od gsal 'char ba'i tshe sngar
NK115(re)001:9339: 'dris kyi gdeng la brten nas ngos bzung ste 'od
NK115(re)001:9340: gsal chos sku'i ngang du grol lo //
NK115(re)001:9341: 'bring snang mun srid pa'i bar dor sgyu lus la brten nas sgyu ma lta bu'i lha skur ldang /
NK115(re)001:9342: tha ma sred len skye gnas kyi bar dor mngal sgo bzang po 'dam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9343: mngal sgo ngan pa 'gegs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9344: dag pa'i zhing khams su 'phen pa gtod pa sogs
NK115(re)001:9345: kyis gsang sngags kyi chos la spyod pa'i snod rung
NK115(re)001:9346: du skyes nas lam gyi 'phro mthud pa'o /
NK115(re)001:9347: drug pa lam gyi blo chod 'pho ba ni /
NK115(re)001:9348: gang zag rab tshe 'dir lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9349: grub mtha' snyogs pa yin na 'pho ba mi dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:9351: lam sbyangs pa dman na 'pho bas bsu /
NK115(re)001:9352: zhes gsungs pa ltar lam gyi sbyang bgrod dman pa
NK115(re)001:9353: dag gis 'chi ltas brtags pas 'chi bar nges shing
NK115(re)001:9355: thim rim ma byung gong du sngar bshad pa'i 'od kyis gong bus 'pho ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9356: sgra yis 'pho ba sogs kyis rnam shes dag pa'i zhing du 'pho ba'o //
NK115(re)001:9357: gnyis pa gzhan lus thabs ldan ni /
NK115(re)001:9359: byed bcings nyin mtshan rnal 'byor so nam bya //
NK115(re)001:9360: rtsa ni yur ba 'dra ste byang bar dgos //
NK115(re)001:9361: byang sems chu 'dra khrid sar 'ong ba dgos //
NK115(re)001:9362: rlung ni khron skyogs 'dra ste skyon med dgos //
NK115(re)001:9363: de ltar rtsa rlung 'byongs nas rjes chags su //
NK115(re)001:9364: 'dod chags chen po bde chen nam mkha' gang //
NK115(re)001:9365: zhes pa ltar rang lus thabs ldan la brten nas
NK115(re)001:9366: rtsa drang thiga le gnas su 'chun rlunga byang ste
NK115(re)001:9367: gsum ga la ganda du songa nasa las su rung
NK115(re)001:9368: bar gyur pa na slar yang bde stonga lhan cig
NK115(re)001:9369: skyes pa'i ye shes cig car du ngo 'phrod nas
NK115(re)001:9370: 'phags pa'i lam du sbyor bar byed pa ni gazhana
NK115(re)001:9371: lusa thabs ldan nam 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i
NK115(re)001:9372: lam phyag rgya la bsten pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:9374: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan ma //
NK115(re)001:9375: stong nyid shes rab mdzes ma nyid //
NK115(re)001:9376: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK115(re)001:9379: des na rgyu'i theg pa'i sde snod gsum du nyon
NK115(re)001:9380: mongs pa'i 'byung gnas su bstan pa'i bud med ni
NK115(re)001:9381: 'dir stong pa nyid kyi 'byung gnas rgyal ba bskyed
NK115(re)001:9382: pa'i yum mam shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK115(re)001:9383: ma'i rang bzhin du bltas te thabs la mkhas pas
NK115(re)001:9384: bsten na mchog gi dngos grub la myur du sbyor
NK115(re)001:9385: bar 'gyur zhing / de yang bsten bya rgyud nas
NK115(re)001:9386: gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid tshang ba rigs lnga'i rigs can
NK115(re)001:9387: bar 'gyur zhing / gyi mi mo'am / khyad par
NK115(re)001:9388: don gyi 'od gsal thob pa'i lhan skyes ma dang
NK115(re)001:9389: bar 'gyur zhing / gyi mi mo'am / / dbang
NK115(re)001:9390: dang bskyed rim gyis rgyud sbyangs pa'i sngags bskyed ma
NK115(re)001:9391: bar 'gyur zhing / gyi mi mo'am / / dang
NK115(re)001:9392: / yul nyer bzhi la sogs par skyes pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:9393: skyes ma ni dngos grub myur te bsten pa tsam
NK115(re)001:9394: gyi thabs dang shes rab tu 'brel ba'i rten 'brel
NK115(re)001:9395: las sgrib pa'i sa bon rlung khug pa gcig 'gags
NK115(re)001:9396: nas 'gyur ba med pa'i bde chen ster zhing /
NK115(re)001:9397: mthar gyis nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i 'gyu ba
NK115(re)001:9398: 'pho ba gcig tu thub nas lam gyi yon tan
NK115(re)001:9399: mtha' dag pa btsan thabs su 'phel ba'o //
NK115(re)001:9400: de ltar bsten rung gi phyag rgya gang yang rung
NK115(re)001:9401: ba la 'du shes gsum gyis bsten nas dbab gzung
NK115(re)001:9402: ldog khyab kyi man ngag bzhi la mkhas par byas
NK115(re)001:9403: na lam gyi yon tan thams cad rdzogs par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:9404: te / thig le rim gyis spyi bo nas mgrin pa /
NK115(re)001:9407: gsang ba'i gnas te bzhir babs pa na dbang bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:9408: ye shes kyi ngo bo dga' ba bzhi nyams su
NK115(re)001:9409: myong / sad pa la sogs pa'i gnas skabs bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:9410: sgo gsum dang bag chags kyi cha 'dzin pa'i thig le dang /
NK115(re)001:9411: sgo gsum dang cha mnyam gyi sgrib pa rnams dag
NK115(re)001:9412: ste nyams dang bral ba'i 'od gsal gyi dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:9413: nyams su myong zhing rdo rje'i bum par 'dzag med
NK115(re)001:9414: du bzung la slar yang ldog pa'i man ngag gis
NK115(re)001:9415: gtsug tor gyi rtser bskyil zhing /
NK115(re)001:9416: rlung dang 'khrul 'khor gyis lus gnas thams cad la khyab par dgram par byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9417: khyad par dbyings rig dbyer med kyi lta bas 'grems
NK115(re)001:9418: pa ni mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK115(re)001:9419: po'o // phyi ma 'di gsum la 'dzin 'dren dgram gsum gyi man ngag zhes kyang zer ro //
NK115(re)001:9420: de ltar byas pas rtsa thams cad chos nyid kyi dbu mar gyur nas dbyings kyi ngo bor dag /
NK115(re)001:9421: rlung sems thig le dang bcas pa thams cad rig
NK115(re)001:9422: pa'i ye shes chen por ro gcig tu gyur nas
NK115(re)001:9423: dbyings rig dbyer med kyi dgongs pa'i ngang du rgyu
NK115(re)001:9424: 'bras kyi lam thams cad rdzogs par 'gyur bas na
NK115(re)001:9425: 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba kun gyi gzhi rtsa
NK115(re)001:9426: rlung thig le thams cad kyanga 'od gsal chen por
NK115(re)001:9427: grol ba'i lam du 'gro bas thabs smad du byung
NK115(re)001:9428: ba ni thabs kyi lam cig car ba'am gzhan lus
NK115(re)001:9429: phyag rgya'i lam 'di nyid yin no zhes pa'am /
NK115(re)001:9430: yang na bskyed rim la brten nas sbyor lam gyi
NK115(re)001:9431: matha'i bar du phyin pa la sogs pas kyang nye
NK115(re)001:9432: rgyu' spyod pa phyag rgya la bsten nas zag med
NK115(re)001:9433: kyi lam la sbyor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9434: rang lus thabs ldan gyi rdzogs rim goms pa rnams
NK115(re)001:9435: kyi yang 'bogs 'dod na bsten pas na bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:9436: kuna kyanga yang dag pa'i lam du 'gro ba thabas
NK115(re)001:9437: kyi lam khyad par ba 'di yid no zhes pa'o
NK115(re)001:9438: // gnyis pa snang med kyi rdzogs rim bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:9439: de ltar snang ba dang bcas pa'i rdzogs rim la
NK115(re)001:9440: goms par byas pa de yang gnyis pa spros bral
NK115(re)001:9441: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes snanga ba meda
NK115(re)001:9442: pa'i rdzogas rima du dag par byed dgos pas de'i
NK115(re)001:9443: tshul ni / mtshan ma zhal phyag la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:9444: rnama para gyura pa'i bskyed rim dang rdzogas rim gyi
NK115(re)001:9445: lha ganga yina na yanga mthar dmigs med du 'jog
NK115(re)001:9446: tshul ni / pa ste / de yang ma dag
NK115(re)001:9447: pa'i dngos zhen sbyangs te daga par bsgoms pa'i snoda
NK115(re)001:9448: bcuda kyi dngos po thams cad zhing dang gzhal yas
NK115(re)001:9449: khang dang lha dang lha mo la sogs pa'i rang
NK115(re)001:9450: bzhin gyi brtan g.yora snanga ba kuna kyang bsdu rim
NK115(re)001:9451: byed pa la bskyed rim gyi dus lhar zhen pa
NK115(re)001:9453: yod na rjes gzhig gi sgo nas bya ba ste
NK115(re)001:9454: phyi ma'i dbang du byas na dag pa'i snod bcud
NK115(re)001:9455: thams cad 'oda du zhu nasa gzhal yas khang la
NK115(re)001:9456: thim ste / de nas rim pa bzhin 'khor rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:9459: snying ga'i sa bona gyi bar rnamas la thim zhing /
NK115(re)001:9460: sa bon h'u yig lta bu yin na zhabs kyu
NK115(re)001:9461: nas thiga le'i bar thima pa de yanga mas rima
NK115(re)001:9462: nasa n+aa da'i bar du thim nas spros pa thams
NK115(re)001:9463: cad dang bral bar 'jog pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:9464: de yang n+aa da zhes bya ba ni shin tu
NK115(re)001:9465: phra ba'i rlung khams gsum pa'i bdag nyid can sangs
NK115(re)001:9466: rgyas ma thob kyi bar du yod pa la bshad
NK115(re)001:9467: pas bsgom dus na'ang khams gsum gyi bag chags 'dzin
NK115(re)001:9468: pa'i cha mtshon pa'i sum 'khyog tu yod pa zhig
NK115(re)001:9469: ste dag pa na sku gsum gyi ngo bo mchog
NK115(re)001:9470: tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'o //
NK115(re)001:9471: cho ga 'ga' zhig na nyer bsdu sogs mi 'byung
NK115(re)001:9472: ba ni zung 'jug lhun gyis grub ba chu bo'i
NK115(re)001:9473: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor la thun mtshams kyi rtsis gdab
NK115(re)001:9474: bral ba rnams la dgongs te de'i dbang du byas
NK115(re)001:9475: kyi / de las gzhan du ni gal che bar gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:9476: bsdu rim ni 'chi ba'i bag chags sbyong zhing chos sku'i rten 'brel bsgrig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9477: rdzogs rim sgyu lus 'od gsal du bsdu ba'i smin byed yin par ma zad /
NK115(re)001:9478: spyir rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi yon tan thams
NK115(re)001:9479: cad rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun nas rtsa
NK115(re)001:9480: rlung thig le dbu mar 'dus pa'i byed pa las
NK115(re)001:9481: skye ba sha stag yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:9482: dpe don gyi 'od gsal gang rgyud la bskyed kyang
NK115(re)001:9483: 'byung ba'i sdud rim las rtags bcu'i snang ba 'char
NK115(re)001:9484: zhing / rang bzhin gyi thim rim las snang gsum
NK115(re)001:9485: gyi 'od gsal shar ba'i klong du tha mal gyi
NK115(re)001:9486: 'khrul snang thams cad nub nas snang gsum 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:9487: du thim pa'i gnas skabs chos nyid spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:9488: bral ba'i ye shes 'char ba sha stag yin pas
NK115(re)001:9489: zhing / / mtshan mo gnyid 'thug dang rmi lam gyi dge sbyor la brtson par 'dod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9490: nyin mo rlung sems dbu mar 'dus pa'i thabs la spro ba yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9491: thun mong ma yin pa'i rdzogs rim sgyu lus la
NK115(re)001:9492: brten nas 'od gsal mngon du byed 'dod pa dang
NK115(re)001:9493: / de las tha mal gyi lus rten dor nas
NK115(re)001:9494: slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha skur bzhengs 'dod pa
NK115(re)001:9495: / dang / mthar thug ma rig bag chags kyi
NK115(re)001:9496: sa pa'i yid lus kyang 'od gsal du bsdus nas
NK115(re)001:9497: mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi go 'phang mngon du
NK115(re)001:9499: gal te tshe 'dir ma grol kyang bar do dang
NK115(re)001:9500: po'i 'od gsal chos sku'i dgongs pa la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:9501: bzhag nas zung 'jug longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhengs par
NK115(re)001:9502: 'dod pa rnams kyis ni bskyed rim las kyang bsdu
NK115(re)001:9503: rim la do gal du byed dgos zhes chos rje
NK115(re)001:9504: bla ma bka' drin can o rgyan 'jigs med chos
NK115(re)001:9507: de ltar bskyed pa'i lha bsdu rim byed pa de
NK115(re)001:9508: bzhin du rdzogs rim gyi lha sku yang dmigs pa
NK115(re)001:9509: dang bcas pa yin pas nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon
NK115(re)001:9510: dengs pa bzhin stong para gyur pa nama mkha'a lta
NK115(re)001:9511: bu'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid kun rtog
NK115(re)001:9512: gi spros pa dang bral ba'i so so rang gi
NK115(re)001:9513: rig pa'i ye shesa chena po'i spyod yula nyid la
NK115(re)001:9514: bazhaga par bya ba ste de ni rdzogs rim kun
NK115(re)001:9516: de las gzhan du rlung gi thabs las skyes pa'i gsal la stong pa'i nyams can dang /
NK115(re)001:9517: thig le la brten pa'i bde stong tsam ni lhan
NK115(re)001:9518: cig skyes pa'i ye shes 'dren byed kyi thabs gnas
NK115(re)001:9519: skabs pa las mthar thug pa'i don du ni bzung
NK115(re)001:9522: lus kyi sbud pa gang yin dang //
NK115(re)001:9523: sbud pa 'bud par byed pa dag /
NK115(re)001:9524: de dag khyad par ma mthong ste //
NK115(re)001:9525: de nyid mthong ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK115(re)001:9526: sbud pa yi ni bya ba non //
NK115(re)001:9528: dbang po gnyis byung bde ba ni /
NK115(re)001:9529: de nyid yin zhes skye ngan smra //
NK115(re)001:9530: de ni bde ba che yin zhes //
NK115(re)001:9531: rgyal ba mchog gis ma gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:9532: bde chen mi rtag ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:9533: bde ba chen po rtag tu rtag /
NK115(re)001:9534: mchan khung g.ya' 'phrug las byung ba //
NK115(re)001:9535: ci yi phyir na bde chen min //
NK115(re)001:9537: des na mtshan bcas kyi skabs su'ang gsal bde la
NK115(re)001:9538: stong pas rgyas 'debs pa'i yid dpyod tsam ma yin
NK115(re)001:9539: par rang bzhin gshis kyi ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK115(re)001:9540: na don dam lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes dngos
NK115(re)001:9541: su 'dren pa'i thabs su 'gyur gyi de las gzhan
NK115(re)001:9542: du ni dka' ste rnam pa 'gal ba'i phyir ro
NK115(re)001:9543: // des na mthar thug gi don du gnyer bya
NK115(re)001:9544: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po ni 'dus byas
NK115(re)001:9545: kyi mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:9546: la bde ba chen po zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:9547: dge sdig las 'das pa'i dbyings la dge ba zhes btags pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:9548: de lta na'ang bskyed rdzogs thun mong ba rnams mthar
NK115(re)001:9549: thug pa'i rdzogs rim zab mo'i ye shes kyi rgyu
NK115(re)001:9550: yin pas 'dor bar ni mi bya ste /
NK115(re)001:9552: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK115(re)001:9553: brtul zhugs can gyi spros pa bsgom //
NK115(re)001:9554: spros pa rmi lam ltar bsgoms nas //
NK115(re)001:9555: spros pa nyid kyis spros med byed //
NK115(re)001:9557: gsum pa byed las brjod pa'i sgo nas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:9558: de ltar bskyed pa'i rima pas phyi snod zhing dang
NK115(re)001:9559: gzhal yas khang nang bcud lha dang lha mor gsal
NK115(re)001:9560: nas / lus lha ngag sngags dran rtog thugs kyi lam 'khyer gyis ni /
NK115(re)001:9561: gnas don lus kyi bag chags sam sgo gsum du
NK115(re)001:9562: snanga ba ma dag pa'i bdena zhena thams cad lha
NK115(re)001:9563: sngags chos nyid kyi ngo bor 'goga par 'gyur la
NK115(re)001:9564: / mtshan bcas dang mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogas rima
NK115(re)001:9565: gyisa ni gya nom lhar zhen te snang spyod thams
NK115(re)001:9566: cad sgyu ma lta bu'i lha skur gsal ba la
NK115(re)001:9567: zhena rtoga phra ba yod pa'ang sponga zhing thig le
NK115(re)001:9568: la brten nas bde ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9569: rlung la brten nas gasla ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9570: rtsa la brten nas mi rtog pa'i ye shes 'dus byas pa rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:9571: lhan cig skyesa pa'i ye shesa 'dus ma byas pa rnams 'achara zhing /
NK115(re)001:9572: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9574: sku gnyis 'thob tshul sogs ni mdor bstan du bshad zin to //
NK115(re)001:9575: de ltar shin tu zaba pa'i bskyed rim dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9576: rdzogas pa'i rima pa rtsa thig rlung gsum la dngos
NK115(re)001:9577: su gnad du bsnun nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:9578: 'char bar byed pa'i thabs bla na meda pa rnamas
NK115(re)001:9579: ni bla na meda pa'i rgyud sde nang pa rnams
NK115(re)001:9580: lasa 'oga ma phyi rgyud sde gsum por thun rjes
NK115(re)001:9582: mi rtog pa bsgom pa tsam las gsungas pa meda do //
NK115(re)001:9583: des na dabnga po shin tu rnona po brtson 'grus
NK115(re)001:9584: dang ldan pa rnams kyis lam bar ma chad du
NK115(re)001:9585: bsgom na tshe gciga la rdo rje 'achanga gi sar
NK115(re)001:9586: 'gro bar byed pa'i nye ba'i lam snod min la
NK115(re)001:9587: sbasa shing skal ba med pa rnams kyi spyod yul
NK115(re)001:9588: du ma gyur pa de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:9589: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba shina tu zaba mo
NK115(re)001:9590: yina zhes pa'o // gsum pa mthun grogs dam tshig bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:9593: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:9594: de ltar dbang thob cing lam bskyed rdzogs kyi rim
NK115(re)001:9595: pa gnyis po bsgom par byed pa la gsuma pa
NK115(re)001:9596: de'i mthuna pa'i rkyen rim pa gnyis po de yang
NK115(re)001:9597: dag pa'i lam du 'gro zhing de la brten nas
NK115(re)001:9598: dngos grub rnam pa gnyis 'grub pa'i grogas su gyur
NK115(re)001:9599: pa ni dama tshiga bsrung ba kho na la rag
NK115(re)001:9600: las te / de ma bsrungs na srog gi dbang
NK115(re)001:9601: po 'gags na dbang po gzhan thams cad kyis bya
NK115(re)001:9602: ba byed mi nus pa bzhin lha bsgom pa dang
NK115(re)001:9603: sngags bzla ba dang rdzogs rim bsgom pa sogs sngags
NK115(re)001:9604: kyi bslab pa thams cad don med par 'gyur bas
NK115(re)001:9605: na ji ltar bsrung ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:9606: dang po gsang sngagas la zhugas te dbang zhus shing
NK115(re)001:9607: thob pa'i dus su ji ltar khas blangs pa'i sngags
NK115(re)001:9608: kyi brtul zhugsa spang blang gi gnas thams cad shes
NK115(re)001:9609: par byas nas mig gi 'bras bu'am snying bzhin du
NK115(re)001:9610: mi nyamsa par bsrung dgos la /
NK115(re)001:9611: de yang gsang sngags ni nyon mongs dang 'dod yon
NK115(re)001:9612: thams cad lam du byed pa'i thams khyad par can
NK115(re)001:9613: yin pas theg pa 'og ma ltar spang blang la
NK115(re)001:9614: don dam par rdzas su mi blta bar ma zad
NK115(re)001:9615: tha snyad tsam du'ang mtshan mar ma zhen pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:9616: nas sngags lam gyi khyad chos dang ldan pas gang
NK115(re)001:9617: zag rang rang gi rgyud tshod dang bstun pa'i lta
NK115(re)001:9618: sgom gyis zin nas lam du byed cing nyon mongs
NK115(re)001:9619: rang mtshan pa'i gnyen pora 'gro ba'i rten 'brela mi
NK115(re)001:9620: 'chola bar bya ste dper na rma bya'i mgrin para
NK115(re)001:9621: gzhan dag 'chi bar 'gyur ba'i batsana dug zhugas na
NK115(re)001:9622: bcud len du gyur nas 'dab ma blta na sdug
NK115(re)001:9623: par 'gyur ba ltar rang gi lam gyi grogs su
NK115(re)001:9624: gyur te lta sgom 'bogs thon pa'i thabs su spyad
NK115(re)001:9626: gal te rang gi rgyud tshod dang ma bstun par
NK115(re)001:9627: spang blang med pa'i spyod pa la mngon par 'chel
NK115(re)001:9628: na ni thar pa'i lam la gegs su de las
NK115(re)001:9629: che ba med pas gzab par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9630: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:9634: bsrungs pa'i phan yon bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9635: dang po dam tshig gi rnam grangs bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:9637: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi khyad par /
NK115(re)001:9638: brtul zhugs nyer lnga dang rigs lnga'i sdom pa bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9639: dang po bla med spyi'i sdom pa bshad pa la drug ste /
NK115(re)001:9645: nyams na phyir bcos pa'i thabs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9646: dang po dam sdom gyi khyad par ni /
NK115(re)001:9647: gsang sngags kyi bsrung bya de la dama tshiga dang
NK115(re)001:9648: ni sdoma pa zhes pa'i tha snyad 'dogs tshul gyi
NK115(re)001:9649: khyad par ni sa ma ya zhes pa'i sgra las
NK115(re)001:9650: dam tshig ste / de yang bsrungs na nyes pa'i
NK115(re)001:9651: phyogs thams cad tshig par byed pa'i phan yon thob
NK115(re)001:9652: pas na dam tshig tu bshad de /
NK115(re)001:9654: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa la //
NK115(re)001:9655: dbang dang byin rlabs thob pa yin //
NK115(re)001:9656: dam pa'i tshul bzhin nges spyad na //
NK115(re)001:9657: mi mthun phyogs rnams tshig par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:9659: ma bsrungs na dmyal ba'i mes bsreg pa'i nyes dmigs bskyed pas kyang dam tshig tu bzhag ste /
NK115(re)001:9661: dam pa rnams kyi bka' bcag cing //
NK115(re)001:9662: byin rlabs dmod bor rang bzhin grub //
NK115(re)001:9664: rdo rje can yang tshig par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:9666: de'i phyir thun mong du ji ltar dama bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:9667: tshiga de las 'ad'a bar bya ba ma yina pa
NK115(re)001:9668: la'ang de skad ces bya ste /
NK115(re)001:9670: rgyal ba'i gsang chen rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:9671: ma nyams dam du 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:9672: bla mas ji skad bstan pa bzhin //
NK115(re)001:9673: dam bcas tshig ni brtan 'dzin pa //
NK115(re)001:9674: dam tshig gces su bshad pa yin //
NK115(re)001:9676: sdoma pa ni gnang ba bkag la dpyad de gang
NK115(re)001:9677: zhig blang bar bya ba sgo gsum dkyil 'khor gsum
NK115(re)001:9678: gyi ngo bor sdom par byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9679: blang bar mi bya ba'i dngos po mtshan ma'i rtog
NK115(re)001:9680: pa cha dang bcas pa las kyang rgyud sdom pa'i
NK115(re)001:9681: mtshams ngesa para bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:9684: thabs ni bde bas sdom pa ste //
NK115(re)001:9686: des na de gnyis ngo bo sngags sdom gciga pu
NK115(re)001:9687: la 'da' mi rung ba dang rgyud sdom par byed
NK115(re)001:9688: pa'i ldoga cha nas dbye ba byas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9689: de ltar yang gsang snying gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK115(re)001:9690: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK115(re)001:9691: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK115(re)001:9692: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK115(re)001:9694: de ltar dam tshig dang sdom pa'i rnam par bzhag pa la /
NK115(re)001:9695: skabs sbyor bdun pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:9696: sangs rgyas kyi dam tshig gang yin pa sems can gyi sdom pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:9697: sems can gyi dam tshig gang yin pa sangs rgyas kyi sdom pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:9698: zhes pa'i dang po ni sangs rgyas kyi sa na
NK115(re)001:9699: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig gi rang bzhin las
NK115(re)001:9700: 'da' ba ma yin pa gang zhig sems can gyi
NK115(re)001:9701: khams la spang gnyen dang bcas pas lam dus kyi
NK115(re)001:9702: sdom pa'i rang bzhin du yod de /
NK115(re)001:9703: thams ni bde bas sdom pa ste //
NK115(re)001:9704: zhes drangs ma thag pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:9705: gnyis pa ni sems can gyi dus na 'da' bar
NK115(re)001:9706: mi rung ba'i dam tshig sangs rgyas rnams la chos
NK115(re)001:9707: thams cad rang snang ye shes kyi ngo bor sdom
NK115(re)001:9708: pa'i 'bras rgyud kyi sngags sdom du gnas te /
NK115(re)001:9710: de nas chos kun sdom gcig pa'i //
NK115(re)001:9711: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes byar bshad //
NK115(re)001:9714: chos kun ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:9715: log rtog ye nas rnam par dag /
NK115(re)001:9716: de bas sdom pa rnam par dag /
NK115(re)001:9718: gnyis pa rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK115(re)001:9719: sngags ni bslab pa kuna gyi spyi dona te rten
NK115(re)001:9720: gzhi ni sngagas sdoma yin pas de nyid rang thob
NK115(re)001:9721: byed kyi dbang chog rnam pa dag pa la brten
NK115(re)001:9722: nas ji bzhin ma thoba pa la ltung ba dang
NK115(re)001:9723: dngos grub gnyis ka med de slong mos 'tsho ba
NK115(re)001:9724: rnams la mnga' dbang dang dpya khral gnyis ka med
NK115(re)001:9725: pa bzhin dang / kun dkris tshang ba'i ltung bas nyams na phyir ma bcos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9726: bslab pa phul ba la sogs pas btang ba yang de bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:9727: smyo ba la sogas pa'i rkyen dbang gis 'du shesa
NK115(re)001:9728: ranga bzhina du mi gansa pa la'ang ltung bar byung
NK115(re)001:9730: ltung ltung min gyi mtshams mi shes pa'i phyir dge
NK115(re)001:9731: slong smyon pas mi bsad kyang pham ltung du mi
NK115(re)001:9733: des na de rnams la ni ltung ba yang med
NK115(re)001:9734: de mi dge ba gzugs can du grub par 'dod
NK115(re)001:9735: pa bdag cag gi ston pa'i lugs ma yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:9736: phyir dang / dngosa grub kyang meda de dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rten ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:9737: de lta bas na sngagas sdoma dang ldana zhing ma nyamsa pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9738: bslab pa ma btang la shesa pa ranga bzhina du
NK115(re)001:9739: rnal du gansa te ltung ltung min gyi mtshams shes
NK115(re)001:9740: shing dran nus pa de ltung ba dang ni dngosa
NK115(re)001:9741: grub gnyis ka 'byung ba'i snoda yin no //
NK115(re)001:9742: gsum pa ltung ba'i yan lag ni /
NK115(re)001:9743: spyir kun dkris zhes bya ba byang sems kyi rtsa
NK115(re)001:9744: ltung gi yan lag tu gsungs pa 'dir sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:9745: ltung ba'i yan lag tu yang sbyar bar byas na
NK115(re)001:9746: / rtsa ltung lnga pa byanga chuba kyi semas btang
NK115(re)001:9747: ba ni yan lag brtsi ba la mi ltos par
NK115(re)001:9748: dang po nas pham par gyur pa'i rtsa ltung yin
NK115(re)001:9749: / zhing / yang mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gis bzhi
NK115(re)001:9750: pa byams pa 'dor ba yang kun dkris tshang ba
NK115(re)001:9751: la mi ltos par rtsa ltung du 'gyur bar bzhed
NK115(re)001:9754: gang zhig gzhan 'byor khro de la //
NK115(re)001:9755: byang chub sems ni ga la yod //
NK115(re)001:9756: ces pa ltar gzhan yon tan gyi 'byor pa dang
NK115(re)001:9757: ldan pa la yid gdung bas de dang bral bar
NK115(re)001:9758: 'dod na byams pa 'dor bar 'gyur bas de la
NK115(re)001:9759: sems can blos btang gi rtsa ltung yang 'byung nye
NK115(re)001:9761: de lasa gazhana pa'i rtsa ltung bcu gsum mam bcu gnyis po la /
NK115(re)001:9762: rtsa ltung gi dngos gzhir grub byed kyi kun dkrisa zhesa bya ba'i yan lag brtsi tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:9763: slob dpon smod pa lta bu'i nyes pa zhig byed
NK115(re)001:9764: bzhin pa na da dunga bya ba de byed 'doda
NK115(re)001:9766: bya ba de la nyes dmigs su bltas pa'i 'gyod pa med pa 2dang /
NK115(re)001:9767: ranga ngora ltosa te bdag la gsang sngags kyi sdom
NK115(re)001:9768: pa dang 'gal ba'i nyes pa 'di byung ba ni
NK115(re)001:9769: shin tu gnong ngo snyam pa'i ngo tsha shesa pa
NK115(re)001:9770: dang / gazhana ngora ltosa te rdo rje slob dpon
NK115(re)001:9771: sogs gong ma rnams kyi thugs kyis khrel ba dang
NK115(re)001:9772: dang / / 'jig rten phal pa rnams kyi sems
NK115(re)001:9773: ma dad cing sun par 'gyur ba'i bya ba 'di
NK115(re)001:9774: ma legs so snyam pa'i khrela yoda meda pa 3ste
NK115(re)001:9775: dang / / chosa gsuma mam / de'i steng du
NK115(re)001:9776: nyes pa de dag la dga' zhing mgu ba 4bsnan
NK115(re)001:9777: nas bzhir byed pa'ang yod cing de dag tshanga ba'i
NK115(re)001:9778: kun slonga ngan pa de skyes pa'i skad cig gnyis
NK115(re)001:9779: pa nas bya ba de yongs su rdzogs pa'i mathara
NK115(re)001:9780: gtugs pa de srida du rgyun chagas su bar ma
NK115(re)001:9781: chad par yoda par gyur na kun dkrisa tshanga ba'i
NK115(re)001:9782: ltung ba chen po bskyed pas mthun phyogs sdom pa
NK115(re)001:9783: gcod cing gnyen po'i phyogs phama para gyur pa yina
NK115(re)001:9784: dang / / chosa gsuma mam / te / rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK115(re)001:9785: de las gzhan pa bcu bzhi ni //
NK115(re)001:9786: phas pham par ni rab tu bshad /
NK115(re)001:9788: gal te rtsa ltung bskyed pa'i kun slong skyes pa
NK115(re)001:9789: nas dngos gzhi ma rdzogs pa'i bar der dus kyi
NK115(re)001:9790: bar chada nas rgyun chagas su meda pa'am /
NK115(re)001:9791: 'di la nyes pa 'di lta bu yod do snyam nas spyod log pa 1dang /
NK115(re)001:9792: ngo tsha khrel yod kyi blo skyes pa 2dang /
NK115(re)001:9793: dga' mgu log pa'i yid cung zad skyes pa 3ste /
NK115(re)001:9794: chosa gsuma po de'i ganga yang rung ba lasa ciga
NK115(re)001:9795: shosa ma tshanga na ltung ba'i dngos gzhi bskyed par
