NK115(re)001:9796: bya ba'i yan lag thams cad ma tshogas pas pham
NK115(re)001:9797: pa'am rtsa ba'i ltung ba dngos min yang nyes pa
NK115(re)001:9799: kun dkris kyi yan lag bzhir dbye ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:9800: bzhi po'i nang nas nyes dmigs su lta ba yod na lhag ma gsum char tshang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9801: gnyis dang gcig tshang ba rnams chung ngu dang /
NK115(re)001:9802: nyes dmigs su mi lta ba yod na lhag ma gsum char med kyang 'bring yin /
NK115(re)001:9803: chen po ni shugs las shes so //
NK115(re)001:9804: bzhi pa srung byed kyi thabs ni /
NK115(re)001:9805: 'di ltar rdo rje theg pa'i ltung ba ni /
NK115(re)001:9806: grangs mang la 'byung nye bas bsrung mi nus so
NK115(re)001:9807: snyam du sgyid lug par mi bya bar chu ma
NK115(re)001:9808: 'ong ba'i snga rol nas chu lon byed pa ltar
NK115(re)001:9809: / kun dkris brtsi ba'i tshul de yisa ltung ba'i mtshams legs par nges shing shesa par byas nas /
NK115(re)001:9810: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig mtha' dag pa kuna /
NK115(re)001:9811: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang yan lag sbom po brgyad
NK115(re)001:9812: lta bu'i nang du gnad bsdus te 'di dag la
NK115(re)001:9813: blang dor byed pa'i nan tan ni bdag gi srog
NK115(re)001:9814: la bab kyang mi gtong ngo snyam du yida kyisa
NK115(re)001:9816: lusa ngag gnyis kyi sgo nas dngos su blang dor
NK115(re)001:9817: byed pa'i bya ba yang dora bar mi bya ste
NK115(re)001:9819: srung bya'i gnas thams cad mi brjed pa'i dran pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9820: nyes pa byung ma byung dang /
NK115(re)001:9821: nyes pa 'byung ba'i rgyu la sgo gsum brtson gyin
NK115(re)001:9822: yod med sogs la yang yang brtags pa shes bzhin
NK115(re)001:9823: / rtag tu snying la bcags te gzab par byed
NK115(re)001:9824: pa bag yod pa ste gsum gyi sgo nas bsrung
NK115(re)001:9825: / bar byed la / de yang lus dang 'brel
NK115(re)001:9826: ba rnams ni bya ba de byas zin pa dang
NK115(re)001:9828: ngag dang 'brel pa rnams pha rol po gang rung gis go ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9829: yid kho nas ltung bar 'gyur ba rnams ni thun
NK115(re)001:9830: mtshams so so'i nang du gnyen pos ma sleb na
NK115(re)001:9831: rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:9832: spyir yang lus ngag gi grogs su yid mi 'gro ba ni med pas na /
NK115(re)001:9833: nyina thun gsum dang matshana mo yang thun gsum ste
NK115(re)001:9834: cha druga tu bgosa pa la cha re re'i nanga
NK115(re)001:9835: du'ang bdag la ni gtan gyi 'dun ma sgrub pa'i
NK115(re)001:9836: rgyu gcig pu nyams len gyi grogs dam tshig bsrung
NK115(re)001:9837: ba 'di yin pas 'di las gal che ba ci
NK115(re)001:9838: yang med do snyam du rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu
NK115(re)001:9839: bzhi po'i nyes pa byung ngama ma byung brtag dpyad
NK115(re)001:9840: zhib tu btang nas sngo bgranga bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:9841: de ltar byas pa'i tshe na ltung ba'i nyes pa
NK115(re)001:9842: gang yang rung bas gosa par gyur pa mthong na
NK115(re)001:9843: ci mi snyam du mi sems par snying thag pa
NK115(re)001:9844: nas nyes dmigs la bsams te 'gyod pa bskyed cinga
NK115(re)001:9845: phyi bshol mi byed par phyir 'chosa pa'i thabs la
NK115(re)001:9846: de ma thag tu semas shing bshags par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9847: gal te nyes pa gang gis kyang gosa pa mina
NK115(re)001:9848: par mthong na bdag gi lam la bar du ma
NK115(re)001:9849: chad pas go bcad do snyam du dag'a ba bsgoma
NK115(re)001:9850: zhing / de ltar nyes pa byung ba bshags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9851: ma byung ba'i dge ba'i rgyun de dag gzhan don du bsngo bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9852: sngona chada ltung ba'i nyes pas gosa sama ma gosa
NK115(re)001:9853: pa ganga yina kyang rung ste phyis mi byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:9854: dam bca' ni gal che ste /
NK115(re)001:9855: sngar byung ba yin na ni dam bca' med na
NK115(re)001:9856: nyes pa'i rgyun mi chod cing bshags pa byas kyang
NK115(re)001:9857: lhag ma med par 'dag mi nus la /
NK115(re)001:9858: sngar ma gos na'ang dam bca' med na phyis 'byung nye bas na /
NK115(re)001:9859: phyin chada ni sroga la baba kyang rtsa ltung gi
NK115(re)001:9860: nyes byas kyi las phyogs mthun dang bcas pas gosa
NK115(re)001:9861: para mi bya ba'i sdoma semas shina tu ste sems
NK115(re)001:9862: stobs drag pos yang yang rgyud la bsten par bya'o
NK115(re)001:9863: // ganga gi tshe na nyin mtshan gyi cha druga
NK115(re)001:9864: po ganga yanga runga ba re'i nanga du sngo bgranga
NK115(re)001:9865: byed pa'i 'du shesa rmongas te brjed par gyura na
NK115(re)001:9866: // / dran shes kyi sgo nas sngo bgrang byed
NK115(re)001:9867: pa las 'das pa'i kha na ma tho ba'i sboma
NK115(re)001:9870: nyin dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK115(re)001:9871: nyin re bzhin gyis bzla bar bya /
NK115(re)001:9872: gang tshe nyams gyur rnal 'byor pa /
NK115(re)001:9873: kha na ma tho sbom par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:9875: de ltar sngo bgrang byed pa'i dran shes ma byung
NK115(re)001:9876: bar thun tshod kyi cha druga ka 'adsa par gyur
NK115(re)001:9877: na sboma po druga tu 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:9878: de ltar 'phel ba de nyin zhaga de'i khong du
NK115(re)001:9879: yang dran shes ma sleb pas phyir bcosa pa'i thabs
NK115(re)001:9880: ma gruba na / zhag phyi ma'i skya rengas dang
NK115(re)001:9881: po 'achara ba dang nyes pa sboma po bcu gnyis
NK115(re)001:9882: dag tu 'gyur bar bshad pas nyes pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:9883: nyin zhag re re bzhin 'phel bar 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:9884: la bsam ste gzab par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:9885: yan lag gi dam tshig sbom po'i rnam grangs rnams
NK115(re)001:9886: la yanga rang rang gi yan lag tshang ma tshang
NK115(re)001:9887: gis sbom ltung dngos dang nyes byas su 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:9888: tshul dang / sngo bgrang byed pa'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:9889: sngo bgrang ma byas na nyes byas 'phel ba la
NK115(re)001:9890: sogs pa ni rtsa ltung la bshad pa de yisa
NK115(re)001:9892: lnga pa bsrung bya dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:9893: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9894: yan lag sbom po'i rnam grangs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9895: rtsa ltung gi khungs smos pa'o //
NK115(re)001:9896: dang po rtsa ltung bcu bzhi bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:9899: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:9900: de la rgyud sde spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig rnams rim pa bzhin du bshad pa las /
NK115(re)001:9901: thoga mara bshad par bya ba ni /
NK115(re)001:9902: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud dang /
NK115(re)001:9905: dgra nag gi rgyud la sogs par rtsa ltung bcu bzhi grangs nges pa can du gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:9906: de dag las gzhan pa'i rgyud sde rnams na grangs
NK115(re)001:9907: de dang mi mthun pa de las nyung ba dang
NK115(re)001:9908: / de bas mang du yod pa rnams kyang don
NK115(re)001:9909: du mtshungs par yod de dngos shugs gang rung gis
NK115(re)001:9910: mang po rnams 'di nyid du bsdu rung zhing /
NK115(re)001:9911: nyung ngu rnams la 'di nyid 'du bar 'gyur bas
NK115(re)001:9912: na bla na meda pa'i rgyud sde spyi'i nyams len
NK115(re)001:9913: la gcesa pa'i chingas chen po yin te /
NK115(re)001:9914: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK115(re)001:9915: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi ni //
NK115(re)001:9916: bklag dang 'dzin pa nyid du bya //
NK115(re)001:9918: de yang shing la sogs pa'i rtsa ba bton na sdong bu dang /
NK115(re)001:9920: lo ma nas 'bras bu'i bar thams cad med par
NK115(re)001:9921: byed pa bzhin du yon tan thams cad bskyed par
NK115(re)001:9922: byed pa'i rtsa ba ni sdom pa yin pa de
NK115(re)001:9923: rtsad nas gcod par byas na yon tan gang yang
NK115(re)001:9925: gnas 'og mar ltung bar 'gyur ba'i rgyu yin pas ltung ba zhes bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:9926: grangs ni dbang bzhi dang 'gal ba'i bcu bzhi'i raba tu dbye bar bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:9927: de'ang gtso che ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK115(re)001:9928: bcu gsum pa byang sems kyi rgyud dam rdzas ji bzhin mi bsten pa dang /
NK115(re)001:9929: lnga pa 'bras bu byang sems 'dor ba gnyis gsang sher gyi dang /
NK115(re)001:9930: khyad par bcu bzhi pa shes rab ma la smod pa sher dbang gi mi mthun phyogs /
NK115(re)001:9931: dgu pa rang bzhin dag pa'i chos la the tshom za ba dang /
NK115(re)001:9932: bcu gcig pa ming bral chos la tshad mas gzhal ba gnyis dbang bzhi pa'i dang /
NK115(re)001:9933: lhag ma dgu po bum dbang dang 'gal ba'i rtsa
NK115(re)001:9934: ltung yin zhing dbang phyi ma phyi ma'i tshe na
NK115(re)001:9935: snga ma snga ma thun mong dang dbang rang skal
NK115(re)001:9936: gyi de nyid thun mong du 'gyur la /
NK115(re)001:9937: des na bum dbang tsam thob pas rang gi dgu po spyad na rtsa ltung du 'gyur gyi /
NK115(re)001:9938: de las gzhan pa lnga la spyad kyang rtsa ltung
NK115(re)001:9939: dngos su mi 'gyur te de dag spong ba'i sdom
NK115(re)001:9940: pa ma thob pa'i phyir ro gsungs //
NK115(re)001:9941: 'o na 'di dag gi go rim dbang bzhi'i rim pa ltar med pa ci yin zhe na /
NK115(re)001:9942: go rim ni 'di ltar sngags kyi dngos grub kyi rtsa ba bla ma dang /
NK115(re)001:9943: de la brten nas lung gi chos dang /
NK115(re)001:9944: chos sgrub pa'i grogs spong ba sogs gnyen po sngags kyi go rim dang /
NK115(re)001:9945: snga ma snga ma lci zhing phyi ma phyi ma
NK115(re)001:9946: yang bas lci yang gi go rim yang yin pas
NK115(re)001:9948: de rnams so so'i yul dang bsam pa dang bya
NK115(re)001:9949: ba'i dngos gzhi sogs kyi mthar thug ltung bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:9950: ba'i mtshams ni 'og tu bshad pa 'di ltar brtaga
NK115(re)001:9951: par bya'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bcu bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:9952: dang po slob dpon smod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:9953: de la rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po'i nang nas nyes
NK115(re)001:9954: pa shin tu lci ba'i rtsa ltung dang po ni
NK115(re)001:9955: / spyir btang yul bla ma'i ngos nas slob dpon
NK115(re)001:9956: drug la sogs pa bshad pa'i phyir sngags chos kho
NK115(re)001:9957: nas sbrel ba zhig mi dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:9958: 'dir yul khyad par ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:9959: rang gi dabang thoba pa'i yul gyi slob dpona ni
NK115(re)001:9960: rang la rdo rje theg pa'i lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:9961: yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi 'dzugs pa po yin
NK115(re)001:9962: pas de la brnyas pa sogs byas na ltung bar
NK115(re)001:9963: 'gyur zhing nyes pa che ba smosa ci dgosa kyang
NK115(re)001:9964: / zab mo'i don la shes rab kyi mig 'byed
NK115(re)001:9965: pa'i slob dpon sngagas kyi rgyud sde mang ngam nyung
NK115(re)001:9966: yang rung kha tshang bar ston pa nas tha na
NK115(re)001:9967: tshigas bacada gciga pa yana chada kyi don phan sems
NK115(re)001:9968: kyis ma nor bar bkrala nas ston par mdzad pa
NK115(re)001:9969: / dang / sgom byung gi shes rab bskyed pa'i
NK115(re)001:9970: phyir rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi nyams len gnad
NK115(re)001:9971: du dril ba'i mana ngaga zaba mo khrid kyi tshul
NK115(re)001:9972: du stona pa ste de gsuma ni yul yin la
NK115(re)001:9973: / dang / / de yang gsum ga bla ma
NK115(re)001:9974: gcig gis mdzad na bka' drin gsum ldan gyi bla
NK115(re)001:9975: ma zhes shin tu gnyan zhing /
NK115(re)001:9976: yang dbang bskur nas rgyud bshad pa lta bu ni gnyis ldan dang /
NK115(re)001:9977: dbang bskur ba lta bu gcig ldan te gang ltar
NK115(re)001:9978: yang de rnams la byang chub snying po'i bar du
NK115(re)001:9979: gsang sngags kyi chosa kyi lam ston du 'brela zin
NK115(re)001:9980: par gyur pa'i zhabs tog rnam pa gsum gyi sgo
NK115(re)001:9981: nas g.yo zol med par bsnyen bkur gyi khura dang
NK115(re)001:9982: du blangs nas gsung gi zur tsam yang mi bcag
NK115(re)001:9984: rang gi 'dod rgyu'i chos de thob zin nas ni
NK115(re)001:9985: snying ring bar gyur nas ji mi snyam du 'dug
NK115(re)001:9986: ste bla mar 'dzin pa'i bsnyen bkur gyi khur de
NK115(re)001:9987: bora bar gyur na yang bla ma'i byin rlabs mi
NK115(re)001:9988: 'jug pas dngos grub kyi skal ba rgyang ring du
NK115(re)001:9989: 'gyur zhing / da dung de'i steng du phrag dog
NK115(re)001:9990: dang zhe sdang gi kun slong ngan pas brnyas shing
NK115(re)001:9991: smod par byas te snying thag pa nas 'di la
NK115(re)001:9992: mi re'o snyam pa byung na kun dkris kyang tshang
NK115(re)001:9993: bar 'gyur bas rtsa ltung gi tshad du slebs shing
NK115(re)001:9994: nyes pa'ang shin tu che ste mtshams med pa las
NK115(re)001:9995: 'gyur zhing / kyang thu'o // 'di ltar mtshams med
NK115(re)001:9996: pa byas pas kyang gdod rdo rje theg pa'i sgor
NK115(re)001:9997: zhugs nas bla ma'i bka' bzhin bsgrub na dngos grub
NK115(re)001:9998: 'gyur zhing / kyang thu'o // thob pa'i tshul / bde ba chen po'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:9999: shan pa smad 'tshong mtshams med spyad pas kyang //
NK115(re)001:10000: rang rig shes pas gang gis bsgrib mi 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:10002: snying nas slob dpon smod cing bshags sdom gyis sor
NK115(re)001:10003: chud par mi byed pa de la gsang sngagsa kyi
NK115(re)001:10004: dngosa gruba ji ltar bsgrubs kyang 'thob pa yoda pa
NK115(re)001:10005: ma yina par ma zad rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro
NK115(re)001:10006: bar 'gyur te / ko sa la'i rgyan las /
NK115(re)001:10007: snying nas slob dpon smod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:10011: bla ma la ni dmod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:10012: thugs dkrugs pa yi nyes pa ni //
NK115(re)001:10013: phyi yi rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK115(re)001:10014: chu de skra yis gtor gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:10015: de yi tshad du sdug bsngal myong //
NK115(re)001:10016: rdo rje'i dmyal bar grags pa yin //
NK115(re)001:10017: zhes bshad pas shin tu gzab par bya'o /
NK115(re)001:10018: gal te slar gso ba'i thabs la 'bad na rnam
NK115(re)001:10019: smin gyi cha sbyong nus kyang dngos grub thob pa
NK115(re)001:10020: la shin tu 'gyang ba yin pas dang po nyid
NK115(re)001:10021: nas de 'dra'i nyes pa la mi sbyor ba'i dam
NK115(re)001:10022: bca' len zhing bla ma rnams la snying bzhin du
NK115(re)001:10024: gnyisa pa bde gshegs bka' 'das kyi rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10025: yul sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'i nyams su
NK115(re)001:10026: blang bya'i snying po so byang sngags kyi sdoma pa
NK115(re)001:10028: bye brag de rnams kyi spang bar bya ba dang
NK115(re)001:10029: blang bar bya ba'i bslaba pa'i gansa gang yang rung
NK115(re)001:10030: ba rang gis shes bzhin du khyad gsod kyi bsam
NK115(re)001:10031: pas ston pa bde bar gshegas pa'i gannga ba dang
NK115(re)001:10032: bakaga pa yi matshamas de lasa 'adsa pa ste mi
NK115(re)001:10033: mthun pa'i phyogs la zhugs te dper na sa bon
NK115(re)001:10034: 'joms pa 'dis thar pa la bar du gcod par
NK115(re)001:10035: mi 'gyur ro zhes 'joms par byed pa lta bu
NK115(re)001:10036: dang / mthun phyogs bla gos sogs legs par bgo
NK115(re)001:10037: ba 'di tsam ni thar pa'i rgyu min no zhes
NK115(re)001:10038: mi bsgrub pa lta bus mtshon nas bslab pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:10039: gang dang 'gal bar byas kyang rung la /
NK115(re)001:10040: de dang 'brel bar gzhan la bshad kyang rung ste kun dkris tshang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10041: de bzhina du mdo rgyud man ngag dang bcas pa'i dgongs don dang /
NK115(re)001:10042: thabs sna tshogs pas gdul bya 'dul ba'i dgos don
NK115(re)001:10043: legs par thugs su chud cing matshana nyid dang ldana
NK115(re)001:10044: pa'i bla ma yisa gdul bar bya ba'i yula dang
NK115(re)001:10046: dbang po dang skal pa'i rim pa sogs la dgongas te snga phyi 'gal ba lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:10047: gnas skabs dang mi 'tshams pa lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:10048: chos dang mi mthun pa lta bu ci 'dra ba
NK115(re)001:10049: zhig bka'a stsal kyang 'di la nges par dgongs gzhi
NK115(re)001:10050: dang dgos pa khyad par can yod do snyam du
NK115(re)001:10051: gsung sna khrid na phyis de'i dgos pa shes shing
NK115(re)001:10052: don dang ldan par 'gyur ba la /
NK115(re)001:10053: de lta ma yin par 'di la ni dgos pa
NK115(re)001:10054: ci yang med do snyam pa la sogs pa lta
NK115(re)001:10055: bu'i sgo nas khyad du basda de ma bsgrubs na'ang
NK115(re)001:10056: kun dkris tshang na rtsa ltung du 'gyur te dngos
NK115(re)001:10057: grub thams cad sangs rgyas dang bla ma'i bka' rjes
NK115(re)001:10058: su 'gro zhing de las 'das pa ni bla ma
NK115(re)001:10059: la brnyas pa'i 'og nas nyes pa che bas rtsa
NK115(re)001:10060: ltung gnyis par bzhag pa yina no //
NK115(re)001:10061: gsuma pa mched la 'khu ba'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10062: yul ni dabnga grala gciga tu 'dus te bla ma
NK115(re)001:10063: dang dkyil 'khor gcig la brten nas dbang zhus na
NK115(re)001:10064: pha ma gcig pa'i spun bzhin nang 'dresa pa'i mcheda
NK115(re)001:10065: ces bya bas de la ku re la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:10066: phyir ma yin par snying nas zhe sdang ba'am /
NK115(re)001:10068: phrag dog gi bsam pas skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10069: mi bkur zhing brnyas bcos byas pa la sogs pas
NK115(re)001:10070: brtse gdung rgyun bcad de ltos med du blos dor
NK115(re)001:10071: nas kun dkris tshang bar gyur na ltung bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:10072: ba'i tshul / sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyi rim pa rnam par bzhag pa las /
NK115(re)001:10073: dkyil 'khor slob dpon rig ma gcig /
NK115(re)001:10074: dbang bzhi dag gi bye brag gis //
NK115(re)001:10075: nye dang khyad par bye brag go //
NK115(re)001:10078: spun zhes bya ba ni gang dang slob dpon gcig la dkyil 'khor du dbang thob pa ste /
NK115(re)001:10079: de la phrag dog la sogs pa'i rgyus skyon rnams brjod par mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10080: zhes pa la sogs pa snga phyis byon bzhugs kyi
NK115(re)001:10081: mkhas pa rnams kyis dmigas kyis basla bar mdzad na'ang
NK115(re)001:10082: / de ni shin tu gnyan pa tsam du zad kyi gzhan la'ang bsrung dgos te /
NK115(re)001:10084: matha'a yasa pa'i semas can thams cad bde gshegas snying
NK115(re)001:10085: po'i rigs gcig gis bsdus pa'i spuna yina pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:10086: spyi'i mched dang / rgyal ba'i bstan pa la zhugs
NK115(re)001:10087: so cog bslab pa'i gnas che phra gang rung zhig
NK115(re)001:10088: dang ldan pas chos brgyad gcig pa ringa ba'i mched
NK115(re)001:10089: spyi'i mched dang / dang / rdo rje theg pa'i
NK115(re)001:10090: sdom pa la gnas pa thams cad dam tshig gcig
NK115(re)001:10091: pa nye ba'i mcheda yin pas de rnams la'ang /
NK115(re)001:10092: bsrung dgos par snga ma dang mtshungas ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:10093: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las kyang sems can
NK115(re)001:10094: la gnod pa'i bsam sbyor spong dgos par bstan pa'i
NK115(re)001:10096: khyad par bskyed rim gyi dam tshig tu'ang snod bcud
NK115(re)001:10097: lha dang lha mor blta dgos na ma 'ongs pa'i
NK115(re)001:10098: sangs rgyas ni sems can rnams yin pas de kun
NK115(re)001:10099: la brnyas sogs spang dgos pa lta ci smos te
NK115(re)001:10101: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK115(re)001:10102: gang dag bdag las gzhan med cing //
NK115(re)001:10103: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK115(re)001:10104: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin na //
NK115(re)001:10105: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK115(re)001:10106: sangs rgyas chos bzhugs ring ba dang //
NK115(re)001:10107: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK115(re)001:10108: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK115(re)001:10110: bzhi pa byams pa 'dor ba'i rtsa ltung ni yul
NK115(re)001:10111: byang sems sngags pa rnams kyis sems can thams cad
NK115(re)001:10112: la byams pa'i sems bla na med pa'i bu gcig
NK115(re)001:10113: pa bzhin du bltas nas blos nam yang 'dor du
NK115(re)001:10115: sems can kun la phan pa'i sems //
NK115(re)001:10116: nam yang gtong bar mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10118: de lta bas na 'di ltar bsam pa ngan zhing
NK115(re)001:10119: sbyor ba rtsuba pasa kun la gnod cing 'tshe bar
NK115(re)001:10120: byed pa'i semas cana zhiga mthonga ba'i chosa tshe 'di
NK115(re)001:10121: la rang gi sngon gyi lasa sam /
NK115(re)001:10122: da lta'i bya ba ngan pa'i stobs kyisa lus sems
NK115(re)001:10123: sdug bsngal dang gnod pa du mas manra bar gyura
NK115(re)001:10124: ba de la'ang dag'a ba bsgomas nasa sems can gcig
NK115(re)001:10125: pu de la byamsa pa'i semas gtonga ba de ni
NK115(re)001:10126: sems can thams cad la byams pa bsgom pa'i mi
NK115(re)001:10127: mthun pa'i phyogs chen po yin te sems can thams
NK115(re)001:10128: cad kham tshang ba'i phyir byanga chub semas dapara nyes
NK115(re)001:10129: pa raba tu lci ba yin na dngos su gazhana
NK115(re)001:10130: bde ba dang ldan pa mthong nas de la mi
NK115(re)001:10131: dga' bar 'di dang brala bar gyur na ci ma
NK115(re)001:10132: rung snyam du 'doda pa bskyed pa la rtsa ltung
NK115(re)001:10133: 'byung ba smosa ci dgosa te sems can gcig tsam
NK115(re)001:10134: la'ang rung ste kun dkris tshang na dngos gazhi'o //
NK115(re)001:10136: 'dis gnas skabs tsam du byams pa 'dor ba yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:10137: gcig shos kyis ni gtan du blos btang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:10138: 'o na lci yang gi go rim dang 'gal lo snyam na /
NK115(re)001:10139: 'di sems bskyed 'dor ba'i rgyur 'gyur nyen che bas sngon du bzhag pa yin nam snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:10140: lnga pa byang sems 'dor ba'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10141: yul sems can gcig nas thams cad kyi bar te
NK115(re)001:10142: gazhana dona du rdzogs pa'i byang chub don du gnyer
NK115(re)001:10143: zhing dam bca' ba'i rnam rig dang dngos su 'gal
NK115(re)001:10144: ba'i byanga chuba semas kyi zur gnyis gang yang rung
NK115(re)001:10145: ba nyams te spangas pa'i blo skyes pa'i moda la
NK115(re)001:10146: smona semas rtsa ba nas gtonga bar 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:10147: / de btang na 'jug sdom yang med par byed
NK115(re)001:10148: pas theg chen mdo sngags kyi lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK115(re)001:10149: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems
NK115(re)001:10150: yin pas da btang ba tsam gyis kuna dkrisa tshanga
NK115(re)001:10151: ba'i phama para gyur pa yina gyi yan lag gzhan
NK115(re)001:10153: khyad par gsang dbang gi lam pas skyug bro'i dbang gis thabs shes kyi khu khrag spangs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10154: shes rab ye shes kyi lam pas gannga ba'i skabas
NK115(re)001:10155: bduna po gang yang rung ba mina para 'dod chags
NK115(re)001:10156: kyi sems kyis dbyung 'dod kyi kun slong gis khu
NK115(re)001:10157: ba phyung ba ste de yang kun dkris tshang na
NK115(re)001:10158: ltung ba'i dngos gzhi bskyed do //
NK115(re)001:10160: gsang ba'i dbang dang gsum pa dang //
NK115(re)001:10161: ro mnyam pa dang lha mchod dang //
NK115(re)001:10162: rigs rgyud spel dang ril bu dang //
NK115(re)001:10163: 'chi ltas brtag pa'i dus yin no //
NK115(re)001:10165: druga pa grub mtha' smod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10167: rang ngam gzhan gyi grub pa'i mtha' //
NK115(re)001:10168: zhes gsungs pa la rang nang pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10169: gzhan phyi rol pa la byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10170: yang na rang gsang sngags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10171: gzhan mtshan nyid theg pa la byed pa'i tshul gnyis las rang lugs ni snga ma ltar te /
NK115(re)001:10172: de la mu stegs can rnams dang theg pa 'og
NK115(re)001:10173: ma'i grub pa'i mtha' rnams la brtags shing dpyad nas
NK115(re)001:10174: pha rol po'i dngos zhen tshar gcod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10175: de yang dag pa'i lam la dkri zhing rjes su 'dzin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10176: yang dag pa'i chos la rgol ba sel ba sogs
NK115(re)001:10177: pa'i dgos pa yod na nyes pa med par ma
NK115(re)001:10178: zad don che zhing bsod nams dang ldan par bshad
NK115(re)001:10179: mod / de lta ma yin par mchog dman du
NK115(re)001:10180: bltas te khyad gsod dang phyogs zhen gyis mu stegs
NK115(re)001:10181: pa'i lam la'ang smad par mi bya ste /
NK115(re)001:10182: de dag gi lam phal cher na bstan pa'i dkar
NK115(re)001:10183: chos rnams kyang mngon mtho'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir dang
NK115(re)001:10184: / kun slong chags sdang gis byas pa rnams lam dang 'gal ba'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:10185: byang sems kyis gzhan sems bsrung dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:10186: khyad par du gsang sngags pas snang ba dag pa rab 'byams su slob dgos pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:10188: mu stegs can la smad byas na //
NK115(re)001:10189: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK115(re)001:10192: gang zhig chos 'di mthong nas chags byed cing //
NK115(re)001:10193: chos ma yin pa thos nas khong khro ba //
NK115(re)001:10194: nga rgyal rgyags pas bcom nas log pa yi //
NK115(re)001:10195: nga rgyal dbang gis sdug bsngal rjes su myong //
NK115(re)001:10198: mu stegs pa'am nyan thos pa //
NK115(re)001:10199: dman kyang de la brnyas mi bya //
NK115(re)001:10202: phyi rol pa'ang lam tshol zhugs //
NK115(re)001:10203: de phyir de la smad mi bya //
NK115(re)001:10204: lam zhugs nyan thos smos ci dgos //
NK115(re)001:10206: khyad par du'ang nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK115(re)001:10207: byang chub sems dpa'i thega pa gsuma po gang yang
NK115(re)001:10208: rung ba la ltos pa ste gtogs pa'i rgyal ba'i
NK115(re)001:10209: bka'a ni gdul bya sna tshogs pa 'dul ba'i dbang
NK115(re)001:10210: gis / mdo dang sngags kyi rim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10211: de yang byung ba'i dus dang /
NK115(re)001:10213: ston tshul gyi rnam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10214: lam gyi 'gros la sogs pa mi 'dra ba sna
NK115(re)001:10215: tshogs par de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi cho 'phrul
NK115(re)001:10216: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mthus gdul bya'i skal ba
NK115(re)001:10217: dang 'tshams par snang ba yin pa la tshul de
NK115(re)001:10218: lta bu mi shes par phyogs gcig tu zhen nas
NK115(re)001:10219: ngag gis 'phya smod kyis dpyasa shinga skur ba 'debs
NK115(re)001:10220: pa dang / 'di la bka' dang mi 'dra ba'i
NK115(re)001:10221: rgyu mtshan 'di 'dra ba snang bas ston pasa ma
NK115(re)001:10222: pa dang / gsungas so // bka' ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:10223: lam rnam dag ma yin no zhesa smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10226: dngosa gruba rnam pa gnyis gang yang rung ba 'grub pa'i rgyur rung ba'i dag snang dang /
NK115(re)001:10227: gter ma'i phyogs su gtogs pa'i sngags kyi cho ga dang /
NK115(re)001:10228: man ngag gi khrid la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:10229: mdo sngags kyi dgongs pa 'grel pa'i bstan bcosa rgya
NK115(re)001:10230: bod kyi mkhas grub dag gis mdzad pa gazhana thams
NK115(re)001:10231: cad kyang rgyal ba'i bka' dang dgos pa mthun zhing
NK115(re)001:10232: rjes su gannga ba dang byina gyis barlabas pa'i bka'a
NK115(re)001:10233: yi phyogs su gtogs pas thar 'dod rnams kyis kun
NK115(re)001:10234: la gus par byed dgos te /
NK115(re)001:10236: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK115(re)001:10237: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK115(re)001:10238: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK115(re)001:10239: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK115(re)001:10241: gal te gus par mi byed pa'i steng /
NK115(re)001:10242: bka' dang mthun zhing yon tan dang ldan pa de
NK115(re)001:10243: ru ma bltasa par bshad sgros sogs rang phyogs dang
NK115(re)001:10244: mi mthun pa cung zad res skyon du bltas te
NK115(re)001:10245: brnyas shinga skur ba btab na chos spong ba'i las
NK115(re)001:10246: su 'gyur bas na don med pa'i nyes pa chen
NK115(re)001:10247: po de lta bu la'ang gzab par bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:10248: khyad par du snying thag pa nas bka' dang bstan
NK115(re)001:10249: bcos de dag gi tshig dang don gyi cha la
NK115(re)001:10251: bka'i phyogs su ma gtogs so //
NK115(re)001:10252: thar pa'i lam ma yin no zhes smod cing kun dkris tshang na ltung ba'i dngos gazhi'o //
NK115(re)001:10253: des na bde mchog rtsa rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:10254: zab mo'i chos ni 'chad pa la //
NK115(re)001:10255: gal te mos par ma gyur kyang //
NK115(re)001:10256: smod pa dag ni mi bya ste //
NK115(re)001:10257: chos nyid bsam mi khyab dran bya //
NK115(re)001:10258: gang gis 'di bdag yul min pa //
NK115(re)001:10259: bdag gis chos nyid mi shes yin //
NK115(re)001:10260: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang de yi sras //
NK115(re)001:10261: bdag nyid chen po rnams kyis mkhyen //
NK115(re)001:10262: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul la bsam par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10263: bduna pa gsang ba sgrog pa'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10265: log par lta ba goms pas las 'bras sogs la'ang
NK115(re)001:10266: yid mi ches pa'i snod min pa la ni gtan
NK115(re)001:10267: nas sngags kyi chos ston mi rung la /
NK115(re)001:10268: dabnga gi cho ga ma byas pa ste bum dbang
NK115(re)001:10269: tsam yang ma thob pa la bskyed rim ston pa
NK115(re)001:10270: dang / cho ga ma rdzogas pa ste dbang gong
NK115(re)001:10271: ma rnams ma thob pa la rdzogs rim zab mo
NK115(re)001:10272: dang / ston pa dang / nyamsa pa ste rtsa
NK115(re)001:10273: ltung byung yang phyir mi 'chos shing khe nyen la
NK115(re)001:10274: yid ches pa'i shes rab med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10275: snoda ngana te dbang thob kyang gsang sngags zaba mo'i lta spyod thos pas skraga pa'i rigs dang /
NK115(re)001:10276: sngags kyi 'dula ba'i dusa kyi bskal te zab mo
NK115(re)001:10277: ston pa'i skabas la ma bab pa'am ma ran pa
NK115(re)001:10278: dang / gansa kyisa bskala ba ste dgag bya dmigs
NK115(re)001:10279: bsal yod pa rnams la gasnga sngagas rdo rje theg
NK115(re)001:10280: pa'i lam thun mong ma yin pa'i lta sgom zaba
NK115(re)001:10281: mo'i dona rjen par bkral nas rgyun bshad lta bur
NK115(re)001:10282: dang / byed pa dang / nyams len gyi dgongas pa barlinga po dang /
NK115(re)001:10283: spyoda pa rmad du byung ba 'di lta bu'o zhes
NK115(re)001:10284: khrid du 'debs pa lta bu'i sgo nas bsgragas pa
NK115(re)001:10285: ste de rnams kun dkris tshang na dmigas kyis basla
NK115(re)001:10286: te rtsa ltung gi dngos gzhir gsungs pa yina gyi
NK115(re)001:10287: / gzhan du rigs gtad dang rjesa gannga dang bzlasa
NK115(re)001:10288: lunga tsam gyis kyanga gasnga sgroga tu 'gyur bar ngosa
NK115(re)001:10289: 'dzina pa yod na'ang 'dira ni snoda la brtag par
NK115(re)001:10290: bya ste rtsa ltung du grub pa'i tshad ni pha
NK115(re)001:10291: rol po skrag pa skye ba la gsungs pas de
NK115(re)001:10292: / tsam gyis / ma dad pa mi skye ba'i
NK115(re)001:10293: rigs la mi rung ba med kyang shin tu log
NK115(re)001:10294: lta che ba la ni gsang sgrog tu 'gyur ro
NK115(re)001:10295: / tsam gyis / snyam mo // brgyada pa phung po smod pa'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10296: 'di'i yul phyi nang gi gzugas kyi phunga po ni
NK115(re)001:10297: gdod ma nas rnama par snanga mdzad kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:10298: yin la / sogas khongs nas tshor ba rin 'byung /
NK115(re)001:10301: rnam shes mi bskyod pa ste rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:10303: de bzhina du mig la sogs pa nang dang //
NK115(re)001:10304: gzugs la sogs pa phyi'i skye mcheda rnams sems dpa'
NK115(re)001:10305: sems ma la sogs pa'i lha'i skura ye nas dag
NK115(re)001:10307: rnal 'byor pas kyang de ltar yin pa'i tshul shes shing gsal btab nas nang gi sbyin bsreg dang //
NK115(re)001:10308: tshogs kyi 'khor lo la sogs pas mchod cing /
NK115(re)001:10309: 'dod yon gyis mnyes par bya rgyu la /
NK115(re)001:10310: tshul de lta bu mi shesa para kun 'byung gis
NK115(re)001:10311: bskyed pa'i sduga bsngal gyi bdena pa'i rang bzhin can
NK115(re)001:10312: du mngon para bsgruba par byed pa'i theg pa 'og
NK115(re)001:10313: ma'i rtoga ge'i blosa gzhal te brnyas sems kyis yan
NK115(re)001:10318: rgud par bya ba'i bsam pas gnas ma yin pa tsha grang sogs 'byung du 'jug pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10319: smyung bar gnas pa la sogs pa daka'a thuba kyi
NK115(re)001:10320: mthu yisa lhaga para gdunga bar byed cing lha'i 'du
NK115(re)001:10321: shes las log ste brnyas sems mthar thug skyes nas
NK115(re)001:10322: kun dkris tshang na rtsa ltung rdzogs pa yin no
NK115(re)001:10323: // de 'dra'i brnyas sems med na chos phyir dka' spyad mi rung ba min no //
NK115(re)001:10324: 'di la 'ga' zhig yul sems can gang yang rung ba'i phung po min te /
NK115(re)001:10325: sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa rang gi phung po nyid
NK115(re)001:10326: rigs lnga'i bdag nyid du lha'i rnal 'byor gyis byin
NK115(re)001:10327: gyis brlabs yod pas de la brnyas pa sogs byas
NK115(re)001:10328: pa yin no zhes ngos 'dzin mdzad 'dug kyang lta
NK115(re)001:10329: ba'i 'dod tshul gyi dbang gis rgyud sde'i dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:10330: de ltar bkral ba yin nam snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:10331: dgu pa rang bzhin dag pa'i chos la the tshom za ba'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10332: 'di ltar gzhi lam 'bras bus bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK115(re)001:10333: cad kyi ranga bzhina gdod nas rnam par daga cing
NK115(re)001:10334: / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:10335: ba'i ngo bo spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK115(re)001:10336: stong pa nyid dang zung du 'jug pa'i tshul du
NK115(re)001:10337: bstan pa'i dona de ni sgrib pa thams cad dang
NK115(re)001:10338: bral ba'i sangas rgyas kho na'i spyod yul te gnas
NK115(re)001:10339: tshul nyid yin gyi de lasa gazhana semas can thams
NK115(re)001:10340: cad kyi khamas bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang
NK115(re)001:10341: 'brela bar bzhugs pas glo bur gyi dri ma dag
NK115(re)001:10342: ma dag tsam las sems can dang sangs rgyas gnyis
NK115(re)001:10343: khyad par med ces pa'i don 'di ni byis pa
NK115(re)001:10344: rnams skrag pa spang ste lam la spro ba bskyed
NK115(re)001:10345: pa'i phyir rang bzhin med pa tsam la dgongs nas
NK115(re)001:10346: gsungs pa'i phyir ldema por dgongas pa kho na yin
NK115(re)001:10347: / no snyam nas / zab mo'i mdo dang rgyud sde rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:10348: de dag gi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos rnams
NK115(re)001:10349: kyang drang don gyi phyogs su bzung nas chos nyid
NK115(re)001:10350: zab mo'i don la yid mi ches pa ste /
NK115(re)001:10351: de la'ang yin shas che snyam pa'i don 'gyur gyi the tshom dang /
NK115(re)001:10352: min shas che snyam pa'i don mi 'gyur gyi the tshom dang /
NK115(re)001:10353: yin nam ma yin snyam pa'i blo gnyis su 'byung
NK115(re)001:10354: ba'i yid gnyis za ba ste gsum las rtsa ltung
NK115(re)001:10355: du grub pa'i tshad ni don mi 'gyur gyi the
NK115(re)001:10356: tshoma zosa nasa yang dag pa'i lam de la bkri
NK115(re)001:10357: bar spangas pa'i blo skyes nas kun dkris tshang ba'o
NK115(re)001:10358: // bcu pa gdug pa can mi sgrol ba'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10359: de la spyir dkona mchoga gsuma la ma dad cing
NK115(re)001:10360: smod la 'tshe bar byed pa'i dkon mchog gi sku
NK115(re)001:10361: dgra dang / bye brag rang gi bla ma la
NK115(re)001:10362: smoda cing sdang bas gnod sbyor la brtson pa slob
NK115(re)001:10364: rgyal ba'i bstan pa lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid
NK115(re)001:10365: can bshad sgrub gnyis kyi sgo nas gnas pa de
NK115(re)001:10366: thabs sna tshogs pas 'jiga par byed pa ste de
NK115(re)001:10367: yang bstan pa gnas zhes pa 'di ni chos dang
NK115(re)001:10368: dge 'dun las gzhan min te bstan pa ni chos
NK115(re)001:10369: dang / bstan 'dzin ni bla ma dang dge 'dun yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:10370: des na de nyid 'jig par byed pa po de
NK115(re)001:10371: sku dgra gnyis las logs su brtsi rgyu min kyang
NK115(re)001:10372: dmigs kyis bsal nas gsungs pa ste nus pa cung
NK115(re)001:10373: zad thob pas kyang rang bzhin du 'jog pa'i 'os
NK115(re)001:10375: sogas khongs nas dam tshig nyams kyang ji mi snyam
NK115(re)001:10376: pas slar mi gso zhing nyams pa'i spyod pa mi
NK115(re)001:10377: gtong ba dang / sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa las slar log ste khyad gsod byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10378: gsang sngags kyi chos la 'khu ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10379: sngags spyod la 'du bar mi dbang bzhin du brku thabs sam shed spyod kyis 'ong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10380: sems can yongs la gnod pa byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10381: dam tshig can la dgra byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10382: mi dge ba 'ba' zhig la 'jug pa ngan pa'i
NK115(re)001:10383: ngang tshul can te sdug bsngal gyi rgyu la spyod
NK115(re)001:10384: pa dgu dang / 'bras bu la spyod pa ngan
NK115(re)001:10385: song gsum po gcig tu brtsis pa'i bcu po de
NK115(re)001:10386: ni draga shul gyi cho ga yi sgo nas sgrol
NK115(re)001:10387: ba'i las mangna du spyod pa'i yul du gsungs te
NK115(re)001:10388: pa dgu dang / / gsal bkra las /
NK115(re)001:10389: 1dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK115(re)001:10392: dam 8dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can 9 //
NK115(re)001:10393: ngan song gsum 10dang bcu po ni //
NK115(re)001:10394: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK115(re)001:10396: de yang sngags lam la zhugs pa'i gang zag spyir
NK115(re)001:10397: btang bas bla ma dang dkon mchog la smod pa
NK115(re)001:10398: la sogs pa'i bsam sbyor ma rungs pa can de
NK115(re)001:10399: la srana cinga bzoda de yi rang ba'i sems kyis
NK115(re)001:10400: spyod lam 'drisa shinga phan 'dogs pa'i bshesa su sbrel
NK115(re)001:10401: nasa lus ngag gis byamsa para byas pa dang kun
NK115(re)001:10404: gdug la thog ma bar mtha' byams //
NK115(re)001:10406: 'on kyang sems kyis byams pa btang na rtsa ltung bzhi bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK115(re)001:10407: byang chub kyi sems dang ldan zhing rtogs pas bdag
NK115(re)001:10408: bsgral ba'i gang zag nus pa thob pa'i dmigs bsal
NK115(re)001:10409: ba rnams kyis ni lus ngag gis byams par mi
NK115(re)001:10410: byed par ma zad ma bsgral na ltung bar gsungs
NK115(re)001:10411: la / de'ang sku dgra gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:10412: khyad par du rgyal bstan rin po che gnas su
NK115(re)001:10413: mi 'jug pa'i rigs rnams thabs gzhan gang gis kyang
NK115(re)001:10414: bzlog ma nus na lta dgongs dang ldan zhing rnam
NK115(re)001:10415: par shes pa dag pa'i zhing sogs su spar nus
NK115(re)001:10416: pa zhig yin na smos ci dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:10417: snying rje dang ldan zhing rang 'dod kyi blo med
NK115(re)001:10418: na dngos sam rdzas sngags kyis kyang de sgrol bar
NK115(re)001:10419: byed rigs te / bstan 'gro la phan thogs pa
NK115(re)001:10420: dang gdug pa can de'i las ngan rgyun chod pa'i
NK115(re)001:10421: byed rigs te / phyir ro // gal te de
NK115(re)001:10422: ltar shes shing nus bzhin du ma bsgral na dam
NK115(re)001:10425: gdug pa rnams las bzlog bya ste //
NK115(re)001:10426: dngos su'am yang na sngags dang gzhan //
NK115(re)001:10428: sman gyis kyang ni bya ba ste //
NK115(re)001:10429: de ltar ma byas de yis ni //
NK115(re)001:10430: dam tshig nges par nyams par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:10432: gzhan yang g.yo sgyus byams pa ltar ston zhing kha
NK115(re)001:10433: 'jam la zhe gdug par byed na'ang rtsa ltung du
NK115(re)001:10435: de dag las gzhan pa rnams dang ngan song gsum
NK115(re)001:10436: po ni spyi tsam du bsgral ba'i zhing du smos
NK115(re)001:10437: kyang / de dang de'i rnam par shes pa zhing khams rnam dag tu gnas spor nus pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10438: sngon dang phyi mtha' shes pas ngan 'gro'i rgyu la
NK115(re)001:10439: spyod pa dag gi 'bras bu ngan pa 'gog cing
NK115(re)001:10440: yun thung ngur byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10441: 'bras bu la spyod pa dag gnas ngan las sgrol nus pa rnams la dgongs kyis /
NK115(re)001:10442: de ltar mi nus pas de rnams la mngon spyod ma byas kyang rtsa ltung du mi 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:10443: bcu gciga pa ming bral chos la tshad mas gzhal ba'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10444: chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin ni btags pa'i minga dang /
NK115(re)001:10446: mtshon pa'i brda la sogs pa dang brala zhing tha snyad thams cad las 'das kyang /
NK115(re)001:10447: chosa nyid de la tha snyad pa'i blo tshad mas
NK115(re)001:10448: stong pa bdag med pa sogs su gazhala nas mthar
NK115(re)001:10449: 'dzin stangs thams cad dang bral ba'i dbyings la 'jog
NK115(re)001:10450: pa'i go ba gshis thog tu ma sleb pa tsam
NK115(re)001:10451: gyis rab tu phye ba de la mthar thug tu
NK115(re)001:10452: zhen cing chosa kyi badga meda pa so so rang
NK115(re)001:10453: gi rig pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul las tha
NK115(re)001:10454: snyad pa'i blo'am rnam shes dang rdzasa 'agla ba yin
NK115(re)001:10455: bzhina du rtog dpyod kyi rig pa rnon pos phunga
NK115(re)001:10456: po la sogas pa'i chos rnams stonga pa nyi tshe
NK115(re)001:10457: bar thos bsam gyis gtan la phebs pa de gnas
NK115(re)001:10458: lugs su blta zhing lta ba la mchog tu 'dzina
NK115(re)001:10459: pa'i blosa mnyam par 'jog pa'i dus nyid na'ang skye
NK115(re)001:10460: ba med pa'i gruba matha'a chos nyid bsam gyis mi
NK115(re)001:10461: khyab pa'i don rtog pa rang mtshan pasa 'ajala zhing
NK115(re)001:10462: mngon par rlom par byas nas kun dkris tshang bar
NK115(re)001:10463: gyur pa'o // de skad du gur las /
NK115(re)001:10464: chos nyid tshad ni gzung mi bya //
NK115(re)001:10467: chos la tshad mas gzhal mi bya //
NK115(re)001:10469: bcu gnyis pa dad ldan sems sun 'byin pa'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10470: sngagas kyi snod runga bla ma'i man ngag 'dzin pa la dbang ba'i gdula bya'am /
NK115(re)001:10471: min kyang rang bzhin du chos la dang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10473: yid ches pa'i dada pa ste gsuma dang ldana pa la /
NK115(re)001:10474: des dona du gnyer ba'i chosa re ston nus bzhin
NK115(re)001:10475: du le lo la sogs pa'i dbang gis mi ston
NK115(re)001:10476: pa tsam ma yin par g.yo sgyu dang chos min
NK115(re)001:10477: gyis de'i dad pa bzlog 'dod kyi kun slong ngan
NK115(re)001:10478: pas / gzhan de'i don du gnyer bya de dang
NK115(re)001:10479: 'gal ba'i tshig smras te sems sun phyung nas dad
NK115(re)001:10480: pa dang 'dun pa phyin ci log tu skyogs pas
NK115(re)001:10481: dad 'dun log cing kuna dkris tshang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:10482: bcu gsuma pa dam rdzas ji bzhin mi bsten pa'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10483: 'di la sngags bla med kyi rtsa ltung du 'gro tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:10484: rnal 'byor rgyud dang thun mong gi rtsa ltung du 'gro tshul gnyis yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:10485: dang po ni spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel bas spyad par bya ba'i dama tshig gi rdzasa /
NK115(re)001:10486: sha lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga dang chang la sogs pa bza' btung gi yo byad dang /
NK115(re)001:10487: dar gos zhing lpags rus rgyan la sogs pa bcangs pa'i yo byad dang /
NK115(re)001:10488: bro gar glu tshigs rig ma la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yo byad rnams tshogs kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK115(re)001:10489: dpa' bo dang dpa' mo'i dga' ston la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:10490: bsten pa'i skabs la bab pa'i tshe na rang rang
NK115(re)001:10491: gi lta sgom gyi nus pa dang bstun pa'i dgag
NK115(re)001:10492: dgos brtsis te dam rdzas khyad du mi gsod cing
NK115(re)001:10493: chags srid rang mtshan par ma gol bas mthar gnyis
NK115(re)001:10494: su ma lhung ba zhig dgos pa la /
NK115(re)001:10495: bza' btung la sogs pa'i dngos po ranga rgyud du
NK115(re)001:10496: bltas nasa ro mi zhim pa dang dri nga ba
NK115(re)001:10498: de las ldog pa la lara chags sreda kyis bsten par byed pa'am /
NK115(re)001:10499: chos nyid mnyam pa'i don rtogs pas ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:10500: rgyan du blang dor med par rol pa'i gsang sngagas
NK115(re)001:10501: kyi brtul zhugas ji lta ba bzhina lta sgom gyi
NK115(re)001:10502: stobs kyis nyamsa 'oga tu ma chud par /
NK115(re)001:10503: nyan thos kyi spyod pa kho na la phyogs gcig
NK115(re)001:10504: tu zhen pa'i mchog 'dzin gyis gtan nas mi bsten
NK115(re)001:10505: pa'am / yang na lta dgongs kyi gdeng med bzhin
NK115(re)001:10506: du smyo thabs kyis bab col du spyod pas matha'a
NK115(re)001:10507: gnyisa kyi mala du 'khyamsa pa dang kun dkris tshang
NK115(re)001:10508: pa'am / ba'o // gnyis pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK115(re)001:10509: dang thun mong gi rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:10510: pa'am / ba'o // ni / rdor dril dang bcas
NK115(re)001:10511: pa'i phyag rgya bsgyur ba la sogs pa ni thabs
NK115(re)001:10512: dang shes rab kyi sgom pa yod na ci dgos
NK115(re)001:10513: snyams nas dgos med du spang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:10514: de la khyad gsod kyi bsam pa yod na rtsa ltung gnyis par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs /
NK115(re)001:10515: yang rdor dril sogs kyi dag pa ma dran par 'phyad smod dang bzhad gad byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10516: dran shes med bzhin bab col du dkrol ba sogs nyes byas su gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:10517: bcu bzhi pa shes rab ma la smod pa'i rtsa ltung ni /
NK115(re)001:10518: rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la sogas pa 'jiga rten
NK115(re)001:10519: las 'adsa pa'i ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma dag
NK115(re)001:10520: la smad na yo ga dang bla med gnyis ka'i
NK115(re)001:10521: rtsa ltung yin par gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:10522: ma mo dang mkha'a 'gro ma la sogas pa 'jig
NK115(re)001:10523: rten las 'das kyang 'jig rten pa'i tshul bzung nas
NK115(re)001:10524: legs nyes kyi stangs 'dzin zhing dam tshig gi rjes
NK115(re)001:10525: gcod pa'i sngags kyi rnal 'byor ma rnams ni 'khor
NK115(re)001:10529: bskal pa mang po'i sngon rol nas //
NK115(re)001:10530: dus gsum rgyal ba'i zhal mthong ste //
NK115(re)001:10531: dman pa'i zhing 'dir sprul sku yi //
NK115(re)001:10532: lha mo'i tshul du skur bstan nas //
NK115(re)001:10533: 'gro ba'i don la rab tu brtson //
NK115(re)001:10534: nyon mongs sgrib pa rab tu spangs //
NK115(re)001:10535: da lta shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong //
NK115(re)001:10536: zhes e ka tsa ti'i sprul par bstan pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:10537: 'jig rten pa'i tshul du yod pa'i ma mo dang
NK115(re)001:10538: mkha' 'gro thams cad la smod par byed pa dang
NK115(re)001:10539: / 'byung ba lnga yi khamas yum lnga yi rang
NK115(re)001:10540: bzhin yin par ma shes nas sa la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:10541: ranga rgyud par bltas te snying nas smod par byed
NK115(re)001:10542: / pa dang / spyir bud med thams cad shes
NK115(re)001:10543: rab kyi rang bzhin yin pas de la smad na
NK115(re)001:10546: bud med thams cad la smod pa gang yin pa
NK115(re)001:10547: de ni nges par te gdon mi za bar ma
NK115(re)001:10548: nu zhes pa bcu bzhi par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:10551: rtsod pa'i dus 'dir 'gro ba rnams bud med la
NK115(re)001:10552: rab tu zhen pas de rnams 'dul ba'i phyir bud
NK115(re)001:10553: med du sprul pa'i lha rnams 'di na gnas pas
NK115(re)001:10554: mi smod / zhes gsungs pa ltar bud med kyi
NK115(re)001:10555: khrod na rdo rje phag mo la sogs pa'i sprul
NK115(re)001:10556: pa'ang yod na gang yin mi shes pas thams cad
NK115(re)001:10557: la mi smod par yang gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:10558: khyad par du bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i yeshesa
NK115(re)001:10559: bskyed par byed pa'i zab mo'i dabnga gi rten du
NK115(re)001:10560: gyur pa'i buda meda la snying nas smoda par byed
NK115(re)001:10561: pa gzhan nam des go zhing de thams cad la
NK115(re)001:10562: kun dkris tshang na ltung ba'i dngos gzhir 'gyur ba'o
NK115(re)001:10563: / de yang dgongs gzhi dang dgos pa'i dbang gis
NK115(re)001:10564: bcom ldan 'das kyis thun mong gi mdo sde rnams
NK115(re)001:10565: las bud med kyi nyes dmigs gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10566: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis kyang de dang tshul mthun par smod par mdzad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10567: dgos ched dang ldan pa yin la de las gzhan
NK115(re)001:10568: pa dag gis ni don med par bud med kyi
NK115(re)001:10569: rigs thams cad la smod par mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10570: de yang smod pa'i yul bud med de sngags bla
NK115(re)001:10571: med kyi sdom pa dang ldan pa ma yin pa
NK115(re)001:10572: zhig dgos kyi / sngags sdom dang ldan pa yin
NK115(re)001:10573: na bla ma dang mched gang rung las mi 'da'
NK115(re)001:10574: ba'i phyir rtsa ltung dang po dang gsum par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:10575: ro zhes gsungs pa'ang snang la /
NK115(re)001:10576: 'byung lnga smod pa ni phung po smod pa'i nang du'ang gtogs mod /
NK115(re)001:10577: 'dir sngags sdom dang ldan pa'i ma mo mkha' 'gro la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10578: 'byung ba lnga la smod pa rtsa ltung bcu bzhi
NK115(re)001:10579: par yang bshad pa ni de thams cad shes rab
NK115(re)001:10580: dbyings kyi rang bzhin du rtogs pa'i lta ba las
NK115(re)001:10581: log pa'i kun slong gis bskyed pa yin pa dang
NK115(re)001:10582: / ltung ba'i mtshams kyang rang rang gi skabs nas
NK115(re)001:10583: bshad pa ltar yin pas gcig tu mi 'gyur par
NK115(re)001:10584: / sems so // de ltar bcu bzhi po de thams cad mdor bsdu na gsum du 'du ste /
NK115(re)001:10585: sngags kyi chos ston pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK115(re)001:10587: nyams su blang bya'i chos gsum la brten pa'i ltung ba gsum gyi dbye ba tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:10588: de yang slob dpon la brten nas rtsa ltung dang po dang /
NK115(re)001:10590: yang dag pa'i grogs la brten nas gsum pa dang bcu gnyis pa gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:10591: phyin ci log gi grogs la brten nas bcu pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10592: nyams su blang bya'i chos la lung dang sgrub pa'i chos gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:10593: lung gi chos la brten nas gnyis pa /
NK115(re)001:10596: sgrub pa'i chos la lam gyi gzhi /
NK115(re)001:10598: lam gyi yan lag gsum las /
NK115(re)001:10599: lam gyi gzhi la brten nas bzhi pa dang lnga pa gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:10600: lam gyi ngo bo bskyed rim la brten nas brgyad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10601: rdzogs rim la brten nas dgu pa dang bcu gcig pa gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:10602: lam gyi yan lag la brten nas bcu gsum pa
NK115(re)001:10603: dang bcu bzhi pa gnyis rnams 'byung ba yin no
NK115(re)001:10604: // gnyis pa yan lag sbom po'i rnam grangs bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:10605: sbom po brgyad bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10606: de las gzhan pa'i sbom po'i rnam grangs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:10607: dang po sbom po brgyad bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:10610: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10611: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi po'i rjes su mthun pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10612: 'di dag bsrung na rtsa ba'i ltung ba rnams kyang
NK115(re)001:10613: mi nyams pa'i thabs su 'gro bas yan lag ste
NK115(re)001:10614: / de yang rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa'i
NK115(re)001:10615: yan lag tshang rung sdoma pa gtong byed kyi phama
NK115(re)001:10617: dngosa gruba myur du thoba pa la gegas su che
NK115(re)001:10618: ba'i nyes pa sboma po rnam pa brgyad yoda de
NK115(re)001:10619: zhes pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10620: dabnga gis rgyud ma smin pa dang dama tshiga dang
NK115(re)001:10621: sdoma pa la gnas pa'i sgo nas rgyud ma sbyangsa
NK115(re)001:10622: pa'i tha mala du gnas pa'i buda meda riga mara
NK115(re)001:10623: bsten pa tsam ni dang po'o //
NK115(re)001:10624: rgyud las gsungs pa'i matshana nyid ma tshang bas bsten
NK115(re)001:10625: byar 'agla ba'i drana pa'i khrona pa ste mkha' gsang
NK115(re)001:10626: nasa / bde stong gi ye shes bskyed pa'i cho
NK115(re)001:10627: ga ji lta ba bzhin ma yina bzhina pasa ril
NK115(re)001:10628: bu'am bde ba'i rgyur bduda rtsi ste dmar cha rang
NK115(re)001:10629: gi rlung stobs kyis lena pa gnyis pa'o //
NK115(re)001:10630: dabnga ma thoba pa dang lhag para yang gsang sngags kyi chos la dada pa meda pa'i rigs la /
NK115(re)001:10631: yi dam lha'i sku gzugas dang rgyud dang man ngag
NK115(re)001:10632: gi glegas bama dang rdo rje dang dril bu la
NK115(re)001:10634: bca' ba'i phyaga rgya sogs dgos pa med par ston pa gsum pa'o //
NK115(re)001:10635: tshogas kyi 'khora lo la sogs pa gsang sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:10636: cho ga'i tshogs gral du 'dus pa'i dusa na bla
NK115(re)001:10637: ma'am rdo rje'i spun la mnar sems pa med par
NK115(re)001:10638: lus ngag gis 'phen btsogs dang kha shags sogs 'athaba
NK115(re)001:10640: baba cola te dran shes kyis ngag mi sdom par
NK115(re)001:10641: mtshar gtam sogs kyala ka sna tshogs smras pas bsam
NK115(re)001:10642: gtan gyi brtul zhugas tha mala par sbyar nas g.yeng
NK115(re)001:10644: snod du rung zhing dad pa dang ldana pas dama
NK115(re)001:10645: pa'i chosa kyi tshig don 'dri ba la de'i don
NK115(re)001:10646: shesa bzhina du 'dun pa dkyogs 'dod ma yin par
NK115(re)001:10647: don de lasa 'agla ba'i bsnyon dora te rnam pa
NK115(re)001:10648: gzhan don med pa zhig lana du ldona te smra
NK115(re)001:10649: ba lnga pa'o // sngagas kyi lta spyod la skura
NK115(re)001:10650: zhing nyamsa sad pa ste tshod blta ba'i nyan thosa
NK115(re)001:10651: dngos sam rtog ge ba'i nanga du zhaga bduna du
NK115(re)001:10652: longas para bsdada pa drug pa'o //
NK115(re)001:10653: sngagas kyi rgyud sde'i don dang /
NK115(re)001:10654: phyi nang gsang ba'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:10655: cho ga'i dngos don sogs mi shesa bzhina du bdag
NK115(re)001:10656: rdo rje 'dzina para rlom nas nga rgyal zhing gzhan
NK115(re)001:10657: dag mgo bskor ba'i rdzuna dang 'grogas pa bdun pa'o
NK115(re)001:10658: // dabnga bskur tsam thoba kyanga sngagas kyi lta dgongs
NK115(re)001:10659: zab mo la ha cang mi dada pa'i the tshoma
NK115(re)001:10660: cana man ngag slob bshad kyi yul ma yin pa
NK115(re)001:10661: tshogs bshad tsam bstan bya'i yul de la slara yanga
NK115(re)001:10662: gasnga ba'i don man ngag gi tshul du 'achada pa
NK115(re)001:10663: // ni brgyad pa'o // de lta bu'i sbom po'i
NK115(re)001:10664: rnam grangs brgyad po de ni dpal mgon 'phags pa
NK115(re)001:10665: klu sgruba kyis rgyud las bsdus pa'i dgongs pa yin
NK115(re)001:10666: // ni brgyad pa'o // no // gnyis pa de
NK115(re)001:10667: las gzhan pa'i sbom po'i rnam grangs bshad pa ni
NK115(re)001:10668: // ni brgyad pa'o // no // / spyir sbom
NK115(re)001:10669: po'i ltung ba de tsam gyis zad pa ma yin
NK115(re)001:10670: kyang rags rim brgyad du bsdus te bstan pa de
NK115(re)001:10671: bzhina du de dang cha mthun pa slob dpon dapa'a
NK115(re)001:10673: rnal 'byor gang zhig rig ma ni //
NK115(re)001:10674: dam tshig med la'ang stobs kyis spyod //
NK115(re)001:10675: de la 'phya bar byed pa yang //
NK115(re)001:10676: de yi ltung ba dang por gsungs //
NK115(re)001:10677: rgyud las ma gsungs rang nyid kyi //
NK115(re)001:10678: gang zhig bdud rtsi bsten pa yang //
NK115(re)001:10679: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10680: rdo rje snying po rgyan las /
NK115(re)001:10681: gong gi sbom po brgyad po las /
NK115(re)001:10683: sngags par rlom pa gnyis ma gtogs pa'i lhag ma drug dang mthun pa'i sbom po drug bstan zhing /
NK115(re)001:10684: yang de dang don mthun pa'i steng du /
NK115(re)001:10685: rnal 'byor ma lak+shim k+aa ra ste phun tshogs 'byung
NK115(re)001:10686: gnas kyis dam tshig kun las btus pa'i 'grel bar
NK115(re)001:10687: / de dag las dona gazhana pa gnyis bsnan nas sbom po brgyad du byas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:10688: de'ang grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa gang rung la
NK115(re)001:10689: bsten nas lha'i rnal 'byor daga para ma byas bzhin
NK115(re)001:10690: du dabnga bskura ba dang raba gansa dang sbyin srega
NK115(re)001:10691: sogs dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba la zhugs nas sloba
NK115(re)001:10692: ma 'khor du bsdu bar ringas ba ste sngas pa
NK115(re)001:10693: dang / bza' btung byin gyis brlabs nas lha'i rnal
NK115(re)001:10694: 'byor dang ldan pas bza' ba'i dam tshig la spyod
NK115(re)001:10695: pa'i gnas skabs tshogas 'khor gyi dus lasa gazhana du
NK115(re)001:10696: yang phyi dro'i kha zasa za ba sogas so thar
NK115(re)001:10697: dang byang sems kyi skabs kyi bacasa pa la dgosa
NK115(re)001:10698: pa chen po yod par mi shes par khyad gsod
NK115(re)001:10699: meda kyang ci mi snyam du lus nas 'ad'a ba'o
NK115(re)001:10700: dang / // de 'dra ba yi sbom po rnams kyis kyang /
NK115(re)001:10701: badga nyid kyi bslab pa suna 'byin pa'i skyon can
NK115(re)001:10702: du gyur na sngags la mos pas spyad pas yon
NK115(re)001:10703: tan gong 'phel du song ba las dngosa gruba thob
NK115(re)001:10704: pa 'phroga pa ste de la gegs byed pa'i rgyur
NK115(re)001:10705: gsungas pa'i sboma po de rnamas la'ang brtaga para bya
NK115(re)001:10706: dgos so // gsum pa rtsa ltung gi khungs bshad pa gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:10708: de las gzhan pa'i rtsa ltung gi khungs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:10709: dang po rtsa ltung gong ma'i khungs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10710: 'di ltar rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:10711: thuna monga gi rtsa ltung bcu bzhira b+ha wi lha
NK115(re)001:10712: ste slob dpon dpa' bos bsdus pa de ni bla
NK115(re)001:10713: med kyi rgyud sde kun la khyaba cinga gsar rnying
NK115(re)001:10714: thams cad la yongas su gragas pa ste sngara bstan
NK115(re)001:10715: pa'i bcu bzhi po rnams so //
NK115(re)001:10716: gnyis pa de las gzhan pa'i rtsa ltung gi khungs ni /
NK115(re)001:10717: gong du bstan pa de las gazhana du bya spyod
NK115(re)001:10718: rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyuda sde bzhi po so
NK115(re)001:10719: so'i ranga lugas kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i grangas ngesa
NK115(re)001:10723: rnam snang mngona byang sogas lasa gasla pora gsungas pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:10724: de yang bla med kyi rtsa ltung dus 'khor du gsungs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10726: dpal ldan bla ma'i thugs dkrugs pa las bu rnams
NK115(re)001:10727: kyi ni rtsa ba'i ltung ba ri bong 'dzin par
NK115(re)001:10729: bud med thams cad la smod nges par ma nur
NK115(re)001:10730: 'gyur te rdo rje theg par gnas pa rnams la'o
NK115(re)001:10731: // zhes pa'i bar te 'di dang gong du bshad pa gnyis phal cher mtshungs so //
NK115(re)001:10732: bya rgyud kyi bcu bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:10734: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK115(re)001:10735: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK115(re)001:10737: gsang sngags rgyud ni legs bsrung zhing //
NK115(re)001:10738: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bya /
NK115(re)001:10743: bla ma dang mched grogs la gus pa /
NK115(re)001:10744: 'das ma 'das kyi lha gzhan la mi sdang ba /
NK115(re)001:10745: rang gi lha dus tshigs su mchod pa /
NK115(re)001:10747: glo bur ba'i mgron mchod pa /
NK115(re)001:10749: sems can gyi don la brtson pa mi 'dor ba /
NK115(re)001:10751: dam tshig gzhan yang ci nus su bsrung ba /
NK115(re)001:10752: snod min la sngags rgya mi sbyin pa /
NK115(re)001:10753: rang gi sngags rgyud bsrung zhing rtogs par bya ba
NK115(re)001:10754: rnams te bcu bzhi po'i mi mthun phyogs rnams rtsa
NK115(re)001:10757: ji skad bshad pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK115(re)001:10758: gal te nyams par gang gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:10759: de ni rang rig snying po'i sngags //
NK115(re)001:10760: chig 'bum du ni bzlas brjod bya //
NK115(re)001:10761: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:10762: spyod rgyud kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:10764: bcu po 'di dag byang chub sems dpa' gsang sngags
NK115(re)001:10765: kyi sgor spyod pa'i bslab pa thams cad kyi rtsa
NK115(re)001:10766: ba yin pas gzhi zhes bya'o zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:10767: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bzhi ni srog gi phyir yang yongs su nyams par mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10768: zhes mi dge bcu spong gi tshul khrims kyi steng
NK115(re)001:10769: du rtsa ba bzhi ste bcu bzhi bsrung bar gsungs
NK115(re)001:10770: so // rtsa ba bzhi ni de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:10771: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyis //
NK115(re)001:10772: dam pa'i chos dang byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:10773: srog gi phyir yang da phyin chad //
NK115(re)001:10774: yongs su btang bar mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10775: khyod kyis ser sna dang ni gang //
NK115(re)001:10776: sems can gnod pa mi bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10777: dam tshig 'di dag sangs rgyas kyi //
NK115(re)001:10778: brtul zhugs bzang po khyod la bshad //
NK115(re)001:10779: ces pas de bzhi'i ldog phyogs dam chos spong ba sogs bzhi'o //
NK115(re)001:10780: 'o na mi dge bcu spong ni lha mi'i theg
NK115(re)001:10781: pa dang nyan rang la'ang yod pas sngags kyi khyad
NK115(re)001:10782: par gyi rtsa ltung du ci'i phyir 'jog ce na
NK115(re)001:10784: gang dag 'das dang ma byon dang //
NK115(re)001:10785: gang yang da lta'i mgon po rnams //
NK115(re)001:10786: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa la //
NK115(re)001:10787: bslabs nas bla med byang chub ni //
NK115(re)001:10788: 'dus ma byas pa de thob bo //
NK115(re)001:10789: thabs dang mi ldan ye shes dang //
NK115(re)001:10790: bslab pa dag kyang bshad pa ni //
NK115(re)001:10791: dpa' bo chen pos nyan thos rnams //
NK115(re)001:10792: de la gzud pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK115(re)001:10793: zhes thabs shes kyis zin pa'i khyad par gyis yin no //
NK115(re)001:10794: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi bcu bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:10796: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK115(re)001:10797: ji lta dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK115(re)001:10798: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa //
NK115(re)001:10799: zhes pa la sogs pa rigs lnga'i sdom bzung bstan pa las /
NK115(re)001:10800: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi tshul khrims ni dkon
NK115(re)001:10801: mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro mi gtong ba ste gsum
NK115(re)001:10802: / rdo rje'i rigs la rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya slob dpon gzung ba ste bzhi //
NK115(re)001:10804: chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs byams pa sbyin pa ste bzhi /
NK115(re)001:10805: pad+ma'i rigs la dam pa'i chos ma lus pa 'dzin pa ste gcig /
NK115(re)001:10806: las kyi rigs la sdom pa de rnams mi gtong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10807: mchod pa'i las la brtson pa dang gnyis te de
NK115(re)001:10808: rnams bsdoms pas bcu bzhi ni bsgrub pa'i bslab bya
NK115(re)001:10809: yin la / de las gzhan pa bcu bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:10810: phas pham par ni rab tu bshad //
NK115(re)001:10811: spong ba dor bar mi bya ste //
NK115(re)001:10812: rtsa ba'i ltung ba zhes bshad do //
NK115(re)001:10813: zhes pa la ngos 'dzin mi mthun pa mang yang /
NK115(re)001:10814: 'dir bsgrub pa'i bslab bya bcu bzhi po de las gzhan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:10815: de'i ldog phyogs bcu bzhi po la bzhag pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:10816: de ltar rgyud sde so so'i ltung ba'i dbye ba
NK115(re)001:10817: dang mtshams rnam par bzhag pa de thams cad khong
NK115(re)001:10818: du chud par byas te phan tshun gung bsgrigs shes
NK115(re)001:10819: na bla med kyi bcu bzhi bo'i nang du thams
NK115(re)001:10820: cad 'du ba'i tshul gyis bsrung chog pa yin pas
NK115(re)001:10821: rnam grangs mang ba tsam gyis ni dka' ba ci
NK115(re)001:10822: yang med do // drug pa nyams na phyir bcos pa'i thabs bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:10823: khe nyen brjod pa'i sgo nas phyir bcos dgos par gdams pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10825: dang po phyir bcos dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10826: dbang bskur thob cing bskyed rdzogs kyi rnala 'byora la
NK115(re)001:10827: brtson pa dang ldana pa rnams ni dam tshig gi
NK115(re)001:10828: phyir rgyal po'i btson rar chud pa sogs 'chi ba'i
NK115(re)001:10830: srog gtong dgos kyang sla ste /
NK115(re)001:10831: dus rtag tu dam tshiga rnams snying nor du bcangs
NK115(re)001:10832: te mngon lkog thub pa zhig bsrunga bar ma byasa
NK115(re)001:10833: na dmyal ba'i gnas su 'gro ba las 'os med
NK115(re)001:10834: de / sngagas lam la zhugs shing spyod pa'i skyes
NK115(re)001:10835: bu ni sbrul smyug dong du bcug pa bzhin dam
NK115(re)001:10836: tshig nyams shing phyir bcos pa'i thabs la ma brtson
NK115(re)001:10837: na shi ma thag ngana songa dmyal ba'i gnas su
NK115(re)001:10839: zhi rgyas la sogs pa'i las gang bsgrub kyang mi 'grub cing /
NK115(re)001:10840: srung ma rnams mchod kyang mi 'khor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:10841: nad gdon dang dgras mnar ba sogs tshe 'dir yang sdug bsngal bar 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:10843: sngags kyi dngos grub don 'dod na //
NK115(re)001:10844: dam tshig bsrung la brtson par bya //
NK115(re)001:10845: gzhan du byas na sngags mkhan gyis //
NK115(re)001:10846: sngags la sogs pa'i don mi 'grub //
NK115(re)001:10847: lha rnams kyang ni dam tshig gis //
NK115(re)001:10848: gsol yang bzhes su mi gnang ste //
NK115(re)001:10850: 'jig rten pha rol dmyal ba rnams //
NK115(re)001:10851: dam tshig spyod las 'das pa yi //
NK115(re)001:10852: rmongs pa'i bdag nyid de thob bo //
NK115(re)001:10854: dam tshig rnam par dag pa zhig bsrungs na tshe
NK115(re)001:10855: 'dir ji skad bshad pa'i nyes dmigs de thams cad
NK115(re)001:10856: las ldog pa'i yon tan thob cing /
NK115(re)001:10857: ji ltar 'gor yang skye ba bcu drug tshun chad sangas rgyas thob par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:10859: gal te ltung ba med gyur na /
NK115(re)001:10860: skye ba bcu drug dag la 'grub //
NK115(re)001:10862: de'i phyir yar mar gang rung du 'gro ba gnyis
NK115(re)001:10863: po de lasa 'gro sa gsum pa bar ma lta
NK115(re)001:10864: bu zhig med do zhes dam tshig dang ldan pa
NK115(re)001:10865: rnam bar do tshun chad du ma grol na gnas
NK115(re)001:10866: skabs mtho ris dang dag pa'i zhing sogs su 'gro
NK115(re)001:10867: yang slar ngan song sogs su ltung bar mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:10868: bar rim gyis grol bar 'gyur bas /
NK115(re)001:10869: mngon mtho'i rgyu kho na bsgrub pa rnams srid rtse'i
NK115(re)001:10870: bar du song nas slar ltung ba lta bu dang
NK115(re)001:10871: / nyan rang rnams kyis thar pa'i 'bras bu nyi tshe ba thob pa lta bu ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:10872: dam tshig nyams pa rnams kyang las de stobs che
NK115(re)001:10873: bas sngon la smin pa las mngon mtho thob byed
NK115(re)001:10874: kyi dge ba yod kyang de sngon la smin mi
NK115(re)001:10875: nus te / las kyi 'khor bar lci gang dang //
NK115(re)001:10876: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:10877: rgyu mtshan de dag gi phyira na sngags kyi ltung
NK115(re)001:10878: ba grangs mang ba dang rang gnyen po chung bas
NK115(re)001:10879: ltung ba'i nyes pa zhig byung na de mthong ba'i
NK115(re)001:10880: tshe na de'i nyes dmigs dran zhing 'gyod pa drag
NK115(re)001:10881: pos bdag nyid sun phyung ste bsam sbyor gnyis ka'i
NK115(re)001:10882: cha la smad nasa ltung ba de dang lhan du
NK115(re)001:10883: skad cig kyang gnas par mi 'dod pa'i bsam pas
NK115(re)001:10884: phyir bcosa pa'i thabsa la phyi bshol med par de
NK115(re)001:10885: ma thaga tu 'abda par bya dgos par gdams so
NK115(re)001:10886: // gnyis pa phyir bcos dngos bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:10887: spyir rtsa ba'i ltung ba thams cad la kun dkris
NK115(re)001:10888: tshang bar gyur na sdom pa nyams par byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:10889: rgyu yin pas phyir bcos tshul bzhin byas nas sdom
NK115(re)001:10891: khyad para rtsa ltung dang po slob dpon la smod pa ni nyes pa shina tu lci ste /
NK115(re)001:10893: bla ma la ni smod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:10894: thugs dkrugs pa yi nyes pa ni //
NK115(re)001:10895: phyi yi rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK115(re)001:10896: chu de skra yis gtor gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:10897: de yi tshad du sdug bsngal myong //
NK115(re)001:10898: rdo rje'i dmyal bar grags pa yin //
NK115(re)001:10899: zhes sngar drangs pa ltar yin pas /
NK115(re)001:10900: da lta rang la rang dbang yod pas de lta
NK115(re)001:10901: bu'i nyes pa de'i phyogs tsam yang mi 'byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:10903: gal te ltung ba byung bar gyur na /
NK115(re)001:10904: snying nas 'gyod pa drag pos kha zas za ba
NK115(re)001:10905: yang yi gar mi 'ong ba tsam du bskyed de
NK115(re)001:10906: / bla ma la lhag par dad cing mos pas
NK115(re)001:10907: sgo gsum gyis bsnyen bkur zhing 'khora gsuma yongas daga
NK115(re)001:10908: ste yod dgu'i dngos po thams cad 'bula zhing bshags
NK115(re)001:10909: pa byas la thugs zin par bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:10910: de'i rjes su dabnga bskur bskyar nasa zhus te sdoma pa gsora gzhuga cinga /
NK115(re)001:10911: gal te bla ma mi bzhugs pa'am nye bar mi
NK115(re)001:10912: gansa pa dang lam 'phrang 'tshe bas bkab pa lta
NK115(re)001:10913: bus mi nus na bla ma dkyil 'khor kun gyi
NK115(re)001:10914: khyab bdag tu shes pas badga 'juga lan grangs manga
NK115(re)001:10915: du blanga nas sor chud par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10916: de yang phyis kyang bdag 'jug la sogs pas sor
NK115(re)001:10917: chud par 'gyur bas sla'o snyam du sdom sems brtan
NK115(re)001:10918: po med na dug nad kyis gzir nas sman pa
NK115(re)001:10919: bsten te sman btung nas slar yang dug za bar
NK115(re)001:10920: byed pa bzhin nyes pa rgyun mi 'chad cing dngos
NK115(re)001:10921: grub thob pa'i dus mi 'ong bas sdom sems brtan
NK115(re)001:10923: tshul de ni nyes ltung sbyong ba'i cha thams cad la shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:10924: de yang thog ma nas ltung bas ma gos pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10925: bcos nas sor chud pa gnyis kyang khyad par che ba'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:10926: thabs la mkhas pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:10928: dper na nyan thos kyi theg pa can la rtsa
NK115(re)001:10929: ba'i ltung ba byung na phung po de nyid kyis
NK115(re)001:10930: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i skal pa med do //
NK115(re)001:10931: zhes tshe de la dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob mi nus par gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10932: de bzhin du byang sa las /
NK115(re)001:10933: byang chub sems kyi rtsa ltung byung na tshe de
NK115(re)001:10934: las dang po thob mi srid par gsungs pa dang
NK115(re)001:10936: tshul de lta bu'i sgo nas rtsa ba'i ltung ba
NK115(re)001:10937: thams cad phyir bcos shing sdom pa nod par byas
NK115(re)001:10938: la / de bzhina du gazhana sbom po gtso bor
NK115(re)001:10939: gyur pa'i nyes ltung rnams la 'gyod sdom drag pos
NK115(re)001:10940: rang gi dmigs pas bshags na'ang 'dag rung la /
NK115(re)001:10941: dbang dang bdag 'jug sogs ma byas kyang sngags sdom
NK115(re)001:10942: med pa min zhing dbang rnon gyis rtsa ltung yang
NK115(re)001:10943: rang stobs kho nas sbyang rung ba ni 'og tu
NK115(re)001:10945: 'on kyang khrela yoda dang ngo tsha'i rtena du gal
NK115(re)001:10946: te bla ma med na sngagas kyi sdoma pa la
NK115(re)001:10947: nyes ltung gi skyon med cing rnam par dag pa
NK115(re)001:10948: dang ldana pa zhig gi mduna du bshags par bya
NK115(re)001:10950: ltung sogs nyes pa'i rim pa las //
NK115(re)001:10951: dang po bdag sems sun phyung ste /
NK115(re)001:10952: yul mdun snyan gsan phab nas kyang //
NK115(re)001:10953: gsum blang gsum 'gal bshags pa dang //
NK115(re)001:10955: de yang 'byor na dpa' bo'i ston mo sogs byas pa'i rjes su /
NK115(re)001:10956: phyag 'tshal ba dang spyod lam zhi zhing dula basa
NK115(re)001:10957: rgyal ba sras bcas dang rig pa 'dzin pa chen
NK115(re)001:10958: po la mkhyen par gsol nas /
NK115(re)001:10959: ranga gi gsang ba'i minga nas smosa nasa bdag ma rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:10960: nyon mongs pa'i dbang du gyur bas rig pa 'dzin
NK115(re)001:10961: pa'i sde snod chen po'i tshul khrims kyi bslab pa'i
NK115(re)001:10962: gzhi las rdo rje thega pa'i 'dula ba dang 'agla
NK115(re)001:10963: ba'i nongas pa bla ma smod pa la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:10964: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:10965: yan lag sbom po'i rnam grangs brgyad las 'di dang 'di byung basa /
NK115(re)001:10966: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams dang rig pa
NK115(re)001:10967: 'dzin pa chen po'i spyan sngar 'achaba pa ste sbed
NK115(re)001:10968: cing gsang na ni badga nyid nyes ltung dang bral
NK115(re)001:10969: ba'i bde ba la reg par gansa pa'i skabs 'byung
NK115(re)001:10970: bar mi 'gyura bas 'achaba pa meda par snying nas
NK115(re)001:10971: bshags shing phyin chad legas para sdom par bagyi'o zhes
NK115(re)001:10973: de la khyod kyis nyes ltung 'di rnams la mnyes
NK115(re)001:10974: para tshul bzhin du mthong ngama zhes dris pa ni
NK115(re)001:10975: / ranga gisa kyang gnod 'gyod dang bcas nas mthonga lagas zhes brjod /
NK115(re)001:10976: bshags yula gyisa phyin chad legs par sdoma para byed dama zhes dri ba na /
NK115(re)001:10977: rang gis kyang sdom sems brtan po'i dam bca' dang
NK115(re)001:10978: bcas chosa bzhina 'dula ba bzhina du spyi bosa noda
NK115(re)001:10979: ces spyi bo'i gtsugs tu khur ba lta bu'i sgo
NK115(re)001:10980: nas dang du blangs te dam baca'o zhes pa'i don
NK115(re)001:10981: no // de skad cesa mthong sdom dri ba dang
NK115(re)001:10982: bcas pa lana gsuma brjod na nyes pa mthong zhing
NK115(re)001:10983: dran pa dang sdom sems brtan par 'gyur bas rtsa
NK115(re)001:10984: ba'i tshig gis dngos bstan ltar byas na legs par
NK115(re)001:10985: no // mngon no // de ltar byas pa'i rjes la bshags yul gyis thabas yin no //
NK115(re)001:10986: zhes nyes ltung dag pa'i thabs yin par bstan pas
NK115(re)001:10987: rang gis legas so zhes de yin par nges shes
NK115(re)001:10988: bskyed par bya'o // gala te de lta bu'i phyir
NK115(re)001:10989: bcos tshul bzhin du byed pa de phyir 'gyangsa par
NK115(re)001:10990: 'gyur na zhag re re bzhina du nyes pa de
NK115(re)001:10993: rtag tu bag med pa gnas dang //
NK115(re)001:10994: nyes pa chung du phra mo yang //
NK115(re)001:10995: sbrul gyi mche bas btab bzhin du //
NK115(re)001:10996: lus ngag sems ni nyams par byed //
NK115(re)001:10998: des na de ltar 'phel bar 'gyur ba de yi
NK115(re)001:10999: gnyen po ru dmigs nas nyin mtshan lan drug gam
NK115(re)001:11000: gsum la sogs par gsang chen rigs gcig rdo rje
NK115(re)001:11001: sems dpa' spyi bor bsgoms te stobas bzhi tshanga ba'i
NK115(re)001:11002: ngang nas yi ge brgya ba nyer gcig gam brgya
NK115(re)001:11003: stong la sogs pa ma yengs par ci nus su
NK115(re)001:11004: bzlas pas rtag tu bashagas shing /
NK115(re)001:11005: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i sngo bgranga brjod pa'i bashagas tshiga
NK115(re)001:11006: b+ha wi lhas mdzad pa dang sbom ltung gi bshags
NK115(re)001:11007: tshig sogs kyang gdona par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:11008: de yang yi ge brgya pa 'don tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:11010: de'i me'i sar mig spel bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:11011: zhes pas sarba sid+d+hi che ge mo pra yats+tsha zhes gdon pa'i don to //
NK115(re)001:11012: des ni ltung ba 'phel ba'i rgyun chad par 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:11014: rdo rje sems dpa' la dmigs te //
NK115(re)001:11015: yi ge brgya pa cho ga bzhin //
NK115(re)001:11016: nyi shu rtsa gcig re re bzlas //
NK115(re)001:11017: ltung sogs byin gyis brlabs gyur bas //
NK115(re)001:11019: grub pa mchog rnams kyis bshad pas //
NK115(re)001:11020: thun mtshams su ni sbyang bar bya //
NK115(re)001:11021: 'bum phrag du ni bzlas gyur na //
NK115(re)001:11022: rnam par dag pa'i bdag nyid 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:11024: gnyis pa mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi khyad par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:11028: gsar rgyud rnams dang thun mong du ma gyur pa'i
NK115(re)001:11029: khyad para ba spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa dang
NK115(re)001:11031: semas sde rdzogs pa chen po ste snga 'gyur gyi
NK115(re)001:11032: rgyud sde gsuma po'i ringa lugas kyi bsrung bya dam
NK115(re)001:11035: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:11036: spyi mdo dgongs 'dus kyi lugs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11037: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lugs bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11038: sems phyogs rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:11039: dang po spyi mdo dgongs 'dus kyi lugs bshad pa ni //
NK115(re)001:11041: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK115(re)001:11042: bsrung dang spyad dang yid 'ong dang //
NK115(re)001:11043: mi 'dor shes bya bsgrub pa dang //
NK115(re)001:11044: zhes pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:11045: bsrung ba'i yul lha dang bla ma gnyis su med par gtso bo yin la /
NK115(re)001:11046: bsrung tshul phan 'dogs pa dang gnod pa spang ba'i
NK115(re)001:11047: gzhi'i gtso bo lus yin pas sku yi dam tshig
NK115(re)001:11048: tu bla ma dang lha la gus par blta zhing
NK115(re)001:11049: / mched dang lcam dral gyis mtshon pa'i 'gro ba
NK115(re)001:11050: thams cad bla ma'i sku'i gdula bya yin pas gnod
NK115(re)001:11052: rnam par smin pa'i lus kyi snang zhen bskyed rim gyis sbyong bar byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:11053: dge mi dge'i rnam 'gyur thams cad ngag la brten
NK115(re)001:11054: nas bskyed pas gsung gi dam tshig tu sngags dang
NK115(re)001:11055: phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11056: ngag gi nyes pa spang ba'i phyir bla mas ci gsung bsgrub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11057: mched lcam gyi ngag mi gcog pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:11058: 'khor ba bskyed pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo yid yin pas
NK115(re)001:11059: thugas rdo rje yi dam tshig tu yid kyi nyes
NK115(re)001:11060: pa spang zhing gsang ba gzhan la mi spel ba
NK115(re)001:11061: dang / byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gnyis bskyed cing bla ma dang thugs yid bsre ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11062: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo du ma la spyod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:11064: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK115(re)001:11065: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK115(re)001:11066: snang stong gnyis med rdo rje'i sku //
NK115(re)001:11067: byas mthong thos pa thams cad kyang //
NK115(re)001:11068: sems phyir gang yang byas snang med //
NK115(re)001:11069: dran dang shes bzhin sngon btang la //
NK115(re)001:11070: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK115(re)001:11071: theg chen sngags par ci yis chud //
NK115(re)001:11073: de ltar rtsa ba'i bsrunga bya gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:11074: yan lag gi dam tshig thabs ldan du spyada par bya ba tan gan sogs lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11075: yida 'onga ste spang byar mi blta bas lam du byed pa nyon mongs lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11076: sme bar bltas nas mi 'dora ba bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11077: lta bas lhar shesa par bya ba phung po 'byung yul sogs lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11078: bsgoms pas dbyer med du bsgruba par byed pa de
NK115(re)001:11079: bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sogs pa lnga'i dbye basa
NK115(re)001:11080: nyi shu rtsa lnga ste rtsa ba'i gsum dang bsdoms
NK115(re)001:11082: yan lag nyer lnga po de rnams ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:11083: gnyis pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lugs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11084: rgyud sde sgyu 'phrula gyi lugs la rtsa ba'i dama tshiga rnama pa lnga gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:11086: bla med mi spong bla ma bkur //
NK115(re)001:11087: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK115(re)001:11088: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK115(re)001:11089: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11090: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK115(re)001:11091: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK115(re)001:11093: yan lag gi dam tshig rnam pa bcur bashada de /
NK115(re)001:11094: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK115(re)001:11095: nga rgyal phra dog mi spong ngo //
NK115(re)001:11096: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK115(re)001:11097: dag pa'i snod chu mi dor ro //
NK115(re)001:11099: dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi phyogas bshad pa la ni /
NK115(re)001:11101: byang sems rnam gnyis slob dpon drug /
NK115(re)001:11102: mched bzhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi //
NK115(re)001:11103: gsang bcu rtsa bar shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:11105: dang po bla med mi spong zhes pa byang chub kyi sems gnyis yin te /
NK115(re)001:11106: don dam byang chub kyi sems lhag pa bden pa
NK115(re)001:11107: dbyer med chos sku chen po'i ngang du 'jog pa
NK115(re)001:11108: dang / kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems de ltar
NK115(re)001:11109: ma rtogs pa'i sems can thams cad sgrol 'dod kyi
NK115(re)001:11111: 'dir yi dam gyi lha bsgom pa nyid la 'du
NK115(re)001:11112: ba'i dbang du mdzad de logs su ma gsungs la
NK115(re)001:11113: / de yang theg chen spyi'i lugs kyi byang chub kyi sems mi gtong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11114: dkon mchog la bsnyen bkur mi 'dor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11115: sngags phyi bas de'i steng du rang gi lhag pa'i
NK115(re)001:11116: lha mchod cing bsgom par bstan pa de dag kyang
NK115(re)001:11117: 'dir stong nyid dang snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:11118: ngang las rtags kyi lha sku phyag rgya bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:11119: la 'du ste / sangs rgyas dang dge 'dun ni
NK115(re)001:11120: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK115(re)001:11122: chos ni de'i chos nyid yin pas byang chub kyi
NK115(re)001:11123: sems dang chos nyid ni kun rdzob tsam du chos
NK115(re)001:11124: can bdag nyid gcig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11125: don dam par spros pa nye bar zhi ba'i rang
NK115(re)001:11126: bzhin yin pas zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes de'i
NK115(re)001:11127: rtags kyi phyag rgya lha sku yin pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11129: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:11130: de stsol bla ma de rgya lhag pa'i lha //
NK115(re)001:11132: de ltar 'du ba'i tshul shes par byas nas 'dir bshad par bya ba ni bzhi yin te /
NK115(re)001:11133: de yang bla ma bkur ba la yul ni slo dpon drug gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:11135: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK115(re)001:11136: nyams chags skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK115(re)001:11137: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /
NK115(re)001:11138: ces pas kun gyis bkur gnas su gyur zhing rang
NK115(re)001:11139: gis kyang chos 'brel cung zad thob pa spyi'i slob
NK115(re)001:11140: dpon dang / rab byung gi mkhan po lta bu chos sgor 'dren pa'i //
NK115(re)001:11141: dbang bskur ba po dam tshig dbang gi //
NK115(re)001:11142: ltung ba bshags pa'i yul nyams chag skong ba'i /
NK115(re)001:11143: rgyud sogs 'chad pa po shes rgyud 'grol ba'i /
NK115(re)001:11144: khrid 'chad pa po man ngag lung gi slob dpon te drug po yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:11145: de dag las gsang sngags kyi chos kyi bka' drin
NK115(re)001:11146: thob pa ni rdo rje slob dpona du gyur pas
NK115(re)001:11147: gnyan la / khyad par du dbang bskur rgyud bshad
NK115(re)001:11148: man ngag ston pa gsum shin tu gnyan pas de
NK115(re)001:11149: rnams mi sponga zhig bkura stis ji ltar bsnyen pa'i
NK115(re)001:11150: gnyan la / tshul ni / bka' drin thob tshul gyis dpe dang sbyar nas rim bzhin gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:11152: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK115(re)001:11153: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK115(re)001:11154: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul bltas te //
NK115(re)001:11156: sngags rgyu rgyun mi bcad pa'i yul ni /
NK115(re)001:11158: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK115(re)001:11159: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK115(re)001:11160: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK115(re)001:11161: zhes pas sngagas gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi po rab
