NK115(re)001:11162: chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam nyin mtshan gyi thun la
NK115(re)001:11163: gnas pa dang / 'bring gis zla ba ngo rer dus drug gam bzhi la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11164: tha mas kyang lo zla'i dus mchod kyis rgyuna mi bacada para bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11165: mched la byams pa la yul ni /
NK115(re)001:11166: sngar gyi bzhi po yin la /
NK115(re)001:11167: de rnams las kyang yang dag pa'i lam du zhugas pa'i mched phyi ma gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:11168: de'i nang nas kyang 'dres pa'i mched lhag par gnyan
NK115(re)001:11169: par shes pa'i rim pas de rnams la rtag tu
NK115(re)001:11170: mi 'bral zhing phan 'dogs pa'i lhag bsam gyis brtse
NK115(re)001:11171: zhing gdung bas byamas para byed pa ste /
NK115(re)001:11173: rdo rje spun la gdung sems kyang //
NK115(re)001:11175: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la //
NK115(re)001:11176: rngan dang bcas pa'i sems tsam yang //
NK115(re)001:11177: rtag tu spang bar bya ba yin //
NK115(re)001:11178: brtse zhing gdung ba'i shugs phyung la //
NK115(re)001:11179: gcig la gcig ni mig bzhin blta //
NK115(re)001:11180: mdor na srog la'ang mi chags par //
NK115(re)001:11181: spun dang ming sring dgos pa sgrub //
NK115(re)001:11182: ci'i phyir rdo rje'i spun rnams ni //
NK115(re)001:11183: 'di nas byang chub bar dag tu //
NK115(re)001:11187: gsang ba mi smra ba la /
NK115(re)001:11188: gang la gsang ba'i yul ni /
NK115(re)001:11190: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK115(re)001:11191: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK115(re)001:11193: zhes lta ba zab mo ni theg dman sogs blo
NK115(re)001:11194: 'phang dma' ba thams cad la gsang zhing spyod pa
NK115(re)001:11195: ni ma 'dres pa thams cad la gsang ngo //
NK115(re)001:11196: lha'i ming gzungs sogs ma 'dres pa la bstan na dam tshig nyams shing /
NK115(re)001:11197: 'dres pa la bstan na'ang dngos grub nyams par gsungs pas thams cad la gsang ngo //
NK115(re)001:11198: gang zhig gasnga bar bya ba'i dona ni /
NK115(re)001:11200: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:11201: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu /
NK115(re)001:11202: zhes gsang ba bcu po de rnams rang rang gi
NK115(re)001:11203: yul dang dus kyi dmigs nges pas gzhan la mi
NK115(re)001:11204: bsgrag pa'o // de la spyi gsang bzhi ni gsal bkra las /
NK115(re)001:11205: lta zab spyod pa barlinga po dang //
NK115(re)001:11206: lha'i ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK115(re)001:11207: spyi gsang rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK115(re)001:11211: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK115(re)001:11212: bar du gsang la bsgrub par bya //
NK115(re)001:11215: thun mong ma yin pa'i sngags kyi spyod pa dang
NK115(re)001:11216: dam rdzas mched kyi ngan spyod sogs mthong thos su
NK115(re)001:11218: gnyer gtad pa ni bla ma dang mched kyis gsang bar bka' rgyas btab pa rnams so //
NK115(re)001:11219: rtsa ba'i dam tshig 'di rnams sgrub bsrung dang sku
NK115(re)001:11220: gsung thugs kyi dam tshig tu bzhag pa'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:11221: rgyud 'grel rnams las gsung tshul mi 'dra ba cung
NK115(re)001:11222: zad byung yang / byang sems dang sngags rgya gnyis sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK115(re)001:11223: gzhan gsum bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin la /
NK115(re)001:11224: yang sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gi dbang du byas na //
NK115(re)001:11225: bla ma dang mched la bsrung ba sku'i dam tshig /
NK115(re)001:11226: sngags rgya gsung gi dam tshig /
NK115(re)001:11227: gsang bcu thugs kyi dam tshig yin zhing byang sems kyang mdor bsdu rigs te /
NK115(re)001:11229: byang chub sems gsum bsgom pa ni //
NK115(re)001:11230: rdo rje thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK115(re)001:11232: rtsa ba'i dam tshig de dag la dbye na brgya dang drug cu ste /
NK115(re)001:11233: de yang theg pa 'og ma'i bsrung sdom ltar mtshan
NK115(re)001:11234: mar bzung nas spang blang gnyis su byed pa ma
NK115(re)001:11235: yin par bsrung bya'i yul bsrung ba po srung byed
NK115(re)001:11236: kyi bsam sbyor thams cad chos nyid don gyi lha
NK115(re)001:11237: rig pa'i ye shes chen po'i rol bar bltas nas
NK115(re)001:11238: tha snyad du blang dor byed kyang don la bzang
NK115(re)001:11239: ngan dang blang dor med par shes rab kyis zin
NK115(re)001:11240: pas bla med mi spong ba lta bu gcig la
NK115(re)001:11241: thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyi cha yod la /
NK115(re)001:11242: de gnyis po re re la /
NK115(re)001:11243: 'gag pa med pa'i cha nas sku /
NK115(re)001:11245: zung 'jug thugs gsum re rer phye bas drug /
NK115(re)001:11247: rten byed pa'i cha nas sku /
NK115(re)001:11248: nyams su myong ba'i cha gsung /
NK115(re)001:11249: rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i cha thugs /
NK115(re)001:11250: rang rang gi chos so sor snang ba'i cha yon tan /
NK115(re)001:11251: de dag gis don byed pa'i cha phrin las te
NK115(re)001:11252: lnga rer phye bas drug lnga sum cur 'gyur la
NK115(re)001:11253: / de'i steng du dbye gzhi gcig po dang /
NK115(re)001:11254: drug po ma bsnan par thabs shes gnyis bsnan pas
NK115(re)001:11255: sum cu rtsa gnyis te bla med mi spong ba
NK115(re)001:11256: la sum cu rtsa gnyis yod pa de bzhin du
NK115(re)001:11257: / bla ma bkur ba sogs gzhan bzhi la'ang sbyar
NK115(re)001:11258: bas so gnyis pa lnga bsdoms pas brgya drug cu'o
NK115(re)001:11259: / // rtsa ba srung byed kyi thabs su gyur
NK115(re)001:11260: pa'i yan lag gi dama tshiga ni mi spang ba
NK115(re)001:11261: dang mi dor ba'i sde tshana gnyis su bsdu bar
NK115(re)001:11262: bya zhing dang po'i phyogas la ni /
NK115(re)001:11263: gti mug dang 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang nga
NK115(re)001:11264: rgyal dang phrag dog ste nyon mongas pa lnga po
NK115(re)001:11266: de la log pa'i dug lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11267: sbas don yang dag pa'i dug lnga gnyis su yod
NK115(re)001:11268: pa las log pa'i dug la ni nyon mongs pa
NK115(re)001:11269: dngos yin zhing de mi spang ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:11270: chags sogs kyi ranga bzhina shesa pasa nyon mongas pa'i
NK115(re)001:11271: de bzhina nyid dam rang gi ngo bo ni ngo
NK115(re)001:11272: bo med pa yin pas smig rgyu'i chu la chu
NK115(re)001:11273: rags mi dgos pa bzhin spong byed kyi gnyen po
NK115(re)001:11274: mi dgos la / thabas kyis zina na rna bar
NK115(re)001:11275: chu zhugs pa chus 'gugs pa'am rma byas duga zosa
NK115(re)001:11276: pa dang 'dra bar ye shes kyi grogs su 'gyur
NK115(re)001:11277: bas rang gi gnyen por rang che bas mi spang
NK115(re)001:11278: ba ste nyon mongs pa thabs kyis ma zin par
NK115(re)001:11279: gnyen po gzhan gyi stobs kyis spangs nas 'dus ma
NK115(re)001:11280: byas pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byas pa las sa
NK115(re)001:11281: bon mes tshig pa bzhin sangs rgyas kyi chos gang
NK115(re)001:11282: yang 'byung bar mi 'gyur bas na nyon mongs rang
NK115(re)001:11283: bzhin med par shes shing thabs kyis zin nas ma
NK115(re)001:11284: zhen cing mi 'gag par spyad na theg chen spyi
NK115(re)001:11285: yi lam gyi sems stobs rmad du byung ba dang
NK115(re)001:11286: mi dgos la / / phyin drug gis bsdus pa'i tshogs thams cad dang /
NK115(re)001:11287: sngags kyi lam gyi ye shes dang dngos grub thams
NK115(re)001:11288: cad ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du rgyu sa bon
NK115(re)001:11289: dang rkyen chu lud drod gsher 'dzom pa las 'bras
NK115(re)001:11290: bu rtsol med du smin pa ltar 'byung ste /
NK115(re)001:11292: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa ste //
NK115(re)001:11293: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK115(re)001:11294: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis //
NK115(re)001:11295: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:11297: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang /
NK115(re)001:11298: ji ltar grong khyer ser skya mi gtsang lud //
NK115(re)001:11299: de ni bu ram shing pa'i zhing la phan //
NK115(re)001:11300: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa'i nyon mongs lud //
NK115(re)001:11301: de ni rgyal ba'i chos kyi zhing la phan //
NK115(re)001:11304: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK115(re)001:11305: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:11307: de ltar yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni ye nasa rigas
NK115(re)001:11308: lngara gnas pa'i tshul shesa nas lam du byas pasa
NK115(re)001:11309: rmongs pa'i sgrib pa dag nas ye shesa lngar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:11311: snum 'dod pas til bsgrub par lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:11312: de ltar yang dam tshig nyer brgyad pa las /
NK115(re)001:11313: phrag dog la sogs nyon mongs lnga rnams ni //
NK115(re)001:11314: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:11316: de yang gti mug ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK115(re)001:11317: dam tshig ste chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so
NK115(re)001:11318: // 'dod chags ni snang ba mtha' yas kyi dam tshig ste so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11319: zhe sdang ni mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig ste me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11320: nga rgyal ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dam tshig ste mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11321: phrag dog ni don yod grub pa'i dam tshig ste bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11322: sbas don yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11323: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du rtogs nas lta ba
NK115(re)001:11324: la phyogs ris dang spyod pa la blang dor gyis
NK115(re)001:11326: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can thams cad la thugs rjes chags pa 'dod chags /
NK115(re)001:11327: log par rtog pa rnams sgrol ba zhe sdang /
NK115(re)001:11328: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba gshongs su mi 'bebs pa nga rgyal /
NK115(re)001:11329: gnyis 'dzin gyi lta spyod chasa nyid kyi klong du
NK115(re)001:11330: mi shong ba phrag dog ste 'di rnams lta ba'i
NK115(re)001:11331: ngang du skyong ba la tshang bas rtag tu nyams
NK115(re)001:11333: gnyis pa mi dor ba'i phyogsa ni rdo rje zil
NK115(re)001:11334: pa rak+ta dri chen m+aam sa dri chu ste bduda
NK115(re)001:11335: rtsi chena po lnga po yin la /
NK115(re)001:11336: de dag kyang dang du blang byar nges pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:11337: grub pa bzhi dang yin pa gsum gyi phyir /
NK115(re)001:11338: de la grub pa bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:11339: chos nyid ngo bos grub pa bdud rtsi lnga po
NK115(re)001:11340: chos nyid kyi ngos na gtsang sme gang du'am grub
NK115(re)001:11341: pa'i chosa nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bor
NK115(re)001:11342: grub pas de nyid rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi rola
NK115(re)001:11343: para blanga bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11344: chos can rang bzhin gyis grub pa de dag chos
NK115(re)001:11345: can ltar snang ba'ang rang bzhin rnam par dag pa
NK115(re)001:11346: rigas lnga'i ranga bzhina nyid du grub pas de ltar
NK115(re)001:11347: shesa pa'i sgo nas blanga bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11348: nus pa'i mthus grub pa de dag la brten nas
NK115(re)001:11349: mchog dang thun mong gi dngosa gruba thams cad bsgrub
NK115(re)001:11350: na 'grub pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa'i dama rdzasa
NK115(re)001:11351: yina pasa blanga bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11352: byin gyis rlabs kyis grub pa dam tshig gi rdzas
NK115(re)001:11353: de rnams ni sngon dpal chen po la sogs pas
NK115(re)001:11354: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang gis tshul bzhin du bsten
NK115(re)001:11355: pa'i sgrub pa po de la ma mo mkha'a 'gro
NK115(re)001:11356: thams cad 'du zhing sgrub pa'i grogs byed cing dngosa
NK115(re)001:11357: gruba thob pa nye basa dang du blanga bar bya'o
NK115(re)001:11359: nad lnga sel ba'i sman yin te /
NK115(re)001:11364: byang sems dkar pos tsha ba'i nad rnams sel ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11365: thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11370: byang sems dkar pos mi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa'o //
NK115(re)001:11371: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin te /
NK115(re)001:11372: dri chen bud+d+ha'i rigs chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11373: dri chu las kyi rigs bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11374: m+aam sa rin po che'i rigs mnyam pa nyid kyii ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11375: rak+ta pad+ma'i rigs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11376: byang sems dkar po rdo rje'i rigs me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11377: de dag gis mtshon nas chos thams cad dag mnyam
NK115(re)001:11378: gyi ngo bor rtogs nas blang dor med par spyod
NK115(re)001:11379: pa ni sangsa rgyas kun gyi brtul zhugsa te tshul
NK115(re)001:11380: yin pas de bzhin du dang du blang nas spyod
NK115(re)001:11381: par bya'o // de la dbye na yan lag gi dam tshig bcu po'i mi spang ba lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11382: mi dor ba lnga tshan re la thabs kyis zin pa'i cha dang /
NK115(re)001:11383: shes rab dang ma bral ba'i cha gnyis rer dbye bas bcu /
NK115(re)001:11384: de la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngas dbye bas lnga bcu re ste brgya /
NK115(re)001:11385: de re re la'ang shes rab thabs su ldan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11386: thabs nyid shes rab dang ldan pa'i cha shasa kyis
NK115(re)001:11387: dbye ba byas na nyis brgya'i grangas su ngesa pa
NK115(re)001:11388: ni / rtsa ba'i dbye gzhi bcu po la thabs
NK115(re)001:11389: shes kyi phye bas nyi shura bsdu ba ni kun
NK115(re)001:11391: gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i don la ma
NK115(re)001:11392: rmongs pa'i rong zom chos kyi bzang pos dkon mchog
NK115(re)001:11395: gti mug lta bu gcig la thabs shes gnyis su dbye zhing /
NK115(re)001:11396: thabs la ye shes lnga dang yul lnga ste bcu /
NK115(re)001:11397: shes rab la'ang ye shes lnga dang yul lnga ste bcu yod pa bsdoms pas nyi shu ste /
NK115(re)001:11398: de bzhin du lhag ma dgu la'ang nyi shu rer dbye bas nyis brgyar mdzad do //
NK115(re)001:11399: de'i don ni nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa gang skye
NK115(re)001:11400: yang de nyid thabs shes khyad pa can gyis zin
NK115(re)001:11401: pa'i tshe na rig pa'i ngang du grol te rang
NK115(re)001:11402: bzhin med pa ni chos dbyings ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11403: rig pa'i rtsal gdangs ma 'gags pa me long ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:11404: gnyis su 'dzin pa med pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11405: yul snang ma 'gags par so sor snang ba sor rtog ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11406: de la 'dzin rtsol med par lhun gyis grub pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:11407: de'i tshe na de dag gi yul du snang ba
NK115(re)001:11408: de'i ngo bo stong pa chos dbyings ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:11409: yul / de bzhin du yul gyi rnam pa ma 'gags par snang ba me long gi /
NK115(re)001:11410: yul de'i ngo bo bzang ngan sogs gnyis chos su ma grub pa mnyam nyid kyi /
NK115(re)001:11411: so sor snang ba sor rtog gi /
NK115(re)001:11412: dgag sgrub dang bral bar stsol med du snang ba bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi yul lo //
NK115(re)001:11413: de ltar dbye ba'i khungs ni /
NK115(re)001:11415: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK115(re)001:11416: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK115(re)001:11417: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis las //
NK115(re)001:11418: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK115(re)001:11420: de ltar na rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK115(re)001:11421: tshig gnyis ka'i dbye ba bsdoms pas sum brgya drug
NK115(re)001:11422: cu'o // de la rong klong rnam gnyis kyi dbye
NK115(re)001:11423: ba mdzad tshul de ni rnam grangs kyis dbye ba
NK115(re)001:11424: ste nyams len zab mo'i phyogs dang sbyar ba'i gnad
NK115(re)001:11425: don chen po dang ldan pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:11426: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po'i nang gses kyi dbye
NK115(re)001:11427: ba so so'i rnam pa gzhan shes par 'dod na
NK115(re)001:11428: phra rgyas su blta bar bya dgos so //
NK115(re)001:11429: gsum pa sems phyogs rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:11430: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK115(re)001:11431: bsrung du yod pa'i dam tshig gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:11432: dang po bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:11433: semas kyi rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin ngo 'phrod cing ngang skyong nus pa'i phyogas la ni /
NK115(re)001:11434: phyi snang ba rten med du go /
NK115(re)001:11435: nang rig pa yul med du go ba'i dus na
NK115(re)001:11436: rig pa'i gshis la spang bya gzhi ma grub pas
NK115(re)001:11437: blang dor gyi dgag sgrub gang yang med par 'jog
NK115(re)001:11438: pa ni meda pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK115(re)001:11440: rang rig ye shes chen po la //
NK115(re)001:11441: bsrung dang srung byed gnyis med pas //
NK115(re)001:11442: nyams dang ma nyams gnyis su med //
NK115(re)001:11443: theg brgyad bcos ma'i tshig gi grangs //
NK115(re)001:11444: nga mi bsrung bas med ces bya //
NK115(re)001:11448: skye 'gag sogs gnyis chos dang rtogs rlom thams cad chos nyid gcig tu gyur /
NK115(re)001:11449: bltas pas ma mthong bas rang bzhin gcig /
NK115(re)001:11450: tshig gis mi mtshon pas ye shes gcig gi ngang
NK115(re)001:11451: la bsal bzhag med par gnas pa'i cha nas tha
NK115(re)001:11452: snyad btags na gciga pu'i dam tshig ces bya ste
NK115(re)001:11454: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig las //
NK115(re)001:11455: 'da' mi srid pa'i bsrung thabs ni //
NK115(re)001:11456: rang rig ye shes gcig pu la //
NK115(re)001:11457: gcig pu zhes su btags pa yin //
NK115(re)001:11459: yang de ltar phyi nang yul med du rtogs pa
NK115(re)001:11460: de gcig pu'i ngang la 'jog pa'i tshe sgo lnga
NK115(re)001:11461: rang yan gyi rig pa la snyam byed kyi blo
NK115(re)001:11462: zhen mi 'jug par chos thams cad chos nyid yangs
NK115(re)001:11463: par la bzla ba ni phyal ba zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:11464: / don la sgo lnga'i yul la shes pa ched
NK115(re)001:11465: du ma bkag par bzhag kyang 'di yin gyi gtad
NK115(re)001:11466: so gang yang med pas gud yangs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:11468: dngos po mi spyod ye shes ma 'gags pa //
NK115(re)001:11469: de la phyal ba zhes su btags pa yin //
NK115(re)001:11471: gzhan yang de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi rig pa
NK115(re)001:11472: ka dag gi gdangs la mkhyen cha yon tan gyi
NK115(re)001:11473: chos rang bzhin lhun grub tu gnas pa chos can
NK115(re)001:11474: snang ba bzhi'i nyams len dang mi 'bral ba la
NK115(re)001:11475: lhun gyis gruba pa'i dam tshig yin no zhesa bya
NK115(re)001:11476: bar gragas pa ste don la thod rgal gyi snang
NK115(re)001:11477: ba bzhi'i nyams len la brten pa ma yin kyang
NK115(re)001:11478: ka dag gi rig pa gcig pu'i ngang skyong ba
NK115(re)001:11479: na yang skye med kyi ngang las 'gag med kyi
NK115(re)001:11480: snang ba ci shar ba thams cad ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:11481: ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa'i phyi de las gzhan
NK115(re)001:11482: na bsgrub bya zhig btsal du med pas de skad
NK115(re)001:11483: ces bya ste / kun byed las /
NK115(re)001:11484: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams ma lus kun //
NK115(re)001:11485: yid chos byang chub sems su rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:11486: lhun gyis grub pa zhes su nga yis bshad //
NK115(re)001:11488: de ltar rnam grangs bzhir gsungs pa yin yang rig
NK115(re)001:11489: pa'i ngang la yengs sgom dang bral bar bzhag pa
NK115(re)001:11490: la ldog pas dbye ba tsam las tha dad pa
NK115(re)001:11491: bzhi yod pa ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:11492: des na chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa nam
NK115(re)001:11493: mkha' lta bu'i ngang na spang bya dang gnyen po'i
NK115(re)001:11494: chos gnyis ka med pas bsrung matshamas dang brala ba'i
NK115(re)001:11495: chos nyid de la rtag tu gnas pa rnams la
NK115(re)001:11496: 'ad'a bar bya ba'i chos rdul tsam mi dmigas pasa
NK115(re)001:11497: rig pa'i ngo bo'i bzhugas tshula la rtogs bya dama
NK115(re)001:11498: tshiga chen po bzhi'i chingas kyisa bcingsa nas gnas lugs
NK115(re)001:11499: kyi gshis de las gzhan du mi g.yo ba'i don
NK115(re)001:11501: rin po che spungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:11502: de dus bsrung ba'i mtshams 'das pa'i //
NK115(re)001:11503: dam tshig lhun grub chen po dang //
NK115(re)001:11504: med dang gcig pu phyal ba yis //
NK115(re)001:11505: de yi grogs su de 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:11507: tshul de ni ye nasa nyamsa pa med pa gzung
NK115(re)001:11508: 'dzin gyis mi phyed pa'i gnas lugs don gyi rdo
NK115(re)001:11509: rje'i ngang la gnas pas snang sems thams cad la
NK115(re)001:11510: chos sku'i ye shes kyis dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir rgyal
NK115(re)001:11511: po'i lugsa zhes bya la 'og ma khyad du gsod
NK115(re)001:11512: pa'i tshig tu 'khrul bar mi bya ste /
NK115(re)001:11513: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pas /
NK115(re)001:11514: rgyal po chen po nga'i gsang sngags 'di lta ba chos kyi sku dang bstun la /
NK115(re)001:11515: spyod pa byang chub kyi phyogs dang bstun nas /
NK115(re)001:11516: lta ba'i phyogs su spyod pa ma shor bar mdzod /
NK115(re)001:11517: shor na dge med sdig med du song nas phyis gsor mi rung /
NK115(re)001:11518: spyod pa'i phyogs su lta ba 'brang na dngos po mtshan mas bcings nas grol bar mi 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:11519: nga'i sngags sems phyogs 'di lta ba shas che /
NK115(re)001:11520: ma 'ongs pa na tshig gi gdeng ni shes te
NK115(re)001:11521: lta ba'i gdeng ma rnyed pa mang po zhig ngan
NK115(re)001:11523: de'i phyiir nyams len la brtan pa ma thob gong
NK115(re)001:11524: nas rdzogs chen gyi chos skad mthon po 'ba' zhig
NK115(re)001:11526: 'du 'dzin dang yul rkyen gyis mi gnod /
NK115(re)001:11527: bsgom bya sgom byed med zer nas tha mal du
NK115(re)001:11528: lus pa ni bstan pa'i bla btsong zhing rang gi
NK115(re)001:11529: chos skal chad pa yin pas sgo gsum chos dang
NK115(re)001:11530: bstun pa'i sgo nas nyams len la rgyun du 'bad
NK115(re)001:11531: pa ni shin tu gnad che'o gsungs /
NK115(re)001:11532: gnyis pa bsrung du yod pa'i dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:11534: yan lag gi dam tshig go //
NK115(re)001:11535: dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:11536: gong du bshad pa lta bu'i sgo gsum gyi spyod
NK115(re)001:11537: pa la blang dor byed pa'i bya ba la ched
NK115(re)001:11538: du ma brtson kyang ye bsrung chen po'i dam tshig
NK115(re)001:11539: la gnas pa'i stobs kyis kha na ma tho ba'i
NK115(re)001:11540: nyes pa thams cad zil gyis mnan nas nam mkha'
NK115(re)001:11541: la rdul gyis mi gos pa bzhin nyes pa gang
NK115(re)001:11542: gis kyang gos par mi 'gyur ba'i rigs rnams la
NK115(re)001:11544: 'on kyang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam la
NK115(re)001:11545: gsar du zhugas shing bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK115(re)001:11546: pa las gdams khrid nod kyang nyams len la brtan
NK115(re)001:11547: pa ma thob pas rkyen khar 'chor ba'i gang zag
NK115(re)001:11548: las dang po ba rnamas kyi rang rgyud nyes pas
NK115(re)001:11549: mi gos shing nyams len rnam par daga par bya
NK115(re)001:11550: ba'i phyir / bla ma'i bka' bzhin bsgrub cing spang
NK115(re)001:11551: blang gang la'ang ma zhen pa'i sgo nas nyes pa
NK115(re)001:11552: gang gis kyang mi gos pa'i thabs la dran shes
NK115(re)001:11553: bag yod dang bcas pas brtson zhing /
NK115(re)001:11554: gal te nyamsa par gyur na yang phyir bcosa su
NK115(re)001:11555: yod pa rina chena gyi buma pa bazanga po zhom
NK115(re)001:11556: yang bcos sla ba bzhin bla mas ji skad gsungs
NK115(re)001:11557: pa bzhin phyir bcos na sor chud par sla ba
NK115(re)001:11558: yin pa'i phyir rtag tu 'bad pas bsrung ba gal
NK115(re)001:11559: che ste / 'jam dpal bshad rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:11560: dbang rnams 'dzin pa'i rten dag ni //
NK115(re)001:11561: dam tshig yin te nyams na yal //
NK115(re)001:11562: dper na gyang na ri mo bzhin //
NK115(re)001:11563: zhes pa ltar gzhi dam tshig rnam par ma dag
NK115(re)001:11564: bzhin nyams len gyi rtogs pa bzang po rgyud la
NK115(re)001:11565: skye ba ni gnas med do //
NK115(re)001:11566: dbye ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:11568: 'bum sder gsungs pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK115(re)001:11569: mdor bstan legs par yid la zung //
NK115(re)001:11570: de yang mdor bstan 'di lta ste //
NK115(re)001:11571: rtogs byed lta ba'i dam tshig 1dang //
NK115(re)001:11572: spyod pa rgyun gyi dam tshig 2 //
NK115(re)001:11573: sgrub pa spyi yi dam tshig 3dang //
NK115(re)001:11574: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig 4dang //
NK115(re)001:11575: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig 5dang //
NK115(re)001:11576: yan lag grangs kyi dam tshig 6dang //
NK115(re)001:11577: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig 7go //
NK115(re)001:11578: zhes bdun du gsungs pa de dag kyang spyi dang
NK115(re)001:11579: khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig gsum du 'du ba
NK115(re)001:11580: las / dang po spyi'i dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:11581: so byang dang phyi rgyud kyi bsrung bya rnams te /
NK115(re)001:11583: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:11584: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams las //
NK115(re)001:11585: bsrung bar bya ba gang gsungs pa //
NK115(re)001:11586: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK115(re)001:11588: gnyis pa khyad par gyi dam tshig ni bla med
NK115(re)001:11589: kyi rgyud sde spyi la khyab pa'i mdo sgyu sems
NK115(re)001:11590: gsum rang rang gi skabs kyi rtsa ba dang yan
NK115(re)001:11591: lag gi dam tshig rnams so //
NK115(re)001:11592: 'dir gsum po de las phyi ma sems phyogs kyi
NK115(re)001:11593: dam tshig kyang spyi mdo'i sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK115(re)001:11594: tshig gsum bstan pa de dang don gcig cing de
NK115(re)001:11596: dama tshiga rnama para bkoda pa las /
NK115(re)001:11597: sku dang gsung dang thugs dag las //
NK115(re)001:11598: re re la'ang dgu dgu ste //
NK115(re)001:11599: 'jug dang las kyi rnam par shes //
NK115(re)001:11600: zhes pa'i gruba matha'a ste tshul ni nyi shu rtsa bdun du dbye bar bya ba ste /
NK115(re)001:11601: de yang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgom
NK115(re)001:11602: phyin ci ma log pa la brten nas don brgyud
NK115(re)001:11603: kyi rtogs pa khyad par can rgyud la skye ba
NK115(re)001:11604: ni bla ma kho na la rag las te dang
NK115(re)001:11606: bar du gegs sel zhing bogs 'don /
NK115(re)001:11607: tha ma chos nyid zad sar skyel bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:11608: de lta bu'i bla ma de ni dus gsum sangs
NK115(re)001:11609: rgyas thams cad kun 'dus pa'i ngo bo rigs dang
NK115(re)001:11610: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag tu bzhugs pas bla
NK115(re)001:11611: ma dang dgongs pa dbyer med dam rdo rje gsum
NK115(re)001:11612: dang sgo gsum dbyer med du bsgrub par bya ba'i
NK115(re)001:11613: phyir bsrung bya'i rtsa ba ni bla ma'i sku gsunga
NK115(re)001:11615: gsum po de re re la phyi'i phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK115(re)001:11616: nanga gi phyi nang gsang gsum /
NK115(re)001:11617: gasnga ba'i phyi nang gsang gsum gyi dama tshiga gsuma tshana gsum gyis dbye bas nyer bdun no //
NK115(re)001:11618: de la dang po sku'i phyii'i gsang ba'i dam tshig
NK115(re)001:11619: la ni sems can yin no cog gi sroga gcod
NK115(re)001:11621: de bzhin du phyi'i nang la mi tshangas pa spyod pa spang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11622: phyi'i phyi la rku ba sponga ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:11623: sku'i nang gi phyi la pha ma spuna sringa ranga lusa rnams smod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11624: nang gi nang la theg pa che chung gi chosa rnams la 'jug par 'dod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11626: zhugs te gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa'i ganga zag rnams la smoda pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11627: nang gi gsang ba la rang gi lus lha'i dkyiil
NK115(re)001:11628: 'khor la dug mtshon sogs kyis gnod pa byed pa
NK115(re)001:11629: rnams spang ba'o // 'di yang rtsa ba'i tshig rang lus zhes pas bsdu dgos par snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:11630: sku'i gsang ba'i gsang ba la /
NK115(re)001:11631: bla ma'i griba ma 'gonga ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11632: spyan sngar mtshon cha 'dzin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11634: sgeg chos byed pa sogs ma gus ba'i bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11635: gsang ba'i nang la bla ma'i yuma gtse ba sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:11636: gsang ba'i phyi la rdo rje'i spuna dang sringa mo
NK115(re)001:11637: rnams kyi lus dang rgyan sogs la smad pa dang
NK115(re)001:11638: / de dag la brdega gam brdeg par brtsam mam /
NK115(re)001:11639: brdeg tu bcug kyang rung ste de rnams spang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11640: gsunga gi phyi nang gsang gsuma gyi dam tshig la /
NK115(re)001:11641: dang po gsung gi phyi'i phyi la rang 'dod kyis 'gro ba phal pa la'ang rdzuna smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11642: phyi'i nang la pha rol dbye ba'i tshig phra ma smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11643: phyi'i gsang ba la gzhan gyi zhe gcod pa'i tshiga rtsuba mo rnas spanga ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11644: gsung gi nang gi phyi la chosa smra rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:11645: nang gi nang la chos kyi dona semas shing bsgrub pa rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:11647: gansa lugas zab mo'i don sgoma pa rnams la gshe zhing skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11648: mi bkura zhing brnyes pa rnams spang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11649: gsung gi gsang ba'i gsang ba la /
NK115(re)001:11651: gsang ba'i nang la bla ma'i yuma dang /
NK115(re)001:11652: gsang ba'i phyi la rdo rje'i spuna sringa ste de
NK115(re)001:11653: rnams la smod pa dang 'di gyis shig ces pa
NK115(re)001:11654: la sogs pa'i tshiga rnams dang du mi len zhing
NK115(re)001:11655: khyad du gsod pa rnams spang ste mi brnyas pa'o
NK115(re)001:11656: // thugas kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i dam tshig gsum la /
NK115(re)001:11657: dang po phyi'i phyi la brnab sems /
NK115(re)001:11658: phyi'i nang la 'gro ba phal pa yan chad la gnod sems /
NK115(re)001:11659: phyi'i gsang ba la grub pa'i mtha' rnams la log lta ste /
NK115(re)001:11660: yida kyi rnama pa gsum po spang dang /
NK115(re)001:11661: nang gi phyi ma spyod pa log pa bag med dang tho co /
NK115(re)001:11662: nang gi nang la sgoma pa log pa bying rgod dang gol sgrib dang /
NK115(re)001:11663: nang gi gsang ba la lta ba loga pa rtag chad dang mthar 'dzin rnams spanga ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11664: gsang ba'i gsang ba la bla ma la mos gus dang /
NK115(re)001:11665: gsang ba'i nang la yi dam gyi lha dang rdo rje mcheda rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:11666: gsang ba'i phyi la rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgoma
NK115(re)001:11667: spyod pa gsum ste de rnams nyin mtshan thuna drug
NK115(re)001:11668: la sogs pa dus kuna tu mi semas pa rnams
NK115(re)001:11669: spangs nas sems shing dran par bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:11670: 'di dag gi don ni rgyud kyi gnas ji lta ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:11671: de dag kyang mdor bsdu na da res rang re
NK115(re)001:11672: rnams 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i lam mkhan bla ma
NK115(re)001:11673: yin pas / de'i sku gsung thugs dang 'gal bar mi spyod pa'i don du 'dus pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:11674: dam tshig mchog gi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:11675: lus dang ngag dang yid stobs kyis //
NK115(re)001:11676: ci nus pa yin bla ma la //
NK115(re)001:11677: bsnyen bkur sri zhu sus byas pa //
NK115(re)001:11678: 'di la mthu dang nus pa'i tshogs //
NK115(re)001:11679: byin rlabs thogs pa med par 'byung //
NK115(re)001:11681: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:11682: spyad bya spyod pa'i dam tshig bco lnga /
NK115(re)001:11683: shes bya lta ba'i dam tshig lnga /
NK115(re)001:11684: bsgrub bya sgom bya'i dam tshig lnga'o //
NK115(re)001:11685: dang po spyad bya spyod pa'i dam tshig bco lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11686: yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag la gnas pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:11687: sngags bla med kyi lam pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK115(re)001:11688: kyis chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:11689: du rtogs nas snang spyod thams cad la kun tu
NK115(re)001:11690: bzang po'i phyag rgyas btab pa las mi 'da' bar
NK115(re)001:11691: spyad na phal pa rnams 'khor bar 'ching byed kyi
NK115(re)001:11692: las dang nyon mongs pa gang gis kyang de la
NK115(re)001:11693: mi gos par ma zad rang gi tshogs rdzogs shing
NK115(re)001:11694: gzhan la phan pa rlabs po che sgrub par byed
NK115(re)001:11695: pas / de lta bu'i thabas kyi khyad par rmad
NK115(re)001:11696: du byung ba de'i dabnga du gyur pa'i yan lag
NK115(re)001:11697: gi dam tshig nyi shu rtsa lnga po rtogs goms
NK115(re)001:11698: kyi gdeng dang ldan pa rnams kyis thams cad sgra
NK115(re)001:11700: nus pa med pa rnams kyis ni srog gcod pa
NK115(re)001:11701: la sogs pa sgra ji bzhin par mi nus pa
NK115(re)001:11702: rnams 'chad 'gyur ltar rlung rtog dbu mar gsod pa'i
NK115(re)001:11703: thabs sogs sbas don rnams la slob cing lta sgom
NK115(re)001:11704: gyi dam tshig bcu po la dngos su bslab par
NK115(re)001:11706: de dag las dang po spyod pa'i dam tshig la lnga tshan dang po ni /
NK115(re)001:11707: ta na zhes pa sgrol ba ste /
NK115(re)001:11708: de yang gsad bya srog dang srog ldan gyi sems can dang /
NK115(re)001:11709: gsod pa po rang la sogs pa'i chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:11710: don dam par gang du'ang ma grub cing tha snyad
NK115(re)001:11711: du sgyu ma dang smig rgyu'i tshul du rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:11712: rnal 'byor pas gzhan la phan pa'i blos sngags kyi
NK115(re)001:11713: thabs mkhas kyis bsgral bar byas na don che ste
NK115(re)001:11715: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed dang //
NK115(re)001:11716: bla mar smod brtson ma rungs dang //
NK115(re)001:11717: rtag tu sems can gnod brtson pa //
NK115(re)001:11718: mkhas pas bsgrims te gsad par bya //
NK115(re)001:11720: byang chub spyod 'phel sems can bde //
NK115(re)001:11721: lha mnyes bdag gi dam skong zhing //
NK115(re)001:11722: las ngan bar chad sdug yun thung //
NK115(re)001:11724: ga na zhes pa sbyor ba ste /
NK115(re)001:11725: chos thams cad la dngos po dang mtshan ma'i mtha'
NK115(re)001:11726: gang du'ang ma chags shing gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:11727: chags pa chen po lam du byed nus pa rnams
NK115(re)001:11728: kyis ji bzhin du spyad pa'i phan yon ni /
NK115(re)001:11730: sangs rgyas rnams ni mnyes bya dang //
NK115(re)001:11731: dam tshig rnams ni bsrung ba dang //
NK115(re)001:11732: gsang sngags rig pas bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:11733: gzhan gyi bud med bsten par bya //
NK115(re)001:11735: ma byin par lena pa yang /
NK115(re)001:11738: len pa po rang dang bcas pa'i chos rnams rmi
NK115(re)001:11739: lam ltar rang snang tsam las tha dad pa med
NK115(re)001:11740: pa'i tshul shes pa'i gang zag gis gzhan gyi tshogs
NK115(re)001:11741: rdzogs pa la sogs pa'i phyir blang bar bya ste
NK115(re)001:11743: ji ltar sgyu mas sgyu ma'i nor blangs te //
NK115(re)001:11744: rmi lam nang bzhin dgos pa de spyad kyang //
NK115(re)001:11745: de la las med rnam pa smin pa med //
NK115(re)001:11746: de bzhin chags med ye shes 'dir bslabs te /
NK115(re)001:11747: mya ngan 'das pa dam pa mchog zhir 'gro //
NK115(re)001:11748: zhes gsungs pa'i don srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:11749: nyes pa ltar snang ba thams cad la shes par
NK115(re)001:11750: bya'o // dgos pa ni rdo rje las /
NK115(re)001:11751: 'jungs pa rnams las nor blangs la //
NK115(re)001:11752: sems can bkren la sbyin par bya //
NK115(re)001:11753: de phyir mi yi bdag po dang //
NK115(re)001:11754: phyug po rnams ni nor 'phrog go //
NK115(re)001:11757: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang gi ngo bos
NK115(re)001:11758: grub ma myong ba'i brdzun pa nyid la ming gis
NK115(re)001:11759: ji ltar btags pa thams cad kyang rdzun du zad
NK115(re)001:11760: pas na de lta bu'i tshul shes pa'i rnal 'byoor
NK115(re)001:11761: pas dgos pa khyad par can gyi phyir rdzun smra
NK115(re)001:11762: bar bya ste / de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:11763: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK115(re)001:11764: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:11765: rdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK115(re)001:11767: kyala ba'i tshiga ni ngag 'khyal te /
NK115(re)001:11768: de yang yi ge dang ming du ma 'dus pa'i
NK115(re)001:11769: tshig dngos po med pa la de ltar mi shes
NK115(re)001:11770: pa'i dngos zhen can rnams la chags sdang la sogs
NK115(re)001:11771: pa kun nas slong ba'i rgyur 'gyur na'ang /
NK115(re)001:11772: sgra thams cad brag cha lta bur rtogs pa'i rnal
NK115(re)001:11773: 'byor pas ji ltar smras kyang nyes pas gos par
NK115(re)001:11774: mi 'gyur zhing gzhan la phan par yang 'gyur te
NK115(re)001:11775: / 'jam dpal dbyangs kyis phyi rol pa'i grub pa'i
NK115(re)001:11776: mtha' la bstod cing nang pa la smad pa'i gtam
NK115(re)001:11777: du ma smras pa'i mthar lta ba log pa can
NK115(re)001:11778: mang po mchog gsum la skyabs su song nas yang
NK115(re)001:11779: dag pa'i lam la zhugs pa'i thabs mdzad pa lta
NK115(re)001:11780: / bu'o // de ltar yang phal po che las /
NK115(re)001:11781: yang dag sems can don 'gyur ba'i //
NK115(re)001:11782: thabs de rgyal sras bslab pa'i mchog /
NK115(re)001:11783: sprin las char chen 'bebs pa yis //
NK115(re)001:11784: lo tog phun sum tshogs par byed //
NK115(re)001:11786: de dag gi sbas don rnams las snga ma bzhi
NK115(re)001:11787: rigs lnga'i dam tshig gi skabs su shes par bya
NK115(re)001:11788: la / phyi ma'i sbas don ni chos rnams rang
NK115(re)001:11789: bzhin med par rtogs pa'i tshe tshig thams cad gab
NK115(re)001:11791: de dag ni lus ngag gis spyad par bya ba
NK115(re)001:11792: lnga ste de ni gannga ba dang bakaga pa'i mtshams
NK115(re)001:11793: ji ltar bshad pa bzhin du shesa pasa spyod par
NK115(re)001:11794: byed do // lnga tshan gnyis pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11795: 'doda chagas dang zhe sdang la sogas pa'i nyon mongas
NK115(re)001:11796: pa lnga po sems rgyud dang mi 'bral bar bya
NK115(re)001:11797: bas mi spanga ba lnga ste de ni nyon mongs
NK115(re)001:11798: skyes pa'i tshe rang mtshan pa la spyad pa las
NK115(re)001:11799: ci yang med na ni tha mal ba dang khyad
NK115(re)001:11800: med pas lam yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ma grub pas
NK115(re)001:11801: na ranga rgyud pa dang dbrala dgos shing /
NK115(re)001:11802: de yang yang dag pa dang log pa'i dug lnga mi spang ba'i tshul sngar yang bshad zin la /
NK115(re)001:11803: khyad par log pa'i dug lnga po gtan tshigs kyis gzhig nas lam du 'dod na ni /
NK115(re)001:11804: gnad du ma song ba'i go ba tsam gyis rgyus 'debs pas ni ci yang mi phan la /
NK115(re)001:11805: gnad du song yang theg chen pa spyi'i nyon mongs pa chos nyid du sbyangs pa tsam yin yang /
NK115(re)001:11806: sngags lam gyi khyad chos su mi 'gro zhing /
NK115(re)001:11807: de dang rnam pa 'a gal ba'i gnyen po byams
NK115(re)001:11808: sogs bsgom na ni gnyen po lam du byed pa
NK115(re)001:11809: yin gyi // nyon mongs pa lam du byas pa
NK115(re)001:11810: ma yin la theg dman gyi lam dang yang thun
NK115(re)001:11811: yin gyi // mong ba'o // nyon mongs 'gags pa'i
NK115(re)001:11812: rjes kyi shes pa thang chad pa lta bu'i ngang
NK115(re)001:11813: du 'jog pa'ang gtad so dang bcas na kun gazhi'am
NK115(re)001:11814: yid rtog med tsam las mi 'da' la /
NK115(re)001:11815: zhen med du gnas kyang ye shes lam du byas
NK115(re)001:11816: pa yin gyi nyon mongs pa nyid lam du byas
NK115(re)001:11818: des na nyon mongs gang skyes kyang so so'i rang
NK115(re)001:11819: bzhin ma 'gags pa'i ngang de nyid kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:11820: ye shes nas ma zhen cing mi dgag na nye
NK115(re)001:11821: bar len pa med pas las dang bag chags mi
NK115(re)001:11822: gsog cing lam gyi grogs sam ngo bor 'gyur te
NK115(re)001:11824: nyon mongs rnams ni sgyu 'dra ngo bos stong //
NK115(re)001:11825: ngang gis mi rtag rang bzhin shes pas grol //
NK115(re)001:11827: de tsam ma rtog na lha'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11828: chags pa lam du byed pa'i mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs
NK115(re)001:11829: rim sogs kyis lcags khams gser du bsgyur ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:11830: rim gyis ye shes su bsgyur ba'i thabs kyis lam
NK115(re)001:11831: du byed pa'o // gsang sngags kyi lam gyi gnad
NK115(re)001:11832: ni 'di kho na la thug pas 'grel ba'i sgros
NK115(re)001:11833: du byed pa'o // dang / bla ma rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:11834: gsung 'ol spyi tsam re sems la yod pa rnams
NK115(re)001:11835: kyis gzhi byas nas bris pa yin na'ang rang nyid
NK115(re)001:11836: ni rtag tu nyon mongs pa'i khol bor gyur nas
NK115(re)001:11837: sdom pa dang dam tshig thams cad 'chal zhing rtog
NK115(re)001:11838: ngan gcig gi dbang du mi 'gro ba'i nyams len
NK115(re)001:11840: go ba tsam gyis lam gnad zab mo rtsal 'don byed rgyu ga la yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:11841: 'dir ngo tsha med par ci dran dran du bris
NK115(re)001:11842: pa 'dis dpyad gzhi tsam gyis la rang dang 'dra
NK115(re)001:11843: ba'i las dang po pa rnams kyi man ngag gnad
NK115(re)001:11844: gzigs pa'i dam pa dag las don gnad zin par
NK115(re)001:11845: gyis shig / lnga tshan gsum pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11848: m+aam sa ste sha chen dang /
NK115(re)001:11850: zila ba ste dkar cha rnams ni dam tshig gi
NK115(re)001:11851: rdzas dang du lena par bya ba lnga ste de
NK115(re)001:11852: rnams la gatsanga sme ru blta ba'i gnyis su 'dzin
NK115(re)001:11853: pa'i rtog pa dang 'brala ba'i sgo nas bsten par
NK115(re)001:11854: bya ste sngar bshad zin la sbas don rnams 'chad
NK115(re)001:11855: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa shes bya lta bu'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11859: dabnga po lnga sems dpa' lnga /
NK115(re)001:11860: kha toga lnga'i dkar po thams cad me long ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11861: ser po thams cad mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11862: dmar po thams cad sor rtog ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11863: ljang gu thams cad bya grub ye shes /
NK115(re)001:11864: mthing ga thams cad chos dbyings ye shes kyi rang
NK115(re)001:11865: gdangs su shes par bya ba ste de ltar phung
NK115(re)001:11866: khams skye mched kyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos su
NK115(re)001:11867: snang ba thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas lhara
NK115(re)001:11868: shesa par bya ba lnga ni dag mnyam rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:11869: shesa raba kyi stobas kyis spyod par bya ba ste
NK115(re)001:11870: gzhi gtan la dbab pa' skabs su bshad pa ltar
NK115(re)001:11871: ro // gsum pa bsgrub bya sgom pa'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11872: de ltar shes bya lta ba'i dam tshig gis ji
NK115(re)001:11873: ltar gtan la phebs pa'i don rnams mngon du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:11874: bar bya ba'i phyir rang rgyud la bsgrub par byed
NK115(re)001:11875: pa la 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:11876: thams cad thugs rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK115(re)001:11877: yon tan rina chena rigs dang /
NK115(re)001:11879: phrin las lasa kyi rigs dang /
NK115(re)001:11880: sku de bzhina gshegs pa'i rigs te bsgruba bya lnga po 'di ru ni 'du ba yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:11881: de yang bsgrub tshul rigs gcig nas rigs brgya'i bar
NK115(re)001:11882: du yod kyang lnga po de'i dbye bsdu tsam du
NK115(re)001:11883: zad kyi 'di las 'da' ba ni med do //
NK115(re)001:11884: de yang lta bas dag mnyam du ma rtogs na
NK115(re)001:11885: sgom pas sgrub tu med pa'am dag par bsgrubs kyang
NK115(re)001:11886: lta sgom 'gal ba can du song nas gzhi'i gnas
NK115(re)001:11887: lugs mngon du 'gyur ba'i skabs med do //
NK115(re)001:11888: des na rtogsa pa'i don de nyid cho ga lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:11889: ting 'dzin gsum la sogs pa'i thabs kyis gomas pa'i mthu yisa bsgruba pa bya ste /
NK115(re)001:11891: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga ni //
NK115(re)001:11892: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga rnams dang //
NK115(re)001:11893: rnam shes yul rnams dkyil 'khor sgrub byed pa //
NK115(re)001:11894: ting 'dzin gsum dang cho ga lnga rdzogs nas //
NK115(re)001:11895: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor sgrub byed pa //
NK115(re)001:11896: ting 'dzin cho ga lnga yi sems rtsol byed //
NK115(re)001:11898: de la cho ga lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11899: lam ma nor bar ston pa'i bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis zin pa /
NK115(re)001:11900: de las zab mo'i dbang thob pa /
NK115(re)001:11901: dam tshig dang sdom pa la gnas pa /
NK115(re)001:11902: sgrub pa'i man ngag la mkhas pa /
NK115(re)001:11903: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs pas bsgrub nus pa'o //
NK115(re)001:11904: de ltar lnga tshan lngar bshad pa 'di daga ni dama tshiga gasla bkra'i dgongas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:11906: spyad pa lnga dang mi spong lnga //
NK115(re)001:11907: dang du blang dang bsgrub de bzhin //
NK115(re)001:11908: shes bya lnga rnams thun min bshad //
NK115(re)001:11910: gsum pa lhag pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:11911: phur pa myang 'das chen po'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:11912: gcan gzan rgyal po seng ge gsad mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11913: za ma tog tu ngan pa'i dug mi byo //
NK115(re)001:11914: rin po che yi lcug ma rtsar mi bcad //
NK115(re)001:11915: gangs kyi zhun chu khol ma yongs mi btung //
NK115(re)001:11916: pad+ma rgyas pa'i ze'u 'bru kha mi dbye //
NK115(re)001:11917: bug rdol can gyi snod du bcud mi blug /
NK115(re)001:11918: ma brtags pa yi nor dang zas mi bsrel //
NK115(re)001:11919: shel gong dkar po rdzab tu bsnub mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11920: snod ngan nang du seng ge'i zho mi bzho //
NK115(re)001:11921: yid bzhin nor bu thab tu bsreg mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11922: bya yi rgyal po khyung gi gshog mi bcag /
NK115(re)001:11923: gnam lcags sder mo sa la brdab mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11924: stag gzig rol pa'i zas kyi lhag mi bza' //
NK115(re)001:11925: rdo rje'i gtams pa'i brag rnams yongs mi bshig /
NK115(re)001:11926: rdo rje'i rwa bas bskor ba'i go mi hral //
NK115(re)001:11927: mun pa sel ba'i sgron ma yongs mi gsod //
NK115(re)001:11928: rdo rje'i chu bo 'ol ka bcad mi bya /
NK115(re)001:11929: rgyal po'i rtags kyi phyag rgya sbyin mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11930: rdo rje'i mkhar rdzong gtams pa'i rming mi bzlog /
NK115(re)001:11931: rgyal mtshan rtser btags nor bu rin po che //
NK115(re)001:11932: 'dod par gyur pa'i mtshan mas dbog mi bya //
NK115(re)001:11934: spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig la gnas nas
NK115(re)001:11935: tshogs chen gyi bsgrub pa la sogs pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:11936: su bsrung bya lhag par du bstan pas lhag pa'i
NK115(re)001:11938: rim pa ltar bla ma la mi brnyas /
NK115(re)001:11940: dad pa can gyis tshogs mi bcad /
NK115(re)001:11941: dkor la mi 'bags shing phung khrol gyi rtsa ba chang myos par mi 'thung /
NK115(re)001:11942: mched kyi rig mar mi spyad /
NK115(re)001:11944: 'dre can dang rtsod can gyi nor mi bsten zhing byin gyis ma brlabs pa'i zas mi za /
NK115(re)001:11945: sems bskyed nyams su mi gzhug /
NK115(re)001:11946: snod min la gdams pa mi ston /
NK115(re)001:11947: snod ldan gyi slob ma mi spong /
NK115(re)001:11948: yab yum mi 'bral ba'i don bde stong la sbyor /
NK115(re)001:11951: bla ma'i gdan sa mi barlama /
NK115(re)001:11952: rang gzhan gyi mtshams rgya mi dbral /
NK115(re)001:11954: bzlas brjod dang cho ga'i rgyun mi tshig gi bar mi gcod /
NK115(re)001:11955: dbang rtags kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' zhing rgyud nas gsungs pa'i brda gzhan la mi brjod /
NK115(re)001:11956: dkyil 'khor mi dkrug cing nyams pa'i mthu bzlog mi byed /
NK115(re)001:11957: rigs kyi bdag po bla ma mi spong ba rnams so //
NK115(re)001:11958: gsum pa brtul zhugs nyer lnga dang rigs lnga'i sdom pa bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:11959: dang po brtul zhugs nyer lnga bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:11960: gsal bkra las lnga tshan lngar bstan pa'i rnam pa'i grangs de bzhina du dus kyi 'khor lo las /
NK115(re)001:11961: bslab pa'i gzhi sdig pa lnga /
NK115(re)001:11965: chags pa lnga ste lnga tshan lnga spong ba'i brtul
NK115(re)001:11966: zhugsa nyi shu rtsa lnga bstan pa las dang po
NK115(re)001:11967: sdig pa lnga spong ba ni /
NK115(re)001:11968: srog chags phra mo yan chad kyi srog la 'tshe
NK115(re)001:11969: ba smos ci dgos kyang kun mnar sems pa dang
NK115(re)001:11970: / bslu ba'i bsam pa can rdzun du smra ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11971: dud 'gro yan chad kyis bdag gir byas pa'i rdzas brku ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11972: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11973: phung khrol thams cad kyis 'byung gnas chang gi btung
NK115(re)001:11974: bas myos par byed pa dang lnga ni 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:11975: gnas su 'ching ba la rdo rje'i zhags pa dang
NK115(re)001:11976: mtshungs shing rang gzhan gyi dge tshogs thams cad 'joms
NK115(re)001:11977: par byed pas de rnams phyogs mthun dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:11978: spang ba'o // gal te de rnams bsrung mi nus
NK115(re)001:11979: na brtul zhugs lhag ma rnams kyang mi sbyin pas
NK115(re)001:11980: bslab pa'i gzhi lnga zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:11981: gnyis pa nye ba'i sdig pa lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11982: cho lo dang mig mang la sogs te rgyan po 'gyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11983: bza' ba dang rin gyi don du bshad pa'i sha
NK115(re)001:11984: la sogs pa kha na ma thob ba'i zas dang
NK115(re)001:11985: / dmag 'khrug dang tshong gi gtam la sogs pa'i ngag 'khyal gyi rim pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11986: pha mes kyi tshun gsol ba dang nad pa'i don
NK115(re)001:11987: du phyugs kyi mchod sbyin byed pa sogs 'byung po'i
NK115(re)001:11988: chos lugs la dga' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:11989: rang gis bsad pa'i sha ma gtogs gzhan mi bza' zhing gos dkar po dang /
NK115(re)001:11990: bya gag gi btung ba 'ba' zhig bsten pa sogs
NK115(re)001:11991: lha min gyi 'jug pa can kla klo'i chos lugs
NK115(re)001:11992: la spyod pa dang lnga ni nye ba'i sdig pa
NK115(re)001:11994: gsum pa gsod pa lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:11995: mtho ris 'dod pa'i mchod sbyin la dmigs nas ba lang gsod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11996: ma mo mchod pa la byis pa gsod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11997: skyes pa'i don du skyes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:11998: bud med kyi don du bud med gsod pa ste mi'i mchod sbyin gnyis /
NK115(re)001:11999: lha mi'i bla ma gsod pa zhes bya ba rgyal
NK115(re)001:12000: ba sras dang bcas pa'i sku gzugs dang bka'i glegs
NK115(re)001:12001: bam dang mchod rten rnams bsnun te bshig pa la
NK115(re)001:12002: gsod pa'i sgras btags pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12003: 'di dag ni 'tshe ba chos su smra ba kla
NK115(re)001:12004: klo'i grub mtha' la zhugs pa rnams sdig pa'i las
NK115(re)001:12005: rngam po che'ang dge bar 'dod pa'i skabs yod pas
NK115(re)001:12006: sdig pa lnga'i dang po las logs su dgar nas
NK115(re)001:12007: de las ldog pa'i don du bshad pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12008: des na dkon mchog bsnyen bkur la bsnyad nas phyugs
NK115(re)001:12009: lug gsod pa yang kla klo'i grub mtha' ma shes
NK115(re)001:12010: kyang spyod pa la mtshungs ldan du slob pa yin
NK115(re)001:12011: no // bzhi pa 'khu ba lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:12016: bla ma dang mkhan slob ste yul lnga po de
NK115(re)001:12017: dag la khong khro zhing 'khu ba ste lnga tshan
NK115(re)001:12018: bzhi po yid kyis sdom zhing spyod lam gyi sgo
NK115(re)001:12020: lnga pa chags pa lnga ni /
NK115(re)001:12021: theg pa chen po'i sde snod thams cad nas /
NK115(re)001:12022: mig gi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba
NK115(re)001:12023: dang zhes pa nas lus kyi bar gsungs pas mtshon
NK115(re)001:12024: te / dbang shes phan tshun rten dang brten par
NK115(re)001:12025: 'brel ba las yul lnga la zhen cing chags nas
NK115(re)001:12026: yang srid 'phen nus kyi las su rdzogs pas de
NK115(re)001:12028: spang tshul ni bskyed rim gyi sgo nas dbang yul
NK115(re)001:12029: dang reg bya reg shes sogs lha skur sbyang zhing
NK115(re)001:12030: rdzogs rim so sor sdud pa'i rnal 'byoor gyis dbang
NK115(re)001:12031: po lnga yul lnga la 'jug pa'i rgyun gcod pa'o
NK115(re)001:12032: // de yang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK115(re)001:12033: 'od srung ma 'ongs pa'i dus na dge slong mngon
NK115(re)001:12034: pa'i nga rgyal can khyi rdo la bsnyegs pa dang
NK115(re)001:12036: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:12037: khyi rdo la bsnyegs pa dang 'dra bar yul gzugs
NK115(re)001:12038: sogs la dpyad nas mi rtag pa sogs su bsam
NK115(re)001:12039: pa tsam ma yin par seng ge 'phen pa po
NK115(re)001:12040: la bsnyegs pa ltar sems kyi rtsar bcad de rang
NK115(re)001:12041: bzhin med par shes nas grol bar bya ba'o //
NK115(re)001:12042: de yang rdo rje sems dpa'i brtul zhugs nyer lnga zhes rgyud 'grel las gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK115(re)001:12043: de dag las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pas dam tshig dang /
NK115(re)001:12044: sgo gsum de'i ngo bor son pa nyid kyis na brtul zhugs zhes grags pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12045: gnyis pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:12046: thun mong rigs lnga'i sdom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12047: khyad par rigs lnga'i sdom pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12048: dang po thun mong rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni 'dir /
NK115(re)001:12049: gasnga 'dusa sangas rgyas mnyam sbyor zla gasnga sogas //
NK115(re)001:12050: zhes pa mchan dkyus su song ba yin pa 'dra ste rnam mkhyen shing rtar mi 'dug go //
NK115(re)001:12051: gang ltar yang sngona bee ro ska cog sogs nas
NK115(re)001:12052: rin bzang la thug gi bar bsgyur ba la snga
NK115(re)001:12053: 'gyur zhes bya bas de dus bsgyur ba'i rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:12054: rnams dang / lo chen rin chen bzang po phyina
NK115(re)001:12055: chada bsgyur ba rnams la phyi 'gyur zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:12056: rnams dang / / de yang mdo phyogs la khyad par med kyang /
NK115(re)001:12057: sngags kyi phyogs nas snga phyi gnyis po so so'i
NK115(re)001:12058: srol 'dzin pa la gsang sngags rnying ma ba zhes
NK115(re)001:12059: dang / gsang sngags gsar ma ba zhes grags pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:12060: de ltar snga phyi gnyis kar 'gyur ba'i rgyuda sde yi spyi dona du gyur pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12061: phal che ba na dngos bstan du gsungs pas thun
NK115(re)001:12062: mong du gyur pa ni rigas lnga'i sdoma pa yin
NK115(re)001:12063: la / de la'ang thun mong dang khyad par gnyis
NK115(re)001:12064: las dang po ni dngos bstan rnams sngags phyi pa
NK115(re)001:12066: de'ang smon 'jug dang tshul khrims gsum sogs phar phyin theg pa dang yang thun mong par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:12067: spyir rigs bye brag pa la zhugs pas rigs lnga
NK115(re)001:12068: ga'i sdom pa bsrung mi dgos pa ma yin kyang
NK115(re)001:12069: rang rigs gang yin pa'i sdom pa la khyad par
NK115(re)001:12070: du bya dgos pa'i rigs lnga so so'i sdom pa'i
NK115(re)001:12072: de yang dang po sangas rgyas rnal 'byor te de
NK115(re)001:12073: bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs rnam snang gi sdom pa ni
NK115(re)001:12075: bdag rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas sems can thams
NK115(re)001:12076: cad kyang de'i go 'phang la 'god par bya'o snyam
NK115(re)001:12077: pa'i smona sems blangs nas 'juga sdom ni tshula khrimas
NK115(re)001:12078: gsuma brtan por bzung bas shugs la blang bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:12079: la / de yang tshul khrims gsum gyi khyad par /
NK115(re)001:12080: tha mal gyi snang zhen las ldog pa'i nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK115(re)001:12081: 'khrul snang ye shes su sdud pa'i dge ba chos sdud /
NK115(re)001:12082: las bzhi'i phrin las la 'jug pa'i sems can don byed do //
NK115(re)001:12083: sdom pa de thams cad kyi rten skyabs 'gro yin
NK115(re)001:12084: pas de'i zhing dkon mchog gsum bzung bas mjug bsdus
NK115(re)001:12086: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK115(re)001:12087: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'i //
NK115(re)001:12088: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK115(re)001:12089: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12090: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12091: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12092: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum /
NK115(re)001:12093: so so brtan por gzung bar bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12094: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK115(re)001:12095: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK115(re)001:12096: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor las byung ba'i //
NK115(re)001:12097: sdom pa deng nas brtan por gzung //
NK115(re)001:12099: sbas don ltar na bde stong dbyer med kyi byang
NK115(re)001:12100: sems dang sems nyid gdod nas rnam par dag pa
NK115(re)001:12101: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin du gzung ba'o //
NK115(re)001:12102: de dag kyang rnam par snang mdzad ni sku'i rigs
NK115(re)001:12103: yin la sku ni 'bras chos thams cad kyi rten
NK115(re)001:12104: yin pa ltar sems bskyed tshul khrims skyabs 'gro rnams
NK115(re)001:12105: ni yon tan kun gyi rten gzhi yin pas de'i
NK115(re)001:12107: gnyis pa rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig ni rgyud sde phyi nang thun mong du /
NK115(re)001:12109: rdo rje mkha' 'gro la sogs pa'i rgyud nas gsungs
NK115(re)001:12110: pa'i tshad dang mtshan nyid dang ldan pa rang nyid
NK115(re)001:12111: rnam snang la sogs pa'i lha sku phyag rgya chen
NK115(re)001:12114: de nyid kyis ni rdo rje bzung //
NK115(re)001:12115: chos kyi dril bu dkrol bar bya //
NK115(re)001:12116: dam tshig gis ni phyag rgya cher //
NK115(re)001:12117: byin gyis brlabs kyi snying po bzla //
NK115(re)001:12119: de nyid dran pa'i sgo nas 'dzin tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:12120: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes ni gang du'ang mi 'gyur la /
NK115(re)001:12121: mtshan ma'i rnam rtog gis mi shigs pa sogs rdo
NK115(re)001:12122: rje'i chos bdun dang ldan pas na rdo rje ste
NK115(re)001:12123: mi bskyod pa'i bdag nyid can no //
NK115(re)001:12124: de'i mtshan nyid don dam byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK115(re)001:12125: bo dran pa'i sgo nas rtag kyi rdo rje 'dzin
NK115(re)001:12126: pa'o // de bzhin du dril bu'ang /
NK115(re)001:12127: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid can //
NK115(re)001:12128: nam mkha' la'ang mtshan nyid med //
NK115(re)001:12129: nam mkha' mnyam pa nyid sbyor ba'i //
NK115(re)001:12130: kun mchog mnyam pa nyid du gsal //
NK115(re)001:12131: zhes sgrog par mos nas dkrol zhing de'i sgra la nges shes drangs ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK115(re)001:12132: rang sems nam mkha'i mtshan nyid tsam du mtshon kyang
NK115(re)001:12133: nam mkha' la'ang mtshan nyid med pas de'i dpes bskrun
NK115(re)001:12134: du med pa 'i phyir rtog dpyod las 'das pa'i
NK115(re)001:12135: ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:12136: 'jog pa ni shes rab kyi rang bzhin don dam
NK115(re)001:12137: pa'i dril bu'i de kho na nyid 'dzin pa ste
NK115(re)001:12139: sems nyid nam mkha' la gnas te //
NK115(re)001:12140: nam mkha' ci yang mi gnas pas //
NK115(re)001:12141: de phyir dpyod pa'i bya byed bral //
NK115(re)001:12142: byar med bsam bral brjod brdas rtogs //
NK115(re)001:12144: rgyud sde phyi nang gnyis kar rdor dril 'dzin res
NK115(re)001:12145: kyi so so'i dag pa dran par ma byas na
NK115(re)001:12146: dam tshig las 'da' bar gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:12147: khyad par gsang sngags nang pa ltar na sbas don
NK115(re)001:12148: nang gi rdor dril nor bu dang pad+ma ste de
NK115(re)001:12149: gnyis phan tshun rgyas gdab pa ni phyag rgya'i dam
NK115(re)001:12150: tshig go // gsang ba ltar na dkar dmar zhu
NK115(re)001:12151: bde'i rkyen gyis mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen ye shes
NK115(re)001:12152: tshig go // rdo rje / rnam kun mchog ldan
NK115(re)001:12153: gyi stong nyid dril bu zung du 'jug pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:12155: de dag gi don brda don rtags gsum gyi sgo
NK115(re)001:12156: nas ston par byed pa'i bla ma bsnyen bkur gyi
NK115(re)001:12157: sgo nas gzunga bar bya ba rnams te /
NK115(re)001:12158: rdo rje'i rigs mchog chen po la //
NK115(re)001:12159: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya yang //
NK115(re)001:12160: yang dag nyid du gzung bar bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12161: slob dpon dag kyang gzungs bar bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12163: gsum pa rin chen rigs rina 'byunga gi dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:12164: phyi ltar na chosa kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12165: zang zing nora gyi sbyin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12166: mi 'jigas pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12167: 'gro ba thams cad bla na med pa'i bde ba
NK115(re)001:12168: la reg 'dod byamsa pa'i sbyin pa dang bzhi po
NK115(re)001:12169: nyin re bzhin yang dus drug tu sbyin pa ste
NK115(re)001:12170: / de'ang rin chen rigs las dgos 'dod 'byung ba
NK115(re)001:12171: dang 'dra bar sbyin pa las kyang dgos 'dod 'byung
NK115(re)001:12173: de yang nyin re bzhin ma nus na rang gi
NK115(re)001:12174: lus longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:12175: thams cad gtong ba'i sems dang byams sogs ci nus
NK115(re)001:12177: sbas don du rjes chags kyi mes dga' bzhi'i ye shes sbyin pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12179: rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK115(re)001:12180: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK115(re)001:12181: nyin re bzhin yang dus drug tu //
NK115(re)001:12182: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK115(re)001:12184: bzhi pa pad+ma'i rigs snanga matha'i dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:12185: phyi ltar na nyan thos byang sems sngags kyi theg pa gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:12186: khyad par bla med kyi lugs la /
NK115(re)001:12187: phyi nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa /
NK115(re)001:12188: nang bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi thega pa /
NK115(re)001:12189: gsang ba pha ma gnyis med kyi theg pa ste
NK115(re)001:12190: de gsum gyi tshig don ci nus su 'dzina zhing
NK115(re)001:12191: chosa de rnamas gzhan la'ang snod dang 'tshams par bshad
NK115(re)001:12192: par bya ba'o // gal te ma nus na yid kyis mi gtong ngo //
NK115(re)001:12193: sbas don du rlung dbu mar bcings pas gzhom med kyi gsung bsgrub pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12194: 'di ni dngos su gsung gi ngo bo yin pas der bzhag go //
NK115(re)001:12196: byang chub chen po'i las 'byung ba'i //
NK115(re)001:12197: pad+ma rigs chen dag pa la //
NK115(re)001:12198: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK115(re)001:12199: dam pa'i chos ni ma lus bzung //
NK115(re)001:12201: lnga pa las kyi rigs dona gruba kyi dam tshig ni /
NK115(re)001:12202: las thams cad pa yin pas rigs bzhi po thams
NK115(re)001:12203: cad la gus shing dang du blang ba'i steng du
NK115(re)001:12204: yo ga dang bla med kyi rgyud sde rnams nas
NK115(re)001:12205: bshad pa'i phyi nang gsang ba'i mchoda pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12207: sbyin sreg la sogs pa'i phrina lasa kuna la gusa
NK115(re)001:12208: shing ci nus su dang du blang bar bya ba'o
NK115(re)001:12209: // sbas don du de thams cad zung 'jug e wam gyi sdom pas rgyas 'debs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12210: zhu bdes phung khams dbang yul gyi lha rnams tshim par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12211: de dag ni gtso bo bya ba'i las kyi char
NK115(re)001:12212: gtogs pas las rigs kyi dam tshig tu bzhag pa
NK115(re)001:12213: ste / las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK115(re)001:12214: sdom pa thams cad ldan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12215: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12216: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK115(re)001:12218: gnyis pa khyad par rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12219: rten gyi gang zag khyad para ba rnal 'byor bla
NK115(re)001:12220: meda kyi lta sgom spyod pa'i gnas gang yin pa
NK115(re)001:12221: gdengs su gyur zhing rigas lnga so so'i dam tshig
NK115(re)001:12222: gam sdoma pa bsten pa la nus pa rnyed pas
NK115(re)001:12223: rang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba dag la sgra
NK115(re)001:12225: gzhan du sngags lam la zhugs pa tsam la dgongs
NK115(re)001:12226: pa can du gsungs pa'i khyad par gnyis gnyis su
NK115(re)001:12227: ston pa ni / dang po rdo rje'i rigas kyi
NK115(re)001:12228: dam tshig tu gyura ba sroga la 'tshe ba ste
NK115(re)001:12230: phyi nang gsang ba gsum las /
NK115(re)001:12231: phyi ltar na zhing bcu tshang ba'am nyams pa bdun
NK115(re)001:12232: dang ldan pa rnams las ngan pa'i rgyun thabs gzhan
NK115(re)001:12233: gang gis kyang gcad par mi nus na drag po
NK115(re)001:12234: mngon spyod kyi las kyis gsad par bya ba dang
NK115(re)001:12235: / nang ltar na de lasa gazhana dgongs pa can
NK115(re)001:12236: du bstan pa srid pa bskyed pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo
NK115(re)001:12237: srog gi rlung dbu mara gsod pa ste ro rkyang
NK115(re)001:12238: nas 'jug pa'i gzung 'dzin las rlunga gi rgyun dbu
NK115(re)001:12239: ma sgra gcan gyi sbubs su gcod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12240: gsang ba ltar na rnam par rtog pa skye med du gsoda pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12242: sems gcig srog chags gsod pa ni //
NK115(re)001:12243: gang phyir srog ni sems su brjod //
NK115(re)001:12245: gnyis pa rina chena rigas kyi dam tshig la ma byin pa blanga byar bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12246: nang ltar na matshana ldana gyi gzungas ma thabs kyis dbang du bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12247: de'i khams dmar cha rlung gi stobs kyis ma byin par len pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12248: phyi ltar na sbyin gtong sogs bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK115(re)001:12249: bsags pa'i skal ba meda pa'i ser sna can gyi
NK115(re)001:12251: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi dam rdzas khyad par can
NK115(re)001:12252: skal ba med pa'i lag tu 'khyams pa rnams 'phrog
NK115(re)001:12253: pa dang / gsang ba ltar na rdzogas pa'i byanga
NK115(re)001:12254: chub kyi yon tan thams cad gzhan sus kyang ma
NK115(re)001:12255: byin par ranga gi sgo stobsa kyi mthu yisa blanga
NK115(re)001:12258: gang phyir theg pa chen po 'di //
NK115(re)001:12259: gang gis kyang ni byin ma lags //
NK115(re)001:12260: de nyid rtogs pas ma byin blang //
NK115(re)001:12262: gsum pa pad+ma'i rigas kyi dam tshig la ri dwagas
NK115(re)001:12263: miga cana te bud med mchoda pa'am bsten par gsungs
NK115(re)001:12264: pa ni / gsang ba ltar na shes rab kyi
NK115(re)001:12265: rang bzhin stong pa nyid kyi buda meda rnam kun
NK115(re)001:12266: mchog ldan ma rig pa ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:12267: dang sbyor ba'i tshul gyis kuna tu spyod pa ste
NK115(re)001:12269: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan ma //
NK115(re)001:12270: stong nyid shes rab mdzes ma nyid //
NK115(re)001:12271: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK115(re)001:12274: nang ltar na yid rig chos kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK115(re)001:12275: gtum mo dam tshig gi phyag rgya gnyis bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12276: phyi ltar na dngos rig lasa kyi phyag rgya bsten
NK115(re)001:12277: pa ste de'i yan lag tu chosa kyi phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:12278: dang dama tshiga gi phyag rgya dang /
NK115(re)001:12279: phyaga rgya chena po mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i rang
NK115(re)001:12280: bzhin gsum bstena pa'ang 'du ba yin te rim pa
NK115(re)001:12281: bzhin / 'du shes gsum ldan gyi bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12282: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang rtogs goms gdengs
NK115(re)001:12283: su gyur pa'i lta ba ste phyag rgya gsum dang
NK115(re)001:12284: mtshungs par ldan pa la brten nas zhu bdes drangs
NK115(re)001:12285: pa'i dpe'i ye shes bskyed pas kun rdzob kyi khams
NK115(re)001:12286: 'gyur med du brtan cing don dam lhan cig skyes
NK115(re)001:12287: pa'i ye shes 'gyur ba med pa mngon du byed
NK115(re)001:12288: pa'o // bzhi pa lasa kyi rigs la rdzuna gyi tshiga smra bar bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12289: phyi ltar na bla ma'i nor rdzas dang /
NK115(re)001:12291: rang gi dam tshig rnams bsrung ba'i phyir chos thams
NK115(re)001:12292: cad sgyu ma lta bura bltas nas rdzun sgrog par
NK115(re)001:12293: bya ba dang / nang ltar na ngag gi rtsa
NK115(re)001:12294: ba srog rlung snying gar thim pas rang ngor chos
NK115(re)001:12295: kyi rnam grags tshad med pa 'char ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12296: gzhan la'ang rang rang dang mthun pa'i chos sgyu ma ltar ston nus pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12298: gang gis srog rlung zos pa na //
NK115(re)001:12299: gcig car 'gro kun skad kyis ni //
NK115(re)001:12300: gang dang gang la de dang de //
NK115(re)001:12301: mthun pa'i chos ston rdzun pa'i tshig /
NK115(re)001:12303: gsang ba ltar na sems can thams cad med snang
NK115(re)001:12304: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i rdzun tshig sgyu ma ltar
NK115(re)001:12305: sgrog pa ste / 'jam dpal gyis bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:12306: bdag dang sems can mi dmigs la //
NK115(re)001:12307: 'khor ba las sgrol rdzun gyi tshig /
NK115(re)001:12309: lnga pa 'khora lo'i rigas kyi dam tshig la sha chang sogs bsten par gsungs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12310: phyi ltar na rigs dang nga rgyal gyi dregs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12311: gtsang sme'i rtog pa gzhig pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:12312: khams byang chub kyi sems 'phel ba'i phyir dam tshig gi rdzasa su 'os pa /
NK115(re)001:12313: mi sha khyi sha rta sha glang gi sha glang
NK115(re)001:12314: po che'i sha ste sha lnga po yul dbus su
NK115(re)001:12315: kha zas kyi don du bsad par ma gyur pa'i
NK115(re)001:12316: sha yin pas de rnams bza' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12317: bdud rtsi chen po lnga dang chang yang bdud rtsi'i
NK115(re)001:12318: rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs nas gdan gsum lha'i
NK115(re)001:12319: dkyil 'khor la mchod pa'i bsam pas myos par mi
NK115(re)001:12320: 'gyur bar btung bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12321: gzugs la sogs pa'i yula rnamas kyi 'doda pa'i yona
NK115(re)001:12322: tan thams cad 'dod yon gyi lha mo lnga la
NK115(re)001:12323: sogs pa'i rol par shes pas zhen med sgyu ma
NK115(re)001:12325: nang ltar na sha lnga ni dbang lnga'i dwangs ma
NK115(re)001:12326: bcings pas rnam rtog gi sa bon ni mi rtog
NK115(re)001:12327: pa'i chos nyid kyi bza' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12328: chang btung ba ni yas babs kyi zhu bde mas
NK115(re)001:12329: brtan lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyis bcings pa
NK115(re)001:12330: las thig le'i rdul phra rab kyi tshogs ye shes
NK115(re)001:12331: chen po'i rang bzhin du btung ba'o /
NK115(re)001:12332: gsang ba ltar na snang sems thams cad chos nyid
NK115(re)001:12333: mnyam pa chen po blang dor rtsol sgrub med pa'i
NK115(re)001:12334: ngang du dag par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12336: rnam rtog dang ni kun rtog gi //
NK115(re)001:12337: dngos dang dngos med sogs 'khrul ba //
NK115(re)001:12338: rnam rtog d+r+wa ba'i sa bon tshogs //
NK115(re)001:12339: rnam par mi rtog pa yis bza' //
NK115(re)001:12340: snying rjes snod kyi mchog tu ni //
NK115(re)001:12341: ye shes chen po mnyam bzhag nas //
NK115(re)001:12342: btung zhing rtag tu btung bar bya //
NK115(re)001:12343: phyag rgya dam tshig ces su bshad //
NK115(re)001:12346: 'khor lo'i rigs kyi dam tshig sngon dang las rigs de'i rjes su 'byung la /
NK115(re)001:12348: 'khor lo'i rigs la sha chen lnga dang chang //
NK115(re)001:12349: zhes tshig rkang gcig las med kyang 'dir rtsa ba
NK115(re)001:12350: spar ma zur du yod pa rnams ltar byas so
NK115(re)001:12351: // de ltar snon 'jug gi sdom pa bzung ba
NK115(re)001:12352: de yi rjes su rigs lnga'i sdom bzung gi yan
NK115(re)001:12353: lag sems bskyed de'i dmigs rnam so sor phye ba
NK115(re)001:12354: tshiga gisa gaba ste dmigs phye nas ma gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:12355: // rnams ni / shes bya'i sgrib pa las ma
NK115(re)001:12356: bsgrala ba'i nyan rang dgra bcom pa rnams de las
NK115(re)001:12357: bsgral bar dam bca' ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12358: sogas khongs nas ma grol ba rnams dgrol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12359: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs 'byung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12360: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs
NK115(re)001:12361: su mya ngan 'das pa la 'god pa'i dam bca'
NK115(re)001:12362: so sor bzung ba nan tan bgyi ba'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:12363: byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang thuna monga ba yin
NK115(re)001:12364: pas le'u brgyad pa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar ro
NK115(re)001:12366: lha dang lha min gsang ba pa //
NK115(re)001:12367: khyod kyis brnyas par mi bya zhing //
NK115(re)001:12368: phyag rgya bzhon pa mtshon bya dang //
NK115(re)001:12370: zhes lha dang lha mina dang gasnga ba rnams mi brnyas par gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12371: phyag rgya dang bzhona pa dang mtshona cha dang matshana
NK115(re)001:12372: ma rnams la smada para mi bya ba dang 'gom
NK115(re)001:12373: par mi rung bar bstan pa'i don rnams las snga
NK115(re)001:12374: ma lha dang lha min gnyis ni dngosa su bstan
NK115(re)001:12375: te de gnyis la mi smod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12376: gasnga ba pa ni gnoda sbyin te ston pa'i dam
NK115(re)001:12377: tshig shes shing de la gnas pas bstan pa skyong
NK115(re)001:12378: ba rnams mi brnyas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12379: phyag rgya ni spyir las chos dam tshig phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:12380: chen po ste bzhi ka la mi smod cing khyad
NK115(re)001:12381: par yi dam lha'i sku gzugas yongs su rdzogas pa
NK115(re)001:12382: la smod par mi bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12383: bzhona pa bla ma'i khri stan dang shing rta dang /
NK115(re)001:12384: rta la sogs pa'i chibas pa dang de la sogas
NK115(re)001:12385: pa'i yo byad rnas la smad pa sogs mi byed
NK115(re)001:12386: pa dang / mtshona cha ni ral gri dang gtun
NK115(re)001:12387: shing sogs lha yi phyag mtshan gyi cheda du byas
NK115(re)001:12388: pa'i rigas te de rnams la smad pa sogs mi
NK115(re)001:12389: pa dang / byed pa dang / matshana ma'i rigs
NK115(re)001:12390: lnga'i phyag mtshan te de la smad pa sogs mi
NK115(re)001:12392: gzhan yang lha'i sku gzugs dang /
NK115(re)001:12394: mchoda rtena la sogs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten
NK115(re)001:12395: thams cad kyi griba ma 'goma pa la smad pa'i
NK115(re)001:12396: sgra yis bkag pa yin pas mi 'gom zhing de
NK115(re)001:12397: la 'dug par yang mi bya la /
NK115(re)001:12398: gal te thabs med kyis 'gom dgos pa byung na /
NK115(re)001:12399: badz+ra be ga a kra ma h+aum zhes rdo rje
NK115(re)001:12400: shugs kyi las sngags dang bcas pas nam mkhar bteg
NK115(re)001:12401: pa'i 'og tu 'dzul bar bsam ste 'gro bar bya'o
NK115(re)001:12402: // de bzhina du me tog dang mchod yon zhal
NK115(re)001:12403: zas sogs mchoda rdzasa lha la phul zin pa'i rnyingsa
NK115(re)001:12404: pa la damna mara gragas te de rnams la mi
NK115(re)001:12406: 'gong ba'i sar khyab gdal du mi 'dor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12407: mar dang zan sogs kyis lha'i phyag matshana gyi rnama
NK115(re)001:12408: par byas pa'nga baza'a bar bakaga pa yina pas mi
NK115(re)001:12409: bza' 'o // de la khyad par rigs lnga'i dam
NK115(re)001:12410: tshig gi skabs su bshad pa'i dngos bstan rnams theg
NK115(re)001:12411: dman du ni nyes pa kun gyi 'byung gnas sam
NK115(re)001:12412: gzhir gyur pa'i rtsa ba bzhi chang dang lnga po
NK115(re)001:12413: spang bya yin pa la sogs pa'i don rang rgyud
NK115(re)001:12415: 'gal ba can du mi blta bar tshul bzhin du shes pa gal che ste /
NK115(re)001:12416: spyir theg chen gyi chos rnams drang nges ldem dgongs
NK115(re)001:12417: bzhir bstan pas bka'i don thams cad sgra ji bzhin
NK115(re)001:12419: sgra ji bzhin pa las 'gal ba sha stag go zhes kyang 'dzin pa ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:12420: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung ni sgra tshig gi gzhan
NK115(re)001:12421: dbang can ma yin par gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams
NK115(re)001:12422: par snang ba yin pas rang rang dang 'tshams pa'i
NK115(re)001:12423: don de nyid nyams su blang na mthar gyis nges
NK115(re)001:12424: don gyi dgongs pa ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs
NK115(re)001:12425: par gyur pa'i tshe na ji spyod thams cad gzhan
NK115(re)001:12426: don 'ba' zhig tu 'gyur bas rnam pa la ltos
NK115(re)001:12428: khyad para du rdo rje'i theg pa'i lam la ni rigs lnga'i dam tshig las /
NK115(re)001:12429: rdo rje'i rigs la gsoda pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12430: rin chen rigs la ma byina par lena pa sogas
NK115(re)001:12431: ji skad bstan pa de rnams rtogs goms dang ldan
NK115(re)001:12432: pa'i gang zag la gnang ba'i dngosa bstana nyid dang
NK115(re)001:12433: / mos pas spyod pa tsam la dgongas pa lunga
NK115(re)001:12434: ston gyi tshul du yod pa'i rlung rtog dbu mar
NK115(re)001:12435: / gsod pa dang / theg pa chen po'i chos
NK115(re)001:12436: kyi don ma byin par len pa sogs rnama dbye
NK115(re)001:12437: ma phyed par mos pas spyod pa las dang po
NK115(re)001:12438: ba rnams kyis kyang srog gcod pa la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:12439: sgra ji bzhin par spyod na sngagas la log par
NK115(re)001:12440: spyod pa de yi nyes pas thura la mnar med
NK115(re)001:12441: pa la sogs pa'i gnas su ltung zhing yun ring
NK115(re)001:12442: por sdug bsngal myong ba'i mthar r+au tra'i skye gnas
NK115(re)001:12443: su nying mtshams sbyor bar 'gyur ba'i tshul rgyud sde
NK115(re)001:12444: rnams nas byung ba de lta bas na /
NK115(re)001:12445: gsang sngags mtha' drug dang tshul bzhis bcings nas bstan
NK115(re)001:12446: pa'i don ma nor bar bkral te ston pa ni
NK115(re)001:12448: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK115(re)001:12449: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK115(re)001:12451: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon yin
NK115(re)001:12452: pas de nyid kyis ji ltar bstan pa bzhin du
NK115(re)001:12453: nyams su len par byed pa las rang bzo dang
NK115(re)001:12454: pho tshod kyis 'jug tu yod pa ma yin no
NK115(re)001:12455: // mdora bsdus te bshad na rang la ye nas
NK115(re)001:12456: gnas pa'i sems kyi gnas lugs nyid mkhris nad can
NK115(re)001:12457: la dung gi dkar snang gab pa bzhin thog ma
NK115(re)001:12458: med pa nas tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pas bsgribs te
NK115(re)001:12459: ma mthong zhing gaba pa'i tshul du yod pa la
NK115(re)001:12462: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK115(re)001:12463: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK115(re)001:12464: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK115(re)001:12465: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK115(re)001:12466: zhes tshul bzhi'i sgo nas gsang ba'i don de nyid
NK115(re)001:12467: mngon sum du ma rtogsa pa de srid kyi bar
NK115(re)001:12468: du ni skal dman rnams la brda la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:12469: sgo nas sbasa par byas pa'i gasnga ba sbyor sgrol
NK115(re)001:12470: la sogs par rang gis ji bzhin spyod mi nus
NK115(re)001:12471: pa'i cha thams cad la mngona par 'chela te spyod
NK115(re)001:12472: par mi byed par de 'dra'i rigs kuna la gzura
NK115(re)001:12473: zhing spyod pa dus tshod dang bstun par bya'o zhes
NK115(re)001:12474: gdams pa'o // gnyis pa nyams na phyir bcos pa'i tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:12476: dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu gnyen po dang bcas pa /
NK115(re)001:12478: dang po sdom pa skye ba'i rten ni /
NK115(re)001:12479: rdo rje theg pa'i lam la tshul bzhin zhugs nas
NK115(re)001:12480: gnang bkag shes pas spyad na lan gzhan las khyad
NK115(re)001:12482: theg pa gzhan gyis spangs pa'i shin tu nyes pa
NK115(re)001:12483: che ba nyin re bzhina du bram ze gsoda pa
NK115(re)001:12484: dang pha ma gsod pa sogs matshamas meda pa'i las
NK115(re)001:12485: la spyod pa lta bu'i sdig pa ldan pa zhig
NK115(re)001:12486: yin kyang sngagas sdoma skye ba'i rten du rung ba
NK115(re)001:12487: yin zhing / ji srid du 'gyod pa dang bcas
NK115(re)001:12488: shing las ngan pa de las log pa'i phyi nas
NK115(re)001:12489: lam ston gyi bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa
NK115(re)001:12490: gcig la sangs rgyas dngos su bltas nas de'i bka'
NK115(re)001:12491: bzhin bsgrub pa las gzhan du ma g.yos na /
NK115(re)001:12493: pha rol tu phyin pa man chad du 'byung mi
NK115(re)001:12494: shes pa'i sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs sngags kyi gnas
NK115(re)001:12496: dam tshig gi cha re re la gus par bltas
NK115(re)001:12497: shing dang du blangs pa las kyang sgrib pa dpag
NK115(re)001:12498: tu med pa 'dzad cing tshogs chen po rdzogs pa
NK115(re)001:12499: dang / thabs zab la rnam grangs mang ba yod
NK115(re)001:12500: pas dbang po rnon po'i dbang du byas na tshe
NK115(re)001:12501: gcig la'ang grol bar 'gyur basa na gasnga sngagas rdo
NK115(re)001:12502: rje'i theg pa 'di theg pa 'og ma las thabas
NK115(re)001:12503: kyisa che zhing khyad par du gyur pa smosa ci
NK115(re)001:12504: dang / dgosa te / gdan bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:12505: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12506: mtshams med lnga ni byed pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12507: chom rkun las kyis longs spyod pa //
NK115(re)001:12509: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:12511: gnyis pa dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu gnyen po dang bcas pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12512: de la dam tshig bsrung 'dod yod pa tsam gyis
NK115(re)001:12513: mi chog ste rtsa ba dang yan lag gi ltung
NK115(re)001:12514: ba so so'i blang dor gyi matshamas mi shesa na
NK115(re)001:12515: nyes pa ci 'dra ba zhig gis nyams par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:12516: ba'i ngos bzung ci yang med pas na de ni
NK115(re)001:12517: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo dang po dang /
NK115(re)001:12518: de ltar shes kyang bla mara mi gusa na des
NK115(re)001:12519: 'doms pa'i gnad la che thang du mi byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:12520: dbang gis ltung ba 'byung bar 'gyur bas gnyis pa
NK115(re)001:12521: dang / gus pa tsam yod kyang bslab pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:12522: bsrung ba la rtag tu gzob par ma byas na
NK115(re)001:12523: baga meda pa la gomas pas nyes pa 'dod rgyal
NK115(re)001:12524: du byed pas na gsum pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12525: gal te bag yod par byas kyang nyon mongas pa
NK115(re)001:12526: shugs drag la mthu che bas gnyen pos mgo mi
NK115(re)001:12527: non par nyes ltung 'byung bar 'gyur ba ni ltung
NK115(re)001:12528: ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:12529: de ltar ltung ba 'byunga ba'i sgo bzhi po de'i stenga du /
NK115(re)001:12530: ltung ba'i mtshams legs par shes pa yin kyang brjed ngasa che bas nyams par gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12531: drana pa mi gasla ba ste ltung ba byung ma
NK115(re)001:12532: byung brtag par byed pa'i shes bzhin gyis sems grims
NK115(re)001:12533: cha lhod pa gnyis bsnana pa dama tshiga nyamsa pa'i
NK115(re)001:12535: mkha' 'gro ma sdom pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:12536: mi shes pa dang bag med dang /
NK115(re)001:12537: nyon mongs mang dang mi gus dang //
NK115(re)001:12538: brjed ngas dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK115(re)001:12539: 'di drug dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu //
NK115(re)001:12541: de basa na de dag gi gnyen po bsten pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:12542: ltung ba'i mtshams phra mo tshun chad legs par shes
NK115(re)001:12543: shing nges par byas nas bla ma dang gdams ngag
NK115(re)001:12544: la gus pas bslab par bya ba'i gnas rnams la
NK115(re)001:12545: gces par blta zhing drana pa dang shesa bzhina gyis
NK115(re)001:12546: nyon mongs pa gang che ba de la ched du
NK115(re)001:12547: gnyen po bskyed pa gtso bor byed pa yisa dper
NK115(re)001:12548: na yun ring por mig longa bar gyur ba de
NK115(re)001:12549: sman pa mkhas pas thur dpyad kyis dbye ba'i gansa
NK115(re)001:12550: skabas thoba pa na de'i shin tu sems bsgrims te
NK115(re)001:12551: baga zon dang bcas pas bsrunga ba ji lta ba
NK115(re)001:12552: bzhina du sngar bshad pa ltar nyin mtshan thuna drug
NK115(re)001:12553: tu bcad pa'i cha so so'i nang du bdag ni
NK115(re)001:12554: nyes pa 'ba' zhig 'dzin cing yon tan gyi rgyun
NK115(re)001:12555: gang yang rgyud la mi chags pas ja tshags dang
