NK115(re)001:12556: 'dra bar gda' bas da lta nyes pa ci byung
NK115(re)001:12557: 'dug / dag snang dang mos gus byams dang snying
NK115(re)001:12558: rje bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i yon tan 'dra cang
NK115(re)001:12559: 'dug gam snyam du spang blanga gi gansa la bsgrimas
NK115(re)001:12560: shinga bsgrimas shinga zhes brtsegs mar gsungs pa ni res
NK115(re)001:12561: 'ga' ba thang lhod can ma yin par rtag tu
NK115(re)001:12562: ma yeng bar brtags dpyad btang ste bsrung dgos par
NK115(re)001:12563: 'dug / gdams so // gsum pa phyir bcos dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:12564: gso sla ba'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12565: ji ltar gso ba'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12566: dang po gso sla ba'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12567: spyir lus ngag gi bya ba'i grogs su sems mi
NK115(re)001:12568: 'gro ba med pas nyes pa gang byung yang gsang
NK115(re)001:12569: 'dod kyi bsam pa dang bcas na ni mdo sngags
NK115(re)001:12570: gnyis ka'i skabs su ltung ba gang yin kyang gso
NK115(re)001:12571: bar dka' yang / gsang sngags kyi skabs su ni
NK115(re)001:12572: gal te ltung ba 'byung ba'i rgyu gang yang rung
NK115(re)001:12573: ba'i dbang gis nyamsa pa'i nyes pa byung na slar
NK115(re)001:12574: gso ba'ang 'oga ma so byang gnyis kyi bslab pa
NK115(re)001:12575: nyams pa gso ba lasa sla ba'i phyir khyad par
NK115(re)001:12576: bar dka' yang / 'aphagas te / 'di ltar nyan
NK115(re)001:12577: thosa kyi sdoma khrimas ni dngos por zhen pa dang
NK115(re)001:12578: lus ngag gis bsdus pa'i gzugs can du blta ba'i
NK115(re)001:12579: dbang gis ltung ba gso dka' la /
NK115(re)001:12580: de yang dge slong la pham pa bzhi gang rung
NK115(re)001:12581: byung nas 'achaba semas sam gsang 'dod kyi bsam pa
NK115(re)001:12582: skad cig ma tsam la'ang ma skyes na /
NK115(re)001:12583: theg dman rang la bstan pa'i mdo'i dgongs pa ltar
NK115(re)001:12584: na chad pa las kyi bslab pa byin te spyod
NK115(re)001:12585: pa'i sgo nas phyir bcos par gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:12586: de 'dra ba de'i gang gi tshe dgra bcom pa
NK115(re)001:12587: thob par gyur na de rang bzhin du gnas par
NK115(re)001:12588: 'gyur te / 'khrul pa'i rgyu thams cad spang ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:12589: der ma zad rtsa ltung thun min byung ste bslab
NK115(re)001:12590: pa sbyin pa mtshan 'gyur na'ang bslab pa spyad mi
NK115(re)001:12592: gal te de'i bslab pa phul nas blang na bsnyen
NK115(re)001:12593: rdzogs kyi sdom pa skye zhing dge tshul la'ang bslab
NK115(re)001:12595: sems tsam yan chad theg chen pa rnams kyis ni
NK115(re)001:12596: pham pa 'chab med can la gsol bzhi'i las kyis
NK115(re)001:12597: dge slong gi sdom pa sbyin rjes chad pa las
NK115(re)001:12598: kyi bslab pa ster bar bzhed pas pham pa 'chab
NK115(re)001:12599: med phyis gsor yod pa'i tshul spyir btang ni de
NK115(re)001:12600: ltar yin zhing / 'dir lana bduna gsora yoda ces grangs nges pa can du gsungs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12601: spyir pham pa 'chab med can bslab sbyin byas pa
NK115(re)001:12602: de'i bslab pa phul te dge slong gi sdom pa
NK115(re)001:12603: blang du yod par gsungs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12605: btsun pa bslab pa brtsal bas bslab pa phul te khyim pa'i dngos por mchis pa las /
NK115(re)001:12606: de slar legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la
NK115(re)001:12607: rab tu byung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs te dge slong
NK115(re)001:12609: de dge 'dun gyis bsnyen bar rdzogs par bgyis na bsnyen par rdzogs pa zhes bagyi'am /
NK115(re)001:12610: u p+aa li bsnyen par rdzogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:12611: bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa ni 'das pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12613: lan bdun gyi nges pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12614: karma sha tam gyi rab byung gi cho ga'i bsnyen
NK115(re)001:12615: par rdzogs pa'i sngon du bar chad dri ba'i skabs
NK115(re)001:12616: / khyod sngon rab tu byung ba ma yin nam /
NK115(re)001:12618: gal te rab tu byung zer na zhes pa'i 'grel
NK115(re)001:12619: bar skyes pa ni rab tu byung ba lan bdun
NK115(re)001:12620: len du gnang ba'i phyir byung ba la sogs pa'o
NK115(re)001:12621: // gal te pham pa byung nas gsang 'dod kyi
NK115(re)001:12622: blo skad cig ma gcig tsam la skyes na 'achaba
NK115(re)001:12623: pa dang bacasa pa zhes bya bas de ni lana
NK115(re)001:12624: gciga kyanga slar gso ba'i yula med de /
NK115(re)001:12625: dper na rdza be'u chaga pa slar bcos su med pa bzhina no //
NK115(re)001:12626: byanga chub sems dpa'i sdoma pa ni chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:12627: gzugs brnyan dang sgyu ma lta bur blta zhing sems
NK115(re)001:12628: kyi las gtso che bas nyams pa rnams dper na
NK115(re)001:12629: rina chena gyi nyer spyad 'ga' zhig chaga grums su
NK115(re)001:12630: gyur na / gzhan mgar gyi las thabs la goms
NK115(re)001:12631: pa zhig gis sngar ma chag pa'i gnas skabs dang
NK115(re)001:12632: 'dra bar bcos su yod pa bzhin du gazhana rkyen
NK115(re)001:12633: dge ba'i bshesa gnyen sdom pa la gnas pa zhig
NK115(re)001:12634: la bsten nasa tshul bzhin bshags te slar blang na
NK115(re)001:12635: sor chud par gso ru yod pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:12636: gasnga sngagas kyi sdoma pa ni dper na gser dngul
NK115(re)001:12637: la sogs pa'i rina chena gyi snoda cung zad zhom
NK115(re)001:12638: par gyur na rang nyid kyis srong bar nus pa
NK115(re)001:12639: ltar / nyams par gyur pa'i ltung ba zhig yod na yang 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:12640: bdag nyid lhar rtogs pa'i stobs kyis dge ba'i bshes
NK115(re)001:12641: gnyen la ma bsten kyang ranga gi stobas bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:12642: la sogs pa'i mthu yisa snga ma bzhin sor chud
NK115(re)001:12643: par gso ru byar yoda pa yin pasa na bskyed
NK115(re)001:12644: rdzogs la goms cha med pa'i rgyud tshod dman pa
NK115(re)001:12645: dang / slob dpon la smod pa la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:12646: ma yin par 'chad 'gyur rnams las rang stobs kyis
NK115(re)001:12647: sbyong tshul dag la bsten nas gso chog pa yin
NK115(re)001:12648: dang / no // gnyis pa ji ltar gsol ba'i thabs bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:12649: sku gsung thugs kyi phyir bcos /
NK115(re)001:12651: de las gzhan pa'i phyir bcos kyi rnam grangs so //
NK115(re)001:12652: dang po sku gsung thugs kyi phyir bcos ni /
NK115(re)001:12653: de la rtsa ltung dang po bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la brnyas shing smod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12654: rdo rje'i spun rnams la 'khon 'dzin dang brnyas thabs
NK115(re)001:12655: shor ba sogs kyis gtso bo sku'i dam tshig nyams
NK115(re)001:12656: par gyur pa yin pas phyi bshol mi byed par
NK115(re)001:12657: snying nas 'gyod pa dang bcas 'phrala du sgo gsum
NK115(re)001:12658: gyis gus shing bkur te tshogs dang yo byad stob
NK115(re)001:12659: pa sogs kyis thugs mnyes par byas te sdom sems
NK115(re)001:12660: dang bcas pas gsor chud pa'am sngar sdom pa rnam
NK115(re)001:12661: par dag pa'i cha de dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes
NK115(re)001:12662: pas kha ma tshang ba lta bur song ba de
NK115(re)001:12664: de ltar myur du bshags dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan yang bkod pa chen po las /
NK115(re)001:12665: bla ma dang ni nye ba'i 'khor /
NK115(re)001:12666: rdo rje'i spun dang sring mo la //
NK115(re)001:12667: ngan smras tshig gi zur tsam yang //
NK115(re)001:12668: brda 'a ma dngos pos brjod mi bya //
NK115(re)001:12669: gal te rmi lam dag tu yang //
NK115(re)001:12670: byung na yid kyis bshags par bya //
NK115(re)001:12671: dngos dang zhe yis byas pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12672: gal te dran pas ma zin par //
NK115(re)001:12673: thal bar gyur kyang ma bshags na //
NK115(re)001:12674: mthur du bltas te dmyal bar 'gro //
NK115(re)001:12676: bla ma dang mched la ngag gis nyes pa song
NK115(re)001:12677: ba'am sngags rgya rgyun bcad pa sogs gsung gi tha
NK115(re)001:12678: tshiga nyamsa par gyur na rtsa ba'i bla ma nyid
NK115(re)001:12679: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung rdo rje'i
NK115(re)001:12680: ngo bo sangs rgyas rdo rje chosa sku mdog dmar
NK115(re)001:12681: po can spyi bor ram yang na bdag dang dbyer
NK115(re)001:12682: med du bsgomas la snying po pad+ma sa t+wa'am de'i
NK115(re)001:12683: yiga brgya 'buma ther 'dona zhing bla ma'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:12684: brjod pa 'ba' zhig don du gnyer bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:12685: yang bla ma dang mched sogs la snying nas gnod sems dang log lta skyes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12686: gsang don snod min la bsgrags pa sogs thugas kyi
NK115(re)001:12687: dam tshig lasa nyamsa par gyur na bdag nyid de
NK115(re)001:12688: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rdo rje'i ngo
NK115(re)001:12689: bo rdor sems su gsal ba'i spyi bor bla ma
NK115(re)001:12690: bsgoms la yan lag bdun pa phul nas dbang bzhi
NK115(re)001:12691: blangs rjes bla ma rang la bstim ste lo gsuma
NK115(re)001:12692: du smra ba bacada la thugs yid bsres pa'i ngang
NK115(re)001:12693: la rtse gciga tu mnyam para gazhaga pa ni gso
NK115(re)001:12695: de skad du'ang rngam glog las /
NK115(re)001:12696: bla ma spun la smad gyur na //
NK115(re)001:12697: tshe 'di nyid la mnyes byas te //
NK115(re)001:12698: mthol bshags drag pos 'gyod byas na //
NK115(re)001:12699: de ni bskang ba'i mchog tu 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:12700: gal te bdag gam bla ma spun //
NK115(re)001:12701: ma bskangs bar du tshe 'phos na //
NK115(re)001:12702: de ni bskang ba'i tshad las 'das //
NK115(re)001:12703: gsung gi dam tshig ral gyur na //
NK115(re)001:12704: rdo rje chos su bdag bsgoms te //
NK115(re)001:12706: thugs kyi dam tshig ral gyur na //
NK115(re)001:12707: rdo rje sems dpar bdag bsgoms la //
NK115(re)001:12708: lo gsum bar du mi smra bar //
NK115(re)001:12709: bsam gtan sbyor ba rab tu bya //
NK115(re)001:12710: yan lag dam tshig ral gyu na //
NK115(re)001:12711: so so rang rang rigs kyis bskang //
NK115(re)001:12713: gnyis pa thun 'das kyi phyir bcos ni /
NK115(re)001:12714: de la spyir ltung ba phal la yan lag bzhi ldan dgos te /
NK115(re)001:12717: lus ngag dang 'brel na de'i sbyor ba /
NK115(re)001:12718: sgo gsum gang gis grub pa'i las lam rdzogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:12719: mthar thug bzhi tshang na sngags sdom gtong ba'i pham
NK115(re)001:12720: pa zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan sngar bkod zin la
NK115(re)001:12721: / yid kyis grub pa'i rtsa ltung gang rung gnyen
NK115(re)001:12722: po dang spel nas skyes na dngos gzhi mi tshang
NK115(re)001:12723: yang de la bshags pa ma byas par drug cha
NK115(re)001:12724: 'das na thun tshod 'das pa'i ltung ba zhes bya
NK115(re)001:12725: / ste / phas pham pa'i 'og nas lci ba ste /
NK115(re)001:12728: tshad ldan ltung bar bshad pa yin //
NK115(re)001:12729: yan lag gtso bo dus 'das pa //
NK115(re)001:12730: lci ba dus ni bshad pa ste //
NK115(re)001:12731: sbyor ba ma rdzogs sbom po'o //
NK115(re)001:12732: yan lag phra ba nyes byas so //
NK115(re)001:12734: de'ang ngo bo la ltos nas rtsa ltung dang /
NK115(re)001:12736: nyes byas rnams kyi lci yang gi khyad par shes par bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:12737: dus la ltos na nyin mtshan thun druga tu bcad
NK115(re)001:12738: pa'i cha gang yang rung ba zhig gi nang du
NK115(re)001:12739: ltung ba la sbyor ba'i bya ba brtsams nas thun
NK115(re)001:12740: de'i nang du gnyen pos ma sleb par dus tshod
NK115(re)001:12741: de lasa thala te thuna tshoda 'ad'a ba'i matshamas la
NK115(re)001:12742: thun 'das kyi ltung ba zhes brjod pa yin la
NK115(re)001:12746: rala ba zhes pa bzhi po'ang zhaga gcig dang /
NK115(re)001:12749: lo gnyis sam gsum 'adsa tshun chad la bshags par
NK115(re)001:12750: byas na gso bar runga ste snga ma snga ma
NK115(re)001:12751: bas phyi ma phyi ma lci zhing lo gsuma 'adsa
NK115(re)001:12752: par gyur na bshags pa byas kyang gso bar runga
NK115(re)001:12754: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:12755: spyir na dam tshig khyad par las //
NK115(re)001:12756: dus la khyad par nges phye ba //
NK115(re)001:12757: dam las 'gal zhes nyes byas gang //
NK115(re)001:12758: zhag gis bar ma chod par ni //
NK115(re)001:12759: dmigs pa'i yul la bshags byas na //
NK115(re)001:12760: des ni sor yang chud pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12761: nyams zhes zla bas ma chod par //
NK115(re)001:12762: 'gyod pa drag pos bshags pas so //
NK115(re)001:12763: dam las 'das na lo dag gis //
NK115(re)001:12764: bar du ma chod bshags pas so //
NK115(re)001:12765: lo ni gnyis dang gsum dag las //
NK115(re)001:12766: dam tshig ral ba zhes bya ba //
NK115(re)001:12767: mchog tu drag na gso ru rung //
NK115(re)001:12768: lo gsum dag las 'das pa ni //
NK115(re)001:12769: de ni gso ru mi rung ste //
NK115(re)001:12770: gal te blangs na gnyis ka 'tshig /
NK115(re)001:12771: nges par sa spyod sdug bsngal la //
NK115(re)001:12772: rgyun du spyod pa kho na'o //
NK115(re)001:12774: de ltar bshags bya la lci yang yod pa ltar bshags tshul yang je cher stobs bskyed pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:12775: 'agla ba'i nyes pa byung na tshogas kyi 'khora lo sngon du 'gro bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12776: nyamsa pa'i nyes pa byung na rang la bdog dgu
NK115(re)001:12777: ste longs spyod yod tshad bla ma dang dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:12778: gyi lha la sogs par phul nas bskanga bar byed
NK115(re)001:12779: pa dang / 'adsa par gyur na de las kyang
NK115(re)001:12780: 'phangs pa'i bu dang chunga ma dag nora gyi dbyiga
NK115(re)001:12781: rin po che gang bzang gtong ba'i sgo nas phyir
NK115(re)001:12782: pa dang / bcos pa dang / rala ba'i nyes
NK115(re)001:12783: stong du gyur na ni rang gi sroga la'ang mi
NK115(re)001:12784: blta ba'i brtson 'grus drag po dag gi sgo nas
NK115(re)001:12785: bla ma'i bka' bzhin byas pas gso ba'i rnama bazhaga
NK115(re)001:12786: rnamas ni rdo rje nyi ma rnama para bkoda pa'i
NK115(re)001:12787: rgyud de nyid lasa gsungas pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:12788: gsum pa de las gzhan pa'i phyir bcos kyi rnam grangs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:12789: rgyud sde tha dad nas gsungs pa rnams bsdus te
NK115(re)001:12790: bstan pa'i don gong du bshad pa de las gazhana
NK115(re)001:12791: yanga 'di ltar bla ma las dabnga bzhi po bskyar
NK115(re)001:12792: nas blang bar bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12793: rang gi dmigs pas badga 'juga blanga bar byas na
NK115(re)001:12794: sdom pa dang dam tshig la nyes pa'i skyon byung
NK115(re)001:12795: ba thams cad rnam par dag par 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:12797: dkyil 'khor rgyal po mthong ba ni //
NK115(re)001:12798: cung zad de ni mi 'grub med //
NK115(re)001:12799: sdig pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK115(re)001:12801: de'ang dus kyi 'khor lo las ni dbang thob mtshams
NK115(re)001:12802: tha dad pa la ltos pa'i spyod tshul 'di ltar
NK115(re)001:12803: rang lugs kyi rigs dbang lnga dang thabs dang thabs
NK115(re)001:12804: byung gnyis te bum dbang bdun thob pas dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:12805: gyi lha grangs re re bzhin nam gtso bo'i bzlas
NK115(re)001:12806: pa sum khri drug stong gis sbyang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12807: de'i steng du bum gsang thob pa las nyams na
NK115(re)001:12808: bla ma'i bkas bsgos pa'i chad las kyis sbyang ba
NK115(re)001:12809: dang / sher dbang yan chad thob pas dben par
NK115(re)001:12810: bskyed rdzogas bsgom pa 'ba' zhig gis rang rgyud byin
NK115(re)001:12812: de gsum gas kyang dag pa'i mtshan ma mthong na
NK115(re)001:12813: slar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas sdom pa bzung ste
NK115(re)001:12815: de'i tshe sngar dbang thob dus kyi bslab gral dang
NK115(re)001:12816: rnyed bkur len pa sogs mi byed pa'i tshul 'dul
NK115(re)001:12817: pa'i sde snod dang sgo bstun par yang snang ste
NK115(re)001:12818: dge 'dun lhag ma'i spo spyod bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:12819: de bzhin du spyi mdo las nyams tshul lnga la ltos nas phyir bcos pa'i tshul bstan te /
NK115(re)001:12821: nyams par gyur pa gang zhe na //
NK115(re)001:12822: kun tu nyams pa chen po dang //
NK115(re)001:12823: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK115(re)001:12824: de bzhin zlas nyams zhar nyams lnga //
NK115(re)001:12825: zhes pa'i kun tu nyams pa chen po ni yul
NK115(re)001:12826: ches gnyan pa la kun dkris drag pos spyad pa'am
NK115(re)001:12827: lan grangs mang du spyad pa la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12828: rtsa ba dang yan lag nyams pa ni spyi dang mthun la /
NK115(re)001:12829: zlas nyams zhes pa gang zag gang zhig rang nyid
NK115(re)001:12830: nyams bzhin du gso ba la mi brtson pa ste
NK115(re)001:12831: / de lta bu dang skad cig tsam yang phrad
NK115(re)001:12832: pa dang smra bar bya ba'ang ma yin na de'i
NK115(re)001:12833: mgon bya ba dang lhan cig mnal ba lta ci
NK115(re)001:12834: / smos te / rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12835: skad cig tsam yang phrad smra mi bya zhes //
NK115(re)001:12837: de'ang sngon legs 'ong gi gtam rgyud ltar /
NK115(re)001:12838: bsod nams med pa'i slong mo ba gcig dang 'grogs
NK115(re)001:12839: te song na slong mo ba thams cad kyi 'tsho
NK115(re)001:12841: sbal pa rma can gcig gis sbal pa gzhan mang po dang /
NK115(re)001:12842: 'o ma rul ba cung zad kyis 'o ma mang
NK115(re)001:12843: po ma rungs par 'gyur ba ltar gang zag gcig
NK115(re)001:12844: po de nyams pa'i skyon gyis de dang 'grogs pa
NK115(re)001:12845: thams cad skyon can du 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:12846: ji ltar 'o ma rul ba dag /
NK115(re)001:12848: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK115(re)001:12849: rnal 'byor can kun ma rungs byed //
NK115(re)001:12851: zhar nyams ni rang gis ched du ma yin kyang gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal ba la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12852: de dag bskang ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:12854: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12855: ting nge 'dzin dang de nyid do //
NK115(re)001:12857: las kyis bskang ba ni sbyin sreg dang /
NK115(re)001:12858: gtor ma dang bzlasa brjod la brten pa rnams te /
NK115(re)001:12859: de yang kun tu nyams pa la chig 'bum sum khri /
NK115(re)001:12860: rtsa ba nyams pa la lnga khri sum stong /
NK115(re)001:12861: yan lag nyams pa la lnga stong sum brgya /
NK115(re)001:12862: zlas nyams la brgya phrag gsum /
NK115(re)001:12863: zhar nyams la lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:12864: rdzas kyis bskang ba ni rigs lnga gang gi dam
NK115(re)001:12865: tshig nyams pa'i khyad par dang bstun nas mi rigs
NK115(re)001:12866: lnga'i bla ma'am / der mos pa la de bzhin
NK115(re)001:12867: gshegs pa'i lnga'i rang bzhin du bltas nas rin po
NK115(re)001:12868: che phangs pa med par stob pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12871: mi dag sdig pa'i bag chags rnams //
NK115(re)001:12872: gdung ba'i glu dang bcas pas bshags //
NK115(re)001:12873: zhes pa ltar gnong 'gyod kyi mngon rtogs gdung ba'i glus ngom pa'i tshul gyis bshags pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12874: ting nge 'dzin gyis bskang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:12875: man ngag dang ldan pa dag gis ni /
NK115(re)001:12876: 'pho meda kyi tshula khrimas rdzogs rim rang lus thabs ldan sogs spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:12877: thiga le'i rnala 'byora bar 'dzag bsgom pa sogs kyis gso bar byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:12878: gal te man ngag med pa'i dang po'i las can gyis nyams pa gso dgos pa yin na ni /
NK115(re)001:12879: bshags yul nyid bla ma'am med na de yi dam
NK115(re)001:12880: la sogs par bsgoms nas stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags
NK115(re)001:12881: pas de'i gnas gsum gyi 'od zer las rang gi
NK115(re)001:12882: nyams chag nyes ltung thams cad sbyangs par bsam mo
NK115(re)001:12883: // de kho na nyid kyis sbyang ba ni 'khor
NK115(re)001:12884: gsum yongs dag chen por rtogs pa'i ngang la mnyam
NK115(re)001:12885: par 'jog pa'i shes rab kyis sbyang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:12886: gzhan yang zhi ba'i sbyin srega rgyas pa'am /
NK115(re)001:12887: za byed rdo rje mkha' 'gro sbyin sreg lta bu me la brten nas sbyong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12888: gtor ma sbyangs rtog sbar gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs
NK115(re)001:12889: pa 'khor 'das thams cad 'khor lo'i dbang phyug gi
NK115(re)001:12890: rnam par sad pa la gtong zhing 'dod don gsol
NK115(re)001:12891: ba dang / yo ga nas bshad pa'i drala ba'i
NK115(re)001:12892: sngagas rgya gnyis te ltung ba slong ba'i phyag rgya
NK115(re)001:12893: ba dang / dang / de'i sngags kyi rim pa la brten nas ngan 'gro dgug dral dang /
NK115(re)001:12894: de bzhin du rdo rje yang tog gi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:12895: yig 'bru sngags kyis sbyang ba ni //
NK115(re)001:12896: rkang mthil gnyis su yam gnyis bsam //
NK115(re)001:12897: gsang ba'i sgo ru ram bsam mo //
NK115(re)001:12898: lte bar rigs drug yig 'bru bsam //
NK115(re)001:12899: snying gar phatahkyi gdan dag la //
NK115(re)001:12900: sku gsung thugs kyi snying po bsam //
NK115(re)001:12901: yam las ye shes rlung byung ste //
NK115(re)001:12902: ram las ye shes me sbar nas //
NK115(re)001:12903: rigs drug bag chags thams cad bsreg /
NK115(re)001:12904: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs su gyur //
NK115(re)001:12906: zhes pa'ang man ngag shin tu zab par gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:12907: rnam 'joms dang sme brtsegs la sogs pa'i gzungs kyis bsgrubs pa'i bum pa'i chus bkru ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12908: mkha' dbyings su shar ba'i dbang lha las rigs pa'i dbang lnga blangs nas bkru ba'i 'dun pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12909: chu klung sogs bam las m+aa ma k+ai'i bdag nyid
NK115(re)001:12910: du mos nas spyod pa'i brtul zhugs kyis lus bkru
NK115(re)001:12911: ba sogs bkru ba'i rim pa rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:12912: gtum mo'i mes lte bar kam yig dang snying gar sha za'i gzugs kyi sdig pa bsrega pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12913: rlung la brten nas sbyang ba yang gtsug lag khang la sogs par /
NK115(re)001:12914: 'phan dang rnga yab sogs sgreng ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12915: tshogas pa mang po'i dbus sama rten byin can gyi drunga du nyesa pa bsgraga pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12918: dpa' bo dang dpa' mo'i dga' ston bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12921: rngon pa la ri dwags dang gcan gzan sogs mi
NK115(re)001:12922: gsod pa'i rngan pa ster ba sogs sroga bslu ba'i
NK115(re)001:12923: thabs thams cad la 'bad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12924: mdo sngags kyi gsunga raba spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:12925: khyad par thar pa chen po'i mdo dang /
NK115(re)001:12926: dri med bshags pa'i rgyud la sogs pa bklaga pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12927: sdig pa 'dag pa'i gnyen por basngagasa pa'i gzugs sngags spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:12928: khyad par du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi yang snying yiga brgya bzla ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12929: yan lag bskyod pa tsam la phan yon che ba man+dala 'bul ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12930: tshogs thams cad kyi sgo yan lag bduna pa bya ba dang /
NK115(re)001:12931: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi spangs rtogs kyi gzugs brnyan mchod rten bzhengs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12932: mi nus na'ang s+aats+tsha gdab pa la sogas pa dam
NK115(re)001:12933: tshig nyams chag sbyong ba'i thabas kyisa dus rtag tu
NK115(re)001:12934: blos mi 'dor bar sbyang ba la brtson par byas
NK115(re)001:12935: na gnyen po'i rim pa ni mthar gtugsa shing zad
NK115(re)001:12936: para 'gyur ba ma yina la sbyong tshul de rnams
NK115(re)001:12937: la ni / phyi nang gi 'byung ba la brten pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12938: snying po rgyan las gsungs pa'i sbyong tshul nyer lnga la sogs pa 'du ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:12939: khyada para du yo ga rnam pa gsum gyi sgor
NK115(re)001:12940: zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag skong
NK115(re)001:12941: zhing rtog sgrib sbyong ba'i spyi khrus rmad du byung
NK115(re)001:12942: ba na raka donga spruga gi man ngag la brten
NK115(re)001:12943: nas / rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs thams cad
NK115(re)001:12944: mngon sum bzhin du gsal ba la dad gus gdung
NK115(re)001:12945: shugs drag po bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12946: lta sgom gyi ngang mdangs ma shor ba'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:12947: phyi yo byad tshogs kyi bskang ba dngos gtsang la
NK115(re)001:12948: spus legs shing rgyu tshogs tshang ba'i sman raka gtor
NK115(re)001:12949: ma mar me rnams re re la brgya rtsa brgyad
NK115(re)001:12950: re'am ci 'byor ba bshams pa sogs mchod pa'i yo
NK115(re)001:12952: nang phung po rten gyi bskang ba dkar cha sman /
NK115(re)001:12955: rlung sems kyi cha mar me dang /
NK115(re)001:12956: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi bskang ba /
NK115(re)001:12957: rang byung gi rig pa'i gshis bde ba chen po sman /
NK115(re)001:12960: rang bzhin gsal ba sgron me yin pa sogs kyis
NK115(re)001:12961: mtshon nas phyi nang gsang ba'i sman raka sogs so
NK115(re)001:12962: so'i bskang ba'i tshig gis gsal btab nas nya stong
NK115(re)001:12963: tshes brgyad sogs la bashagas pa byas na des ni
NK115(re)001:12964: nyams chag thams cad gang yang mi 'adga pa meda
NK115(re)001:12965: par gsungs shing / de lta ma grub na'ang phyag
NK115(re)001:12966: gi bko byang tsam rgyun du yid dam du bgyis
NK115(re)001:12967: pas kyang nyams chag thams cad 'dag par 'gyur te
NK115(re)001:12968: par gsungs shing / / ji skad du /
NK115(re)001:12969: gang gis sgyu 'phrul zhi khro yi //
NK115(re)001:12971: nyams chag thams cad byang 'gyur te //
NK115(re)001:12972: mtshams med lnga yi sdig kyang 'byang //
NK115(re)001:12973: na raka gnas kyang dong sprugs te //
NK115(re)001:12974: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK115(re)001:12976: de ltar dmigas bacasa kyi bshags pa kuna la nyes
NK115(re)001:12977: ltung phra mo yan chad la 'gyod pa'i semas bskyed
NK115(re)001:12978: pa ni lhaga para gces te /
NK115(re)001:12979: 'gyod pa med na nyes pa sun 'byin pa'i mthu med la /
NK115(re)001:12980: bshags yul gyi rten kyang bslus par 'gyur zhing /
NK115(re)001:12981: sdom sems kyang nus pa chung la gnyen po kun
NK115(re)001:12982: tu spyod pa'ang stobs zhan par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro
NK115(re)001:12983: // de yang slob dpon gyis shes pa bcus bsrung
NK115(re)001:12984: la slob mas de ltar mi shes pas slob dpon
NK115(re)001:12985: gyi bka' bzhin du bsrung bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:12986: de la shes pa bcu ni /
NK115(re)001:12987: tshig don gyi gnad shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12988: dris pa'i lan shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12989: dbang dang man ngag gi skabs shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12990: lta ba yangs par shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12991: bsgom pa ngang che bar shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12992: 'khor ba dang ma 'dres par shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12993: chos nyid zab par shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12994: 'das pa'i sa la gnas par shes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:12995: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid shes pa dang //
NK115(re)001:12996: chos can dang chos nyid kyi mtshan nyid shes pa ste /
NK115(re)001:12998: shes pa gcig gi khyad par gyis //
NK115(re)001:12999: khyad par bcu yi bsrung thabs 'phags //
NK115(re)001:13001: gsum pa nyams pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK115(re)001:13003: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK115(re)001:13004: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:13005: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i //
NK115(re)001:13007: zhes pa ltar nyes pa byung yang ma bashagas par
NK115(re)001:13008: de dang lhan du 'grogs na tshe 'dira ci tsam
NK115(re)001:13009: brtson kyang dngos grub med pa'i steng /
NK115(re)001:13010: nad gdon sogs zhi ba'i las bsgrub na de nyid 'phel bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13011: tshe bsod sogs rgyas pa'i las bsgrub na de nyid
NK115(re)001:13012: zhi bar 'gyur ba sogs sgrub pa thams cad phyin
NK115(re)001:13013: ci log tu 'gyur zhing sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK115(re)001:13017: sems smyo 'bogs sogs su 'gyur bas bde legas kyi
NK115(re)001:13018: yona tan thams cad 'griba cing mi 'dod pa du
NK115(re)001:13019: ma khab len la lcags bzhin 'du ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13020: phyi ma dmyal ba gang gis kyang do zla meda
NK115(re)001:13021: cing rgyal ba sras dang bcas pas kyang skyob para
NK115(re)001:13022: mi nus shing shin tu thar bar dka' ba'i rdo
NK115(re)001:13023: rje'i dmyal ba zhes bya bar ltunga bar 'gyur te
NK115(re)001:13025: rtsa kun nyams pa'i 'chal ba dag /
NK115(re)001:13026: gso la nye bar ma brtson na //
NK115(re)001:13027: rdo rje'i dmyal bar de ltung ste //
NK115(re)001:13028: dmyal ba phal pa thams cad kyi //
NK115(re)001:13029: sdug bsngal gcig tu bsdoms pas ni //
NK115(re)001:13030: de yi 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK115(re)001:13031: sangs rgyas stong gi 'od zer dang //
NK115(re)001:13032: byang chub sems dpa'i phrin las kun //
NK115(re)001:13033: rgyun du mdzad kyang phan mi 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:13034: bskal pa ther 'bum dung phyur bcu /
NK115(re)001:13040: bzhi pa bsrungs pa'i phan yon ni /
NK115(re)001:13041: de la mdo sngags gnyis ka'i tshul khrims kyi bslab
NK115(re)001:13042: pa ni yon tan thams cad kyi rten gzhi yin
NK115(re)001:13043: pa'i phyir / sngags kyi tshul khrims sam dama tshiga
NK115(re)001:13044: rnam par dag pa bsrung ba dang ldana pa las
NK115(re)001:13045: ni byin rlabs che bas lam myur ba /
NK115(re)001:13046: thabs zab pas 'jug pa bde ba'i bskyed rdzogs gnyis
NK115(re)001:13047: kyi yon tan thams cad 'byung ste de dag gi
NK115(re)001:13048: gzhi rten dam tshig yin pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:13049: gal te dam tshig nyams na dbang dang bskyed rdzogs
NK115(re)001:13050: las byung ba'i yon tan gang yang 'grub par mi
NK115(re)001:13051: 'gyur te 'bras bu 'byung ba'i rgyu sa bon yin
NK115(re)001:13052: kyang gzhi sa la ma brten na myu gu skye
NK115(re)001:13055: ji ltar sa gzhi gshin pa la //
NK115(re)001:13056: brten nas sa bon btab pa las //
NK115(re)001:13057: 'bras bu smin par gyur pa yis //
NK115(re)001:13059: chos rnams kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:13060: dam tshig 'di la gnas pa na //
NK115(re)001:13061: bla med byang chub rnams smin pas //
NK115(re)001:13064: de bas na dam tshig bsrung ba'i gang zag de /
NK115(re)001:13065: gnas skabs su'ang bsam don yid bzhin du 'grub /
NK115(re)001:13067: 'jig rten pa'i lha chen po dag gis bkur /
NK115(re)001:13068: rgyal dang rgyal sras rnams kyis dgongs par mdzad pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:13070: gsang sngags rdo rje'i dam la gnas //
NK115(re)001:13071: de yis smon pa kun 'grub cing //
NK115(re)001:13072: lha rnams kyis kyang rtag tu bsrung //
NK115(re)001:13073: rgyal ba rgyal mchog sras bcas kyis //
NK115(re)001:13074: bu bzhin dgongs pa dam pa mdzad //
NK115(re)001:13075: ting 'dzin yon tan dpag yas shing //
NK115(re)001:13076: kun bzang rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK115(re)001:13079: skye ba bcu druga gama zhes pas lam la 'bad
NK115(re)001:13080: pa chung yang de tshun chad na thob par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:13081: te / dam tshig lnga pa las /
NK115(re)001:13082: gal te ltung ba med gyur na //
NK115(re)001:13083: skye ba bcu drug dag las 'grub //
NK115(re)001:13085: thabs brtson shes rab kyi dbang du gyur pa dag
NK115(re)001:13086: ni myur na tshe 'di nyid la grol ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:13087: / rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:13088: bla med sngags kyi dngos grub gang //
NK115(re)001:13089: shin tu brtson pas gang bsgrubs pa //
NK115(re)001:13090: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas te //
NK115(re)001:13091: gdul bya'i zhing du mdzad pa ston //
NK115(re)001:13092: grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi /
NK115(re)001:13093: zab mo'i nye lam mthar thug pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13094: zhes pas skye ba 'di la zung 'jug gi sku brnyes pa'am /
NK115(re)001:13095: 'bring rnams 'chi kha'i sdud rim gyi mthar dpe'i 'od
NK115(re)001:13096: gsal de gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal dang 'phrad nas
NK115(re)001:13097: don gyi 'od gsal du gyur te slob pa'i zung
NK115(re)001:13098: 'jug gi skur ldang nus la gal te da lta
NK115(re)001:13099: sad dus na don gyi 'od gsal la 'jug nus
NK115(re)001:13100: pa zhig yin na de gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:13101: dang gnyis med du 'dres pas yang dag pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:13102: shes kyi mtha' mngon sum du gyur nas mi slob
NK115(re)001:13103: pa'i zung 'jug gi skur ldang ba'i sgo nas sangs
NK115(re)001:13105: gal te dpe'i 'od gsal tsam la'ang brtan pa ma
NK115(re)001:13106: thob pas 'chi srid der grol bar ma gyur na
NK115(re)001:13107: srid pa bar ma dora gdams ngag dran nas rang
NK115(re)001:13108: bzhin sprul pa'i zhing sogs su skyes te der lam
NK115(re)001:13109: gyi 'phro sbyangs nas grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:13110: de'ang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rtsa rlung thig le
NK115(re)001:13111: gsum las su rung zhing sems rgyud la ting nge
NK115(re)001:13112: 'dzin dang zag med kyi yon tan je cher 'phel
NK115(re)001:13113: bas thun mong gi dngos grub gruba pa brgyad thob
NK115(re)001:13115: mkha' spyod ral gri ril bu dang //
NK115(re)001:13116: rkang mgyogs bum pa gnod sbyin khol //
NK115(re)001:13117: bcud len dang ni mig sman no //
NK115(re)001:13118: zhes pas mkha' spyod ni nam mkha' la gnas nus shing 'chi ba med pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13119: ral gri ni pha rol las rgyal bar byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13120: ril bu ni sman gang dag bsgrub pa lag tu thogs pas lus mi snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13121: rkang mgyogs ni mchi lhwam grub ste gyon pas yud tsam la rgya mtsho'i mtha' yang 'khor ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13122: bum pa ni de'i nang du zad mi shes pa'i 'dod dgu'i gter 'byung ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13123: gnod sbyin khol po ni de'i bran byas nas ci
NK115(re)001:13124: dgos pa bsgrub cing mi 'bum phrag gis bsgrub dgos
NK115(re)001:13125: pa'i las nyin gcig la zin pa rgyal po mya
NK115(re)001:13126: ngan med kyi mchod rten bye ba nub gcig la
NK115(re)001:13128: bcud len ni nyi zla'i tshe glang po'i stobs pad+ma'i mdangs dang ldan zhing /
NK115(re)001:13129: ldang ba na shing bal las yang ba la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13130: mig sman ni mig la byugs pas sa 'og gi
NK115(re)001:13131: ga ter mthong ba khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin
NK115(re)001:13133: dabnga bcu ni so so'i ngo bo ni sngar mdo
NK115(re)001:13134: lam du bshad zin la de rnams ma dag sa
NK115(re)001:13135: bdun na phyi dang dag sa gsum na nang du
NK115(re)001:13136: bzhag pa dang gnyis yod cing /
NK115(re)001:13137: de yang dag sa gsum na phul du byung bas te /
NK115(re)001:13140: gang tshe mar me mdzad kyis nga //
NK115(re)001:13141: lung bstan gyur pa de yi tshe //
NK115(re)001:13142: sa brgyad pa ni thob gyur cing //
NK115(re)001:13143: dbang bcu dag kyang thob par gyur //
NK115(re)001:13145: rgyun mthar 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur ba thob pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:13147: byang chub sems dpa' sa chen po thob pa 'od
NK115(re)001:13148: zer gyi sprin chen po'i dbang bskur bas dbang bskur
NK115(re)001:13149: ba / dbang bcu thob pa sha stag tu gyur te /
NK115(re)001:13151: dbang bcu shin tu rnam dag ni sangs rgyas kyi sa na yod do //
NK115(re)001:13152: dabnga phyug brgyad dang zhes pa 'di'i don gzhan du
NK115(re)001:13153: thun mong gi dngos grub dang sbyar nas bshad la
NK115(re)001:13154: / thun mong zhes pa'ang 'jig rten pa'i lam dang /
NK115(re)001:13155: bskyed rim kho na'i lam gyis kyang 'grub pas de dag dang thun mong par bzhag kyang /
NK115(re)001:13156: gzhung 'dir ni slob lam mthar thug pa'i tshe na
NK115(re)001:13157: gzung 'dzin gyi rten rtsa rlung thig le'i rgyu ba
NK115(re)001:13158: shin tu phra ba dang tshogs brgyad rtog pa'i bag
NK115(re)001:13159: chags dang bcas pa rnam par dag nas mi slob
NK115(re)001:13160: pa'i 'bras bu rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin mngon
NK115(re)001:13161: du 'gyur ba'i sbyor ba slob pa'i lam du 'phags
NK115(re)001:13162: lam brgyad kyi ngo bo dbang phyug gi don brgyad
NK115(re)001:13165: phra zhing yang la phra bar nus pa dang //
NK115(re)001:13166: spyod par nus dang bdag nyid chen po dang //
NK115(re)001:13167: dga' mgur byed dang thams cad dbang du 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:13168: ci 'dod byed dang dbang phyug don brgyad do //
NK115(re)001:13170: de la phra zhing ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dbu ma'i rang bzhin du mthong ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13171: yang ba ni ye shes kyi rlung ste de'i stobs
NK115(re)001:13172: kyis mkha' khyab kyi 'jig rten gyi khams su rdzu
NK115(re)001:13173: 'phrul gyis skad cig tsam la 'gro ba dang blta
NK115(re)001:13174: bar nus pa'o // phra bar nus pa ni dbu
NK115(re)001:13175: mar rlung sems zhugs pas bdag gzhan mtha' dag stong
NK115(re)001:13176: pa nyid du thim par rtogs pas gnyis snang thams
NK115(re)001:13177: bar nus pa'o // cad nub pa'o // spyod par
NK115(re)001:13178: nus pa ni nang gi btsun mo dbu ma yin
NK115(re)001:13179: pas der rlung sems zhugs pa'i rten 'brel gyis phyi
NK115(re)001:13180: rol tu gzugs rdo rje ma'i rang bzhin can la
NK115(re)001:13181: sogs pa 'dod yon lnga la chos nyid kyi rol
NK115(re)001:13182: bar nus pa'o // cad nub pa'o // par spyod
NK115(re)001:13183: pa'o // bdag nyid chen po ni mtshan dpe 'bar
NK115(re)001:13185: bdud bzhi las rnam par rgyal ba dang mthu stobs kyi bdag por gyur pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13186: dga' mgur byed pa ni 'gro ba rnams la ji
NK115(re)001:13187: ltar 'dod pa'i sku dang gsung la sogs pa'i rnam
NK115(re)001:13188: par 'phrul pa sna tshogs bstan nas bsam pa tshim
NK115(re)001:13190: thams cad dbang du 'gyur ba ni sems can rnams
NK115(re)001:13191: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i go 'phang la 'god nus pas
NK115(re)001:13192: gzhan don du mi 'gyur ba skad cig kyang med
NK115(re)001:13193: pa'o // ci 'dod byed pa ni rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don du rgya mtsho 'khrugs pa'i sgra dang /
NK115(re)001:13195: du ma gcig tu byed pa sogs rdzu 'phrul la dbang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13196: de dag gang la mnga' ba'i gnas skabs riga 'dzina rnam pa bzhi ste sngar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:13197: de yang rig 'dzin zhes pa rig pa bde gshegs
NK115(re)001:13198: snying po'i don ma nor bar sngags kyi man ngag
NK115(re)001:13199: la brten nas 'dzin pa dang de mthar phyin pa
NK115(re)001:13200: la bya'o // yang rigs 'dzin zhes pa ltar na
NK115(re)001:13201: sku dang ye shes gang gi rigs la gnas pa
NK115(re)001:13203: de ltar slob lam mthar phyin nas mchoga gi dngosa
NK115(re)001:13204: gruba mthar thug pa ni kha sbyor yan lag bduna
NK115(re)001:13206: slob dpon ngag gi dbang phyug grags pa'i zhal nas /
NK115(re)001:13207: longs spyod rdzogs dang kha sbyor bde chen rang bzhin med //
NK115(re)001:13208: snying rjes yongs gang rgyun mi 'chad dang 'gog pa med //
NK115(re)001:13210: sku rnam pa thams cad pa shes bya'i gzugs brnyan yod dgur 'char ba ni kha sbyor /
NK115(re)001:13211: gsung rnam pa thams cad la sgra tshig gi sgrib pa dang bral ba ni longs spyod rdzogs pa /
NK115(re)001:13212: thugs rnam pa thams cad pa gzung 'dzin gyi rtog
NK115(re)001:13213: pa las grol zhing 'gyur ba med pa'i bde chen
NK115(re)001:13215: de yang rang bzhin med pa ste med dgag gi
NK115(re)001:13216: dpyad mtha' las grol ba'i so so rang rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:13217: mtshan nyid can te bzhi po des rang don phun
NK115(re)001:13219: snying rjes yongs su gang ba las yid bzhin gyi
NK115(re)001:13220: nor bu'am dpag bsam gyi shing ltar gzhan don 'bad
NK115(re)001:13221: med du 'byung ba dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje
NK115(re)001:13222: chen po dang / thugs rje chen po de nyid
NK115(re)001:13223: dus nam du yang rgyun chad med pas rtag pa
NK115(re)001:13224: chen po dang / dang / gdul bya'i mos pa
NK115(re)001:13225: dang dbang po la 'tshams par gzugs sku'i snang brnyan
NK115(re)001:13226: chen po dang / dang / dang / chos kyi
NK115(re)001:13227: sgo mtha' yas pa nam yang 'gog pa med pa
NK115(re)001:13228: 'char ba dang gsum gyis gzhan don phun sum tshogs
NK115(re)001:13229: pa shugs la grub pas sku lnga'i yon tan thams
NK115(re)001:13230: cad yongs su rdzogs te 'og min gyi zhing du
NK115(re)001:13231: 'gro zhing dona gnyis lhun gyisa grub pa la sangs
NK115(re)001:13233: de yang chos nyid gang du'ang mi 'gro /
NK115(re)001:13236: 'khor 'das thams cad du khyab par son pa /
NK115(re)001:13237: gdul bya'i ngor thams cad mkhyen pa /
NK115(re)001:13238: rnam pa dang don thams cad sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la gnas pa /
NK115(re)001:13239: sdig pa thams cad las rnam par grol ba /
NK115(re)001:13240: yon tan thams cad kyis nye bar brgyan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:13241: de gang las byung na shes bya'i bud shing skam
NK115(re)001:13242: po ma lus pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:13243: shes kyi mes bsregs nas mngon du mdzad pa la
NK115(re)001:13244: / byis pa rnams skrag pa spang ba'i phyir de
NK115(re)001:13245: bzhin gshegs pa'i tshig bla dwags su btags pa ste
NK115(re)001:13247: 'jam dpal skye ba med cing 'gag pa med pa
NK115(re)001:13248: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshig bla dwags so
NK115(re)001:13251: sangs rgyas rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK115(re)001:13252: rnam dag nam mkha' lta bu yin //
NK115(re)001:13254: yona tan rina po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i chara zhesa bya ba lasa /
NK115(re)001:13255: riga pa 'dzina pa'i sde snoda bstan pa'i tshomas te le'u bcu pa'i 'grel pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13257: // don gsum pa lam gyi nye lam rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ltar bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:13260: 'bras bu lhun grub chen po bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13261: dang po gzhi gtan la dbab pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:13264: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13265: bstan pa mtha' dag gi rtse mor gyur pa rang
NK115(re)001:13266: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ba de gang
NK115(re)001:13267: la brjod pa yin zhe na /
NK115(re)001:13268: de'i rang bzhin ngos bzung ba ni /
NK115(re)001:13269: 'di ltar thabs mkhas la thugs rje chen po dang
NK115(re)001:13270: ldan pa'i rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK115(re)001:13272: gdul bya las dang po ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13273: dbang po dman pa rnams la dgongs nas bden bzhi
NK115(re)001:13274: spang gnyen du bya bas 'khor ba las bzlog pa'i
NK115(re)001:13275: phyir spang bya las rnam par grol ba'i thabs su
NK115(re)001:13276: bka' 'khor lo dang po gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:13277: der ni brjod bya'i gtso bo bden bzhi mi rtag
NK115(re)001:13278: sogs bcu drug gi sgo nas gang zag gi bdag
NK115(re)001:13279: med pa tsam zhig bstan la /
NK115(re)001:13280: gdul bya yongs su sbyangs pa byas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13281: dbang po 'bring po la dgongs nas gnyen por 'dzin
NK115(re)001:13282: pa'i 'ching ba las grol ba'i thabs su 'khora lo
NK115(re)001:13283: bar para ni / chos thams cad rnama par thar pa'i sgo gsuma gyi rang bzhin du gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:13284: de la rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid
NK115(re)001:13285: ni dmigs pa med pas rang gi ngo bos rnam
NK115(re)001:13286: par dben pa'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK115(re)001:13287: 'di ltar gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyis bsdus
NK115(re)001:13288: pa'i chos thams cad ni rang gi ngo bos grub
NK115(re)001:13289: pa rdul tsam yang med pas rnam par rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:13290: spyod yul las 'das pa'i phyir na de'i mi mthun
NK115(re)001:13291: pa'i phyogs sam de la sgrib par byed pa ni
NK115(re)001:13292: rnam par rtog pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:13293: rnam par rtog pa'am sems dang sems las byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:13294: ngo bo zhig yin phan chad yul dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:13295: zhig yin na chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni
NK115(re)001:13296: bden pa'i yul du med par ma zad /
NK115(re)001:13297: tha snyad kyi yul tsam du yang ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13298: rnam par thar pa'i sgo mtshan ma med pa ni zhi ba'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK115(re)001:13299: stong pa'i rang rtsal rten 'byung gi snang ba 'di
NK115(re)001:13300: thams cad snang ba'i dus nyid nas yod med la
NK115(re)001:13302: bzang ngan la sogs pa'i mtshan ma dang /
NK115(re)001:13303: skyed byed kyi rgyu dang phan 'dogs pa dang gnod
NK115(re)001:13304: par byed pa'i rkyen gang yang mi 'jug pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:13305: na de'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni bdag gzhan dang
NK115(re)001:13306: dag ma dag la sogs pa'i mtshan ma'i snang ba
NK115(re)001:13307: 'di dag yin te rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK115(re)001:13308: shes kyi yul stong pa nyid dam chos kyi dbyings
NK115(re)001:13309: kyi rang bzhin la de ltar ma grub pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:13310: ro // rnam par thar pa'i sgo smon pa med
NK115(re)001:13311: pa ni sdug bsngal dang gti mug las 'das pa'i
NK115(re)001:13313: 'di ltar snod dang bcud du snang ba'i sdug bsngal gyi bden pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13314: de'i rgyu gti mug ste ma rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13315: des bskyed pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin can kun 'byung gi bden pa ste /
NK115(re)001:13316: mdor na sdug kun gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:13317: gdod ma nas yod ma myong ba'i phyir mya ngan
NK115(re)001:13318: las 'das pa zhes bya ba'ang de las gzhan na
NK115(re)001:13320: de ni cung zad min de'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:13321: sems can rang bzhin mya ngan 'das //
NK115(re)001:13323: de'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni 'khor 'das tha dad
NK115(re)001:13324: du bltas ste myang 'das la thob bya zhen pa
NK115(re)001:13325: de yin te 'khor 'das gnyis po yul can sems
NK115(re)001:13326: kyi chos nyid du dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13328: stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK115(re)001:13329: dmigs pa med pas rnam dben nyid //
NK115(re)001:13330: mtshan ma med pa zhi nyid de //
NK115(re)001:13331: gsum pa'i mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang //
NK115(re)001:13332: gti mug med rnam thar rnams kyi //
NK115(re)001:13333: mtshan nyid rnam par grol byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13335: 'di rnams gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum la'ang sbyar te /
NK115(re)001:13336: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid ni yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pas gzhi /
NK115(re)001:13337: mtshan ma med pa ni da ltar yang mi gnas pas lam //
NK115(re)001:13338: smon pa med pa ni ma 'ongs pa la ltos mi 'cha' bas 'bras bu ste /
NK115(re)001:13340: da lta na ni mi gnas shing //
NK115(re)001:13342: gang du de dag mi dmigs pa //
NK115(re)001:13343: de la mi dmigs pa zhes brjod //
NK115(re)001:13345: de ltar bka' bar pa'i dngos bstan stong nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:13346: dgongs pa 'grel pa'i dbu ma rigs pa'i tshogs la
NK115(re)001:13347: sogs pa nas thal 'gyur gyi rigs pa rnon pos
NK115(re)001:13348: grub matha'i khas len gyi dngos zhen thams cad sun
NK115(re)001:13349: phyung bar mdzad pa ni lta ba yid dpyod kyis
NK115(re)001:13350: gtan la phab nas rang bzhin med pa'i don ma
NK115(re)001:13351: nor ba la nges pa 'dren pa'i shes rab la
NK115(re)001:13352: de las mchog tu gyur pa med kyang gshis kyi
NK115(re)001:13353: bzhugs tshul ji lta ba ni bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK115(re)001:13354: dang man ngag gi thabs la brten nas rtogs par
NK115(re)001:13356: des na de dag gis gtan la dbab pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:13357: dper na zla ba mthong ma myong ba'i gang zag
NK115(re)001:13358: zhig yod na de la zla ba'i dbyibs ni gru
NK115(re)001:13359: bzhi ma yin zur gsum ma yin la sogs pa
NK115(re)001:13360: dang / kha dog ni nag po ma yin dmar
NK115(re)001:13361: po ma yin zhes pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:13362: mtshon te ston pa na bstan par bya ba'i ngo
NK115(re)001:13363: bo pha rol po des shes dgos rgyu ni zla
NK115(re)001:13364: ba rang gi dbyibs dang kha dog zlum po dang
NK115(re)001:13365: dkar po de yin pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:13366: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni yod pa ma
NK115(re)001:13367: yin med pa ma yin rtag pa ma yin chad
NK115(re)001:13368: pa ma yin zhes pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:13370: de ltar bstan pa na'ang gnas skabs gdul bya de'i
NK115(re)001:13371: gnyen po bdag med pa sogs spros pa'i mtha' la
NK115(re)001:13372: zhen pa gcod pa'i phyir de tsam las gtso bor
NK115(re)001:13373: mi ston kyang bstan par bya ba'i ngo bo gdul
NK115(re)001:13374: bya des lam de la brten nas mngon du bya
NK115(re)001:13375: dgos rgyu ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:13376: so so ranga riga pa'i ye shes nyid yin gyi
NK115(re)001:13377: de las gzhan ni med do //
NK115(re)001:13378: yang sbyangs pa mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13379: dbang po rnon po'i ngor shes bya'i gshis ji ltar
NK115(re)001:13380: gnas pa de ltar ni bka' tha mas ston te
NK115(re)001:13381: / de yang bar pas bstan bya'i ngo bo de
NK115(re)001:13382: nyid semas cana thams cad kyi khamas la bde bar
NK115(re)001:13383: gshegas pa'i snying po ru rang bzhina gyis bzhugas par
NK115(re)001:13384: gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo dang
NK115(re)001:13385: / / mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo la sogs par gsungs shing /
NK115(re)001:13386: ji ltar na chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK115(re)001:13387: par dag pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:13388: de ni ye nas gnas pa 'gyur ba med pa
NK115(re)001:13389: de'i snang cha las gzugs kyi sku mtshan dang dpe
NK115(re)001:13391: stong cha la chos kyi sku spros pa dang bral
NK115(re)001:13392: ba ye nas lhun grub tu gnas pa nyid yon
NK115(re)001:13393: tan lhun gyis grub pas nor bu dang /
NK115(re)001:13394: gzhan du mi 'gyur bas nam mkha' dang /
NK115(re)001:13395: sems can thams cad la brlan zhing khyab pas chu dag pa'i dpes bstan te /
NK115(re)001:13397: rin chen nam mkha' chu dag bzhin //
NK115(re)001:13398: rtag tu rang bzhin nyon mongs med //
NK115(re)001:13400: snying po rab tu bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:13401: thog ma med pa'i dus kyi dbyings //
NK115(re)001:13402: chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK115(re)001:13404: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa yin //
NK115(re)001:13406: chos dbyings bstod pa las kyang /
NK115(re)001:13407: sa yi dkyil na gnas pa'i chu //
NK115(re)001:13408: dri ma med par gnas pa ltar //
NK115(re)001:13409: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK115(re)001:13410: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK115(re)001:13412: des na bka' bar tha gnyis po de las kyang
NK115(re)001:13413: nges don mthar thug pa ni tha ma yin te
NK115(re)001:13414: / mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las de gnyis dpe'i bstan te /
NK115(re)001:13415: dper na bud med zhig la bu chung ngu zhig
NK115(re)001:13416: yod pa nad kyis btab par gyur na sman pas
NK115(re)001:13417: de gso ba'i phyir sman btang nas /
NK115(re)001:13419: bu 'di la sman ma zhu'i bar du nu zho ma blud cig ces basgo'o //
NK115(re)001:13420: ma des nu ma la mkhris pa byugs nas 'di
NK115(re)001:13421: la dug gis bskus pas nu mi rung zer ro
NK115(re)001:13422: // bu de nur 'dod kyang kha ba'i ro bro ba tshor ma thag tu nur mi btub bo //
NK115(re)001:13423: sman zhu nas nu ma dag par bkrus te nur
NK115(re)001:13424: bcug pa'i tshe kha ba'i ro la skrag nas ma
NK115(re)001:13425: btub pa na / rgyu mtshan ji lta ba bzhin
NK115(re)001:13426: bshad pas rim gyis nye ste 'thung du btub bo
NK115(re)001:13427: btub pa na / // de ltar bud med des
NK115(re)001:13428: nu ma la mkhris pa bskus pa bzhin du de
NK115(re)001:13429: bzhin gshegs pas stong pa nyid bsgom pa'i phyir chos
NK115(re)001:13430: thams cad bdag med ces gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:13431: nu ma bkrus te bsnun pa ltar de bzhin gshegs
NK115(re)001:13432: pa'i snying po sems can thams cad la yod par
NK115(re)001:13433: gsungs so zhes pa'i dpe bstan pa'i rjes la /
NK115(re)001:13434: dge slong khyod kyang bye brag phyed par gyis shig /
NK115(re)001:13435: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni med par bya ba ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:13436: ngas sngon pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdo sde brjod
NK115(re)001:13437: pa dag las stong pa nyid du bstan pa de
NK115(re)001:13438: yang rang bzhin med pa tsam la dgongs nas gsungs
NK115(re)001:13440: gzhan du na ci yang med pa'i stong pa nyid
NK115(re)001:13441: bsgom pa las ni sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye
NK115(re)001:13442: shes kyang 'byung bar mi 'gyur te 'bras bu ni
NK115(re)001:13443: rgyu'i rjes su byed pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:13445: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i mdo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:13446: 'khor lo dang po gnyis so sor /
NK115(re)001:13447: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK115(re)001:13448: de bla na mchis pa skabs mchis pa drang ba'i
NK115(re)001:13449: don rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur pa lags kyi
NK115(re)001:13450: zhes drang don du bstan nas /
NK115(re)001:13451: tha ma legs par rnam par phye ba dang ldan
NK115(re)001:13452: pa shin tu ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos
NK115(re)001:13453: kyi 'khor lo gsum pa bskor te /
NK115(re)001:13454: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK115(re)001:13455: 'di ni bla na ma mchis pa skabs ma mchis
NK115(re)001:13456: pa nges pa'i don lags te /
NK115(re)001:13457: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su ma gyur pa lags so //
NK115(re)001:13459: gzhan yang gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal po'i zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:13460: nor bu rin po che sbyong ba'i tshul lan tsh+wa'i chus sbangs nas skra'i re bas phyi ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13461: zas kyi khu bas sbas nas bal gyi lwa bas sbyong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13462: a ru ra'i khu bas spangs nas ras srab mo'i
NK115(re)001:13463: phyi bar byed pa ltar khams kyi dri ma sbyong
NK115(re)001:13464: byed 'khor lo gsum po snga ma snga ma las
NK115(re)001:13465: phyi ma phyi ma mthu che bar gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:13466: de ltar bar tha gnyis kyis bstan bya'i snying po
NK115(re)001:13467: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs zab pa zhi ba
NK115(re)001:13468: rang bzhin gyis spros pa dang bral zhing 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:13469: ba'i chos nyid de sems dang ye shes logs su
NK115(re)001:13470: phye nas ye shes rang gi ngo bo rjen par
NK115(re)001:13471: ston pa la rdzogas pa chena po zhes bya bar
NK115(re)001:13472: gragas pa yin pas na ston tshul tsam las mthar
NK115(re)001:13473: thug pa'i don du ni zung 'jug dbu ma chen
NK115(re)001:13474: po dang yang don gcig go //
NK115(re)001:13475: de la gzhi rdzogs pa chen po ni rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:13476: ngo bo la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rdzogs
NK115(re)001:13477: pas na rdzogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:13478: de yang 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ni rmi lam
NK115(re)001:13479: gyi snang ba ltar med snang yin kyang rig rtsal
NK115(re)001:13480: la bdag tu bzung ba las gzhan na med pa'i
NK115(re)001:13481: phyir dang / mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK115(re)001:13482: cad ni nyi ma dang 'od zer bzhin lhun gyis
NK115(re)001:13483: grub pa'i tshul du rdzogs so //
NK115(re)001:13484: de nyid srid zhi kun khyab kyi ye shes yin pa'i phyir chen po zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:13485: lam rdzogs pa chen po ni //
NK115(re)001:13486: sems dang sems byung dbyings su zhi ba'i spros bral
NK115(re)001:13487: rang byung gi ye shes bya bral blo 'das chen
NK115(re)001:13488: po'i rgyun rang bzhag rang gnas la bzo mi 'chos
NK115(re)001:13489: pas rtsal snang glo bur ba'i dri ma rang dengs
NK115(re)001:13491: de la lam dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad lhun gyis grub par rdzogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13492: de nyid theg pa dang lam thams cad kyi mthar thug yin pas chen po zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:13493: 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK115(re)001:13494: rig pa'i ye shes nyid sgrib byed kyi dri ma
NK115(re)001:13495: bag chags dang bcas pa dag pa'i gnas skabs te
NK115(re)001:13496: / de nyid sku dang ye shes thams cad kyi
NK115(re)001:13497: 'char gzhi yin pas rdzogs pa dang spangs rtogs phrin
NK115(re)001:13498: las te chen po gsum gyi rang bzhin yin pas
NK115(re)001:13499: / na chen po'o // de bas na gdul bya'i
NK115(re)001:13500: khams ganga du so so'i mos pa dang 'tshams par
NK115(re)001:13501: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa
NK115(re)001:13502: bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba'i chos kyi rnam
NK115(re)001:13503: grangs rgya che zhing grangs mang ba'i sgo nas bstan
NK115(re)001:13504: pa'i lam bazanga po srid pa'i rgyur mi 'gro zhing
NK115(re)001:13505: mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong khyer du dkri bar
NK115(re)001:13506: byed pas dama pa'i dona nyan thos kyi theg pa
NK115(re)001:13507: nas a nu'i bar matha'a daga pa kun blo yi
NK115(re)001:13508: dri ma byi dora byed pa kho na'i phyir gsungs
NK115(re)001:13509: / na chen po'o // pa ste / de la
NK115(re)001:13510: blo zhes pa dri ma sbyang ba'i gzhi nor bu
NK115(re)001:13511: rin po che lta bu rig pa'i ye shes la
NK115(re)001:13512: byas na de yi sgrib byed du gyur pa'i dri
NK115(re)001:13513: ma dag par byed pa'i thabs su bstan pa yin
NK115(re)001:13514: / na chen po'o // pa ste / zhes bya
NK115(re)001:13515: la / yang na blo zhes pa sbyang bya'i dri
NK115(re)001:13516: ma nor bu la sgrib pa'i 'dam rdzab lta bu
NK115(re)001:13517: rig pa la sgrib pa'i khams gsum gyi sems dang
NK115(re)001:13518: sems las byung ba'i cha thams cad la byas nas
NK115(re)001:13519: de nyid dag pa'i ched du bstan pa yin zhes
NK115(re)001:13521: des na theg pa de dag gi lam gyi nyams len sdoma pa gsuma dang /
NK115(re)001:13522: phar phyin theg par bshad pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa druga dang /
NK115(re)001:13523: gsang sngags thun mong ba'i lam bskyed pa dang rdzogas
NK115(re)001:13524: pa'i rim pa la sogas pa ji snyed pa de
NK115(re)001:13525: kuna kyang rang bzhin rdzogas pa chena po'i lam stegas
NK115(re)001:13526: yina te / rang bzhin med pa'i shes rab yang
NK115(re)001:13527: dag pa ni rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung gis mngon
NK115(re)001:13528: sum du gtan la 'bebs dgos pas so //
NK115(re)001:13529: 'o na shes rab ni phyin drug gi khongs su
NK115(re)001:13530: 'du bas pha rol tu phyin pa drug ka lam
NK115(re)001:13531: stegs su ji ltar 'gyur snyam na /
NK115(re)001:13533: rtog dpyod kyi shes rab me 'bar ba lta bus
NK115(re)001:13534: ni gnyis med rang byung gi dgongs pa dran bsam
NK115(re)001:13535: rang rgyud pa las 'das pa'i ye shes rtogs par
NK115(re)001:13536: mi nus zhes mtshams sbyar te sdom pa gsum dang
NK115(re)001:13537: sogs gsungs pas / so skye'i gnas skabs kyi phyin
NK115(re)001:13538: drug sogs la bshad kyi sa thob pa yan chad
NK115(re)001:13539: kyi phar phyin mtshan nyid pa la bshad pa ma
NK115(re)001:13540: sogs gsungs pas / yin no // de bas na
NK115(re)001:13541: 'phags pa'i ye shes thad drang du ston pa'i dus
NK115(re)001:13542: na ni shes rab nyid kyang dmigs bsam las 'das
NK115(re)001:13543: pa'i gshis thog tu phebs dgos te /
NK115(re)001:13545: gang tshe 'dus byas 'dus ma byas dang dkar nag chos //
NK115(re)001:13546: shes rab rnam par bshigs nas rdul tsam mi gnas tshe //
NK115(re)001:13547: 'jig rten dag na shes rab pha rol phyin grangs 'gro //
NK115(re)001:13548: nam mkha' gang la'ang cung zad mi gnas de dang 'dra //
NK115(re)001:13550: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:13552: kun tu bzang po'i grol tshul bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:13553: ma dag sems can gyi 'khrul tshul bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13554: dang po 'khor 'das kyi spyi gzhi bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:13557: dang po gzhi bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:13558: gzhi'i bzhugs tshul spyir bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:13559: grub matha'i 'dod gzhung bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:13560: skyon med rang gzhung gi gzhi rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13561: dang po gzhi'i bzhugs tshul spyir bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13562: de la phar phyin theg pa'i skabs su 'khor 'das
NK115(re)001:13563: gnyis ka rang bzhin med pa tsam du dbyer med
NK115(re)001:13564: kyang tha snyad du so sor snang ba yin par
NK115(re)001:13565: bshad la rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi gtan
NK115(re)001:13566: la dbab pa'i skabs 'dira ni phung sogs su snang
NK115(re)001:13568: sku dang ye shes su snang ba mya ngana las
NK115(re)001:13569: 'adsa pa'i chosa thams cad tha snyad du'ang rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:13570: ngang du tshul gcig par gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:13571: 'di ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ji lta
NK115(re)001:13572: ba bzhin du rtogs te sangs rgyas kyi chos sku
NK115(re)001:13573: dang ye shes rnams gsar du byung ba ma yin
NK115(re)001:13574: te rig pa rang byung gi ye shes sku gsum
NK115(re)001:13575: gyi bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa'i dbyingsa lasa gzhan
NK115(re)001:13577: gnas lugs ma rtogs par 'khrul te 'khor ba'i phyi
NK115(re)001:13578: nang gi dngos po sna tshogs su snang ba 'di
NK115(re)001:13579: ma byung ste 'khrul dus nyid nas rig pa'i rang
NK115(re)001:13580: bzhin ye nas rnam par dag pa las gazhana du
NK115(re)001:13581: gyur pa meda pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i chos rnams ni
NK115(re)001:13582: ri bong rwa bzhin gang byung ba'i chos kyi ngo
NK115(re)001:13584: des na 'khora 'adsa gnyis ka ma grub bzhin du
NK115(re)001:13585: 'khor 'das su snang ba'i gzhi rig pa yi chosa
NK115(re)001:13586: nyid kyang ngo bo stong pa chos kyi sku /
NK115(re)001:13587: ranga bzhina ngang gis 'od gsal ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK115(re)001:13588: thugas rje rig pa'i snying po can sprul pa'i sku
NK115(re)001:13589: ste sku gsuma du ye nas rdzogas pa yin te
NK115(re)001:13591: dbyings de'i ngo bo ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:13592: rang bzhin ni ngang gis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK115(re)001:13593: thugs rje ni rig pa'i snying por gnas te yon
NK115(re)001:13594: tan thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gyur pa'o zhes so
NK115(re)001:13595: // 'o na 'khor 'das gnyis su ji ltar snang ba yin snyam na /
NK115(re)001:13596: gzhi de nyid kyi nganga las gzhi snang shar ba'i
NK115(re)001:13597: dus na tshogs brgyad kyi nyer len sprin dang 'dra
NK115(re)001:13598: ba rnams rang sar dengs pas sku dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:13599: kyi snang ba rnam par daga pa sangas rgyas dang
NK115(re)001:13600: / gzhi snang de nyid lhan cig skyes pa'i ma
NK115(re)001:13601: rig pas bsgribs te kun tu brtags pa can gyi
NK115(re)001:13602: ma rig pas rang snang la yul du bzung bas
NK115(re)001:13603: gzung 'dzin gnyis su mched de ma daga 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:13604: rang bzhin rmi lam lta bur snang bas semas can
NK115(re)001:13605: te 'khora 'adsa gnyis kyi chara snang na'ang gnyida kyi
NK115(re)001:13606: nganga na rmi lam gyi snang ba bzang ngan ci
NK115(re)001:13607: shar yang gnyid de las gzhan du mi g.yo ba
NK115(re)001:13608: bzhina gzhan las gsar byung med pas ganga nasa kyang
NK115(re)001:13609: / ma 'onga la / gzhi las g.yos pa med pas gazhana du 'pho ba'ang meda do //
NK115(re)001:13610: gnyis pa grub matha'i 'dod gzhung bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13611: de la spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyi gzhi'i
NK115(re)001:13612: rang bzhin ka dag dang lhun grub zung 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:13613: tha snyad nye bar btags shing rang bzhin ci yang
NK115(re)001:13614: ma yin pa las rol pa sna tshogs su 'char
NK115(re)001:13615: du rung yang dngos po yod med kyi mthas ma
NK115(re)001:13616: reg pa gong du ji skad bstan pa ltar gnas
NK115(re)001:13617: pa la / re zhiga rdzogs pa chen po'i lam
NK115(re)001:13618: la zhugs pa rnams kyis gzhi de yi bzhugas tshula
NK115(re)001:13619: te yin lugs la dpyad pa btang ste rang rang
NK115(re)001:13620: gis ji ltar 'dod pa'i phyogs gzung nas gruba pa'i
NK115(re)001:13621: matha'a smra ba rnams kyi lugs ni rnam pa bdun
NK115(re)001:13622: pa la / te / de yang rang bzhin ji
NK115(re)001:13623: lta ba bzhin skyon med du ma rtogs par phyogs
NK115(re)001:13624: rer zhen pa'i gol sa 'byung ba'i rnam grangs mang
NK115(re)001:13625: yang bdun po 'di las mi 'da' bas na klong
NK115(re)001:13626: drug pa la sogs pa'i rgyud sde rnams nas tshul
NK115(re)001:13627: 'di dag so so'i skyon barjona dang bcas pa byung
NK115(re)001:13628: pa la / te / ba yin no // de
NK115(re)001:13629: la dang po gzhi ka daga tu 'dod pa ni
NK115(re)001:13630: pa la / te / ba yin no // /
NK115(re)001:13631: gzhi'i rang bzhin gdod nas spros pa thams cad dang
NK115(re)001:13632: bral ba'i bdag nyid can du smra ba las ye
NK115(re)001:13633: gdangs 'gag pa med pa'i lhun grub kyi snang cha
NK115(re)001:13634: pa la / te / ba yin no // /
NK115(re)001:13635: ma bzung ba'o // de ltar na ngo bo stong
NK115(re)001:13636: pa'i cha nas 'thad kyang spros bral zhes pa ci
NK115(re)001:13637: yang med pa'i ka dag stong rkyang de la ma
NK115(re)001:13638: rig pa mi ldan pas 'khor ba 'byung ba'i 'khrul
NK115(re)001:13639: pa skye mi srid pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i gzhi yang
NK115(re)001:13640: pa la / te / ba yin no // /
NK115(re)001:13641: ma bzung ba'o // ma grub bo // 'o na
NK115(re)001:13642: gzhi la ma rig pa ldan nam zhe na /
NK115(re)001:13643: gzhi rang gi ngo bo la ma rig pa med
NK115(re)001:13644: kyang gdangs 'char rung du yod pa shar ba ngo
NK115(re)001:13645: ma shes pas 'khrul pa yin pa'i phyir ma rig
NK115(re)001:13646: pa'i brgyud rgyur 'gyur ba la de lta bu'i gzhi
NK115(re)001:13647: de ni brgyud rgyur yang mi rung ste nam mkha'i
NK115(re)001:13649: ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma yin pas skye rung ngo zhe na /
NK115(re)001:13650: rgyu bkag na 'bras bu khegs pas glo bur gyi dri ma 'byung mi rung ste /
NK115(re)001:13651: gal te 'byung na 'khor ba rgyu med du 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:13652: de bzhin du myang 'das kyang mi srid de chad par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:13653: gnyis pa gzhi lhun gruba tu 'dod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13654: 'khor 'das gnyis ka gzhi las gzhan na yod pa
NK115(re)001:13655: ma yin pas de gnyis ka gzhi la lhun gyis
NK115(re)001:13657: de yang gdangs 'gag med las rtsal snang sna tshogs
NK115(re)001:13658: su 'char ba'i cha nas 'thad kyang mtha' gcig tu
NK115(re)001:13659: de ltar 'dod na yod pa'i dngos po rtag par
NK115(re)001:13660: 'gyur bas 'khor 'das gnyis su dgyes pa'i rgyur mi
NK115(re)001:13661: rung ste / 'khor ba lhun gyis grub na sol
NK115(re)001:13662: ba byi dor byas pas dkar por 'gyur mi rung
NK115(re)001:13663: ba bzhin grol bar mi rigs la /
NK115(re)001:13664: myang 'das lhun gyis grub na rang ngo shes pa
NK115(re)001:13665: dang tshogs rdzogs pa la sogs pa'i rkyen la ltos
NK115(re)001:13666: mi rigs shing / gnyis ka lhun gyis grub na ni /
NK115(re)001:13667: sems rgyud gcig la 'khor ba yang yin la myang
NK115(re)001:13668: 'das kyang yin pa'i gzhi mthun srid dgos pa la
NK115(re)001:13669: de mi srid pa'i phyir mi 'thad do //
NK115(re)001:13670: sems kyi rang bzhin myang 'das la 'khrul pa glo
NK115(re)001:13671: bur ba yin zhes pa ni 'di dang mi 'dra
NK115(re)001:13672: bar gong 'og thams cad du bshad pas shes so
NK115(re)001:13673: // gsum pa gzhi ma ngesa par 'dod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13674: gzhi sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'khor 'das gang du
NK115(re)001:13675: yang 'gyur rung bas mtha' gcig tu ma nges par
NK115(re)001:13676: 'dod pa'o // de yang gzhi spros bral la 'khor
NK115(re)001:13677: 'das ma grub pa'i cha nas ma nges pa 'thad
NK115(re)001:13678: kyang sems kyi gshis lugs de gzhi yin pas de
NK115(re)001:13679: nyid don la ma nges na /
NK115(re)001:13680: dri ma dag nas kyang ma dag par ldog pa'am
NK115(re)001:13681: ma dag kyang dag pa'i rang bzhin nyid du thal
NK115(re)001:13682: bar 'gyur te sa zin med pas gang du'ang 'gyur
NK115(re)001:13683: ba'i phyir / 'dod na sems can kyang 'bad med du grol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13684: sangs rgyas kyang 'khor bar 'gyur bas 'khor 'das 'chol bar 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:13685: bzhi pa gzhi ngesa pa dona gyi dngos gzhir 'dod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13686: gzhi'i rang bzhin 'dus ma byas 'pho 'gyur med pa zhig tu 'dod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:13687: 'di yang byung tshor gyi rtog pa 'di ma yin
NK115(re)001:13688: pa'i sems kyi rang bzhin zhes gang du'ang mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:13689: ba'i yod yod po zhig tu zhen pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13690: de yang glo bur gyi dri ma med snang yin
NK115(re)001:13691: pa'i cha nas gzhi nges don yin pa 'thad kyang
NK115(re)001:13692: / rnam pa thams cad du de ltar nges don du 'dod na 'khor ba snang mi srid la /
NK115(re)001:13693: myang 'das kyang rtogs nas nges par 'dod na rtogs
NK115(re)001:13694: pa'i sngon du rtogs gzhi myang 'das de yod dgos
NK115(re)001:13695: pas mu stegs rtag lta ba dang mtshungs pas rgyu
NK115(re)001:13696: rkyen las grol bar 'dod pa dang 'gal la /
NK115(re)001:13697: ma rtogs kyang gzhi yin par gang gis shes /
NK115(re)001:13698: 'khor ba'i ngo bo myang 'das yin pa shes so
NK115(re)001:13699: zer na ngo bo myang 'das yin na gdod grol
NK115(re)001:13700: mi dgos te chu'i rang bzhin la gsher ba gzod
NK115(re)001:13702: lnga pa gzhi cira yanga bsgyur du btub par 'dod pa dang ni /
NK115(re)001:13703: gzhi'i rang bzhin rkyen gyis 'khor 'das gang du yang bsgyur rung bar 'dod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:13704: 'di sems kyi rang bzhin la rkyen 'jug tu yod par zhen pa'o //
NK115(re)001:13705: de yang spyir stong nyid yin pas rten 'byung gi snang ba 'char rung zhes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13706: gzhi las gzhi snang 'char zhes pa gnad gcig pas
NK115(re)001:13707: gzhi snang 'char ba na ngo shes ma shes las
NK115(re)001:13708: grol 'khrul du 'gyur ba la bsgyur ba'i tha snyad
NK115(re)001:13709: tsam byed na 'thad du rung gi /
NK115(re)001:13710: gazhi'am sems kyi ngo bo bsgyur du yod par 'dod
NK115(re)001:13711: na ni bsgyur rgyu'i dngos po zhig yod dgos pas
NK115(re)001:13712: de ltar na rtag mi rtag gang rung las mi
NK115(re)001:13713: 'da' bas na / rtag pa yin na bsgyur du
NK115(re)001:13714: mi rung ste nam mkha' la bcad btub mi pher
NK115(re)001:13715: 'da' bas na / ba bzhin no // mi rtag
NK115(re)001:13716: pa bsgyur mi dgos te ma bsgyur yang 'gyur ba
NK115(re)001:13717: chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13718: gzhan yang rig pa bem por dang /
NK115(re)001:13719: 'bras bu myang 'das thob zin nas kyang 'khor bar
NK115(re)001:13720: bsgyur du rung ba srid pa'i phyir mi 'thad do
NK115(re)001:13721: // drug pa gzhi cir yanga khasa blanga du btuba pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13722: gzhi sems kyi rang bzhin 'di 'khor 'das dang yod
NK115(re)001:13723: med la sogs gang yang yin rung bas cir yang
NK115(re)001:13724: khas blang du rung bar 'dod pa ste spros bral
NK115(re)001:13725: gshis thog tu ngo ma 'phrod pas sa zin med
NK115(re)001:13726: pa'i 'dod pa'o // de yang gzhi sems kyi chos
NK115(re)001:13727: nyid kyi rtsal 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i cha
NK115(re)001:13728: nas 'khor ba'i gzhi yang yin la myang 'das kyi
NK115(re)001:13730: ka dag gi ldog pa nas med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13731: lhun grub kyi ldog pa nas yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13732: zug 'jug gi ldog pa nas gnyis ka yin zhes tha snyad tsam du khas blang rung gis /
NK115(re)001:13733: rnam pa kun tu gang rung rung khas blang du btub na /
NK115(re)001:13734: khyad chos drug gis grol ba'i gzhi de 'khrul gazhi'o zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:13735: ma rig pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i 'khrul gzhi
NK115(re)001:13736: de grol ba'i gzhir khas blang du rung dgos shing
NK115(re)001:13737: / de ltar na ri bong gi rwa dang mo
NK115(re)001:13738: gsham gyi bus 'khor 'das byed par khas blang yang
NK115(re)001:13739: rung ste rgyu mtshan mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13740: bdun pa gzhi sna tshogas su 'doda pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13741: gzhi las 'khor 'das kyi chos sna tshogs pa 'char
NK115(re)001:13742: ba'i chos de rnams gzhi'i chos nyid do zhes 'dod
NK115(re)001:13743: de don la 'khor 'das dang phyi nang gi chos
NK115(re)001:13744: sna tshogs pa ci snang yang sems las gzhan du
NK115(re)001:13745: grub pa med pas thams cad sems nyid do zhes
NK115(re)001:13746: zhen pa'o // lhun grub dang 'di gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK115(re)001:13747: gzhi la 'khor 'das grub ces pa dang /
NK115(re)001:13748: gzhi nyid 'khor 'das gnyis ka yin zhes pa'i khyad par ro //
NK115(re)001:13749: de yang thugs rje'i rang rtsal 'gag pa med pa
NK115(re)001:13750: las rol pa sna tshogs su snang ba sems nyid
NK115(re)001:13751: las gzhan ma yin pa'i cha nas 'thad kyang rnam
NK115(re)001:13752: pa kun tu gzhi de ltar 'dod na sems nyid
NK115(re)001:13753: gcig pu 'di dag ma dag gnyis ka yin par
NK115(re)001:13754: thal ba dang / phyi snang ba la 'dod na gzhi bem por thal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13755: nang shes pa la 'dod na gzhi snyam byed du thal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13756: de gnyis tshogs pa la 'dod na gzhi gzung 'dzin can du thal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13757: dbyings gcig gi rang bzhin yin par mi rung bas mi 'thad do //
NK115(re)001:13758: de ltar 'dod cing grub pa'i mtha' bzung ba'i gzhi
NK115(re)001:13759: bduna po de dag thams cad kyis kyang gtan la
NK115(re)001:13760: dbab bya'i ngo bo ni ka daga dang lhun grub
NK115(re)001:13761: zung du 'jug pa'i gzhi'i rang bzhin gciga pu'i phyogsa
NK115(re)001:13762: re re la so sora 'di kho na gzhi'i gnas
NK115(re)001:13763: lugs so snyam du blos btagsa pa'i ranga rang gi
NK115(re)001:13764: gzhunga 'dzina la skyon med pa'i gzhi smra ba las
NK115(re)001:13765: gazhana du gyur pa de rnams kyis ni gzhi'i phyogs
NK115(re)001:13766: re tsam la ma rmongs pas shes na'ang rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:13767: ji lta ba bzhin rdzogs par ma shes pas skyon
NK115(re)001:13768: dang bcas pa yin pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13769: da lta rang re las dang po pa rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:13770: sems kyi gnas lugs 'tsho ba la zhugs pa na
NK115(re)001:13771: yod med sogs phyogs bdun po gang du zhen kyang
NK115(re)001:13772: 'ching byed yin pas mtha' gang la yang ma zhen
NK115(re)001:13773: par bya ba'i don du go dgos pa yin nam
NK115(re)001:13774: snyam mo // de ltar phyogs re tsam las ma
NK115(re)001:13775: rtogs pa de dper na khonga nas skye ba'i dus
NK115(re)001:13776: nas kyang mig med pa'i dmus longa bduna gyisa glanga
NK115(re)001:13777: po che'i skye mcheda de gzugs dbyibs la ga nom
NK115(re)001:13778: byas nas brtags na phyogs re shes kyang yongs rdzogs
NK115(re)001:13779: mi shes pa dang 'dra ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:13781: rgyal pos long ba du ma bsags te glang po che bstan nas /
NK115(re)001:13782: glang po che'i mtshan nyid so sor smros shig ces bsgo ba las /
NK115(re)001:13783: glang po che'i sna la reg pa rnams ni lcags kyu dang 'dra'o zhes zer ro //
NK115(re)001:13784: mig la reg pa rnams ni phor pa dang 'dra'o zhes zer ro //
NK115(re)001:13785: rna ba la reg pa rnams ni zhib ma dang 'dra'o zhes zer ro //
NK115(re)001:13786: rgyab la reg pa rnams ni khyogs dang 'dra'o zhes zer ro //
NK115(re)001:13787: mjug ma la reg pa rnams ni thig gu dang 'dra'o zhes zer ro //
NK115(re)001:13788: long ba rnams kyis glang po che las gzhan smras
NK115(re)001:13789: pa ma yin yang thams cad du rtogs pa ni
NK115(re)001:13790: ma yin no // de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi
NK115(re)001:13791: rang bzhin yang stong pa nyid dang sgyu ma lta
NK115(re)001:13792: bu dang 'od gsal ba la sogs pa tha dad
NK115(re)001:13793: par smras kyang thams cad du rtogs pa ni ma
NK115(re)001:13794: yin no zhes pa lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:13795: yang don dam pa'i bden pa gzhi'i gnas lugs de
NK115(re)001:13796: nyid sgra rtog gi blos ji ltar gzhal kyang ji
NK115(re)001:13797: bzhin pa shes par mi 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:13798: dper na dmus long la nganga pa'i kha doga brjod pa ji lta ba bzhina no //
NK115(re)001:13799: de ltar yang de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:13800: gang so so'i skye bo dang /
NK115(re)001:13803: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang ji lta ba
NK115(re)001:13804: bzhin sangs rgyas kyi snying po mthong ba ma yin
NK115(re)001:13805: te dper na dmus long zhig gis gzhan zhig la
NK115(re)001:13806: mar gyi kha dog dris pa las kha ba 'dra'o
NK115(re)001:13808: des kha ba la lag pa reg pas mar gyi kha dog grang mor 'dzin to //
NK115(re)001:13809: dris pa kha ba'i kha dog ci 'dra /
NK115(re)001:13810: smras pa ngang pa'i gshog pa dang 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:13811: ngang pa'i gshog sgra thos pas kha dog 'ur 'ur por 'dzin to //
NK115(re)001:13812: dris pa gshog pa'i kha dog ci 'dra /
NK115(re)001:13814: dung la reg pas 'jam por 'dug pa na /
NK115(re)001:13816: ji ltar smras kyang dmus long gis kha dog ji
NK115(re)001:13817: lta ba bzhin mi shes pa de ltar sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:13818: kyi rang bzhin yang mthong ba rab tu dka' 'o
NK115(re)001:13819: zhes so // gsum pa skyon med rang gzhung gi gzhi rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13820: 'gal ba 'du ba'i skyon med pa'i gzhi'i gnas lugs
NK115(re)001:13821: gtan la dbab pa'i skabs 'dira ni rig pa'i ngo
NK115(re)001:13822: bo ka nasa daga pa la rang bzhin yona tan
NK115(re)001:13823: gyi cha ye nas lhuna gyis gruba kyang snang stong
NK115(re)001:13824: gi ldog pa tha dad pas gciga ma yin pa
NK115(re)001:13825: dang ngo bo gcig las med pas rdzas tha dada
NK115(re)001:13826: mina te dper na chu dang rlan bzhin te 'di
NK115(re)001:13827: ltar stong pa'i ngos nas dbyibs dang kha dog sogs
NK115(re)001:13828: ngo bo 'di lta bu'i zhes ngos bzung rgyu'i dngosa
NK115(re)001:13829: po'i matshana ma'i spros pa thams cad dang brala basa
NK115(re)001:13830: ka daga ces brjod pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:13831: de yang nam mkha' bzhin du cang med pa zhig
NK115(re)001:13832: ma yin par snang ba'i ngos nas gting gasla gyi
NK115(re)001:13833: cha rang gdangs 'agga pa meda pa las thugs rje'i
NK115(re)001:13834: rtsal ci yang 'char rung du yod pas lhuna gyis
NK115(re)001:13835: gruba bo zhes brjod pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:13837: ngo bo ka dag brjod gzhi bral //
NK115(re)001:13838: rang bzhin lhun grub cir snang rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:13841: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK115(re)001:13842: mtshan med ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK115(re)001:13843: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK115(re)001:13844: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK115(re)001:13845: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK115(re)001:13846: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK115(re)001:13847: zhes pa ltar rtag chad kyang zhar la spangs pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:13848: 'o na khyed kyis ka dag dang lhun grub so
NK115(re)001:13849: so ba'i gnas skabs de skyon can du bsgrub na
NK115(re)001:13850: 'dir yang gnyis ka yin par bshad pas skyon de
NK115(re)001:13852: 'dir ni gzhi sems kyi chos nyid gciga la yod med dam /
NK115(re)001:13853: snang stong gi rdzasa tha dad gnyis su yod pa
NK115(re)001:13854: ma yin par ngo bo gcig la ldog pas phye
NK115(re)001:13855: ba tsam yin pa'i phyir de 'dra ba'i 'agla ba
NK115(re)001:13857: 'di ltar dper na gnyid du phyogsa pa nas rags
NK115(re)001:13858: phra'i rtog pa thams cad rim gyis 'gags te gnyid
NK115(re)001:13859: 'thug tu gyur pa'i gnas skabs rang bzhin brgyad cu'i
NK115(re)001:13860: rtog pa 'gags pa'i shes ngo la rmi lam med
NK115(re)001:13861: pa dang / mched pa'i mdangs rlung gi chas khur
NK115(re)001:13862: ba'i shes ngo la rmi lam du snang ba'i gnyid
NK115(re)001:13863: dusa kyi shesa pa gnyis gnyid gcig gi ngo bo
NK115(re)001:13865: ngo bo ka daga gi cha la 'khrul pa gzhi
NK115(re)001:13866: ma grub pa yina pasa 'khor bar 'khora ma myonga
NK115(re)001:13867: mi myong myong bar mi 'gyur na'ang rang bzhin lhun
NK115(re)001:13868: gyis gruba pa'i rtsal lam gdangs 'gag pa med pa
NK115(re)001:13869: lasa rola pa sna tshogs pa cir yanga snang du
NK115(re)001:13870: rung ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13871: 'o na 'khrul gzhi zhes bya ba de bde gshegs snying po la 'dod dam /
NK115(re)001:13872: ma rig pa rgyu dang bcas pa la 'dod /
NK115(re)001:13873: dang po ltar na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa 'khrul pa dang bcas par 'gyur la /
NK115(re)001:13874: gnyis pa ltar na 'khrul ba'i ngo bo mi rnyed par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK115(re)001:13875: bde gshegs snying po la 'khrul pa ma grub kyang
NK115(re)001:13876: lhun grub kyi rtsal la kun gzhi tshogs brgyad dang
NK115(re)001:13877: bcas pas bsgribs te rang ngo ma shes na 'khrul
NK115(re)001:13878: zhing shes na grol ba ni 'thad pa dang bcas
NK115(re)001:13879: pas tshig gis gnod pa mi 'jug ste /
NK115(re)001:13881: brjod pa'i sgra tshig dang bral bas //
NK115(re)001:13882: ci yi ngo bo grub med phyir //
NK115(re)001:13883: tshig gis 'di la gnod pa bral //
NK115(re)001:13884: sems can bdag 'dzin blo yul la //
NK115(re)001:13885: sna tshogs dran bsam ma 'gags pas //
NK115(re)001:13886: tshig gnod ngo bo khyad par med //
NK115(re)001:13887: don dam kun rdzob tha snyad phyir //
NK115(re)001:13889: de dag gi don man ngag gis phye nas bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:13890: dpe ji ltar na nor bu beed+aur+ya yi rang 'od
NK115(re)001:13891: dang dwangs shel gtsang ma 'ja' ldan rnams kyi ranga
NK115(re)001:13892: 'oda ni snod du bcug pa la sogs pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:13893: gting gasla gyi tshul du yod kyang nyi ma la
NK115(re)001:13894: sogs pa'i rkyena gyisa ma bskyed par ni rang 'od
NK115(re)001:13895: phyir mi snang ba mngon sum du shes su rung
NK115(re)001:13896: ste 'od dang 'ja' tshon de la med pa ni
NK115(re)001:13897: ma yin te rdo ba la sogs pa phal pa
NK115(re)001:13898: dang mi 'dra bar nam rkyen dang 'phrad pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:13899: 'char bar 'gyur bas 'jig rten pa rnams kyis kyang
NK115(re)001:13900: 'di la 'od dang 'ja' tshon yod zer gyi med
NK115(re)001:13902: 'on kyang gting na gsal zhes pa de dag gi
NK115(re)001:13903: nang na dngos su kha dog gi rnam par ni
NK115(re)001:13905: de bzhina du 'chi srid la sogs pa gzhi'i 'od
NK115(re)001:13906: gsal la gnas pa'i tshe na ka daga gi rig
NK115(re)001:13907: pa ston gnam g.ya' dag pa lta bu rkyen gang
NK115(re)001:13908: yang med pa'i gnas skabs na dbyibs dang kha dog
NK115(re)001:13910: de bzhin du sgra dang dri la sogs pa yul
NK115(re)001:13911: dang de dag 'dzin byed kyi tshogs drug la sogs
NK115(re)001:13912: pa ma dag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:13913: sku dang 'od zer la sogs pa dag pa'i snang
NK115(re)001:13914: ba ste mdor na dngosa po matshana mar snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:13915: cha thams cad spangas pa ste de dus med kyang
NK115(re)001:13916: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i rang gadngas nang gsal
NK115(re)001:13917: gyi tshul du yod pa lhun gruba kyi snang ba
NK115(re)001:13918: phyi shar du mched pa'i rkyen dang ma 'phrad pas
NK115(re)001:13919: rgya ma rala pa ste phyir ma shar ba de
NK115(re)001:13920: la gzhon nu buma pa'i sku zhes pa'i tha snyad
NK115(re)001:13921: nye bar btags pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:13922: 'di ltar rig pa'i ngo bo ni 'dus ma byas
NK115(re)001:13923: yin pas 'dus byas kyi dngos po ltar rgud pa
NK115(re)001:13924: dang 'jig pa'i mtshan nyid can ma yin pas gzhon
NK115(re)001:13925: nu zhes dang / dbyings kyi ngang na sku gsum
NK115(re)001:13926: gyi 'char gzhi ma 'gags pas bum pa'i sku zhes
NK115(re)001:13927: nu zhes dang / bya la / de yang ngo
NK115(re)001:13928: bo bsam brjod dang bral bas skye med du stong
