NK115(re)001:13929: la rang gadngas lhun grub kyi cha las sku gsum
NK115(re)001:13930: gyi snang ba ma 'aggas par 'char rung du yod
NK115(re)001:13931: nu zhes dang / bya la / pasa / de
NK115(re)001:13932: las gzhi snang shar ba'i gnas skabs na ngo shes
NK115(re)001:13933: pa dang ma shes pa'i dbang gis mya ngan las
NK115(re)001:13934: 'das pa dang 'khor ba'i chos su snang bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:13935: ba'i phyir 'khor 'das kuna gyi 'achara gzhira gzhi'i rig
NK115(re)001:13936: pa de bzhugas pa yin kyang ka dag lhun grub
NK115(re)001:13937: ngo bo gcig pa'i gzhi'am rig pa rang mal lasa
NK115(re)001:13938: g.yosa pa meda pa'i gnas lugs de la ni phung
NK115(re)001:13939: po lnga'i dri mas gdod nas gos ma myong bas
NK115(re)001:13940: nu zhes dang / bya la / pasa / byang
NK115(re)001:13941: la / sku gsum yon tan gyi ngo bo rang
NK115(re)001:13942: chas su yod pas chuba cing 'char tshul ci yang
NK115(re)001:13943: ma 'gags pas semas zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:13944: de lta bu'i phra ba'i ye shes nang gsal gyi
NK115(re)001:13945: tshul du gnas pa de'i tshe na kha dog la
NK115(re)001:13946: sogs pa'i matshana ma dag ma dag gi risa su
NK115(re)001:13947: chada pa cana du phyir mi gasla ba yin no
NK115(re)001:13948: // des na bee d+aur+ya dang dwangs shel gyi dpe'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin /
NK115(re)001:13949: gzhon nu bum pa sku'i gnas skabs na sku gsum
NK115(re)001:13950: gyi yon tan thams cad med pa ni ma yin
NK115(re)001:13951: te de las gzhi snang 'char rung du yod cing
NK115(re)001:13952: shar ba'i gnas skabs na 'ang dag pa dang ma
NK115(re)001:13953: dag pa'i snang ba sna tshogs pa ma 'dres par
NK115(re)001:13954: mngon sum du grub pa'i phyir ri rwa lta bu
NK115(re)001:13955: ci yang 'byung du med kyang snang du mi rung
NK115(re)001:13957: yod pa'ang ma yin te mtshan mar grub pa ci yang med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:13958: rgyu mtshan de tsam la dgongs nas bum pa'i sku zhes pa'i tha snyad kyang btags pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:13959: dper na bum pa'i nang du zhal phyag sogs yongs
NK115(re)001:13960: su rdzogs pa'i sku gzugs yod na de la sku'i
NK115(re)001:13961: cha shas thams cad yongs su rdzogs kyang phyi rol
NK115(re)001:13962: du bum pas bsgribs nas dngos su mi mthong ba
NK115(re)001:13963: de bzhin du ye shes nang gsal gyi cha la
NK115(re)001:13964: yon tan gyi cha shas thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK115(re)001:13966: 'on kyang dpes bstan pa thams cad kyi don de
NK115(re)001:13967: phyogs thams cad nas thams cad du dpe de dang
NK115(re)001:13968: 'dra dgos pa ma yin pas bum pa'i nang gi
NK115(re)001:13969: sku la zhal phyag sogs dbyibs dang kha dog gi
NK115(re)001:13970: mtshan ma yod pa de 'dra ba'i sku la sogs
NK115(re)001:13971: pa'i mtshan ma'i dngos po yod mi dgos te 'char
NK115(re)001:13972: rung gi gdangs 'gag med tsam la bya'o //
NK115(re)001:13973: de dang tshul mthun par nges don gyi mdo dang
NK115(re)001:13974: de'i dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos rnams nas kyang
NK115(re)001:13975: / bde gshegs snying po sgrib pa'i sbubs na yod pa'i dpe yang gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:13976: de skad du dge rtsa yongs su 'dzin pa'i mdor /
NK115(re)001:13977: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni /
NK115(re)001:13978: bum pa'i nang gi mar me dang 'dra ste bum pa chag nas gsal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:13981: chos kyi dbyings su bstod pa las //
NK115(re)001:13982: ji ltar bum nang mar me ni //
NK115(re)001:13983: phyi rol kun tu mi snang ltar //
NK115(re)001:13984: de bzhin chos kyi dbyings 'di yang //
NK115(re)001:13986: bum pa de nyid bcag gyur na //
NK115(re)001:13987: thams cad kun tu snang ba ltar //
NK115(re)001:13988: gang tshe ting 'dzin rdo rje yis //
NK115(re)001:13989: sgrib pa kun tu bcom gyur ba //
NK115(re)001:13990: de tshe nam mkha'i mthar thug gsal //
NK115(re)001:13993: ji ltar pad nang bde gshegs dbang po ni //
NK115(re)001:13994: lha mig dag pa'i mi yis de mthong nas //
NK115(re)001:13995: chu skyes 'dab ma'i sbubs nas 'byin pa ltar //
NK115(re)001:13996: de yi sgrib pa rab tu sel ba yin //
NK115(re)001:13997: zhes pa la sogs pa dpe dgus bstan no //
NK115(re)001:13999: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK115(re)001:14000: gang la srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK115(re)001:14001: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu ster bar byed pa yin //
NK115(re)001:14002: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:14004: gzhi de la ming gi rnam grangs tha dad par btags pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14005: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:14006: 'di la ming gi rnam grangs mang yod de //
NK115(re)001:14007: 'khor 'das 'byung bar dbyings zhes rab brjod cing //
NK115(re)001:14008: ye nas yod pas rang bzhin lhun grub ces //
NK115(re)001:14009: dri mas sgrib phyir snying po'i khams dang ni //
NK115(re)001:14010: gnas lugs yin phyir don dam bden pa dang //
NK115(re)001:14011: gdod nas dag phyir 'od gsal dri med nyid //
NK115(re)001:14012: mtha' gnyis gnas bsal dbu ma'i rang bzhin dang //
NK115(re)001:14013: spros las 'das phyir shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK115(re)001:14014: stong gsal rnam dag bden pa dbyer med dang //
NK115(re)001:14015: 'pho 'gyur med pas chos nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK115(re)001:14016: la sogs mig ldan mkhas pa rnams bzhed do //
NK115(re)001:14018: 'o na dbu ma dang sher phyin zhes pa de
NK115(re)001:14019: dang rdzogs pa chen po zhes pa rnams don gcig
NK115(re)001:14020: la ming gi rnam grangs tsam yin na phar phyin
NK115(re)001:14021: theg pa las 'di khyad par du ji ltar 'phags
NK115(re)001:14022: snyams na / sngar bshad pa ltar mthar thug pa'i
NK115(re)001:14023: don du ni de thams cad gcig pa kho na
NK115(re)001:14024: snyams na / yin kyang / gzhi gtan la dbab
NK115(re)001:14025: tshul dang lam bsgom tshul la ni khyad par shin
NK115(re)001:14026: snyams na / yin kyang / tu che ste /
NK115(re)001:14027: phar phyin theg pa las snying po sa bon gyi
NK115(re)001:14028: tshul du yod pa rkyen tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i stobs
NK115(re)001:14029: kyis 'bras bu'i yon tan gsar du 'grub par 'dod
NK115(re)001:14030: pas lam la rtsol ba dang bcas la /
NK115(re)001:14031: 'dir ni snying po de la sangs rgyas kyi yon
NK115(re)001:14032: tan thams cad da lta nas lhun gyis grub par
NK115(re)001:14033: 'dod pas lam la rtsol ba yang zhi ba yin
NK115(re)001:14034: no // des na dbu ma pas stong dang rten 'byung zug 'jug gam //
NK115(re)001:14035: bden pa dbyer med ces pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14036: sngags spyi'i lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med ces brjod pa sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:14037: 'dir ka dag lhun grub dbyer med ces pa rnams
NK115(re)001:14038: gtan la dbab cing nyams su len tshul tha dad
NK115(re)001:14039: pa dang / don la gnad gcig par shes pa 'di gal che bar snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:14040: dbu ma'i skabs su phung sogs rten 'brel gyi chos
NK115(re)001:14041: rnams so sor rang rang gi sa nas snang stong
NK115(re)001:14043: sngags su rdo rje phung po'i grong khyer ram gnyug
NK115(re)001:14044: ma'i sgo gsum du gnad bsdus nas bden pa dbyer
NK115(re)001:14045: med du bsgrub cing de yang snang ldog lhar blta
NK115(re)001:14046: ba yin no // sngags kyi theg pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:14047: kyi yang rtse mor gyur pa a ti'i gzhi'i gtan
NK115(re)001:14048: la dbab pa'i skabs 'dir ni snang ba lhar blta
NK115(re)001:14049: ba yin no // ba dang / bde stong lam
NK115(re)001:14050: du byed pa la sogs pa'i dngos zhen las kyang
NK115(re)001:14051: 'das te 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rig stong
NK115(re)001:14052: bsam gyis mi khyab pa sangs rgyas chos kyi sku'i
NK115(re)001:14053: ngo bor mngon sum du ngo sprad nas rtsol ba
NK115(re)001:14054: med par 'jog pa ma gtogs de las gzhan pa'i
NK115(re)001:14055: sku dang ye shes la sogs pa'i bsgrub bya zhig
NK115(re)001:14056: yod par mi blta bas gnad bsdu tshul 'og ma
NK115(re)001:14057: nas gong ma khyad par du 'phags pa yin no
NK115(re)001:14058: ba yin no // ba dang / // de lta
NK115(re)001:14059: bu'i gzhi'i gnas lugs de nyid snang stong gi phyogs
NK115(re)001:14060: su ma lhung ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14062: ngo bo'i gnas lugs chen po de yang sku ltar
NK115(re)001:14063: gnas la kha mig rna bar dod pa ni cang
NK115(re)001:14064: mi bzhugs / stong pa ltar gnas pa la bem stong ltar cang mi bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:14065: 'od lngar snang ba chen po la kha dog tu phye ba ni cang mi bzhugs /
NK115(re)001:14066: rgya ma chad par snang ba la 'brel ba ltar cang mi bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:14067: mtha' dbus med pa ltar dmigs la phyogs su dmigs pa ni cang mi bzhugs /
NK115(re)001:14068: cha yis ma gos pa ltar snang ba la ris su phye ba ni cang mi bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:14069: rgya ma 'gags pa ltar snang zhing dpangs mtho ba
NK115(re)001:14070: la steng 'og tu snang ba ni gang yang med
NK115(re)001:14071: do zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14072: gnas lugs de ni ka dag gi ngos nas gzhal
NK115(re)001:14073: na sku dang ye shes su'ang grub pa med pas
NK115(re)001:14075: phung khams skye mched sogs su grub pa med pas semas cana mina la /
NK115(re)001:14076: thig le nyag gcig tu brjod kyang gciga rgyu'i dngos po med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14077: sku gsum la sogs pa'i tha snyad btags kyang dbyings
NK115(re)001:14078: gcig gi ngo bo la tha dada du dbye ba
NK115(re)001:14080: rang gi ngo bo spros pa dang bral ba la
NK115(re)001:14081: matha'a dang dbus su bzhag tu yod pa mina no
NK115(re)001:14082: // rang bzhin lhun grub kyi cha nas gzhal na
NK115(re)001:14083: stong pa phyang chada pa ma yin par sku dang
NK115(re)001:14084: ye shes la sogs pa'i 'char gzhi nang gsal thim
NK115(re)001:14085: la ma rmugs pa'i tshul du yod kyang dngosa po
NK115(re)001:14086: rdos can du grub pa mina no //
NK115(re)001:14087: gnyis ka'i cha nas gzhal na rang bzhin gyis skye
NK115(re)001:14088: ba meda pa'i gzhi de la ldog pas phye na
NK115(re)001:14089: zhes pa'am / dpe la lar rkyen med ces snang
NK115(re)001:14090: bas de ltar na grol 'khrul gyi rkyen gang yang
NK115(re)001:14091: med pa'i gnas skabs de ni ngo bo la yod
NK115(re)001:14092: med sogs spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral bas
NK115(re)001:14093: chos nyid gang du yang ma phye ba'i ka dag
NK115(re)001:14094: zhes pa'am / / rang bzhin 'gag pa med pas
NK115(re)001:14095: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i lhun grub
NK115(re)001:14096: zhes pa'am / / / thugs rje go ma 'gags
NK115(re)001:14097: pas mdzad pa phrin las kun la khyab pa'i snang
NK115(re)001:14098: ba gsuma dang thabas gciga gi rang bzhin las 'du
NK115(re)001:14099: 'bral med pa'i bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa ni
NK115(re)001:14100: gzhi rkyang ba'i rnam bzhag go //
NK115(re)001:14101: de skad du'ang thal gyur las /
NK115(re)001:14102: med phyir snang la snang phyir stong //
NK115(re)001:14103: snang stong 'jug pa'i yan lag can //
NK115(re)001:14104: sangs rgyas sems can dag yul lo //
NK115(re)001:14105: 'dir ltar gzhi zhes mngon par gnas //
NK115(re)001:14107: gnyis pa gzhi snang bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:14108: gzhi snang 'char tshul spyi bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14109: lhun grub sgo brgyad kyi 'char tshul bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14111: gdod ma'i gnas lugs ka dag chen po nang gsal
NK115(re)001:14112: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:14113: du rtse gcig rnam par mi rtog pa nyid du
NK115(re)001:14114: gnas pa de nyid kyi nganga lasa gzhi snang lhun
NK115(re)001:14115: grub kyi cha thams cad 'char bar 'gyur ba yin
NK115(re)001:14116: la / de yang 'di ltar 'phel pa'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:14117: thugs rje nyid gzhi lhun grub 'od gsal gyi ngang
NK115(re)001:14118: na riga pa'i ye shes nang gsal phyogs lhung med
NK115(re)001:14119: pa'i shes rab shin tu phra ba srog gam snying
NK115(re)001:14120: po'i badga nyid can du bzhugs pa la gyen du
NK115(re)001:14121: rgyu shes rab kyi rta dang /
NK115(re)001:14122: thur du sel shes rab kyi zer mdangs 'od dang /
NK115(re)001:14123: me dang mnyam pa smin par byed pa'i stobs can dang /
NK115(re)001:14124: khyab byed rdzogs par byed pa'i stobs can de bzhi
NK115(re)001:14125: po yan lag tu yod pa'i rlunga lnga'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:14126: ni lhun grub kyi snang ba thams cad 'char ba'i
NK115(re)001:14127: gazhi'am snying po'i tshul du gadngas 'gag pa med par
NK115(re)001:14128: gnas pa las nang gsal gyi thugs rje nyid rig
NK115(re)001:14129: tsam zhig g.yos pa rlung gi rta byas pa'i stobs
NK115(re)001:14130: kyis phyir 'aphagas pa ste bskyed par brtsams pasa nanga
NK115(re)001:14131: 'od gasla gyi sku dang ye shes thugs rje rnams
NK115(re)001:14132: rlung lnga dang dbyer med ro gcig tu gnas pa
NK115(re)001:14133: dngos su grub pa med pa gzhona nu buma pa'i
NK115(re)001:14134: sku'i tshul du yod pa de'i phyi rgya rala nasa
NK115(re)001:14135: dus gcig la phyi gsal du gdod ma'i gzhi ka
NK115(re)001:14136: dag gi ngang lasa g.yosa pa meda bzhina du ye
NK115(re)001:14137: shes 'od kyi sbubs sam gzhi yi snang ba shara
NK115(re)001:14138: ba ni rang bzhin lhun grub kyi snang ba zhes
NK115(re)001:14139: bya'o // gnyis pa lhun grub sgo brgyad kyi 'char tshul bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:14140: 'di la dang po lhun grub kyi 'char lugs /
NK115(re)001:14141: gnyis pa gzhi snang chen po'i //
NK115(re)001:14143: bzhi pa sprul sku'i snang lugs dang bzhir gsungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:14144: dang po lhun grub kyi snang ba shar ba ganga
NK115(re)001:14145: gi tshe na ngo bo'i gdangs nam mkha' ltar go
NK115(re)001:14146: phye ba'i tshul du yod pa la rang bzhin gyi
NK115(re)001:14147: gdangs 'od lnga'i rnam par shar ba na thugas rje'i
NK115(re)001:14148: rig gadngas rnama pa'i yula de nyid la dpyoda par
NK115(re)001:14149: byed pa'i shesa par shara ba'i tshe gzhi ka dag
NK115(re)001:14150: rang gi ngo bo na nam mkha'i ngo bo na
NK115(re)001:14151: sprin med pa bzhin ma rig pa zhes bya ba
NK115(re)001:14152: gzhi ma grub kyang thugs rje'i gdangs riga para shar
NK115(re)001:14153: ba la ltos te rang snang ngo ma shes pa'i
NK115(re)001:14154: ma riga pa can gyi cha bzunga ba'i stobs kyis
NK115(re)001:14155: dper na sprin dang bral ba'i nam mkha'a shin tu
NK115(re)001:14156: dwangs pa la skad cig gis sprin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:14157: 'dus nas khebs pa bzhina rnam pa'i spros pa thams
NK115(re)001:14158: cad dang bral bas shin tu dwangas pa'i ka daga
NK115(re)001:14159: skye ba med pa'i rang rtsal lasa lhuna gruba kyi
NK115(re)001:14160: snang ba phyir gsal du g.yo ba la 'achara ba'i
NK115(re)001:14161: tshula drug dang sgo gnyis te rnam pa brgyada du
NK115(re)001:14163: dang po 'char lugs rnam pa drug ni /
NK115(re)001:14164: ngo bo ma grub kyang rten 'brel gyi snang ba
NK115(re)001:14165: ma 'gags par rtsol ba med par 'char ba'i grub
NK115(re)001:14166: pa chen po lhun grub ltar 'char ba dang /
NK115(re)001:14167: thugs rje ltar 'char ba'i go ma 'gags pas sems can gyi don byung /
NK115(re)001:14168: yang na lhun grub ltar 'char ba mi bgrang bar
NK115(re)001:14169: 'od ltar 'char bas 'od zer gyis khyab par snang
NK115(re)001:14170: / ye shes ltar 'char ba'i longs spyod ma 'gags
NK115(re)001:14171: pas ye shes kyi rang 'od sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK115(re)001:14172: khams dag pa mngon sum du gsal /
NK115(re)001:14173: sku ltar 'char ba'i ngo bo ma 'gags pas rig
NK115(re)001:14174: pa sku ru smin te snang ba thams cad rigs
NK115(re)001:14176: gnyis med ltar 'char ba'i lta ba ma nges pas
NK115(re)001:14177: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i mi rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:14179: mtha' grol ltar 'char ba'i thabs ma 'gags pas 'khrul
NK115(re)001:14180: snang rang rgyud par mi gnas te chos nyid la
NK115(re)001:14182: sgo gnyis ni de ltar rang snang gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:14183: su snang ba de rang snang yin par rig na
NK115(re)001:14184: gdod ma'i gzhi la kun tu bzang por mngon par
NK115(re)001:14186: ma rig na sems can du 'khrul ba'i sgo gnyis so //
NK115(re)001:14187: 'di la snang ba 'di'i yar 'khrul mar 'khrul las
NK115(re)001:14188: kun tu bzang po'i grol gzhi shes par bya'o zhes
NK115(re)001:14189: gsungs pas / yar 'khrul zhes pa de yang dag
NK115(re)001:14190: pa'i sgo las sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba
NK115(re)001:14191: de grol ma zin pa'i gang zag rnams la thog
NK115(re)001:14193: 'chi srid kyi rjes chos nyid bar do'i gnas skabs dang /
NK115(re)001:14194: rnal 'byor pa la lam snang du shar ba gang
NK115(re)001:14195: yin kyang dang po nas ma rig pa can gyi
NK115(re)001:14196: cha bzung ba las shar bas ye gdangs phyir shar
NK115(re)001:14197: ba las rlung dang sems kyi chas bslad pas bzang
NK115(re)001:14198: 'khrul tsam las bag chags mtha' dag zad pa'i sangs
NK115(re)001:14199: rgyas kyi rang snang lta bu ma yin pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:14200: da dung ngo shes nas dbyings su ldog dgos pa'i
NK115(re)001:14202: mar 'khrul zhes pa'ang ma dag pa 'khor ba'i sgo
NK115(re)001:14203: las rigs drug gi snang ba shar ba de grol
NK115(re)001:14204: zin pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la ni dmigs pa med
NK115(re)001:14205: pa'i thugs rje chen po las snang ba de la
NK115(re)001:14206: zhen pa'i sems can rang rang gi mos pa dang
NK115(re)001:14207: 'tshams pa'i phrin las 'jug pa'i yul du snang ba
NK115(re)001:14208: yin pas 'khrul snang ma yin kyang rang snang rigs
NK115(re)001:14209: drug gi snang ba la zhen pa zhugs pa rnams
NK115(re)001:14210: ni der 'khrul bar 'gyur ba'i phyir rang snang du
NK115(re)001:14211: ngo shes na skad cig la snang ba rang log
NK115(re)001:14212: ste ka dag gi sa la gtan srid zin par
NK115(re)001:14213: 'gyur ba yin pa'i phyir na dag par shar ba
NK115(re)001:14215: ma dag par shar ba tsam gyis gnod pa mi
NK115(re)001:14216: skyel yang snang ba de dag rang snang du rig
NK115(re)001:14218: rang snang du ma shes par zhen pa gnyis po
NK115(re)001:14219: 'di la grol 'khrul gyi rtsa ba'am gnad thug pa
NK115(re)001:14220: yin pas gnas skabs thams cad du gang snang gang
NK115(re)001:14221: shar thams cad la rtsis gdab gang yang mi byed
NK115(re)001:14222: par rig pa rgya yan du 'jog pa ni gzhi
NK115(re)001:14223: snang 'char tshul gyi gnad shes pa'i don po yin
NK115(re)001:14224: no // 'di rnams kyang bla ma'i gsung rgyun yin
NK115(re)001:14225: snang shar yang shin tu zab pa'i gnad mthar thug
NK115(re)001:14226: pa 'di lta bu ni snying po'i nyams len dang
NK115(re)001:14227: bral zhing shes rab kyi mig mdong ba'i skal chad
NK115(re)001:14228: bdag 'dra bas go yul tsam du'ang ji bzhin pa
NK115(re)001:14229: nges dka' bas dpyad par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:14230: gnyis pa gzhi snang chen po'i 'char lugs ni /
NK115(re)001:14231: snang ba de rnams rang snang du ma rig pa'i 'og tu snga ma nub ste /
NK115(re)001:14232: ye shes kyi snam bu la 'od kha dog lnga
NK115(re)001:14233: ldan phyogs bcur 'ja' tshon brtsegs ma shar ba ltar
NK115(re)001:14234: snang ba la kha dog lnga'i tshom bus brgyan pa'i
NK115(re)001:14235: ye shes kyi snang bas khyab par 'char ro //
NK115(re)001:14236: la la snang ba de rang ngo shes pas gdod ma'i gzhi la grol bar gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:14237: gsum pa longs sku'i 'char lugs ni /
NK115(re)001:14238: snang ba snga ma nub ste phyogs thams cad 'od
NK115(re)001:14239: gsal gyi snang ba mtshan dang dpe byad kyi 'bar
NK115(re)001:14240: ba'i rigs lnga'i tshom bu yab yum du gsal ba
NK115(re)001:14241: la ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro ba 'khor lnga
NK115(re)001:14242: lngas brgyan pa thams cad kyang rang snang gi 'dod
NK115(re)001:14243: yon drug ma 'gags pa la longs spyod cing 'byung
NK115(re)001:14244: ba lnga'i byed las kyang 'dzin pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14245: bzhi pa sprul sku'i snang ba 'char lugs ni /
NK115(re)001:14246: snga ma'i sku dang ye shes de dag ni snang
NK115(re)001:14247: cha las 'od phyi ma nang ltar shar ba'i gzugs
NK115(re)001:14248: brnyan sprul pa'i sku gsum snang ba'i dang po rang
NK115(re)001:14249: bzhin sprul pa'i sku ni mngon dga' la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:14250: zhing khams gzhi rten dang brten par bcas pa me
NK115(re)001:14251: long la nyi ma shar ba ltar snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:14252: de'i snang cha las gnyis pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa thub pa drug so sor snang ste /
NK115(re)001:14253: de'i tshe yar sku dang ye shes kyi zhing khams
NK115(re)001:14254: na sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK115(re)001:14256: thad kar rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing khams 'od gsal /
NK115(re)001:14257: mar 'gro drug gi yul khams so so'i bde sdug
NK115(re)001:14258: sna tshogs pa mthong ba rnam par dag pa'i spyan
NK115(re)001:14259: la ma 'gags par gsal bas na thub pa drug
NK115(re)001:14261: de'i snang cha las gsum pa sna tshogs sprul pa so so'i snang ba dang mthun par gsal lo //
NK115(re)001:14262: la la 'gro drug gi snang ba la 'dzin pa
NK115(re)001:14263: zhugs pas rmi lam sad pa ltar de'i rjes thog
NK115(re)001:14264: nyid du 'khor bar 'jug par gsungs pas rang gang
NK115(re)001:14265: la zhen pa'i gnas rigs de las gzhan dag ma
NK115(re)001:14266: dag gi snang ba thams cad nub par 'gyur ro
NK115(re)001:14267: // de ltar 'khor 'das kyi snang ba thams cad
NK115(re)001:14268: rang snang stong gzugs kyi rol pa kho na yin
NK115(re)001:14269: pas snang ba thams cad la dgag sgrub gang yang
NK115(re)001:14270: mi byed par rang sor bzhag pas spang gnyen du
NK115(re)001:14271: blta ba'i shes sgrib phra ba yang rang dengs la
NK115(re)001:14272: 'gro ba ni lam 'di'i khyad chos te gzhan du
NK115(re)001:14273: a nu man chod kyi sngags lam gyis kyang ma
NK115(re)001:14274: dag pa'i mtshan ma la skyon dang dag pa'i snang
NK115(re)001:14275: ba la yon tan du bltas nas ched du rtsol
NK115(re)001:14276: ba dang bcas pa'i phyir 'di'i gol sar bstan pa
NK115(re)001:14277: // yin no // mdor bsdu na lhun grub rin
NK115(re)001:14278: po che la gzhi lam 'bras bu'i sbubs gsum ste
NK115(re)001:14279: gzhi'i gnas skabs na snang ba phra rags thams cad
NK115(re)001:14280: 'khrul stobs kyis thim ste nang gsal du gnas pa
NK115(re)001:14281: la ni 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i snang ba 'char rung
NK115(re)001:14282: gi gdangs yod pas gzhi lhun grub rin po che'i
NK115(re)001:14284: de las gzhi snang lhun grub rin po che'i snang
NK115(re)001:14285: ba sogs bzhir shar ba ni 'khor 'das su snang
NK115(re)001:14286: ba'i 'khrul gzhi dang grol gzhi gnyis ka yin pas
NK115(re)001:14287: lam lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs zhes bya zhing
NK115(re)001:14288: / gzhi snang rang snang du ngo shes nas grol
NK115(re)001:14289: stobs kyis thim ste nang gsal du gnas pa ni
NK115(re)001:14290: sangs rgyas kyi chos khams rgya mtsho lta bu'i 'char
NK115(re)001:14291: gzhi yin pas 'bras bu lhun grub rin po che'i
NK115(re)001:14292: / sbubs zhes bya'o // de ltar thog ma'i ka
NK115(re)001:14293: dag gi gzhi la rang chas su ldan pa'i rang
NK115(re)001:14294: mal gyi gzhi lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs med
NK115(re)001:14295: na gzhi snang 'char ba'i rgyu med la /
NK115(re)001:14296: gzhi snang med na lhun grub sgo brgyad kyi 'char tshul las /
NK115(re)001:14297: ye shes kyi snang ba longs sku dang /
NK115(re)001:14298: de'i rtsal las byad dang me long ltar 'char zhing
NK115(re)001:14299: rdzogs pa chen po'i gdul bya'i rang ngo la snang
NK115(re)001:14300: ba'i phyed sprul longs sku'am rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku
NK115(re)001:14301: dang / rang snang 'gro drug gi khams ston pa
NK115(re)001:14302: dang bcas pa ste 'khor 'das gnyis 'byung ba'i sgo
NK115(re)001:14304: de gnyis yan man du 'brel ba chad de gdul bya 'dul byed du'ang mi 'thad do //
NK115(re)001:14305: spyir sems can gyi rang ngo 'khrul pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14306: sangs rgyas kyi rang ngo rnam dag yin pas snang
NK115(re)001:14307: ba mi gcig kyang gzhi la thugs 1rje yod pa
NK115(re)001:14308: gzhi snang las shar te gdul bya 'dul byed du
NK115(re)001:14310: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK115(re)001:14311: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK115(re)001:14313: de yang 'gro drug gi snang ba rang rang la
NK115(re)001:14314: snang rung gi 'khrul pa'i cha ni rang sgo'i 'khor
NK115(re)001:14315: bas bkod pas rang snang gi cha de sbubs 'pho
NK115(re)001:14317: thun mong gi cha ni spyi mthun gyi las dang
NK115(re)001:14318: ston pa'i mdzad pas bkod pas rang nyid med kyang
NK115(re)001:14319: gzhan ngor shul na yod pa gnyis kyang dbye ba
NK115(re)001:14320: phyed dgos gsungs / de ltar phyed nas lhun grub
NK115(re)001:14321: kyi sgo las shar ba'i rang sgo'i 'khrul snang med
NK115(re)001:14322: bzhin du snang ba'i 'gro drug gi cha rmi lam
NK115(re)001:14323: lta bu ka dag gi sa la rang log tu
NK115(re)001:14324: phyed dgos gsungs / gtong dgos la / de'i mtshon
NK115(re)001:14325: nas bar dor yang rang ngor snang ba'i 'gro drug
NK115(re)001:14326: la rang snang gi sprul pas don byed pa dang
NK115(re)001:14327: mi byed pa'i cha gnyis su bshad pa ni ma
NK115(re)001:14328: dag 'khor ba'i sgo ma shar ba'i gong du rang
NK115(re)001:14329: ngo shes na bya ba'i yul med la /
NK115(re)001:14330: shar na don byed dgos pa'ang 'khrul snang stongs ma stongs kyi rjes su 'brang ngo //
NK115(re)001:14331: de bzhin rig pa'i gzhi la 'byung lnga'i 2'od mdangs
NK115(re)001:14332: dang snang cha'i sgo med na rig pa nang du
NK115(re)001:14333: rgya chad / 'byung ba phyir rgya chad pas snod bcud kyi snang ba'ang mi 'byung la /
NK115(re)001:14334: gnyis med ltar 3snang ba med na sems can gyi
NK115(re)001:14335: sgo gsum dang sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs su
NK115(re)001:14336: 'brel mi shes pas sems can sangs rgyas su'ang mi
NK115(re)001:14337: 'gyur / sku ltar 4snang ba med na 'gro ba'i lus dang rgyal ba'i skur snang ba'ang mi rigs /
NK115(re)001:14338: ye shes ltar 5snang ba med na shes bya rang
NK115(re)001:14339: mtshan par gyur pas gzhi lam 'brel ba'i mtshams mi
NK115(re)001:14340: sbyor / mtha'6grol ltar snang ba med na 'bras bu rgyur ldog pas nges pa'i sa zin mi thob //
NK115(re)001:14341: ma dag 'khor ba'i sgo med na sems can du
NK115(re)001:14342: 'khrul mi shes pas 'khor 'das kyi bsti gnas su
NK115(re)001:14343: mi rung / dag pa ye shes kyi sgo med
NK115(re)001:14344: na rig ngo la sangs rgyas kyi yon tan mi
NK115(re)001:14345: mi rung / 'byung ngo // de bas na de
NK115(re)001:14346: rnams yod pa ni lhun grub sgo brgyad kyi yon
NK115(re)001:14347: mi rung / 'byung ngo // tan no // gzhi
NK115(re)001:14348: la dag ma dag gnyis ka mi srid kyang gzhi
NK115(re)001:14349: snang lhun grub la 'khor 'das gnyis su 'char ba'i
NK115(re)001:14350: sgo yod pa la lhun grub sgo brgyad kyi snang
NK115(re)001:14351: mi rung / 'byung ngo // tan no // ba
NK115(re)001:14352: zhes bya'o // de ltar gzhi dang gzhi snang gi
NK115(re)001:14353: 'char tshul de dag ni rang ngo rig pa rnams
NK115(re)001:14354: la grol rkyen du snang bas sangs rgyas su 'grub
NK115(re)001:14355: mi rung / 'byung ngo // tan no // ba
NK115(re)001:14356: zhes bya'o // la / ma shes na so so'i
NK115(re)001:14357: cha brgyad pos 'khrul gzhi re byed pas 'khor bar
NK115(re)001:14359: de yang lhun grub snang tshul gyi cha las skyon med du shar kyang /
NK115(re)001:14360: 'khrul pa 'jug tshul gyi cha nas bdag gzhan gnyis snang du grub la /
NK115(re)001:14361: 'khrul pa ldog tshul gyi cha nas mtha' grol ris med du rtogs nas sangs rgya'o //
NK115(re)001:14362: dper na ga bur de tsha ba'i nad la yon tan du snang la /
NK115(re)001:14363: grang ba'i nad la skyon du shar yang ga bur
NK115(re)001:14364: gyi ngo bo la skyon dang yon tan ma grub
NK115(re)001:14365: pa bzhin du ma rtogs pa rnams la lhun grub
NK115(re)001:14367: rtogs pa rnams la yon tan du 'char bas na
NK115(re)001:14368: 'khrul grol gnyis ka'i sgo lhun grub la thug pa
NK115(re)001:14369: yin no // lar gzhi'i bzhugs tshul ma shes na
NK115(re)001:14370: rdzogs pa chen po'i grub mtha' shes pa ma yin
NK115(re)001:14371: la de'i gnad kyang ye gzhi ka dag gi ngos
NK115(re)001:14372: nas 'khor 'das gnyis ka ma grub na'ang /
NK115(re)001:14373: lhun grub kyi sbubs gsum po 'di ni 'khora 'adsa
NK115(re)001:14374: gnyis ka phyogs su ma chad par 'brela ba'i sgo
NK115(re)001:14376: gzhi lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs na 'khor 'das
NK115(re)001:14377: kyi snang ba 'char rung gi gdangs ma 'gags par
NK115(re)001:14378: yod pas gzhi gcig tu 'brel la /
NK115(re)001:14379: de las gzhi snang shar ba lam lhun grub kyi
NK115(re)001:14380: sbubs ni grol 'khrul gnyis ka'i rkyen yin pas 'khor
NK115(re)001:14382: gal te 'khrul par gyur na'ang gong du bshad pa
NK115(re)001:14383: sgo brgyad so so'i yon tan gyis sangs rgyas kyi
NK115(re)001:14384: phrin las 'jug pa'i yul du yang rung la sangs
NK115(re)001:14385: rgyas su 'gyur bar yang rung ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:14386: 'bras bu lhun grub kyi sbubs la yang sku dang zhing khams sogs 'char rung du yod pas /
NK115(re)001:14387: de las de ltar shar nas gdul bya la mdzad
NK115(re)001:14388: pa ston nus pas gdul bya 'dul byed du 'brel
NK115(re)001:14389: rung ba'i gnad ni de yin no //
NK115(re)001:14390: 'di dag kyang kun mkhyen yab sras gnyis kyi gsung
NK115(re)001:14391: la brten nas cung zad kha gsal bar byas nas
NK115(re)001:14392: bris pa yin kyang dgongs pa lon min ni dpyad
NK115(re)001:14393: par gyis shig / tshul de lta bu ni shin
NK115(re)001:14394: tu rtogs dka' ba'i gnas te thega pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:14395: kyi rtse mor gyur pa shina tu rnal 'byor a
NK115(re)001:14396: ti yo ga'i rgyud sde rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:14397: de'i dgongs pa 'grel bar byed pa'i 'phags yul gyi
NK115(re)001:14398: rig pa 'dzin pa dag gi mana ngaga rnams na
NK115(re)001:14400: don de ma nor bar phye ste ston pa'i lde
NK115(re)001:14401: miga lta bu ni gangas ldana ri yi ste bod
NK115(re)001:14402: gangs can gyi ljongas 'dir sngon chad 'phags yul nas
NK115(re)001:14404: bod kyi mkhas grub phal che bas ni rtsal du bton nas ma gsungs la /
NK115(re)001:14405: phal cher gyis ni ji bzhin par slong ma nus pas na /
NK115(re)001:14406: blo gros la ma rtogs pa la sogs pa'i dri
NK115(re)001:14407: ma meda cing spyir gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas
NK115(re)001:14409: khyad par rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i zab gnad
NK115(re)001:14410: thun mong ma yin pa ye shes kyi 'oda zera
NK115(re)001:14411: stong mnga' bas thogs pa med par mkhyen pa dang
NK115(re)001:14412: ldana pa kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen
NK115(re)001:14413: rab 'byams gciga gisa gsal bar phye nas bstan pas
NK115(re)001:14414: na de nyid kho na yin te /
NK115(re)001:14415: theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:14416: tshul 'di ni gsang ba snying thig gi dka' ba'i gnas te /
NK115(re)001:14417: rgyud dang man ngag nas gsal bar gsungs kyang bod
NK115(re)001:14418: 'dir sngon chad slong nus pa tsam yang ma byung
NK115(re)001:14419: bas kho bos shin tu gsal bar phye nas bstan
NK115(re)001:14420: pas phyin chad gnas 'di shes pa byung na yi
NK115(re)001:14423: gnyis pa kun tu bzang po'i grol tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:14424: chos sku'i dbyings su grol tshul /
NK115(re)001:14425: longs sku'i zhing khams bkod tshul /
NK115(re)001:14426: sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad tshul lo //
NK115(re)001:14427: dang po chos sku'i dbyings su grol tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14428: thog ma'i dbyings las lhun grub kyi nang gdangs phyir
NK115(re)001:14429: 'phags te thugs rje'i rig pa ma rig pa'i char
NK115(re)001:14430: ldog pa'i mgo rtsams pa de yi tshe na gzhi
NK115(re)001:14431: snang rang bzhin med par mthonga ba'i skad ciga ma
NK115(re)001:14432: der khyad chos drug gi tshul du grol te /
NK115(re)001:14433: sangs rgyas thams cad las sngon rol ba'i ston par
NK115(re)001:14434: bzhugs pa'i dang po'i sangsa rgyas kuna tu bazanga po
NK115(re)001:14435: desa ji ltar mthong zhing grol ba'i khyad chos drug
NK115(re)001:14436: ni / 'di ltar rang ngor snang ba /
NK115(re)001:14441: rang sar gnas pa ste rim pa bzhin gzhi snanga
NK115(re)001:14442: shar ba de la shes pa kha phyir bltas kyis
NK115(re)001:14443: zhen nas 'khrula pa rgyun chags par ma mcheda cing
NK115(re)001:14444: rang gi rig pa'i ngor 1snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:14445: ranga snanga du riga pasa grol 'khrul gang du yang
NK115(re)001:14446: lunga ma bstan pa'i rang bzhin gyi gzhi dang gzhi
NK115(re)001:14447: snang lhun grub kyi cha de gnyis rang bzhin de
NK115(re)001:14448: las 'aphagas te grol gzhi ru song bas phyis 'khrul
NK115(re)001:14450: gzhi snang gi rig pa nyid 'brasa bura smina pa
NK115(re)001:14451: zhes sgrib byed kyi dri ma zhen pa'i bag chags
NK115(re)001:14452: dag pa'i shesa raba kyis skada ciga ma gciga po
NK115(re)001:14453: de nyid la dbyings la yon tan rang chas su
NK115(re)001:14454: ldan pa rang snang du bag chags sna tshogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:14455: kun gzhi'i sgrib pa sangs te nyi ma sprin las
NK115(re)001:14456: grol ba bzhin bye brag raba tu 3phyed pa dang
NK115(re)001:14457: / phyed pa'i thoga gam 4de ma thag tu shesa
NK115(re)001:14458: raba nyid kyang ngo bo nyid skura smina nas ye
NK115(re)001:14459: shes chos kyi sku dang dbyer med par ka dag
NK115(re)001:14460: gdod ma'i gzhi la btsan sa zin te rtag tu
NK115(re)001:14462: de ni gazhana gyi bstan pa sogs las byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:14463: rkyen la ma ltos te rang gi ngo bo rang
NK115(re)001:14464: stobs kyis rig nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir dang 5
NK115(re)001:14465: / grol gzhi gdod ma'i ngang du ranga sara gansa te 'khrul pa'i rkyen mi 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:14466: de ltar khyad chos drug gis sku dang ye shesa
NK115(re)001:14467: rgya mtsho'i badga nyid du gzhi snang mthong ba'i skada
NK115(re)001:14468: ciga ma gciga la mngona para byang chub pa ni
NK115(re)001:14470: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis lam bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis
NK115(re)001:14471: khyad chos drug dang ldan par sangs rgyas pa la'ang
NK115(re)001:14472: thog ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po zhes bya
NK115(re)001:14473: ste sangs rgyas pa'i thog ma yin pa'i phyir ro
NK115(re)001:14474: // khyad chos drug po de la brjod tshul gzhan du /
NK115(re)001:14475: gzhi snang dang po shar dus /
NK115(re)001:14481: 6rang rig chos sku yin pas thugs rje'i rig pas
NK115(re)001:14482: phyir skad cig ma nyug tsam shar bas chos drug
NK115(re)001:14483: po de rtogs nas sangs rgyas par gsungs pa dang
NK115(re)001:14484: / yang lung las ma byung ba'i gdams ngag1 /
NK115(re)001:14485: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas2 /
NK115(re)001:14486: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu3 /
NK115(re)001:14489: rang grol du 6sangs rgyas so zhes gsungs pa'i don gzhi snang ye shes sgron me las /
NK115(re)001:14490: lung las ma byung ste ston byed kyi slob dpon med pas dpal rang byung gi sangs rgyas so //
NK115(re)001:14491: sems las ma byung ste ye shes nyid rang gsal du sangs rgyas so //
NK115(re)001:14492: rgyu las ma byung ste rig mkhan nyid rang grol du sangs rgyas so //
NK115(re)001:14493: rang snang ste dbyings sems nyid 'od gsal bar rang ngor shar ro //
NK115(re)001:14494: rang shar te rig pa de nyid de ltar snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:14495: rang grol te rig dus rig pa rang 'khrul med ye yin chen por rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:14497: de ltar brjod tshul tha dad pa de rnams kyang don la gcig go //
NK115(re)001:14498: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas de nyid kyi phyir gzigs
NK115(re)001:14499: kyi shes bya yul snang la shar ba'i rnam pa
NK115(re)001:14500: rang ngor mkhyen pas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa
NK115(re)001:14501: zhes bya la / de ltar mkhyen kyang rang ngo
NK115(re)001:14502: nang gsal las mi g.yo bar dpyod byed kyi spros
NK115(re)001:14503: pa chos nyid kyi ngang du zhi ba ni thams
NK115(re)001:14504: cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas te /
NK115(re)001:14505: de gnyis ldog pa tha dad kyang ngo bo gcig las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK115(re)001:14506: gnyis pa longs sku'i zhing khams bkod tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14507: 'di ltar gang gi tshe dbyings dag mnyam spros pa
NK115(re)001:14508: dang bral ba ka dag gdod ma'i gzhi la gnas
NK115(re)001:14509: pa de'i tshe chosa sku'i dbyingsa de lasa ma g.yosa
NK115(re)001:14510: bzhina du sgrib byed kyi dri ma bag chags dang
NK115(re)001:14511: bcas pa las rnama par grola bas dbyings kyi yona
NK115(re)001:14512: tan nang gsal du rgyas pa'i rtsal lhun gruba kyi
NK115(re)001:14514: rang snang longas spyod rdzogas pa'i zhing khams dang rigs lnga'i sku ru snang bar byasa nasa /
NK115(re)001:14515: rigs lnga po de yi so so'i rtsala lasa rigs
NK115(re)001:14516: lnga gangs chen mtsho'i sku dang gsung dang thugs mi
NK115(re)001:14517: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo la brten pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:14518: khams rab 'byams sangs rgyas dang sems can dpag tu
NK115(re)001:14519: med pa'i gnas mtha' klas pa tshangas chena gyi bskala
NK115(re)001:14520: pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par bkoda par mdzad do
NK115(re)001:14521: // gsum pa sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzad tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14522: de las gdul bya'i skal pa dang 'tshams par zhing khams dang sku'i bkod pa ston par mdzad de /
NK115(re)001:14523: 'di ltar sgrib pa phal cher daga pa sar gnas
NK115(re)001:14524: kyi byang sems rnams la ranga bzhina sprul pa'i sku'i
NK115(re)001:14525: zhing khams dang ston par snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:14526: ma daga pa 'khora ba'i sgo lasa shar ba'i semsa
NK115(re)001:14527: can rnams la ji ltar snang ba ni khams dang
NK115(re)001:14528: mos pa bsam pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pa can
NK115(re)001:14529: gyi so so'i snang ba nyid dang mthuna pa'i mchog
NK115(re)001:14530: gi sprul pa'i sku nas sna tshogs sprul pa'i bar
NK115(re)001:14531: ston pa yisa 'khora ba'i 'khrul snang thams cad stongsa
NK115(re)001:14532: par mdzad pa'i phrina lasa kyi 'jug pa ni ji
NK115(re)001:14533: srid nam mkha'i mtha' dang srid pa'i mtha' ma zad
NK115(re)001:14534: pa de srid du zada mi shesa par snang ba
NK115(re)001:14535: yin no // de yang ye nas rang bzhin rnam
NK115(re)001:14536: par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings sam zaga pa meda
NK115(re)001:14537: pa'i ye shes bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ranga
NK115(re)001:14538: ngo shesa pa'i stobs kyis glo bur gyi sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:14539: bag chags dang bcas pa dag nas dag pa gnyis
NK115(re)001:14540: dang ldan pa'i 'bras bu mngon du gyur te rtsol
NK115(re)001:14541: bas ma bsgrubs kyang rang bzhin yongs shes kyi shes
NK115(re)001:14542: rab kyis ye shes kyi tshogs dang dbyings na lhun
NK115(re)001:14543: grub tu yod pa'i yon tan thams cad mngon du
NK115(re)001:14544: gyur pas bsod nams kyi tshogs te dge ba'i tshogas
NK115(re)001:14545: chen po gnyis kyi yon tan la mang'a dabnga rdzogas
NK115(re)001:14546: pa'i longs spyod can ston pa chena po de'i zhing
NK115(re)001:14547: khams kyi bkod pa dang sems can gyi don madzada
NK115(re)001:14548: pa'i phrin las kyi rol pa bsam mi khyab pa
NK115(re)001:14549: sems can gyi grangs dang chosa kyi dbyingsa dang mnyam
NK115(re)001:14550: par snang bas sangas rgyas nyid kyi ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:14551: snanga ba ni de tsam du tshad las 'das pa
NK115(re)001:14552: yin pas mtha' gcig tu dbang thob pa'i byang chub
NK115(re)001:14553: sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang dpogs par mi 'gyur na
NK115(re)001:14554: phal ba'i blo'i yul du byar rung bar ni mi
NK115(re)001:14555: yin no // bsam mo // de ltar mi rtog
NK115(re)001:14556: pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid
NK115(re)001:14557: kyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa'i sangs rgyas de
NK115(re)001:14558: la sems dang sems byung gi bag chags phra ba'ang
NK115(re)001:14559: zad pas na gnyis su 'dzina pa yoda pa mina
NK115(re)001:14560: pasa gdula bar bya ba'i sems can 'di dang 'di
NK115(re)001:14561: la 'dula byed kyi sku dang mdzad pa 'di dang
NK115(re)001:14562: 'di lta bu ston par bya'o zhes rnama para mi
NK115(re)001:14563: yin no // bsam mo // rtog kyang / dgos
NK115(re)001:14564: 'dod 'byung ba'i nora bu mchoga dang dapaga bsam gyi
NK115(re)001:14566: rtsol ba meda bzhin du mdzad pa'i phrin las ni
NK115(re)001:14567: chos sku spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang na dmigs
NK115(re)001:14568: med thugas rje chen po'i gdangs ma 'gags par yod
NK115(re)001:14569: pa las gazhana ngora snanga ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:14570: 'di'i don theg mchog rin po che'i mjod las /
NK115(re)001:14571: dbu ma thal 'gyur ba dag sangs rgyas dngos ni
NK115(re)001:14572: chos sku rnam dag stong pa de la 'dod la
NK115(re)001:14573: / rang ngor yod med kyi spros pa zhi bas sku dang ye shes tsam yang ma grub cing /
NK115(re)001:14574: gzhan snang la sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang /
NK115(re)001:14575: gdul bya'i smon lam las gzugs sku phrin las dang
NK115(re)001:14576: bcas pa snang ba ni nam mkha' lding gi mchod
NK115(re)001:14578: dpag bsam gyi shing ltar 'dod de /
NK115(re)001:14580: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur la //
NK115(re)001:14581: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnam mi rtog /
NK115(re)001:14582: 'gro grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK115(re)001:14583: 'di ni spros dang bral la snang ba yin //
NK115(re)001:14585: 'dir yang ka dag gi rang ngo de dang 'dra rung las /
NK115(re)001:14586: phra ba'i ye shes dbyings na yod pa las sku dang ye shes 'char la /
NK115(re)001:14587: des sems can sangs rgyas kyis dngos su don byed
NK115(re)001:14588: par smon lam btab pa rnams kyi don byed la
NK115(re)001:14589: / ngo bo'i cha nas lhun grub yin pas rgyu
NK115(re)001:14590: smon lam gyis bskyed par mi 'dod pa'i khyad par
NK115(re)001:14593: de ltar gdod ma'i dbyings su mngon par rdzogs par
NK115(re)001:14594: sangs rgyas pa'i tshul dang sku gsum gyi dgongs pa'i
NK115(re)001:14595: ngang nas don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul ji
NK115(re)001:14596: skad bshad pa de dang mthun par thun mong gi
NK115(re)001:14597: theg pa las kyang byung ste /
NK115(re)001:14599: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub //
NK115(re)001:14600: gzhan gyi rkyen gyis rtogs min dang //
NK115(re)001:14601: mkhyen dang brtse dang nus par ldan //
NK115(re)001:14602: don gnyis ldan pa'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK115(re)001:14603: thog ma dbus mtha' med pa yin //
NK115(re)001:14604: rang bzhin yin phyiir 'dus ma byas //
NK115(re)001:14605: zhi ba chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK115(re)001:14606: lhun gyis grub ces bya bar brjod //
NK115(re)001:14607: so so rang gi rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:14608: gzhan gyi rkyen gyis rtogs min pa //
NK115(re)001:14609: de ltar rnam gsum rtogs phyir mkhyen //
NK115(re)001:14610: lam ston phyir na thugs brtse ba //
NK115(re)001:14611: nus pa ye shes thugs rje yis //
NK115(re)001:14612: sdug bsngal nyon mongs spangs phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:14613: dang po gsum gyis rang don te //
NK115(re)001:14614: phyi ma gsum gyis gzhan don yin //
NK115(re)001:14616: gsum pa ma dag sems can gyi 'khrul tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:14619: snang sems kyi dbye ba bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14620: dang po 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:14621: gzhi snang lhun grub rin po che'i sbubs shar ba
NK115(re)001:14622: de nyid rang snang yin par ma riga pas zhi
NK115(re)001:14623: nas rtse gcig pa'i sems ming bzhi'i phung po la
NK115(re)001:14624: brten pa can gzugs med pa'i khams dang /
NK115(re)001:14625: yang dag pa'i lhag mthong dang bral ba'i bsam gtan
NK115(re)001:14626: gyi sems dwangs ma 'od kyi lus la brten pa
NK115(re)001:14628: sna tshogs su 'gyu ba'i rtog pa rags pa'i sems
NK115(re)001:14629: gdos bcas sha khrag gi lus la brten pa can
NK115(re)001:14630: 'dod pa'i khams te khamas gsuma gyi semas can de
NK115(re)001:14632: thoga ma'i gzhi ka dag dang lhun grub ngo bo
NK115(re)001:14633: gcig pa'i rang mal las ma bskyod pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:14634: de la 'khrula pa'i snang ba rgyu dang bcas pa
NK115(re)001:14635: ma mchisa kyang zhes pa ste rgyu med ces pa'i
NK115(re)001:14636: don gzhi lam rig pa dngos med pa'i don yin
NK115(re)001:14637: gyi / gzhi snang 'char rung du yod pa'i gdangs
NK115(re)001:14638: brgyud rgyu tsam med pa'i bshad pa ni min no
NK115(re)001:14639: gyi / // 'o na 'khrul pa'i rgyu ci las byung zhe na /
NK115(re)001:14640: gzhi yi gdangs rang snang du shara ba'i rnama pa
NK115(re)001:14641: rang snang yin par ma shes pa'am ma riga pa'i
NK115(re)001:14642: cha de thog ma'i gzhi la'ang med /
NK115(re)001:14643: phyis gzhi thog tu phyin pa'i dus na'ang med pas na glo bura ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:14644: 'di la brten nas 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen thams cad
NK115(re)001:14645: 'byung bas na rkyen te de ni rig pa rang
NK115(re)001:14646: gi rtsal rang la sgrib byed du song ba las
NK115(re)001:14647: gzhan ma yin pas na badga nyid gciga pa'i ma
NK115(re)001:14649: 'di ni rig pa'i ldog phyogs rang ngo ma rig
NK115(re)001:14650: pa'i rgyu'i char song ba tsam gyi gnas skabs so
NK115(re)001:14651: // de nyid nus pa je thura songa nas dpyod
NK115(re)001:14652: byed kyi shes pa'i nus pa phra mo langs nas
NK115(re)001:14653: rang ngo ma shes pa tsam gyi ldog pa ni
NK115(re)001:14654: lhan ciga skyes pa'i ma rig pa yin la de'i
NK115(re)001:14655: ngang las rang rig dang 'od snang ro gcig yin
NK115(re)001:14656: par ma shes nas bdag gzhan gyi blos gnyis su
NK115(re)001:14657: phye ba'i cha nas minga dang /
NK115(re)001:14659: badga tu rtog pa'i rtog pa rags pa ma shar
NK115(re)001:14660: kyang 'char du rung ba'i char song ba'i ldog pa
NK115(re)001:14661: ni kuna tu brtagsa pa yi ma riga pa ste
NK115(re)001:14662: de gsuma tshogs shing 'dus pa lasa ni dper na
NK115(re)001:14663: yul dang mig dang mig shes gsum tshogs pa las
NK115(re)001:14664: mig gi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba
NK115(re)001:14665: 'byung ba bzhin 'khrula pa'i rkyen bzhi mcheda par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:14666: ro // de la rkyen bzhi ji ltar mched pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14667: gzhi la ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum yod
NK115(re)001:14668: pa las ngo bo'i gdangs nam mkha' ltar go 'byed
NK115(re)001:14670: rang bzhin gyi gdangs nyid 'od khyim gyi rnam pa
NK115(re)001:14671: ltar shar zhing gansa pa 'khrul pa'i yul can bskyed
NK115(re)001:14672: pa'i rgyu yi rkyen te skyes bu gzugs dang yan
NK115(re)001:14673: lag dang ldan pa la byad rang chas su 'byung
NK115(re)001:14674: ba ltar te / 'od snang ma rig pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:14675: skabs nas yod kyang ma rig pa gsum gyi nus
NK115(re)001:14676: pas 'khrul shes bskyed pa'i rgyu'i nus pa can du
NK115(re)001:14678: rgyu'i rkyen du snang ba de la thugs rje rig
NK115(re)001:14679: pa'i gdangs rtog dpyod kyi rnam pa phra bar shara
NK115(re)001:14680: ba'i dbang gis 'khrul ba phyi ma rnams 'byung bas
NK115(re)001:14681: badga po'i rkyen zhes bya ste byad 'dzin pa'i me
NK115(re)001:14682: long gi ngos lta bu snang yul 'dzin pa'i cha'o
NK115(re)001:14683: // de gnyis lhan du tshogs pa lasa phyi yula dang /
NK115(re)001:14684: nang yula cana zhes tha dad du grub pa med
NK115(re)001:14685: bzhin tha dad par dmigas pa'i yul du song ba
NK115(re)001:14686: ni gzung bar rtog pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14687: 'dzin par rtog pa gnyis kyi dmigs pa'i rkyen te
NK115(re)001:14688: me long dang byad tshogs pa las gzugs brnyan shar
NK115(re)001:14689: ba na me long dang gzugs brnyan tha dad med
NK115(re)001:14690: kyang tha dad par 'dzin pa ltar ro //
NK115(re)001:14691: rkyen de gsuma po dusa gcig tu mtshungas par ldan
NK115(re)001:14692: pa las 'khrul pa'i rgyun bar ma chad par 'byung
NK115(re)001:14693: ba'i rkyen byed pas de ma thaga pa'i rkyen te
NK115(re)001:14694: de bzhi po las rgyu dang 'bras bu dang /
NK115(re)001:14695: ming dang snang ba sna tshogs su 'khrul pa'i tshul yang /
NK115(re)001:14697: de yang rkyen bzhi yis 'khrul te /
NK115(re)001:14698: tha ma yang rkyen bzhi la thug go //
NK115(re)001:14699: rgyu dmigs pa can du 'dzin pa'i rkyen las 'bras bu sna tshogs pa'i rgyur 'khrul /
NK115(re)001:14700: bdag po yul can du 'dzin pa'i rkyen las ming sna tshogs su 'khrul /
NK115(re)001:14701: dmigs pa blo can du 'dzin pa'i rkyen las 'bras bu thug pa med par 'khrul lo //
NK115(re)001:14702: de ma thag 'dzin pa can gyi rkyen las snang ba sna tshogs su 'khrul lo //
NK115(re)001:14704: rkyen bzhi po de lam du 'gro tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:14705: rgyu'i ngang du sangs rgyas dang sems can gcig pas
NK115(re)001:14706: spang blang las 'das pa'i ye shes su ngos zin
NK115(re)001:14707: pas rgyu'i rkyen rang sar grol /
NK115(re)001:14708: yul sna tshogs su shar ba chos nyid rang snang du log pas bdag po'i rkyen las grol /
NK115(re)001:14709: de yang rang byung gi ye shes las mi 'da' bar shes pas dmigs pa'i rkyen las grol /
NK115(re)001:14710: dus med kun tu bzang po la snga phyi phan
NK115(re)001:14711: tshun gyi 'gal ba las de ma thag pa'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:14712: las grol ba'o // de ltar grol bar ma gyur
NK115(re)001:14713: ba rnams ni rgyu rkyen tshogas pa lasa rima pa
NK115(re)001:14714: bzhina 'khrula pa'i snang ba 'khrul 'dzin dang bcas goms
NK115(re)001:14715: pa stobsa su gyur nas tshul min yid byed kyi
NK115(re)001:14716: las grol ba'o // rtogs pa dang / nyon mongas
NK115(re)001:14717: pa'i tshogsa dang de dag gi rten lus dang yul
NK115(re)001:14718: dang gnas su gyur pa snod kyi 'jig rten dang
NK115(re)001:14719: bcas pa'i bag chags 'thas shing 'phela ba'i dbang gis
NK115(re)001:14720: don la yod ma myong ba'i 'khora ba'i gansa mtho
NK115(re)001:14721: dman dang rigas sna tshogs pa 'di gruba pa ltar
NK115(re)001:14724: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK115(re)001:14725: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK115(re)001:14726: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK115(re)001:14727: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs snang //
NK115(re)001:14729: de ltar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na dang po'i ma
NK115(re)001:14730: rig pa nas bzung rten cing 'brela bar 'byung ba
NK115(re)001:14731: bcu gnyis po shinga rta'i 'aphanga lo bzhina du lugs
NK115(re)001:14732: 'byung du bar ma chad par brgyud nas 'khor bar
NK115(re)001:14733: 'gyur te de yang thugs rje'i rtsal rang ngo ma
NK115(re)001:14734: shes pa'i ma rig pa gsum ni ma rig pa'o
NK115(re)001:14735: // de las rkyen bzhi ni 'khor bar 'du byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14736: de las shes pa rags par 'phel bas yul gyi rnam pa la dpyod pa ni rnam shes so //
NK115(re)001:14737: de las tha dad kyi ming dang gzugs su 'byung ba ni ming gzugs so //
NK115(re)001:14738: de'i khyad par 'byung ba so so'i cha dang kha dog tu grub pa ni skye mched do //
NK115(re)001:14739: de las yul la longs spyod pa ni reg pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14740: de las dga' gdung bar ma gsum skye ba ni tshor ba'o //
NK115(re)001:14741: de las bde ba la sred cing sdug bsngal mi 'dod pa'i shes pa ni sred pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14742: de las yul dang du len pa ni len pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14743: de las las dang nyon mongs pa rgyas te phyi ma'i skye bar 'phen pa ni srid pa'o //
NK115(re)001:14744: de las 'gro ba tha dad du skye ba ni skye ba'o //
NK115(re)001:14745: de la byis gzhon gyi gnas skabs myangs nas rgas pa dang shi ba ni rga shi'o //
NK115(re)001:14746: tshe 'di lta bu la mtshon na /
NK115(re)001:14747: snga ma'i 'chi srid gzhi'i 'od gsal nub ste /
NK115(re)001:14748: srid pa bar do snang rung gi skad cig ma
NK115(re)001:14749: dang po rang ngo ma shes pa ni ma rig
NK115(re)001:14750: pa ste de nas bzung phyis 'chi ba'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:14751: la bab pa'i tshe phyi dbugs chad dus shi ba
NK115(re)001:14752: ste de'i bar bcu gnyis po de lugs 'byung yin
NK115(re)001:14753: la / de phan chad kyi thim rim rnams rdzogs
NK115(re)001:14754: nas gzhi'i 'od gsal gyi steng du slebs pa ni
NK115(re)001:14755: la / lugs ldog ste / de yang 'khrul snang
NK115(re)001:14756: lugs las bzlog ste stongs nas 'khor ba ru log
NK115(re)001:14757: pa na mya ngan las 'das pa rang byung gi
NK115(re)001:14758: gnas lugs dang po ka dag gi snang ba shar
NK115(re)001:14759: ba nas chos nyid bar do'i snang ba rnams ni
NK115(re)001:14760: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rten 'brel mngon du snang
NK115(re)001:14761: la / lugs ldog ste / ba'o // de rang ngo ma shes na yang 'khor la /
NK115(re)001:14762: shes na grol bas 'khor ba myang 'das su grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:14763: de'ang gzhi dang gzhi snang gnyis ka la ma rig
NK115(re)001:14764: pa med kyang sprin bzhin glo bur du byung nas
NK115(re)001:14765: rkyen byas / ma dag pa 'khor ba'i sgo ltar
NK115(re)001:14766: shar bas rgyu byas te khams gsum rigs drug tu
NK115(re)001:14768: gnyis pa 'khrul pa'i snang lugs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:14769: 'di ltar gzhi snang la bdag tu 'dzin pa mthu
NK115(re)001:14770: brtas pa de'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i snod dang bcud
NK115(re)001:14771: kyis bsdus pa'i chos dpag tu med pa zhig yod
NK115(re)001:14772: pa thams cad rigas bsdu na mtho ris gsum dang
NK115(re)001:14773: ngan song gsum ste druga dang /
NK115(re)001:14774: de dag gi skye ba 'dzin pa'i tshul yang skye
NK115(re)001:14775: gansa rnam pa bzhi po ste de lta bu'i bcud
NK115(re)001:14776: kyi sems can snod dang bcas pa yod yod grub
NK115(re)001:14777: grub ltar snang ba 'di'nga rags par snang ba med
NK115(re)001:14778: par ma zad / 'khrul gzhi ma rig pa tsam
NK115(re)001:14779: yang gzhi grub pa med bzhin du mkha' la skra
NK115(re)001:14780: shad 'dzag pa ltar snanga ba dang gnas skabs pa'i
NK115(re)001:14781: 'khrul rgyus bskyed pa'i sgyu ma'i ranga gzugsa da lta
NK115(re)001:14782: snang bzhin pa'i dusa nas rang gi ngo bo rdul
NK115(re)001:14783: phra rab tsam du grub pa'ang yoda ma myong ba'i
NK115(re)001:14784: stong gzugsa nyag gcig ste snang ba de la brten
NK115(re)001:14785: nas da lta 'khrul bzhin pa'i gnas skabs 'di'i thoga
NK115(re)001:14786: ma la ma rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14787: ma rig pa'i rol pa las sems /
NK115(re)001:14789: yid las nyon mongs su shar nas 'khrul lo //
NK115(re)001:14790: de la dang po ma rig pa ni drug ste /
NK115(re)001:14791: thog mi'i rig pa rang ngo ma shes pas rang
NK115(re)001:14792: la gzhan du 'khrul pa'i rmongs pa rtsa ba sems
NK115(re)001:14794: snang yul gyi ngo bo rang bzhin med par ma
NK115(re)001:14795: shes pa'i rmongs pa 'khrul pa yul gyi ma rig
NK115(re)001:14796: pa dang 2 / rkyen las tho yor la mir
NK115(re)001:14797: 'khrul ba lta bu'i rmongs pa 'khrul pa gzhi'i ma
NK115(re)001:14799: rig pa'i ngo bo la bdag med bzhin du rnam
NK115(re)001:14800: pa la bdag tu rmongs pa 'dzin pa rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:14802: lam ltar bcos pa dang gnyen po dug tu song
NK115(re)001:14803: nas grol du mi ster ba'i rmongs pa bcos ma
NK115(re)001:14804: lam gyi ma rig pa dang 5 /
NK115(re)001:14805: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i don ma shes pas
NK115(re)001:14806: rtag tu 'khor ba na rmongs pa mi shes rmongs
NK115(re)001:14808: de las byung ba sems kyi dbye ba ni /
NK115(re)001:14810: sems kyi dbye ba 'di lta ste /
NK115(re)001:14811: sna tshogs sdud pa chu lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14812: gtsang btsog med pa phag lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14813: dpa' brtul che ba stag lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14814: yang ba sgro lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14815: bskyod pa rlung lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14816: rab tu myos pa 'dam rdzab lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14817: mched pa me stag lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14818: 'dod pa bya lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14819: rgyas pa yal ga lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14820: 'gog par dka' ba gar spyin lta bu'i sems dang /
NK115(re)001:14821: gza' gtad med pa smyon pa lta bu'i sems dang bcu gcig go zhes so //
NK115(re)001:14822: de dag kyang rim pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:14823: yul dang bag chags sna tshogs sdud pas chu dang /
NK115(re)001:14824: blang dor la rmongs pas phag dang /
NK115(re)001:14825: zhe sdang dang nga rgyal rags pas stag dang /
NK115(re)001:14826: yul du ma la 'jug la sa zin gcig tu ma nges pas bya sgro dang /
NK115(re)001:14827: 'gyu ba la thogs pa med pas rlung dang /
NK115(re)001:14828: yul la sred pas myos pas 'dam rdzab dang /
NK115(re)001:14829: rnam rtog gcig nas du mar mched pas me stag dang /
NK115(re)001:14830: yul dang du len par 'dod pas bya dang /
NK115(re)001:14831: shes pa'i rtsal rgyas pas don la dpyod pas yal ga dang /
NK115(re)001:14832: yul gyis rig pa bzung nas de'i dbang du song bas gar spyin dang /
NK115(re)001:14833: yal ma yul gyi shes pa gtad med du 'phyo bas smyon pa lta bu'i sems so //
NK115(re)001:14834: 'di dag yul dang rkyen gyis dge mi dge lung
NK115(re)001:14835: ma bstan gyi sems su 'gyur bas de gsum du
NK115(re)001:14836: 'dus so // sems las ni dpyod byed kyi yida druga langas te /
NK115(re)001:14837: 'di ltar ma rig pa dngos la yid kyi 'gyu
NK115(re)001:14838: ba bcas pa ni ma rig pa dang mtshungs par
NK115(re)001:14840: yul la nga yi bar bzung ba yid kyi rnam par shes pa'i yid 2dang /
NK115(re)001:14841: de la chags shing zhen pa gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid 3dang /
NK115(re)001:14842: yul gyi dbang du song nas nyon mongs pa phra
NK115(re)001:14843: ba thams cad zla la sdud pa kun tu tshol
NK115(re)001:14844: ba'i yid 4dang / nyon mongs pa rags pas srog
NK115(re)001:14845: gcod pa sogs slong pa rnam par rags pa'i yid
NK115(re)001:14846: ba'i yid 4dang / 5dang / de rnams kyi gnas
NK115(re)001:14847: skabs la bdag dang gzhan du bzung nas rgyun 'dzin
NK115(re)001:14849: 'di rnams 'dzin pa rtog pa'i ma rig pa la'ang sdud do //
NK115(re)001:14850: de nasa tshogsa druga gi rtog pa shin du rags pa shara te rtsa ba'i nyon mongs dang /
NK115(re)001:14851: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa sna tshogs pa'i sgo nas las du ma gsog par byed do //
NK115(re)001:14852: de ltar ma rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14855: tshogs drug gi rtog pa dang /
NK115(re)001:14856: nyon mongs rnams phal cher 'dra ba ltar byung yang
NK115(re)001:14857: rim gyis mched pa na phra ba nas mched pas
NK115(re)001:14859: thams cad rtsal rdzogs zin nas las gsog pa'i gnas skabs na'ang snga ma rnams kyi rgyun yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:14860: ngo ma shes pa'i cha dang /
NK115(re)001:14864: sems gdung bar byed pa'i cha nas 'jog pa yin nam snyam ste dpyad par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:14865: de ltar rnama par rtog pa'i dbang gis snang zhing
NK115(re)001:14866: btags pa'i chos rnams la badga tu 'dzina pa'i 'chinga
NK115(re)001:14867: ba 'di ni raba tu mthu che ste semas kyi
NK115(re)001:14868: chos nyid nama mkha'i khamas lta bu ngo bo nyid
NK115(re)001:14869: med cing spros pa dang bral ba 'di yanga raba
NK115(re)001:14870: tu bcingsa nasa chos dang gang zag gi badga gnyis
NK115(re)001:14871: su bden par grub pa ltar snang zhing /
NK115(re)001:14872: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin du yoda par bzung
NK115(re)001:14873: nas de la zhena pa ste snang ba dang zhen
NK115(re)001:14874: pa gnyis po bar ma chad par magla me'i 'khora
NK115(re)001:14875: lo bzhina du 'khor ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:14876: yul 'khor skyong gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:14877: chos rnams gang la rang bzhin 'ga' med de //
NK115(re)001:14878: sgyu ma smig rgyu chu yi zla ba 'dra //
NK115(re)001:14879: mi mkhas bden par zhen pas 'ching gyur te //
NK115(re)001:14880: rtag tu rdza mkhan 'khor lo bzhin du 'khor //
NK115(re)001:14884: 'khor lo lta bur phan tshun du //
NK115(re)001:14887: de yang kha nang du phyogs nas rang gi rgyud
NK115(re)001:14888: la bsam gzhig legs par btang na nyin mo ni
NK115(re)001:14889: tshogs drug gi snang ba la zhen /
NK115(re)001:14890: mtshan mo ni rmi lam gyi snang ba la zhen
NK115(re)001:14891: nas nyin mtshan thams cad du 'khrul pa'i rtog pa
NK115(re)001:14892: bar ma chad pa gcig rjes su gcig mthud nas
NK115(re)001:14893: 'ong ba 'di 'dra bas thog ma med pa'i dus
NK115(re)001:14895: zab mo'i nyams len gyi skal ba med pa rnams
NK115(re)001:14896: ni tshul des tha ma med par yang 'khor bar
NK115(re)001:14897: 'gyur bas 'khor ba la zhen pa log pa'i nges
NK115(re)001:14898: 'byung zhes bya ba de yang nang rang gi sems
NK115(re)001:14899: 'khrul pa rgya 'byams su song ba 'di yi mtshang
NK115(re)001:14900: rig nas 'di la sun pa skye ba la zer
NK115(re)001:14901: ba yin pas / da ni ri dwags smig rgyu'i
NK115(re)001:14902: chus bslus pa lta bu'i ci yang med pa'i stong
NK115(re)001:14903: gzugs 'di la zhen rtog gi 'khrul pa rgyun bcad
NK115(re)001:14904: nas rtog med bde ba chen po'i ngang du bag
NK115(re)001:14905: yangs par ngal bso ba la yid phyogs par bya'o
NK115(re)001:14906: ba yin pas / gsungs / snang ba de dag
NK115(re)001:14907: phyi don du ma grub cing nang sems kyi bag
NK115(re)001:14908: chags smin pa las yin pa'i rgyu mtshan nges pa'i
NK115(re)001:14909: ba yin pas / gsungs / tshul yang / srida
NK115(re)001:14910: pa 'khor ba'i gnas 'di na phyi don du snang
NK115(re)001:14911: ba'i dngos po 'di rnams kyi bye brag 'ga' zhig
NK115(re)001:14912: gis mtshon te bsam na phyi rol du snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:14913: nyi ma gcig pu 'adi'ang mi la sogs pa la
NK115(re)001:14914: la'i ngor gzugs rnams gsal bar byed pa'i snanga ba
NK115(re)001:14915: ba yin pas / gsungs / tshul yang / ltar
NK115(re)001:14916: gyur la / 'ug pa la sogs la la'i ngor
NK115(re)001:14917: ni gzugs rnam pa bsgribs te mi mthong bar byed
NK115(re)001:14919: de bzhin du chu gcig pu la'ang lha la sogs
NK115(re)001:14920: pa la la'i snang ba la bdud rtsira snang zhing
NK115(re)001:14921: / mi sogs la la'i ngor chu dang /
NK115(re)001:14922: dmyal ba pa rnams la mera snang ste byed las kyang bde sdug gi rkyen so sor byed do //
NK115(re)001:14923: de bzhin du sa gcig pu la'ang dmyal ba la me dang /
NK115(re)001:14924: zhing pa la longs spyod dang /
NK115(re)001:14925: rgyud kyis non pa'i 'gro ba la sdug bsngal du snang la /
NK115(re)001:14926: me la'ang me lhar longs spyod dang /
NK115(re)001:14927: yi dwags me'i lus can la gnas dang /
NK115(re)001:14928: me'i srin bu la kha zas su snang ba la
NK115(re)001:14929: sogs pas mtshon nas dngos po'i chos thams cad 'gro
NK115(re)001:14930: ba so so la phan tshun kuna nasa rnama para
NK115(re)001:14931: 'agla ba can du snang zhing rang rang la ji
NK115(re)001:14932: ltar snang ba'i dngos po de la de ltar 'du
NK115(re)001:14933: shesa pa ni 'gro ba rnamas so so'i sems kyi
NK115(re)001:14934: baga chagas goms tshul gyi rjesa su 'gro ba las
NK115(re)001:14935: yul gyi ngos na rang gi rang bzhin 'di yin
NK115(re)001:14936: zhes pa'i ngesa pa 'ag'a yanga meda de rang gi
NK115(re)001:14937: ngo bo ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:14939: dngos gcig yid ni tha dad phyir //
NK115(re)001:14940: don ma grub pa mthong ba yin //
NK115(re)001:14942: de thams cad kyang 'gro ba rang rang gi las
NK115(re)001:14943: snang dang bag chags 'ba' zhig gi rnam par rtog
NK115(re)001:14945: pad+mo rnam par rol pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:14946: lha'i bu pad+ma rnam par rol pas 'jam dpal la smras pa /
NK115(re)001:14947: 'jam dpal phyi rol gyi yul 'di dag byed pos byas pa'am /
NK115(re)001:14950: lha'i bu phyi rol gyi yul 'di rnams ni byed
NK115(re)001:14951: pa pos byas pa ma yin te sems sam rtog
NK115(re)001:14952: pa'i bag chags kyis snang ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:14953: lha'i bus smras pa bag chags ji ltar brtas kyang
NK115(re)001:14954: ri dang rgya mtsho dang nyi ma dang zla ba
NK115(re)001:14955: la sogs pa sra zhing 'thas pa ltar gyur pa
NK115(re)001:14958: lha'i bu snang du rung ste grong khyer chen po
NK115(re)001:14959: w+aa ra n+aa si na bram ze me sbyin zhes
NK115(re)001:14960: bya bas rang gi lus stag tu bsgoms pas /
NK115(re)001:14961: grong khyer gyi mi rnams kyis stag tu mthong nas bros pas grong khyer stongs par byung ngo //
NK115(re)001:14962: zad par sa dang chu bsgoms pas sa dang chur snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:14963: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dge slong gis mi gtsang ba
NK115(re)001:14964: dang rus gong gi 'du shes bsgoms pas der snang
NK115(re)001:14965: ba yin na thog ma med pa'i bag chags brtas
NK115(re)001:14968: des na snga ma'i bag chags smin pa la mi
NK115(re)001:14969: zhen cing phyin chad kyi bag chags mi gsog pa'i
NK115(re)001:14970: phyir 'khrul pa'i sems gdul ba la 'bad dgos pa'i
NK115(re)001:14971: tshul yang / yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:14972: sems kyis 'du byed sems kyis las kun byed //
NK115(re)001:14973: sems la snang zhing sems kyis brtags pas na //
NK115(re)001:14974: 'khrul pa'i sems gdul slad du 'bad par mdzod //
NK115(re)001:14976: gsum pa snang sems kyi dbye ba bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:14977: phyi rol du snang ba thams cad sems kyi bag
NK115(re)001:14978: chags smin pa las gzhan med pa de lta na'ang
NK115(re)001:14979: snang ba dang snang yul gyi zlas phye ba'i snanga
NK115(re)001:14980: yula phyi rol tu bag chags smin pa 'di ni
NK115(re)001:14981: nang du bag chags bzhag pa'i semas dngos ni ma
NK115(re)001:14982: yina te bag chags 'jog tshul tha dad pa'i dbang
NK115(re)001:14983: gis so sor snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:14984: de yang dper na skyes bu'i bzhina gyi rnam pa
NK115(re)001:14985: me long la gtad dus gzugas brnyan me longa gi
NK115(re)001:14986: nanga du zhugsa pa ltar bzhin gyi rnam pa ci
NK115(re)001:14987: 'dra ba de 'dra bar snang ba yin kyang me
NK115(re)001:14988: long dwangs pa de nyid kyis gzungs brnyan 'char ba'i
NK115(re)001:14989: rten byas te bzhin gyi rnam pas 'brel ba'am /
NK115(re)001:14990: gtod byed byad kyi nus pa tshogs pa'i rten cinga
NK115(re)001:14991: 'brela bar 'byunga ba'i rkyen gyis snang ba tsam lasa
NK115(re)001:14992: phyi rol gyi bzhina dngos de dang me longa gnyis
NK115(re)001:14993: gcig tu nama yanga 'dresa pa ni yod ma myong
NK115(re)001:14994: bas gzugs brnyan de bzhin dngos kyang ma yin la
NK115(re)001:14995: / bzhin las gzhan pa'ang min te rnam pa gtod byed gzhan med pa'am /
NK115(re)001:14996: de la ma brten par mi snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:14997: de bzhin du gzugs sgra sogs phyi rol yul gyi
NK115(re)001:14998: rnam pa sems la shar ba na phyi rol gyi
NK115(re)001:14999: yul de dang sems gnyis gcig tu 'dres pa med
NK115(re)001:15000: pas sems nyid ji ltar yin te min la /
NK115(re)001:15001: sems la shar ba'i rnam pa de yang yul dngos kyang ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:15002: yul de las gzhan pa'i rnam pa gtod mkhan med pas gzhan yang ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:15003: des na bzhin lta bu'i phyi rol gyi snang yul
NK115(re)001:15004: ni sems kyi bag chags kyi dbang gis snang ba
NK115(re)001:15005: yin pas sems las gzhan du'ang ma grub la bag
NK115(re)001:15006: chags 'jog tshul tha dad pas sems nyid du'ang ma
NK115(re)001:15007: grub pas na don la gcig dang tha dad du
NK115(re)001:15008: ma grub kyang / tha snyad du ni snang tshul
NK115(re)001:15009: tsam la sems ma yin no zhes khas blang bar
NK115(re)001:15010: ma grub kyang / bya la / gzugs brnyan lta
NK115(re)001:15011: bu'i sems la shar ba'i snang ba'am rnam pa ni
NK115(re)001:15012: rten 'brel tshogs pa'i med snang tsam yin pas don
NK115(re)001:15013: la sems dang gcig tha dad du brjod du med
NK115(re)001:15014: kyang tha snyad du sems yin no zhes khas blang
NK115(re)001:15015: ma grub kyang / bya la / bar bya'o //
NK115(re)001:15016: 'o na tha snyad du sems la dbyibs dang kha
NK115(re)001:15017: dog yod par 'gyur te rnam pa la de yod
NK115(re)001:15018: pa'i phyir snyam na snang ba'am rnam pa la dbyibs
NK115(re)001:15019: dang kha dog sogs su zhen pa yin gyi yod
NK115(re)001:15021: de ltar yang ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK115(re)001:15022: me long ngos sam 'bru mar snod dag tu //
NK115(re)001:15023: bud med kha bzhin brgyan pas bltas pa na //
NK115(re)001:15024: de na bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor kun snang yang //
NK115(re)001:15025: yod pa ma yin med pa'ang ma yin ltar //
NK115(re)001:15026: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:15028: de ltar na srid par 'ching byed kyi rtsa ba
NK115(re)001:15029: gzung 'dzin gnyis po rang gi sems rgyud kyis bsdus
NK115(re)001:15030: pa yin pa'i tshul 'thad pa dang bcas pa ste
NK115(re)001:15031: / snang ba'i mtshan nyid ni meda bzhina du snang
NK115(re)001:15032: ba rmi lam gyi shes pa lta bu las ma
NK115(re)001:15033: 'das pa yin kyang de la dera 'dzina gyi 'khrula
NK115(re)001:15034: pa'i semas rtog glo bur ba /
NK115(re)001:15035: dper na phyi'i yul gzugs kyi phung po la mtshon
NK115(re)001:15036: na thaga khra mthonga ba'i tshe mig bslad pa'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:15037: gyis sbrul gyi rnam pa shar dus gzung rnam gyi
NK115(re)001:15039: de kho na ma yin par sbrul du 'dzin byed
NK115(re)001:15040: kyi shes pa rtog med tshor ba'i phung pos bskyed
NK115(re)001:15041: pa'i sems kyi cha skad cig ma dang po de
NK115(re)001:15042: ni gzung ba'i chos yina la /
NK115(re)001:15043: de'i rjesa la sems byung gis rtog dpyod zhugas te
NK115(re)001:15044: sbrul du 'du shes pa'i 'du shes kyi phung po'i
NK115(re)001:15045: bdag nyid can ni 'dzina pa'i sems yin no //
NK115(re)001:15046: de'i tshe sems byung gzhan rnams 'du byed kyi phung
NK115(re)001:15047: po ste phung po lnga'i nye bar len pa dang
NK115(re)001:15048: bcas pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par skye ba lta
NK115(re)001:15049: bu'o // de yang snga ma la tshor ba'i phung
NK115(re)001:15050: pos bskyed bcas pa bskyed bya skyed byed kyi rgyu
NK115(re)001:15051: 'bras dngos lta bu ma yin te tshor bas sbrul
NK115(re)001:15052: gyi rnam par myong ba na de'i stobs kyis gtso
NK115(re)001:15053: sems kyis kyang de ltar 'dzin pas gtso che bas
NK115(re)001:15054: bu'o // smos shing / phyi ma la 'du shes
NK115(re)001:15055: kyi bdag nyid ces pa'i don yang de dang mtshungs
NK115(re)001:15056: bu'o // smos shing / la / lar sbrul gyi
NK115(re)001:15057: rnam par shar ba'i skad cig dang po'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:15058: na'ang gzung 'dzin gnyis ka'i cha yod kyang 'dir go
NK115(re)001:15059: sla ba'i phyir rags par dpes mtshon te bstan pa
NK115(re)001:15060: ltar snga phyi can du gsungs pa yin nam snyam
NK115(re)001:15061: bu'o // smos shing / la / mo // tshul
NK115(re)001:15062: de lta bur yang spyan ras gzigs kyi brtul zhugs
NK115(re)001:15063: bu'o // smos shing / la / mo // las
NK115(re)001:15064: / de la gzung ba ni yul du 'dzin pa'i
NK115(re)001:15065: bu'o // smos shing / la / mo // las
NK115(re)001:15066: / sems dang / 'dzin pa ni de la dpyod
NK115(re)001:15069: de lta ma yin par gala te phyi rol gyi
NK115(re)001:15070: snang yul sbrul dngos la sbrul du snang ba tsam
NK115(re)001:15072: 'dzina pa ni badga po zhes pa de gang la
NK115(re)001:15073: snang ba'i gang zag de'i de shesa pa tsam zhig
NK115(re)001:15074: yin par smra bar byed na gzung 'dzin las grol
NK115(re)001:15075: ba'i 'phags pa rnams la sgyu ma lta bu'i snang
NK115(re)001:15076: ba yang med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:15077: sangs rgyas kyi ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:15078: phung sogs shes bya thams cad mkhyen par yang mi
NK115(re)001:15079: rung ba la sogs pa'i nyes pa du ma yod
NK115(re)001:15080: la / khyad par du snanga ba dang snang yula
NK115(re)001:15081: so sor ma phyed par snang ba thams cad sems
NK115(re)001:15082: yin no zhes 'dod pa ni skyon che ste /
NK115(re)001:15083: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:15084: mi shes pa dag thams cad sems yin lo //
NK115(re)001:15085: snang ba rnam gsum don la shin tu rmongs //
NK115(re)001:15086: skyon mang phan tshun 'chol zhing ha cang thal //
NK115(re)001:15087: skyong byed dag gi lugs ngan de spongs shig /
NK115(re)001:15089: de yang sems su bag chags bzhag pa sems yin
NK115(re)001:15090: gyi lus dang yul du bzhag pa gnyis sems yin
NK115(re)001:15091: na sems mthong thos sogs su 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:15092: yang na sems bzhin du de dag la mthong thos sogs med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:15093: skyes bu gcig sangs rgyas pa'i tshe thams cad kyang der 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:15094: snang ba ri dang khang khyim la sogs pa yod
NK115(re)001:15095: du sems de yanga snanga ba de nyid dang lhana
NK115(re)001:15097: gnas dang khang khyim zhig pa la sogs pas med
NK115(re)001:15098: par gyur na sems kyang meda par 'gyur bas snang
NK115(re)001:15099: ba'i rjes su 'gro ldog byed pa sogs skyon mang
NK115(re)001:15100: la / bem pos sems rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15101: sems phyi na yod par 'gyur ba sogs 'chol zhing
NK115(re)001:15102: rang ma skyes gong du sems 'di na yod pa
NK115(re)001:15103: dang / rang shi dus sa phyogs sogs snang ba
NK115(re)001:15104: thams cad med par 'gyur ba sogs ha cang thal
NK115(re)001:15105: dang / bar 'gyur ro // de ltar rang sems
NK115(re)001:15106: gzung 'dzin du gol ba'i rtsa ba stongs na mya
NK115(re)001:15107: ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul ni 'di ltar chos nyid
NK115(re)001:15108: ganga du'ang ma grub pa'i don ma riga pa'i dbang
NK115(re)001:15109: gis gzunga 'dzina sgro btags glo bur ba'i rkyen gyis
NK115(re)001:15111: srida pa 'khor ba'i rang bzhin dang po bskyed pa'i
NK115(re)001:15112: rtsa ba dang bar du 'dzin pa'i gnas su gyur
NK115(re)001:15113: pa'i badga po ni ngara 'dzin pa dang nga yi
NK115(re)001:15114: bar 'dzin pa de nyid yin te /
NK115(re)001:15116: dang po nga zhes bdag la zhen gyur cing //
NK115(re)001:15117: bdag gi 'di zhes dngos la chags bskyed pa //
NK115(re)001:15118: zo chun 'phyan ltar rang dbang med pa yi //
NK115(re)001:15119: 'gro la snying rjer gyur gang de la 'dud //
NK115(re)001:15121: des na don la med bzhina yod par bzung nas
NK115(re)001:15122: 'khor bar 'khrula pa'i gzhi gzung 'dzin gyi rtsa ba
NK115(re)001:15123: stongs te rgyun choda par gyura na /
NK115(re)001:15124: rnam shes tshogs brgyad dang mtshungs ldan gyi kun gzhi
NK115(re)001:15125: lung ma bstan rig pa'i dbyings su rang log ste
NK115(re)001:15127: de'i tshul yang chos nyid gdod ma'i gshis rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:15128: ngang las rtsal g.yos pa rang snang yin par ngo
NK115(re)001:15129: shes pa dang ma shes pas myang 'das dang 'khor
NK115(re)001:15130: ba gnyis su snang bas na rig pa la kuna
NK115(re)001:15131: byed rgyal po zhes smos te 'khor ba'i chos glo
NK115(re)001:15132: bur ba'i dri ma thams cad rgya mtsho las rlabs
NK115(re)001:15133: ltar sngar rig pa'i dbyings ranga las byung zhing phyis
NK115(re)001:15134: su yang ranga gi dbyings la thima nas 'tshang rgya
NK115(re)001:15135: bar 'gyur te / mu tig phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:15136: sems ni bag chags kun gyi sa //
NK115(re)001:15137: lus can rnams kyi dri ma yin //
NK115(re)001:15138: gzung ba yul la 'dzin pa sems //
NK115(re)001:15139: de phyir 'khor ba'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:15140: sems dang bral na sangs rgyas sa //
NK115(re)001:15141: lus can kun gyi dri ma zad //
NK115(re)001:15143: yona tan rina po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i chara zhesa bya ba lasa /
NK115(re)001:15144: gzhi'i bzhugas tshula bstan pa'i tshomas te le'u bcu gciga pa'i 'grel pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15146: // don gnyis pa lam nyams su len tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:15150: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15151: de ltar chos nyid yid dpyod dang bral ba'i don
NK115(re)001:15152: gtan la dbab pa de nyid ji ltar nyams su
NK115(re)001:15154: lam rang gi mtshan nyid bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15155: skal ba dang ldan pa'i gang zag ganga zhiga 'bras
NK115(re)001:15156: bu'i mthar thug sloba pa mina pa'i zunga 'juga gi
NK115(re)001:15157: go 'phang la dkri zhing sbyor bar byed pa'i mdo
NK115(re)001:15158: sngags kyi gzhung lam chena po pha rol tu phyina
NK115(re)001:15159: pa druga gi yona tan te /
NK115(re)001:15160: gnas skabs lam gyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15161: mthar thug 'bras bu sku gnyis thob par byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:15162: nus pa ni rnam pa kuna tu chos rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:15163: gnas lugs sems nyid spros pa dang bral zhing rang
NK115(re)001:15164: bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i don ma nor bar rtogs
NK115(re)001:15165: pa'i shesa raba kyi pha rola tu phyin pa la
NK115(re)001:15166: yang dag par brten pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:15167: shes rab 'di dang mi ldan na sbyin pa nas
NK115(re)001:15168: bsam gtan gyi bar gyi lnga dang rtog dpyod dang
NK115(re)001:15169: bcas pa'i shes rab kyis chos can dang chos nyid
NK115(re)001:15170: kyi don gtan la 'bebs par byed pas kyang zab
NK115(re)001:15171: mo'i mthar thug chos sku'i dgongs pa rnyed par mi
NK115(re)001:15173: dmus long dmigs bu med pa bye ba khrag khrig rnams /
NK115(re)001:15174: lam yang mi shes grong khyer 'jug par ga la 'gyur /
NK115(re)001:15175: shes rab med na mig med pha rol phyin lnga yang /
NK115(re)001:15176: dmigs bu med pas byang chub reg par 'gyur ma yin //
NK115(re)001:15178: des na so skye'i skabs su thos pa dang bsam pa'i shes rab bskyed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15179: sgom pa'i shes rab la mnyam par 'jog pa rnams
NK115(re)001:15180: kyang sbyin sogs thabs kyi cha rnams la dngos por
NK115(re)001:15181: bden par mi zhen pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15182: mthong lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:15183: rgyu tsam du 'gyur gyis don la sbyin sogs drug
NK115(re)001:15184: ka la'ang phar phyin gyi ming gis btags pa las
NK115(re)001:15185: phar phyin dngos min pa'i tshul ni sngar bshad zin
NK115(re)001:15186: to // de'i phyir phar phyin theg par yang shes
NK115(re)001:15187: rab ni dmus long gi sna khrid lta bur sngon
NK115(re)001:15189: dang por rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes stong
NK115(re)001:15190: nyid mngon sum du rtog pa'i shes rab rang rgyud
NK115(re)001:15191: la bskyed nas bzod sbyin sogs rgyal sras kyi spyod
NK115(re)001:15192: pa rgya mtsho'i sgo nas skal pa grangs med par
NK115(re)001:15193: gzhan phan gyi spyod pa lhur blangs te rdzogs min
NK115(re)001:15194: sbyangs gsum mthar phyin nas yang dag mtha' mngon du
NK115(re)001:15195: byed pa ni lam gyi 'brel ma nor ba yin
NK115(re)001:15196: par gsungs pa bzhin du 'dir yang man ngag zab
NK115(re)001:15197: mo'i thabs kyis 'phags pa'i lam gyis shes rab mngon
NK115(re)001:15198: sum pa'i chos nyid de ngo sprad nas bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:15199: yin pas / sher phyin dang rdzogs chen ming tha
NK115(re)001:15200: dad kyang don la gnas skabs gtan la dbab tshul
NK115(re)001:15201: yin pas / dang / nyams su len tshul phar
NK115(re)001:15202: phyin theg pa nas bshad pa dang mi 'dra ba
NK115(re)001:15203: tsam las gcig pa kho na yin no //
NK115(re)001:15204: de ltar chos nyid kyi don rnal ma mthong ba'i
NK115(re)001:15205: lam shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa de
NK115(re)001:15206: ni dus nama du yanga mi slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK115(re)001:15208: zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'das gazhana gyi rgyur
NK115(re)001:15209: mi 'gyur bas srid zhi gnyis ka'i mthar gol bar
NK115(re)001:15212: bar snang 'phur ba'i bya la gnas yod ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:15213: de na gnas pa ma yin sa la ltung mi 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:15214: de ltar byang chub sems dpa' rnam thar sgor spyod pa //
NK115(re)001:15215: mya ngan 'das la mi reg mtshan mar spyod ma yin //
NK115(re)001:15216: zhes pa ltar te shes rab de nyid mtha' gnyis
NK115(re)001:15217: la mi gnas pa'i chos sku'i ngo bo yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:15218: phyir ro / 'o na rdzogs pa chen po'i lam
NK115(re)001:15219: 'dir ni shes rab gcig pu de bsgom pas sbyin
NK115(re)001:15220: sogs thabs kyi cha la ma bslab par yang grol
NK115(re)001:15221: ba mthar thug mi gnas pa'i myang 'das thob par
NK115(re)001:15222: 'dod na nyan rang rnams kyis kyang de ci'i phyir
NK115(re)001:15223: mi thob ste rgyu mtshan mtshungs pa'i phyir snyams na
NK115(re)001:15224: phyir ro / / mi mtshungs te nyan rang gi
NK115(re)001:15225: shes rab nyi tshe ba de la ni chos nyid
NK115(re)001:15226: kyi rtogs pa yongs su ma rdzogs pas dmigs med
NK115(re)001:15227: snying rje chen po rtsol med du 'byung bar mi
NK115(re)001:15228: 'gyur zhing sbyin sogs thabs kyi cha thams cad de
NK115(re)001:15229: la ngang gis 'du bar yang mi 'gyur bas zhi
NK115(re)001:15230: ba'i mtha' la zhen nas myang 'das phyogs gcig par
NK115(re)001:15231: phyir ro / / 'gyur la / rang bzhin rdzogs
NK115(re)001:15232: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis dri ma
NK115(re)001:15233: med pa'i shes rab de lta bu mngon du gyur
NK115(re)001:15234: pa ni chos nyid kyi rtogs pa yongs su rdzogs
NK115(re)001:15235: pa yin pas rang gdangs 'gag pa med pa'i rtsal
NK115(re)001:15236: las snying rje chen po shugs 'byung du skye la
NK115(re)001:15238: thabs kyi cha thams cad la'ang ched du ma brtson
NK115(re)001:15239: kyang shes rab de la ngang gis 'du ste /
NK115(re)001:15240: dper na sher phyin rgyan las /
NK115(re)001:15241: sbyin pa la sogs re rer ni //
NK115(re)001:15242: de dag phan tshun bsdus pa gang //
NK115(re)001:15243: skad cig gcig pa'i bzod pa yis //
NK115(re)001:15244: bsdus pa de 'dir mthong ba'i lam //
NK115(re)001:15245: zhes mthong lam rtse mo'i skabs su pha rol tu
NK115(re)001:15246: phyin pa drug drug sum cu rtsa drug gi rang
NK115(re)001:15247: bzhin mthong lam yin par bshad pa bzhin ka dag
NK115(re)001:15248: gi rig pa spros pa dang bral ba la mnyam
NK115(re)001:15249: par bzhag pa na lhun grub kyi snang cha 'gag
NK115(re)001:15250: med du yod pa la sbyin sogs kyi ngo bo'am
NK115(re)001:15251: rnam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs te /
NK115(re)001:15253: rnam kun mngon rdzogs byang chub pa //
NK115(re)001:15254: zhes pa dang tshul mthun pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:15255: rnam pa thams cad du rdzogs pa chen po'i lam
NK115(re)001:15256: la zhugs pa rnams kyis sbyin sogs kyi spyod pa
NK115(re)001:15257: la mi bslab pa 'dor ba'ang min te snga phyir
NK115(re)001:15258: gshegs bzhugs kyi theg rtse'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:15259: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam par thar pa dang gzhan
NK115(re)001:15260: phan gyi spyod pa rgya mtsho lta bus 'gro ba'i
NK115(re)001:15261: ded dpon mdzad pa thos mthong du gyur pa rnams
NK115(re)001:15262: kyis shes so // de lta bu'i shes rab de'i mtshan nyid dngos ni /
NK115(re)001:15263: mtshan nyid med pa ste 'di ltara dus gsum du
NK115(re)001:15264: mngon par rdzogas par byang chub pa'i sangas rgyasa bcom
NK115(re)001:15265: ldan 'das kun gyi thugs kyi gasnga ba theg chen
NK115(re)001:15266: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi ye shes /
