NK115(re)001:15267: zung 'jug 'od gsal gyi rdzogs rim mthar thug pa'i
NK115(re)001:15268: ngo bo ni stong pa nyid gnas lugs don dam
NK115(re)001:15269: pa'i bden pa yin pas de la dag ma dag
NK115(re)001:15270: la sogs pa'i mtshan ma med pas spyi dang rang
NK115(re)001:15271: gi matshana nyid mi gansa shinga /
NK115(re)001:15272: spros pa'i matha'a thams cad dang bral ba'i dona la
NK115(re)001:15273: blo'i 'jug pa zhi ba'i tshul gyis zhugs pas dbu
NK115(re)001:15274: mar gzung ba'ang meda cing mi dmigs pas rang gi
NK115(re)001:15275: ngo bo nyida spangsa pa ste stong la /
NK115(re)001:15276: lhun grub kyi cha nas dwangs gsal g.yo ba med
NK115(re)001:15277: pa'i 'od gsal ye shes kyi sgyu ma mi 'gag
NK115(re)001:15278: pa ni rdzogsa pa chen pora grub pa yin pas
NK115(re)001:15279: de ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK115(re)001:15280: mtshan nyid de / de skad du'ang bshad rgyud dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK115(re)001:15281: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK115(re)001:15282: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK115(re)001:15283: ma bcos ma bslad byas pa med //
NK115(re)001:15284: ji bzhin rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK115(re)001:15285: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK115(re)001:15286: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK115(re)001:15287: rang bzhin med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK115(re)001:15288: bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub //
NK115(re)001:15289: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK115(re)001:15290: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK115(re)001:15292: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:15293: lam gyi khyad par bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15295: dang po lam gyi khyad par bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:15296: lam gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:15297: nang gses sde gsum gyi khyad par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15298: dang po lam gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:15299: tshul de lta bu zab cing gting dpag dka' bas rtog ge rig pa'i spyod yul las 'das te /
NK115(re)001:15300: 'di ltar rang lugs sgrub cing gzhan phyogs sun 'byin
NK115(re)001:15301: par byed pa'i sgo nas rtsod pa mngona para 'phela
NK115(re)001:15302: ba'i bsam byung gis bskyed pa'i rtog ge'i rig pa
NK115(re)001:15303: rnon pos ni ji tsam brtagsa shinga dpyad kyang mtha'
NK115(re)001:15304: bral gyi don la sgro 'dogs pa dang skur pa
NK115(re)001:15305: 'debs pa'i tshul gyis rjes su dapaga pa'i kun rtog
NK115(re)001:15306: gi 'thor rlung g.yo ba'i phyi bzhina 'brang bas na
NK115(re)001:15307: / don dam pa'i bden pa rtogs par mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:15308: te rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba ye shes
NK115(re)001:15309: kyi spyod yul bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid
NK115(re)001:15310: ni de dang 'agla ba cana yin pa'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:15312: don dam blo yi spyod yul min /
NK115(re)001:15313: blo ni kun rdzob yin par brjod //
NK115(re)001:15316: byis pa ngan pa rtog ge ba //
NK115(re)001:15317: ro dang 'dra bar de dag brtags //
NK115(re)001:15319: des na de'i rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin ni /
NK115(re)001:15320: so so ranga gi riga pa'i ye shes kyis rtog
NK115(re)001:15321: pa'i bud shing bsregs te rang bzhin nye bar zhi
NK115(re)001:15322: ba / spros pa dang bral ba bsam pa dang
NK115(re)001:15323: brjod pa'i yula lasa 'adsa pa'i chos nyid dang ro
NK115(re)001:15324: gcig tu gyur nas rnam rtog gi rlung gis ma
NK115(re)001:15325: ba / bskyod pa ste / 'jam dpal gnas pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:15326: rtog pa rnams ni g.yo bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:15327: rtog pa med na mya ngan 'da' //
NK115(re)001:15328: gang gis rang bzhin de shes pa //
NK115(re)001:15329: de ni ye shes ldan zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:15331: khyad par du yul dang yul can gyi spros pa
NK115(re)001:15332: nye bar zhi ba'i ye grol gyi chos nyid la
NK115(re)001:15333: yang grol gyi sgro 'dogs pa'i dngosa pora smra ba'i
NK115(re)001:15334: gruba pa'i matha'i tshul la zhen pa rnams kyis rang
NK115(re)001:15335: rang gi rtog ge'i rigs pas snang sems gnyis char
NK115(re)001:15336: ram gang rung zhig yod ces pa'i sgro 'dogs pa
NK115(re)001:15337: dang / de las gzhan med ces pa'i skur 'debs
NK115(re)001:15338: kyi rtog pas rang nyid bcings nas mi rtogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:15339: tshul rigs pa drug cu pa'i 'grel ba las /
NK115(re)001:15340: khyed cag thog ma med pa'i dus nas nyon mongs pa'i 'ching bas bcings par ma zad /
NK115(re)001:15341: da dung yang rang gi grub mtha' ngan pas sbyar
NK115(re)001:15342: ba'i 'ching bas bcings pa dar gyi srin bu rang
NK115(re)001:15343: gi kha chus 'ching ba bzhin du zhes so //
NK115(re)001:15344: gzhan yang spyir sa matshamas kyis damna pa so so'i skye bo'i gnas skabs na /
NK115(re)001:15345: rang grol gyi gnad med pa'i gang zag rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:15346: rtog ge yi shes rab gsum gyis chos nyid la
NK115(re)001:15347: ji ltar rtoga cing dpyod kyang rtogs par mi 'gyur
NK115(re)001:15348: la / bye brag rgyu'i theg pa'i bden bzhi dang bden gnyis la sogs par lta ba'i blo dang /
NK115(re)001:15349: sngags kyi theg par thabs shes 'brel ba'i lam rim
NK115(re)001:15350: pa gnyis la sogs pa'ang rgyu 'bras snga phyir smin
NK115(re)001:15351: 'dod sogs yid dpyod kyi 'phrang dang gol sgrib sna
NK115(re)001:15352: tshogs pa'i cha las ma grol bas chos nyid byang
NK115(re)001:15353: chub sems kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa de dag
NK115(re)001:15354: gi yul lasa kyang 'adsa par kun byed las gsal
NK115(re)001:15355: bar bstan to // des na rgyal ba'i ye shesa rang byung gi dgongs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15356: gdoda ma nasa grola ba'i chos nyid yin pas /
NK115(re)001:15357: da gzod ma grol ba grol bar byed pa'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:15358: gzhan mi 'jug kyang rang bzhin rdzogas pa chena po'i
NK115(re)001:15359: lam du de nyid rjen par bstan nas rnam shes
NK115(re)001:15360: tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa'i glo bur gyi dri ma
NK115(re)001:15361: rang grol gyi gnad la brten nas dag par byed
NK115(re)001:15362: pa yin no // gal te gdod nas grol zin
NK115(re)001:15363: na sems can thams cad lam la ma brten par
NK115(re)001:15364: rang grol du 'gyur rigs so zhe na /
NK115(re)001:15365: sems can yid no cog gis dam pa'i bla ma yang ma bsten /
NK115(re)001:15366: dbang gis smin par yang ma byas /
NK115(re)001:15367: grol byed kyis grol bar yang ma byas /
NK115(re)001:15368: thabs kyi 'jug sgo yang ma rig /
NK115(re)001:15369: lam gyi sngon du 'gro ltos nas de nyid rtogs
NK115(re)001:15370: pa'i thabs sgrib pa sbyang ba dang tshogs rdzogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:15372: dngos gzhi la ltos nas rang grol dang cog bzhag gi gnad kyang ma go //
NK115(re)001:15373: mos gus la ltos nas bla ma'i byin rlabs zhugs
NK115(re)001:15374: pa'ang med pas 'bad med du ga la grol te
NK115(re)001:15376: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:15377: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK115(re)001:15378: thams cad sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK115(re)001:15379: rtog pas bsgribs pas ngo ma shes //
NK115(re)001:15381: 'o na dngos gzhi'i skabs su rtog dpyod kyi shes
NK115(re)001:15382: rab med na lhag mthong med pa'i skyon yod do
NK115(re)001:15383: zhe na / rnam par rig pa can gyi so
NK115(re)001:15384: sor rtog pa'i shes rab de ni las dang po
NK115(re)001:15385: ba rnams kyis sems yongs su tshol ba'i brtson 'grus
NK115(re)001:15386: tsam ste dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK115(re)001:15387: 'od srung 'di la chos rnams kyi so sor rtog pa'i shes rab gang zhe na /
NK115(re)001:15388: sems yongs su tshol ba'i brtson 'grus so //
NK115(re)001:15390: mthar gyis de ltar rtog pa'i yul dang rtog byed
NK115(re)001:15391: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab nyid kyang bsreg bya
NK115(re)001:15392: tshig nas sreg byed mi gnas pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:15393: rang bzhin med par song ba ni shes rab kyi dbang po lhag mthong dngos yin te /
NK115(re)001:15395: dper na shing gnyis rlung gis drud pa las //
NK115(re)001:15396: me byung nas ni de nyid bsreg par byed //
NK115(re)001:15397: de bzhin shes rab dbang po skyes nas ni //
NK115(re)001:15398: so sor rtog pa de nyid bsreg par byed //
NK115(re)001:15400: 'dir rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ye shes bsam
NK115(re)001:15401: gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid kyi don la mnyam
NK115(re)001:15402: par 'jog pa ni dus gsum gyi rtog pa thams
NK115(re)001:15403: cad dang bral ba yin kyang /
NK115(re)001:15404: ston pa rang nyid kyis yongs su grags par bstan
NK115(re)001:15405: pa'i sde snod chen po rnams dang mi 'gal ste
NK115(re)001:15407: 'od srung 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sman gang yin zhe na /
NK115(re)001:15408: sems yongs su tshol ba'i brtson 'grus so //
NK115(re)001:15409: 'od srung sems ni dpyad du med pa /
NK115(re)001:15412: rnam pa rig pa med pa /
NK115(re)001:15414: 'od srung sems ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang ma gzigs /
NK115(re)001:15417: 'od srung sems ni kun tu btsal na mi rnyed do //
NK115(re)001:15418: gang ma rnyed pa de ni mi dmigs so //
NK115(re)001:15419: gang mi dmigs pa de ni 'das pa yang ma yin /
NK115(re)001:15421: da ltar byung ba yang ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:15424: da ltar byung ba yang ma yin pa de ni dus gsum las yang dag par 'das pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15426: de lta bu'i rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs gtan
NK115(re)001:15427: la phebs na mtha' bral dbu ma'i man ngag gi
NK115(re)001:15428: yang gting phyin pa yin pas /
NK115(re)001:15429: de'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe na gzung
NK115(re)001:15430: 'dzin 'brel chad de snang sems thams cad chu bo
NK115(re)001:15431: la rlabs thim pa ltar chos nyid du phyam gcig
NK115(re)001:15432: grol bas shesa bya gshis kyi bzhugs tshul la snanga
NK115(re)001:15433: ba yul gyi rnam pasa ma bcingsa par phung po
NK115(re)001:15434: lnga'i nye bar len pas stong pa'i rang bzhin dngosa
NK115(re)001:15435: po'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin pa'i thog tu
NK115(re)001:15436: phebs la / stong pa de yang ranga bzhina 'od
NK115(re)001:15437: gasla ba'i snying po can te zung du 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:15438: bdag nyid ni riga pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:15439: sangs rgyas chos kyi sku'i dgongs para bzhugas pa 'ching
NK115(re)001:15440: grol med pa'i chos nyid la sku dang ye shesa
NK115(re)001:15441: kyi chos khamas ma lus pa gdod nas ye rdzogs
NK115(re)001:15442: chen por 'du 'brala meda par gnas pa ni nyi
NK115(re)001:15443: ma'i snying po la 'od zer 'du 'bral med pa
NK115(re)001:15444: phebs la / bzhina te / de'i tshe na gzugs
NK115(re)001:15445: sogs snang yul ma 'gags par shar yang de yi
NK115(re)001:15446: rnam pas rig pa la ma gos pas stong la
NK115(re)001:15447: rig pa yul thog tu ma shor bar rang so
NK115(re)001:15448: zin pas snang yul la blo yis ma gos pa'am
NK115(re)001:15449: 'dzin pas stong ste bar med har sangs su song
NK115(re)001:15450: phebs la / bzhina te / ba ni / bsal
NK115(re)001:15451: bzhag dang bri gang med pa'i chos nyid la phyam
NK115(re)001:15454: gang yang ma spang kun las 'das pa'i don //
NK115(re)001:15455: phyogs bral rig pa gtad med rang yan te //
NK115(re)001:15456: 'di zhes mi mtshon bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK115(re)001:15457: gnyis med yangs pa chen por phyam gcig go //
NK115(re)001:15459: shes rab snying po las kyang /
NK115(re)001:15462: gzugs las kyang stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin /
NK115(re)001:15463: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:15464: phung po lnga po 'di dag kyang rang bzhin gyis stong par blta'o //
NK115(re)001:15466: gnyis pa nang gses sde gsum gyi khyad par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15467: de ltar bya rtsol blo 'das rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK115(re)001:15468: gnas lugs ganga la dbye ba dang bzang ngan ma
NK115(re)001:15469: grub kyang dbang po dang blo yi rima pasa 'ajala
NK115(re)001:15470: lugas rnam pa gsuma du gsungs pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:15471: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK115(re)001:15472: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK115(re)001:15473: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK115(re)001:15474: rim rtsol bral la man ngag go //
NK115(re)001:15475: zhes pa ltar rang gi sems nyid las gzhan du
NK115(re)001:15476: gyur pa'i chos gang yang med pas spang bya'i mtha'
NK115(re)001:15477: las grol ba gnas pa semas kyi sde pa rnams
NK115(re)001:15479: chos dbyings mdzod 'grel lung gi gter mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:15480: byang chub sems ni gang du'ang ma grub la gang gi'ang gzhir gyur pas nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:15481: de'i rtsal ni 'char tshul ma 'gags pa me long g.ya' dag pa'i ngos lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:15482: rol pa ni sna tshogs su shar ba'i chos sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad lta bu'o //
NK115(re)001:15483: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis
NK115(re)001:15484: bsdus pa'i chos rnam pa sna tshogs su snang yang
NK115(re)001:15485: rola pa sna tshogs pa'i 'char gzhi rig pa'i rtsala
NK115(re)001:15487: de las shar ba'i rol pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15488: de gnyis ka'i rang bzhin byang chub kyi sems gsum
NK115(re)001:15489: du gtan la dbab pas rol par shara ba'i nyon
NK115(re)001:15490: mongs pa la sogs pa'i bzang ngan gyi rtog tshogs
NK115(re)001:15491: gang yang ched du mi dgag la /
NK115(re)001:15492: de yang dbyings dag mnyam chen po'i ye shes spros
NK115(re)001:15493: pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid la gcig dang tha
NK115(re)001:15495: de ltar gsum du phye ba'ang don la grub par
NK115(re)001:15496: mi 'dzin pas snang ba sems su bsgrub cing sems
NK115(re)001:15497: nyid yod par 'dod pa'i log rtog las 'das shing
NK115(re)001:15498: dran rtog rang bzhin med par shes pas 'di ni
NK115(re)001:15501: 'di ni de mi brjed pa'i dran pa'o snyam pa'i
NK115(re)001:15502: rtog dpyod rang mtshan pa'am thams cad stong pa'o snyam
NK115(re)001:15503: pa'i rang mtshan pa ma yin pa'i blos rgyas 'debs
NK115(re)001:15504: pa'i phyogs las grol ba ste /
NK115(re)001:15506: ma skyes rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK115(re)001:15507: skye ba dngos por snang ba'i gzugs brnyan shar //
NK115(re)001:15508: ji ltar skyes pa rang bzhin gnyis med pas //
NK115(re)001:15509: ji bzhin rtsol bral bde ba chen por zhog /
NK115(re)001:15511: sems kyi gnas lugs bya rtsol dang bral ba'i don
NK115(re)001:15512: de lta bu la mnyam par mi 'jog pa'i rtog
NK115(re)001:15513: ge sna tshogs pa'i rjes su 'brang ba ni don
NK115(re)001:15514: med par ma zad 'ching ba'i rgyu ste /
NK115(re)001:15516: gang zhiig bla ma'i man ngag bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK115(re)001:15517: gdung sel bsil ba ngoms par mi 'thung bar //
NK115(re)001:15518: de ni bstan bcos don mang mya ngam gyi //
NK115(re)001:15519: thang la skoms pas gdungs te 'chi bar zad //
NK115(re)001:15521: chos can phyi nang gi snang ba ji snyed pa
NK115(re)001:15522: thams cad chos nyid skye ba med pa kun tu
NK115(re)001:15523: bzang mo'i klong las 'gro sa gzhan med pas gnyen
NK115(re)001:15524: pos mtha' las grol ba bya bral klonga gi sde
NK115(re)001:15525: pa rnam kyis ni yin min phyogs bral chen po'i
NK115(re)001:15526: dgongs pa la 'ching grol med de //
NK115(re)001:15527: snang ngo la phyi snang ba sna tshogs nang sems
NK115(re)001:15528: kyi 'gro ldog ji ltar snang yang stong ngo nas
NK115(re)001:15529: ye grol yin pas rig pa nyid phyi shar du
NK115(re)001:15530: mi 'dod cing sems dang sems byung thams cad rang
NK115(re)001:15531: snang ba tsam las shar bya shar byed du ma
NK115(re)001:15532: grub pas snang phyogs yul gyi rkyen dang kun tu
NK115(re)001:15533: rtog pa thams cad kyis stong pa don dam pa'i
NK115(re)001:15534: de kho na nyid la glags ma rnyed pas snang
NK115(re)001:15535: ba sna tshogs rang stong rang yal du cha la
NK115(re)001:15536: la / ji ltar snang yang nam mkha' la gza'
NK115(re)001:15537: skar bkram pa bzhin ranga snanga bkoda pa'i rgyan tsam
NK115(re)001:15538: las sems sde ltar rtsal dang rol par rig pa
NK115(re)001:15539: shar bar mi 'dod pas de gsum phan tshun ltos
NK115(re)001:15540: grub dang phyogs lhung can du mi blta ba'i ye
NK115(re)001:15543: mtshon tshig du ma'i spros dang bral //
NK115(re)001:15544: sngags las ma skyes ye rdzogs nyid //
NK115(re)001:15545: rgyu dang rkyen rnams yongs su zad //
NK115(re)001:15546: lta sgom dri ma kun dang bral //
NK115(re)001:15547: mtha' med dbus su dmigs pa med //
NK115(re)001:15548: rnam pa med cing yul rnams med //
NK115(re)001:15550: rig pa gsal ba'i cha dang stong pa'i dbyings su
NK115(re)001:15551: mi blta bar yin lugs gshis thog tu 'bebs pas
NK115(re)001:15552: spang gnyen gnyis ka'i mtha' las grol ba zab pa
NK115(re)001:15553: mana ngaga gi sde pa rnams kyis ni ngo bo
NK115(re)001:15554: ka dag brjod bral blo 'das chen po'i gdangs rang
NK115(re)001:15555: snang lhun grub kyi sgo la rang shar bas rtsal
NK115(re)001:15556: snang la sgrib byed dang 'dzol sa med cing chos
NK115(re)001:15557: can gyi snang ba chos nyid spros bral du 'dum
NK115(re)001:15558: pa'i gnad kyis khyad par du 'phags te /
NK115(re)001:15559: sems sde bas sems gsal ba las zab mo'i phyogs
NK115(re)001:15560: shas che bar bsgrubs kyang gsal ba'i rtsal chos nyid
NK115(re)001:15561: du ma lhongs nas rtsal dang rol pa la yid
NK115(re)001:15563: klong sdes zab gsal cha mnyam par bsgrubs kyang chos
NK115(re)001:15564: nyid la 'dzin pa'i yid dpyod las stong phyogs kyis
NK115(re)001:15566: de gnyis kas yul snang dang shes pa phyam gcig
NK115(re)001:15567: ro mnyam yod ma myong med ma myong ba'i gzhi
NK115(re)001:15568: bral spyi 'byams su gdengs 'cha' bas gnad du ma
NK115(re)001:15569: song na shis shor gyi gol sgrib che ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:15570: te / bkod pa chen po las /
NK115(re)001:15571: de ltar gtan la ma phab na //
NK115(re)001:15572: yid dpyod 'dzin pa rnams dang ni //
NK115(re)001:15573: khyad par ci yang med par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:15574: de phyir nges gsang snying po 'di //
NK115(re)001:15575: kun gyi nang nas khyad par 'phags //
NK115(re)001:15578: tha mal snang 'di 'khrul pa nyid yin pas //
NK115(re)001:15579: de la sor gzhag 'khrul snang phyir phyir 'phel //
NK115(re)001:15580: de bzhin 'khrul rtog lam du sus byed pa //
NK115(re)001:15581: 'khrul pa'i rgyu 'bras nyid las thar dus med //
NK115(re)001:15582: de bas ma 'khrul 'od gsal snang ba dang //
NK115(re)001:15583: sems 'gags ye shes lam du byed pa gces //
NK115(re)001:15584: de yang mi g.yo mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe //
NK115(re)001:15585: 'od gsal dmigs gtad rig pa dwangs phyed pas //
NK115(re)001:15586: gnas lugs gcig la snang lugs nyams gsum skye //
NK115(re)001:15587: ngo bo'i gdangs las mi rtog spros dang bral //
NK115(re)001:15588: rang bzhin gdangs las rang gsal gsal dwangs phyed //
NK115(re)001:15589: thugs rje'i gdangs las rig bde rgyun mi 'chad //
NK115(re)001:15590: sku gsum nyams ni nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK115(re)001:15592: de bas na man ngag sde pa 'di'i khyad par 'phags chos thod rgal la gsungs kyang /
NK115(re)001:15593: ka dag gi lta sgom la'ang khyad par che ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:15594: 'og ma gnyis kas rol pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15595: rgyan du blta ba'i snang sems glo bur ba thams
NK115(re)001:15596: cad 'dir meda bzhin du snanga bas stong pa'i gzugas
NK115(re)001:15597: brnyan nyag gcig yin pa'i phyir rol pa dang rgyan
NK115(re)001:15598: tsam du'ang mi blta zhing gsal stong gi phyogs so
NK115(re)001:15599: sor bsgrub pa de yang brjod med blo las 'das
NK115(re)001:15600: pa'i chos nyid la gsal ba dang stong pa'i tha
NK115(re)001:15601: snyad tsam yang med par shes nas ched 'dzin gang
NK115(re)001:15604: gang snang gang shar chos sku'i rol pa zhes //
NK115(re)001:15605: bzang rtog gzeb kyang don la mi gnas phyir //
NK115(re)001:15606: ched du 'dzin zhen blang dor med pa'i ngang //
NK115(re)001:15607: ma spangs rang sar grol ba'i tshul gyis spyad //
NK115(re)001:15609: yang sems sder grol tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:15610: klong sder bzhag thabs gtso bor bstan pa yin gsungs pas de ltar na'ang /
NK115(re)001:15611: rnam rtog grol ba dang ngang la 'jog pa'i rtsol
NK115(re)001:15612: ba phra mo de yang man ngag sde pa la
NK115(re)001:15613: med pas khyad par du 'phags pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:15614: gnyis pa lam dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:15615: grol lugs kyi gdeng bshad pa /
NK115(re)001:15617: nyams len gyi gnad bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15618: dang po grol lugs kyi gdeng bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:15619: dgrol gzhi med pa'i go don spyir bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15620: grol tshul so so'i 'thad pa bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15622: de lta bu'i rdzogs chen sde gsum po de dag
NK115(re)001:15623: la nang gses kyi dbye ba mang du snang yang
NK115(re)001:15624: kuna kyang bsdu na klong dgur 'du ba yin te
NK115(re)001:15625: / de yang sems sde rnams ni /
NK115(re)001:15626: chos nyid la brjod du med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15627: lta ba la min pa med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15628: spyod pa la yin pa med pa'i klong gsum du 'dus so //
NK115(re)001:15630: sgom pa la yin pa med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15631: rang bzhin la btsal du med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15632: mtshan nyid la tha dad med pa'i klong gsum du 'dus so //
NK115(re)001:15633: man ngag sde pa thams cad kyang /
NK115(re)001:15634: rol pa 'gag pa med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15635: blo la ma grol ba med pa'i klong dang /
NK115(re)001:15636: ngo bo la bzang ngan med pa'i klong gsum du 'du ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:15637: de thams cad kyis kyang a nu man chad kyi
NK115(re)001:15638: lam 'og ma rnams ltar nyon mongs pa spong bsgyur
NK115(re)001:15639: lam du byed pa sogs ma yin par rang grol
NK115(re)001:15640: du gtong yang / khyad par du man ngag sde
NK115(re)001:15641: pa rnams kyis gdeng grol thog tu bca' ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:15642: du gtong yang / / spyi rig pa bde bar
NK115(re)001:15643: gshegs pa'i snying po'i gnas lugs kyi rang zhal rnam
NK115(re)001:15644: par rtog pas bsgribs te mi mthong ba 'di rang
NK115(re)001:15645: grol gyi gnad la brten nas grol dgos pa yin
NK115(re)001:15646: du gtong yang / / na'ang / gang zhig dgrola
NK115(re)001:15647: bar bya ba'i gzhi ni gang yang meda de dri
NK115(re)001:15648: mas bsgribs pa'i gzhi rig pa'i ngo bo la bya
NK115(re)001:15649: du gtong yang / / na'ang / na / chos
NK115(re)001:15650: nyid byanga chuba semas kyi gshis ni yod de bltar
NK115(re)001:15651: du gtong yang / / na'ang / na / mi mngon / med de rgya ma chad /
NK115(re)001:15652: gnyis ka'i phyogs su ma lhung /
NK115(re)001:15653: dbu mar bzung ba'ang med pas /
NK115(re)001:15658: mtha' dbus sogs las 'das pa'i phyir gang zhig dgrol bar bya /
NK115(re)001:15659: yang dgrol gzhi zhes bya ba sgrib byed kyi dri
NK115(re)001:15660: ma la bya na ni rnam par rtog pa thams
NK115(re)001:15661: cad skyes tsam nyid nas grol bar mi 'gyur ba
NK115(re)001:15662: med cing chos nyid kun tu 'gro ba'i phyir rnam
NK115(re)001:15663: par rtog pa zhes bya ba de yang gzhi ma
NK115(re)001:15664: grub na thabs ganga gisa sgrib pa gang 'grola zhes
NK115(re)001:15665: bya ba yang spangsa pa'i phyir mngon sum pa'i lhag
NK115(re)001:15666: mthong ranga gasla gyi gadngas 'gags pa med par brten
NK115(re)001:15667: pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba meda pa'i rig
NK115(re)001:15668: pa ka dag gi klong na rang gasla ba'i ngang
NK115(re)001:15669: der ma bcos par bzhag na rnam rtog thams cad
NK115(re)001:15670: rang sar zhig ste rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan babs
NK115(re)001:15672: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:15673: ye nas lhun mnyam rig pa byang chub sems //
NK115(re)001:15674: ji bzhin rang babs chos nyid yangs pa ni //
NK115(re)001:15675: rang bzhin chos sku mnyam nyid gdod ma'i klong //
NK115(re)001:15676: kun la yod de skal ldan 'ga' yi yul //
NK115(re)001:15677: ji bzhin bzhag na ngang der babs kyis 'grub //
NK115(re)001:15679: de la gang zag gi blo rim gyi 'jug sgo'i dbang las 'bad bcas dang /
NK115(re)001:15680: 'bad med kyi rang grol gnyis su yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:15681: dang po ni gshis kyi gnas tshul las g.yo ba
NK115(re)001:15682: med pa'i ngang nas nyon mongs pa dang rnam par
NK115(re)001:15683: rtog pa gang skyes kyang rang bzhin shes pa'i lhag
NK115(re)001:15687: rjes su mi 'brang ba nyid du bzhag pas rig
NK115(re)001:15688: pa'i gzhi la de ltar ma grub pa'i phyir chu
NK115(re)001:15689: ma rnyogs par bzhag na dwangs pa ltar 'gyu ba'i
NK115(re)001:15690: cho 'phrul rang bzhin med par dwangs pa yin la
NK115(re)001:15691: / 'bad med ni shar sa dang shar mkhan ro
NK115(re)001:15692: gcig pas chos nyid dang rnam rtog ngo bo dang
NK115(re)001:15693: rtsal snang gnyis su ma grub par shar zhing rang
NK115(re)001:15694: gis rang grol bas gang skyes tshugs mi thub pa'o
NK115(re)001:15695: / // gnyis pa grol tshul so so'i 'thad pa bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15696: mu tig phreng ba las 'gag pa med pa'i rig pa la //
NK115(re)001:15697: 'khrul rgyu med pas ldog pa med //
NK115(re)001:15698: ye grol yin pas gtan nas 'phags //
NK115(re)001:15699: rang grol yin pas yul rkyen zad //
NK115(re)001:15700: cer grol yin pas snang ba dag /
NK115(re)001:15701: mtha' grol yin pas mu bzhi 'gags //
NK115(re)001:15702: gcig grol yin pas du ma stong //
NK115(re)001:15703: zhes rnam grangs lngar bstan pa las /
NK115(re)001:15704: dang po ye grol ni phung po lnga dang tshogs
NK115(re)001:15705: brgyad kyi nyer len sprin dang 'dra ba'i dbus na'ang
NK115(re)001:15706: rig pa nyid nam mkha' ltar rang bzhin med pas
NK115(re)001:15707: srid par kun tu sbyor ba'i skyon de dag gis
NK115(re)001:15708: ma gos shing rang ngo spros pa dang bral bas
NK115(re)001:15709: na phyi nas grol rkyen gyis byas shinga bcosa pa
NK115(re)001:15710: med para dang po nas ye grola du yod pa
NK115(re)001:15711: yina te / mu tig phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:15712: 'bad pas grol ba ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:15713: ye nyid nas ni grol bar gnas //
NK115(re)001:15716: ye nas grol ba'i sems nyid ni //
NK115(re)001:15717: phyi nas grol rkyen ga la srid //
NK115(re)001:15719: des na sems can phal pa rnams ni nga dang
NK115(re)001:15720: nga yir 'dzin pas yid ma myong ba'i 'khrul snang
NK115(re)001:15721: glo bur ba la zhen te bslus pa yin pas
NK115(re)001:15722: rnal 'byor ba rnams kyis rig pa'i ngo bo ye
NK115(re)001:15723: stong rtsa bral ltos gzhi las 'das pa rgyu 'bras
NK115(re)001:15724: rjes med nam mkha' lta bu de'i ngang las rtsal
NK115(re)001:15725: snang ji ltar mched kyang med snang stong pa'i rang
NK115(re)001:15726: gzugs shar grol ris med du dwangs su bcug pa
NK115(re)001:15727: tsam las rnam 'gyur gzhan du song ma myong bar
NK115(re)001:15729: de yang dper na smig rgyu chu nyid du snang
NK115(re)001:15730: ba'i dus chur ye nas med pas chu ma yin
NK115(re)001:15731: par grol zin pa la de ltar shes nas thag
NK115(re)001:15732: chod pa tsam las gzod grol mi dgos pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:15733: no // de ltar yang chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las //
NK115(re)001:15734: mi 'gyur spros dang bral ba'i rig pa la //
NK115(re)001:15735: shar ba ye shar gnas pa ye gnas la //
NK115(re)001:15736: grol ba ye grol nam mkha'i rang bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:15739: gnyen po la ltos bzhag med pa'i don te /
NK115(re)001:15741: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK115(re)001:15743: snang grags kyi chos thams cad rig pa ranga gi
NK115(re)001:15744: rtsal las rang shar zhing shar ba'i dus nyid nas
NK115(re)001:15745: yod med rtag chad las 'das pa'i chos nyid rang
NK115(re)001:15746: la grub zin pas rkyen gzhan gyis grol bas byas
NK115(re)001:15748: rang gis rang la grol ba'i bya ba byas pa
NK115(re)001:15749: yang ma yin par chu klung 'jam po rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:15750: gyis grol bar gnas pa bzhin ranga grola du yod
NK115(re)001:15751: pa la / byis pa rang ga ba rnams ni bdag tu 'dzin pas bcings shing /
NK115(re)001:15752: phung po lnga la stong par lta ba la sogs
NK115(re)001:15753: pa'i bcos ma'i lta sgom spyod pa'i 'du shes skyon
NK115(re)001:15754: can gyis kyang lhad bcug pas chu la dar chags
NK115(re)001:15755: pa ltar rang grol gyi ngo bo la sgrib pas
NK115(re)001:15756: na / dang po nas rang grol gyi gnad mi
NK115(re)001:15757: rtogs pa'i rigs rnams la lta sgom spyod pa'i tha
NK115(re)001:15758: snyad can gyi lam bden 'dus byas kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:15759: can du bstan pa'ang mthar chos sku'i dbyings su rang
NK115(re)001:15760: grol la 'gro dgos pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:15761: des na rang gi ngo bo nyid med pa de
NK115(re)001:15762: nyid rang grol gyi gnas lugs yin pas rnam par
NK115(re)001:15763: rig pa dang bcas pa'i thabs shes sogs lam gyi
NK115(re)001:15764: rkyen gzhan rnams ni de'i ldog phyogs su 'gro 'dogs
NK115(re)001:15765: pa yin pas de la raga ma lusa pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:15766: lam 'dir zhugs pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa rnams
NK115(re)001:15767: kyis rig pa zang ka chos sku'i rang dbyings su
NK115(re)001:15768: ka dag rjen par gnas pa der ngo shes nas
NK115(re)001:15769: rang sa zin na rtsal las shar ba'i rnam rtog
NK115(re)001:15770: thams cad sbrul gyi mdud pa bzhin rang yal rjes
NK115(re)001:15773: mi g.yo mnyam pa chen po'i rig pa la //
NK115(re)001:15774: shar ba'i dus na rang shar rang sa zin //
NK115(re)001:15775: gnas pa'i dus na rang gnas rang sa zin //
NK115(re)001:15776: grol ba'i dus na rang grol rang sa zin /
NK115(re)001:15779: rtag tu rig pa rgyun chad med pa chu bo'i
NK115(re)001:15780: rgyun bzhin yod pa de'i rtsal ma 'gags pa las
NK115(re)001:15781: chags yul lam sdang yul sogs gang yang rung ba
NK115(re)001:15782: zhig mig gis mthong ba'i tshe chags sdang la sogs
NK115(re)001:15783: pa'i rnam rtog 'phro bar rtsom pa na sems kyi
NK115(re)001:15785: mig gi lta stangs thog babs chen po'i gnad kyis
NK115(re)001:15786: gzir te der gcera gyis gtad nas rig thog tu
NK115(re)001:15787: rjen par bzhag pas skad cig dang po la gzugs
NK115(re)001:15789: shes pa yul la ma zhen /
NK115(re)001:15790: snang bas shes pa la ma gos kyang snang yul
NK115(re)001:15791: gang du ma song bzhin shes pa gtan yal du
NK115(re)001:15792: grola ba ni mig gi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen
NK115(re)001:15793: gyis tshor ba mi dmigs pa zhes bya ba yina
NK115(re)001:15794: la / de bzhin du rna bas sgra thos sam /
NK115(re)001:15797: lus kyi reg bya la reg gam /
NK115(re)001:15798: yid kyi sgo lnga'i yul de dag gam /
NK115(re)001:15799: don spyi sogs gang la dmigs pa na chos can
NK115(re)001:15800: khol bu'i snang ba tha dad pa de thams cad
NK115(re)001:15801: la skad cig gis thog babs chen po'i gnad kyis
NK115(re)001:15802: cer grol du gtong ba la goms na mthar gyis
NK115(re)001:15803: snang ba thams cad cer grol du dag pasa yul
NK115(re)001:15804: dang yul can phan tshun ltosa pa'i dbang gis gzung
NK115(re)001:15805: 'dzin du 'brel nas 'khor ba'i bag chags sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:15806: rgyu 'bras kyi gzhi kuna dang brala te shar grol
NK115(re)001:15807: rgyun chad med par shugs kyis 'byung ba ste /
NK115(re)001:15809: thog babs chen po'i sems nyid la //
NK115(re)001:15810: snang ba thad kar rang sar dag /
NK115(re)001:15813: shar gnas grol gsum shar grol rgyun chad med //
NK115(re)001:15814: rgyun chad med pas rgyu 'bras bar ma chod //
NK115(re)001:15815: rgyu 'bras med pas 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chod //
NK115(re)001:15816: g.yang sa med pas gol sa ga la yod //
NK115(re)001:15819: rig pa'i ngo bo skye med kyi cha nas yod mtha' las grol kyang /
NK115(re)001:15820: 'gag med kyi cha nas med mtha' la mi gnas /
NK115(re)001:15821: rgyun mi 'chad pas med mtha' las grol kyang /
NK115(re)001:15822: rtag dngos ma yin pas yod mtha' la mi gnas /
NK115(re)001:15823: rtsal snang sna tshogs su 'char bas gciga pur ma grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:15824: ngo bo spros pa dang bral bas du mara gadgas
NK115(re)001:15825: pa'i matha'a las grola ba'i rang bzhin ni kun tu
NK115(re)001:15826: bzang po ste / stong gsal zang thal bas rdo
NK115(re)001:15827: rje sems dpa'i klong yangs pa de ngo shes pa'i
NK115(re)001:15828: ngang la 'pho 'gyur med par gnas pas phyi yul
NK115(re)001:15830: nang sems la tshur mi rtog /
NK115(re)001:15831: bar skye med la rang sar mi 'jog par rig
NK115(re)001:15832: pa rjen la phud pas sangs rgyas rang las rnyed
NK115(re)001:15833: pa ste / rtsa la rdzogs las /
NK115(re)001:15834: mtha' dang bral bas grol zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:15837: ye nas mi 'gyur kun tu bzang po'i klong //
NK115(re)001:15838: 'pho 'gyur med pas rdo rje sems dpa'i klong //
NK115(re)001:15839: gnas lugs rang ngo shes pa tsam nyid la //
NK115(re)001:15840: sangs rgyas zhes pa ming du btags par zad //
NK115(re)001:15843: bden pa dbyer med kyi rig pa spros bral la gcig dang du ma ma grub kyang /
NK115(re)001:15844: tha snyad du chos sku thig le nyag gcig ces
NK115(re)001:15845: bya bar btags pa'i zang thal gyi ye shes gciga
NK115(re)001:15846: po 'og ma'i lam gyi thabs dang shes rab lta
NK115(re)001:15847: bu'i rkyen la ma ltos par rjen par riga pa'i
NK115(re)001:15848: ngang der ma grola ba'i chos gang yang med pas
NK115(re)001:15849: de'i ngang ma shor na lus kyi 'gro 'dug dang
NK115(re)001:15851: yid kyi bsam rtog thams cad med pa gsal snang
NK115(re)001:15852: tsam las rig pa'i ngo bor ma grub pas matshana
NK115(re)001:15853: nyid med pa ni rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs su
NK115(re)001:15856: thig le nyag gcig spros med de //
NK115(re)001:15857: blo yi bye brag brjod las 'das //
NK115(re)001:15860: ji ltar 'dug kyang rang gi ngang la 'dug /
NK115(re)001:15861: ji ltar gnas kyang rang gi ngang la gnas //
NK115(re)001:15862: ji ltar 'gro yang rang gi ngang la 'gro //
NK115(re)001:15863: byang chub dbyings la 'gro 'ong ngang gis med //
NK115(re)001:15864: 'gro 'ong med pa rgyal ba rnams kyi sku //
NK115(re)001:15865: ji ltar smras kyang rang gi ngang la smra //
NK115(re)001:15866: ji ltar brjod kyang rang gi ngang la brjod //
NK115(re)001:15867: byang chub sems la smra brjod ngang gis med //
NK115(re)001:15868: smra brjod med pa dus gsum rgyal ba'i gsung //
NK115(re)001:15869: ji ltar bsams kyang rang gi ngang la bsam //
NK115(re)001:15870: ji ltar brtags kyang rang gi ngang la rtog /
NK115(re)001:15871: byang chub sems la bsam rtog ye nas med //
NK115(re)001:15872: bsam rtog bral ba dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK115(re)001:15874: de yang don la rig pa'i ngang las ma g.yos
NK115(re)001:15875: pas rig pa 'gro 'ong smra brjod dran rtog thams
NK115(re)001:15876: cad kyi yul las 'das par bzhugs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15877: de ltar rig pa gcig pu'i ngang las ma g.yos
NK115(re)001:15878: na sku gsum gyi dgongs pa yang de las gzhan
NK115(re)001:15879: na med de / de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:15880: med la cir yang 'byung ba sprul pa'i sku //
NK115(re)001:15881: nyid la nyid longs spyod pa longs spyod rdzogs //
NK115(re)001:15882: de la dngos gzhi med pa chos sku ste //
NK115(re)001:15883: 'bras bu sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i klong //
NK115(re)001:15885: de'i phyir gang zag gi dbang po'i rim pas grol
NK115(re)001:15886: lugs snga ma bzhi po'ang mthar thug so so rang
NK115(re)001:15887: gi rig pa'i chos nyid gcig tu grol ba'i mtshan
NK115(re)001:15888: nyid shes na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgya
NK115(re)001:15889: grol ye 'byams chen po'i stong pa nyid du la
NK115(re)001:15891: la bzla ba zhes pa ni shes shing thag chod
NK115(re)001:15892: pa'i don te 'di ltar me gcig gi mtshan nyid
NK115(re)001:15893: shes pa dang / bu ram gcig gi ro shes pas me thams cad tsha ba dang /
NK115(re)001:15894: bu ram thams cad mngar bar shes pa lta bu ste /
NK115(re)001:15896: me yi rang bzhin tsha ba dang //
NK115(re)001:15897: bu ram rang bzhin mngar ba ltar //
NK115(re)001:15898: de bzhin chos rnams thams cad kyang //
NK115(re)001:15899: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gcig /
NK115(re)001:15901: gnyis pa shan 'byed kyi 'phyong bshad pa la bcu ste /
NK115(re)001:15911: dbugs 'byin zhing gi shan 'byed bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:15912: dang po sems rig don gyi shan 'byed bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:15913: ganga daga zhes pa'i 'og tu rtogs pa zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:15914: ma rtogs zhes pa ga nyis la bsnyegs pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:15915: de la semas zhes bya ba ni bag chags sna
NK115(re)001:15916: tshogs pa 'dzin pa'i gsal rig gi shes pa 'dus
NK115(re)001:15918: de las shar ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi rnam pa can te /
NK115(re)001:15919: de yang bzung ba'i sems las gzung yul med pa
NK115(re)001:15920: gsal snang gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lngar snang
NK115(re)001:15921: la / 'dzin pa'i sems las las dang rnam smin
NK115(re)001:15922: nyon mongs pa dpag tu med pa snang bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:15923: la / ro // de lasa 'adsa pa'i riga pa
NK115(re)001:15924: ni stong gsal 'dus ma byas pa nam mkha' lta
NK115(re)001:15925: bu'i ngang na mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK115(re)001:15926: cad rang gdangs 'gag pa med pa'i tshul du gnas
NK115(re)001:15927: la / ro // pa ste / yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:15928: thog ma'i 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po nyid //
NK115(re)001:15929: don gyi kun gzhi rang bzhin 'dus ma byas //
NK115(re)001:15930: ye nas rnam dag nyid mkha' lta bu las //
NK115(re)001:15932: de lta bu'i rig pa car phog tu ngo sprad
NK115(re)001:15933: pa ni ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po'i khyada chosa
NK115(re)001:15934: yina te rig pa'i chos nyid tshul bzhin du rtogsa
NK115(re)001:15935: pa rnamas ni gzhi rig pa'i rtsal lasa rol par
NK115(re)001:15936: shar dus phyi yul du ma dpyad /
NK115(re)001:15937: nang sems su ma bzung bas snang shes kyi 'dzin pa las grol /
NK115(re)001:15939: las dang nyon mongs pa stongs nas 'khor ba'i chos
NK115(re)001:15940: thams cad riga pa rang bzhin med pa'i ngang der
NK115(re)001:15941: grol te / chos nyid zad pa'i sar thug pa
NK115(re)001:15942: na kun tu bzang po'i zhing du phyin te chos
NK115(re)001:15943: sku rgyal po'i gtan srid zin pa zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:15944: grol te / / chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:15945: de tshe mkha' 'dra phyi nang 'khrul pa'i chos //
NK115(re)001:15946: gang yang mi dmigs chos sku'i dgongs par phyin //
NK115(re)001:15947: zad pa'i sar thug 'gro dang 'ong med pas //
NK115(re)001:15948: thams cad klong 'byams kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK115(re)001:15949: chos sku'i pho brang mchog tu phyin pa yin //
NK115(re)001:15951: rig pa'i chos nyid ma rtogsa pa rnams kyis kun
NK115(re)001:15952: gzhi las shar ba'i phyi nang gi dngos po rnams
NK115(re)001:15954: bdag gzhan du bzung bas semas can zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:15955: rig pa'i dbyings de nyid las ma g.yos bzhin kun gzhi'i nganga du 'khora bar 'gyur te /
NK115(re)001:15957: mi shes byis pa'i ngang nyid kyis //
NK115(re)001:15958: nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa bor //
NK115(re)001:15959: yul snang med la snang bar bzung /
NK115(re)001:15960: bdag dang gzhan du med pa la //
NK115(re)001:15961: bdag dang gzhan du 'khrul pas bzung //
NK115(re)001:15963: mdor na rig pa dang sems gnyis po de dpe yi rnama pasa dbye ba phye ste bstan na /
NK115(re)001:15964: 'di ltar rig pa ni ma rig pa tshogs brgyad
NK115(re)001:15965: dang bcas pa'i rlabs kyis rnam par ma dkrugs pa'i
NK115(re)001:15966: chos nyid yangs pa chen po'i rgya mtsho'i chu lta
NK115(re)001:15967: bu yin pas theg pa'i rtse mo a ti yo
NK115(re)001:15968: ga'i lam du zhugs pa rnams kyis de nyid thad
NK115(re)001:15969: drang du skyong shes nas sems rtog chu la ri
NK115(re)001:15970: mo bris pa lta bu'i spang gnyen sna tshogs pa
NK115(re)001:15971: la ltos mi dgos par chos sku'i dgongs pa las
NK115(re)001:15973: nyan thos pa rnams kyis 'khor 'das la skyon yon
NK115(re)001:15974: du bltas nas bden pa bzhi'i blang dor la brtson
NK115(re)001:15975: pa nas / a nu'i lam du bde stong gi
NK115(re)001:15976: rdzogs rim bsgom pa'i bar gyi rim pa brgyad po'i
NK115(re)001:15977: theg pa thams cad du ni /
NK115(re)001:15978: gdod ma nas chos sku'i gshis la grub ma myong
NK115(re)001:15979: ba'i sems rtog glo bur ba chu'i dbu ba'am chu
NK115(re)001:15980: wura bzhina mi rtag cing 'gyur ba'i chos can de
NK115(re)001:15981: lam du byas nas sems kyi dri ma dang bral
NK115(re)001:15982: na chos sku'i ye shes gzod mngon du 'gyur bar
NK115(re)001:15983: 'dod pa gnyis kyi khyad par te /
NK115(re)001:15985: rig pa dang ma rig pa'i dpe ni chu dang ri mo'i tshul te /
NK115(re)001:15987: sems dang rig pa'i dpe ni chu dang dbu ba'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:15988: sems kyi dbang du ma gyur zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:15990: sems dang ye shes dbye ba ni //
NK115(re)001:15991: mkhas pa rnams kyi shes par bya //
NK115(re)001:15992: sems kyi bag chags kun gyi gzhi //
NK115(re)001:15993: lus can rnams kyi dri ma yin //
NK115(re)001:15994: gzung ba yul la 'dzin pa sems //
NK115(re)001:15995: de phyir 'khor ba'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:15996: sems de bral na sangs rgyas sa //
NK115(re)001:15997: lus can kun gyi dri ma zad //
NK115(re)001:15999: de min 'gro bar nus min te //
NK115(re)001:16002: yang mnyam par bzhag pa'i gnas skabs na sems rtog
NK115(re)001:16003: gi 'gyu ba mngon 'gyur ba 'gags nas meda pa
NK115(re)001:16004: tsam du semas rtse gcig tu zin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16005: riga pa yul med du zin pa gnyis mtshungas pa ltar yod na'ang /
NK115(re)001:16006: riga pa yul med du zin pa ni ranga bzhina
NK115(re)001:16007: meda pa'i chos nyid yongs shes kyi ngo bor sems
NK115(re)001:16008: kyi sgrib g.yogs dang bral bar zanga thala du gnas
NK115(re)001:16009: pas lta sgom rgyu 'bras las 'das pa'i phyir de'i
NK115(re)001:16010: ngang la goms na yang srid len pa'i las dang
NK115(re)001:16011: bag chags thams cad zad par 'gyur ba yin la
NK115(re)001:16012: semas ni mi rtog par bzhag pa'i tshe rtse gcig
NK115(re)001:16013: tu zin na'ang gting mtha' dang bral ba'i chos kyi
NK115(re)001:16014: dbyings dang ro gcig tu ma gyur par dmigs pa'i
NK115(re)001:16015: yul bye brag pa gcig la bzung bas rgya chung
NK115(re)001:16016: ba lteng ka'i chu bran lta bura 'khyil zhing ma
NK115(re)001:16017: rig pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi
NK115(re)001:16018: brtod phur bag nyal gyi tshul du yod pas rig
NK115(re)001:16019: pa rang byung gi sgron ma la rmongas nas sgrib
NK115(re)001:16020: par 'gyur te / klong drug pa las /
NK115(re)001:16021: lta ba sems kyi dri ma yin //
NK115(re)001:16022: dri med dag pa'i chos nyid la //
NK115(re)001:16023: blta bya lta byed gnyis dang bral //
NK115(re)001:16024: lta ba nyid la blta ru med //
NK115(re)001:16025: ci phyir blta ba yod gyur na //
NK115(re)001:16026: rig pa'i sgron ma med par 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:16028: gzhan yang dper na riga pa ni rtsal snang yid
NK115(re)001:16029: shes kyi yul la mi 'jug pas so so rang
NK115(re)001:16030: gi rig pa'i ye shes zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:16031: ganma stonga gi zla ba rang 'od phyir mi 'gro
NK115(re)001:16032: bar gting na gasla ba dang 'dra bar rang gnas
NK115(re)001:16033: kyi rig pa'i gsal cha ma 'gags pa la ye
NK115(re)001:16034: shes lnga po lhun grub tu yod kyang yul gyi
NK115(re)001:16035: rang bzhin la dang por mi rtog /
NK115(re)001:16036: rjes su mi dpyod rgyun chags su mi 'dzin pas
NK115(re)001:16037: rang ngo la me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar snang
NK115(re)001:16038: yul thams cad ma 'gags par bkra yang phar yul
NK115(re)001:16040: semas ni kha phyir bltas su yul sna tshogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:16041: rjes su 'brangs nas de dang der 'dzin cing dpyod
NK115(re)001:16042: pas tshes bco lnga'i zla ba rang 'od phyir 'phro
NK115(re)001:16043: te sa gzhi'i bar gyi yula thams cad la khyab
NK115(re)001:16044: cing 'dresa pa dang mtshungas pa des na mngon sum
NK115(re)001:16045: pa'i lhag mthong gsal ba'i cha la ma rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:16046: rnyog pa med pas dwangsa la yula gyi rnam pas
NK115(re)001:16047: gos pa meda pas rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i zhi
NK115(re)001:16048: gnas dang ye nas bcos pa med par zung 'brel
NK115(re)001:16049: du yod pas gzung 'dzin gyi gzhi stongs pa ni
NK115(re)001:16050: riga pa'i yona tan yin te /
NK115(re)001:16051: de las gzhan pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos med la /
NK115(re)001:16052: tshogs drug gi yula dang kuna nasa 'dresa te sems
NK115(re)001:16053: byung dang bcas pa'i rtog pa rags pa du ma
NK115(re)001:16054: mched de dge sdig gi las du ma 'du byed
NK115(re)001:16055: pas srid pa'i rgyu sna tshogs pa sdud par byed
NK115(re)001:16056: pa ni semas kyi khyad par yin la /
NK115(re)001:16057: der ma zad yod med la sogs pa'i spros pa rtog dpyod kyi dpyad rig rnon pos bcad nas /
NK115(re)001:16060: spros pa dang bral lo snyam pa'i nges shes de'i
NK115(re)001:16061: ngang la mnyam par bzhag nas rtse gcig pa'i cha
NK115(re)001:16063: rang bzhin med par dpyod pa'i cha la lhag mthong zhes zung 'jug tu bsgrubs kyang /
NK115(re)001:16064: gzung 'dzin dang bcas pas 'jig rten pa'i bsam gtan
NK115(re)001:16065: las na mi 'phar ba'i phyir thun mong ba'i lam
NK115(re)001:16066: du yang dag pa'i lhag mthong gi rgyu tsam du
NK115(re)001:16067: mi spang mod kyang rig pa lam du byed pa'i
NK115(re)001:16068: lam 'dir ni gol sa yin no //
NK115(re)001:16069: de ltar yang kun byed las /
NK115(re)001:16070: rang byung ye shes yul la mi rtog pas //
NK115(re)001:16071: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags gos mi 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:16073: gnyis pa gnas pa ngo bo'i shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16074: de bzhina du rig pa zang thal du ngos zin
NK115(re)001:16075: pa'i ngang la gnas na de ni ranga gi chos
NK115(re)001:16076: nyid kyi gshis la ye nas gansa pa'i shesa raba
NK115(re)001:16077: bam lhag mthong ste ngo bo bsal bzhag dang bral
NK115(re)001:16078: bas bsam gatana gyi ngang du sems gcur nas 'phro
NK115(re)001:16079: ba dgag pa dang gnas pa sgrub pa sogs kyi
NK115(re)001:16080: thabas la ma ltos par rang bzhin gyis rig pa
NK115(re)001:16081: gsal ba'i ngar dang ldan pas bying ba yang med
NK115(re)001:16082: la 'gyur ba rang grol du dag pas rgoda pa
NK115(re)001:16084: semas lam du byed pa'i bsam gtan ni /
NK115(re)001:16085: lha dang mi rtog pa la sogs dmigas pa'i yula
NK115(re)001:16086: la 'dzin stangs dang bcas pas rtse gciga tu 'jog
NK115(re)001:16087: pa yin pasa / bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzina dang
NK115(re)001:16088: sngar gtan la dbab par byas pa'i lta ba'i don
NK115(re)001:16089: de gnyis yul bsgom bya lta ba'i rang bzhin rten
NK115(re)001:16090: dang yul can sgom byed ting nge 'dzin brten pa
NK115(re)001:16091: lta bur zung du 'brela bas na gzung 'dzin dang
NK115(re)001:16092: bral ba'i rig pa'i sgrib byed du song nas gnas
NK115(re)001:16093: skabs rnam rtog ngal gso ba'i bsti gnas tsam las
NK115(re)001:16095: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:16096: bsam gtan shes gzhi byar med dang //
NK115(re)001:16097: rdzogs chen lhag mthong rig pa gnyis //
NK115(re)001:16100: gsum pa 'phro ba rtsal gyi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16101: riga pa ni yula la shara ba ste thugs rje'i
NK115(re)001:16102: rtsal mdangs ma 'gags par snang ba yin kyang rang
NK115(re)001:16103: ngo dang rtsal shar ba gnyis tha dad du gyes
NK115(re)001:16104: te yul gyi phyi bzhin rtog pa rjes mthud nas
NK115(re)001:16105: rtsa ba ma chod pa ma yin par phyir ma
NK115(re)001:16107: bar du ma bzhag pa'i chos nyid rjen par bud
NK115(re)001:16108: pa las gzhan du mi 'gyur bas 'gyu ba thams
NK115(re)001:16109: cad dngos med rang dag la 'gro ba'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:16110: snanga ba yi chas zila gyis mi nona pa dper
NK115(re)001:16111: na dngula chu sar lhunga ste rdul gyi gseb tu
NK115(re)001:16112: tshud kyang de rdul dang mi 'dre bas de la
NK115(re)001:16113: gos pa med pa dang 'dra ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:16114: semas ni yul snang rig pa la snang dus rang
NK115(re)001:16115: snang rang bzhin med par ngo shes pa'i ngang ma
NK115(re)001:16116: 'khyong nas yul gyi rnam pa la zhen te gzung
NK115(re)001:16117: 'dzina gyi cha dang bacasa pa yi rnama par rtog
NK115(re)001:16118: pa gcig rjes su gcig mthud de gzhi rtsa ma
NK115(re)001:16119: chod par srid pa nye bar lena pa'i phyogsa dang
NK115(re)001:16122: rang rig bsam pa bral ba dang //
NK115(re)001:16123: sems kyi byung tshor sna tshogs gnyis //
NK115(re)001:16125: shes rab rang rtsal rdzogs pa dang //
NK115(re)001:16126: yid kyi dran bsam sna tshogs gnyis //
NK115(re)001:16130: shar grol thugs rje'i cha de lam du mi byed dam zhe na /
NK115(re)001:16131: thugs rje'i cha 'char gzhi'i rig pa zang ma rang
NK115(re)001:16132: mal las ma g.yos pa la zer bas de lam
NK115(re)001:16133: du byed kyi / rtsal las sems su shar zin
NK115(re)001:16134: rtog pa'i cha de rnam pa thams cad nas lam
NK115(re)001:16136: ngo bo rig pa la bzhag dus sems gar dgar
NK115(re)001:16137: rang sangs la bskyur ba yin no zhes yang yang
NK115(re)001:16139: gnad 'di shin tu gal che ste /
NK115(re)001:16140: thun mong gi theg par yang /
NK115(re)001:16142: sems dang yid dang rnam par shes pa dang yang bral la /
NK115(re)001:16143: ting nge 'dzin gyi gnas kyang mi 'dor ba ste
NK115(re)001:16144: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyi
NK115(re)001:16145: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:16147: sems dang sems las byung ba'i spros pa yang rgyud cha da pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16150: sems 'gags pa de sku yis mngon sum mdzad //
NK115(re)001:16152: rgyu mtshan des na chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:16153: deng sang a tir rlom pa'i glang chen dag /
NK115(re)001:16154: 'gyu 'phro'i rtog tshogs byang chub sems yin lo //
NK115(re)001:16155: rmongs pa 'di kun mun pa'i klong nyid du //
NK115(re)001:16156: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don la ring //
NK115(re)001:16157: rtsal dang rtsal las shar ba'ang mi shes na //
NK115(re)001:16158: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo smos ci dgos //
NK115(re)001:16161: deng sang 'ga' zhig gang shar chos sku'i rang bzhin /
NK115(re)001:16162: rtog pa zang ma 'di nyid rang byung gi ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:16164: ting 'dzin yid bzhin ma rig yid //
NK115(re)001:16165: ces pa la sogs pas 'gro ba bslu ba'i bcos ma nye bar ston pas /
NK115(re)001:16166: gzhan la med pa'i zab chos su 'chad pa dag mthong ste /
NK115(re)001:16167: 'di ni theg pa 'adi'o chom rkun pa zhig deng sang byung bar zad mod /
NK115(re)001:16168: 'di ltar rang byung gi ye shes las thugs rje'i rtsal g.yos te /
NK115(re)001:16169: yul la shar ba'i shes pa de nyid la rtsal las shar ba'i rol pa zhes bshad kyi /
NK115(re)001:16170: rang byung gi ye shes ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:16171: yul yod med kyi rjes su byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:16172: thabs kyis ma zin na srid par 'jug pa'i las dang nyon mongs 'du byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:16173: rtog pa dang dpyod pa'i rang bzhin 'khor ba'i rang ngo las ma 'das pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:16175: rang byung ye shes ye nas shes //
NK115(re)001:16176: yul la rtog pa'i ye shes te //
NK115(re)001:16177: yul las byung bas rang byung min //
NK115(re)001:16179: thun mong gi theg par yang /
NK115(re)001:16180: sems dang sems byung khams gsum pa'i //
NK115(re)001:16181: sgro btags rnam pa can rtog yin //
NK115(re)001:16183: rnam rtog ma rig chen po ste //
NK115(re)001:16184: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ltung byed yin //
NK115(re)001:16185: zhes bshad pa dang 'gal ba nyid du snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:16186: phyir log par rtog pa rngam che ba nyid do
NK115(re)001:16187: // 'di lta bu'i 'dod pa thos par yang mi
NK115(re)001:16188: bya na rjes su phyogs pa lta ci smos so
NK115(re)001:16190: 'on kyang zab mo'i nyams len gyi skal ba dman pa bdag lta bus ni /
NK115(re)001:16191: rang gi bla ma dam pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK115(re)001:16192: lan gcig ma yin par yang nas yang du zung 'jug dbu ma chen po dang /
NK115(re)001:16193: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16194: mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim dang /
NK115(re)001:16195: rdzogs pa chen po rnams gnad gcig pa yin pas
NK115(re)001:16196: mdo sngags kyi dngos gzhi'i nyams len thams cad hril
NK115(re)001:16197: gyis dril na zhen med gcig po 'di ka yin
NK115(re)001:16198: pas 'di la blo gtad bcol dgos gsungs kyang /
NK115(re)001:16199: da dung zhen med kyi go ba phyin ci log
NK115(re)001:16200: tu bzung nas rtog ge'i rig pa ngan skyugs dang
NK115(re)001:16201: 'dra bas bslad de rtog pa 'gyus kyang stong par
NK115(re)001:16202: shes na zhen med yin pas ci gnod snyams kyang
NK115(re)001:16204: grol lugs khyad par gnad du che //
NK115(re)001:16206: zhen med yin na gang shar thams cad rang grol
NK115(re)001:16207: du song nas rgyud mi 'ching ba zhig dgos pa
NK115(re)001:16208: la / chags sdang la sogs pa'i rtog pa gang
NK115(re)001:16209: skyes kyang rtsub hrag hrag dam sbrang sbrang du song
NK115(re)001:16210: nas phyi bzhin 'brang dgos pa ni sngar las ma
NK115(re)001:16211: la / 'gyur bar 'dug / yang gsal stong gi
NK115(re)001:16212: ngo bor rtse gcig tu gnas na de zhen med
NK115(re)001:16213: kyi rig pa yin pas de na skyong rgyu zhig
NK115(re)001:16215: gsal ba de yod pa yin pas yod tshul zhig
NK115(re)001:16216: mthong rgyu yod na de nyid skyong dang de ni
NK115(re)001:16218: mi 'dug / stong pa de med pa la zer
NK115(re)001:16219: dgos pas med pa'i thag chod zhig yod na de
NK115(re)001:16220: gar gtod dang der yang thag ma chod pas ji
NK115(re)001:16221: ltar bsam yang rtog ge las ma 'das /
NK115(re)001:16222: ji ltar bzhag kyang gtad so dang bcas pas rang
NK115(re)001:16223: gi log rtog la rang nyid zhe khrel te yi
NK115(re)001:16224: mug nas lan re btab nas tha mal du lus
NK115(re)001:16225: pa 'di ni / kun mkhyen chen pos 'di skad du /
NK115(re)001:16226: a la la 'di'i theg pa dang gzhan la khyad par gnam sa las che ste /
NK115(re)001:16229: da dung chos kyi kha 'dzin tsam las /
NK115(re)001:16230: ngo sprod snga ma'i steng du 'thogs pa rnams la
NK115(re)001:16231: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba snying thig
NK115(re)001:16233: ci byas kyang sangs rgyas la snga 'dris gcig gis
NK115(re)001:16234: nyer ma song ba yi mug la dgod 'chor ba
NK115(re)001:16235: mtshar che'o zhes gsungs pa'i don thog tu babs 'dug
NK115(re)001:16236: par gda' bas / bdag bzhin ha cang rtog ge'i
NK115(re)001:16237: rjes su mi 'brang bar mos gus kyi nye bar
NK115(re)001:16238: len pas bla ma'i man ngag gi bdud rtsis snying
NK115(re)001:16239: sim ste gud yangs la blo bde ba re byung
NK115(re)001:16240: na shin tu skal ba bzang po zhes rang dang
NK115(re)001:16241: skal ba mnyam pa'i chos kyi mched po rnams la
NK115(re)001:16242: rang mtshang bshad pa'i zhor la phan pa'i gros 'debs
NK115(re)001:16244: kye ma kyi hud drin ldan bla ma des //
NK115(re)001:16245: zab don man ngag bdud rtsi mang bstsal kyang //
NK115(re)001:16246: rtog ges myos chu 'thung bas ma ngoms bzhin //
NK115(re)001:16247: chos skal chad pa bdag la mi gzigs sam //
NK115(re)001:16248: bzhi pa grol tshul gnad kyi shan 'byed ni //
NK115(re)001:16249: de la spyir gang zhig grol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:16250: gang gi ngang du grol ba'i sems dang rig pa
NK115(re)001:16251: gnyis po byed las dang ming 'dogs kyi cha nas
NK115(re)001:16252: dbye na / sdud pa chu lta bu'i sems kyis dran bsam gyi gzhi 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:16253: brten pa sa lta bu'i sems kyis tshogs pa sna tshogs sdud /
NK115(re)001:16254: 'phro ba me lta bu'i sems kyis yul la mngon du spyod /
NK115(re)001:16255: yang ba rlung lta bu'i sems kyis kun tu bskyod
NK115(re)001:16256: par byed pas na sems zhes ma rig pa'i bdag
NK115(re)001:16258: skye med kyi gnas lugs rtogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16259: 'gag med kyi dran pa ma nyams pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16260: 'gyur med kyi dpe don 'dres pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16261: rang rdzogs kyi dngos don gang du'ang ma phye ba'i
NK115(re)001:16262: cha nas sems nyid ces rig pa'i bdag nyid can
NK115(re)001:16263: du bzhag go // de bas na 'dir rig pa
NK115(re)001:16264: rjen par rtogs pas dbang po la rno rtul med
NK115(re)001:16265: du bzhag go // pa dang / rig pa de'i
NK115(re)001:16266: rgyun bar ma chad par bskyangs pas rang babs kyi
NK115(re)001:16267: shes rab rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16268: rig gdangs dbang po'i mngon sum par gsal bas rtog dpyod la rag ma lus pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16269: blo dang snyam byed las 'das pa'i rig pa zang
NK115(re)001:16270: thal du rtogs pas thos bsam gyi shes rab la
NK115(re)001:16272: rig pa rkyang par ded pas lta sgom spyod 'bras bcos mar rtogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16273: don de nyid ji lta ba bzhin rang babs lhun
NK115(re)001:16274: grub chen por rtogs pa'i gang zag ni gnyis te
NK115(re)001:16275: / chos nyid dang mthun par bya bral 'bad rtsol
NK115(re)001:16276: zhig pa blo rtse mi rgod cing shugs dal la
NK115(re)001:16277: glen pa'i lhod yod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16278: yang na shes rab shin tu rno bas thos bsam
NK115(re)001:16279: gyi dpyad pa rdzogs nas bcos ma las 'das pa'i
NK115(re)001:16280: lam la nges pa gting nas rnyed nus pa zhig
NK115(re)001:16282: rang bzhin yod med brtag daka'i sems la reg nus min //
NK115(re)001:16283: ma bsam 'khrul pa zhig pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK115(re)001:16284: bya bral glen pa'i shugs 'chang blo bde ba //
NK115(re)001:16285: spros med nam mkha'i yid can rnams kyis byos //
NK115(re)001:16288: yang na ngang ring shugs dal ba //
NK115(re)001:16289: lhug pa glen pa'i lhod yod pa //
NK115(re)001:16290: rtog pa chung zhing rang bzhin dal //
NK115(re)001:16291: lus ngag bya ba bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:16294: de ltar sems dang rig pa gnyis po'i khyad par shes nas /
NK115(re)001:16295: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin sems kyi cha rang grol du
NK115(re)001:16296: dag nas rig pa'i ngo bo mngon du 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:16297: tshul ni / riga pa ni sems kyi chos nyid
NK115(re)001:16298: yin pasa na sems can gyi dus na semas de
NK115(re)001:16299: nyid gazhana du ma spanga par de'i khyab byed du
NK115(re)001:16300: tshul ni / yod kyang / semas ni ma rig
NK115(re)001:16301: pa'i rang bzhin can yin pas des rig pa la
NK115(re)001:16302: tshul ni / yod kyang / ma khyab ste /
NK115(re)001:16303: ma rig pa'i bag chags zad pa'i sangs rgyas la
NK115(re)001:16304: de mi srid pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:16305: gnas skabs rig thog tu gnas pa'i tshe na'ang 'gags
NK115(re)001:16306: par 'gyur ba'i phyir de dang riga pa gnyis snang
NK115(re)001:16307: mun bzhin lhana ciga tu mi 'du bas /
NK115(re)001:16308: bcos ma'i blo yis gtan nas ma bslad par rig
NK115(re)001:16309: pa rjen par ngo 'phrod de de'i ngang la rang
NK115(re)001:16310: babs su gnas pa rgyun bsrings na gzung ba'i yula
NK115(re)001:16311: dang / de 'dzin par byed pa'i rnama para shes
NK115(re)001:16312: pa ma rig pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i shes
NK115(re)001:16313: sgrib kyi rang bzhin can de dang /
NK115(re)001:16314: de nyid ranga dang rdzasa gciga pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16315: de'i rnam par skyes pa'i chags sogs nyon mongsa rnamas
NK115(re)001:16316: kyang lhana ciga ces cig car du phan tshun sbrana
NK115(re)001:16317: nasa te / gcig gis gcig la skad btang ba
NK115(re)001:16318: bzhin du brosa pa ste nam mkhar sprin dengs pa
NK115(re)001:16319: bzhin rang dengs la 'gro ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:16320: de ltar brosa shing 'gags pasa gzung 'dzin gyi rnam
NK115(re)001:16321: par rtog pa dang nyon mongas pa'i btsona ra shin
NK115(re)001:16322: tu brgal dka' ba 'di lasa kyang tshegs med par
NK115(re)001:16323: myur du nges para 'byin par byed pa ni /
NK115(re)001:16324: mana ngaga sde pa yi khyad para gyi chosa yin te /
NK115(re)001:16326: lam 'di las gazhana du gyur pa'i lam rnams ni
NK115(re)001:16327: shin tu zab pa'i man ngag 'di lta bu dang
NK115(re)001:16329: 'di ltar nyon mongas pa'i tshogas thams cad la /
NK115(re)001:16330: nyan thos dang ranga rgyal rnams kyis srid pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:16331: su 'ching bar byed pa'i rtog pa rang gi ngo
NK115(re)001:16332: bo'i rdzas su grub par bltas nas spong ba dang
NK115(re)001:16333: 'gag pa'i thabs su brtson pa la /
NK115(re)001:16334: 'dir ni nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin rig pa'i gshis
NK115(re)001:16335: la yod ma myong bar shes nas de ltar mi
NK115(re)001:16336: spong zhing / byang chub semas dpa' mtshan nyid theg
NK115(re)001:16337: pa ba rnams kyis don dam par rdzas su ma
NK115(re)001:16338: grub par shes kyang tha snyad du gnyen posa 'dula
NK115(re)001:16340: 'dir spang gnyen thams cad rig pa'i cho 'phrul tsam
NK115(re)001:16341: las tha snyad du yang rdzas su med pa'i ngo
NK115(re)001:16342: bor gcig par shes pas de ltar mi 'dul /
NK115(re)001:16343: a nu man chad kyi sngagas spyir nyon mongs rang
NK115(re)001:16344: rgyud pas 'khor bar 'ching zhing thabs kyis zin na
NK115(re)001:16345: lam du 'gyur bar bltas nas lam du gtong bar
NK115(re)001:16346: byed kyang / lam du gtong rgyu'i nyon mongs rang rgyud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16347: gtong byed thabs mkhas gnyis sems rgyud gcig la dus mnyam du ni 'byung mi srid la /
NK115(re)001:16348: mi mnyam na ni des de lam du byed par yang mi rigs pas lam du yang mi byed /
NK115(re)001:16349: semas sdera rtog pa gang skyes thams cad ngos zin
NK115(re)001:16350: nas rig pa'i gshisa thoga tu dgrola bar 'dod kyang
NK115(re)001:16351: / ngos zin mkhan de sems yin dgos na sems kyis sems mi mthong bas de ltar mi dgrol /
NK115(re)001:16352: klonga sdera snang sems thams cad rig pa'i rgyan du
NK115(re)001:16353: bltas nas chosa nyid gciga tu mnyam par bzhag nas
NK115(re)001:16355: rig pa ni ye shes kyi ngo bo yin pas
NK115(re)001:16356: de'i ngang la bzhag pa'i tshe ma rig pa'i sems
NK115(re)001:16357: med pa'i phyir / ye shes kyis sems mi mthong
NK115(re)001:16358: bas de ltar dbyings kyi ngang du 'jog pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:16359: nas dag par byed pa'i rtsol ba yang ma dgos
NK115(re)001:16360: par riga pa'i chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi klonga
NK115(re)001:16361: na chos can ranga ngos nas stong pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16362: chos nyid gzhan ngos nas stong pa'i grub mtha' dang
NK115(re)001:16363: 'dod zhen thams cad tshugsa mi thub par spang gnyen
NK115(re)001:16364: kun rang grol rjes med du zhiga pa ni shin
NK115(re)001:16365: tu ngo matshara bas na lam gzhan las khyad par
NK115(re)001:16367: de lta bu'i man ngag zab mo la brten nas
NK115(re)001:16368: zang thal gyi rig pa mngon sum du rtogs shing
NK115(re)001:16369: tshad du phyin pa'i sngon gyi bla ma dam pa
NK115(re)001:16370: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i brgyud pa 'dzin pa
NK115(re)001:16371: rnams ni 'di ltar yin par gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:16372: yul snang rig ngo la mi 'gag kyang rig pa
NK115(re)001:16373: yul thog tu mi 'dre bas gzung 'dzin 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:16374: chos thams cad chu la ri mo bris pa bzhin
NK115(re)001:16375: rang grol du song bas spang bya'i mtha' zad /
NK115(re)001:16376: yul thog tu ma shor ba'i rig ngo la chags zhen dang /
NK115(re)001:16377: dgag sgrub mi mngon par gnyen po'i 'dzin pa las grol /
NK115(re)001:16378: rig pa chos skur grub pa la chos can gyi
NK115(re)001:16379: gtan tshigs med pas mtha' bral chen po'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:16380: su zang thal / rnam rtog rig par grol bas
NK115(re)001:16381: lta sgom spyod 'bras kyi rdzun phugs rdib nas cho
NK115(re)001:16382: ga dang chos spyod kyis mi gdung yang spros pa
NK115(re)001:16383: med pa'i chos nyid byang chub kyi sems dang mi
NK115(re)001:16384: su zang thal / 'bral / chos brgyad kyi rtog
NK115(re)001:16385: pa med kyang dkon mchog dang las 'bras la gus
NK115(re)001:16386: pa mi lhod pas bya byed thams cad sems can
NK115(re)001:16388: re dogs yul med du sangs kyang khrel yod dang
NK115(re)001:16389: ngo tsha shes pas chags sdang dang tho co'i spyod
NK115(re)001:16391: tha snyad dang grub mtha' la ma sbyangs bzhin rig
NK115(re)001:16392: pa'i rtsal ye shes su rgyas pas tha snyad kyi
NK115(re)001:16393: rnam bzhag kun la ma rmongs kyang nga rgyal dang
NK115(re)001:16394: 'gran sems med / pha rol gyi dgag sgrub la
NK115(re)001:16395: mi 'jigs kyang grub matha'i blo tshod shes pas chos
NK115(re)001:16396: dang gang zag tshad ma la phyogs lhung med /
NK115(re)001:16397: mnyam bzhag la skyong sgom med kyang rjes thob la
NK115(re)001:16398: rig cha yod pas ri sul du mi tshe bskyal
NK115(re)001:16399: ba yin zhes phyi rabs kyis brgyud 'dzin rnams la
NK115(re)001:16400: de 'dra ba dgos pa'i tshul shugs la 'doms par
NK115(re)001:16401: mdzad pa bzhin / da lta rang re'i bla ma
NK115(re)001:16402: rnams kyang de 'dra ba sha stag tu bzhugs pa
NK115(re)001:16403: mngon sum yin na rang cag rnams chos brgyud 'di
NK115(re)001:16404: lta bu la 'jug tu yod pa skal ba re
NK115(re)001:16405: bzang pha rjes bu yis zin pa zhig nges par
NK115(re)001:16406: mdzad pa bzhin / bya dgos / gal te tshe
NK115(re)001:16407: 'dir de tsam ma 'ong yang lta sgom la drod
NK115(re)001:16409: spyod pa chos dang mthun pa sogs rjes su mthun
NK115(re)001:16410: pa tsam zhig ni 'chi kha tshun la ma 'ong
NK115(re)001:16411: thabs med yin no snyam du snying la dam baca'i
NK115(re)001:16412: ri mo rdo la bris pa lta bu zhig dgos
NK115(re)001:16413: gsungs // lnga pa kun gzhi dang chos sku'i shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16414: sems dang rig pa'i khyad par dbye ba de bzhina du /
NK115(re)001:16415: de gnyis kyi spyi'i rang bzhin kuna gzhi dang ni
NK115(re)001:16416: chosa sku gnyis kyi dbye ba ji ltar phye na
NK115(re)001:16417: lhun grub kyi rtsal snang rig thog tu ma grol
NK115(re)001:16418: zhing ma rig pa'i gzhan dbang du gyur nas sems
NK115(re)001:16419: dang sems byung gi rang bzhin snang ba du ma'i
NK115(re)001:16420: gzhi / khams gsum pa'i bag chags thams cad thog mar 'jog pa'i rten /
NK115(re)001:16422: tha ma smin pa'i snod du gyur pa'i cha la kun gzhi zhes bya /
NK115(re)001:16423: yang ma rig pa'i gzhan dbang du ma gyur pa'i
NK115(re)001:16424: ye shes kyi rten chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo
NK115(re)001:16425: gzung 'dzin dang lhan cig mi gnas pa /
NK115(re)001:16426: las dang bag chags kyis ma sbags pa'i cha ni chos sku yin te /
NK115(re)001:16429: sems kyi gnas ni kun gzhi yin no //
NK115(re)001:16431: kun gzhi ni bsam pa'i yul thams cad sdud cing sems su shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:16432: ye shes kyi gnas ni chos sku yin no //
NK115(re)001:16434: chos sku ni dran rtog thams cad mi mnga' zhing
NK115(re)001:16435: yul tha dad du 'dzin pa'i shes pa med pa'i
NK115(re)001:16437: de yang dpe'i sgo nas dbye na dgongs pa zang thal gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:16438: kun gyi gzhi ni 'dus ma byas //
NK115(re)001:16439: rang byung klong yangs brjod du med //
NK115(re)001:16441: de nyid rig na sangs rgyas te //
NK115(re)001:16443: zhes gsungs pa ltar rig pa 'dus ma byas pa'i dbyingas su tha dad pa med pas gciga kyang /
NK115(re)001:16444: chosa sku ni ka dag spros bral gyi rig pa
NK115(re)001:16445: rang bzhin gang du'ang ma grub la sna tshogs su
NK115(re)001:16446: 'char ba'i go ma 'gags kyang glo bur gyi dri
NK115(re)001:16447: mas ma bslad cing rgya tshad dang bral bas rgya
NK115(re)001:16449: kuna gzhi'i rnama shesa ni rtsal snang lhun grub kyi
NK115(re)001:16450: rig cha ldog pa las byung ba'i ma rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:16451: rang bzhin chos sku de yi don la sgriba par
NK115(re)001:16452: byed pa'i cha sems dang sems byung gis bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:16453: 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad dang por byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:16455: bar du khyab byed dang ngo bor gnas pa ste
NK115(re)001:16456: gru lta bu'i nang du lus dang bag chags kyis
NK115(re)001:16457: sprul pa'i rnam par shes pa tshogs bdun gyi byed
NK115(re)001:16458: las can mi du mas gang pa bzhina du 'khora
NK115(re)001:16459: ba'i bag chags smin pas rigs drug gi snang ba
NK115(re)001:16461: lam gyi bag chags goms pas nyan rang rnams zhi
NK115(re)001:16462: ba phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'adsa thob kyang kun gzhi
NK115(re)001:16463: las ma 'das pas gnyis kara ldinga zhes pa'am /
NK115(re)001:16464: yang na 'das pa ni glo bur gyi ma rig
NK115(re)001:16465: pa dang lhan cig pa'i kun gzhi ldog pas gru
NK115(re)001:16466: gzings skam la phyin pa ltar chos sku'i sgrib byed
NK115(re)001:16467: sangs pas dag pa gnyis ldan mngon du gyur pa'o
NK115(re)001:16470: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi /
NK115(re)001:16471: bag chags lus kyi kun gzhi /
NK115(re)001:16472: bag chags sna tshogs pa'i kun gzhi dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK115(re)001:16473: dang po ni dbyings de'i ngang nas dpyod byed thog
NK115(re)001:16474: ma'i 'gyu ba rig pa la ltos pa'i ma rig
NK115(re)001:16475: pa mtshungs ldan gyis 'khor ba'i go 'byed pa'i cha
NK115(re)001:16476: nas brjod pa'o // gnyis pa ni dpyod byed kyi
NK115(re)001:16477: shes pa de nyid rang ma rig pa kha phyir
NK115(re)001:16479: rang gi rang bzhin rig pa las myang 'das su sbyor ba'o //
NK115(re)001:16480: gsum pa ni de nyid la lus kyi bag chags
NK115(re)001:16481: yod pas 'byung bzhi rags pa'i lus dang yid lus
NK115(re)001:16482: sogs snang ba'i rten byed pa'i cha nas brjod pa'o
NK115(re)001:16483: // bzhi pa ni de nyid kyis sems kyi bag chags sna tshogs bstan pa'i cha nas brjod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:16485: kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin te //
NK115(re)001:16486: myang ngan 'das pa'i gzhi ma'ang yin //
NK115(re)001:16487: zhes gsungs pas kun gzhi chos skur 'dod pa ni ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:16488: skabs 'ga' rer chos sku la kun gzhi'i ming gis brjod pa yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:16489: de ni 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi gzhi yin pa
NK115(re)001:16490: la brjod kyi bag chags 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi dang
NK115(re)001:16491: gcig tu bshad pa min no //
NK115(re)001:16492: chos sku ni ngo bo stong pa ye shes kyi snying po /
NK115(re)001:16493: rang bzhin gsal ba 'od kyi snying po /
NK115(re)001:16494: thugs rje 'gag med rig pa'i snying po can yin
NK115(re)001:16495: pas sems kyi sgrib pas de'i rang bzhin la gos
NK115(re)001:16496: ma myong ba'o // de yang ming gi sgo nas chos sku dang byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK115(re)001:16497: rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:16498: dbyings lhun grub chen po la sogs pa'i brdar btags
NK115(re)001:16499: kyang 'dogs byed de nyid rnam rtog yin pas rang
NK115(re)001:16500: ngo brjod med blo 'das spros bral nyag gcig tu
NK115(re)001:16501: ston pas chos sku'i gnas lugs rdzogs pa chen po
NK115(re)001:16502: zhes bya ste grub matha'i blos btags pa'i gsal rig
NK115(re)001:16503: dang / stong pa sogs dang mi mtshungs pas gsal
NK115(re)001:16504: stong la sogs pa'i mthar bzung na gol bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:16505: dang / ro // de'i ngo bo yang thog ma'i
NK115(re)001:16506: ka dag gi gzhi la gnas tshul gyi cha nas
NK115(re)001:16507: mtshan nyid rnam pa gsum du bzhag la /
NK115(re)001:16508: 'khrul pa'i yul la gnas tshul gyi cha nas de'i
NK115(re)001:16509: gdangs la gzhig pas blo dngos spros bral nyag gcig
NK115(re)001:16510: tu rtogs pa'i nyams myong cha dang bcas pas thog
NK115(re)001:16511: bzhag rang grol du rgyas gdab pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16513: bzhugs tshul gnas lugs rnam pa gnyis //
NK115(re)001:16514: thog ma'i gzhi la gnas pa dang //
NK115(re)001:16516: thog ma'i ngo bo rang bzhin dang //
NK115(re)001:16517: thugs rje rnam pa gsum du gnas //
NK115(re)001:16519: 'khrul pa'i yul la rang bzhag dang //
NK115(re)001:16520: cog bzhag rang grol rgyas gdab bo //
NK115(re)001:16522: de'ang gzhi ka dag gi ngos na skur med kyang
NK115(re)001:16523: thod rgal gyi gnad la brten nas sku gsum lam
NK115(re)001:16524: snang du shar ba la gsum mtshan gsum du dabye'o
NK115(re)001:16525: // mdor na sems dang ye shes gnyis rten kun
NK115(re)001:16526: gzhi chos sku dang bcas pa'i dbye ba phye shes
NK115(re)001:16527: nas sems las 'das pa'i ye shes lam du byed
NK115(re)001:16528: pa ni theg pa'i rgyal po 'di'i khyad chos yin
NK115(re)001:16529: // pas / theg pa 'og mas tha snyad kun
NK115(re)001:16530: rdzob pa'i sems lam du byed pa la brten nas
NK115(re)001:16531: gzod thabs de las byung ba'i don dam pa'i de
NK115(re)001:16532: kho na nyid rtogs dgos par 'dod pa dang mi
NK115(re)001:16533: 'dra ba'i khyad par shes pa ni gal che'o //
NK115(re)001:16534: drug pa 'khrul grol skabs kyi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16535: de la spyir sems kyi rang bzhin spros pa thams
NK115(re)001:16536: cad dang bral ba'i rig pa 'od gsal ba'i ye
NK115(re)001:16537: shes rang gi ngo bo na 'khrul grol gnyis ka
NK115(re)001:16538: med de / de ci'i phyir na //
NK115(re)001:16539: 'khrul pa med na der ltos kyi grol ba'ang yod par mi 'gyur ba la /
NK115(re)001:16540: 'khrul pa ni med de bshad zin ltar tshogs brgyad
NK115(re)001:16541: yul dang bcas pa med snang nyag gcig yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:16542: phyir ro // tshogs brgyad char med na sems gtan
NK115(re)001:16543: nas med pas sangs rgyas pa'i tshe bem po lta
NK115(re)001:16545: sems med kyang gzhi'i gnas lugs ni sems nyid 'od
NK115(re)001:16546: gsal ba'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir de nyid yod
NK115(re)001:16547: de / 'phags pa brgyad stong pa las /
NK115(re)001:16548: sems la sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'o zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:16550: sems de rang bzhin 'od gsal bas na nyon mongs ngo bo med gzigs pas /
NK115(re)001:16552: 'o na 'khrul grol ltar snang ba 'di ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK115(re)001:16553: ka dag gi rig pa spros pa dang bral ba
NK115(re)001:16554: nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nasa ma g.yos bzhin du
NK115(re)001:16555: sprin gyi skye 'gags ltar lhun grub kyi rtsal snang
NK115(re)001:16556: shar ba ngo ma shes shing der zhen pas yod
NK115(re)001:16557: pa chos nyid kyi don ni ma mthong /
NK115(re)001:16558: med pa 'khor ba'i 'khrula snang thams cad rgyun mi 'chad par snang ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:16560: gang zhig yod pa mi mthong med mthong ba //
NK115(re)001:16561: 'di 'dra'i mun nag rnam pa de gang zhig /
NK115(re)001:16563: gzhi snang de ngo shes shing ma zhen na 'khrul
NK115(re)001:16564: pa'i cha thams cad dbyings su ldog te gshis kyi
NK115(re)001:16565: bzhugs tshul ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa ni grola
NK115(re)001:16566: ba mya ngan las 'das pa ste chosa de gnyis
NK115(re)001:16567: ka'i mtshan nyid kyi khyad kyang dper na rmi lam
NK115(re)001:16568: sna tshogs 'char ba'i rten gnyid du song ba dang
NK115(re)001:16569: rmi lam gyi snang ba rgyun chad nas gnyid de
NK115(re)001:16570: las sada pa'i gnas skabs bzhina te /
NK115(re)001:16571: 'di ltar kun gzhi'i ngang du 'khrula ba na ye
NK115(re)001:16572: shes kyi mkhyen cha ma rig pas sgrib pa ni
NK115(re)001:16573: sgo lnga'i dabnga po nang du sdud de nyamsa pa'i
NK115(re)001:16574: gnyid stug gi gnas skabs lta bu yin la /
NK115(re)001:16575: med snang gi dngos po sna tshogs pa la spyod pa ni rmi lam gyi skabs bzhina no //
NK115(re)001:16576: sgrib pa las grola ba chos sku'i ngo bo mngon
NK115(re)001:16577: du gyur pa'i dag pa gnyis ldan ni 'khrul snang
NK115(re)001:16578: rgyun chad de mkhyen pa'i rtsal rgyas nas shes bya
NK115(re)001:16579: thams cad mngon sum du gyur pa yin pas /
NK115(re)001:16580: gnyid de lasa sada pa'i tshe sgo lnga'i rang yul mngon sum du mthong ba'i gansa skabas dang 'dra'o //
NK115(re)001:16581: bdun pa gzhi 'bras lhun grub kyi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16582: thoga ma 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma phye ba'i gnas
NK115(re)001:16583: skabs na grol 'khrul gang gi rgyur ngesa pa meda
NK115(re)001:16584: pa'i gzhi yi rig pa ka dag gi ngang na
NK115(re)001:16585: lhuna gruba kyi gdangs 'gag pa med par yod pa
NK115(re)001:16586: de dang / lam mathara phyin pa'i tshe na gzhi
NK115(re)001:16587: snang phyir gsal gyi cha mkha' la sprin dengs pa
NK115(re)001:16588: bzhin dbyings su ldog ste khyad chos drug gis grola
NK115(re)001:16589: sa'i ka daga glo bur gyi dri ma dang brala
NK115(re)001:16591: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK115(re)001:16592: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:16593: zhes pa ltar rang bzhin gsum ldan gyi dbyings kyi
NK115(re)001:16594: ngo bo la 'pho 'gyur dang tha dad med pas
NK115(re)001:16595: rdzasa su gciga ces pa'i tha snyad 'dogs chog kyang
NK115(re)001:16596: / thog ma'i lhun grub ni 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i
NK115(re)001:16597: 'char gzhi yin pas slada kyi 'khrula pa'i gzhi yang
NK115(re)001:16598: / byed la / grol sa ni de dang mi
NK115(re)001:16599: 'dra ste dbyings kyi yon tan mthar phyin pas sku
NK115(re)001:16600: gsum gyi snang cha ma 'gags par yod kyang ma
NK115(re)001:16601: rig pa med pas 'khrul pa'i gzhi mi byed pas
NK115(re)001:16602: de gnyis kyi khyad para phyed shesa pa ni gcesa
NK115(re)001:16603: te gzhi zhes pa'i tha snyad 'dogs yul mgo nas
NK115(re)001:16604: 'bras bu thob tshe gzhi thog tu grol zer ba
NK115(re)001:16605: ni rdzogs pa chen po'i gzugs brnyan tsam yin no
NK115(re)001:16606: / byed la / gsungs // brgyad pa lam 'bras ka dag gi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16607: tshul de bzhina du dbyingsa kyi yon tan mthar phyin
NK115(re)001:16608: pa'i grola sa yi ka daga nang gsal gyi ye
NK115(re)001:16609: shes de dang / da lta'i lam gyi gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:16610: na riga pa ka daga gi ngo bo spros pa
NK115(re)001:16611: thams cad dang bral ba'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK115(re)001:16612: shes de dang / pa gnyis kyang / gnyis snang
NK115(re)001:16613: dbyings su nub nas rang bzhin spros pa dang bral
NK115(re)001:16614: bas rgya gar yang ma chada cing snang stong la
NK115(re)001:16615: sogs pa'i phyogsa su lhung ba meda para mnyam pa
NK115(re)001:16616: tsam du yod pa yin na'ang /
NK115(re)001:16617: grola sa ka dag gi dbyings nyid ni ma dag
NK115(re)001:16618: pa'i rlunga semas bag chags kyi cha dang bacasa pa
NK115(re)001:16619: rnama para byang zhing dag par gyur pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:16620: 'khora ba'i 'khrul snang med par ma zad ye shes
NK115(re)001:16621: phyir gsal gyi cha yang dbyings su thim nas nang
NK115(re)001:16622: gsal gyi ye shes shin tu phra ba gzhon nu
NK115(re)001:16623: bum pa'i sku'i gnas skabs yin pas mya ngan las
NK115(re)001:16624: 'adsa pa'i snang ba yang med par ka daga gi
NK115(re)001:16625: rig pa chos sku'i ngang du 'pho 'gyur med par
NK115(re)001:16626: rtag tu mnyam par bzhag pa las mi g.yo ba
NK115(re)001:16627: ste phyir mi ldog pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:16628: yang na 'khor 'das ka dag zhes pa chos sku'i
NK115(re)001:16629: dgongs pa mngon du gyur pas 'khora ba'i mtha' la
NK115(re)001:16630: mi gnas shing lhun grub kyi rang gdangs 'gag pa
NK115(re)001:16631: med par gzugs sku gnyis kyi 'char gzhir yod pas
NK115(re)001:16632: mya ngan las 'adsa pa'i mtha' la mi gnas pa'i
NK115(re)001:16633: dbyings ka daga ste zhes 'grel kyang rung ste don
NK115(re)001:16634: la 'dra'o // lam dusa su ni rlunga semas ma
NK115(re)001:16635: daga pa'i cha gtan zad du ma song ba'i 'khrul
NK115(re)001:16636: rkyen dabnga po dang yul la sogs pa dang 'grogas
NK115(re)001:16637: shinga rig pa'i sgrib byed semas dang semsa byung gi
NK115(re)001:16638: dri ma'i chasa rig rtsal la bslad cing khura basa
NK115(re)001:16639: rig pa ka dag gi dbyings la gnyis snang nub
NK115(re)001:16640: pa'i tshul gyis dngosa su gansa pa ni resa 'ag'a
NK115(re)001:16641: la 'dra'o // tsam la / res 'ga' ni 'khrul 'byams su 'gro ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:16642: de yang shes rab rang rtsal du rdzogs pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:16643: na rig pa spros bral du shes byed de nyid
NK115(re)001:16644: kyang thad kar zang thal du zhig nas nang du
NK115(re)001:16645: mi 'dzin / phyir mi bzung phan tshun ltos grub
NK115(re)001:16646: can du mi gnas kyang rig cha de rlung sems
NK115(re)001:16647: kyi chas khur ba'i tshe rang ngo las ma g.yos
NK115(re)001:16648: par bzhag na de dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge
NK115(re)001:16649: 'dzin dang mtshungs pas lam gyi gegs mi byed kyang
NK115(re)001:16650: rtog pa'i cha de nyid kyis phyi rol du yul
NK115(re)001:16651: mi 'dzin / dang / nang du sems kyi tshogs
NK115(re)001:16652: pa sbrel nas gzung 'dzin gyi 'dra 'bag tsam du
NK115(re)001:16653: snang bas chos nyid zad pa'i bar du 'gag mi
NK115(re)001:16654: shes pa 'di nyams myong gi thog nas bshad par
NK115(re)001:16655: rig par bya'o zhes rang gi 'grel par gsungs pas
NK115(re)001:16656: sangs ma rgyas kyi bar du rtag par mnyam rjes
NK115(re)001:16657: dbyer med du 'dres pa med pas gnyis snang phra
NK115(re)001:16659: gzhi'i gnas lugs mthong tshul gyi khyad par ni /
NK115(re)001:16660: theg pa 'og ma'i grub mtha' 'dzin pa rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:16661: bdag med dang spros bral sogs su dpyad pa'i don
NK115(re)001:16663: bya rog gis zan sa khung du sbas nas tshad
NK115(re)001:16664: sprin la byed pa ltar don dngos gnas pa'i thog
NK115(re)001:16666: 'dir ni mngon gsum yid dpyod dang bral bar rtogs pas khyad par 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:16668: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po 'di'i lugs kyis mtha'
NK115(re)001:16669: bral la sogs pa'i 'jal tshul phal cher dbu ma
NK115(re)001:16670: thal 'gyur ba dang mtshungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:16671: dbu mar stong stong po nam mkha' dang 'dra bar rtsis gzhir byed pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16672: 'dir rig pa ka nas dag pa rjen zang nge
NK115(re)001:16673: ba ma grub la mi 'gag pa tsam de la
NK115(re)001:16674: gzhir byas nas de'i ngang las shar ba'i chos rnams
NK115(re)001:16675: mtha' grol nam mkha' ltar 'jal ba ste /
NK115(re)001:16677: rang sde rnams kyis kyang dpe don rtags gsum gyis gzhal tshul tsam 'dra yang /
NK115(re)001:16678: 'dir dpyod ldan gyis rten gsum gzhal ba'i tshe so
NK115(re)001:16679: sor sgro 'dogs chod pa ltar dngos dang gzhi gnyis
NK115(re)001:16680: ka'i mtshan nyid gtan la phebs la /
NK115(re)001:16681: gzhan du ni byis pas lha khang la bltas na
NK115(re)001:16682: rten gsum mthong yang so sor sgro 'dogs chod pa
NK115(re)001:16683: mi shes pa ltar gzhi'i ngo bo tsam mthong yang
NK115(re)001:16684: dngos gnas ji bzhin par gtan la ma phebs pa'i
NK115(re)001:16686: dgu pa bar do lha yi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16687: de bzhina du da lta lam 'dir zhugs nas nyams
NK115(re)001:16688: len la brtson zhing khyad par lhun grub thod rgal
