NK115(re)001:16689: gyi nyams len la goms pa brtan pa rnams bar
NK115(re)001:16690: do dang por ma grol kyang chosa nyid bar dora
NK115(re)001:16691: gzhi la lhun grub tu yod pa'i riga gadngas lhun
NK115(re)001:16692: grub chen po'i snang ba sogs bsam gtan gyi zhag
NK115(re)001:16693: gi grangs su rim gyis 'char ba dang /
NK115(re)001:16694: yang da lta rtog pa dang bcas pas rdzogs rim
NK115(re)001:16695: gyi lha sku sgyu ma lta bu la bslab cing
NK115(re)001:16696: de nyid mi rtog par bsdu ba la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:16697: bsre 'pho la gomas pa'i stobs kyis srid pa bar
NK115(re)001:16698: dor lha yi sku sgyu ma lta bur ldang nus
NK115(re)001:16699: pa'i sgyu lusa gnyis po bar dor lha skura snang
NK115(re)001:16701: snang ba zhing khamas su shar ba de gnyis las
NK115(re)001:16702: snga ma ni 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:16703: rang gdangs rtsol med du shar ba yin pas rgya
NK115(re)001:16704: che zhing rang snang du ngo shesa pa tsam gyis
NK115(re)001:16705: dbyings thoga tu grola bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK115(re)001:16706: phyi ma ni bag chags bzang goms rlung sems kyi
NK115(re)001:16707: rtsal las snang ba yin pas rgya chung zhing da
NK115(re)001:16708: dung lam gyi lhag ma ma bgrod par mi grol
NK115(re)001:16709: ba'i khyad par yod pa'ang shes dgos te /
NK115(re)001:16710: rang lam gyi khyad chos shes na sgom pa la spro ba skye ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:16711: bcu pa dbugs 'byin zhing gi shan 'byed ni /
NK115(re)001:16712: khyad para du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam
NK115(re)001:16713: 'dira zhugs pa'i gang zag rnams ni lam gyi sbyangs
NK115(re)001:16714: bgrod mthar ma phyin kyang nyin mtshan 'od gsal gyi
NK115(re)001:16715: rnam 'byor la cung zad goms shing mos gus dang
NK115(re)001:16716: ldan la dama tshiga rnam par dag pa bsrung ba'i
NK115(re)001:16717: skal ba cana zhig yin na gzhan las lhag ste
NK115(re)001:16718: / theg pa 'og ma'i lam la zhugs pa rnams
NK115(re)001:16719: kyis grangs med la sogs pa'i yun ring por tshegs
NK115(re)001:16720: chen pos rim gyis rgyud sbyangs pa'i mthar 'das lam
NK115(re)001:16721: mngon du gyur pa'i tshe sa dang po nas bcu
NK115(re)001:16722: pa'i bar gyi rang rang gi snanga basa bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:16723: sangs rgyas longas spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhing khams dang
NK115(re)001:16725: rang lam de tshe gcig la sogs pa yun thung
NK115(re)001:16726: ngur sbyang ba tsam gyis thod rgal du bgrod pa
NK115(re)001:16727: ni med do // gang zag snga ma ni de
NK115(re)001:16728: lta bu'i dbyings kyi longs sku de mthong ba la'ang
NK115(re)001:16729: de 'dra'i yun ring por 'thogsa pa ma yina te
NK115(re)001:16730: ni med do // / longs sku de yi dpe
NK115(re)001:16731: byad ni me long du shar ba ltar rang snang
NK115(re)001:16732: lhun grub kyi sgo las sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes
NK115(re)001:16733: ranga bzhina sprul pa'i zhing lngar bkoda pa la tshe
NK115(re)001:16734: 'di barjesa ma thag tu srid pa bar do la
NK115(re)001:16735: chos nyid kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyi mthus rmi
NK115(re)001:16736: lam sad pa'i tshul gyis myur du 'gro ste /
NK115(re)001:16738: snyigs ma lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK115(re)001:16739: gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni mi yul snang //
NK115(re)001:16740: de rjes 'dzin pa'i gang zag skal ba can //
NK115(re)001:16741: snying po 'di ni su la snang gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:16742: de dag rnams ni mi 'gyur sa la 'da' //
NK115(re)001:16743: gal te snyigs ma tshe thung nad mang bas //
NK115(re)001:16744: snying po don 'di gdeg du ma gyur kyang //
NK115(re)001:16745: 'di nyid mthong bas dbugs chen nyid 'byin pa //
NK115(re)001:16746: bcu gcig kun tu 'od de sprul pa'i zhing //
NK115(re)001:16747: bardzusa skyes dag pas mngal gyi rgya dang bral //
NK115(re)001:16749: mdor na rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs ni rig
NK115(re)001:16750: pa rang gnas kyi bsam gtan yin pas chos nyid
NK115(re)001:16751: kyi rlan dang mi bral la /
NK115(re)001:16752: gzhan du ni rtsa rlung gis gcud pa'i sgom yin pas rtsol ba'i rkyen kha na yod do //
NK115(re)001:16753: de bzhin du thod rgal gyi dus na rig pa
NK115(re)001:16754: skur smin pa la sogs pas ni lam snang du
NK115(re)001:16756: rtog bcas goms pa'i lha skus ni rdzogs rim gyi smin byed dam /
NK115(re)001:16757: 'dod gzugs kyi lha dang rjes su mthun pa'i lus
NK115(re)001:16758: kyis mkha' spyod du grub mtha' snyogs pa tsam las
NK115(re)001:16759: med do // yang 'od gsal ye gdangs kyi thig le ni /
NK115(re)001:16760: dbyings rig gi snang ba yin pas srog rtsol gyi
NK115(re)001:16761: rkyen la ma ltos pa'i snang nyams mngon sum pa'i
NK115(re)001:16762: chos nyid yid dpyod dang bral ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:16765: gsang 'dus kyi phra tig la sogs pa'i stong gzugs
NK115(re)001:16766: ni rtsa rlung gi byed pa bcings pa las byung
NK115(re)001:16767: zhing shes bya'i nyams 'phel 'grib can du ma zad
NK115(re)001:16768: / snying thig ltar phyi nang gi 'byung ba dbyings
NK115(re)001:16769: su dengs pas rdo rje'i sku bsgrub mi nus so
NK115(re)001:16770: / // gsums pa nyams len gyi gnas bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:16771: rig pa rang snang gi blo can gyi nyams len bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16772: snang ba yul gyi blo can gyi nyams len bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:16773: dang po rig pa rang snang gi blo can gyi nyams len bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:16774: ka dag khregs chod kyi lam bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16775: lhun grub thod rgal gyi khyad par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:16776: dang po ka dag khregs chod kyi lam bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:16777: lta ba grong khyer rgyun gcod /
NK115(re)001:16779: spyod pa snang ba dbang bsgyur /
NK115(re)001:16780: 'bras bu rtsol med yongs grub bo //
NK115(re)001:16781: dang po lta ba grong khyer rgyun gcod ni /
NK115(re)001:16782: khyad chos dang ldan pa de yi phyir na /
NK115(re)001:16783: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam 'di ni gsang
NK115(re)001:16784: sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam thams cad kyii nang
NK115(re)001:16785: nas kyang mchoga tu gyur pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16786: theg pa'i rgyal po 'di'i lta ba ni /
NK115(re)001:16787: rang bzhin gshis kyi bzhugs tshul ji lta ba bzhin mngon sum gyi tshul du rtogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16788: de yang sngon chad bsdams pa las phyi nas grol
NK115(re)001:16789: ba lta bu ma yin par gdoda ma nasa gzung
NK115(re)001:16790: 'dzin glo bur gyi dri mas gshis la gos ma
NK115(re)001:16791: myong zhing / rnam par grol ba'i riga pa ka
NK115(re)001:16792: daga gi ngo bo ni rnam thar sgo gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:16793: rang bzhin du gnas pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:16794: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang
NK115(re)001:16795: bral ba'i zang thal rjen pa'i rig pa rang gi
NK115(re)001:16796: ngo bo ni / ye nas stong zhing 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:16797: ba spros ba thams cad dang bral bas ngo bo
NK115(re)001:16798: ngo bo ni / nyid med pa / bdag rtog
NK115(re)001:16799: gi yul las 'das shing tha snyad kyis mtshon du
NK115(re)001:16800: med pa'i phyir bsam brjod las 'adsa pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16802: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni brda tsam btags pa tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:16803: brda tsam btags pa tsam gang yin pa de ni
NK115(re)001:16804: glo bur ba ste ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa
NK115(re)001:16805: yin no // zhes pa lta bu'i don de ni
NK115(re)001:16806: chos sku rang babs kyi dgongs pa rnam par thar
NK115(re)001:16807: pa'i sgo stong pa nyid yin te /
NK115(re)001:16809: stong gsal rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK115(re)001:16810: chos sku rtog med zang thal nyid //
NK115(re)001:16811: 'dzin pa bcos ma'i mtha' dang bral //
NK115(re)001:16812: mtha' bral chos la zhe 'dod med //
NK115(re)001:16814: rig pa de yi rang bzhin gsal ba'i cha la
NK115(re)001:16815: snang yul ma 'gags par shar yang matshana nyid 'di
NK115(re)001:16816: lta bu'o zhes ngos gzung dang bral ba'i phyir gzung
NK115(re)001:16817: 'dzin dang bcas pa'i blo yi brjod pasa mtshon du
NK115(re)001:16818: med pas thug pa spangas pa ste de ni rang
NK115(re)001:16819: gsal longs sku'i dgongs pa rnam par thar pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:16822: longs sku'i ye shes rgya che rnam par rol //
NK115(re)001:16823: rang gsal bya byed med par lhun grub yin //
NK115(re)001:16825: rig pa rang gnas kyi ngang las thugs rje'i rtsal
NK115(re)001:16826: 'char 'char 'dra ba'i zang ma rjen pa de blang
NK115(re)001:16827: dor dang bya btsal gyis smon pa med par rang
NK115(re)001:16828: babs su bzhag pa la riga pa'i yona tan rdo
NK115(re)001:16829: rje gsum gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad 'char ba ni
NK115(re)001:16830: chu dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan gsal ba bzhin te
NK115(re)001:16833: sku yi dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa //
NK115(re)001:16834: thams cad ma lus snang bar gsal //
NK115(re)001:16835: gsung gi dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa //
NK115(re)001:16836: thams cad ma lus grags par ston //
NK115(re)001:16837: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa //
NK115(re)001:16838: thams cad ma lus rtogs par sangs //
NK115(re)001:16841: rgya mtsho bzhin du ye gnas la //
NK115(re)001:16842: chos rnams sna tshogs 'byung bar byed //
NK115(re)001:16843: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK115(re)001:16844: bsdu ba'i gnas su nges pa med //
NK115(re)001:16846: de ltar rig rtsal 'gag pa med pa la 'bras
NK115(re)001:16847: bu'i yon tan thams cad lhun grub rdzogas pa ni
NK115(re)001:16848: lhun grub sprul sku'i dgongs pa rnam par thar pa'i
NK115(re)001:16849: sgo smon pa med pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16850: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:16851: btsal bas mi rnyed gdod nas dag pa'i chos //
NK115(re)001:16852: sangs rgyas byang chub rang byung klong na gsal //
NK115(re)001:16853: sngar grub zin pas da gzod bsgrub mi dgos //
NK115(re)001:16854: che ba rang gnas dgongs pa chos nyid klong //
NK115(re)001:16855: mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub la rtsol ma byed //
NK115(re)001:16858: ngang la gnas na g.yo med lhun gyis grub //
NK115(re)001:16860: de lta bu'i riga pa rang bzhin med par shes
NK115(re)001:16861: pa'i lta ba de'nga shes bya shes byed kyis bsdus
NK115(re)001:16862: pa'i lta ba min te shesa bya'i yul la mi
NK115(re)001:16863: gansa para yul med du zang thal bas gnyis su
NK115(re)001:16864: med pa'i chos nyid la gnyis chos 'gal ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:16865: dang / nga dang nga yi bar 'dzina pa'i chosa
NK115(re)001:16866: dang brala bas skad cig la bya byed ma grub
NK115(re)001:16867: dang / pa'i phyir dang / so so rang gis
NK115(re)001:16868: rig pas na blta bya lta byed dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:16869: lta ba la sogs pa'i don med pa'i phyir te
NK115(re)001:16870: dang / pa'i phyir dang / / gtan tshigs gsum gyis lta ba'i srog 'dzin pa med pa ste /
NK115(re)001:16872: gang gi phyogs su ma lhung nam mkha' bzhin //
NK115(re)001:16873: yod pa ma yin stong pa gcig pu nyid //
NK115(re)001:16874: med pa ma yin yang dag bde ba'i sku //
NK115(re)001:16875: byas pa ma yin rang byung rtog med nyid //
NK115(re)001:16877: de phyir rdzogs chen a ti la //
NK115(re)001:16878: lta ba 'dzin pa'i chos nyid med //
NK115(re)001:16880: de bas na snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:16881: chos thams cad la dag pa dang ma dag pa
NK115(re)001:16882: zhes bya ba'i mtshan ma'i dngos po so sor grub
NK115(re)001:16883: pa rdul tsam yang med par zang thal gyi rig
NK115(re)001:16884: pa rnam thar sgo gsum gyi rang bzhin can yid
NK115(re)001:16885: dpyod dang bral bar rtogs pa des ni sems kyis
NK115(re)001:16886: bzos pa'i 'khor ba'i grong khyer thams cad rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:16887: ngang du rgyun gcod par byed pas na lta ba
NK115(re)001:16888: grong khyer rgyun gcod ces bya ste /
NK115(re)001:16889: lta ba de'i don rtogs pas ni theg pa mtha'
NK115(re)001:16890: dag gi gnad don thams cad cig char du khong
NK115(re)001:16892: theg pa gzhan rnams kyis ni 'di'i don rtogs par
NK115(re)001:16893: mi 'gyur bas dper na ri'i rgyal po gleng gzhi'i
NK115(re)001:16894: dbus na mchog tu 'phags pa lta bu ste /
NK115(re)001:16896: lta ba kun gyi yang rtse ni //
NK115(re)001:16897: a ti rdzogs pa chen por bshad //
NK115(re)001:16900: ji ltar ri rgyal rtse mor phyin pa na //
NK115(re)001:16901: dma' ba'i lung rnams dus gcig mthong ba ste //
NK115(re)001:16902: lung gi rtse mo'i rang bzhin mthong dang bral //
NK115(re)001:16903: de bzhin a ti rdo rje snying po ni //
NK115(re)001:16904: theg pa'i yang rtse don kun gsal bar mthong //
NK115(re)001:16905: 'og ma'i theg pas 'di don mthong ba med //
NK115(re)001:16907: gnyis pa sgom pa 'dzin med rang grol ni /
NK115(re)001:16908: de ltar ngo 'phrod pa'i lta ba de'i ngang la
NK115(re)001:16909: 'jog pa la sgom pa zhes bya ba'i tha snyad
NK115(re)001:16910: btags pa tsam las sgom byed kyi blo dang bsgom
NK115(re)001:16911: para bya ba'i lta ba zhes tha dad pa ni
NK115(re)001:16912: med de / so so rang gi rig pa'i stong nyid /
NK115(re)001:16913: shes bya'i gshis la ma shor ba'i spros bral rnam rig dbu mar ma bzung ba'i rang grol /
NK115(re)001:16914: ye grol rgya yan du ma shor ba'i ngang bsgom
NK115(re)001:16915: gnas bya gnas byed la ma ltos pa'i zhi gnas
NK115(re)001:16916: / yul la rnam shes kyis mi dpyod pa'i lhag mthong /
NK115(re)001:16917: rang ngo ka dag las mi g.yo ba'i mnyam bzhag /
NK115(re)001:16918: lhun grub 'gag pa med pa'i rjes thob /
NK115(re)001:16919: kun gzhi dang ma 'dres pas thog ma nas grol ba /
NK115(re)001:16920: rnam shes dang ma 'dres pas glo bur du ma
NK115(re)001:16921: bsdams pa'i ngang la ma bcosa par rnal mara bazhaga
NK115(re)001:16922: na zang thal du rjen par mthonga zhing /
NK115(re)001:16923: mthong ba de yi ranga gi ngo bo rnam rtog bzang ngan gyi phyogs su ma lhung zhing /
NK115(re)001:16924: btang snyoms lung ma bstan du yang ma song bar
NK115(re)001:16925: shar grol ris med du dag ste gazhana du mi
NK115(re)001:16926: 'gyur na rtsal snang la zhen pa'i ma riga pa
NK115(re)001:16927: gzung 'dzina gyi rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pasa
NK115(re)001:16928: srid pa'i gnas su 'phen par byed pa'i las gsog
NK115(re)001:16929: par mi 'gyur bas 'khrid par byed mi nus te
NK115(re)001:16931: rtsa thag mes tshig pa'i thal ba ltar rtog pa
NK115(re)001:16932: rang rgyud pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:16933: de ltar bsgom pa'i tshe na zang thal gyi rig pa ngos ma zin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16934: rtsal las shar ba'i rnam rtog grol ma thub na
NK115(re)001:16935: 'phro gnas gang ltar yang srid par 'ching byed las
NK115(re)001:16938: de ltar bsgom pa'i tshe rang sde la zhugs pa'i
NK115(re)001:16939: lta sgom nor ba dag rtog pa gang shar de
NK115(re)001:16940: nyid rang byung gi ye shes yin no zhes zer
NK115(re)001:16941: ba ni / rig pa'i chos nyid ngos ma zin
NK115(re)001:16942: pa'i rtsal dang rol pa kun 'byung gi phyogs su
NK115(re)001:16944: rtog pa ni bag chags gzhan byung yin pas yul gyi rjes su byed pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:16945: yul du snang ba las gzhig cing gzhom du rung bas gzugs su 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:16946: tshor bas de dang de'i rang bzhin la sred cing nyams su myong /
NK115(re)001:16947: 'du shes kyi sa g.yo zhing rnam pa la dpyod /
NK115(re)001:16948: 'du shes kyis zag bcas kyi sems byung rgyun chags //
NK115(re)001:16949: rnam par shes pas yul du byed pa dang bcas
NK115(re)001:16950: rang byung gi ye shes la bkab ste sems dang
NK115(re)001:16951: sems byung mu mthud pa'i dran rgyun la ma yengs
NK115(re)001:16952: par 'dug go snyams kyang sems kyis sems la rtog
NK115(re)001:16953: dpyod dang bcas pas 'khor ba'i rang bzhin las cung
NK115(re)001:16954: zad kyang 'phags pa med do gsungs /
NK115(re)001:16955: des na mdo rgyud thams cad kyi dgongs pa phyin
NK115(re)001:16956: ci ma log pa'i zhi lhag gi ngo bo ni
NK115(re)001:16957: / srid pa'i kun rtog phung khams skye mched kyi
NK115(re)001:16958: nye bar len pa thams cad rab tu zhi ba'i
NK115(re)001:16959: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la mnyam par
NK115(re)001:16962: brjod par bya ba ldog pa ste //
NK115(re)001:16963: sems kyi spyod yul ldog pas so //
NK115(re)001:16964: ma skyes pa dang ma 'gag pa //
NK115(re)001:16965: chos nyid mya ngan 'das dang mtshungs //
NK115(re)001:16968: rgyal ba'i spyod yul 'di la gang zhig 'jug 'dod pa //
NK115(re)001:16969: des ni bsam pa thams cad nam mkha' lta bur sbyangs //
NK115(re)001:16970: rtog dang rnam par rtog dang 'du shes 'dzin spongs la //
NK115(re)001:16971: nam mkha' lta bu'i yid kyis 'di la 'jug par gyis //
NK115(re)001:16973: ye shes de lta bu'i ngang la bzhag na gzugs
NK115(re)001:16974: sku gnyis kyang 'dus byas kyi rgyu la mi ltos
NK115(re)001:16977: stong pa'i ngang las rig pa'i nyi shar bas //
NK115(re)001:16978: nub pa med pa'i gter chen dkyil 'khor nas //
NK115(re)001:16979: 'gyur ba med pa'i sku sngar shar gyis byung //
NK115(re)001:16980: rtog pa med pa'i ngang du gnyis med rol //
NK115(re)001:16982: de ltar bsgom pa des ni /
NK115(re)001:16983: rang byung gi rig pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK115(re)001:16984: la 'dzin med du bzhag pas glo bur gyi kun
NK115(re)001:16985: rtog thams cad sprin dengs pa ltar rang grol du
NK115(re)001:16986: 'gro ba'i phyir sgom pa 'dzin med rang grol zhes
NK115(re)001:16987: bya'o // gsum pa spyod pa snang ba dbang bsgyur ni /
NK115(re)001:16988: 'di ltar phyi rola gyi yula snod bcud du snang ba thams cad dang /
NK115(re)001:16989: nang badga tu zhen pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:16990: de las byung ba'i rtog tshogs ji snyed pa rnamas
NK115(re)001:16991: byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas te glo bur
NK115(re)001:16992: du skyes pa'i semas rtoga gis ri mo ltar bris
NK115(re)001:16993: shing de nyid la zhen pa'i bag chags mthu brtas
NK115(re)001:16994: pa lasa grub pa ltar snang ba 'di thams cad
NK115(re)001:16995: gzhi sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu ci yang ma
NK115(re)001:16996: grub pa'i ngang las rang gdangs 'gag med kyi stong
NK115(re)001:16997: gzugs ci yang shar ba dang rtsa ba sems nyid
NK115(re)001:16998: rang gi ngo bo la grub pa med bzhin glo
NK115(re)001:16999: bur du byung ba'i ma rig pas bslad pa lasa
NK115(re)001:17000: thams cad skyes pa ltar snang yang skyes tsam nyid
NK115(re)001:17001: nasa rig pa'i chos nyid skye ba med para rdzogas
NK115(re)001:17002: pa ste / mu tig phreng ba las /
NK115(re)001:17003: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK115(re)001:17004: glo bur rnam rtog sprin gyis bsgribs //
NK115(re)001:17005: ma 'khrul pa yi chos nyid kyang //
NK115(re)001:17006: blo la 'khrul pa'i tshul du snang //
NK115(re)001:17009: sems ni ri mo mkhan dang 'dra //
NK115(re)001:17010: sems kyi phung pos byas pa ste //
NK115(re)001:17011: 'jig rten khams ni ji snyed pa //
NK115(re)001:17012: de dag sems kyi ri mo yin //
NK115(re)001:17014: chos rnams rang gi ngo bo de ltar yin pa
NK115(re)001:17015: bzhin rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis skye med kyi rtsa
NK115(re)001:17016: ba chod pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nas 'gag
NK115(re)001:17017: med kyi rtsal ji ltar g.yo yang chu la ri
NK115(re)001:17018: mo'i gzugs brnyan bris tsam nyid nas chu rang gi
NK115(re)001:17019: ngang du dengs par 'gyur ba bzhin skyes tsam nyid
NK115(re)001:17020: nas skye ba med pa'i chos nyid du grol bar
NK115(re)001:17021: gyur na sgo gsum gyi bya spyod cir snang thams
NK115(re)001:17022: cad la zhen med rig pa'i chos nyid kyis dbang
NK115(re)001:17023: bsgyur bas na spyod pa snang ba dbang bsgyur zhes
NK115(re)001:17024: bya'o // bzhi pa 'bras bu rtsol med yongs grub ni /
NK115(re)001:17025: de lta bu'i lta sgom spyod gsum zung du 'jug
NK115(re)001:17026: pa'i ngang la goms su 'jug pa lasa gazhana pa'i
NK115(re)001:17027: rtogsa para bya ba'i 'bras bu zhig yod pa ma
NK115(re)001:17028: yin pas bsgrub mi dgosa te /
NK115(re)001:17029: de nyid goms pa klong du phebs tsa na /
NK115(re)001:17030: phyi yul med du rtog pas gzung ba'i chos rnam par dag /
NK115(re)001:17031: nang yul can du mi gnas pas 'dzin pa gzhi med rtsa bral du song /
NK115(re)001:17032: rten gzhi med pa'i rig pa la blos mtshon du
NK115(re)001:17033: med pas nam yang 'khrul mi shes pa'i tshe na
NK115(re)001:17035: tshig don blo la 'dzina pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17036: dmigs pa la rtse gcig tu 'jog pa la sogs pa'i bsgom pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17037: bstan bcosa la sogs pa'i don la semas shing brtags
NK115(re)001:17038: pa la sogs pa matha'a daga pa ni kun rtog
NK115(re)001:17039: gi blo yisa glo bur du bcos pa'i chos yin
NK115(re)001:17040: pas de lta bu'i gruba matha'a yi tha snyad bcos
NK115(re)001:17041: ma'i chos la ltos mi dgos pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:17042: thun dang thun mtshams kyi dbye ba med pas lta sgom spyod pa'i khrigs zhiga /
NK115(re)001:17043: dran pa chos nyid du sangs pas gnyen po'i chos zad /
NK115(re)001:17044: rig pa chos skur shes pas sems can dang sangs
NK115(re)001:17045: rgyas su ma grub pa 'i gdeng rnyed par gyur
NK115(re)001:17046: pa na / yid smon gyi 'bras bu gud na tshol du meda de /
NK115(re)001:17047: gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i rig pa'i chos nyid la
NK115(re)001:17048: dus gsum gyi sangas rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:17049: rdzogs par 'gyur bas na 'bras bu ni rang gi
NK115(re)001:17051: de ltar yang rtsal rdzogs las /
NK115(re)001:17052: gnyis med rig pa'i rang snang ci yang 'char //
NK115(re)001:17053: chos sku dngos bral ye shes gsang ba nyid //
NK115(re)001:17054: snang ba rang lugs ye 'byams thugs la gnas //
NK115(re)001:17055: zag med rig pa'i snang ba cir yang snang //
NK115(re)001:17056: 'gag med rol pa'i rig pa ci yang 'char //
NK115(re)001:17057: rtog med thugs kyi dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:17058: dus gsum sangs rgyas rig pa gzung 'dzin bral //
NK115(re)001:17060: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:17061: sems can rang bzhin byang chub nyid du gsungs //
NK115(re)001:17062: byang chub rang bzhin sems can thams cad de //
NK115(re)001:17063: sems can rnams dang byang chub gzhan ma yin //
NK115(re)001:17064: de ltar shes na skyes bu mchog tu 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:17066: de'i phyir ka dag gi rig pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la goms shing brtan pa rnams ni /
NK115(re)001:17069: gsang ba sems su 'dus pa'i tshogs pa gsum las
NK115(re)001:17070: rdos bcas kyi gsal snang chu zla lta bur rtogs
NK115(re)001:17072: ri brag dang rtsig pa la thogs pa med /
NK115(re)001:17073: sems 'phags pa'i bden pa la gnas pas spyan dang
NK115(re)001:17074: mngon shes la sogs pa thob cing yang srid las
NK115(re)001:17075: rnam par grol // lus kyi 'byung bzhi'i rdul phran
NK115(re)001:17076: kyang ye shes kyi mes sbyangs te na bun yal
NK115(re)001:17077: ba ltar nam mkha'i mthongs su cho 'phrul chen po
NK115(re)001:17079: rig pa chos sku'i dbyings su 'khyil nas sprul pa'i
NK115(re)001:17080: sku rgyun chad med pas 'khor ba ma stongs kyi
NK115(re)001:17081: bar du 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17082: gzhan don du 'gyur na rdul phran du dengs pa
NK115(re)001:17083: de dag ring bsrel du byin gyis brlabs nas 'jog
NK115(re)001:17084: pa'ang yod la / rtogs pa tshad du phyin nas
NK115(re)001:17085: gzhan don gyi rnam g.yeng med pas rlung sems rang
NK115(re)001:17086: mal du dwangs su bcug pa rnams rdul phran du
NK115(re)001:17087: cung ma phyin yang phung po ltos chung zhing lcid
NK115(re)001:17088: shin tu yang ba la sogs pa 'byung la /
NK115(re)001:17089: de rnams ni rig pa zang thal goms pa ka dag la thim pa las byung ste /
NK115(re)001:17091: ka nas dag pas dri ma zad //
NK115(re)001:17092: thog mar byung bas rgyud pa zad //
NK115(re)001:17094: de yang rig pa ka dag gi ngang la ma
NK115(re)001:17095: bcos rtsol med du bzhag pas rang gnas kyi ye
NK115(re)001:17096: shes yongs grub chen po'i gnas lugs mngon du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:17097: pas 'bras bu rtsol med yongs grub ces bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17098: 'on kyang thugs rje yas sprul rnams ni gdul bya'i dbang gis snang tshul sna tshogs pas na /
NK115(re)001:17099: lam gyis grol tshad dag gis dpag par bya mi nus so //
NK115(re)001:17100: gnyis pa lhun grub thod rgal gyi khyad par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:17101: khyad par can gyi lam dngos bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17102: khyad par gyi chos shes dgos par gdams pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17103: dang po khyad par can gyi lam dngos bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17104: spyir le lo can 'bad med du grol ba ka dag khregs chod kyi lam dang /
NK115(re)001:17105: brtson 'grus can 'bad bcas su grol ba lhun grub
NK115(re)001:17106: thob rgal gyi lam gnyis po 'di gang yin yang
NK115(re)001:17107: zang thal gyi rig pa rjen par ngo 'phrod nas
NK115(re)001:17108: rtsal snang gang la'ang ma zhen par byas te de'i
NK115(re)001:17109: ngang skyong ba tsam du mtshungs kyang khregs chod kyi
NK115(re)001:17110: lam gyis ni de ltar nyams su len pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:17111: na gzung yul tha mal pa'i cha la dbang shes
NK115(re)001:17112: kyis 'brel ba'i 'dzin cha dbang rnon gyis gzhi med
NK115(re)001:17114: dbang rtul gyi sgyu ma lta bur rgyas 'debs pa'i
NK115(re)001:17115: yid dpyod tsam las med pa las khyad para du
NK115(re)001:17116: 'phags shing theg rtse'i rnal 'byor thams cad kyi yang
NK115(re)001:17117: mthar thug pa yin pas 'di'i gong na man ngag
NK115(re)001:17118: gi lam gzhan med pas bla na med pa'i thod
NK115(re)001:17119: rgal gyi lam du ni bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs
NK115(re)001:17120: sogs kyis gnad gcun pas rtog pa shed can rnams
NK115(re)001:17121: rang 'gags shing / shed chung stong yal la song
NK115(re)001:17122: ste thog ma nas dbyings kyi snang ba 'od lnga
NK115(re)001:17123: dang rigas gadngas rdo rje lu gu rgyud nas lha
NK115(re)001:17124: sku'i bar dbang po'i mngona suma du mthonga basa stong
NK115(re)001:17125: nyid gshis shor gyi gola sa'ang nyunga zhing /
NK115(re)001:17126: phyi 'byunga sa rdo ri brag la sogs tha mal
NK115(re)001:17127: pa'i yul snang gi bag chags thog ma med pa
NK115(re)001:17128: nas bzhag pa'i rdos bcas ltar snang ba'i dri ma
NK115(re)001:17129: ngang gis zad para 'gyur te phyi nang gnyis ka'i
NK115(re)001:17130: 'khrul snang dang 'khrul 'dzin thams cad ma spangs rang
NK115(re)001:17131: dag tu grol ba'i gnad kyis 'byung chen phyi ltar
NK115(re)001:17132: snang ba'ang ye shesa 'od gasla chena pora dwangsa pa'i
NK115(re)001:17133: thabs kyis sku gsum lam snang du rdzos shing mngona
NK115(re)001:17134: du byed pa yin pasa nang rang gi phung pos
NK115(re)001:17135: bsdus pa'i 'byung ba rnams khregas choda tshad du phyin
NK115(re)001:17136: pa'i stobs kyis rdul phran nyid du 'gro ba tsam
NK115(re)001:17137: lasa 'od lus su dwangsa para ma nus pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:17138: 'pho ba chen po'i sku mi thob pa'ang /
NK115(re)001:17139: 'dus byas ltar snang ba'i 'byung ba snyigs ma'i khams
NK115(re)001:17140: de nyid 'pho ba chena po zung 'jug gi ye
NK115(re)001:17141: shes skye 'chi bgres rgud dang bral ba'i rdo rje'i
NK115(re)001:17142: skur smin nasa rten des gazhana dona 'khora ba ma
NK115(re)001:17143: stongsa kyi bar du madzada pa ni rgyal dbang pad+ma
NK115(re)001:17144: lta bu'o // de lta bu'i khyad par can gyi
NK115(re)001:17145: lam 'di'i lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi po zung 'brel
NK115(re)001:17146: du shes pa'i phyir cung zad bshad pa la gnyis
NK115(re)001:17147: lta bu'o // te / ye shes kyi rten sgron
NK115(re)001:17148: ma bzhi'i rnam par dbye ba spyir bshad pa dang
NK115(re)001:17149: lta bu'o // te / / nyams len gyi lam dngos bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17150: dang po sgron ma bzhi bshad pa la'ang spyir bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17151: so sor bshad pa gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:17153: thog mar lus chags dus na chu'i rang bzhin gsher
NK115(re)001:17154: ba la brten nas lte ba'i rtsa mdud kyi nang
NK115(re)001:17155: du sgron ma dang 'byung ba'i spyan gnyis sngon du
NK115(re)001:17156: chags pa las / 'byung ba'i spyan gyis lus bskyed cing /
NK115(re)001:17157: sgron ma'i spyan las ye shes kyi snang ba 'od
NK115(re)001:17158: dang thig le dang sku la sogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:17159: don dam pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i gzhir mig
NK115(re)001:17160: gnyis kyi a 'bras kyi dkyil du rtsa ba men
NK115(re)001:17161: gyi rwa 'dra ba rtsa ba phra la rtse mo
NK115(re)001:17162: che ba gnyis chags pa de la rgyang zhags chu'i
NK115(re)001:17164: dbus ma gcig tshangs bug la zug pa'i nang na
NK115(re)001:17165: rig pa rtog med lu gu rgyud dang 'od kyi
NK115(re)001:17166: thig le brtsegs ma lnga ldan dgu 'char ba la
NK115(re)001:17167: sgron ma bzhi ka'i cha yod de /
NK115(re)001:17171: shes pa mi rtog pa ni shes rab sgron ma'i cha'o //
NK115(re)001:17172: des na tha mal ba'i gzugs snang 'dzin byed ni rten 'byung ba'i spyan yin la /
NK115(re)001:17173: brten pa chu'i sgron ma ni 'od snang 'char byed
NK115(re)001:17174: kyi sgo yin pas ye shes kyi snang ba 'dzin
NK115(re)001:17176: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma ni 'char ba'i rnam
NK115(re)001:17177: pa rtsol byed kyi rten thig le zlum po 'od
NK115(re)001:17179: dag pa dbyings kyi sgron ma ni 'char gzhi'i nang dbyings phyi ru gsal ba'i gdangs yin te /
NK115(re)001:17181: phyi ni nam mkha' dag pa'i dkyil na 'od gdangs sngo ri ba gcig thog mar snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17182: phyi'i nam mkha' ni go 'byed pa'i rkyen tsam las dbyings dngos min no //
NK115(re)001:17183: nang ni de las mched pa ltar shar te 'od lnga'i mdangs kha dog lngar gsal ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17184: de gnyis la phyi nang du bzhag pa ni de las de byung bar snang bas yin gyi /
NK115(re)001:17185: phyi nang du yod pa ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:17186: de'ang so sor brjod kyang 'ja' 'od kyi gur khyim
NK115(re)001:17187: sngar mi gsal ba la phyis gsal bar go 'phos
NK115(re)001:17188: pa tsam las tha dad pa med do //
NK115(re)001:17189: shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma la ngo bo dang /
NK115(re)001:17192: ngo bo ni rgyang zhags gzigs stangs kyi gnad las
NK115(re)001:17193: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma la gtad dus nang
NK115(re)001:17194: gi rig pa dwangs sangs rang gsal yul med du
NK115(re)001:17195: 'char ba yin pas 'di las ma 'khrul ba gal
NK115(re)001:17197: rtsal ni phyir gsal du shar ba'i shes rab rno
NK115(re)001:17198: ba myur ba tshig don klong rdol du 'char ba
NK115(re)001:17199: rnams so // gdangs ni rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK115(re)001:17200: kyi snang ba gser gyi skud pa lding ba lta
NK115(re)001:17201: rnams so // bu'o // shes rab rang byung gi
NK115(re)001:17202: sgron ma de la byed las kyi sgo nas dbye
NK115(re)001:17205: rnam par sgron byed shes rab 1ni //
NK115(re)001:17206: thams cad sgrol bar byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17207: nyon mongs dag pa'i zhing du sgrol //
NK115(re)001:17208: rtog med skye med ngang du sgrol //
NK115(re)001:17209: ma rig rig pa'i klong du sgrol //
NK115(re)001:17210: shes rab rtog med ngang du sgrol //
NK115(re)001:17211: de phyir sgrol byed shes rab bo //
NK115(re)001:17212: rnam pa bskyod byed shes rab 2ni //
NK115(re)001:17213: sku lnga ka dag dbyings su bskyod par byed //
NK115(re)001:17214: 'od lnga 'dzin med dbyings su bskyod par byed //
NK115(re)001:17215: rig pa ye shes dbyings su bskyod par byed //
NK115(re)001:17216: sgron ma nam mkha'i dbyings su bskyod par byed //
NK115(re)001:17217: de phyir bskyod byed shes rab bo //
NK115(re)001:17218: rnam par sdud byed shes rab 3ni //
NK115(re)001:17220: nam mkha' sgron ma'i nang du sdud //
NK115(re)001:17221: sku lnga rig pa'i ngang du sdud //
NK115(re)001:17222: rig pa rtog med nang du sdud //
NK115(re)001:17223: de phyir sdud byed shes rab bo //
NK115(re)001:17225: ma rig rig pa gnyis su 'byed //
NK115(re)001:17226: nyon mongs ye shes gnyis su 'byed //
NK115(re)001:17227: dag dang ma dag gnyis su 'byed //
NK115(re)001:17229: rtogs dang ma rtogs gnyis su 'byed //
NK115(re)001:17230: bzang dang ngan pa gnyis su 'byed //
NK115(re)001:17231: de phyir 'byed byed shes rab bo //
NK115(re)001:17233: 'di ni thod rgal gyi chings bla na med pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:17234: 'di ltar rtogs na shes rab kyi mig gis mthong
NK115(re)001:17235: ba yin pas snang ba la go rim med par
NK115(re)001:17236: cig car du zad pa yang 'byung la /
NK115(re)001:17237: chu bur gyi mig gis mthong ba ni dang por chos nyid mngon sum nas rim par 'char dgos /
NK115(re)001:17238: de la lhag mthong rnam par mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis zin nas ma zhen dgos /
NK115(re)001:17239: de la brten nas rlung gi cha dag dgos //
NK115(re)001:17241: phyis las rlung dang mnyam du zad nas ye shes
NK115(re)001:17242: kyi rlung dang lhan cig nang dbyings su chos zad
NK115(re)001:17243: kyi rang sa zin dgos pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17244: de ltar ma rtogs par dbang po yul rkyen gyis
NK115(re)001:17245: bslad pa'i stong gzugs tsam la che thang du bzung
NK115(re)001:17246: nas lam gyi mu brtsi ba ni srid pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:17247: gong mar 'phen byed tsam las rnam par grol ba'i
NK115(re)001:17249: de ltar sgron ma bzhi po gzhi la med na
NK115(re)001:17250: lus ngag yid sems bzhi rtag tu 'khor bar 'khyams
NK115(re)001:17251: pa las grol bar mi 'gyur ba la 'di bzhi
NK115(re)001:17252: yod pas / gzhi smin byed dbang bzhis rgyud sbyangs
NK115(re)001:17253: nas lam snang bzhi tshad du phyin te 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:17254: sku bzhi dbyings su 'khyil ba 'byung ba yin no
NK115(re)001:17255: yod pas / // de'ang rin po che bum pa'i
NK115(re)001:17256: dgongs pa tsit+ta rin po che snying ga'i bum pa
NK115(re)001:17257: na rang byung gi sgron ma nam mkha' ltar gnas
NK115(re)001:17258: yod pas / // pa / bar gyi kha'i 'brel
NK115(re)001:17259: thag gi nam mkha' ltar sgron ma bzhi'i mtshams sbyar
NK115(re)001:17260: yod pas / // pa / bas / phyi'i nam
NK115(re)001:17261: mkha' chen po ltar ka dag dbyings kyi grol sar
NK115(re)001:17262: ma bu sprad de tshad la phebs sam /
NK115(re)001:17263: bar dor rang gsal gyi chos nyid shar dus rdos bcas lus kyi bum pa chag pas /
NK115(re)001:17264: lhun grub rin po che gsang ba'i sbubs la zang
NK115(re)001:17265: thal ba ni sgron ma bzhi'i chos nyid nyams su
NK115(re)001:17267: de yang thog ma nas gnas tshul ni gzhi ka
NK115(re)001:17268: dag gi dus na sgron ma bzhi lhun grub kyi
NK115(re)001:17269: cha la nang gsal phra bar yod la /
NK115(re)001:17270: gzhi snang du shar dus dbyings 'od lnga'i snang bar shar /
NK115(re)001:17271: thig le so so'i 'od khyim na sku'i char shar /
NK115(re)001:17272: rgyang zhags rang gsal 'od zer gyi sbrel thag tu shar /
NK115(re)001:17273: shes rab rig par shar bas grol 'khrul gnyis kyi mtshams rig ma rig tsam du gnas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17274: gnyis pa so sor bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:17276: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma /
NK115(re)001:17277: dbyings rnam dag gi sgron ma /
NK115(re)001:17278: shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma'o //
NK115(re)001:17279: dang po rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma'i ngo bo ni /
NK115(re)001:17280: dag ma dag gnyis ka'i cha 'dzin pas ye shes
NK115(re)001:17281: kyi snang ba dang 'khrul snang mthong byed du skyes
NK115(re)001:17282: pa'i dbang rten dwangs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17283: de la brten pa'i 'od rtsa dwangs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17284: nges tshig ni snang ba gnyis rgyang ring po na 'dug pa 'dzin zhing /
NK115(re)001:17285: rtogs na 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang 'khrul rtog dang bcas pa ring du 'phen pas rgyang zhes bya la /
NK115(re)001:17286: ma rtogs na myang 'das rgyang du 'phen pas rgyang zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17287: rang snang mthong dus ma dag pa 'ching ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17288: ma rtogs na 'khrul snang la zhen nas rang rig 'ching bas zhags zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17289: yang rang snang yas su mi 'jug par 'ching bas kyang zhags pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17290: snang ba la zhen pa med par nang ting nge 'dzin gyi dga' bdes brlan par byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17291: chu'i dwangs pa 'dus pa la brten pas kyang chu zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17292: gzugs snang dbang shes la gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17293: 'od snang gong 'phel du shar bas sgron zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17294: dbyings rig gi snang ba bskyed pa'i gzhi ma yin pas ma zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17295: gzugs la blta ba'i rten byed pas kyang ma zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17297: 'byung ba 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags rlung gi dwangs ma las rtsa ba men gyi rwa 'dra ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17298: ye shes 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags 'od rtsa dwangs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17299: dbang po 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags dbang lnga'i dwangs ma
NK115(re)001:17300: mig gi dkyil na yod pa'i dbang rten dwangs ma'o
NK115(re)001:17301: // de yang sgron ma dngos ni ye shes 'dus pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17302: mtshan nyid ni gzugs snang 'dzin rung du skyes pa spyi'i mtshan nyid yin la /
NK115(re)001:17304: snang ba sdud 'dzin mched pa'i char gnas pa dang po'o /
NK115(re)001:17305: 'od gsal gyi rang snang gsal bar 'dzin pa gnyis pa'i /
NK115(re)001:17306: snang ba dang snang yul dang rang shes mig gi rnam shes 'dzin pa gsum pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK115(re)001:17307: gnyis pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma la /
NK115(re)001:17308: ngo bo ni thog ma'i ka dag gi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:17309: las 'od gsal lhun grub kyi thig le 'od lnga'i
NK115(re)001:17310: mu khyud zlum pos bskor ba rang gsal kha dog
NK115(re)001:17311: dwangs pa'o // nges tshig ni rang gnas 'od zlum de mi 'gyur bas thig /
NK115(re)001:17312: yul la khyab par gdal bas le /
NK115(re)001:17313: dngos po ngos bzung med pas stong pa /
NK115(re)001:17314: stong pa'i rang 'od 'bar bas sgron ma zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17315: dbye na gnas pa gzhi'i thig le snying ga na 'khor 'das kyi 'char gzhir gnas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17316: lus gnas rtsa'i thig le khyad par chen po'i rtsa
NK115(re)001:17317: bzhin rang gsal bas bde sdug rang grol du gnas
NK115(re)001:17318: pa dang / kun rdzob rgyu'i thig le ro ma
NK115(re)001:17319: la sogs pa na lus kyi zungs tsam 'dzin byed
NK115(re)001:17321: don dam spros med kyi thig le rig pa ka
NK115(re)001:17322: nas dag pas dbyings rig zad pa'i dgongs pa la
NK115(re)001:17323: gnas pa dang / rang byung 'bras bu'i thig le
NK115(re)001:17324: dbang po'i mngon sum du snang bas nyin mtshan 'od
NK115(re)001:17325: gsal du 'dres te sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rgya
NK115(re)001:17326: yan yongs grol chen po la spyod pa ste lnga'o
NK115(re)001:17327: gnas pa dang / // mtshan nyid ni /
NK115(re)001:17328: zla dang bral ba'i stong pa dbang po'i yul du
NK115(re)001:17329: shar na ma bsgom chu bo'i rgyun gyi rnal 'byor
NK115(re)001:17331: gsum pa dbyings rnam dag gi sgron ma la /
NK115(re)001:17332: ngo bo ni rang bzhin ka dag tu gnas pa la /
NK115(re)001:17333: gdangs mthing ga las lnga ldan du mched de 'od
NK115(re)001:17334: lnga'i mu khyud zlum po'i nang na pad 'dab dang
NK115(re)001:17335: bcas pa za 'og ber khyim ltar snang ba ste
NK115(re)001:17336: / rig pa lu gu rgyud gzer 'debs pa'i rwa bar byung ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17337: nges tshig ni rig pa'i rang yul dang snang ba'i 'char gzhi byed pas dbyings /
NK115(re)001:17338: yul du snang ba la dri ma med pas rnam par dag pa /
NK115(re)001:17339: lu gu rgyud go rar bzung nas snang rig gsal bar byed pas sgron ma zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17340: dbye na gzhi la gnas pa'i dbyings tsit+ta'i nang na
NK115(re)001:17341: ye shes dang 'od kyi sku lhun grub nang gsal
NK115(re)001:17343: lam la snang ba'i dbyings mu khyud lnga'i rwa bas
NK115(re)001:17344: bskor ba dbus na pad+ma'i 'dab ma can gyi thig
NK115(re)001:17345: le'i dwangs ma sdud pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17346: 'bras bu yul la snang ba'i dbyings lu gu brgyud brtson du 'dzin pa ste /
NK115(re)001:17349: za 'og ris la sogs pa ste gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:17351: phyi 'od kyi dbyings stong gsal zang ma dang nang
NK115(re)001:17352: rig pa'i dbyings ka dag zang ma gnyis ye nas
NK115(re)001:17354: bzhi pa shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma la /
NK115(re)001:17356: sgron ma kun gyi shes byed dgongs pa chos nyid
NK115(re)001:17357: stong gsal rang gnas shes pa'i rtsal dang bcas pa'o
NK115(re)001:17359: nang du rang gnas lhun grub kyi dgongs pa shes
NK115(re)001:17360: dus phyir snang ba rang snang zang thal du shes
NK115(re)001:17361: te / chos thams cad kyi spyi stong zhing bdag med par shes la /
NK115(re)001:17362: rang gi ye shes kyi tshad rnams shes pas shes /
NK115(re)001:17363: kun gyis rtog dka' ba'i dgongs pa ma btsal rang
NK115(re)001:17364: las rnyed pas ches 'phags shing rtse mor gyur pas
NK115(re)001:17365: rab / ye nas rang la yod pa'i nor bu rnyed pas rang /
NK115(re)001:17366: rang shar 'gag med du byung bas byung /
NK115(re)001:17367: chos rnams gsal bar shes pas sgron /
NK115(re)001:17368: rang snang rang ngo rig pas khyab cing shes pas ma zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17370: gzhi nas rang byung gi shes rab ni /
NK115(re)001:17371: nang gnas rig pa'i mkhyen cha ste 'char gzhi dang rten du gnas pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17372: snang ba cer 'dzin gyi shes rab ni /
NK115(re)001:17373: dbyings rig gnyis med zung 'jug gi ngang dus rang
NK115(re)001:17374: gsal dri med du dag pas dgongs pa chos nyid
NK115(re)001:17376: dran pa 'gag med kyi shes rab ni /
NK115(re)001:17377: shar ris med du shar yang /
NK115(re)001:17378: grol rang ngo chos nyid gcig tu sdud pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17379: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab ni //
NK115(re)001:17380: chos dang chos can rang dang spyi'i rnam pa dang
NK115(re)001:17381: mtshan nyid la sogs pa ji ltar snang ba ma
NK115(re)001:17383: 'jug byed rnam gsum gyi shes rab ni /
NK115(re)001:17384: rang bzhin bar do 'dir thos pas gtan la 'bebs //
NK115(re)001:17386: sgom pas ro myong bas 'khor ba las nges pas 'byin pa ste tshig don rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17387: mtshan nyid ni yul snang bas bsdus pa'i chos dang /
NK115(re)001:17388: yul can rig pas bsdus pa'i chos rnams rang bzhin med par shes pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17389: de ltar sgron ma bzhi'i rnam par bzhag pa mdor
NK115(re)001:17390: bsdus pa 'di tsam zhig ni nges par shes par
NK115(re)001:17391: byed dgos te / zung 'jug gi rdzogs rim mthar
NK115(re)001:17392: thug pa lhun grub thod rgal gyi lam bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:17393: byed dgos te / la / bsgom par bya ba'i gzhi nges par bya dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:17394: gnyis pa nyams len gyi lam dngos bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:17398: sngar yang mdo tsam smos la /
NK115(re)001:17399: 'dir dgos ched dang bcas mdor bsdus te bstan na /
NK115(re)001:17400: rten gyi gang zag 'khor ba las blo log nas 'jig rten 'di la zhen pa dang bral ba /
NK115(re)001:17401: chos kyi don cig car du 'thob par 'dod pa rnams kyis /
NK115(re)001:17402: thog mar bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa zhig las dbang bskur rdzogs par nod par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:17403: de la dang po phyi spros bcas kyi dbang dkyil
NK115(re)001:17404: 'khor dang bum pa la brten nas lus la dbang
NK115(re)001:17405: bskur bas / lus yi dam lha'i skur dbang bas phyi snod gzhal yas khang dang /
NK115(re)001:17406: nang lus lha skur gsal ba byung /
NK115(re)001:17407: de ni lus rgya rdos bcas las grol bar byed pa'i gnad do //
NK115(re)001:17408: de nas nang spros med kyi dbang man+dala dang bum pa la brten nas ngag la bskur bas /
NK115(re)001:17409: ngag yi dam lha'i bzlas par gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17410: nang du brjod med kyi don yi ge a'i brjod pa la brten nas nyams su myong ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17411: de nas gsang ba shin tu spros pa med pa'i
NK115(re)001:17412: dbang brda dang rten 'brel la brten nas sems la
NK115(re)001:17413: bskur bas / sems dngos po gshis kyi steng du phebs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17414: 'od gsal chen po'i don nyams su myong ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17415: de nas gsang ba bla na med pa rab tu
NK115(re)001:17416: spros med kyi dbang lus kyi 'dug stangs dang lta
NK115(re)001:17417: stangs la brten nas lus ngag yid gsum la bskur
NK115(re)001:17418: bas / lus bzhugs stangs kyi gnad la brten nas sku gsum gyi bzhugs stangs su grol ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17419: ngag smra ba bcad pa la brten nas sgra'i nus
NK115(re)001:17420: pa nyams pas brjod du med pa'i don khong du
NK115(re)001:17421: chud pa dang / sems byin rlabs bskul ba brda'i
NK115(re)001:17422: gnad la brten nas 'od gsal stong pa ci'i ngo
NK115(re)001:17423: bor yang ma grub pa ni sngags kyi lam smin
NK115(re)001:17425: de ltar lus kyi smin pa rdzogs pas bskyed rim cig car du gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17426: ngag gi smin pa rdzogs pas nus pa thun mong ma yin pa skye ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17427: sems kyi smin pa rdzogs pas rdzogs pa'i rim pa rtags tshad la phebs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17428: lus ngag yid sems kyi smin pa rdzogs pas chos
NK115(re)001:17429: nyid mngon sum gyi lam nyams su myong ba mngon
NK115(re)001:17430: par rdzogs pa'o // gnyis pa grol byed gdams ngag bshad pa la /
NK115(re)001:17431: spyir gdams ngag gi 'debs lugs thams cad bsdu na gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:17432: khrid kyi lugs su gdab pa /
NK115(re)001:17433: ngo sprod kyi lugs su gdab pa /
NK115(re)001:17434: mgron po la brgal ba la tshang sprugs su gdab pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17435: dang po'i nang du phyi ma gnyis 'du ste /
NK115(re)001:17436: ngo sprad car phog tu gdab pa khregs chod dang thod rgal yin la /
NK115(re)001:17437: tshang sprugs su gdab pa bar do'i gdams ngag yin no //
NK115(re)001:17438: des na khrid kyi lugs ltar bshad na /
NK115(re)001:17439: sngon 'gro dang dngos gzhi gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:17441: dper na 'jigs bcas kyi lam du 'gro ba la
NK115(re)001:17442: sngon du 'jigs pa'i skungs nyul nas lam du blo
NK115(re)001:17443: bde bar 'gro ba dang 'dra bar dngos gzhi la
NK115(re)001:17444: bag tsha ba med par 'gro ba'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:17445: sngon 'gro med na skyes ma med par 'jigs bcas
NK115(re)001:17446: kyi lam du 'gro mi nus pa dang 'dra la
NK115(re)001:17447: / dngos gzhi'i gnad med na sngon 'gro sbyangs kyang
NK115(re)001:17448: 'bras bu mi 'thob pas de gnyis zung du 'brel
NK115(re)001:17449: / dgos pas na / sngon 'gro la gsum las /
NK115(re)001:17450: dang po ni sku gsum gyi sna 'khrid par byed pa 'byung gzhi'i rnal 'byor la bslab pa ste /
NK115(re)001:17452: sku gsum bslab pa'i rim pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:17453: 'byung ba'i yon tan gtsor byas te //
NK115(re)001:17454: mchog tu sa chu me rlung gis //
NK115(re)001:17455: sgra la bslab pas nges par 'grub //
NK115(re)001:17457: gnyis pa ni rig pa'i sna 'khrid par byed pa
NK115(re)001:17458: 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa la bslab
NK115(re)001:17461: khams gsum lus ngag yid kyis kyang //
NK115(re)001:17465: gsum pa ni sems kyi sna 'khrid par byed pa lus ngag yid gsum gyi sngon 'gro ste /
NK115(re)001:17466: 'di la dngos dang rnal dbab gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:17469: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17470: lus kyi sngon du 'gro ba la //
NK115(re)001:17471: so so'i byed pa'i rgyu 'gag pa //
NK115(re)001:17472: rdo rje skyil krung du byas te /
NK115(re)001:17473: lus sbyangs sems la phan pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17474: ngag ni h'u zhes gnas pa la //
NK115(re)001:17475: rgyas gdab pa dang rtsal nyid sbyang //
NK115(re)001:17476: mnyen btsal lam du zhugs pa yis //
NK115(re)001:17477: de ltar ngag sbyangs sems la phan //
NK115(re)001:17478: sems ni thog ma byung sa dang //
NK115(re)001:17479: bar du gnas sa tha ma 'gro //
NK115(re)001:17480: de ltar gsum la brtags dpyad na //
NK115(re)001:17481: sems spyangs sems kyi gnas lugs shes //
NK115(re)001:17485: rnal du dbab pa'i cho ga yang //
NK115(re)001:17486: 'di dus lus ngag sems kyi gnad //
NK115(re)001:17487: rnal 'byor ldan pas rnal dbab bya //
NK115(re)001:17489: de dag gi dgos pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17490: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bar chad zhi ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17491: sdig sgrib 'dag pa thun mong gi dang /
NK115(re)001:17492: sku gsung thugs gsum du grol ba mchog gi dgos pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17493: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:17494: gnad gzir nas mngon sum rang thog tu dbab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17495: nyams su blangs pas snang bzhi'i 'char tshul bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17496: mtha' rten gyi man ngag go //
NK115(re)001:17497: dang po la bca' ba lus kyi gnad gsum /
NK115(re)001:17500: snang ba yul gyi gnad gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:17501: dang po bca' ba lus kyi gnad gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:17502: bzhugs stangs gsum po gang 'cha' yang rung ste /
NK115(re)001:17503: ha cang bsdams ches pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17505: 'chus pa ma yin par bde lugs bca' bas /
NK115(re)001:17506: rtsa 'chus dang rlung log 'byams kyi nyes pa sel la /
NK115(re)001:17507: sems kyi bzhon pa las rlung gi 'gyu ba yang
NK115(re)001:17508: rang 'gags la gtong ba'i phyir rlung kha sgo nas
NK115(re)001:17509: dal bus drangs la phyir ji ltar gnas gnas su
NK115(re)001:17510: glod do // gnad des sems kyi bzhon pa rta lta bu'i rlung phyir gyes /
NK115(re)001:17511: dran rtog mi lta bu rig pa la thim pas
NK115(re)001:17512: rang babs kyi bsam gtan la gnas pa ni rlung
NK115(re)001:17514: gnyis pa 'char byed sgo'i gnad gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:17515: gzigs stangs gsum gang byed kyang /
NK115(re)001:17516: ha cang gcun pa ma yin pa'i ngos nas mig
NK115(re)001:17517: gi 'gul ba'i lta stangs gzir bas sgron ma bzhi'i
NK115(re)001:17519: snying ga'i 'od gsal gyi gdangs las mig rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma gzigs stangs las mi 'gul bas /
NK115(re)001:17520: dbyings rnam dag gi sgron ma 'ja' 'am na ro
NK115(re)001:17521: lta bu'i nang du rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang
NK115(re)001:17522: / thig le stong pa'i sgron ma 'od dmar ser
NK115(re)001:17523: mu khyud lnga pa mthe bong tsam las mang du
NK115(re)001:17524: mched pa la gtad nas blo gang du yang mi
NK115(re)001:17525: 'dzin la ma yengs par bltas pas shes rab rang
NK115(re)001:17526: byung gi sgron ma khong nas 'char te /
NK115(re)001:17527: gsal stong mi rtog pa'i ye shes nang nas spros pa dang bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17528: shes rab kyi rtsal sngon bas rgyas pa 'phral la
NK115(re)001:17529: skyes nas chos kyi tshig don la dbang ba la
NK115(re)001:17530: sogs pa'i shes rab dri ma med pa 'char ro
NK115(re)001:17531: // gsum pa 'khrid pa dbyings kyi gnad gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:17532: zur dang steng 'og gsum du dbyings snang dal bus
NK115(re)001:17533: 'khrid pa'i skabs las gzhan du mig mi 'gul ba
NK115(re)001:17535: dran rtog tha mal du ma song ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17536: bzhi pa snang ba yul gyi gnad gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:17537: phyi'i yul nam mkha' sprin med la gtad pas dbyings kyi dwangs phyed /
NK115(re)001:17538: nang gi yul rig pa dbyings sgron la gtad pas gzung ba rang 'gag /
NK115(re)001:17539: gsang ba'i yul gtad med chos sku la gtad pas 'dzin pa rang bzhin med par grol ba ste /
NK115(re)001:17540: dang pos yul dang yul can bsre /
NK115(re)001:17541: gnyis pas shes bya nang du sdud /
NK115(re)001:17542: gsum pas du ma ro gcig tu byed pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17543: gnad 'di ma rtogs par kha mig gnam la bgrad
NK115(re)001:17544: nas bltas kyang shes pa phyi ru lus pa gzung
NK115(re)001:17545: yul du song / rig pa nang du bskyil ba
NK115(re)001:17546: 'dzin byed du gol bas gzung 'dzin 'khor ba'i rgyu
NK115(re)001:17547: yul du song / las mi 'ada'o // gnyis pa
NK115(re)001:17548: nyams su blangs pas snang bzhi'i 'char tshul bstan pa
NK115(re)001:17549: yul du song / las mi 'ada'o // ni /
NK115(re)001:17550: de ltar bltas pas nam mkha'i dbyings su 'od lnga'i
NK115(re)001:17552: rdo rje lu gu rgyud 'char ba ni chos nyid mngon sum mo //
NK115(re)001:17553: de nas 'phel te 'od snang rtsib shar dang /
NK115(re)001:17556: za 'og ris la sogs pa shar ba snang nyams
NK115(re)001:17557: dang bde gsal mi rtog pa skye ba shes nyams
NK115(re)001:17558: dang bcas pa ni nyams gong 'phel lo //
NK115(re)001:17559: de nas sku dang zhing khams su rdzogs pa ni rig pa tshad phebs so //
NK115(re)001:17560: phyi nang gi rdos bcas sems kyi 'khrul rtog snang
NK115(re)001:17561: ba'i 'phel dang bcas pa zad pa ni chos nyid
NK115(re)001:17563: gsum pa mtha' rten gyi man ngag la bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:17564: mi 'gul ba gsum la gzhi bca' ba /
NK115(re)001:17565: sdod pa gsum gyis tshad gzung ba /
NK115(re)001:17566: thob pa gsum gyis gzer gdab pa /
NK115(re)001:17567: gdengs bzhis grol tshad bstan pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17569: lus bzhugs stangs las mi 'gul bas rtsa rlung gi srog gcod /
NK115(re)001:17570: mig gzigs stangs las mi 'gul bas chos nyid kyi yul snang 'dzin //
NK115(re)001:17571: sems bzo med las mi 'gul bas sgron ma rgyan du 'char ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17572: gnyis pa sdod pa gsum gyis tshad gzung ba ni /
NK115(re)001:17573: lus bya ba la mi gnas par sdod pas rlung sems dbang du sdud /
NK115(re)001:17574: des rig pa g.yo med du sdod pas tshogs brgyad kyi 'phel zad /
NK115(re)001:17575: ye shes la chags pa med pas snang ba g.yo
NK115(re)001:17576: med du sdod pas zhing khams tshad la phebs pa'o
NK115(re)001:17577: // 'di'i skabs su tshad rmi lam gyis gzung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17578: rtags lus la 'char ba gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:17580: brtson 'grus rab kyis rmi lam gtan nas 'gags /
NK115(re)001:17581: 'bring gis rmi lam rmi lam du shes /
NK115(re)001:17582: tha mas rmi lam ngan pa med par bzang po sha stag tu 'gyur pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17584: dbang bzhi po'i nus pa lus /
NK115(re)001:17587: sems bzhi la thebs pas rim pa ltar chos nyid
NK115(re)001:17588: mngon sum gyi dus na lus rus sbal 'khar gzhong
NK115(re)001:17589: du bcug pa ltar 'dug stangs la 'bral mi phod
NK115(re)001:17590: pa dang / ngag lkugs pa ltar barjooda du med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17591: sems mkha' 'gro rnyi la zin pa ltar rnam rtog
NK115(re)001:17592: 'phro ba ltar snang yang gzhi las ma g.yos pa'o
NK115(re)001:17593: // nyams gong 'phel gyi dus na lus skyes bu
NK115(re)001:17594: nad kyis gdungs pa ltar rgyan dang byi dor med
NK115(re)001:17595: // pa / ngag smyon pa ltar zang thal rjes med pa /
NK115(re)001:17596: sems dug nad kyis zin pa ltar rtog pa'i 'phro 'du chad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17597: rig pa tshad phebs kyi dus su lus glang po
NK115(re)001:17598: che 'dam la mi ltos pa ltar skad cig gis
NK115(re)001:17599: ri brag la thogs med du 'gro /
NK115(re)001:17600: ngag grul bum gyi phrug gu ltar snyan cing yid du 'ong /
NK115(re)001:17601: sems snying la mdas zin pa ltar dran bsam gyi 'phro 'du chad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17602: chos nyid zad sa'i dus na lus dur khrod kyi
NK115(re)001:17603: mi ro ltar dgag sgrub kyi 'khrul pa med pa
NK115(re)001:17604: / ngag brag ca ltar gzhan gyi rjes su zlo ba /
NK115(re)001:17605: sems rims nad byang ba'i skyes bu ltar dran bsam
NK115(re)001:17606: dbyings su dag nas rig pa rang gsal du gnas
NK115(re)001:17607: pa'o // gsum pa thob pa gsum ni /
NK115(re)001:17608: phyi snang ba la dbang thob pas snang rkyen zhing khams su grol /
NK115(re)001:17609: nang phung po la dbang thob pas sgyu lus 'od gsal du grol /
NK115(re)001:17610: gsang ba dbyings rig la dbang thob pas 'khrul rtog rang sar 'gag pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17612: yar sangs rgyas la thob tu re ba dang ma thob kyis dogs pa med /
NK115(re)001:17613: mar 'khor bar mi skye ba'i re ba dang skye yis dogs pa med pa'o //
NK115(re)001:17614: de dag gis ni brtson 'grus rab tshe 'dir grol ba'i gdams pa bshad zin nas /
NK115(re)001:17615: 'bring bar dor grol ba'i gdams ngag la rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK115(re)001:17616: rang bzhin gnas pa'i bar do la shes bya'i dras
NK115(re)001:17617: thag bcad pa thi bya tshang du 'jug pa lta
NK115(re)001:17618: bu'i gdams ngag / 'chi kha bar do la mi
NK115(re)001:17619: gsal ba gsal 'debs pa sgeg mo me long la
NK115(re)001:17620: blta ba lta bu'i gdams ngag /
NK115(re)001:17621: chos nyid bar dor rang snang la yid ches pa
NK115(re)001:17622: ma pang du bu 'jug pa lta bu'i gdams ngag
NK115(re)001:17623: / srid pa'i bar dor lam gyi 'phro mthud pa
NK115(re)001:17624: yur ba rkang chag la wa 'dzugs pa lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:17626: tha ma rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du grol ba'i gdams ngag /
NK115(re)001:17627: rang bzhin gnas pa'i dus su sbyong ba /
NK115(re)001:17629: sprul sku'i zhing du grol ba'i tshul rnams ni 'di'i gong 'og rnams su'ang yod la /
NK115(re)001:17630: khrid du bsdebs nas nyams su len pa'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:17631: kun mkhyen yab sras kyi man ngag gzhan rnams las
NK115(re)001:17632: shes par bya'o // de yang rnam pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:17633: du ka dag dang lhun grub kyi lam gnyis po
NK115(re)001:17634: gang nyams su len yang bzhag thabs bzhi las mi
NK115(re)001:17635: g.yo ba gal che bas na de bshad pa la
NK115(re)001:17636: shes par bya'o // / dang po rgya mtsho cog bzhag ni /
NK115(re)001:17637: 'di ltar rgya mtsho rlung gis ma dkrugs pa la
NK115(re)001:17638: gza' skar gcal du bkram pa ltar snang yang chu
NK115(re)001:17639: la gza' skar gyis ma gos shing /
NK115(re)001:17640: gza' skar rang mal las ma g.yos pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:17641: rig pa zang thal la gtad pas yul med pa /
NK115(re)001:17642: dbang po'i gdangs ma 'gags kyang yid kyi rtog par ma 'gyus pa /
NK115(re)001:17643: so so rang gis rig kyang dpyod pa'i rnam shes med pa /
NK115(re)001:17644: snang yul grwa ma chag kyang ris chad du med pa ste /
NK115(re)001:17646: dbang po'i sgo rnams gsal ba la //
NK115(re)001:17647: yid kyi rtog pa med pa ste //
NK115(re)001:17649: de yang gshis de'i ngo bo cir yang mi gnas kyang stong pa gud du ma bzung ba /
NK115(re)001:17650: rang bzhin bya rtsol dang bral yang btang snyoms lteng por ma song ba /
NK115(re)001:17651: rtsal snang 'gag pa med kyang zhen 'dzin yul med du song ba ste /
NK115(re)001:17653: rgya mtsho cog bzhag dag gi dgongs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17654: snang ba ma yin snang bar byed pa min //
NK115(re)001:17655: stong pa ma yin stong par yod ma yin //
NK115(re)001:17656: gsal ba ma yin gsal ba chen po'i yul //
NK115(re)001:17657: bying ba ma yin rgod pa ngang gis med //
NK115(re)001:17659: gnyis pa rig pa cog bzhag ni /
NK115(re)001:17660: rig pa ngo shes phyin chad dbang po cig car
NK115(re)001:17661: ba'i grol lugs la blo'i grub mtha' yod mi srid
NK115(re)001:17662: cing zhen 'dzin med pa'i chos nyid kyi ro myong
NK115(re)001:17663: bas khams gsum du ldog pa'i rten zad pa yin
NK115(re)001:17664: la / de'i phyir rig pa nyid la rang babs
NK115(re)001:17665: kyi bsam gtan yod pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:17666: bcos ma nye bar bsgrub mi dgos pa'i tshul yang
NK115(re)001:17667: ka dag gi rig pa zang thal ngos bzung med
NK115(re)001:17668: pa la slad kyi blo'i zhen pas byas shing bcos
NK115(re)001:17669: pa la dgos pa med pas /
NK115(re)001:17670: rang grol klong yangs chen po bar mtshams dang phyi
NK115(re)001:17671: nang med pa'i dgongs pa la rang gnas su bzhag
NK115(re)001:17672: cing / de'ang thod rgal dang 'brel na rig gdangs
NK115(re)001:17673: lu gu rgyud shar ba lhag mthong dang du ma
NK115(re)001:17674: ro gcig tu nyams su blang ba ste /
NK115(re)001:17676: snang ba cig chod dgongs pa ni //
NK115(re)001:17677: rig pa nyid kyi bzhag thabs btsal //
NK115(re)001:17678: gsang ba'i gsang ba chen po ste //
NK115(re)001:17679: snang ba'i stobs kyis pha rol sgrol //
NK115(re)001:17680: chags pas ma bcing rang snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:17682: gsum pa snang ba gcer bzhag ni /
NK115(re)001:17683: rig pa'i dwangs me long lta bu de snang ba
NK115(re)001:17684: kun gyi 'char gzhi yin pas bkag kyang mi khegs
NK115(re)001:17685: te 'gag med kyi rtsal yin pas so //
NK115(re)001:17686: bsgrubs kyang mi 'grub ste skye med du rang log par 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:17687: de bas na yul rig cing rnam pa la 'jal 'jal 'dra ba de ched du mi sdud /
NK115(re)001:17689: rang sa ru mi bskyil bar cer yan du bzhag
NK115(re)001:17690: pas chos nyid kyi ngang las 'da' mi shes pa
NK115(re)001:17691: ste / rin po che spungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:17692: chos can mtshan mar snang dus su //
NK115(re)001:17693: nga la yon tan rang snang bas //
NK115(re)001:17694: 'di la blang dang dor mi bya //
NK115(re)001:17696: 'di'i dgongs pa ni snang shes gnyis med ro gcig tu nyams su blang ba'i don te /
NK115(re)001:17697: de ltar ma shes nas gang shar la ce re
NK115(re)001:17698: blta ba ni shes pa yul 'byams kyi gdon gyis
NK115(re)001:17700: rtog pa nying 'khrul du song ba'i gnad ma go /
NK115(re)001:17701: rang sa ru bzung yang gnyen po'i gol sgrib ste
NK115(re)001:17702: srin bu rang nyid kyi kha chus bcings pa dang
NK115(re)001:17703: mtshungs la / yang gnas pa ngo bor bzung nas mi rtog par bsgrub /
NK115(re)001:17704: 'char ba rtsal du bltas nas shar grol du bskyang
NK115(re)001:17705: ngo zer ba yang dngos gcig rdzas su 'gal ba'i
NK115(re)001:17706: nyams len cha gnyis par song bas skye 'gag la
NK115(re)001:17707: so 'dzugs pa'i bsam gtan pa zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17708: 'o na ji ltar yin na rang ngo dang rtsal
NK115(re)001:17709: zhes brjod pa de 'khrul gzhi dang 'khrul snang 'byed
NK115(re)001:17711: rig pa ngos zin nas lhag mthong gi de nyid
NK115(re)001:17712: shes pa'i gnas skabs na chu bo dang rba rlabs
NK115(re)001:17713: sam / me long dang byad gzugs ltar dngos gcig rnam 'gyur log pa tsam yin pas /
NK115(re)001:17717: rtog dpyod du langs pa gang gi tshe yang rig
NK115(re)001:17718: pa rjen pa zang ka ma de nyid rang ngos
NK115(re)001:17719: bzung bas / dus gsum gyi rtog pa'i 'brel thag
NK115(re)001:17720: chod pas chos sku rang gnas kyi gnas lugs so
NK115(re)001:17721: so rang gis rig pa'i ye shes zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:17722: bzung bas / / klong drug pa las /
NK115(re)001:17723: skyes bu gang gis 'das pa'i rjes ma bzung /
NK115(re)001:17725: da lta'i shes pa rang so la bzhag na shes
NK115(re)001:17726: pa thams cad snga phyi med par gcig tu 'dres
NK115(re)001:17727: nas gcig 'dus ngo bo gcig pa zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:17728: / dus gsum mnyam pa nyid du rig pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK115(re)001:17730: 'di'i dran pa ni gzung dran ma yin pas rig pa rtod phur la mi gtad /
NK115(re)001:17731: ma rig pa ni ye ngas brjed 'byams 'khrul la brjod pas lhag mthong gi gdangs mi rnal /
NK115(re)001:17732: sangs rgyas ni rig pa yin pas dus gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:17733: 'brel thag bcad la bcas bcos mi bya ba'i don
NK115(re)001:17735: de ltar bzhag thabs gsum goms pa las /
NK115(re)001:17736: bzhi pa ri bo cog bzhag ngang gis 'byung ste /
NK115(re)001:17737: dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang la gnas nas ri
NK115(re)001:17738: bo lta bu las mi g.yo ba'i gdengs rnyed pa'i
NK115(re)001:17739: tshe / rkyen snang sna tshogs rlung lta bus mi g.yo ba ste /
NK115(re)001:17741: ri bo cog bzhag lta ba gsang ba nyid //
NK115(re)001:17742: the tshom ma yin 'gyu ba ngang gis med //
NK115(re)001:17744: mdor na rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs ni /
NK115(re)001:17756: smras tshad nang 'gal bas tshig lam du tha chad /
NK115(re)001:17757: bsam tshad spros par song bas rang ngo khas len mi shes pa'i ngang du la bzla ba ste /
NK115(re)001:17758: rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me lo las /
NK115(re)001:17759: rig pa'i chos thams cad bdag rtog gi blo dang bral bar shes par gyis shig /
NK115(re)001:17761: bzhag thabs bzhi po 'di ni 'grel ba'i tshig la bcos bslad med par bris pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17762: de ltar ma rtogs pa la ngo sprad pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:17763: sems kyi ngo sprod gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:17764: ye shes kyi ngo sprod nyi shu rtsa gcig rnams ni 'grel pa las shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:17765: gnyis pa khyad par gyi chos shes dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17766: gong du ji skad bshad zin pa de yi phyir
NK115(re)001:17767: na gsang ba'i theg pa thams cad kyi nang nas
NK115(re)001:17768: kyang yang rab spros pa dang bral ba rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:17769: don du bstan pa'i rig pa rang snang gi lam
NK115(re)001:17770: yang gsang bla na med pa 'dir zhugs pa'i ranga
NK115(re)001:17771: gi sde pa rnams kyis 'og ma'i yid dpyod kyi
NK115(re)001:17772: lta sgoma spyod 'brasa kuna dang khyad zhugas pa'i khyad
NK115(re)001:17773: chos kyi matshana nyid legas para phyed shes para byas
NK115(re)001:17774: nas dben par phyi nang gi rnam par g.yengs pa
NK115(re)001:17775: thams cad spangs nas dad mos dang brtson 'grus drag
NK115(re)001:17776: pos bsran tshugs par byas te bsgom pa ni mana
NK115(re)001:17777: ngaga zab mo 'di lta bu dang 'phrad pa'i don
NK115(re)001:17778: po yina pas tshul bzhin shes nas 'bad par gyis
NK115(re)001:17780: de yang kun mkhyen chos rjes gnad rnam pa bdun gyis 'phags par gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:17781: brtson 'grus che chung tsam las dbang po la rno rtul med pa'i gnad 1dang /
NK115(re)001:17782: de bzhin du mngon sum bltar yod pas yid dpyod la mi ltos pa 2dang /
NK115(re)001:17783: don ji bzhin pa mthong bas tshig la mi ltos pa 3dang /
NK115(re)001:17784: rang gsal mngon du gyur pas gzhi lam 'bras bu dus la mi ltos pa 4dang /
NK115(re)001:17785: rgyu 'bras bzang ngan la mi ltos pas 'bad rtsol blang dor med pa 5dang /
NK115(re)001:17786: rang byung gi 'od gsal khong nas 'char bas na so la rgan gzhon med pa 6dang /
NK115(re)001:17787: sku gsum lam snang du rdzogs nas ka dag gi
NK115(re)001:17788: klong du lhun grub rig pa'i gtan srid zin pa'i
NK115(re)001:17790: 'o na 'di a ti yin na a ti las 'phags sam zhe na /
NK115(re)001:17791: a ti la sems klong man ngag gi sde gsum
NK115(re)001:17792: las sems klong gnyis kas gzhi bral la gdeng du
NK115(re)001:17793: byed kyang dngos su bltar med pas yid dpyod tsam
NK115(re)001:17794: las gnad nges pa mngon du ma mthong ba las
NK115(re)001:17795: 'phags la / man ngag gi sde'i yang /
NK115(re)001:17796: phyi nang gsang ba'i skor gsum bar do'i dus la ltos 'cha' ba las /
NK115(re)001:17797: 'di la tshe 'dir 'od lus su grol ba'i gnad yod pas 'phags pa yin no gsungs /
NK115(re)001:17798: gnyis pa snang ba yul gyi blo can gyi nyams len bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:17799: mnyam bzhag zhi lhag gi skyong tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:17800: rnam rtog lam du 'khyer tshul lo //
NK115(re)001:17801: dang po mnyam bzhag zhi lhag gi skyong tshul la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:17804: zhi lhag zung 'brel gyis don bsdu ba'o //
NK115(re)001:17805: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:17806: de ltar rig pa rang snang gi blo can rnams
NK115(re)001:17807: ni mngon sum rang thog tu ngo 'phrod pa de
NK115(re)001:17808: gcig pu'i ngang skyong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17809: gnad gcun pa la brten nas rig gdangs mngon sum
NK115(re)001:17810: du mthong ba la sogs pa'i stobs kyis grol bar
NK115(re)001:17811: 'gyur ba de lta yin moda kyi /
NK115(re)001:17812: 'on kyang badga dang bdag gir 'dzina pa dang bcas
NK115(re)001:17813: pa'i tshogs brgyad glo bura ba nang gi 'khrul pa'i
NK115(re)001:17814: rkyen chosa kyi dbyingas ka nas daga pa'i klong du
NK115(re)001:17815: ma nuba para te nub par byed mi nus pa'i
NK115(re)001:17816: snang ba yul gyi blo can rnams la rig ngo
NK115(re)001:17817: cung zad re 'phrod kyang gshis la grub ma myong
NK115(re)001:17818: ba'i 'khrul snang glo bura ba phyi yul gyi rkyen
NK115(re)001:17819: bzang ngan gyis bslu bar 'gyur ba'i phyir na rtog
NK115(re)001:17820: tshogsa thams cad gzung 'dzin gyi chosa su snang zhing
NK115(re)001:17821: bslad pa 'di gdul ba'i thabs la brtson dgos te
NK115(re)001:17822: / bsags pa dman pa'i gang zag tha mala pa
NK115(re)001:17823: de nyid kyis ngo sprod re thob pa dang dal
NK115(re)001:17824: khom res 'ag'i nyams len tsam la dgag sgrub blang
NK115(re)001:17825: dor las 'das pa'i lam du rlom nas tha snyad
NK115(re)001:17826: 'dogs kyang 'chi kha dang bar dor mi phan zhing
NK115(re)001:17827: rtog pa dang nyon mongs rang rgyud pas rgyud bcings
NK115(re)001:17828: te thog med nas rang nyid 'khor ba'i gnas su
NK115(re)001:17829: 'dzin par byed pa'i tshul de las gzhan du ma
NK115(re)001:17831: srida pa'i rtsa bar gyur pas na badga po ste
NK115(re)001:17832: gzung 'dzin de yis dang po'i las can rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:17833: ngo bo la sgrib pa'i phyir na thun mong ba
NK115(re)001:17834: dang mthun pa'i sems gnas bsgrub tshul yang 'di nas
NK115(re)001:17837: bsgom pa zhes ni sems gnas la //
NK115(re)001:17838: 'gyu ba phyi nang gcod pa ste //
NK115(re)001:17841: rtsa dang rlung dang thig le dang //
NK115(re)001:17842: lus gnad dmigs dang stong pa ni //
NK115(re)001:17843: bsgom pa zhes ni 'dod pa yin //
NK115(re)001:17844: zhes ngo bo dmigs gtad la brten pa'i sems gnas /
NK115(re)001:17845: dgos pa'i de nyid brtan pa las 'bras bur re ba /
NK115(re)001:17846: byed las gzung 'dzin 'gog 'dod kyi zhi gnas dang lhag mthong 'brel bar bsgrub pa ste /
NK115(re)001:17847: 'di la zhi gansa dang lhag mthonga ngo bo gciga pa'i 'khrid tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:17848: zhi lhag so so ba yi 'khrida tshul rnam pa
NK115(re)001:17849: gnyis yod pa lasa theg pa 'og ma dang thun
NK115(re)001:17850: mong ba ni mdo lam du yang bshad zin to
NK115(re)001:17851: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:17852: zhi lhag ngo bo gcig pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17854: dang po zhi lhag ngo bo gcig pa'i 'khrid tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:17855: 'dir dang po zhi lhag ngo bo gcig pa'i phyogsa
NK115(re)001:17856: 'phags pa 'da' ka ye shes kyi mdo'i dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:17858: 'khor 'das su 'dzin pa'i chos rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK115(re)001:17859: par dag pa de kho na nyid kyi ting nge
NK115(re)001:17860: 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe na /
NK115(re)001:17861: rtse gcig pa'i ngang las mi g.yo bar gansa pa'i cha'i bsam gatana te zhi gnas dang /
NK115(re)001:17862: de'i mtshan nyid dngos po med par 'du shes pa'i
NK115(re)001:17863: gasla cha'i so sor rtog pa'i shesa raba ni lhag
NK115(re)001:17864: mthong ste // zhi lhaga zunga du 'brel ba'i don
NK115(re)001:17865: de lasa gzhan gzung 'dzin gnyis su 'dzin pa min
NK115(re)001:17866: pa'i matha'a dang bral ba'i chos nyid kyi dona de
NK115(re)001:17867: la mnyam par bazhaga par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:17869: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas
NK115(re)001:17870: na dngos po med pa'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom
NK115(re)001:17872: de yang yang goms pas theg chen gyi chos thams
NK115(re)001:17873: cad kyi snying po byang chub kyi sems rnam pa
NK115(re)001:17874: gnyis rgyud la skye bas rjes thob thams cad snying
NK115(re)001:17875: rje chen po'i rang bzhin du 'char ba'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:17877: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems su 'dus pas
NK115(re)001:17878: snying rje chen po'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par
NK115(re)001:17880: de ltar mnyam bzhag tu stong nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:17881: rjes thob tu snying rje gnyis zung du 'jug pa
NK115(re)001:17882: la goms pas tshogs gnyis cig car du rdzogs te
NK115(re)001:17883: 'od gsal gyi rang bzhin 'phags pa'i bden pa la
NK115(re)001:17884: reg pa'i tshul / chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis
NK115(re)001:17885: mi dmigs shing 'od gsal bas na dngos po ci
NK115(re)001:17886: la yang mi chags pa'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom
NK115(re)001:17887: reg pa'i tshul / par bya'o // zhes so //
NK115(re)001:17888: de yang dngos por lta ba ni 'khor bar zag
NK115(re)001:17889: byed dang shes bya'i sgrib pa yin pas so so
NK115(re)001:17890: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis bcom nas sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:17891: kyi rang bzhin rang sems rtogs pa las byung ba'i
NK115(re)001:17892: tshul / sems rtogs na ye shes yin pas na
NK115(re)001:17893: sangs rgyas gzhan du mi btsal ba'i 'du shes rab
NK115(re)001:17896: rkang pa bzhi po 'dis bsgom pa'i mdo thams cad nye bar bsdus pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:17897: 'di'i 'du shes ni thos bsam gyi dus na rnam par rig pa can gyi rtog dpyod yin kyang /
NK115(re)001:17898: bsgom pa'i shes rab kyi dus na rnam par rig
NK115(re)001:17899: pa las 'das pa'i ye shes yin pas bag chags
NK115(re)001:17901: 'jam dpal gyi lta ba mdor bstan pa las /
NK115(re)001:17902: ye shes kyis ni phug pa'i sems //
NK115(re)001:17905: gnyis pa zhi lhag so so ba'i 'khrid tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:17906: gnyis pa zhi gnas dang lhag mthong so so ba'i phyogsa la'ang 'khrid tshul lam /
NK115(re)001:17907: bsgrub tshul gyi dbye ba gnyis su grub ste /
NK115(re)001:17908: gtso bo thos bsam gyi shesa rab lasa byung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17909: gtso bo bsgom thabs kyi gadmas ngaga lasa byunga ba gnyis yod par mdo las kyang byung ngo //
NK115(re)001:17910: de ltar yang dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK115(re)001:17911: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong ni gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:17912: shes rab las byung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:17914: shes rab las byung ba ni mdo sde bcu gnyis
NK115(re)001:17915: kyi tshig yid la byed pa ni zhi gnas so
NK115(re)001:17916: // de'i don rtogs pa ni lhag mthong ngo //
NK115(re)001:17917: gdams ngag las byung ba ni man ngag gis sems mi g.yo bar byed pa ni zhi gnas so //
NK115(re)001:17918: de'i don rtogs pa ni lhag mthong ngo //
NK115(re)001:17920: de la dang po shes raba lasa byung ba zhes
NK115(re)001:17921: bya ba ni sgra yi rjesa su mthuna pa'i don
NK115(re)001:17923: de yang sgrar grags pa gzhan gyis bshad pa la nyan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17924: brdar gyur pa dpe char gnas pa la bltas pa
NK115(re)001:17925: lta bu'i rkyen gyis sgrar snang ba rang gi blo
NK115(re)001:17926: la sgra spyi'i rnam par snang ba gtan tshigs la
NK115(re)001:17927: sogs pas dpyad cing gzhig pas bdag med pa la
NK115(re)001:17928: sogs pa'i don spyir shar zhing bsam byung gis sgro
NK115(re)001:17929: 'dogs nang nas chod de nges pa rnyed par byas
NK115(re)001:17930: pa'i don de nyid bsgom pa yin pas /
NK115(re)001:17931: dang po thosa pa dang bsam pa'i shes rab kyis
NK115(re)001:17932: ji ltar nges pa'i dona gyi dmigs pa de'i ngang
NK115(re)001:17933: la sems gnas pa'i thabs dgu la sogs pa'i sgo
NK115(re)001:17934: nas rtse gciga tu yang yang rgyun bsrings te bzhag
NK115(re)001:17935: pas rnam rtog gi rgyu ba thams cad dmigs pa
NK115(re)001:17936: de kho na'i ngang la zhi ba dang ste de
NK115(re)001:17937: nyid la gnas pa na dngos po la mngon par
NK115(re)001:17938: zhen pa'i blo rtog rags pa nub cing sems las
NK115(re)001:17939: su rung ba'i zhi gnas grub pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:17940: de lasa dmigs par bya ba'i yul bdag med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17941: dmigs pa byed pa'i blo bdag med do zhes pa'i
NK115(re)001:17942: rnam pa de yang rang bzhin gyis spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:17943: bral ba'i dona du rtogsa te dmigs pa'i 'dzin stangs
NK115(re)001:17944: kun dang bral bar gyur pa ni gnas lugs kyi
NK115(re)001:17945: don la rab tu zhugs pa'i lhag mthonga matshana nyid
NK115(re)001:17946: pa yin pas 'bad pas sgrub par byed pa nyid
NK115(re)001:17947: do // man ngaga las byung ba zhes bya ba
NK115(re)001:17948: ni de 'dra ba'i sgra tshig gi rjes su 'brangs
NK115(re)001:17949: te dpyod pa la mi ltos par don gyi rjes
NK115(re)001:17951: zhi lhag bsgrub pa'i thabs bla mas man ngag gi
NK115(re)001:17952: sgo nas ji ltar bstan pa'i don de la mnyam
NK115(re)001:17954: de yang phyi'i dmigs pa sku gzugs sogs la gtad nas bsgom pa'am /
NK115(re)001:17955: nang gi dmigs pa rlung thig sogs la sems 'dzin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:17956: lus gnad dang rtsa rlung sogs kyi gnad gcun pas
NK115(re)001:17957: bde gsal mi rtog pa skye ba la sogs pa'i
NK115(re)001:17958: dmigs pa de dag gi ngang la semsa ni rnam
NK115(re)001:17959: rtog gis g.yo ba med par rtse gcig tu gnas
NK115(re)001:17961: gang snang ba'i dmigs pa de dag sems las gzhan du'ang ma grub la /
NK115(re)001:17962: sems nyid kyang ma yin pas rang bzhin med la /
NK115(re)001:17963: gang la snang ba'i sems de yi rang gi ranga
NK115(re)001:17964: bzhina yang gdod ma nas ma skyes shing mi 'gag
NK115(re)001:17965: pa rang bzhin gyis zung 'jug 'od gsal ba'i bdag
NK115(re)001:17966: nyid can du shes nas gang la'ang 'dzin pa med
NK115(re)001:17967: pa ni lhag mthonga mtshan nyid pa ste /
NK115(re)001:17969: gnyis dang gnyis med dag pa ni //
NK115(re)001:17970: bsgom dang mi bsgom ming du btags pa ste //
NK115(re)001:17972: de lta bu'i zhi lhag gi don sgom pa la
NK115(re)001:17973: snying nas brod pa ma bskyed na rnam g.yeng dang
NK115(re)001:17974: phyi bshol du lus nas nam yang bsgom pa'i dus
NK115(re)001:17975: mi 'ong bas 'di ltar bsam par bya ste /
NK115(re)001:17976: bdag ni thog ma med pa nas med snang rnam
NK115(re)001:17977: rtog gi rba rlabs glo bur ba 'di kho na'i
NK115(re)001:17978: dbang du song nas sngar yang sdug bsngal de tsam
NK115(re)001:17979: zhig gis mnar / da lta yang blo lang shor
NK115(re)001:17980: gyi ngan goms shog dril dang 'dra ba 'di'i dbang
NK115(re)001:17981: du song nas rang sems so mi bsod cing sdug
NK115(re)001:17982: bsngal sna tshogs pa 'du byed pas phyi ma'i mu
NK115(re)001:17983: mtha' med par 'khor ba'i g.yang sa nyam nga bar
NK115(re)001:17985: phung khrol kun gyi rtsa ba ni rnam par rtog
NK115(re)001:17986: pa'i gzhan dbang du gyur pa 'di la thug pas
NK115(re)001:17987: lus srog 'dor ba la bab kyang sems sbyong ba'i
NK115(re)001:17988: dran rgyun 'di ni gtong bar mi bya snyam du
NK115(re)001:17989: yang yang dam bca' bar bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:17990: yang sems la phan pa'i gdams ngag nyams su blang na ni thos rgya mi che yang /
NK115(re)001:17992: kha bshad mi mkhas kyang sems nyid rgya mtsho lta bu je dwangs dang /
NK115(re)001:17993: rnam rtog rba rlabs lta bu je zhi la song
NK115(re)001:17994: nas sa lam gyi yon tan thams cad rgya mtsho
NK115(re)001:17995: la gza' skar bkra ba bzhin ngang gis rgyud la
NK115(re)001:17996: skye bar 'gyur bas na 'di las ches mchog tu
NK115(re)001:17997: gyur pa'i don zhig ni bsgrub tu med do snyam
NK115(re)001:17998: du bkres pa zas la gdung ba bzhin du don
NK115(re)001:17999: gnyer gyi 'dun pa drag po bskyed par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:18000: de ltar bskyed nas kyang gus sbyor dang rtag sbyor
NK115(re)001:18001: gyi brtson 'grus kyis sems rgyud 'dul ba la 'bad
NK115(re)001:18002: par bya'o // de lta ma yin par 'jig rten
NK115(re)001:18003: tshe 'di'i bya ba tshong so nam sogs kyis g.yeng
NK115(re)001:18004: bar gyur na smos ci dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:18005: sems rgyud la ma sbyar ba'i thos bsam la brtson khul che ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18006: gdams khrid kyi zhus grangs mang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18007: gzhan snang du spyod tshul btsun pa sogs kyis ni ci yang mi phan te /
NK115(re)001:18008: mkhas pa'i grags pa thob pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18009: kun gyi bkur gnas su gyur pa phal che ba
NK115(re)001:18010: yang rkyen ngan pa zhig thog tu babs tshe 'jig
NK115(re)001:18011: rten phal pa rnams dang khyad par med par mthong
NK115(re)001:18012: ba 'di lta bu la bsams nas blo sna nang
NK115(re)001:18013: du bkug ste gdams ngag yod dgu'i rno so ji
NK115(re)001:18014: snyed pa thams cad sems kyi tha ba 'di kho
NK115(re)001:18016: gsum pa zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:18017: mdora bsdu na gang zag gi blo rim gyis zhi
NK115(re)001:18018: lhag gi rnal 'byor la brten nas gzung 'dzin gyi
NK115(re)001:18019: rnam rtog grol tshul rnam pa gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:18020: gang zag dbang po raba kyisa ni zhi lhag rim
NK115(re)001:18021: gyis bsgrub mi dgos par rig pa ngo 'phrod cing
NK115(re)001:18022: gdengs su gyur pas ngan pa'i rtog pa tshul min
NK115(re)001:18023: yid byed dang / nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa ji
NK115(re)001:18024: snyed pa thams cad shar ba'i rang dus de nyid
NK115(re)001:18025: na rjes mthud med par grol bar gyur na gang
NK115(re)001:18026: shar kun chosa skur lhongsa pa yin pas /
NK115(re)001:18027: de'i tshe na rnam rtog bazanga po dad pa la sogs pas phan 'dogs mi dgos te /
NK115(re)001:18028: dge bas bsgrub par 'dod pa'i 'bras bu chos sku rang gi ngang la gnas pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:18029: rnam rtog ngana pa nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa skyes
NK115(re)001:18030: kyang chos sku zang thal de nyid du lhongs pa
NK115(re)001:18031: las 'khor bar 'phen pa'i las mi gsog pas gnod
NK115(re)001:18032: pa mi skyel ba'i phyir de gnyis gang skyes kyang
NK115(re)001:18033: mgo manyama par gyur pa na gnyen po bsten mi
NK115(re)001:18034: dgosa te / yul thog tu shor ma myong ba'i
NK115(re)001:18035: shes pa rig pa'i ngang du shar grol dus mtshungs
NK115(re)001:18036: dgosa te / pa'i phyir te / kun byed las /
NK115(re)001:18037: ji bzhin ma bcos rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la //
NK115(re)001:18038: sems dang sems byung rtog pa ci skyes kyang //
NK115(re)001:18039: de nyid skye med ngang du gnas shes pas //
NK115(re)001:18040: bya btsal mtshan ma'i 'du shes kun dang bral //
NK115(re)001:18042: dbang po 'bring gisa lta ba skye med du rtog
NK115(re)001:18043: pa'i nganga ma shor ba'i dwangsa bying rgod dang bral
NK115(re)001:18044: bar zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi lam gomsa pas ting
NK115(re)001:18045: nge 'dzin nam mkha' lta bu'i klong du sems dang
NK115(re)001:18046: sems las byung ba'i bzang ngana gyi rtog pa matha'a
NK115(re)001:18047: dag nam mkha'i dbyingsa su sprin dengs pa bzhin nub
NK115(re)001:18048: par 'gyur ba'i phyir nan tan bskyed nas bsgom par
NK115(re)001:18050: ting nge 'dzin dam pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:18051: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK115(re)001:18052: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag na //
NK115(re)001:18053: ming du mi thogs nyams myong 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:18054: des na ting nge 'dzin ces bya //
NK115(re)001:18056: de la ting nge 'dzin gyi gegs bying rgod gnyis kyi ngos 'dzin ni /
NK115(re)001:18057: spyir rmugs pa dang bying ba gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:18062: lus las su mi rung ba nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:18063: sems las su mi rung ba nyid gang yin pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18065: de yang bsgribs lung ma bstan dang mi dge ba
NK115(re)001:18066: gang rung gti mug gi char gtogs par gsungs la
NK115(re)001:18069: de la gal te rmugs pa dang gnyid kyis non
NK115(re)001:18070: nas sems bying ngam bying du dogs par mthong na
NK115(re)001:18071: / zhes rmugs pa las byung ba'i sems mun pa babs pa lta bu'i yul mi gsal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18072: blo'i 'dzin stangs 'phang dma' ru song bas bying ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18073: ha cang nang du bsdus pas na zhum pa zhes kyang bya ste /
