NK115(re)001:18075: lhag mthong brtson pa'i stobs kyi mthus //
NK115(re)001:18076: zhum par gyur na gzengs kyang bstod //
NK115(re)001:18078: de yang dmigs pa la 'dzin stangs lhod nas mi
NK115(re)001:18079: gsal ba'am dam par mi 'dzin dwangs cha yod kyang
NK115(re)001:18080: bying bar 'gro zhes gsungs pa de ni zhi gnas
NK115(re)001:18083: dmigs pa la ni brten nas su //
NK115(re)001:18084: mi dmigs pa ni rab tu skye //
NK115(re)001:18085: zhes pa ltar lhag mthong mtshan nyid pa bsgrub pa'i
NK115(re)001:18086: sngon du chos rang bzhin med pa'i nges pa brtan
NK115(re)001:18087: par goms pa sogs la shin tu gal che bar
NK115(re)001:18088: snang ste / dge ba'i dmigs pa gang yin kyang
NK115(re)001:18089: der sems kyi rnam pa lhang gi shar nas de'i
NK115(re)001:18090: rgyun goms dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:18091: 'on kyang dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i sems 'dzin gyi
NK115(re)001:18092: sgom thams cad la de ltar bshad pa yin gyi
NK115(re)001:18093: / dbu ma'i sgom don dngos gzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:18094: mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim thun min rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:18095: skabs su ni sems rtog thams cad dbyings su nub
NK115(re)001:18096: cing ye shes kyi dwangs cha gsal ngar dang ldan
NK115(re)001:18097: na ting nge 'dzin skyon med du song ba yin
NK115(re)001:18098: pas 'dzin stangs lhod pas ni bying bar mi 'gro
NK115(re)001:18103: sdug pa'i mtshan ma'i rjes su 'jug pa'i 'dod chags
NK115(re)001:18104: kyi char gtogs pa'i sems ma zhi ba ste zhi
NK115(re)001:18105: gnas kyi bar du gcod pa'i las can no //
NK115(re)001:18108: dge ba'i dmigs pa gzhan la sems 'phro ba rgod pa ma yin par gsungs na'ang /
NK115(re)001:18111: gang la dmigs par bya ba'i gnas de nas gzhan
NK115(re)001:18112: pa'i dge ba yin yang 'dra ste rlung gis yid
NK115(re)001:18113: sbur nas cung zad kyang gnas su mi ster na
NK115(re)001:18114: bsam gtan gyi bar chad yin par blta'o //
NK115(re)001:18115: yang dbang po tha mas ni thos bsam gyi dpyad
NK115(re)001:18116: pas drangs pa'i bdag med la nges shes cung zad
NK115(re)001:18117: thob pa'am / khyad par bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas rig ngo cung zad re 'phrod kyang /
NK115(re)001:18118: mi bsam dgu bsam gyi rnam rtog shin tu mang ba mtsho rlabs 'khrugs pa lta bu'am /
NK115(re)001:18119: rang dbang mi 'thob pa shing bal rlung gis khyer ba lta bu'am /
NK115(re)001:18120: lhag mthong gi don la gnas su mi ster zhing
NK115(re)001:18121: nyam chung ba rlung gseb tu bzhag pa'i mar me
NK115(re)001:18123: thog mara lhag mthong gi rten du zhi gansa 'ab'a zhiga batsala bar bya ba ni /
NK115(re)001:18124: dmigs pa'i rten gang yang rung ba la sems rtse
NK115(re)001:18125: gcig tu gtad nas skad cig kyang mi yeng bar
NK115(re)001:18127: sems kyi glang chen myos pa ni //
NK115(re)001:18128: chos la sems pa'i ka chen la //
NK115(re)001:18129: ji ltar btags pa mi 'chor bar //
NK115(re)001:18130: de ltar 'bad pa kun gyis brtag /
NK115(re)001:18132: de'ang res 'ga' tsam dang yun thung du tsam gyis
NK115(re)001:18133: ni mi 'grub pas nyams lnga mthar phyin gyi bar
NK115(re)001:18136: bi ma la'i phyag rgya bsam gtan gyi 'grel bar /
NK115(re)001:18137: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga //
NK115(re)001:18138: bsam gtan nyams kyi skye tshul yin //
NK115(re)001:18140: sems rtse gcig tu bzung ba'i rgyun bsrings te bsgom pa na /
NK115(re)001:18141: thog mar g.yo ba'i nyams zhes bya ba rnam rtog
NK115(re)001:18142: dang nyon mongs thams cad ri gzar gyi 'bab chu
NK115(re)001:18143: ltar langs pa na sgom gyi mgo zin pa yin
NK115(re)001:18144: kyang shin tu bzod par dka' zhing rnam rtog gi
NK115(re)001:18145: rkyen khar 'chor du nye bas rnam rtog dgra ru
NK115(re)001:18147: de ltar rtog pa sngar bas mang du song bas
NK115(re)001:18148: sgom snying mi 'dod pa lta bu byung yang 'dun
NK115(re)001:18149: brtson sems pa dpyod pa'i rkang pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK115(re)001:18150: bsran btsugs shing rgyun bsrings te bsgom pa na /
NK115(re)001:18151: thob pa'i nyams zhes bya ba rong khung dog pa'i
NK115(re)001:18152: 'bab chu lta bu rnam rtog 'phro mu nas yud
NK115(re)001:18153: tsam re rtog med du zhi me re gnas pa
NK115(re)001:18154: zhig 'byung la / de'i rgyun mthud de bsgoms pas
NK115(re)001:18155: goms pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog thang chad pa'i nyams
NK115(re)001:18156: zhes bya ba dper na g.yo 'gul mang po byed
NK115(re)001:18157: mi nus pa rgan po'i spyod po lta bu'am /
NK115(re)001:18158: 'dab chags rnying bzung ba ltar phal cher rtog med
NK115(re)001:18159: du gnas pa las res 'ga' rtog pa ban bun
NK115(re)001:18161: 'di dag gi skabs rnam rtog khong shed chag pa'i dus zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:18162: skabs skabs su rnam rtog skyes pa de'i dbang du
NK115(re)001:18163: 'gro mi dgos pas bsgom 'dod kyi brod pa skyes
NK115(re)001:18164: nas bsgoms pas brtan pa'i nyams zhes bya ba mtsho
NK115(re)001:18165: chung ser bus bskyod pa ltar phal cher rtog med
NK115(re)001:18166: du gnas pa las rkyen drag pos cung zad g.yo
NK115(re)001:18167: yang sgyu ma'i dmag dang smig rgyu'i chu ltar nus
NK115(re)001:18168: med du song nas gnod par mi 'gyur ro //
NK115(re)001:18169: da dung yang 'bad de bsgoms pas mthar phyin pa'i
NK115(re)001:18170: nyams zhes bya ba rgya mtsho rlabs dang bral ba'am
NK115(re)001:18171: / ri bo ltar gnas pa la rkyen gang gyis
NK115(re)001:18172: kyang mi gnod par ma zad slar la bogs 'byin
NK115(re)001:18173: cing btang 'gro bzhag sdod la rang dbang thob nas
NK115(re)001:18174: rten gang dang gang la dmigas na de dang de
NK115(re)001:18175: la lhan gyis gnas pa'i brtan pa thoba pa na
NK115(re)001:18176: rnam rtog gnyen du shar ba'i dus zhes bya ba
NK115(re)001:18177: bran khol bzang po lta bu rnam rtog rang dbang
NK115(re)001:18179: 'on kyang zhi gnas rkyang ba'i lam gyi nyams lnga
NK115(re)001:18180: mthar phyin nas gnas skabs rnam rtog gi g.yul las
NK115(re)001:18181: rgyal ba ltar snang yang srid pa'i sa bon 'byin
NK115(re)001:18183: de nasa lhag mthonga gi ye shesa so sora rtog pa bskyed de /
NK115(re)001:18184: zhi lhag zung 'brel la yang yang gomsa par byas na /
NK115(re)001:18185: mathara gyis rnam rtog rang sar grol ba'i dus zhes bya ba /
NK115(re)001:18186: dper na rin po che gsera gyi gling du phyin
NK115(re)001:18187: nas rdo phal pa btsal kyang mi rnyed pa bzhina
NK115(re)001:18188: / yengs yul chos nyid du shar nas semsa dang
NK115(re)001:18189: semas byung gi rtog pa gang skyes kyanga rang gnas
NK115(re)001:18190: kyi bsam gtan la spang gnyen gnyis ka mi dgos
NK115(re)001:18191: par snang semsa dbyer med gzhi grol klong yangs chen
NK115(re)001:18192: por 'char bas bsams gtan thun 'jog dang bral ba'i
NK115(re)001:18193: / tshul / rin po che spungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:18194: rang bzhin bsam gtan bar med la //
NK115(re)001:18195: bying rgod med pa ngo mtshar che //
NK115(re)001:18198: 'dzin med chos nyid rang gsal bde ba'i klong //
NK115(re)001:18199: rtog med mkha' khyab chos nyid kun la rol //
NK115(re)001:18201: gnyis pa rnam rtog lam du 'khyer tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:18202: spyir rdo rje'i theg pa'i lam thams cad rnam rtog
NK115(re)001:18203: mi spong bar lam du byed pa'i thabs mkhas can
NK115(re)001:18204: yin yang de'i nang nas thabsa kyi lam mchoga tu
NK115(re)001:18205: gyur pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam pa
NK115(re)001:18206: rnams kyis lhag mthong gi shes rab skyes pa nas
NK115(re)001:18207: bzung rtog pa bzang ngan ganga shara yanga de nyid
NK115(re)001:18208: ched du dgag par yang mi bya la /
NK115(re)001:18209: rtsol bas bsgrub para bya ba yang med cing zhen nas rjes su yang mi 'brang ste /
NK115(re)001:18210: 'di ltar rtog pa dgag na zhi gnas phyogs gcig tu ltung /
NK115(re)001:18211: rtsol bas bsgrub na lhag mthong gshis la 'chor /
NK115(re)001:18212: rjes su 'brangs na rtog pa'i gzhi rtsa mi chod
NK115(re)001:18213: pas tha mal pa dang khyad par med pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:18214: / skye med du rtog pa'i rig pa rnal ma'i
NK115(re)001:18215: nganga de las ma g.yosa tsam du rang sar gnas
NK115(re)001:18216: te dbang po'i sgo mi dgag par tshogs drug lhug
NK115(re)001:18217: par bzhag na sha'i mig dang /
NK115(re)001:18219: shes rab kyi mig sogs spyan lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:18220: sngon gnas rjes dran sogs mngona par shes pa drug
NK115(re)001:18221: la sogsa pa dabnga po dang dbang shes rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:18222: gyis dwangsa pa'i lam gyi yon tan matha'a dag pa
NK115(re)001:18223: so sor rtsol bas bsgrub mi dgos par ngang gis
NK115(re)001:18226: thog ma tha ma dbus zhi zhing //
NK115(re)001:18227: srid dang mya ngan 'das zhi ba //
NK115(re)001:18228: lhun gyis grub pa'i bde chen ni //
NK115(re)001:18229: mtshungs pa med pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK115(re)001:18230: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK115(re)001:18234: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:18235: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:18236: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK115(re)001:18237: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK115(re)001:18239: de ltar rig pa'i ngang skyong zhing rnam rtog ched
NK115(re)001:18240: du dgag pa ma yin pa la sogs pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:18241: bstan pa de'i gol sa bcad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18242: rtoga pa ched du ma bkag kyang rang grol du 'gro dgos kyi /
NK115(re)001:18243: de ltar ma yin par tshogs drug gi yul dang
NK115(re)001:18244: 'brela te gyi nar 'phyan par gyur na ni nyon
NK115(re)001:18245: mongs pa'i rtog pa rags pa'i sgo nas las sna
NK115(re)001:18246: tshogs bsags te gnas 'og ma ngan song la sogs
NK115(re)001:18247: pa'i rgyu bsgrub pa las mi 'da' bas nas skye
NK115(re)001:18248: bo tha mala ba dang khyad par med la /
NK115(re)001:18249: gal te nang du sems 'dzin brtan pa'i ngang la
NK115(re)001:18250: goms na bsam gzugs la sogs pa'i snyoms 'jug thob
NK115(re)001:18251: ste mngon par shes pa la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:18252: 'grub na'ang thabs khyad par can gyis ma zin na
NK115(re)001:18253: snying po med cing nyams par 'gyur ba'i chos can
NK115(re)001:18254: yin zhing / sgra rtog dang zhen yul gyi bdag
NK115(re)001:18255: med la sogs pa'i lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin
NK115(re)001:18256: pa'ang blo'i rnam pa nye bar ma zhi ba nyid
NK115(re)001:18257: kyi phyir shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'am
NK115(re)001:18258: yin zhing / / dbu ma la sogs pa'i man ngag zab mor sgro btags kyang /
NK115(re)001:18259: zab zhi spros bral 'dus ma byas pa'i don dang shin tu ring ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:18261: rtog dang rnam par rtog dang 'du shes 'dzin spongs la //
NK115(re)001:18262: nam mkha' lta bu'i yid kyis 'di la 'jug par gyis //
NK115(re)001:18264: de bas na rig pa'i ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub cing /
NK115(re)001:18265: gang gi'ang 'char gzhir gyur pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe na /
NK115(re)001:18266: de'i gdangs sam rtsal me longa g.ya' dag pa lta
NK115(re)001:18267: bur dwangsa pa'i shes pa la snang yul gzugs la
NK115(re)001:18268: sogs pa ma 'gagsa par rgya mtsho la gaza'a skara
NK115(re)001:18269: bzhina rol pa sna tshogs pa 'char 'char 'dra ba'i
NK115(re)001:18270: cha de dbang po'i gdangs ma 'gags pa'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:18271: du bkra yanga snang dus nyid nas rang gi ngo
NK115(re)001:18272: bos stong pa'i med pa gsal snang tsam yin pas
NK115(re)001:18273: / shes rab snying po las kyang /
NK115(re)001:18274: gzugs stong pa'o zhes bstan la /
NK115(re)001:18275: 'on kyang tha snyad tsam du sgyu ma la sogs
NK115(re)001:18276: pa ltar gzugs su snang ba ni rig pa'i rtsal
NK115(re)001:18277: las rol pa 'gag med du shar ba ste /
NK115(re)001:18278: phar phyin theg pa'i chos skad la /
NK115(re)001:18279: stong nyid kyi ngang las rten 'byung gi snang ba
NK115(re)001:18280: 'gag med du 'char zhes pa de dang don gcig
NK115(re)001:18282: stong pa nyid gzugs so zhes bstan to //
NK115(re)001:18283: des na snang yul gyi rnam pa la 'di lta
NK115(re)001:18284: bu'o zhes der 'dzin pa'i blo yisa gos par ma
NK115(re)001:18285: gyur te / cir yang mi 'dzin na snang tsam
NK115(re)001:18286: gyis mi 'ching ste 'ching byed ni gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK115(re)001:18287: po yin na gzunga ba'i yul dang 'dzina pa'i semsa
NK115(re)001:18288: gnyis phan tshun yul yul can du 'brel ba yul
NK115(re)001:18289: med kyi rig pa'i ngang du chad pa'am rgya mtsho
NK115(re)001:18290: la rlabs thim pa ltar zhig pas chos can gyi
NK115(re)001:18291: dngos po gzugs su snang ba'i rjes su mi rtog
NK115(re)001:18292: cing mi dpyod par ma zad /
NK115(re)001:18293: chos nyid rig pa'i ngang la'ang ched du mi blta /
NK115(re)001:18294: go yul gyi dngos med dang bdag med stong pa
NK115(re)001:18295: la sogs pa la'ang sems mi 'dzin par so so
NK115(re)001:18296: ranga gis rig pa'i ye shes rnama para mi rtog
NK115(re)001:18297: pa'i ngang shugs 'byung gi dran pas bskyangs pas phyi
NK115(re)001:18298: nang gi 'byung ba'i snyigs ma'ang rang dag tu 'gro
NK115(re)001:18300: dngos dang dngos med par dag nas //
NK115(re)001:18301: sgo lnga'i yul zhen dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18302: 'byung ba'i rags pa dag pa dang //
NK115(re)001:18303: ye shes dag pas 'phel snang ston //
NK115(re)001:18304: de las zad pa'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:18306: de lta bu'i rtogs pa mthar phyin pa ni dus
NK115(re)001:18307: gsum gyi rgyal ba'i gshegs shul ye shesa bla ma'i
NK115(re)001:18308: sa la tshe rabs mang po dang yun ring po'i
NK115(re)001:18309: mthar ltos mi dgos par da lta nyid du phyin
NK115(re)001:18310: pa yin te / skye med rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK115(re)001:18311: gar yang ma rtog cir yang ma bsams shig /
NK115(re)001:18312: bcas bcos ma byed rang bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK115(re)001:18313: ma bcos pa de skye med rin chen mdzod //
NK115(re)001:18314: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gshegs shul yin //
NK115(re)001:18316: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu zhing lam la 'bad dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18317: rgyu 'bras dag grol du 'dzin pa 'og ma'i lam
NK115(re)001:18318: lnga po rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po bden pa
NK115(re)001:18319: dbyer med chos nyid yid dpyod las 'das pa'i lam
NK115(re)001:18321: zab mo dbu ma'i skabs su lta bas shes par
NK115(re)001:18322: bya ba'i gzhi stong pa nyid dam spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:18323: bral ba de la 'dir dbyingsa kyi lam 1zhes rig
NK115(re)001:18324: pas rtogs par bya ba'i gzhir tha snyad btags kyang
NK115(re)001:18325: de'i rang bzhin ni tha snyad dang shes byas mi
NK115(re)001:18327: blo dang snyam byed du ma langs pas zhi ba /
NK115(re)001:18328: yod med dang bden rdzun las 'das pas spros bral /
NK115(re)001:18329: rang bzhin gyi gdangs ma 'gags pas 'od gsal /
NK115(re)001:18330: dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pas 'dus ma byas pa ste /
NK115(re)001:18332: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK115(re)001:18333: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig kho bos rnyed //
NK115(re)001:18335: de lta bu'i dbyings de la man ngag gi rgyud
NK115(re)001:18336: 'di nas mtshan nyid gsum dang ldan par bstan te
NK115(re)001:18338: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni //
NK115(re)001:18339: stong pa chen po'i yul nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:18340: gsal ba 'od kyi snang ba dang //
NK115(re)001:18341: ye shes rig pa'i spyod yul gsum //
NK115(re)001:18342: de gsum 'dzom pas dbyings zhes bya //
NK115(re)001:18344: de yang rang bzhin mi 'gyur bas stobs sogs kyi yon tan ye ldan /
NK115(re)001:18345: dbyings snang rig pa dang rten dang brten par 'brel yang ngo bo la bdag tu mi 'dzin /
NK115(re)001:18346: stong pa nye tshe ba ma yin pa /
NK115(re)001:18347: blo'i dngos po dang dran pa'i rang yul zad pas
NK115(re)001:18348: 'khor ba gzhi med du mtshan nyid chad kyang bem
NK115(re)001:18350: myang 'das kyi gzhi ye nas lhun gyis grub pas
NK115(re)001:18351: rang bzhin 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po'i dbyings zhes
NK115(re)001:18352: bya ste / de'i rang bzhin khregs chod kyi lam
NK115(re)001:18353: du dbang rnon gyis cig car du rtogs nas ngang
NK115(re)001:18355: 'bring dang tha mas kyang rim gyis goms pa'i stobs
NK115(re)001:18356: kyis rtogs nas de'i ngang la 'jog pa'i bsgom pa
NK115(re)001:18357: ni rtogs byed kyi rig pa rang dang tha dad
NK115(re)001:18358: du med pas chos nyid gciga pa'i lam ma nor
NK115(re)001:18359: ba yin par rig par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:18360: tshul de lta bu la thod rgal gyi gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:18361: na gzhi na gnas pa'i dag dbyings zhes bya ste
NK115(re)001:18362: / de'i ngang la goms pas 'od gsal gyi lam
NK115(re)001:18363: snang yang zhar la mthong tshul sngar bshad zin to
NK115(re)001:18364: / // riga pa'i lam 2ni shesa rab khyad para can yin te /
NK115(re)001:18365: 'di ltar gzhal bya'i yul dbyings kyi rang bzhin shes
NK115(re)001:18366: pa'i shes rab med na bshad ma thag pa'i nang
NK115(re)001:18367: dbyings stong pa zang thal de yang stong chad cang
NK115(re)001:18368: med por gol ba'i nyen yod pas /
NK115(re)001:18369: dbyings kyi rang bzhin de rang dang ro gcig pa'i
NK115(re)001:18370: tshul du rtogs pa'i so so rang gi rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:18371: shes rab khyad par can de rig pa'i cha nas
NK115(re)001:18373: ngo bo nyid ma grub pas rtag par ma gol /
NK115(re)001:18374: yul rig pa'i cha nas yid dang mtshungs kyang yul
NK115(re)001:18375: phyir mi 'brang zhing rnam rig gis bslad pa med
NK115(re)001:18376: pas las dang bag chags 'du mi byed pas mya
NK115(re)001:18377: ngan las 'das pa'i bdag nyid can no //
NK115(re)001:18378: 'oda gasla gyi lam 3zhes pa ni ngo bo ngos
NK115(re)001:18379: bzung med pa'i sems nyid kyang bem stong lta bur
NK115(re)001:18380: song ba med pas nang gsal ka dag gi dbyings
NK115(re)001:18381: mtha' bral dri ma med pa'i ngang la goms pas
NK115(re)001:18382: dbyings la ye ldan du yod pa'i sku gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:18383: snang cha las rlung dag pa'i cha las 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:18384: gyi lam snang du mngon pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:18386: ye nas med pa'i stong pa yis //
NK115(re)001:18388: bya byed bral ba'i stong pa yis //
NK115(re)001:18389: sku gsum mtshon pa'i 'od snang rnyed //
NK115(re)001:18391: de yang ye shes 'od gsal gyi snang ba 'dzin
NK115(re)001:18392: byed rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma lta stangs kyis gzir
NK115(re)001:18393: bas mig phugs kyi 'od tshon gang ba dbang po'i
NK115(re)001:18394: mngon sum par gsal ba'i 'od lnga zlum skor rang
NK115(re)001:18395: gsal kha dog dwangs pa nyag gcig spros pa dang
NK115(re)001:18396: bral ba'i don mtshon par 'char ba ni thig le
NK115(re)001:18397: stong pa'i sgron ma yin pas rnam pa gnyis po
NK115(re)001:18398: de la brten nas 'od gsal gyi snang ba 'char
NK115(re)001:18400: khregsa choda kyi lam 4ni ngo rang thog tu 'phrod
NK115(re)001:18401: de gzhi yul med du rtogs pa'i dus nas gshis
NK115(re)001:18402: ka dag gi las mi 'gyur ba'i don la thag
NK115(re)001:18403: gcig thog tu bcad pas rtsal snang ji ltar g.yo
NK115(re)001:18404: yang snang ba gzhi med du go //
NK115(re)001:18405: shes pa yul med du go //
NK115(re)001:18406: rig pa rten med du go //
NK115(re)001:18407: chos zad ming med du go bas /
NK115(re)001:18408: rol pa chos nyid du rtogs pa'i chos rab khyad
NK115(re)001:18409: par can de nyid rang sa ru cog gis bzhag
NK115(re)001:18410: pas rang gis rang grol nas ngo bo nyid med
NK115(re)001:18411: pa'i chos nyid mthong ba la shar grol dusa mnyam
NK115(re)001:18412: du tha snyad btags pa ste /
NK115(re)001:18414: snang srid thams cad chos sku'i zhing du shar //
NK115(re)001:18415: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK115(re)001:18417: de'ang rig cha rlung gis spur bas yid 'gyu byed
NK115(re)001:18418: du langs pa las gyur ba'i spang bya'i dri ma
NK115(re)001:18419: dang gegs dang gol sa mtha' dag chos nyid shes
NK115(re)001:18420: pa'i shes rab rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang du
NK115(re)001:18421: rig pa'i gnas lugs ched 'dzin gza' gtad med par
NK115(re)001:18422: grol ba de la ni sems skad cig rjes mthud
NK115(re)001:18423: kyi rnam pa med pas ye grol la bskyar gzhi
NK115(re)001:18424: med cing rang grol la gnyen po las 'das pa'i
NK115(re)001:18425: don te / de la nyams len gyi gdeng bca'
NK115(re)001:18426: ba ni gdeng grol thog tu bca' ba zhes bya
NK115(re)001:18427: don te / la / de ltar grol tshul gyi
NK115(re)001:18428: gnad ma shes na bsgom bsran che yang phan pa
NK115(re)001:18429: don te / la / med de / ji skad du /
NK115(re)001:18430: bsgom pa shes kyang grol ma shes //
NK115(re)001:18431: bsam gtan lha dang cis mi 'dra //
NK115(re)001:18433: thoda rgal gyi lam la phan tshun rten dang brten
NK115(re)001:18434: pa'i sgo nas sgron ma rnam pa bzhir bzhag kyang
NK115(re)001:18435: / lam gyi ngo bo ni dbyingsa dang rig pa gnyis yina te /
NK115(re)001:18436: dbyings kyi ra bar rig pa'i gdangs 'dzud pa la 'dus pas so //
NK115(re)001:18437: de yang 'di ltar sngon du thos bsam gyi shes
NK115(re)001:18438: rab la brten nas rgyang zhags kyi 'khor 'das kyi
NK115(re)001:18439: cha gnyis 'dzin pa'i gnas legs par khong du chud
NK115(re)001:18440: par byas nas ye shes 'dus pa'i rgyang zhags kyis
NK115(re)001:18441: 'od gsal gyi snang ba 'dzin pa gang zhig gzigs
NK115(re)001:18442: stongs kyis gcun pas bsgom pa'i shes rab chos nyid
NK115(re)001:18443: mngon sum pa'i 'od gsal gyi klong du phebs nas
NK115(re)001:18444: nang dbyings rnam par dag pa la sgrib byed kyi
NK115(re)001:18445: las rlung dag pa'i cha las phyi rol tu dbyings
NK115(re)001:18446: dang thig le'i sgron ma ro gcig pa mngon sum
NK115(re)001:18447: du snang zhing / de la shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma ngo bo dang /
NK115(re)001:18449: gdangs kyi yon tan gsum ldan du 'char ro //
NK115(re)001:18450: de lta bu'i lam de la 'bad dgos pa gdams
NK115(re)001:18451: pa ni lam 'di daga la dbang po dang skal
NK115(re)001:18452: ba rab kyis gzhi lta ba khregs chod dang /
NK115(re)001:18453: lam lhun grub 'od gsal thabs shes zung 'jug tu
NK115(re)001:18454: nyams su blangs pas thun mong gis lam rim gyis
NK115(re)001:18455: bgrod pa la ma ltos par ranga bzhin rdzogas pa
NK115(re)001:18456: chena po yi thuna monga ma yina pa'i lam lngara
NK115(re)001:18457: sku gsum lam snang du rdzogs nas tshe gcig lus
NK115(re)001:18458: gcig la 'bras bu khyad chos drug ldan gyi gzhi
NK115(re)001:18459: thog tu mthar phyin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18460: 'bring dang tha ma yang bar do gang rung du
NK115(re)001:18461: grol bar 'gyur ba'i lam gyi khyad chos mkhyena par
NK115(re)001:18462: 'atshala ba ste shes par byas nasa /
NK115(re)001:18463: de ltar grol ba la chos rdzogs pa chen po
NK115(re)001:18464: la mos pa gcig pos mi chog ste tshe rabs
NK115(re)001:18465: snga mar sku gsung thugs la sbyangs pa'i rtags ldan
NK115(re)001:18466: rnams kyis kyang 'dir ma 'bad na srid pa gzhan
NK115(re)001:18468: dang po'i las can rnams ni lhan cig skyes pa
NK115(re)001:18469: dang kun tu brtags pa'i ma riga pa dang des
NK115(re)001:18470: bskyed pa'i kun rtog sna tshogs pa'i grogas dang 'grogs
NK115(re)001:18471: nas med snang 'khrul pa'i rang gzugs yul gyi bslu
NK115(re)001:18472: brid kyi dbang du song nas /
NK115(re)001:18473: sdug bsngal gting matha'a med pa'i 'khora ba'i 'brog dgona
NK115(re)001:18474: pa 'jigas su rung zhing ya nga ba 'dir srid
NK115(re)001:18476: de kun nas slong byed kyi nyon mongas pa'i 'du
NK115(re)001:18477: byed lcagsa sgrog lta bu dag gis de ring phana
NK115(re)001:18478: chad de da lta yan bcingsa nas ma thar la
NK115(re)001:18479: / da dung yang bdud dang sdig pa'i grogs ni thag nye zhing /
NK115(re)001:18480: 'khrul pa'i bslu brid ni grangs mang la gnyen po zhan /
NK115(re)001:18481: chos ma yin par grags pa rnams la ngo tsha
NK115(re)001:18482: dang khrel la 'jigs nas tshul 'chos kyang man ngag
NK115(re)001:18483: gnad thog tu ma phebs pa rnams la bar chad
NK115(re)001:18484: kyis bslu brid / lus la rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung dang /
NK115(re)001:18486: yid la mngon shes sogs nges pa med pa'i rtags
NK115(re)001:18487: brgyad dang bcu drug tu sku gdung 'bar ba'i rgyud
NK115(re)001:18489: rtogs rlom dang stong zhen gyis rgyu 'bras khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18490: rang nyid ma grol bzhin gzhan don byed pa'i ltar
NK115(re)001:18491: snang sogs kyis mi tshe stong zad du song na
NK115(re)001:18492: mtha' med pa'i bar du yang de ltar srid pa'i
NK115(re)001:18493: gnas su 'khyams par 'gyur bas tshul de la skyo
NK115(re)001:18494: ba'i semsa gting nas bskyed nas zhi ba dam pa
NK115(re)001:18495: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i grong khyer ga la
NK115(re)001:18496: ba der myur du mya ngan las 'ad'a zhing gdod
NK115(re)001:18497: ma'i sa la gtan srid zin nas 'gro ba'i don
NK115(re)001:18498: rtsol med du 'byung ba'i myur lam zab mo mchoga
NK115(re)001:18499: 'di la bsnyen par mdzoda cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18500: de ltar lam nyams su len pa'i tshe na bar chad bdud kyi rtags dang /
NK115(re)001:18501: lam la goms pa'i rtags rnams 'dra ba ltar 'byung
NK115(re)001:18502: bar gsungs pa rnams la'ang brtag par bya dgos kyang
NK115(re)001:18503: / mdor bsdu na rtags snang ji tsam byung ba
NK115(re)001:18504: de tsam gyis mngon zhen dang rlom sems chung zhing
NK115(re)001:18505: byams pa dang snying rje sogs je cher song na
NK115(re)001:18507: yang mngon shes dang lung bstan rdzu 'phrul zhal gzigs
NK115(re)001:18508: sogs ji tsam 'ong yang de la mngon rlom skye
NK115(re)001:18509: zhing byams snying rje sogs la bsgribs par gyur na
NK115(re)001:18510: bar chad yin pas gzab dgos gsungs /
NK115(re)001:18511: lar lam gyi gegs sel dang bogs 'don thams cad
NK115(re)001:18512: kyi snying po dus dang rnam pa thams cad du
NK115(re)001:18513: mos gus dang zhen med gnyis po 'di la gdeng
NK115(re)001:18514: bcol ba 'di ni shin tu gal che bar yang
NK115(re)001:18515: yang gsungs / gsang ba zab mo'i lam de nyams
NK115(re)001:18516: su blangs pas yang rab phung po'i zag pa dengs
NK115(re)001:18517: pa rnams la'ang khregs chod du grol nas lus rdul
NK115(re)001:18518: phran du dengs pa nam mkha' dang mkha' 'gro'i 'chi
NK115(re)001:18519: yang gsungs / lugs dang / lhun grub thod rgal
NK115(re)001:18520: du grol nas 'od phung du yal ba me dpung
NK115(re)001:18522: rtogs pa tshad du phyin yang bstan 'gro'i don mdzad nas las rlung zad par ma byas shing /
NK115(re)001:18523: gzhan don du sku gdung dang ring bsrel 'jog pa'i tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:18524: yang yul gyi mngon zhen dag pas na na mo sman sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:18525: shi na bdun tshigs sogs la mi re bar 'brog
NK115(re)001:18526: dgon pa chen por spro ba ri dwags lta bu
NK115(re)001:18527: dang / 'chi ba la bag mi tsha ba seng ge lta bu dang /
NK115(re)001:18528: sprang po ltar brgya lam sogs su shi yang yid chad pa med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18529: 'chi mi 'chi'i gtad ra med pa bu chung lta bu rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:18530: gzhan yang bar do bzhi'i rnam bzhag dang /
NK115(re)001:18531: der grol ba'i tshul sogs yod kyang yi ge'i khur
NK115(re)001:18532: gyis 'jigs nas bri bar ma nus pas 'grel bar
NK115(re)001:18533: blta'o // yona tan rina po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i chara zhesa bya ba lasa /
NK115(re)001:18534: ranga bzhina rdzogsa pa chena po'i lam thun monga ma
NK115(re)001:18535: yin pa bstan pa'i tshomsa te le'u bcu gnyis pa'i
NK115(re)001:18537: don gsum pa 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i go 'phang bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:18538: 'bras bu gzhan las ma byung bar bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18539: sku lnga'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18540: dang po 'bras bu gzhan las ma byung bar bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18541: de ltar rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi yi
NK115(re)001:18542: gnas lugs legs par gtan la phebs nas ka dag
NK115(re)001:18543: ye bab sor bzhag gi don dang lhun grub thod
NK115(re)001:18544: rgal 'od gsal gyi lam thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK115(re)001:18545: matshana nyid tshul bzhin du legsa par rtogsa nasa /
NK115(re)001:18546: goms pa mathara phyin te sangs rgyas pa'i tshe 'brasa
NK115(re)001:18547: bu'i dbye ba shin tu mang po zhig yod na'ang
NK115(re)001:18548: / bsdu na rten sku dang brten pa ye shesa gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:18550: sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK115(re)001:18551: khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK115(re)001:18554: 'gyur med don gyi sku lngar gnas //
NK115(re)001:18556: de lta bu'i 'bras bu sku dang ye shesa kyi
NK115(re)001:18557: rang bzhin de yang sngar med pa zhig lam bsgoms
NK115(re)001:18558: pa la brten nas gsar du ni gazhana zhig lasa
NK115(re)001:18559: ma byung ste / rang gnas kyi ye shes la
NK115(re)001:18560: sgrib byed kyi dri ma glo bur ba 'khor ba'i
NK115(re)001:18561: bag chags thams cad 'dzin pa'i rten kun gzhi'i rnyog
NK115(re)001:18562: pa dwangsa pa na de la brten pa'i semsa dang
NK115(re)001:18563: semas byung yul dang bcas pa'ang chosa kyi dbyingsa su
NK115(re)001:18564: zhi ba las gzhi la lhun grub tu yod pa'i
NK115(re)001:18565: yon tan thams cad ji bzhin par mngon du 'gyur
NK115(re)001:18566: ma byung ste / ba yin gyi / sems kyi
NK115(re)001:18567: gnas lugs la ni 'gyur ba cung zad kyang med
NK115(re)001:18568: ma byung ste / ba yin gyi / do // de ltar yang /
NK115(re)001:18570: nyes pa glo bur dang ldan dang //
NK115(re)001:18571: yon tan rang bzhin nyid ldan phyir //
NK115(re)001:18572: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK115(re)001:18573: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK115(re)001:18575: de yang 'di ltar dper na nyi ma sprin gyis
NK115(re)001:18576: bsgribs par snang ba yang rtsa ba nyi ma'i rtsal
NK115(re)001:18577: la thug ste / nyi zer gyi rtsal sa gzhi
NK115(re)001:18578: dang rgya mtshor phog pas drod skyes pa'i rlangs pa
NK115(re)001:18579: na bun long long po nam mkhar 'khrigs pas sprin
NK115(re)001:18580: du song ba des nyi ma nyid bsgribs pa ltar
NK115(re)001:18581: thog mar 'khrul ba'i dus gang du gzhi rig pa
NK115(re)001:18582: sku gsum gyi rang bzhin can de lasa rang gi
NK115(re)001:18583: rtsal gzhi snang du g.yosa pa yi tshe na rang
NK115(re)001:18584: snang du ngo ma shes par badga dang gzhan du
NK115(re)001:18585: 'dzina pa'i baga chagas goms pa las rol pa shes
NK115(re)001:18586: bya snod bcud snang srid kyi chos su shar ba'i
NK115(re)001:18587: cha 'dzina pa'i yul can tshogas brgyad kyi rtog pa
NK115(re)001:18588: srid pa nye bar len pa'i rang bzhin can de
NK115(re)001:18589: ni rig pa'i ye shes nyi ma lta bu rang
NK115(re)001:18590: nyid kyi sgrib byed du song bas sprin dang 'dra
NK115(re)001:18591: la thug ste / ba yin la / yang rnal
NK115(re)001:18592: 'byor pas lam bsgoms pas dri ma glo bur ba
NK115(re)001:18593: de rnamas rnama para dag pa'i tshe rang byung gi
NK115(re)001:18594: ye shesa mngon du 'gyur ba'i tshul dper na nyi
NK115(re)001:18595: ma ni sgrib pa med par nam mkha'i dkyil na
NK115(re)001:18596: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba de yang nyi ma
NK115(re)001:18598: nyi zer 'phros pas kun tu gseng byed kyi rlung
NK115(re)001:18599: rang sor gnas pa bskyod de langs pa las sprin
NK115(re)001:18600: rnams nam mkha'i ngang du gar song med par gtong
NK115(re)001:18601: bas nyi ma rang sa na 'od gsal ba ltar
NK115(re)001:18602: / rig pa chos sku'i snying po las rang rtsal
NK115(re)001:18603: 'char sgo ma 'gags pas rang ngo rig par shar
NK115(re)001:18604: ba des snang ba rang sems kyi rol pa gzhi
NK115(re)001:18605: med rtsa ba dang bral ba stong pa'i rang gzugs
NK115(re)001:18606: su shes te spang blang byed don med par mthong
NK115(re)001:18607: nas cog bzhag tu btang bas snang sems de dag
NK115(re)001:18608: rang gis rang grol ba ye shes kyi rgyan du
NK115(re)001:18609: / shar te / ma spangs rang sar dag pas /
NK115(re)001:18610: gang du song ba dang song ba po gzhi med
NK115(re)001:18611: du sangs pas sku gsum gyi dgongs pa rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:18612: ye shes la rang chas su yod pa nyid sgrib
NK115(re)001:18613: pa med para chos kyi dbyings nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:18614: ngang na rang bzhina gyis 'od du gasla ba yin
NK115(re)001:18616: rang bzhin 'od gsal zhes brjod gang yin nyi dang mkha' bzhi glo bur gyi //
NK115(re)001:18617: nyon mongs shes bya'i sprin tshogs stug pos bsgribs pa las ni grol gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:18618: dri med sangs rgyas yon tan kun ldan rtag brtan g.yung drung sangs rgyas nyid //
NK115(re)001:18619: de ni chos la mi rtog rnam 'byed ye shes dag la brten pas 'thob //
NK115(re)001:18621: gnyis pa sku lnga'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:18622: dbyings nang gsal gyi sku gsum bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18623: ye shes phyir gsal gyi sku gnyis bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18624: dang po dbyings nang gsal gyi sku gsum bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:18625: sku gsum so sor bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18626: chos nyid kyi ngos nas dbye bsal med par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18627: dang po sku gsum so sor bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:18629: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK115(re)001:18630: zhi ba chos kyi sku bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18631: dang po mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18632: sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la ngo bo ye dag ces bya zhing /
NK115(re)001:18633: de la glo bura gyi dri ma sgrib pa gnyis
NK115(re)001:18634: po cha dang bcas pa ste bag chags dang bacasa
NK115(re)001:18635: pa spangsa pa na daga pa gnyis dang ldan pa
NK115(re)001:18636: mthar thug gi 'bras bu byang chub mchoga gi dngosa
NK115(re)001:18637: gzhi nyid thob pa yin pas de ni sku rnams
NK115(re)001:18638: kyi dbye gazhi'o // de la ldog pas dbye na
NK115(re)001:18639: gdoda ma nas spros pa dang bral ba'i sangsa rgyas
NK115(re)001:18640: bden pa dbyer med dag mnyam chen po la rang
NK115(re)001:18641: ngo'i cha nas sku dang ye shes su grub pa
NK115(re)001:18642: med pas smon pa med pa'i dbyingsa /
NK115(re)001:18643: dper na nya rgyas zla ba 'od snang gi spros
NK115(re)001:18644: pa phyir gasla cana de nyid stonga gi cha la
NK115(re)001:18645: bla 'og ril gyis log nas 'od snang med pa
NK115(re)001:18646: ma yin kyang dbyingsa su nub pa ste steng du
NK115(re)001:18647: song nas phyir mi mngon pa ltar rnam pa kun
NK115(re)001:18648: tu mi rtog pa'i chosa nyid 'pho 'gyur dang bral
NK115(re)001:18649: ba rang bzhin med bzhin sku dang ye shes thams
NK115(re)001:18650: cad kyi dbyingsa kyi char rtag pa ni ye shes
NK115(re)001:18651: kyi snying po can mi 'gyura rdo rje'i sku ste
NK115(re)001:18652: / de yang rdo rje ni mi phyed pa'i don
NK115(re)001:18653: te sku thams cad chos nyid skye ba med pa'i
NK115(re)001:18654: ngang du dbyer mi phyed pa'i ldog pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18657: spros bral chos nyid 'gyur ba med //
NK115(re)001:18658: mtha' dang dbus med phyogs cha bral //
NK115(re)001:18659: rang snang chos dbyings rnam dag cing //
NK115(re)001:18660: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa //
NK115(re)001:18661: tha ma rkyen gyis bskyed du med //
NK115(re)001:18662: stong pa ye shes snying po can //
NK115(re)001:18663: mtha' la mi gnas rdo rje'i sku //
NK115(re)001:18665: dbu ma thal 'gyur ba dag ni /
NK115(re)001:18666: chos sku rnam dag stong pa de la 'dod cing
NK115(re)001:18667: nang gsal gyi ye shes phra ba mi bzhed pas
NK115(re)001:18668: / gzhan snang la 'byung ba'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK115(re)001:18669: rje dang phrin las kyang nor bu dang dpag bsam
NK115(re)001:18670: gyi shing ltar rnam par mi rtog bzhin du gdul
NK115(re)001:18671: bya'i smon lam gyi dbang las snang bar 'dod la
NK115(re)001:18672: / / 'dir ni rnam pa rtog bcas ma yin
NK115(re)001:18673: yang dbyings kyi ngang na ye shes kyi 'char gzhi
NK115(re)001:18674: lhun grub tu yod pas smon lam gyi rgyu la
NK115(re)001:18675: ma ltos par gzhan snang la thugs rje'i 'jug pa
NK115(re)001:18676: rgyun mi 'chad cing gzugs sku phrin las dang bcas
NK115(re)001:18677: pa rang bzhin du 'byung bar 'dod pa 'di rtogs
NK115(re)001:18678: par dka' ba'i gnad gcig yin par gsungs pas sngar
NK115(re)001:18679: smos pa bzhin 'dir yang brjod do //
NK115(re)001:18680: gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni /
NK115(re)001:18681: 'di ltar med snang glo bur ba 'khrul ba'i rten
NK115(re)001:18682: cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i phung sogs kyi chos kyis
NK115(re)001:18683: chos can byas nas de ma grub pa'i stong nyid
NK115(re)001:18684: tsam don dam pa'i bden pa mthar thug gi thob
NK115(re)001:18685: bya'i 'bras bur lta ba lta bu ma yin par
NK115(re)001:18686: / rnama pa kun gyi mchoga rang byung 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:18687: ba'i ye shes dang dbyer med par ldana pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:18688: nyid spros pa mtha' dag zhi ba'i dbyingas su sgrib
NK115(re)001:18689: byed glo bur ba'i dri ma rang sar dag pas
NK115(re)001:18690: stobsa la sogsa pa'i yona tan gyi chos tshul rgya
NK115(re)001:18691: mtsho lta bu kun sangs rgyas pa'i skad cig ma
NK115(re)001:18692: der mngon par rdzogs par byang chub ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:18693: dang yon tan thams cad chos nyid kyi ngo bor
NK115(re)001:18695: spangs pa dang rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi snanga cha
NK115(re)001:18696: rang rang gi ngo bo so sor ma 'dresa par
NK115(re)001:18701: phyogs chos so bdun la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen
NK115(re)001:18702: pa'i chos tshul dpag tu med pa mnga' ba'i spangsa
NK115(re)001:18703: rtogsa kyi cha nas gazhala ba la ni mngona para
NK115(re)001:18704: byang chub pa'i sku zhes brjod pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:18706: dri ma bral phyir byang ba ste //
NK115(re)001:18707: yon tan rgyas pas chub pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:18709: mngon par byang chub skur brjod do //
NK115(re)001:18711: 'on kyang stobs la sogs pa'i yon tan yod tshul
NK115(re)001:18712: yul la 'jug pa'i ye shes ji lta dang ji
NK115(re)001:18713: snyed mkhyen pa'i sprul sku'i ye shes kyis gzigs tshul
NK115(re)001:18714: lta bu la go rgyu min pa 'dra ste /
NK115(re)001:18715: 'di dbyings nang gsal gyi sku yin pa'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:18716: de yang spyir sku gsum du bshad pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:18717: na nang gsal gyi sku gsum ga chos skur bsdu
NK115(re)001:18718: rgyu yin la / sku gsum la ye shes ldan tshul gyi dbang du byas na /
NK115(re)001:18719: chos sku la ye shes gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:18720: ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes /
NK115(re)001:18721: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi ye shes /
NK115(re)001:18722: thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes gsum mtshan nyid
NK115(re)001:18723: ris chad du med pas rig pa'i gsal cha las
NK115(re)001:18724: ngang ngam shugs kyis mkhyen pa'i 'char gzhi byed pa
NK115(re)001:18725: dang / longs sku la ye shes lnga ldan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:18726: chos dbyings me long sogs rnam pa lnga yul dang
NK115(re)001:18727: yul can du ma yin par thad ka'i snang ba
NK115(re)001:18729: sprul sku'i dus na ye shes gnyis gnas te /
NK115(re)001:18730: ji lta ba dang ji snyed mkhyen pa ste /
NK115(re)001:18731: de yang bya byed dang bcas pa ma yin par 'bad med du mkhyen par gsungs pas na /
NK115(re)001:18732: mngon byang gi skabs su ston la sogs pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:18733: tan nam ye shes ni rang bzhin lhun grub kyi
NK115(re)001:18734: ye shes la byas na bade'am snyam ste /
NK115(re)001:18735: lar sangs rgyas kyi yon tan la rtog ge'i blos
NK115(re)001:18736: kha tshon bcad nas 'di lta bu'o zhes brjod du
NK115(re)001:18737: mi 'os kyang bla ma'i gsung rgyun 'ol spyi tsam
NK115(re)001:18739: kun mkhyen chos rje'i gsung rnams la dpag nas bshad pa yin la /
NK115(re)001:18740: yang sku gsum gyis mkhyen tshul /
NK115(re)001:18741: sprul pa'i sku'i phyir snang gi shes bya'i rnam pa snang stong gnyis mkhyen pa la ltos nas /
NK115(re)001:18742: chos can don gyi rnam pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18743: chos nyid zhi ba'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:18744: longs sku'i thad ka'i rang snang 'od gsal ye shes
NK115(re)001:18745: kyis shes bya'i rnam pa rang gsal du mkhyen pa
NK115(re)001:18746: la ltos nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang
NK115(re)001:18747: / chos sku nang gsal gyi ngo bo gzhi gnas
NK115(re)001:18748: kyi ye shes 'char gzhi'i cha tsam rang mal ka
NK115(re)001:18749: dag gi dbyings na rang mkhyen du gsal bas dbyings
NK115(re)001:18750: rnam par dag pa'i char gnas pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:18752: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK115(re)001:18753: ye shes rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK115(re)001:18754: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang //
NK115(re)001:18755: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang //
NK115(re)001:18756: gzhi la gnas pa'i ye shes so //
NK115(re)001:18757: zhes gsungs pa ltar na'ang gzhi la gnas pa'i ye shes 'char gzhi tsam de yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:18758: snang cha ma 'dres zhes pas kyang mi 'thad pa
NK115(re)001:18759: med de snang cha ma 'dres par 'char ba'i gzhi'i
NK115(re)001:18760: ldog pa la go chod pa'i phyir ro snyam yang
NK115(re)001:18761: gsung rab dang dgongs 'grel tshad ldan rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:18762: chos spyan mnga' ba'i gang zag tshad ma rnams la gtugs par gyis shig /
NK115(re)001:18763: gsum pa zhi ba chos kyi sku bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18765: ches phra'i ye shes nang du gsal //
NK115(re)001:18766: dmigs med 'char gzhi chos kyi sku //
NK115(re)001:18768: phyi shes bya gzung ba'i yul la blo yi ste
NK115(re)001:18769: sems dang snyam byed sems byung gi 'jug pa zhi
NK115(re)001:18770: bas / nang shes byed kyi blo la yul de
NK115(re)001:18771: 'dzina para byed pa'i kun rdzoba 'khrul pa'i cha thams
NK115(re)001:18772: cad skye 'gag med pa'i ngang du zhi zhing spangsa
NK115(re)001:18773: pas khams gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i rten cing
NK115(re)001:18774: 'brel bar 'byung ba mtha' dag 'gags shing 'gag gzhi'i
NK115(re)001:18775: de kho na nyid so so ranga gi rig pa
NK115(re)001:18776: rtag chad gang gi'ang mathara ma lhung ba ye shes
NK115(re)001:18777: phyir gsal gyi cha thams cad dbyings su thim pa
NK115(re)001:18778: ste zhi ba'i ldog pa la gnas kyang ma rmugsa
NK115(re)001:18779: pa zhes mkhyen cha gtan med du song ba ma
NK115(re)001:18780: yin par shin tu phra ba'i nang gsal gyi ye
NK115(re)001:18781: shesa ni mkhyen cha 'agga pa med pa sku dang
NK115(re)001:18782: ye shesa phyir gsal gyi cha thams cad 'char ba'i
NK115(re)001:18784: de yang sangs rgyas kyi sar bem po'i chos ni
NK115(re)001:18785: 'ga' yang med pas sku zhes phyir gsal gzugs sku'i
NK115(re)001:18786: rnam par shar ba'i tshul thams cad kyang ye shes
NK115(re)001:18787: nyag gcig gi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir chos sku
NK115(re)001:18788: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes de las longs sprul gyi
NK115(re)001:18789: ye shes gnyis 'char bas 'char byed ma 'gags par
NK115(re)001:18792: de yang sems nyid smin pa'i tshe //
NK115(re)001:18793: chos kyi sku la gzhi gnas te //
NK115(re)001:18794: ka nas dag pas dri ma zad //
NK115(re)001:18795: ngo bo ye nas 'khrul pa med //
NK115(re)001:18798: sku gsum gyi ye shes kyi byed las ni /
NK115(re)001:18800: gzhi la gnas pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK115(re)001:18801: rang bzhin shugs kyi 'char gzhi byed //
NK115(re)001:18802: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK115(re)001:18803: rkyen gyis dag pa smin par byed //
NK115(re)001:18804: shes dang shes bya'i ye shes kyis //
NK115(re)001:18805: mos gus can la dngos grub ster //
NK115(re)001:18807: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes gsum po des 'char gzhi byed pa'i tshul yang /
NK115(re)001:18808: ngo bos sku gsum gyi 'char gzhi byed la sku gsum tha dad snang char ma grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18809: rang bzhin gyi 'od lnga'i 'char gzhi byed la kha dog rang mtshan du ma grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18810: thugs rjes ye shes gnyis kyi 'char gzhi byed la
NK115(re)001:18811: yul dang rnam pa la dngos su 'jal bar med
NK115(re)001:18812: pa'o // de lta bu'i nang gsal gyi sku'am ye
NK115(re)001:18813: shes de'i rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin ni sgrib
NK115(re)001:18814: pa bag chags dang bcas pa shin tu rnam par
NK115(re)001:18815: dag cing chos kyi dbyings la rtag tu mnyam par
NK115(re)001:18816: bazhaga pa las mi g.yo ba sangs rgyas rnamas kyis
NK115(re)001:18817: mngon sum du mthong gi gzhan gyis ni ma yin
NK115(re)001:18818: pa'o // no // de ltar rten nam 'char gzhi'i
NK115(re)001:18819: ldog pa gang yin pa de la zhi ba chosa
NK115(re)001:18820: kyi sku zhesa brjod pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:18821: de ltar nang gsal gyi sku gsum po de yang
NK115(re)001:18822: chos kyi sku gcig la ldog pas dbye ba tsam
NK115(re)001:18823: ste / ngo bo chos nyid stong pa ye shes
NK115(re)001:18824: kyi snying po can 'gyur ba med pa'i cha nas
NK115(re)001:18826: rang bzhin la yon tan lhun grub tu yod pa'i cha nas mngon byang dang /
NK115(re)001:18827: thugs rje phyir gsal gyi 'char gzhi byed pa'i cha nas zhi ba chos kyi skur bzhag cing /
NK115(re)001:18828: gzhan du chos sku'i dbye ba /
NK115(re)001:18829: dngos po mtshan nyid dang 'brel ba'i chos sku /
NK115(re)001:18830: gnas pa khyab tshul dang 'brel ba'i chos sku /
NK115(re)001:18831: rnam dbye snang tshul dang 'brel ba'i chos sku zhes chos nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:18832: kun khyab kyi ye shes dang yon tan gyi char
NK115(re)001:18833: ltos nas gsum du gsungs pa'ang 'di dag dang don
NK115(re)001:18835: des na dbyings nang gsal gyi sku gsum po de gcig tu byas nas chos sku dang /
NK115(re)001:18836: longs sprul gnyis te sku gsum po de rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs la lam snang yang yin la /
NK115(re)001:18837: 'bras bu yin pa yang mi 'gal ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:18839: sku gsum lam snang du bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK115(re)001:18840: bla ma snga rabs pa dag na re /
NK115(re)001:18841: 'bras bu ma yin zer ba ni /
NK115(re)001:18842: 'bras bu sku gsum du zhen pa'i mthar 'dzin dang bral bar byed pa la dgongs pa'am /
NK115(re)001:18843: sgo gsum las sbubs gsum mthar thug tu 'dod pa
NK115(re)001:18844: de dgag pa la dgongs pa'o zhes 'gal spong mdzad
NK115(re)001:18845: nas / don la 'bras bur 'jog pa'ang ka dag
NK115(re)001:18846: gi nang dbyings kyi ngo bo ma dgongs pa'i rnam
NK115(re)001:18847: 'gyur yin pas shin tu nor te ma legs so
NK115(re)001:18848: nas / // 'dir sngar khas blangs pa bzhin lam snang yang yin la /
NK115(re)001:18849: 'bras bu yang yin pa mi 'gal bar 'dod de /
NK115(re)001:18850: dang po lam snang yin te /
NK115(re)001:18851: lhun grub kyi sbubs ka dag chen po don gyi 'bras bu khang pa lta bu las /
NK115(re)001:18854: gzhi ka dag las phyir snang du 'char dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:18855: 'char tshul ngo bo skur gnas pa las 'char ro //
NK115(re)001:18856: lam snang la gnyis yod de /
NK115(re)001:18857: rang nyid sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i lam 'bras bu'i sngon rol ba rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:18858: rang nyid sangs rgyas grub zin nas gdul bya 'dren
NK115(re)001:18859: pa'i lam sku gsum mngon par snang bas don mdzad
NK115(re)001:18860: pa'o // de las 'dir mi slob pa'i lam snang
NK115(re)001:18861: du 'dod pas sku gsum lam snang yin pa dang
NK115(re)001:18862: pa'o // / 'bras bu yin pa gnyis mi 'gal la 'brel ba grub pa'i don to //
NK115(re)001:18863: rnam par grol ba'i chos sku nang dbyings las sku
NK115(re)001:18864: gsum phyir snang lam du shar bas sku dang ye
NK115(re)001:18865: shes kyi rnam 'phrul snang ba yang /
NK115(re)001:18866: chos sku ye shes kyi thugs /
NK115(re)001:18868: sprul sku mdzad par snang bas don 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:18869: de'ang nang gsal 'char gzhi'i sku dang ye shes 'du
NK115(re)001:18870: 'bral med pa rdo rje sems dpa'i chos nyid dang
NK115(re)001:18871: / de las phyir gsal du sku gsum gyi lam
NK115(re)001:18872: snang rang snang du shar ba gnyis rig pa'i ngang
NK115(re)001:18873: / du 'dra yang / phyi nang gi khyad par
NK115(re)001:18874: phye la rang snang gi cha las gdul bya'i snang
NK115(re)001:18875: ngor longs sprul 'char bas don mdzad pa'ang rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:18876: rol par gcig kyang rang snang gdul byas mi mthong
NK115(re)001:18877: / du 'dra yang / la / de las shar
NK115(re)001:18878: ba de mthong ba'i khyad yod pas 'dra gnyis shan
NK115(re)001:18881: rdo rje sems dpa'i chos nyid dang //
NK115(re)001:18882: rang snang dkyil 'khor dag pa gnyis //
NK115(re)001:18883: 'dra gzhi gcig la gol sa che //
NK115(re)001:18885: de ltar nang dbyings dang phyi gsal lam snang gi
NK115(re)001:18886: cha ma phyed par sku gsum rang snang gi 'bras
NK115(re)001:18887: bur 'dod na / sprul sku gdul bya la snang ba bzhin //
NK115(re)001:18888: grol sa'i ka dag gi chos sku gdul bya la snang bar thal /
NK115(re)001:18889: sku gsum ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:18890: chos sku 'phro 'du dang kha dog tu snang bar thal /
NK115(re)001:18891: khyod dang ngo bo gcig pa'i longs sprul la chos de snang ba'i phyir /
NK115(re)001:18892: yang na sprul sku gdul bya la mi snang bar thal /
NK115(re)001:18893: chos sku mi snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:18894: des na sku gsum yang rig par ngo bo gcig gi /
NK115(re)001:18895: rnam pa ngo bo gcig pa de 'dra khas mi blang zhing /
NK115(re)001:18896: sprul sku thugs rje'i cha yin la /
NK115(re)001:18897: des sprul pa'i snang ba de gzugs brnyan sprul pa yin gyi /
NK115(re)001:18898: sprul sku dngos ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:18899: thugs rje ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:18900: grub matha'i dbye ba 'di yang shin tu phra bas
NK115(re)001:18901: shes rab can rnams kyis dpyod la khong du chud
NK115(re)001:18902: par gyis shig / gnad 'di gal po che yin no //
NK115(re)001:18904: gnyis pa chos nyid kyi ngos nas dbye ba med pa'i tshul bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:18905: blo'i yul las 'das par bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18906: chos kyi dbyings su bzhugs tshul bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:18907: dang po blo'i yul las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18908: de ltar nang gsal gyi sku gsum po yon tan
NK115(re)001:18909: gyi ldog pa nas so sor btags kyang rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:18910: ngo bo nyid med par gnas pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:18911: dbyings nang gsal du yod pa'i cha nas ji lta
NK115(re)001:18912: ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes so so ranga gi rig
NK115(re)001:18913: byara gnas pas rgyal ba'i khamsa zhes btags pa ste
NK115(re)001:18914: / don la gciga dang du mara grub pa ma yina pas dngosa po can min pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18915: ji snyed pa'i mkhyen cha nang du gsal bas dngosa med las kyang 'adsa la /
NK115(re)001:18916: rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa nam mkha'a ltar
NK115(re)001:18917: gnas shing phyir gsal gyi sku dang ye shes ma
NK115(re)001:18918: 'dres pa'i 'char gzhir yod pas rgyal sras sar gnas
NK115(re)001:18919: dang sems can gyi tshogs la gzugs sku snang ba
NK115(re)001:18921: 'phags pa'i tshul khrims kyi ngad ldang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18922: chos kyi ro myong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:18923: bsam gtan gyi dga' bdes reg pa dang /
NK115(re)001:18924: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis tshig don 'jal
NK115(re)001:18925: ba'i rgyu byed kyang rang ngo la gnyis su rnama
NK115(re)001:18926: par mi rtog la dag ma dag gi mtshan mas
NK115(re)001:18927: gos pa med cinga rnama 'gyur gyi sprosa pa phyir
NK115(re)001:18928: gsal gyi cha dbyings su zhi ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:18930: de bzhin gshegs pa mkha' bzhin dam pa yi //
NK115(re)001:18931: dbang po drug don nyams su myong ba'i rgyu //
NK115(re)001:18932: 'byung med gzugs don blta dang gtam bzang ni //
NK115(re)001:18933: gtsang ma mnyan dang bde gshegs tshul khrims kyi //
NK115(re)001:18934: dri gtsang snom dang 'phags chen dam chos ro //
NK115(re)001:18935: myong dang ting 'dzin reg bde nyams myong dang //
NK115(re)001:18936: rang gi ngo bo nyid kyis zab pa'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:18937: rtogs pa'i rgyu gyur zhib mor bsam pa na //
NK115(re)001:18938: don dam bde mdzad de bzhin gshegs pa ni //
NK115(re)001:18939: nam mkha' bzhin du rgyu mtshan rnams dang bral //
NK115(re)001:18941: des na de'i rang bzhin ni ngaga gisa brjod pa'i yul las 'adsa pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:18942: chos nyid don dam pa'i bdena pas bsdus pa'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:18943: rtog dpyod dang tha snyad kyi dpe dang gatana tshig kyi sgras ji bzhin par mi mtshona te /
NK115(re)001:18944: shes byed kyi blo ste sems dang /
NK115(re)001:18945: snyam byed sems byung dang dpe la sogs pa dang 'agla ba'i phyir na /
NK115(re)001:18946: sa bcu'i dabnga phyug rgyun mtha' ba dag gi yanga
NK115(re)001:18947: spyod yul min na gzhan gyis lta ci smos te
NK115(re)001:18949: ngag yul min phyir don dam gyis bsdus phyir //
NK115(re)001:18950: rtogs gnas min phyir dpe las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:18951: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK115(re)001:18952: rgyal yul 'phags rnams kyis kyang bsam mi khyab //
NK115(re)001:18954: des na nang gsal gyi cha la chos dang longs sprul gyi sku gsum dang /
NK115(re)001:18956: chos dbyings dang me long lta bu la sogs par brjod pa rnams ni ngo bo'am dngos yin la /
NK115(re)001:18957: phyir gsal gyi cha'i sku dang ye shes ni rtsal
NK115(re)001:18958: las shar ba'i rol pa yin par shes par bya
NK115(re)001:18960: chos sku'i ngo bo rang byung ye shes te //
NK115(re)001:18961: rol pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mtsho //
NK115(re)001:18962: gdod ma'i dbyings la thig le gcig tu bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:18963: longs sku'i ngo bo rang bzhin lhun grub ste //
NK115(re)001:18964: rol pa rigs lnga ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK115(re)001:18965: nam mkha'i dbyings kun gang bar snang ba yin //
NK115(re)001:18966: sprul sku'i ngo bo thugs rje'i 'char gzhi ste //
NK115(re)001:18967: rol pa gang la gang 'dul der snang zhing //
NK115(re)001:18968: phrin las chen pos mnga' dbang 'byor ba yin //
NK115(re)001:18970: gnyis pa chos kyi dbyings su bzhugs tshul bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:18971: 'drena pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnamas kho na
NK115(re)001:18972: la mngona suma du gyur ba'i gansa ni chos kyi
NK115(re)001:18973: dbyings te / de ni bsam gyis mi khyab pas zaba pa /
NK115(re)001:18974: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas zhi ba /
NK115(re)001:18976: sangs rgyas kyi chos khams rgya mtsho lta bu 'char
NK115(re)001:18977: ba'i gdangs ma 'gags pas bum pa'i khanga mdzesa nanga
NK115(re)001:18978: zhes pa'i tha snyad nye bar btags te /
NK115(re)001:18981: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK115(re)001:18983: rang bzhin gyi gnas chos kyi dbyings de na phyogs
NK115(re)001:18984: bcu dus gsum gyi sangsa rgyas rnams ni dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:18985: la snga phyi dang mtho dman med par rtag tu
NK115(re)001:18986: bzhugs kyang rang snang dbyings su thim pa'i gnas skabs
NK115(re)001:18987: de na rnam pa'i chos med pas rten brten par
NK115(re)001:18988: tha snyad btags pa tsam gyis mtshon pa las gnas
NK115(re)001:18990: de ltar rnam pa med pa dang rgyud tha dad pas phye ba med pa de yi phyir /
NK115(re)001:18991: rnama pa'i cha nasa gzhal te sangs rgyas gciga gisa gciga mi gzigas te /
NK115(re)001:18993: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na dus gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:18994: sangs rgyas thams cad gcig gis gcig mi gzigs pa'i
NK115(re)001:18997: de yang go bde bar bshad na /
NK115(re)001:18998: chos rnams kyi rang bzhina ni gcig dang du ma'i
NK115(re)001:18999: spros pa dang bral ba'i bdag nyid can du gnas
NK115(re)001:19000: la / dbyingsa de'i rang bzhin du rtogs pa mthar phyin pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams te /
NK115(re)001:19002: gang phyir de bzhin nyid du gshegs //
NK115(re)001:19003: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod do //
NK115(re)001:19005: de'i phyir chos nyid kyi ngos na sangs rgyas thams
NK115(re)001:19006: cad dgongas klong ro gcig tu gyur nas gzigs bya
NK115(re)001:19007: gzigs byed med pas mi gzigs par bshad do //
NK115(re)001:19008: gnyis pa ye shes phyir gsal gyi sku gnyis bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:19011: dang po longs sku bshad pa la yang gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:19012: gzhi 'bras dbyer med kyi longs sku bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19013: 'bras bu lhun grub kyi longs sku bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19014: de gnyis ka'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK115(re)001:19015: dang po gzhi 'bras dbyer med kyi longs sku bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:19018: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19019: de la spyir longs sku'i dbye ba la rnam pa bzhir gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:19021: gnas pa khyab tshul gyi sku /
NK115(re)001:19023: gdul byar snang tshul gyi sku'o //
NK115(re)001:19025: chos sku'i 'char gzhi las rang shar te 'od gsal lnga ldan gyi skur rdzogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19026: gzhi snang 'byung ba chen po'i rang bzhin gsal ba
NK115(re)001:19027: dro ba bsil ba yang ba khyab pa'i bdag nyid
NK115(re)001:19029: sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad la 'od dang
NK115(re)001:19030: 'od khyim gyis khyab pa'i cha mngon du gyur pa
NK115(re)001:19032: sku la 'od kyi snying por gnas //
NK115(re)001:19033: rtog med rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK115(re)001:19034: 'gran zla med pa'i nyag gcig po //
NK115(re)001:19035: dkyil dang 'khor dang pho brang dang //
NK115(re)001:19036: rigs dang stong dang gsal ba'o //
NK115(re)001:19039: gzhi snang chos nyid kyi longs sku sems can la bar dor lam du snang ba de /
NK115(re)001:19040: skabs 'dir gdul bya 'dren pa'i lam du chos sku'i nang dbyings las rang shar te /
NK115(re)001:19041: 'od dang kha dog gi klong na dkyil dang 'khor
NK115(re)001:19042: dang so so'i tshom bu dang sku dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:19043: dang yab dang yum dang sku mdog dang phyag mtshan
NK115(re)001:19044: la sogs par gsal ba ste /
NK115(re)001:19045: gsang ba sa bon gyi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:19046: ngo bo nyid kyi snang ba la //
NK115(re)001:19047: ngo bo nyid kyi sku shar ba //
NK115(re)001:19048: dper na rang dang gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK115(re)001:19049: sku gsum 'od gsal stong pa nyid //
NK115(re)001:19050: rtag pa ma yin dngos po med //
NK115(re)001:19051: chad pa ma yin 'od gsal sku //
NK115(re)001:19052: tha dad ma yin phyi nang med //
NK115(re)001:19055: longs skus 'dul ba'i gdul bya so so la rigs dang dkyil 'khor so sor snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:19056: des na 'di ltar nang dbyings spros bral chos nyid
NK115(re)001:19057: kyi ngang las mi g.yo yang rang bzhin 'od gsal
NK115(re)001:19058: gyi mkhyena cha 'agga pa med pa'i rang gdangsa las
NK115(re)001:19059: thugsa rje phyira gasla gyi cha rang gi ngo bo
NK115(re)001:19061: rang gi ngo bo nyid longsa spyod rdzogas pa'i skura snang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:19062: gansa 'od gsal stug po bkod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19063: dus gzhir rdzogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19064: ston pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK115(re)001:19065: chosa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK115(re)001:19066: 'khora nyid las mi gzhan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19067: ngesa pa lnga dang ldan par rang shar zhing /
NK115(re)001:19068: de yang gtso bo dang 'khor la sogs pa'i sku'i
NK115(re)001:19069: rnam pa so sor ma 'dres par gsal ba dang
NK115(re)001:19070: / zhing khamsa dang gzhal yas khang gi bkod pa phun sum tshogs shing /
NK115(re)001:19071: ston 'khor thams cad kyang thun mong dang thun mong
NK115(re)001:19072: ma yin pa'i matshana dang dpe byad sogs yona tan
NK115(re)001:19073: rgya mtsho'i badga nyid can du bzhugs pa de'i thugs
NK115(re)001:19074: kyis chos sku'i cha bzung la /
NK115(re)001:19075: phrin las kyis sprul sku'i cha bzung bas sku gsum
NK115(re)001:19076: tha mi dad pa'i rang bzhin can yin par yang
NK115(re)001:19078: rig pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK115(re)001:19079: rig pa sna tshogs su 'char ba ni sprul pa'i sku /
NK115(re)001:19080: ji ltar snang yang don skye med las ma 'das pa chos kyi sku'o //
NK115(re)001:19082: de ltar yin pas sangs rgyas kyi rang snang tsam
NK115(re)001:19083: las phyogs ga shed na yod pa'i rten dang brten
NK115(re)001:19084: pa rang mtshan par mi bzung ste /
NK115(re)001:19086: lhun rdzogs rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK115(re)001:19087: zhing dang gzhal yas gdan khri rgyan //
NK115(re)001:19088: 'od zer du mar snang ba ste //
NK115(re)001:19090: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK115(re)001:19096: dang po gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni 'og min te /
NK115(re)001:19098: sku gsum gyi gnas kyis dbye bas gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:19099: dang po chos sku'i 'og min ni /
NK115(re)001:19100: mtha' dbus phyogs cha gang du'ang bzhag tu med cing
NK115(re)001:19101: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ngo bo sangs
NK115(re)001:19102: rgyas kyi mthar thug gi bgrod bya dam pa ste
NK115(re)001:19103: / yang dag don gyi 'og min zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:19106: ston pa chos sku'i gnas ni 'di lta ste //
NK115(re)001:19107: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ste //
NK115(re)001:19108: yang dag don gyi 'og min de ru bshad //
NK115(re)001:19110: gnyis pa longs sku'i 'og min ni /
NK115(re)001:19111: chos sku'i dbyings las ye shes chen po'i snang bar
NK115(re)001:19112: rang byung ba 'od kyi gzhal yas khang dang gtso
NK115(re)001:19113: 'khor du snang ba ye shes lnga'i rigs su lhun
NK115(re)001:19114: gyis grub cing dus thams cad du 'pho 'gyur med
NK115(re)001:19115: pa ste / sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK115(re)001:19116: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spangs pa yi //
NK115(re)001:19117: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK115(re)001:19118: rigs bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK115(re)001:19119: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa //
NK115(re)001:19121: gtsang ma'i gnas spangs zhes pa gtsang gnas gyi ya rol na yod pa'i don min te /
NK115(re)001:19122: de'i snang ba las 'das te sangs rgyas rnams gang
NK115(re)001:19123: na bzhugs pa'i rang snang yin pas phyogs kyi ris
NK115(re)001:19124: su chad pa med par chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam
NK115(re)001:19125: pa'o // de'ang 'di ltar sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las /
NK115(re)001:19127: nyis 'gyur du ni spags pa yi //
NK115(re)001:19128: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK115(re)001:19129: yon tan lnga yi bdag nyid de //
NK115(re)001:19130: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang //
NK115(re)001:19131: gru bzhi spyi bo 'khyil bar gnas //
NK115(re)001:19132: zhes pas 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min dang /
NK115(re)001:19133: sar gnas kyi snang ba rang bzhin sprul sku'i 'og min gnyis las 'phags pa'i don to //
NK115(re)001:19134: gsum pa sprul sku'i 'og min la gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:19135: sar gnas rnams la snang ba ni rang bzhin sprul sku'i 'og min te /
NK115(re)001:19137: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK115(re)001:19138: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK115(re)001:19139: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK115(re)001:19140: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK115(re)001:19141: sku yi chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK115(re)001:19143: de'ang rigs lnga'i zhing lngar snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:19145: 'dres ma'i don du snang ba'i gtsang ris kyi 'og min te /
NK115(re)001:19146: de yang 'jig rten du sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i tshe
NK115(re)001:19147: sprul pa'i dang po longs sku dang chos mthun pa
NK115(re)001:19148: mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i sangs rgyas su bstan nas /
NK115(re)001:19149: lha dang grub pa dang rig sngags 'chang gi dbang po tshad med pa la /
NK115(re)001:19150: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud sogs dang /
NK115(re)001:19151: pha rol tu phyin pa la sogs pa'i theg pa du mas 'dul bar kun tu ston to //
NK115(re)001:19152: de skad du'ang legs par grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:19153: gtsang ma'i 'og min rnam mdzes par //
NK115(re)001:19154: grub pa dbang po la sogs la //
NK115(re)001:19155: rig sngags gzungs sngags rnal 'byor dang //
NK115(re)001:19156: rgyu chos du mas tshim par mdzad //
NK115(re)001:19158: gzhan yang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i gsung las 'di ltar byung ste /
NK115(re)001:19159: don gyi 'og min chos kyi dbyings te /
NK115(re)001:19160: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bzhugs gnas yin zhing de'i gong na zab pa gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:19161: rtags kyi 'og min dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med
NK115(re)001:19162: pa'i rtags gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs dang kha dog
NK115(re)001:19164: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i bzhugs gnas yin zhing chos
NK115(re)001:19165: kyi dbyings mtshon byed kyi rtags de'i gong na gzhan
NK115(re)001:19167: rig pa'i 'og min dngos po'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i rig pa'i ye shes te /
NK115(re)001:19168: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi chos sku'i bzhugs gnas yin
NK115(re)001:19169: zhing de'i gong na rig pa gzhan med pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:19170: ro // gsang ba'i 'og min yum gyi mkha' ste
NK115(re)001:19171: gsang ba sku'i bzhugs gnas yin zhing lam gnas dang
NK115(re)001:19172: yon tan gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:19173: rtog pa'i 'og min las dang po pas 'og min
NK115(re)001:19174: gyi gzhal yas khang bsgom pa ste lhag pa ting
NK115(re)001:19175: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi bzhugs gnas yin zhing
NK115(re)001:19176: / don spyi 'dzin byed kyi rtog pa de'i gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:19177: 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min gtsang ma'i ris lha lnga'i ya ta ste /
NK115(re)001:19178: 'phags pa rnams kyi bzhugs gnas yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:19179: gzugs khams kyi gnas de'i gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:19180: zhes rnam grangs drug tu bstan pa las /
NK115(re)001:19181: don dang rig pa'i 'og min chos skur 'du zhing /
NK115(re)001:19182: rtags kyi 'og min longs skur 'du la /
NK115(re)001:19183: gzhan gsum sprul skur 'du ste gnas kyi 'og min
NK115(re)001:19184: dngos dang gsang ba dang rtog pa'i 'og min sprul
NK115(re)001:19185: sku'i lam nyams su len pas de'i khongs su 'adu'o
NK115(re)001:19186: // de ltar sku gsum gyi 'og min bshad pa las 'dir ni longs sku'i 'og min te /
NK115(re)001:19187: de yang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i bzhugs gansa ni
NK115(re)001:19188: rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang rtsal lhuna rdzogas su
NK115(re)001:19189: snang zhing snang ba'i gnas gang gi'ang 'og tu ma
NK115(re)001:19190: gyur pa'i 'oga mina gyi zhing ye shes rang snang
NK115(re)001:19191: gi bkod pa phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:19192: / stuga po bkoda pa ste de na ye shesa
NK115(re)001:19193: lnga yi rang rtsal 'gag med du shar ba'i 'od
NK115(re)001:19194: dang 'od zer kha dog sna tshogs pa gasla zhing
NK115(re)001:19195: 'tshera la bkrag mdangs 'abra bas mkha'a dbyingsa thams cad
NK115(re)001:19196: dbang po'i mtshona cha ste 'ja' tshon gyis bakaba pa
NK115(re)001:19197: bzhina du khyab cing gzhi ye shes rin po che
NK115(re)001:19198: las grub pa'i rang bzhin manna na nema zhing btegsa
NK115(re)001:19199: na 'aphara ba la sogs pa de lta bu'i bkod
NK115(re)001:19200: pa phun sum tshogs pas mdzes par byas pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:19201: khams rnam par dag pa na gzhal yas khang gi
NK115(re)001:19203: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK115(re)001:19204: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK115(re)001:19205: rgyan dang sgo khyud rta babs dang //
NK115(re)001:19206: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK115(re)001:19207: zhes don bcu gcig bstan pa ltar go rim bsnol
NK115(re)001:19208: dgos kyang rnam pa 'dzin bde ba'i phyir 'dir yang
NK115(re)001:19210: gzhi ni ye shes lnga mtshon byed kyi rtags 'khor
NK115(re)001:19211: lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i lte ba
NK115(re)001:19212: zlum po'i steng na gazhala meda khanga rdzogs par snang
NK115(re)001:19213: ba ste / rol pa chen po las /
NK115(re)001:19214: 'khor lo chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NK115(re)001:19215: khang pa gru bzhi'i rnam par brjid //
NK115(re)001:19217: dbyibs ni rang byung gi ye shes la che ba'i
NK115(re)001:19218: yon tan rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhi'i rnam par mdzesa
NK115(re)001:19219: pa'o // sgo khyud ni rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK115(re)001:19222: 'dus ma byas shing 'od gsal ba ste bzhi po
NK115(re)001:19223: nas kun tu bzang po lhun gyis grub pa'i gzhal
NK115(re)001:19225: 'od gsal ba'i ngang nas rang bzhin shugs kyi tshad
NK115(re)001:19226: med bzhi snang ba'i brdar phyogs bzhir sgo 'aphara rnam
NK115(re)001:19227: pa bzhi po re rer 'khyud 'gram logs gsum bsgrigs
NK115(re)001:19228: res brgyan pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19231: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK115(re)001:19233: rta babs ni rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi yon
NK115(re)001:19234: tan rdzogs pa'i brdar sgo bzhi'i phyi 'gram gnyis na
NK115(re)001:19235: ka ba gnyis gnyis te bzhis bteg pa'i sgo steng
NK115(re)001:19236: na rdo rje'i gdung bzhi'i steng rta rkang la sogs
NK115(re)001:19237: pa'i rta babs bang rim brgyad dang ldan pa la
NK115(re)001:19238: rin po che'i gdugs kyi rtsa bar chos kyi 'khor
NK115(re)001:19239: lo ri dwags gnyis kyis bskyod pas 'khor ba dang
NK115(re)001:19240: / rgyu ni dbyings las ye shesa lngara snang bas
NK115(re)001:19241: dgos 'dod kyi re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i
NK115(re)001:19242: brdar nang nas mthing ljang dmar ser dkar ba'i rin
NK115(re)001:19243: po che'i rtsiga pa lnga bsgrags su yod pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19244: glo 'bur ni ye shes de re re la'ang lhag
NK115(re)001:19245: pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su
NK115(re)001:19246: gru chad las phyi 'phyar ba'i rin po che'i glo
NK115(re)001:19247: 'bur rigs bzhi'i kha dog dang ldan pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19248: rgyan ni rtsig pa'i steng na chos nyid 'gyur ba
NK115(re)001:19249: med pa mtshon pa'i brdar pha gu ser po dang
NK115(re)001:19250: / thugs rje dang phrin las rgyun mi 'chad pa'am
NK115(re)001:19251: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i brdar kha bad kyi
NK115(re)001:19252: gdung sna sogs na rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang
NK115(re)001:19253: d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang ba nyi zla'i rlung bskyod
NK115(re)001:19255: thugs rjes 'gro ba skyob pa'i brdar mad'a yab dang /
NK115(re)001:19256: kun gyi bla mar gyur pa'am chos nyid bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:19257: mi khyab pa mtshon pa'i pu shu mchod rten sum
NK115(re)001:19258: brtsegs su bsgrigs pa can dang /
NK115(re)001:19259: phyi nang gi rtsig 'gram gyi snam bur 'doda pa'i
NK115(re)001:19260: yona tan thams cad ma spangs par ye shes rang
NK115(re)001:19261: snang gi rgyan du rol pa'i brdar mig yangsa ma
NK115(re)001:19262: ste mchod pa'i lha mo gzugs rdo rje ma la
NK115(re)001:19263: sogs pa bde stong gnyis su med pa'i mchoda pa'i
NK115(re)001:19264: sprina spro bas rtse zhing dag'a ba'i rnam 'gyur sna
NK115(re)001:19266: gzhan yang thugs rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang
NK115(re)001:19267: 'gag pa med pa las yon tan dang phrin las
NK115(re)001:19268: kyi rnam par 'phrul pa dpag tu med pa snang
NK115(re)001:19269: ba'i brdar rnga yaba dang 'aphana gdugas rgyal matshana la
NK115(re)001:19270: sogs pa'i rgyan gyi bkod pa dpag tu med pas
NK115(re)001:19272: rtse mo'i don ni nor bu rin po che'i tog la sogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19273: de yang bla ste gzhal yas khang gi steng phub
NK115(re)001:19274: chen gyi dbus mthongs ka'i rnam par yod pa'i gdung
NK115(re)001:19275: zlum gyi steng na de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:19276: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad
NK115(re)001:19277: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i yon tan thams cad chos
NK115(re)001:19278: kyi dbyings su ro gcig par zlum pa'i brdar bum
NK115(re)001:19279: pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil ba'i steng du nang
NK115(re)001:19280: gi ka ba brgyad kyis btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung
NK115(re)001:19281: bzhi bsnol ba'i steng bre mtshon pa'i ka thung bzhis
NK115(re)001:19282: bteg pa'i phub chung gi rtser pad+ma la gnas pa'i
NK115(re)001:19283: chos kyi 'khoor lo rin po che'i zara tshagas dang
NK115(re)001:19284: bcas pas brgyan pa'i gatsanga khanga phyur bur mdzesa pa'i
NK115(re)001:19285: steng na / de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan ni
NK115(re)001:19286: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:19287: thams cad kyi pha rol tu son zhing kun gyi
NK115(re)001:19288: rtse mor gyur pas tshad gzung du med pa'i brdar
NK115(re)001:19289: rin po che'i tog stong 'od zer 'phro ba sangs
NK115(re)001:19290: rgyas kyi dbu'i gtsug tor ltar mi mngon pas mdzes
NK115(re)001:19291: steng na / pa'o // rgya tshad ni chos kyi
NK115(re)001:19292: dbyings rgya tshad dang bral ba'i rtags su gzhal yas
NK115(re)001:19293: khang de'i chu zheng dang mtho dam'i srid tshad du
NK115(re)001:19294: steng na / pa'o // mi mngona pa'o // mtshan
NK115(re)001:19295: nyid ni chos thams cad chos kyi dbyings rig pa'i
NK115(re)001:19296: ngang las ma g.yos pa'i brdar phyogs ganga bltas ganga
NK115(re)001:19297: du ye shes kyi 'od lnga rab tu dwangs pa'i
NK115(re)001:19298: gzhal yas khang de las mi 'da' bar snang zhing
NK115(re)001:19299: steng na / pa'o // mi mngona pa'o // /
NK115(re)001:19300: ye shes re re la lnga re ste nyi shu
NK115(re)001:19301: rtsa lnga la sogs pa'i ye shes dang yon tan
NK115(re)001:19302: grangs tshad gzung du med pa'i brdar gzhal yas khang
NK115(re)001:19303: gi grangsa kyi tshad kyang mthas mi gtugsa pa mkha'a
NK115(re)001:19304: dbyingsa thams cad snod du gyur pa bzhina gsal bar
NK115(re)001:19305: steng na / pa'o // mi mngona pa'o // /
NK115(re)001:19306: snang ba'o // gdan gyi rnam pa ni de ltar
NK115(re)001:19307: rten gzhi gazhala meda khanga gis mkha' dbyings thams cad
NK115(re)001:19308: khyab par snang ba de dag re re'i nanga du
NK115(re)001:19309: steng na / pa'o // mi mngona pa'o // /
NK115(re)001:19310: snang ba'o // / brtena pa lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK115(re)001:19311: gtso bo rigs lnga yi gadna khri ni /
NK115(re)001:19312: mi 'jigs pa bzhis bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i brdar dbus su 'phroga byed de seng ge'i khri dang /
NK115(re)001:19313: stobs bcus mi dge ba bcu 'dul ba'i rtags su
NK115(re)001:19314: shar du gnyis 'thunga ste glang po che'i khri dang
NK115(re)001:19315: / rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes
NK115(re)001:19316: pas gdul bya rnams 'khor ba las thogs pa med
NK115(re)001:19317: par myur du sgrol ba'i rtags su lho ru canga
NK115(re)001:19318: shes te rta mchog gi khri dang /
NK115(re)001:19319: dbang bcu mthar phyin nas snang ba la rang dbang
NK115(re)001:19320: thob pa'i brdar nub tu zlos gar can te rma
NK115(re)001:19321: bya'i khri dang / phrin las rnam pa bzhis skye
NK115(re)001:19322: gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba rnams sgrol ba'i rtags
NK115(re)001:19323: su byang du shanga shanga te'u'i khri rnams kyi steng
NK115(re)001:19325: rin po che dbang gi rgyud las /
NK115(re)001:19326: sku ni mi 'jigs bdud bzhi rab tu 'joms //
NK115(re)001:19327: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:19328: thugs ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK115(re)001:19329: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:19330: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med bgrod //
NK115(re)001:19331: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:19332: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i tshul //
NK115(re)001:19333: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:19334: las ni phrin las rnam bzhis skye bzhi sgrol //
NK115(re)001:19335: de grub rtags su mkha' lding khri la bzhugs //
NK115(re)001:19337: de yang srog chags kyi gzugs su snang ba de dag gis //
NK115(re)001:19338: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i rtags su rin po che'i khri bteg pa'i steng na /
NK115(re)001:19339: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i brdar chu skyes pad+ma'i gdan dang /
NK115(re)001:19340: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'jug pa'i brdar nyi
NK115(re)001:19341: ma dang zla ba'i gdan gyi steng na bzhugs pa
NK115(re)001:19342: 'o // de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad
NK115(re)001:19343: pa de rnams lam pa'i gang zag gis bsgom dus
NK115(re)001:19344: rnam dag dran pa'i ched du yin la /
NK115(re)001:19345: 'dir bstan pa rnams gdul byas don de dag rtogs pa'i ched tsam ma yin par /
NK115(re)001:19346: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i yon tan lhun rdzogs su shar ba ste /
NK115(re)001:19347: me long gi ngos la gzugs brnyan snang ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:19348: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19349: gdul bya'i sems snang gis bsdus pa'i dus gsum du
NK115(re)001:19350: nges pa 'dren pa las 'das pa ni chos nyid
NK115(re)001:19351: gzhira rdzogsa kun tu bazanga po 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK115(re)001:19352: dus te / dper na sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:19353: ni chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba yin pas
NK115(re)001:19354: bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid la'ang sangs rgyas kyi
NK115(re)001:19355: dus na zhes gzhal yul la ltos nas bzhag pa
NK115(re)001:19356: dus te / bzhin / 'dir yang chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:19357: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po dang gnas 'pho 'gyur
NK115(re)001:19358: med pa ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa'i dus la
NK115(re)001:19361: dus gsum dus med rtogs pa po //
NK115(re)001:19364: ye shes kyi snang ba chen po rang gsal bas mi g.yo ba'i dus te /
NK115(re)001:19366: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang /
NK115(re)001:19367: 'od srung sems dang chos kyi de bzhin nyid ni gang nas kyang ma 'ongs /
NK115(re)001:19369: gar yang mi gnas pas na ma nges pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19370: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK115(re)001:19372: gsum pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19373: ngo bo chos nyid las g.yo ba med pas 'pho
NK115(re)001:19374: 'gyura dang brala ba'i ye shes kyi sku matshana bzang
NK115(re)001:19375: po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po
NK115(re)001:19376: brgyad cu gnas na gnas pa dang gsal ba dang
NK115(re)001:19377: yongs su rdzogsa pas spras shing rang snang gi 'khor
NK115(re)001:19378: la dgongs brgyud kyi ston pa lngara snang ba ste
NK115(re)001:19379: / de yang rig pa'i ye shes la 'bras chos
NK115(re)001:19380: lnga dang ye shes lnga la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:19381: ji snyed cig lhun gyis grub par yod pa rnams
NK115(re)001:19382: sems can gyi dus su rig rtsal las rlung gis
NK115(re)001:19383: bslad pas ma dag pa phung khams skye mched kyi
NK115(re)001:19384: chos su snang yang 'bras bu'i chos dang tshul mthun
NK115(re)001:19385: par phung po lnga dang dug lnga la sogs par
NK115(re)001:19386: snang bas phung sogs 'di nyid 'bras bu'i chos su
NK115(re)001:19387: snang ba yang ma yin la /
NK115(re)001:19388: 'di las gzhan zhig kyang med do zhes gsungs pa'i
NK115(re)001:19389: don gdul bya'i mos pa dang 'tshams par bstan pa'i
NK115(re)001:19390: rgyud sde 'og ma rnams las lcags khams gser du
NK115(re)001:19391: 'gyur ba bzhin gnas 'gyur lta bu'i tshul du lha
NK115(re)001:19393: 'dir ni rang snang la bdag tu bzung ba'i med
NK115(re)001:19394: snang glo bur ba'i chos rtog tshogs su snang ba
NK115(re)001:19395: thams cad rang bzhin med pa gdod ma'i dbyings su
NK115(re)001:19396: dag pa'i tshe na rang gnas kyi yon tan ji
NK115(re)001:19397: lta ba bzhin mngon du 'gyur bas /
NK115(re)001:19398: dper na rmi lam gyi snang ba dang sad dus
NK115(re)001:19399: kyi snang ba gnyis tshul mthun yang de der gnas
NK115(re)001:19400: 'gyur ba ma yin pa bzhin rig gdangs 'gag pa
NK115(re)001:19401: med pa la rten 'brel gyi chos su snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:19402: phung sogs ma dag pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19403: sku dang ye shes kyi chos dag par snang ba
NK115(re)001:19404: gnyis po grogs la sogs pa'i chos 'ga' zhig mthun
NK115(re)001:19405: pas rtog pa'i grangs kyi lhar gsungs pa ltar yod
NK115(re)001:19406: kyang de der gnas 'gyur ba ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:19407: de ltar go bar byas nas phyi snod du snang
NK115(re)001:19408: ba'i bag chags thams cad dag pas 'og min gyi
NK115(re)001:19409: zhing dang gzhal yas khang du snang ba de'i tshe
NK115(re)001:19410: nang bcud du 'dzin pa'i bag chags dag pas brten
NK115(re)001:19411: pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba'i gtso bo ni
NK115(re)001:19412: / dbus su chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes 'gyur
NK115(re)001:19413: ba med pas sku rnama par snanga mdzad sku mdog
NK115(re)001:19415: de yang kun mkhyen chen po ni /
NK115(re)001:19416: rnam par shes pa'i rang bzhin tha dad du 'char
NK115(re)001:19417: zhing me long du gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:19418: ye shes dang ldan pa rnam par snang mdzad du
NK115(re)001:19419: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud sder 'grel to //
NK115(re)001:19420: de bzhin du shar du me long lta bu'i ye
NK115(re)001:19421: shes dri ma thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir mtshan
NK115(re)001:19422: ma'i skyon gyis ma gos pas thugs mi bskyod rdo
NK115(re)001:19423: rje dkar po / lho ru mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:19424: ye shes che ba'i yon tan du ma dang ldan
NK115(re)001:19425: pas yon tan rina chena 'byung ldan ser po /
NK115(re)001:19426: nub tu so sor rtog pa'i ye shes 'gro ba'i
NK115(re)001:19427: don la rjes su chags pas gsung 'od matshana stong
NK115(re)001:19429: byang du bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis sems
NK115(re)001:19430: can gyi don sna tshogs su mdzad pas don yod
NK115(re)001:19431: gruba pa ljang gur snang ba ste /
NK115(re)001:19432: yab lnga po de rnams ni zhal gsum phyag drug pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19436: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK115(re)001:19437: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes //
NK115(re)001:19438: dang po thugs dang g.yon 'khyud pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19440: de dag gi dag pa'ang gsang snying las /
NK115(re)001:19441: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyis skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK115(re)001:19442: ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK115(re)001:19444: ye shes lnga po de rnams ranga ranga gi yul
NK115(re)001:19445: dbyings lnga'i rtsal snang rang rigas kyi yum dbyings kyi
NK115(re)001:19451: de dag kyang sku mdog yab dang mtshungs shing zhal
NK115(re)001:19452: gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rang rtags dang g.yon dbyings kyi
NK115(re)001:19453: phyag rgya dril bu 'dzin pa dang bacasa pa rnamas
NK115(re)001:19454: rnam pa longs spyod rdzogs kyang des chos kyi sku
NK115(re)001:19455: dang sprul pa'i sku yang gzung bas sku gsum gyi
NK115(re)001:19456: yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa kha sbyor
NK115(re)001:19457: yan lag bduna gyi badga nyid chena pora bzhugas te
NK115(re)001:19458: / 'di ltar dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rgyud snying rje chen pos gang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19459: de'i phrin las kyi 'jug pa sems can gyi khams la rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19460: gdul bya nam 'dul ba'i dus la bab pa de'i
NK115(re)001:19461: tshe phrin las 'gog med du 'char ba ste sprul
