NK115(re)001:19463: ye shes kyi rang 'od kyi lha mo dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19464: de las zag med kyi bde ba chen po rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19465: tshig dang yi ge med pa dgongs rgyud kyi chos
NK115(re)001:19466: 'khor la rtag par longs spyod pa ste longs sku'i
NK115(re)001:19467: yan lag gsum / rnam pa de dag dang ldan
NK115(re)001:19468: yang rang gi ngo bo spros pa kun gyi pha
NK115(re)001:19469: rol tu son pas rang bzhin med pa chos sku'i
NK115(re)001:19470: yan lag gcig ste bdun no //
NK115(re)001:19471: bzhi pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19472: rgyud mas sbyang gi gang zag sar gnas kyi byang
NK115(re)001:19473: sems la sogs pa lta bu ma yin par ston
NK115(re)001:19474: pa nyid kyi thugs rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal
NK115(re)001:19475: las snang ba yin pas ranga lasa rgyud tha dad
NK115(re)001:19476: pa dang mchog dman med cing mi gazhana pa'i 'khor
NK115(re)001:19478: 'joms byed khro bo gnyis su snang ba las /
NK115(re)001:19479: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor la phyi nang gi semsa
NK115(re)001:19480: dapa'a brgyad dang de dag gi yum semsa ma'i 'khora
NK115(re)001:19482: de dag las dang po nang sems yab yum brgyad ni /
NK115(re)001:19483: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan gyi ye shes sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:19484: med pa tha mal ba'i mig shes ltar ma yin
NK115(re)001:19485: par / yul lnga ga la 'jug pas chos nyid
NK115(re)001:19486: du ro gcig par gzigs pa sa yi snying por
NK115(re)001:19487: par / snang ngo // de bzhin du yul lnga ga la 'jug pa kun la sbyar te /
NK115(re)001:19488: snyan gyi ye shes kyis de bzhin nyid du ro gcig par gsan pa phyag na rdo rje /
NK115(re)001:19489: shangs kyi ye shes kyi skye ba med par ro gcig tu tshor ba nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK115(re)001:19490: ljags kyi ye shes kyis gnyis su med par ro
NK115(re)001:19491: gcig tu myong bas spyan ras gzigs su snang ba
NK115(re)001:19492: ste yab bzhi'o // chos nyid sogs bzhi ni /
NK115(re)001:19493: don dam spros pa dang bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19494: kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bur dang /
NK115(re)001:19495: rang bzhin skye ba med par dang /
NK115(re)001:19496: mtshan nyid gnyis su med par mkhyen pas ye shes re re la'ang bzhi ka ldan par sems so //
NK115(re)001:19497: de dag gi yum bzhi yang ye shes bzhi po
NK115(re)001:19498: de'i gzigs pa'i yul tha mal pa la snang ba
NK115(re)001:19499: las khyad par du 'phags te ye shes rang dang
NK115(re)001:19500: ro gcig par ye shes re res kyang yul thams
NK115(re)001:19502: mkhyen bya gtso bo'i dbang du gzugs rdo rje sgeg mo /
NK115(re)001:19505: ro gar ma ste bzhir snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:19506: phyi sems yab yum brgyad ni /
NK115(re)001:19507: sangs rgyas kyi rdo rje'i spyan gyi dbang po ni
NK115(re)001:19508: tha mal pa las khyad par du 'phags te yul
NK115(re)001:19509: lnga ga la gzigs pa'i ye shes kyi rten byed
NK115(re)001:19510: pa de nyid byams par snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19511: khyad chos de bzhin du sbyar te /
NK115(re)001:19512: snyan gyi dbang po nyams pa med pa sgrib pa rnam sel dang /
NK115(re)001:19513: shangs kyi dbang po kun tu bzang po dang /
NK115(re)001:19514: ljags kyi dbang po 'jam dpal rnams su snang zhing /
NK115(re)001:19515: yum bzhi yang de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi spyan
NK115(re)001:19516: la sogs pa'i dbang po de rnams kyis rten byas
NK115(re)001:19517: nas yul mkhyen pa'i tshul tha mal bas da lta'i
NK115(re)001:19518: gzugs sogs kho na shes la /
NK115(re)001:19519: de yang chags thogs dang bcas pa yin pas de
NK115(re)001:19520: las khyad par du 'phags de dus bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK115(re)001:19521: chos thams cad gcig car du chags thogs med par
NK115(re)001:19522: gzigs pas na / gzigs tshul de lta bus 'das
NK115(re)001:19523: pa'i dus la gzigs pa 'jug pa bdug spos ma
NK115(re)001:19524: gzigs pas na / / da ltar gyi dus la gzigs pa 'jug pa me tog ma /
NK115(re)001:19525: ma 'ongs pa'i dus la gzigs pa 'jug pa snang gsal ma /
NK115(re)001:19526: de dag kyang dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi ye
NK115(re)001:19527: shes te rang byung gi snang ba ji bzhin pa'i
NK115(re)001:19528: ngang nas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i chos nyid la zhugs
NK115(re)001:19529: pa dri chab mar snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:19530: de dag yul dus bzhi dang yul can ye shes
NK115(re)001:19531: gang la sbyar kyang don 'dra ste yul dang yul
NK115(re)001:19532: can ro gcig par mkhyen pas so //
NK115(re)001:19533: tshul 'di dag gis ni gzugs sku'i ye shes phyir
NK115(re)001:19534: gsal gyi chas shes bya thams cad mngon sum du
NK115(re)001:19535: mkhyen pa'i ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK115(re)001:19536: de'i rang bzhin ye shes rang gi chos nyid dang
NK115(re)001:19537: dbyer med par mkhyen pa'i ji lta'i ye shes dang
NK115(re)001:19538: / rang snang na gzugs sku yod med kyi dgag
NK115(re)001:19539: sgrub kyang mi dgos par sku dang ye shes yul
NK115(re)001:19540: dang bcas pa thams cad thugs rang byung gi ye
NK115(re)001:19541: shes rang las shar zhing rang la ma 'gags par
NK115(re)001:19542: snang yang chos nyid kyi ngos na rang gzhan dang
NK115(re)001:19543: snang mi snang la sogs pa'i tha snyad thams cad
NK115(re)001:19544: las 'das pa rnams la nges shes kyang skyes par
NK115(re)001:19545: / rlom mo // 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19546: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thabs dang shes rab chen po'i
NK115(re)001:19547: rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas bdud
NK115(re)001:19548: dang log par 'dren pa thams cad 'joms shing rang
NK115(re)001:19549: snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la mtshan ma'i rtog
NK115(re)001:19550: pa gang gis kyang glags rnyed pa'i skabs med pa'i
NK115(re)001:19551: rtags su sgo ba bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19552: de bzhina du so so'i yuma dang bcas par snang ste /
NK115(re)001:19553: de yang tha mal pa'i lus kyi shes pa /
NK115(re)001:19556: de gsum 'dus pa'i reg pa bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19557: de bzhin du ngag la sgra'i shes pa /
NK115(re)001:19564: de gsum 'dus pa ste bzhi po de dag gi
NK115(re)001:19565: sgo nas sgo gsum rang rang gi bya byed du
NK115(re)001:19566: snang ba la khyad par du 'phags pa de bzhin
NK115(re)001:19567: gshegs pa rnams kyi gsang ba gsum gyi ye shes
NK115(re)001:19570: de gsum 'dus pa'i cha bzhi pos shes bya thams
NK115(re)001:19571: cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i rang bzhin gshin rje'i gshed
NK115(re)001:19574: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ste bzhir snang zhing /
NK115(re)001:19575: de yang skye 'jig med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19577: rnam par rig byed med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:19578: rnam pa med par rtogs pa'i ye shes bzhir gnas dag pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19579: de dag gi yum yang ye shes de dag gi
NK115(re)001:19580: yul rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i dbyings
NK115(re)001:19581: kyi cha dang / dbyings de las shar ba'i tshad med pa bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19582: bsdu ba bzhi'i sgo nas 'gro ba rnams sdud pa'i rtags su lcags kyu /
NK115(re)001:19585: dril bu ma bzhir snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:19586: lnga pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19587: ston pas gsungs pa med bzhin 'khor gyi sems dpa'
NK115(re)001:19588: rnams la rang ngo'i shes rab kyi cha la rang
NK115(re)001:19589: snang ba'i tshul gyis ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po'i
NK115(re)001:19590: chosa kyi 'khora lo ni grag pa'i sgra dang brjod
NK115(re)001:19591: pa'i tshig gi matshana ma'i yul lasa 'adsa par bskora
NK115(re)001:19592: ba ni / klong drug pa las /
NK115(re)001:19593: nyid kyi zhal nas ma gsungs par //
NK115(re)001:19594: rmi lam lta bu'i mtshan nyid du //
NK115(re)001:19595: 'khor gyi sems dpa' rnams la ni /
NK115(re)001:19596: shes rab rtog dpyod blo la snang //
NK115(re)001:19598: de skad du mdo las kyang /
NK115(re)001:19599: rgyal ba'i sras po cang mi gsung //
NK115(re)001:19600: ma gsungs pa nyid rgya cher gsungs //
NK115(re)001:19601: zhes pa ltar sangs rgyas rnams kyi don dam pa'i
NK115(re)001:19602: chos kyi 'khor lo ni skyes bu'i rnam rig dang
NK115(re)001:19603: 'brel ba ma grub pas sgra tshig mtshan ma'i spyod
NK115(re)001:19604: yul las 'das pa'i don rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK115(re)001:19605: po'i ngo bor gnas pa yin te /
NK115(re)001:19607: chos ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ste //
NK115(re)001:19608: snying po lhun 'byams smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK115(re)001:19610: de lta bu'i chos 'khor la 'gog lam gyi bden pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i tshul yang /
NK115(re)001:19611: zla ba sgron ma'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:19612: gang gis chos gcig po yongs su bslabs pas yon
NK115(re)001:19613: tan gyi chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur
NK115(re)001:19614: ro // gcig po gang zhe na /
NK115(re)001:19615: gang de kho na nyid du shes pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19617: gnyis pa 'bras bu lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:19618: steng khang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK115(re)001:19620: dang po steng khang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:19621: de lta bu'i sku gsum yan lag bdun ldan gyi
NK115(re)001:19622: longs sku de las rlung cha dang bcas pa dag
NK115(re)001:19623: nas 'og min rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK115(re)001:19624: rang snang ba'i tshe na dkyil 'khor ji ltar bkod
NK115(re)001:19625: pa'i tshul la / spyir chos nyid skye ba med
NK115(re)001:19626: pa'i gdangs las rol pa 'gag pa med par cir
NK115(re)001:19627: yang 'char du rung bas na rgyud sde so sor
NK115(re)001:19628: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor bkod tshul gyi rnam pa
NK115(re)001:19629: dang lha'i grangs la sogs pa mi 'dra ba du
NK115(re)001:19630: ma yod kyang de dag las 'di ni yin la
NK115(re)001:19631: gzhan ltar ni ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:19632: zhes bya bar phyogs gcig tu gzung bar byar med
NK115(re)001:19633: na'ang 'dir ni zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis su gsungs
NK115(re)001:19634: pas / rang snang gi khro bo'ang yod par bshad de /
NK115(re)001:19636: mnyam nyid ngang gis khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:19637: khros pas longs spyod rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:19638: rdo rje'i 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:19639: zhes pas chos nyid kyi khro bo dngos po dang
NK115(re)001:19640: mtshan mar med pas chos sku spros pa'i mtha' dang
NK115(re)001:19641: bral ba ste de'i ngang las 'og min du he
NK115(re)001:19642: ru ka'i dkyil 'khor snang ba ni longs spyod rdzogs
NK115(re)001:19643: pa'i rang bzhin don gyi gnas lugs yin par gsungs
NK115(re)001:19644: shing / de'i thugs rje lhun gyis grub pas gang
NK115(re)001:19645: la gang 'dul gyi khro bo'i rol pa sna tshogs
NK115(re)001:19646: par snang ba ni mdzad pa phrin las kyi rang
NK115(re)001:19648: de ltar zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis po de lus
NK115(re)001:19649: la ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul sngar bshad pa ltar
NK115(re)001:19650: snying ga na zhi ba'i lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa
NK115(re)001:19651: gnyis su gnas pa'i gdangs las klad pa dung khang
NK115(re)001:19652: gi gzhal yas na khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams yod
NK115(re)001:19653: par bshad pa'i steng 'og gi go rim bzhin gzhal
NK115(re)001:19654: yas khang gi nang du zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams
NK115(re)001:19655: gsal ba'i rang 'od steng gi nam mkhar dbu'i phyur
NK115(re)001:19656: bu'i nang du khro bo'i lha tshogs kun gsal bar
NK115(re)001:19657: gsungs pa'i tshul de yang 'og min gyi zhing gi
NK115(re)001:19658: rnam pa lam byed yin pas de ltar yang yin
NK115(re)001:19659: mod / skabs 'dir ni 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor
NK115(re)001:19660: steng khang zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo
NK115(re)001:19661: bzhi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'i 'og tu khro
NK115(re)001:19662: bo'i dkyil 'khor yod pa'i lugs ltar las /
NK115(re)001:19663: zhi ba'i lha grangs ni rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa'i rtsa
NK115(re)001:19664: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi'i le'u'i dgongs pa gsang 'grel mun
NK115(re)001:19665: sel gyis ji ltar bkral ba bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:19666: de yang 'og min rdo rje dbyings byang chub snying
NK115(re)001:19667: po'i gansa la mnga' dabnga madzada pa'i rgyal ba zhi
NK115(re)001:19668: ba'i lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyisa su gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:19669: lasa / dbyings dang rig pa zung du 'jug pa
NK115(re)001:19670: la dam pa'i stang dpyal du smos pa kun bzang
NK115(re)001:19671: yab yum gnyisa ni longs sprul gnyis kyi sprul gzhi
NK115(re)001:19672: ste gzugs sku kun la khyab par brdal ba'i thugs
NK115(re)001:19673: dmigs bsam spros pa las 'das pa yin pas chosa
NK115(re)001:19674: lasa / kyi sku ste / rin chen sgron ma las /
NK115(re)001:19675: mi gnas chos dbyings dkyil 'khor na //
NK115(re)001:19676: kun bzang yab yum zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:19677: de las longs skur bzhengs pa na //
NK115(re)001:19678: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yin par grags //
NK115(re)001:19679: sprul pas 'gro don mdzad pa na //
NK115(re)001:19680: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje 'dzin //
NK115(re)001:19681: grangs med dpag gis mi lang ngo //
NK115(re)001:19683: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba drug po so so'i
NK115(re)001:19684: gansa su rang rang gi mos pa dang 'tshams par
NK115(re)001:19685: don mdzad pa'i riga pa'i skyes bu thub pa druga
NK115(re)001:19686: ni gdul bya'i ngor sprula par shara ba'i phyir gdul
NK115(re)001:19687: bya de dag gi bsod nams kyi snang bas bsdus
NK115(re)001:19688: pa yin pas 'og min du mi snang yang /
NK115(re)001:19689: rgyal pa'i thugs rje gdul yul drug tu 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:19690: phrin las kyi gzugs brnyan lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:19692: de bas na rang snang don gyi 'og min longas
NK115(re)001:19693: spyod rdzogs pa sku'i zhing na gzugs sku'i rnam par
NK115(re)001:19694: dngos su snang ba ni rgyal ba sum cu rtsa
NK115(re)001:19695: bzhi ste / de yang gtso bo rigs lnga yab
NK115(re)001:19696: yum bcu la phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum
NK115(re)001:19697: bzhi ste / bcu drug dang / sgo skyong yab
NK115(re)001:19698: yum brgyad de nyer bzhi po ni 'khor gyi tshul
NK115(re)001:19699: bzhi ste / bcu drug dang / du bzhugs so
NK115(re)001:19700: // de dag kyang rgyud sde 'og ma'i lugs ltar
NK115(re)001:19701: phung sogs gnas su dag pa'am /
NK115(re)001:19702: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lugs
NK115(re)001:19703: kyi chos nyid stong pa nyid dang chos can snang
NK115(re)001:19704: ba nyid ni rang bzhin gyi rdo rje phung po
NK115(re)001:19705: / de'i yan lag rnam par shes pa la sogs pa'i phung po lnga rigs lnga /
NK115(re)001:19706: nam mkha' la sogs pa'i khamas rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK115(re)001:19707: mig la sogs pa nang gi skye mched drug dang /
NK115(re)001:19708: gzugs la sogs pa phyi'i drug ste skye mched bcu gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:19709: de dag gi khams bcu gnyis dang /
NK115(re)001:19710: rnam par shes pa'i khams drug ste bco brgyad po
NK115(re)001:19711: thams cad kun kyang phyi nang gi sems dpa' sems
NK115(re)001:19712: ma sgo skyong gi khro mo'i rang bzhin du ye
NK115(re)001:19713: nas gansa pa'i phyi srid gsum thams cad sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:19714: kyi zhing khams su gdod nas rnam par dag pa'i
NK115(re)001:19715: lha gadna gsum tshanga ba'i dkyila 'khora chena pora gnas
NK115(re)001:19716: pa yin te / de skad du'ang /
NK115(re)001:19717: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK115(re)001:19718: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK115(re)001:19719: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK115(re)001:19720: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK115(re)001:19721: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK115(re)001:19722: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK115(re)001:19723: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK115(re)001:19724: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas shing //
NK115(re)001:19726: tshul 'di daga ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19727: dpal sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang /
NK115(re)001:19728: 'dus pa'i rgyud snga phyi gnyis la sogsa pa'i bla
NK115(re)001:19729: na med pa'i rgyud sde phal mo che las lusa
NK115(re)001:19730: grub kyi dkyil 'khora ni ji snyed cig bstan pa
NK115(re)001:19731: rnams rang snang gis bsdus pa'i zhing khams yin pas
NK115(re)001:19732: de rnams dang rnama dag kyang mtshungsa pa yina la
NK115(re)001:19733: / gzhan snang la shar ba'i zhi ba'am /
NK115(re)001:19734: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni 'og min gyi zhing khams las gzhan du gyur pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19735: dper na sgrub sde las bgegs 'dul phyir rmi lam
NK115(re)001:19736: ltar sprul pa 'jig rten pa'i 'khor gtso bor gyur
NK115(re)001:19737: ba'i dkyil 'khor gsum du bstan pa bzhin te 'chad
NK115(re)001:19738: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa 'og khang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19739: zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang gi 'og na rang byung
NK115(re)001:19740: gi khanga pa tshogsa chena po 'dus pa'i dkyila 'khora
NK115(re)001:19741: lhun grub tu snang ba ni /
NK115(re)001:19742: yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:19743: 'byung ba rim brtsegs rus pa'i ri rab dang bcas
NK115(re)001:19744: pa'i khar rin po che'i brag gtams pa'i steng ye
NK115(re)001:19745: shes kyi rang 'od me'i phung po rab tu 'abra
NK115(re)001:19746: ba'i klong na gazhala yasa khang phyi nang rim pa
NK115(re)001:19747: dgu ye shes rang snang gi rgyan rab tu rngam
NK115(re)001:19748: zhing 'jigs su rung bas brgyan pa /
NK115(re)001:19749: sgo khyamsa rim pa dgu pa'i bar khyams dgu po
NK115(re)001:19750: nang nas rim par dang po gsum ser dkar dmar
NK115(re)001:19751: ba / de nas gsum ser dmar dkar ba /
NK115(re)001:19752: de nas gsum nag po phyogs mdog ljang gu /
NK115(re)001:19753: sgo phyi mara rgyu 'brasa kyi rta babas gnyis las
NK115(re)001:19754: dang po stegs babs zhon gyi tshul du yod cing
NK115(re)001:19755: / gnyis pa sgo khang gi steng na rgyan gyi rnam par ldana pa /
NK115(re)001:19756: pho branga dbus ma'i nanga du gru chad bzhi glo
NK115(re)001:19757: 'bur gyis mdzes pa'i steng na 'khor lo ser po
NK115(re)001:19758: rtsibs brgyad pa'i lte bar rdo rje'i brag chen po
NK115(re)001:19759: gtams pa'i khar pad+ma dkar po 'dab ma stong du
NK115(re)001:19760: brdala ba la thabas shes kyi rang bzhin nyi ma
NK115(re)001:19761: nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang zla ba nyi shu rtsa
NK115(re)001:19762: bzhi kha sbyor du bkod par dregs pa'i dabnga phyug
NK115(re)001:19763: khyo shuga ni nyi shu rtsa bzhi byi chings su
NK115(re)001:19764: bsnol ba'i steng du dapa'a gtum stag dang /
NK115(re)001:19771: zhe sdang lto 'gro ste byol song gi gtso bo
NK115(re)001:19772: brgyad po re res dregsa pa pho rnams kha sbub
NK115(re)001:19773: tu yod pa'i sog phrag dang /
NK115(re)001:19774: mo rnams gan rkyal du yod pa'i nu phrag tu
NK115(re)001:19775: bzung zhing bardzisa pa'i steng na 'khora 'adsa kun gyi
NK115(re)001:19776: spyi dapala chen po bcoma ldan 'adsa 'jig rten na
NK115(re)001:19777: che ba'i lha chen po la sogs pa las kyang
NK115(re)001:19779: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad kyi che ba'i
NK115(re)001:19780: yon tan thams cad gcig tu rdzogs pas che ba'i
NK115(re)001:19781: machaga sku mdog mthing nag in+d+ra n+ai la'i mdangsa can
NK115(re)001:19782: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od snang ltar 'bar ba'i gzi
NK115(re)001:19784: zhal bdun sum nyi shu rtsa gcig gi rtsa zhal sku lus dang mtshungs pa /
NK115(re)001:19785: g.yas zhal gsum ser dmar ljang ba /
NK115(re)001:19786: g.yon zhal gsum dmar sngo ljang ba /
NK115(re)001:19787: de'i steng gi dbus zhal ser po /
NK115(re)001:19790: de'i steng gi dbus zhal mthing ga /
NK115(re)001:19796: kun gyi steng zhal dmar po rta skad mtsher ba /
NK115(re)001:19798: phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyisa kyis dang po gnyis na kun bzang yab yum thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK115(re)001:19799: lhag ma g.yas kyi nyi shu na rigs lnga sems
NK115(re)001:19800: dpa' brgyad khro bo bzhi mtho ris kyi thub pa
NK115(re)001:19801: gsum dang / g.yon nyi shu na yum lnga sems
NK115(re)001:19802: ma brgyad khro mo bzhi ngan song gi thub pa
NK115(re)001:19803: gsum ste zhi ba'i lha tshogas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK115(re)001:19804: gsum dang / bsnamsa pa / phyag rgya drug dang /
NK115(re)001:19805: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang /
NK115(re)001:19806: dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK115(re)001:19807: dbu re re la sangs rgyas kyi sku res brgyan
NK115(re)001:19808: pa'i dbu la 'khor lo mchod rten rin po che
NK115(re)001:19809: bdun bdun snang ba'i steng rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi
NK115(re)001:19810: mtshan ma bcus brgyan pa'i rtse mo gcig tu 'dus
NK115(re)001:19811: pa la tog stong 'od zer 'bar ba /
NK115(re)001:19812: ganma zhala yuma mchoga dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad /
NK115(re)001:19814: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyisa kyis rdo rje dang dung khrag 'dzina pa /
NK115(re)001:19815: lhag ma g.yas brgyad na gansa kyi dang /
NK115(re)001:19816: g.yon brgyad na yula gyi ma mo dang phra mena brgyad brgyad bsnamas pa /
NK115(re)001:19817: yaba yuma khro makhara te dbang mchog dang /
NK115(re)001:19819: che mchog rnams thod brtsegs kyi tshul lam /
NK115(re)001:19820: yang na manyama par sbyor ba'i tshul du bzhugs pa /
NK115(re)001:19821: srid pa khams gsum dang zhi ba theg rim dgu'i
NK115(re)001:19822: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos khamsa ma lus pa kun
NK115(re)001:19823: bcoma ldan 'adsa dpal chen po nyid kyi zhabsa kyi
NK115(re)001:19824: gadna khri nasa steng gi dbu rgyan gyi 'khora lo'i
NK115(re)001:19825: rtse mo'i bar la ranga bzhina gyis rdzogsa par snang
NK115(re)001:19826: ste / de yang 'dod khams khrag gi rgya mtsho la rdzogs /
NK115(re)001:19827: gzugs khams zhing chen gyi sa gzhi la /
NK115(re)001:19828: gzugs med keng rus kyi ri rab la /
NK115(re)001:19829: nyan rang byang sems gsum rin po che'i brag la /
NK115(re)001:19830: phyi rgyud gsum rdo rje'i brag la /
NK115(re)001:19831: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor pad+ma dkar po la /
NK115(re)001:19832: rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dbu rgyan gyi sangs rgyas dang rgyal mtshan bcu la /
NK115(re)001:19833: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor tog stong 'od zer 'phro ba la rdzogs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19834: yab yum khro mkhar gyi tshul ltar na dbus dang /
NK115(re)001:19835: mnyam par sbyor ba'i tshul ltar na gtso bo dpal
NK115(re)001:19836: chen po'i mdun du dabnga mchoga he ru ka sku
NK115(re)001:19837: mdog mthing nag dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad zhabs bzhi
NK115(re)001:19838: pa yum khro mo dbyings phyug ma dang ni mnyam
NK115(re)001:19839: par sbyor ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa /
NK115(re)001:19840: sgo gsum la bdag tu 'dzin pa dang khams gsum
NK115(re)001:19841: sa dgu dag pa'i he ru ka dapala dgu las
NK115(re)001:19842: / dbang mchog gi mdun du badz+ra he ru ka dang /
NK115(re)001:19843: 'khor lo'i rtsibs brgyad kyi phyogs bzhir bud+d+ha sogs bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19844: mtshams bzhir rak+ta sogs bzhi ste dpal dgu po thams
NK115(re)001:19845: cad zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum mnyam par sbyor
NK115(re)001:19847: glo 'bur bzhi dang gru chad rnam pa bzhi ste
NK115(re)001:19848: brgyad la ni rnam par shes pa tshogas brgyad gnas
NK115(re)001:19849: su dag pa koo r+ai ma la sogas pa brgyad
NK115(re)001:19850: 'khod do // dkyila 'khora dang po'i khyamsa la yul
NK115(re)001:19851: brgyad dag pa'i rang bzhin phyogs bzhir seng gdong ma
NK115(re)001:19852: la sogs pa mche ba can bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19853: mtshams bzhi rgod gdong ma la sogs pa gshog pa can bzhi ste phra mena ma brgyad gnas so //
NK115(re)001:19854: de'i sgo bzhir chu bo bzhi gnas su dag pa
NK115(re)001:19855: rta gdong dkar mo la sogs pa sgo ma bzhi'o
NK115(re)001:19856: // gnyis pa'i khyamsa la phyogs mtshams kyi dngos po
NK115(re)001:19857: gnas su dag pa 'bar ma nyi zer can la
NK115(re)001:19858: sogs pa spor ma rnam pa brgyad dang /
NK115(re)001:19859: sgo bzhir 'byung bzhi dag pa rgyas 'debs ma sogs sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:19860: gsum pa'i khyamsa la sgal tshigs nyer brgyad dag pa shar du srin mo smug nag sogs drug /
NK115(re)001:19861: lhor zhi ba dmar mo sogs drug /
NK115(re)001:19862: nub tu dga' byed dmar mo sogs drug /
NK115(re)001:19863: byang du gsod byed ljang nag sogs drug /
NK115(re)001:19864: sgo bzhir nag mo chen mo sogs sgo ma bzhi
NK115(re)001:19865: ste dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang bcas khyams
NK115(re)001:19866: gsum po kuna la ranga ranga gi sgo ma bzhi
NK115(re)001:19867: bzhira ldan pa'i lha tshogs de dag thams cad kyang
NK115(re)001:19868: sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyi dpal dang /
NK115(re)001:19869: gsung rngam pa'i gdangs kyi dpal dang /
NK115(re)001:19870: thugs snying rje chen po'i dpal du 'abra ba'i rnam
NK115(re)001:19871: par rola pa can gar dgu'i nyamsa kyis brjid cing
NK115(re)001:19872: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na rtog
NK115(re)001:19873: bral bde ba chen po'i rang rtsal las rang shar
NK115(re)001:19874: ba'o / 'di daga la rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK115(re)001:19875: de yang rang snang longas spyod rdzogs sku'i dkyil 'khora yin te /
NK115(re)001:19876: gzhi ka dag gi snang cha ye nas lhun gyis grub pa don gyi 'og min yin no //
NK115(re)001:19877: des na 'dir bshad pa'i dreegs pa nyer bzhi la sogs pa'ang /
NK115(re)001:19878: gdul bya de ltar 'dul ba'i rten 'brel gyi sgo dbyings la lhun grub tu shar ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:19879: de'i phyi rol du gzhan snang gis bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK115(re)001:19880: phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK115(re)001:19883: pho nya'i dkyil 'khor dang bzhi las /
NK115(re)001:19884: dang po phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19885: bzhi pa'i khyams la shar du mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma sogs bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:19886: lho ru mkha' 'gro 'joms byed ma sogs bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:19887: nub tu mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin ma sogs bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:19888: byang du mkha' 'gro phag gdong ma sogs bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:19889: sgo bzhir mkha' 'gro bum sna ma sogs bzhi ste mkha'a 'gro suma cu rtsa gnyis gnas so //
NK115(re)001:19890: gnyis pa dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19891: lnga pa'i khyamsa la bzhugs te /
NK115(re)001:19892: rdo rje kun grags ma sogs ma mo bdun dang /
NK115(re)001:19893: sgo bzhir gling bzhi mgyogs ma sogs sringa mo bzhi rnams so //
NK115(re)001:19894: gsum pa sgrol ba ging gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19895: drug pa'i khyamsa la phyogs rer gsum gsum dang sgo
NK115(re)001:19896: bzhi re re bka' nod pa'i tshul du shar nub
NK115(re)001:19897: gnyis su re re gnas te /
NK115(re)001:19899: rdo rje 'byung po sogs ging chena drug tshana gsuma ste bco brgyad do //
NK115(re)001:19900: bzhi pa pho nya'i dkyil 'khor la'ang gsum las /
NK115(re)001:19901: khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19903: rnam par rgyal ba dang snyems ma /
NK115(re)001:19904: dbyug sngon can dang sder mo sogs khro bo yab
NK115(re)001:19905: yum bcu phraga drug po phyogs mtshams brgyad du gsum
NK115(re)001:19906: gsum dang / shar nub kyi nang dang sgo bzhir re re'o //
NK115(re)001:19907: myur mgyogs yid kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19908: khyams brgyad pa'i phyogs bzhir sku dang yon tan dang
NK115(re)001:19909: gsung dang phrin las kyi pho nya drug cu rer
NK115(re)001:19910: gnas pas nyis brgya dang bzhi bcu ste phyogs kyi
NK115(re)001:19912: dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK115(re)001:19913: dgu pa'i khyamsa la 'khod pa ste /
NK115(re)001:19914: de yang pho nya ma mo drug cu rnams phyogs bzhi po re rer bco lnga bco lnga'o //
NK115(re)001:19915: khyams bzhi pa nas dgu pa'i bar du bka' nyan
NK115(re)001:19916: gyi tshul du 'khod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di log par
NK115(re)001:19917: 'drena pa'i ma rungs pa rnams 'dul ba'i phyir du
NK115(re)001:19918: sprul pas bsdus pa yin pa'i phyir na bgegsa la
NK115(re)001:19919: sogas pa gdul bya so so'i ranga ngora snang ba
NK115(re)001:19920: yin pa de yi phyir na rang snang 'og min
NK115(re)001:19922: des na de dag dkyil 'khor du dgod pa'i tshul de ni /
NK115(re)001:19923: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas 'og min drug gsungs pa las /
NK115(re)001:19924: rtog pa'i 'og min lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du bsdu'o //
NK115(re)001:19925: 'o na 'dir 'bras bu'i yon tan brjod pa'i skabs
NK115(re)001:19926: yin pas ma 'brel to snyams na lam dus su
NK115(re)001:19927: de ltar bsgoms pa las bar chad med lam mngon
NK115(re)001:19928: du gyur nas 'bras bu'i dus gzhi snang lhun grub
NK115(re)001:19929: rtags kyi 'og min dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med
NK115(re)001:19930: pa'i rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhing du mngon
NK115(re)001:19931: par sangs rgyas shing chos dbyings don gyi 'og min
NK115(re)001:19932: la sbyor ba'i cha nas skabs 'dir don gyi 'og
NK115(re)001:19933: min du smos pa yin par gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:19934: gsum pa de gnyis ka'i don bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:19935: de dag rang snang du bzhugs pa'i tshul chos sku'i
NK115(re)001:19936: ye shesa 'dus ma byas pa ngo bo nyid kyis
NK115(re)001:19937: rtag pa'i ngang las phyi ru gasla bar snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:19938: rang mdangsa phun sum tshogsa pa lnga dang ldana pa'i
NK115(re)001:19939: longsa skur rdzogas pa'i gansa rgyun gyi rtag pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:19940: khams su lhun gyis grub nas /
NK115(re)001:19941: sprul pa'i sku rgyun mi 'chad par rtag pa'i 'char
NK115(re)001:19942: gzhir bzhugs pa ni slob pa'i lam mthar phyin pa'i
NK115(re)001:19943: dus gang du khams la sgrib para byed pa'i dri
NK115(re)001:19944: ma matha'a daga pa spangsa par gyur pa'i sangas rgyas
NK115(re)001:19945: kho na'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa yi ye shes kyi
NK115(re)001:19946: rola pa gnas dang ston 'khor la sogs pa nyid
NK115(re)001:19947: du snang ba yin pa'i phyir rten zhing khams dang
NK115(re)001:19948: gzhal yas / brten pa gtso bo dang 'khora du
NK115(re)001:19949: snang yang phyi nang dang mchoga damna med de thams
NK115(re)001:19950: cad kun tu bzang po rang byung gi ye shes
NK115(re)001:19951: gcig gi rnam rol du mnyam zhing tha dad med
NK115(re)001:19952: gzhal yas / pa'i phyir te / dpal gsang ba'i
NK115(re)001:19953: snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi
NK115(re)001:19955: thabs las thabs byung thabs bsam yas //
NK115(re)001:19956: tha dad min las tha dad pa'i //
NK115(re)001:19957: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK115(re)001:19958: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes rol //
NK115(re)001:19959: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK115(re)001:19960: zhes pa'i tshig rkang snga ma sku gsum snang tshul la sbyar ro //
NK115(re)001:19961: de ltar longs sku gcig la sku gsum rdzogs pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:19962: sku gsum bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:19963: chos sku ni ngo bo nyid kyi rtag pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19964: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni rgyun gyi rtag pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19965: sprul pa'i sku ni rgyun mi 'chad pa'i rtag pa'o //
NK115(re)001:19967: de lta bu'i rang snang gi longs sku kuna gyi
NK115(re)001:19968: thugsa kyang chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos pas rnam
NK115(re)001:19970: gsung ni sgra tshig rang mtshan pa las 'das pas brjod pa dang bral ba dang /
NK115(re)001:19971: sku ni gzi brjid chen por snang bas matshana dang dpe byad gsal bar rdzogsa shing /
NK115(re)001:19972: rang snang gi chos thams cad ye shesa kyi mthonga
NK115(re)001:19973: ba daga pa'i spyan gyis gzugs sku phan tshun gcig
NK115(re)001:19974: gisa gciga gzigas pa dus nam du yang sgrib pa
NK115(re)001:19975: meda de / dper na yongs grub chen po'i bskyed
NK115(re)001:19976: rim goms pa'i snang ba ni rang gi rig ngo
NK115(re)001:19977: la mngon sum yin yang snang bya snang byed med
NK115(re)001:19978: meda de / pa bzhin no // de lta bu'i
NK115(re)001:19979: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku de ni sangs rgyas las
NK115(re)001:19980: gzhan pa'i spyod yul min pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:19981: dus gsum du gshegs shing byon pa'i rgyal ba rnams
NK115(re)001:19982: kyi khams dang yon tan gyi spyod yul ni bla
NK115(re)001:19983: na ste / de'i gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:19984: dang srid pa 'khor bas ma bsdus pas dngos po
NK115(re)001:19985: rang mtshan pa med pa'i phyir rtag pa'i mthar ma
NK115(re)001:19986: na ste / lhung zhing / zhi ba mya ngan
NK115(re)001:19987: las 'das pa phyogs gcig pas ma bsdus pa'i phyir
NK115(re)001:19988: chad pa'i mthar ma lhung bas na ngag gi yul
NK115(re)001:19989: las 'das shing don dam pa'i mthar thug pa /
NK115(re)001:19990: rtog pas gzhal bya dang dpe dang tha snyad kyis
NK115(re)001:19991: mi mtshon pas sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar
NK115(re)001:19992: gyi daga pa'i semsa cana chena po byang sems 'phags
NK115(re)001:19993: pa rnams kyis kyang mthonga bar mi nus te /
NK115(re)001:19995: rgyal ba'i ye shesa bsam gyis mi khyab pa de
NK115(re)001:19996: dang 'agla ba'i khams kyi sgrib pa'i cha da dung
NK115(re)001:19997: yang ma spangas pa'i phyir na /
NK115(re)001:19998: rgyal ba rnams kyi ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK115(re)001:19999: pa'i yon tan mtha' dag la gzigs pa'i blo mig
NK115(re)001:20002: bla med ye shes thugs rje che sogs yon tan gyis //
NK115(re)001:20003: yon tan pha rol phyin pa'i rgyal ba bsam mi khyab //
NK115(re)001:20004: des na rang byung rnams kyi tha ma'i tshul 'di ni //
NK115(re)001:20005: drang srong chen po dbang thob rnams kyis kyang rig min /
NK115(re)001:20007: de yang 'adsa pa dang ma 'ongsa pa dang da
NK115(re)001:20008: lta ste 'dus byas kyi dus gsum kun rdzob pa
NK115(re)001:20009: kun gyi ngesa pa las 'adsa pa'i rang snang don
NK115(re)001:20010: gyi 'og mina chen po na rtag pa rgyun gyi
NK115(re)001:20011: 'khor lor bzhugs pa'i sangsa rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab
NK115(re)001:20012: pa'i dus bzhi'i bdag nyid can gtso bo dang 'khora
NK115(re)001:20013: thams cad dgongs pa mnyam pa'i phyir ngo bo la
NK115(re)001:20014: bzang ngan dang tha dad med pa'i tshul gcig tu
NK115(re)001:20015: mthuna para shar ba'i rang snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:20016: de ltar yang gsang snying las /
NK115(re)001:20017: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK115(re)001:20018: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK115(re)001:20019: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK115(re)001:20020: 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK115(re)001:20021: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK115(re)001:20022: mthong nas nye bar brnyes pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20023: rgya chen gsung la don 'byung ba'am //
NK115(re)001:20024: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK115(re)001:20026: rgya chen gsung zhes pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20028: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung /
NK115(re)001:20029: longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung /
NK115(re)001:20030: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung /
NK115(re)001:20031: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK115(re)001:20032: mi 'gyur rdo rje'i dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK115(re)001:20033: gnyis pa sprul sku bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:20036: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20037: rang snang longs sku de nyid kyi ngang lasa dag
NK115(re)001:20038: pa dang ma dag pa'i gdul bya'i semsa can rnams
NK115(re)001:20039: 'dul ba'i phyir ston pa'i thugs rje las 'dula byed
NK115(re)001:20040: kyi ston pa gsum du rtsol ba med bzhin bkoda
NK115(re)001:20041: pa ni / longs sku dang tshul mthun par snang ba ranga bzhina sprul pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20042: 'gro drug gi ston par snang ba 'gro 'dula sprul pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20043: sems ldan dang bem po'i rigs su snang ba sna tshogas sprul pa ste gsum mo //
NK115(re)001:20044: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:20048: dang po rang bzhin sprul pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:20049: bgrangs pa'i rang bzhin sprul pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20050: gnas pa'i rang bzhin sprul pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20051: dang po bgrangs pa'i rang bzhin sprul pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:20055: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20056: sprul pa'i sku rnam pa gsum du snang ba de
NK115(re)001:20057: dag lasa dang po ranga bzhina sprul pa'i sku zhes
NK115(re)001:20058: bya ba ni / rgyal ba chos kyi sku'i ye
NK115(re)001:20059: shesa phyir gsal du snang ba 'oga mina gyi zhing
NK115(re)001:20060: na dbyingas snanga longas spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i rnam par
NK115(re)001:20061: bzhugs pa'i dpe byad ni dwangsa shel gyi nang du
NK115(re)001:20062: 'phosa pa ste shar ba lta bu'i rgyal sras 'phags
NK115(re)001:20063: pa gdul bya mchog rnams la snang ba'i gzugs brnyan
NK115(re)001:20064: ni rang snang gi ston pa dang cha 'dra bas
NK115(re)001:20066: gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus pas sprul pa'i phyogs su yang bgrangs pas phyed sprul longas sku'i gansa te /
NK115(re)001:20067: rang snang gi zhing dang ston pa nam mkha'i zla
NK115(re)001:20068: ba dngos lta bu las gzhan snang gi zhing dang
NK115(re)001:20069: ston pa chu zla ltar gzugs brnyan du shar ba'i
NK115(re)001:20071: ji ltar sprin med nam mkha'i zla ba'i gzugs //
NK115(re)001:20072: ston ka'i chu sngon mtshor ni mthong ba ltar //
NK115(re)001:20073: de bzhin rgyal sras tshogs kyis khyab bdag gzugs //
NK115(re)001:20074: rdzogs sangs dkyil 'khor nang du mthong bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:20076: de yang nye ba'i 'khor gdul bya rgyud dag pa rnams la gzhan snang longs sku dang /
NK115(re)001:20077: ring ba'i 'khor rgyud cung zad dag kyang 'phags sa
NK115(re)001:20078: sogs ma thob pa rnams la mchog gi sprul sku
NK115(re)001:20081: mthong na tshim byed yon tan gang //
NK115(re)001:20082: sum cu rtsa gnyis zhes bya ba //
NK115(re)001:20083: sprul pa chos la rdzogs par ni //
NK115(re)001:20084: longs spyod rdzogs sku gnyis la brten //
NK115(re)001:20085: dag las nye dang ring rnams la //
NK115(re)001:20087: chu dang nam mkhar zla gzugs bzhin //
NK115(re)001:20088: de mthong ba ni rnam pa gnyis //
NK115(re)001:20090: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la drug ste /
NK115(re)001:20098: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i 'bras chos lnga
NK115(re)001:20099: dang ye shes lnga'i rtsal las sar gnas kyi sems
NK115(re)001:20100: dpa' rnams kyi ngor zhing khams lnga bkod pa ni
NK115(re)001:20101: / dbus na sku chos dbyings ye shes kyi rtsal
NK115(re)001:20102: las dbang phyug chen po'i 'og mina gyi zhing dang
NK115(re)001:20103: / / shara na thugs me long ye shes kyi rtsal las mngona para dag'a ba'i zhing dang /
NK115(re)001:20104: lho na yon tan mnyam nyid ye shes kyi rtsal las dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing dang /
NK115(re)001:20105: nub na gsung sor rtog ye shes kyi rtsal las pad+ma brtsegsa pa'i zhing dang /
NK115(re)001:20106: byang na phrin las bya ba grub pa'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:20107: kyi rtsal las lasa raba grub pa'i zhing dang rnam
NK115(re)001:20108: pa lngar snang ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:20110: zhing khams lnga po der rim pa bzhin /
NK115(re)001:20111: gzugsa kyi rgyal po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK115(re)001:20112: la sogas pa'i khongs nas rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po mi bskyod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20113: tshor ba'i rgyal po rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK115(re)001:20114: 'du shes kyi rgyal po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK115(re)001:20115: 'du byed kyi rgyal po don yod grub pa ste /
NK115(re)001:20116: ston pa mchoga lnga po matshana dang dpe byad sogs
NK115(re)001:20117: yona tan rgya mtsho lta bu'i bdag nyid can du
NK115(re)001:20118: sar gnas rnams la snang ngo //
NK115(re)001:20119: de la gzugs kyi rgyal po zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20120: dper na mya ngan las 'das pa chen po zhes brjod na mya ngan ni 'khor ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:20121: de las 'das pa la myang 'das zhes brjod cing /
NK115(re)001:20122: de yang mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pas chen po zhes brjod pa bzhin du /
NK115(re)001:20123: gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga po las 'das
NK115(re)001:20124: shing de dag gi pha rol tu son yang 'bras
NK115(re)001:20125: chos lnga'i rtsal 'gag pa med par snang ba'i sku
NK115(re)001:20126: sogs la gzugs kyi rgyal po la sogs par brjod
NK115(re)001:20127: pas na / de dag rtags kyi phyag rgyar shar ba'i rang snang dang /
NK115(re)001:20128: gzhan snang gi ston pa lnga po la'ang de dang de'i ming gis btags pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20129: kun mkhyen chen po ni rnam par shes pa'i rgyal
NK115(re)001:20130: po rnam par snang mdzad ces thun min gyi rgyud
NK115(re)001:20131: sder 'grel to // de yang rang snang gi gzugs
NK115(re)001:20132: sku bkod pa dang tshul mthun par gzhan snang du
NK115(re)001:20133: yang zhi ba dang khro bo la sogs pa'i rnam
NK115(re)001:20134: 'gyur dapaga tu meda cing mtha' yas par snang ngo
NK115(re)001:20135: sder 'grel to // // gsum pa ye shes ni /
NK115(re)001:20136: de ltar zhing khams lngar ston pa lnga so sor
NK115(re)001:20137: snang yang rgyud tha dad pa ma yin par sangs
NK115(re)001:20138: rgyas kyi ye shes gcig gi rnam rol du shar
NK115(re)001:20139: ba'i rigs lnga'i thugs ye shesa rnam pa lnga po
NK115(re)001:20140: re re la'ang 'di ltar rnam snang gi thugs chos
NK115(re)001:20141: kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la /
NK115(re)001:20142: chos dbyings ye shes kyi me long lta bu'i ye shes sogs bzhi yod pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:20143: gzhan me long lta bu'i ye shes la'ang /
NK115(re)001:20144: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi chos dbyings ye
NK115(re)001:20145: shes sogs bzhi dang ldan pas mtshon lhag ma rnams
NK115(re)001:20146: la yang bzhi bzhi'i 'khora dang bacasa pasa ye shes
NK115(re)001:20147: nyi shu rtsa lngar 'gyur yang rtsa ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:20148: lnga po la 'du bas na de dag gi don
NK115(re)001:20149: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i mdo las byung ba ltar bshad
NK115(re)001:20150: pa la / ye shes dang po ni /
NK115(re)001:20151: chosa kyi dbyingsa ni chos thams cad la chos nyid
NK115(re)001:20152: du khyab kyang rang gi ngo bo tha dad pa
NK115(re)001:20153: med pa ltar de mkhyen pa'i ye shesa kyang chos
NK115(re)001:20154: nyid de'i rjes su song bas g.yo ba med pa
NK115(re)001:20155: ni nama mkha'i rang bzhin gzugsa su gyur pa thams
NK115(re)001:20156: cad na yod kyang rang gi ngo bo du ma
NK115(re)001:20157: med par ro gcig pa bzhina shesa bya'i thams cad
NK115(re)001:20158: chos nyid mkhyen yang brjod pa'i matha'a lasa 'adsa pa'i
NK115(re)001:20161: dper na me long gi ngos la gzugs brnyan 'char
NK115(re)001:20162: rung gi dwangs yod kyang de la rtsol ba dang
NK115(re)001:20163: mngon par 'du bya ba med pa bzhin mkhyen cha
NK115(re)001:20164: 'gag pa med pa'i ye shesa gzung 'dzina gyi rdul
NK115(re)001:20165: dang bral ba ni mngona par 'du byed pa'i g.yo
NK115(re)001:20166: rtsol med bzhina shes bya mkhyen tshul gyi ldog pas
NK115(re)001:20167: dbye ba'i ye shes phyi ma gsum po mcheda pa'i
NK115(re)001:20170: me long ye shes mi g.yo ste //
NK115(re)001:20171: ye shes gsum ni de la brten //
NK115(re)001:20172: mnyam pa nyid dang so sor rtog /
NK115(re)001:20173: bya ba grub pa kho na'o //
NK115(re)001:20176: chos thams cad la bzang ngan dang tha dad la
NK115(re)001:20177: sogs pa'i mtshan ma med pa ni mnyam pa nyid
NK115(re)001:20179: de mkhyen pa'i ye shesa kyis kyang 'khor 'das kyi
NK115(re)001:20180: chosa kun bzang ngan dang blang dor gyi matshana nyida
NK115(re)001:20181: med par srid zhi dbyer med spros pa'i mtha' thams
NK115(re)001:20182: cad zhi ba'i dbyingsa su thugs zhugsa pa'i tshul gyis
NK115(re)001:20183: mkhyen pa ste / de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:20184: mi gnas zhi bar zhugs pa ni //
NK115(re)001:20185: mnyam nyid ye shes chen por 'dod //
NK115(re)001:20188: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung bas bsdus pa'i shes bya'i
NK115(re)001:20189: chos thams cad kyi snang cha rgyu dang 'bras bu
NK115(re)001:20190: sogs ma 'dres par snang ba ni so sora rtog
NK115(re)001:20191: pa yin la / de mkhyen pa'i ye shesa kyis
NK115(re)001:20192: kyang chosa nyid ji lta ba bdag med pa dang
NK115(re)001:20193: pa yin la / // chosa can shesa bya phung
NK115(re)001:20194: sogs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyi chos ji snyed
NK115(re)001:20195: pa thams cad rtag tu thogas pa med par mkhyen
NK115(re)001:20196: pa yin la / // pa ste / de nyid las /
NK115(re)001:20197: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni //
NK115(re)001:20198: shes bya kun la rtag mi thogs //
NK115(re)001:20199: ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs rnams kyi //
NK115(re)001:20200: gter dag 'dra ba kho na yin //
NK115(re)001:20203: bya ba ni gzhan don gyi mdzad pa yin la
NK115(re)001:20204: de rtsol med du gruba cing mkhyen pa'i ye shesa
NK115(re)001:20205: kyis lhun gyis grub pa'i phrina lasa gazhana ngor snang
NK115(re)001:20206: ste so so'i mos pa dang 'tshams par sku gsung
NK115(re)001:20207: thugs kyi rnam par 'phrul pa sna tshogs pas gnas
NK115(re)001:20208: skabs dang mthar thug gi phana pa rlabs chen po
NK115(re)001:20209: bsgrub pa'i tshul cana du chagas pa dang thogas pa
NK115(re)001:20210: spangas pa'i madzada pa lhun gyisa gruba par 'khor ba
NK115(re)001:20211: ma stongs kyi bar du 'jug pa ste /
NK115(re)001:20213: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni //
NK115(re)001:20214: khams rnams kun tu sna tshogs shing //
NK115(re)001:20215: dpag med bsam yas sprul pa yis //
NK115(re)001:20216: sems can kun don bsgrub pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20218: ye shes de rnams gnyis su bsdu na /
NK115(re)001:20219: chos dbyings ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin la /
NK115(re)001:20220: gzhan bzhi ka ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes te /
NK115(re)001:20221: de yang mkhyen cha 'gag pa med pa las shes bya'i yul la ye shes 'jug pa na /
NK115(re)001:20222: mnyam nyid blang dor dang bral bar mkhyen pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20224: 'bad med du mkhyen pa'i ldog pa bzhis phye'o //
NK115(re)001:20225: de ltar na 'dir sor rtog ye shes kyi skabs
NK115(re)001:20226: su chos nyid ji lta dang zhes pa chos can
NK115(re)001:20227: ma 'dres par mkhyen pa na de'i rang bzhin bdag
NK115(re)001:20228: gi ngo bor ma grub bzhin du snang ba mkhyen
NK115(re)001:20229: pa la bshad na bade'am snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:20231: ston pa rang las rgyud gzhan gyis bsdus pa'i 'khora
NK115(re)001:20232: ni sa dang po rab dga' nas chos kyi sprin
NK115(re)001:20233: gyi bar la gnas pa'i sa bcu'i byanga chub semas
NK115(re)001:20234: dpa' 'ab'a zhiga dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs pa la
NK115(re)001:20235: chos phun sum tshogs pa sku yisa theg pa chen
NK115(re)001:20236: po'i chosa rnamas kyi don gdul bya'i blo la 'ajala
NK115(re)001:20237: ba'i thabs kyi 'oda zer bkye basa chos kyi longs
NK115(re)001:20238: spyod kyi dga' bde la nye bar spyod pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:20240: byang chub sems dpa' sa chen po la bzhugs pa
NK115(re)001:20241: rnams dang thabs gcig tu theg pa chen po'i chos
NK115(re)001:20242: kyi longs spyod kyi dga' ba dang bde ba shin
NK115(re)001:20243: tu kha na ma tho ba med pa la nye
NK115(re)001:20244: bar spyod pa'i phyir sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK115(re)001:20245: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin no zhes so //
NK115(re)001:20246: de'i tshul sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs kyi 'di ltar rang
NK115(re)001:20247: gi byad kyi dri ma rang gis mi mthong ba
NK115(re)001:20248: de me longa gi nanga du gsal nas sbyong ba
NK115(re)001:20249: ltar / sar gnas kyi byang sems des sprul pa'i
NK115(re)001:20250: longs sku la bltas pas rang gi sa la sgrib
NK115(re)001:20251: pa yod pa ngos zin pas da dung byang sems
NK115(re)001:20252: badga dang ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i khyad
NK115(re)001:20253: par ji ltar yin mthonga nasa /
NK115(re)001:20254: byanga chuba chen po'i 'bras bu la sgriba para byed
NK115(re)001:20255: pa'i dri ma gting dapaga daka'a ba ste shin tu
NK115(re)001:20256: phra ba ngos zin dka' ba daga rim gyis sbyangas
NK115(re)001:20257: te / de yang sa dang por ser sna /
NK115(re)001:20263: bdun par thabs la mi mkhas pa /
NK115(re)001:20264: brgyad par gzhan don gyi snying stobs la sgrib pa /
NK115(re)001:20265: dgu par smon pa'i don la g.yel ba /
NK115(re)001:20266: bcu par ye shes kyi sgrub pa phra mo dang
NK115(re)001:20267: bcas pa dag nasa bcu gciga kuna tu 'oda la
NK115(re)001:20268: 'gro ba ste mngon par byang chub pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:20270: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK115(re)001:20271: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK115(re)001:20272: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK115(re)001:20273: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK115(re)001:20274: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK115(re)001:20275: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK115(re)001:20276: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK115(re)001:20277: 'khor gyis de bzhin sku bltas na //
NK115(re)001:20278: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag med //
NK115(re)001:20279: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK115(re)001:20280: de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byang //
NK115(re)001:20281: bla med byang chub yang dag 'thob //
NK115(re)001:20284: gzugs brnyan longs sku'i ston pa de ji tsam snang
NK115(re)001:20285: ba'i dusa ni 'di ltar 'khor sa bcu'i dabnga phyuga
NK115(re)001:20286: byang chub sems dpa' chena po rnamas 'jiga rten mgona
NK115(re)001:20287: po ston pa bde bar gshegs pa'i chos kyi sku
NK115(re)001:20288: ngo bo nyid med pa'i dbyingsa mi zada pa rgyan
NK115(re)001:20289: gyi 'khora lo sku gsunga thugsa kyi nganga du ston
NK115(re)001:20290: 'khora dgongsa pa gcig tu ma gyur gyi bar du
NK115(re)001:20291: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul mi ston pas 'chi
NK115(re)001:20292: ba'i bduda bcoma zhing dag pa'i 'jiga rten byang chub
NK115(re)001:20293: sems dpa' rnams la theg pa chen po'i yon tan
NK115(re)001:20294: gyi 'byor ba khyad par can bsgrub pa'i slad du
NK115(re)001:20295: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor bzhugs pa yin te
NK115(re)001:20297: chos kyi dbang phyug 'chi ba'i bdud bcom dang //
NK115(re)001:20298: ngo bo med phyir 'jig rten mgon po rtag /
NK115(re)001:20300: drug pa sbyang bya'i khyad par ni /
NK115(re)001:20301: spang gnyen chos mtshungs pa'i zhing dang ston pa la sogs pas sbyangs te /
NK115(re)001:20302: de la gdul bya'i rgyud kyi gti muga la sogsa
NK115(re)001:20303: pa'i sbyang bya'i dri ma nyona mongsa pa bag la
NK115(re)001:20304: nyal lnga po ganga gi gnyen pora che ba'i 'og
NK115(re)001:20305: min la sogs pa'i zhing khamas lnga dang /
NK115(re)001:20306: gdul bya de'i ngor zhing der ston para bstan pa'i
NK115(re)001:20307: sku rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa lngasa chos
NK115(re)001:20308: dbyings ye shes la sogs pa sgra tshig gi tha
NK115(re)001:20309: snyad las 'das pa'i chosa raba lnga bstan pas gti
NK115(re)001:20310: mug gansa 'gyur ba chos dbyings ye shesa sogs rnama
NK115(re)001:20311: pa lnga po thob pa'i tshul yanga /
NK115(re)001:20313: 'dod chags la sogs nyon mongs lnga //
NK115(re)001:20314: rnam dag ye shes lngar bshad do //
NK115(re)001:20316: 'di la gti mug gi dri ma sbyong dus bcom
NK115(re)001:20317: ldan 'das gzugs kyi rgyal po las chos dbyings ye
NK115(re)001:20318: shes / de bzhin du zhe sdang la rnam par shes pa'i rgyal pos me long ye shes /
NK115(re)001:20319: nga rgyal la tshor ba'i rgyal pos mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK115(re)001:20320: 'dod chags la 'du shes kyi rgyal pos sor rtog ye shes /
NK115(re)001:20321: phrag dog la 'du byed kyi rgyal pos bya grub
NK115(re)001:20322: ye shes kyi chos rab lnga bstan pas gnas 'gyur
NK115(re)001:20323: lnga thob pa yin par gsungs pa 'di'i don la
NK115(re)001:20324: bsam na / dang po byang chub sems dpa' sbyor
NK115(re)001:20325: lam gyi mthar gnas pa zhig gis mchog gi sprul
NK115(re)001:20326: sku las gdams ngag dngos su thos pa de rnam
NK115(re)001:20327: par snang mdzad kyis chos dbyings ye shes las brtsam
NK115(re)001:20328: pa'i chos thos pa'i don yin pas gnas 'gyur gyi
NK115(re)001:20329: ye shes kyang chos dbyings ye shes kyi ngo bo
NK115(re)001:20330: mthong lam thob pa'i rgyu yin kyang da dung rang
NK115(re)001:20331: gi ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnam par
NK115(re)001:20332: snang mdzad dngos su mi mthong ba ni mthong spang
NK115(re)001:20333: shes sgrib kyi cha ma spangs pas yin la /
NK115(re)001:20334: nam mthong spangs de spangs pa na rang gi ston pa de mthong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20335: de bzhin du sa 'og ma rang rang gi skabs
NK115(re)001:20336: su mjal ba'i ston pa las chos kyi don khong
NK115(re)001:20337: du chud pa des rang rang gi sgrib pa'i gnyen
NK115(re)001:20338: por gyur pa'i ston pa de'i gsung thos pa dang
NK115(re)001:20339: 'dra ba'i byed las su song yang da dung rang
NK115(re)001:20340: sa'i shes sgrib rnam par dag ma zin gyi bar
NK115(re)001:20341: du sa de'i gnyen por gyur pa'i rang gi ston
NK115(re)001:20342: pa dngos rin 'byung sogs mthong bar mi 'gyur ba'i
NK115(re)001:20344: 'di'i 'grel pa rnam mkhyen shing rta dang theg mchog mdzod sogs na bgrangs pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20345: pha rol tu phyin pas bcu gcig kun tu 'od
NK115(re)001:20346: kyi sar 'dod de sangs rgyas kyi snang ba khyad
NK115(re)001:20348: 'dir sangs rgyas kyi gsung ni thos la /
NK115(re)001:20349: rang gi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la shes bya'i sgrib pas bsgribs nas sku mi mthong ste /
NK115(re)001:20350: de dag gi sku nam mthong ba na shes bya'i
NK115(re)001:20351: sgrib pa zad nas sangs rgya bar 'dod pa'o zhes
NK115(re)001:20352: gsungs pa'i phyir te don 'di la'ang blo ldan rnams
NK115(re)001:20353: kyis da dung dpyod par mdzod cig /
NK115(re)001:20354: de ltar lnga tshan lnga yang sa bcu po dang sbyar nas gsungs pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:20355: mthonga lam gyi dus su kun brtags las gyur pa'i gti mug gnas gyur /
NK115(re)001:20356: kun gzhi dbyings su nub pa chos dbyings ye shes
NK115(re)001:20357: kyi ngo bo sa dang po rab tu dga' ba
NK115(re)001:20359: de nasa bzunga rim pa bzhan du 'phags pa'i bsgom lam chung ngu gsum du nga rgyal gnas gyur /
NK115(re)001:20360: yid kyi rnam shes dbyings su nub pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes brnyes /
NK115(re)001:20365: 'bring po gsum du rnam pa thams cad pa'i chags rtog gnas gyur /
NK115(re)001:20366: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dbyings su nub pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thob /
NK115(re)001:20371: chen po gsum las sa brgyad pa la zhe sdang gi sa bon rtog pa'i zug rngu dang /
NK115(re)001:20372: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa gnas gyur /
NK115(re)001:20373: me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:20374: kyi 'char gzhir gyur kyang rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK115(re)001:20375: bdag nyid thob / mi bskyod pa mthong /
NK115(re)001:20376: sa dgu pa dang bcu par phrag dog gi sa bon dag /
NK115(re)001:20377: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa dbyings su nub nas
NK115(re)001:20378: so so yang dag rig pa bzhis 'gro ba rgya
NK115(re)001:20379: mtsho'i don byed pa'i phrin las rlabs po che'i bdag
NK115(re)001:20380: nyid bya ba grub pa'i ye shes thob /
NK115(re)001:20381: don yod grub pa'i sku mthong /
NK115(re)001:20382: de ltar sa bcu pa'i rgyun matha'i bar sgom lam
NK115(re)001:20383: sa dgu po rima gyis rdzogas pa na bcu pa'i
NK115(re)001:20384: byang chub sems dpa' de la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:20385: thams cad kyis 'od zer chen pos dbang bskur ba'i
NK115(re)001:20386: mod la rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK115(re)001:20387: sogs pa'i yon tan brjod du med pa snyed thob
NK115(re)001:20388: pa'i tshul / mdo sde'i rgyan las /
NK115(re)001:20389: bsgom pa tha ma rdzogs nas ni //
NK115(re)001:20390: 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur ba //
NK115(re)001:20391: zhes pa'i don sa bcu pa'i mdo la sogs pa las shes par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:20392: de'i tshe rang la yod pa'i lhun grub kyi yon
NK115(re)001:20393: tan ci yin pa mngon du gyur nas spangs rtogs
NK115(re)001:20394: kyi yon tan yongs su rdzogas pa'i byang chub snying
NK115(re)001:20395: pora 'gro ba ste dbyings kyi 'og min du 'tshang
NK115(re)001:20396: rgya ba'i tshul / sgyu 'phrul mngon byang las /
NK115(re)001:20397: dag sa pa yi dbang nyid phyir //
NK115(re)001:20398: ston pa lnga dang chos rab lnga //
NK115(re)001:20399: ye shes lnga yongs rdzogs pa las //
NK115(re)001:20400: rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK115(re)001:20402: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK115(re)001:20403: de lta bu'i zhing khams la phyed sprul du gdags
NK115(re)001:20404: pa'i 'thad pa yang 'dir bshad pa'i zhing khams lnga
NK115(re)001:20405: po 'di ni sa bcu'i byang chub semas dapa'a rnams
NK115(re)001:20406: kho na la snang ba lasa so skye dang nyan
NK115(re)001:20407: thos 'phags pa la sogs pa'i gdul bya gazhana gyi
NK115(re)001:20408: spyod pa'i yula du dngos su snang ba min zhing
NK115(re)001:20409: / de bzhina du ston pa lnga po dbyings kyi
NK115(re)001:20410: longas spyod rdzogsa pa'i sku ltar snang na yanga 'khora
NK115(re)001:20411: dang zhing khams la sogas pa ston pa'i thugs rig
NK115(re)001:20412: pa'i ye shes kyi ranga snang thun mong ma yina
NK115(re)001:20413: pa kho na min te rgyud gzhan pa byang sems
NK115(re)001:20414: sar gnas rnams kyi sems dag pa'i snang bas bsdus
NK115(re)001:20415: pa yin pa'i phyir phyed snanga ranga bzhina sprul pa'i
NK115(re)001:20416: zhing zhesa nyi zla kha sbyor chena po'i rgyud kyis
NK115(re)001:20418: de dag ni pha rol tu phyin pa'i sa lam gyis bgrangs pa'i rang bzhin sprul pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20419: gnyis pa gnas pa'i rang bzhin sprul pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:20420: rang bzhin sprul pa dngos bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20421: zhar byung 'og min mkha' spyod kyi gnas bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20422: dang po rang bzhin sprul pa dngos bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:20423: phyogs bcu'i sprul pa'i zhing mdor bstan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20424: rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa lnga rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20425: dang po phyogs bcu'i sprul pa zhing mdor bstan pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20426: khyad para thun mong ma yin pa'i lam ranga bzhina
NK115(re)001:20427: rdzogas pa chena po yi gdams ngag dang phrad pa'i
NK115(re)001:20428: gang zag de ni dbang po tha ma yin yang
NK115(re)001:20429: sa thob pa'i nges pa sogs la ltos mi dgos
NK115(re)001:20430: par / da lta snying ga na yod pa'i rig
NK115(re)001:20431: gdangs ranga snang ye shesa kyi dkyil 'khora yid dpyod
NK115(re)001:20432: la ma ltos par mngon sum pa'i snang ba dama
NK115(re)001:20433: pa de ru bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs la sogs
NK115(re)001:20435: gnas lugs mchoga gi don gzigas pa'i bla ma dam
NK115(re)001:20436: pas thod rgal rig pa'i rtsal dabnga bskura te ngo
NK115(re)001:20437: sprad cing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20438: de'i srog dam tshig rnam par dag cing ma nyamsa la /
NK115(re)001:20439: nyin dusa su bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs kyi ranga snanga mngona suma zer gdangs kyi 'od gsal dang /
NK115(re)001:20440: matshana mo snyinga ga'i 'oda gadngas shes bya bum 'jug
NK115(re)001:20441: gi man ngag la gomas pa rnams kyis de ltar
NK115(re)001:20442: nyams su blangs kyang snang ba cher yang ma 'phel
NK115(re)001:20443: / rtogs pas chos zad ka dag gi dgongs pa
NK115(re)001:20444: ngo ma 'phrod pas rtogsa pa'i ranga bzhina tshad du
NK115(re)001:20446: mi dge ba'i 'jug pa srab ste rmi lam dge
NK115(re)001:20447: bar gyur ba'i gang zag skal ldan de chosa nyid
NK115(re)001:20448: bdena pa'i stobs kyis rang bzhin sprul par skye ste
NK115(re)001:20450: bden pa mthong ba'i sems can ni //
NK115(re)001:20451: rtogs pa rgyud la ma skyes kyang //
NK115(re)001:20452: phyogs bcu sprul pa'i zhing khams su //
NK115(re)001:20453: gnas ni mthar ni grol bar 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:20454: zhes gsungs pas dbang po tha ma'i tha ma de
NK115(re)001:20455: chos nyid kyi bar do shar yang bden pa'i stobs
NK115(re)001:20456: ma rnyed pas srid pa bar do rmi lam dang
NK115(re)001:20457: 'dra ba shar dus nga shi 'dug snyam du ngos
NK115(re)001:20458: zin / srid pa bar dor kha 'khyal ba de
NK115(re)001:20459: dran te bla ma yang dran de'i gdams pa yang
NK115(re)001:20460: zin / dran pa las / da ni rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:20461: sprul pa'i zhing du 'gro bar bya'o snyam pa tsam
NK115(re)001:20462: zin / dran pa las / las / sngar gyi
NK115(re)001:20463: chos nyid bden pa'i byin rlabs dang bla ma dam
NK115(re)001:20464: pa'i byin rlabas kyis srid pa bar do la rang
NK115(re)001:20465: gar 'dzin pa'i dri ma med pas srid pa phyi
NK115(re)001:20466: mar brgyud pa'i bag chags zad de sa thoba pa
NK115(re)001:20467: rnamas la rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing snang ba de
NK115(re)001:20468: dang skala ba mtshungsa par gyura nasa /
NK115(re)001:20469: rang la yod pa'i gzhi snanga lhuna gruba kyi sgor
NK115(re)001:20470: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes bkod pa'i phyogsa bcu sprul
NK115(re)001:20472: der pad+ma las rdzus te skad cig gis skyes nas dbugs 'byin te /
NK115(re)001:20473: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK115(re)001:20474: snyigs ma lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK115(re)001:20475: gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni mi yul snang //
NK115(re)001:20476: de rjes 'dzin pa'i gang zag skal ba can //
NK115(re)001:20477: snying po 'di ni su la snang gyur pa //
NK115(re)001:20478: de dag rnams ni mi 'gyur sa la 'da' //
NK115(re)001:20479: gal te snyigs ma tshe thung nad mang bas //
NK115(re)001:20480: snying po'i don 'di gdeng du ma gyur kyang //
NK115(re)001:20481: 'di nyid mthong bas dbugs chen nyid 'byin pa //
NK115(re)001:20482: bcu gcig kun tu 'od de sprul pa'i zhing //
NK115(re)001:20483: bardzusa skyes dag pas mngal gyi rgya dang bral //
NK115(re)001:20485: de ltar na zhing 'di dag tu skye ba'i gang zag ni /
NK115(re)001:20486: gdams pa 'di'i sgo mthong ba'i dbang po tha ma'i tha ma la'ang rigs gnyis las /
NK115(re)001:20487: yang tha ni mngon sum gyi sgo mthong yang yid ma ches pas nyams su ma blangs pa'am /
NK115(re)001:20488: yid ches kyang nyams su blang long skad cig kyang
NK115(re)001:20489: med par tshe 'dis g.yengs pa dag ni srid pa
NK115(re)001:20490: gzhan du brgyud par zangs yig can nas bshad la
NK115(re)001:20491: / sgo mthong nas nyams su len pa rnams kyis ni /
NK115(re)001:20492: sngar bshad pa'i nyin mtshan gyi man ngag bsgom dus /
NK115(re)001:20493: mtshan mo snying nang gi 'od lnga sprul pa'i zhing du blta ba'i ngang la nyal ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20494: thun bar 'pho bas rtsal sbyang ba ste yul sprul pa'i zhing der /
NK115(re)001:20495: ye shes snying nas tshangs bug gam mig nas gtso
NK115(re)001:20496: bo'i thugs kar rnam shes rlung zhon gyi gnad kyis
NK115(re)001:20497: 'phangs pas / bar do'i g.yang sa chod nas grong
NK115(re)001:20498: bzang po gcig nas gcig tu 'pho ba la nye
NK115(re)001:20499: zho med pa lta bu ste /
NK115(re)001:20500: de yang 'chi khar rlung phar song tshur ma 'dus
NK115(re)001:20501: pa'i skabs der dmigs pa gsal btab nas hig gis
NK115(re)001:20502: 'pho ba ni / nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NK115(re)001:20503: yul gnas dag la 'jug lugs ni //
NK115(re)001:20505: rnam shes rlung zhon dag la sbyangs //
NK115(re)001:20506: de yang gong du 'byongs pa gces //
NK115(re)001:20507: rig pa bsdu dang 'phang ba gces //
NK115(re)001:20510: de ltar byas pas kha cig de nyid du dag pa'i zhing du skye ba yang yod la /
NK115(re)001:20511: gal te srid pa bar do'i snang ba shar yang
NK115(re)001:20512: ngos zin par nges pas zhing de dran pa tsam
NK115(re)001:20513: gyis skye ba yin gyi gdams ngag gzhan gab pa
NK115(re)001:20514: ni ci yang med do gsungs //
NK115(re)001:20515: gnyis pa rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa lnga rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20516: spyir zhing bcu me ri 'bar ba dang bcu gcig yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:20517: khyad par du srid pa'i sdug bsngal las rnama par
NK115(re)001:20518: grola zhing gdod ma'i sa la dbugsa chena po 'byin
NK115(re)001:20519: para byed pa'i zhing khams lnga por bsdus te bstan
NK115(re)001:20520: pa ni / shara nasa rima pa bzhina du zhing khams bzhi yod de /
NK115(re)001:20521: de yang shar na mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams
NK115(re)001:20522: sa gzhi dang gzhal yas khang la sogs pa thams
NK115(re)001:20523: cad shel las grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20524: lho na dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing khams thams cad su war+na ste gser las grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20525: nub na pad+ma brtsegs pa'i zhing khams thams cad pada r+aaga ste pad+ma r+aa ga las grub pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20526: byang phyogs na rin chen rnam par bkod pa'am las
NK115(re)001:20527: rab grub pa'i zhing rin po che in+d+ra n+ai la'i
NK115(re)001:20528: rang bzhin las sa gzhi la sogs pa thams cad
NK115(re)001:20529: grub pa ste / gazhala meda khanga de dag kyang
NK115(re)001:20530: sgo 'khyamsa bzhi dang ldan pa'i steng rta babas kyis
NK115(re)001:20531: grub pa ste / brgyan pa / phyog bzhir snang
NK115(re)001:20532: byed ba langa gi miga lta bu las nyi ma
NK115(re)001:20533: shar ba na nang du 'od lnga'i snang ba 'char
NK115(re)001:20534: grub pa ste / brgyan pa / ba / byang du ni 'od ljang gu'i snang ba 'char ba /
NK115(re)001:20535: zura bzhira ni mu tig las grub pa'i mchoda rten bzhi yod do //
NK115(re)001:20536: de bzhi po'i bar na drila bu dang g.yera khasa
NK115(re)001:20537: sbrel ba'i dpyangas thaga rlunga gis bskyod pa'i sgra las
NK115(re)001:20538: rnama thara sgo gsuma dang ldana pa'i chosa kyi dbyangs
NK115(re)001:20540: phyogsa bzhira rlung gis bskyod pas dri zhim po sna
NK115(re)001:20541: tshogs 'byung bas sposa sprin g.yo ba'i dar sna tshogs
NK115(re)001:20542: kyi ba dana bzhi yod pa gzhal yas khang gi
NK115(re)001:20543: phyi rima na yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i rdzinga
NK115(re)001:20544: bu'i 'grama na / t+aa la'i ljona pa dri bzang
NK115(re)001:20545: po'i ngad dang ldan pa yal ga dang lo ma
NK115(re)001:20546: rnams la rin po che sna tshogs kyi dra phyed
NK115(re)001:20547: dang 'phyang 'phrul g.yo ba can mang pos brgyan pa
NK115(re)001:20548: bu'i 'grama na / / de'i phyi rol na matshe'u brgyad yod pa /
NK115(re)001:20549: de na bya'i rigs 'di lta ste /
NK115(re)001:20554: ne tso mi skada 'byin pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20560: lha'i bya drila bu'i sgra can dang /
NK115(re)001:20562: gsera gyi rdo rje'i gzugas cana kri ti pa la sogs te /
NK115(re)001:20564: byi ru ltar dmar ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20565: in+d+ra n+ai la ltar ljang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20566: dunga ltar dkar ba la sogs pa kha doga ma
NK115(re)001:20567: 'dres par phyed pa'i bya rigs sna tshogas pa rnams
NK115(re)001:20568: kyis skad snyan pa dang yid du 'ong ba sgroga
NK115(re)001:20569: cing mgrina pa'i rgyuda manga kuna tu 'khrol bas dga'
NK115(re)001:20571: zhing de dag na bzhugas pa'i byang chuba semas dapa'a
NK115(re)001:20572: rnamas kyang skye ba gcig gis thogs pa sha stag
NK115(re)001:20573: la / zas dang skom yang yid la dran pa tsam gyis tshim zhing /
NK115(re)001:20574: nyona mongas pa'i gnoda pa med la nad med pas mchog tu bde ba /
NK115(re)001:20575: byung srid na yang de zhi ba'i nusa pa dang
NK115(re)001:20576: ldan pa'i chu klunga la khrus byas pa sogs spyad
NK115(re)001:20577: pa tsam gyis sel zhing phyis 'du ba'i nada de
NK115(re)001:20579: gzhan yang gos rgyan sogs yid la ci dang ci bsam thams cad drana pa'i moda la 'byung zhing /
NK115(re)001:20580: mdor na zhing snga ma gsum suma cu rtsa gsuma pa'i lha dang longas spyod mnyam zhing /
NK115(re)001:20581: las rab grub pa ni gzugs khams kyi lha dang mnyam mo //
NK115(re)001:20582: phyi rima na rina chena sna bduna las grub pa'i lcags ri pha gu can yod do /
NK115(re)001:20583: de rnams kyi dbus na rin po che sna bdun
NK115(re)001:20584: las byas pa'i chos 'chad pa'i khri stan dang ldan
NK115(re)001:20585: pa yod do // zhing mchoga de rnams na rigas
NK115(re)001:20586: bzhi'i ston pa rdor sems rin 'byung snang mtha' don
NK115(re)001:20587: grub ste bzhi po yisa nyin mtshan gyi dusa bzhira
NK115(re)001:20588: dam pa'i chosa kyi sgra sgroga pa rgyun mi 'achada
NK115(re)001:20589: pa yod do // de / de yang rdo rje sems dpa' sogs ston pa gsum gyis /
NK115(re)001:20591: nam phyed na sngags phyi pa'i chos /
NK115(re)001:20592: tho rangs na sngags nang gi chos /
NK115(re)001:20593: nyin phyed na rdzogs pa chen po 'bras bu bla na med pa'i chos 'chad do //
NK115(re)001:20595: srod la gdams ngag gi chos /
NK115(re)001:20596: nam phyed na dbang gi chos /
NK115(re)001:20598: nyi ma phyed na lta sgom gyi chos ston to //
NK115(re)001:20599: zhing khams de dag kuna gyi dbus kyi bar snanga
NK115(re)001:20600: na he ru ka dapala chen po'i zhing dura khroda
NK115(re)001:20601: chen po me ri 'abra ba zhes bya ba yod
NK115(re)001:20602: de / de na gzhal yas khang 'di lta bu ste /
NK115(re)001:20604: thod pa skam pos 'bras bu byas pa /
NK115(re)001:20605: shar ri yod pas rtsig pa byas pa /
NK115(re)001:20606: b+han+d+ha lcang lo can gyis kha bad byas pa /
NK115(re)001:20607: rgya dang dpangs su dpag tu med de /
NK115(re)001:20608: gnam lcags kyi gzer btab pa /
NK115(re)001:20610: nyi zla'i ka gdan byas pa /
NK115(re)001:20611: chu srin kha'i ka gzhu byas pa /
NK115(re)001:20612: lha chen po brgyad gdung du bres pa /
NK115(re)001:20613: mchog chen pos grab btang ba /
NK115(re)001:20616: gzhal yas khang gi gru bzhi na /
NK115(re)001:20617: zhing chen gyi gdugs phub pa /
NK115(re)001:20618: lha mo lnga gar byed pa /
NK115(re)001:20619: sa gzhi thabs cad kyang rak+ta'i rba klong 'khrugs pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20620: gzhal yas khang de'i nang na ston pa sprul pa'i
NK115(re)001:20621: sku phyi ltar sh+aakya thub pa dang nang ltar rdo
NK115(re)001:20622: rje 'chang du snang ba nyid gsang ba ltar na
NK115(re)001:20623: gzhona nu dapa'a bo stobs ldan zhes bya ba'i bcoma
NK115(re)001:20624: ldan 'adsa thugs zhi ba las ma g.yos kyang /
NK115(re)001:20625: sku khro bo'i cha byad du bstan pa /
NK115(re)001:20626: lag na rdo rje la sogas pa'i dapa'a bo dang mkha' 'gro ma purna nye bar zhi ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20627: tshangs pa dung mgrin can dang /
NK115(re)001:20628: drang srong zla 'od gzhon nu dang /
NK115(re)001:20629: yang 'khor mkha' 'gro e ka tsa ti spun drug dang /
NK115(re)001:20630: de'i bran mo bcu bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:20631: g.yog mo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK115(re)001:20632: yang g.yog 'bum khri 'bum stong la sogs pa mkha'a 'gro'i sprina phunga 'phro ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20633: dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa mi'i 'khor dpag
NK115(re)001:20634: tu med pas bskor ba'i dbus nyida na 'brasa bu
NK115(re)001:20635: gsang sngags bla na meda pa'i chosa kyi 'khora lo
NK115(re)001:20636: bskora nas 'khor gyi rgyud grol bar mdzad do //
NK115(re)001:20637: zhing khams de rnams na pad+ma lasa rdzus te skyes
NK115(re)001:20638: pa'i rgyala srasa dapaga tu meda pa thams cad kuna
NK115(re)001:20639: kyanga lha dang lha mo dang /
NK115(re)001:20640: khye'u dang bu mo'i rnama pa sngags bla med kyi
NK115(re)001:20641: brtul zhugs mthar son pa'i dranga sronga dngos grub rnam
NK115(re)001:20642: pa gnyis gruba pa'i bdag nyid cana no //
NK115(re)001:20643: de rnams la gzung 'dzin gyi rnama para rtoga pa meda cinga bag chags 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:20644: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang /
NK115(re)001:20645: de dag ldan pa'i sgo lnga'i 'jug pa ste semsa gsuma kyang med la /
NK115(re)001:20646: 'khrul pa skyed byed kyi dpyod par byed pa'i yida
NK115(re)001:20647: druga dang ni rtsa ba'i nyona mongas pa druga kyang
NK115(re)001:20648: med cing / ma riga pa gsum med la rkyen
NK115(re)001:20649: bzhi yoda pa ma yina zhing de dang mtshungas para
NK115(re)001:20650: ldana pa'i sems sems byung rnamas kyanga meda do //
NK115(re)001:20651: zhing de dag ni ston pa bcom ldan 'das rdo
NK115(re)001:20652: rje 'achanga gi byin rlabas lasa ranga bzhina nyid du
NK115(re)001:20654: ranga bzhina ni sprula pa'i zhing zhesa rgyala ba'i srasa po rig pa 'dzin pa rnamas la gragas so //
NK115(re)001:20655: zhing lnga po de dag snang ba'i rgyu ni snying
NK115(re)001:20656: ga na me long lta bu la sogs pa ye
NK115(re)001:20657: shes rin po che rang gsal ba'i rang gdangs dang
NK115(re)001:20658: / dung khang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du ye
NK115(re)001:20659: nas bzhugs pa'i snang ba las shar ba yin pas
NK115(re)001:20660: na ranga bzhina rdzogas pa chena po'i mngon sum 'od
NK115(re)001:20661: gsal la goms pa'i gasnga lam du snang ba yin
NK115(re)001:20662: par riga pa ranga shara chena po'i rgyuda lasa bstan
NK115(re)001:20663: / pa yin no // 'di dag ni ye nas
NK115(re)001:20664: lam snang du gnas te gzhi snang lhun grub kyi
NK115(re)001:20665: sgo'i longs sku'i phyogs bzhi na snang bas gnas pa'i
NK115(re)001:20666: rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing zhes bya'o //
NK115(re)001:20667: de bas na 'khor la snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20668: dbang po tha mas mthong nus pa'i rgyu dang /
NK115(re)001:20669: grol nges pa'i rgyu yang de yin par rig par bya'o //
NK115(re)001:20670: gnyis pa zhar byung 'og min mkha' spyod kyi gnas bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20671: de dag las gazhana du de dang rnam pa mthun
NK115(re)001:20672: pa tsam du snang ba'i gnas gsang sngags thun mong
NK115(re)001:20673: ba rnams la grags pa zangs mdog dpal ri dang
NK115(re)001:20675: sham+b+ha la la sogs pa lta bu bde chena sngags
NK115(re)001:20676: la spyod pa rnams kyi rang snang dag pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:20677: ste / de yang yul nyer bzhi lta bu'i gnas
NK115(re)001:20678: kyis mtshon na nam mkha' nas 'ong ba'i lha dang
NK115(re)001:20679: dri za la sogs pas bzung ba'i gnas brgyad la
NK115(re)001:20680: mkha'a la spyod pa zhes grags pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20681: sa steng nas 'ong ba'i gnod sbyin dang srin po'i
NK115(re)001:20682: 'khor la sogs pas bzung ba'i gnas brgyad la sa
NK115(re)001:20684: yang klu dang ri rab kyi khong seng nas 'ong
NK115(re)001:20685: ba'i lha min la sogs pas bzung ba'i gnas brgyad
NK115(re)001:20686: la ni sa 'og la spyod pa zhesa gragas pa
NK115(re)001:20687: ste / de lta bu'i zhing de rnams su dona
NK115(re)001:20688: gyi 'oda gasla la dabnga thoba pa'i lhana cig skyes
NK115(re)001:20689: ma'i yes kyi d+aa k+ki ma dang /
NK115(re)001:20690: dang po nas yula chena po nyer bzhi po der gnas shing spyod pa'i zhing skyes ma dang /
NK115(re)001:20691: sngags kyi sgom spyod goms pa'i stobs kyis gnas de
NK115(re)001:20692: dag tu bgrod nus pa'i sngags skyes ma la sogas
NK115(re)001:20693: pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i dapa'a bo dang rnala 'byora
NK115(re)001:20694: ma rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyis bsod nams dang
NK115(re)001:20695: ye shes kyi stobs nus mthun par sad pa'i dbang
NK115(re)001:20696: gis rje btsun ma h+aa gu ru dang /
NK115(re)001:20697: gsang bdag lag na rdo rje la sogs pa'i tshom
NK115(re)001:20698: bu'i 'khor du lhan cig par tshogas pa de rnams
NK115(re)001:20699: dang skala ba mnyam pa'i tshogs gnyis nus pa mthu
NK115(re)001:20701: riga 'dzina du ma tshogs pa'i grala ganga yin pa
NK115(re)001:20702: de thams cad du song nas bskyed pa dang rdzogs
NK115(re)001:20703: pa'i lam gyi 'phro sbyong ba ste /
NK115(re)001:20704: de yang da lta rang rang la lam ston du
NK115(re)001:20705: gyur pa'i riga pa 'dzina pa yi rdo rje'i bla
NK115(re)001:20706: ma rnamas ni gnas dang zhing 'di na bzhugs dang
NK115(re)001:20707: 'di ru mi bzhugs zhes pa ni med de mos
NK115(re)001:20708: gus dag pa'i snang ngor rang nyid gang du song
NK115(re)001:20709: ba'i zhing der raba tu ste mngon sum du bzhugs
NK115(re)001:20710: pa'i drung nasa gsang sngagas kyi lta ba zab mo
NK115(re)001:20712: de la brten nas zhen med brtul zhugs kyi spyod
NK115(re)001:20713: pa rlabas po che la spyod nus pa'i mthu thob
NK115(re)001:20714: cing / rig 'dzin gyi bla ma dam pa de
NK115(re)001:20715: rnams kyi phrin las nye bar bsgrub pa'i phyir 'jig
NK115(re)001:20716: rten gyi khams sna tshogs pa rnams su rnam 'phrul
NK115(re)001:20717: gyi bkod pa du ma ston pas skal med log
NK115(re)001:20718: lta can bstan 'gro la 'tshe ba'i rigs rnams tshar
NK115(re)001:20719: cing / gcod pa dang / skal ldan gdul byar
NK115(re)001:20720: gyur pa rnams kyi don rang rang gi mos pa
NK115(re)001:20721: dang 'tshams par byed nus pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:20722: ji skad bshad pa'i zhing 'di daga ni ranga gi
NK115(re)001:20723: mos gus dang dag snanga la sogs pa dge ba'i
NK115(re)001:20724: sa bona mthu brtas pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20725: bskyed rim gyis rang snang dag par shar ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20726: rdzogas rim gyis rtsa thig rlung sems las su rung
NK115(re)001:20727: ba la sogs pa zaba mo'i brtula zhugas mathara sona
NK115(re)001:20728: pa'i gasnga sngagas kyi nus mthu rang dbang du gruba
NK115(re)001:20729: pa rnamas ni rang rang gi nye bar len pa'i
NK115(re)001:20731: sangs rgyas rnams kyi phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab
NK115(re)001:20732: pa'i mthus tshe 'dir yang mkha' spyod kyi grub mtha'
NK115(re)001:20733: snyogs nas lus ma bor bar zhing de dag tu
NK115(re)001:20734: bgrod nus pa yang yod la /
NK115(re)001:20735: 'chi ba'i tshe na zhing de dag gi dpa' bo dang mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs kyis /
NK115(re)001:20738: rol mo'i sprin phung gis bsu zhing /
NK115(re)001:20739: rig 'dzin gyi sa la mngon sum du bzhugs pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK115(re)001:20740: de la dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20742: go 'phang khyad par can la 'jog pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:20743: pa'i gnas khyad par can du snanga ba yin te
NK115(re)001:20745: sar bzhugs rnams la snang ba bzhin //
NK115(re)001:20746: rig pa 'dzin la khro bo'i zhing /
NK115(re)001:20747: mkha' spyod yon tan tshogs chen po //
NK115(re)001:20748: grub pa'i mtshan mas brgyan pa zhig /
NK115(re)001:20749: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por snang //
NK115(re)001:20751: de lasa gzhan du zhing de rnams snang ba'i rgyu
NK115(re)001:20752: bsod nams med bzhin rtog dpyod rang rgyud pas 'doda
NK115(re)001:20753: pa bskyed de dngos su 'gro ba'i bya ba can
NK115(re)001:20754: gyi sgo nas song na phyin tu yoda pa yi
NK115(re)001:20755: gnas risa su chada pa cana mthun snang du grub
NK115(re)001:20756: pa'i rang rgyud pa nyid du bsam par mi bya
NK115(re)001:20757: ste rang snang dag pa'i stobs las snang ba yin
NK115(re)001:20758: pa'i phyir na'o // de skad du'ang gsang snying las /
NK115(re)001:20759: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK115(re)001:20760: rin po che dang 'byung ba kun /
NK115(re)001:20761: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:20762: rang sems bsod nams brtan pa yin //
NK115(re)001:20763: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK115(re)001:20764: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK115(re)001:20765: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK115(re)001:20766: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK115(re)001:20768: gnyis pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:20770: de las yang sprul gyi rnam grangs /
NK115(re)001:20771: de nyid sgyu ma ltar snang tshul lo //
NK115(re)001:20772: dang po 'gro 'dul sprul pa dngos bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:20773: chos sku spros pa dang bral ba de nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:20774: nganga lasa rang snang ba'i longas spyod rdzogas pa yi
NK115(re)001:20775: sangs rgyas kyi sku'i gnas drug las yi ge phreng
NK115(re)001:20776: ba'i sprina gyi 'od zera raba tu 'phrosa pasa rigs
NK115(re)001:20777: drug gi 'jiga rten rnams su 'gro ba 'dula bar
NK115(re)001:20778: byed pa'i sprula pa'i sku mchoga snang ba'i tshul ni
NK115(re)001:20780: longs sku yab yum gyi ljags las /
NK115(re)001:20781: 'a chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i sgra /
NK115(re)001:20782: a gzung 'dzin gnyis snang dag pa'i sgra /
NK115(re)001:20783: ha chos nyid rang byung gi sgra /
NK115(re)001:20784: sha shes rab 'gag pa med pa'i sgra /
NK115(re)001:20785: sa chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i sgra /
NK115(re)001:20786: ma chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi sgra ste /
NK115(re)001:20787: yi ge drug pa'i 'khor los 'dzam bu'i gling bye
NK115(re)001:20788: ba phrag brgya la sogs pa'i 'jig rten drug gi
NK115(re)001:20790: phyed sprul te longs sku'i dkyil 'khor la snang ba rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK115(re)001:20791: thub pa drug ste 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK115(re)001:20792: so so'i snang ba dang mtshungs par bzo dang skye
NK115(re)001:20793: ba la sogs pa ma dag pa sprul pa'i sku
NK115(re)001:20794: dpag tu med pa 'phros nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK115(re)001:20795: / ces pa ltar mtho ris gsum dang ngan song gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:20796: gansa rigas druga gi gdula bya so so'i snanga ba la de dang 'tshams par sprul pa ston te /
NK115(re)001:20797: de yang 'gro ba drug po ranga ranga gi rgyal
NK115(re)001:20798: po la sogs pa'i minga gi mngona brjod lha dbang
NK115(re)001:20799: brgya byin la sogs pa lta bu skal pa dang
NK115(re)001:20800: mos pa'i rjesa su 'gro ba'i 'dula byed riga pa'i
NK115(re)001:20801: skyes bu thuba pa druga tu snang ba yin la
NK115(re)001:20802: / de dag las mi yi thub pa na mchog
NK115(re)001:20803: gi sprul sku mtshan dpes brgyan pa tshangs par spyod
NK115(re)001:20804: pa'i cha lugs can du snang ba yin zhing /
NK115(re)001:20805: lha la sogs pa gzhan rnams la ni rang rang
NK115(re)001:20806: gi rgyala po la sogs pa gang 'dul gyi gzugs
NK115(re)001:20807: su snang ba la de dang de'i thub par brjod
NK115(re)001:20808: kyi / mchog gi sprul pa'i sku'i rnam pa re re ste drug yod pa ma yin no //
NK115(re)001:20809: des na lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam bsnams
NK115(re)001:20810: pa sogs ni gsang sngags thabs la mkhas pas rigs
NK115(re)001:20811: bsdus te rnam dag sbyar ba'i bsgom tshul lo //
NK115(re)001:20812: de dag gi gdul yul 'gro ba'i bye brag phyogsa
NK115(re)001:20813: bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams grangs matha'a yasa shing mu
NK115(re)001:20814: zad pa meda pa'i stong gsuma gyi stong chen po
NK115(re)001:20815: yan man du rgya them brtsegs pa lta bu dang
NK115(re)001:20816: / phan tshun du za 'og kha phye ba lta
NK115(re)001:20817: bur tshad med par snang ba de snyed dang grangs
NK115(re)001:20818: mnyam para 'dul byed sprul pa'i sku yang raba tu
NK115(re)001:20819: sprul nasa gdula ba bzhi yi tshul gyis 'khor ba
NK115(re)001:20820: ma stongs kyi bar du 'gro ba'i dona bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:20821: mi khyab par mdzad pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:20822: de yang mchog sprul gcig gi gdul zhing stong gsum
NK115(re)001:20823: gcig yin la stong gsum po der 'dzam gling bye
NK115(re)001:20824: ba phrag brgya yod par mchog gi sprul sku yang
NK115(re)001:20825: bye ba phrag brgya snang nas mdzad pa ston pa
NK115(re)001:20826: yin zhing / lha la sogs pa'i gnas rnams la'ang
NK115(re)001:20827: rang rang 'dul byed kyi gzugs sna tshogs pa de
