NK115(re)001:20829: de ltar snang ba'i stong gsum gyi 'jig rten de
NK115(re)001:20830: yang rgya khyon 'di lta bu'i go na yod ces
NK115(re)001:20831: mtha' gcig tu nges pa yang med de /
NK115(re)001:20832: sems can gyi las snang bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20833: rten 'brel gyi snang tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20834: sangs rgyas kyi rnam pa 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir te /
NK115(re)001:20836: skra rtse'i khyon la 'gro ba lnga gnas te //
NK115(re)001:20837: sems can dmyal dang dud 'gro'i 'gro ba dang //
NK115(re)001:20838: gshin rje'i 'jig rten lha dang mi rnams gnas //
NK115(re)001:20839: 'dres pa med cing gnas par gyur pa med //
NK115(re)001:20841: de yi gnas su sangs rgyas rnams skye zhing //
NK115(re)001:20842: 'jig rten rig pa'i bstan pa 'bar ba snang //
NK115(re)001:20843: de yi gnas nyid na yang chos nub cing //
NK115(re)001:20844: 'dren pa mya ngan 'das pa'i sgra yang thos //
NK115(re)001:20845: mi dag bdag gi khyim na rmi lam bzhin //
NK115(re)001:20847: bdag cag gnas pa'i stong gsum 'di yang rnam snang
NK115(re)001:20848: gangs chen mtsho'i phyag na rdul phra rab gcig gi
NK115(re)001:20851: khab mig tsam gyi nam mkha' na'ang las mthun par
NK115(re)001:20852: bsags pa'i sems can snod bcud dang bcas pa grangs
NK115(re)001:20854: de thams cad du rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi gzigs pa 'jug pas don mdzad pa yin no //
NK115(re)001:20855: de ltar don mdzad yul gyi stong gsum yang phyi rol ba'i drang srong dang /
NK115(re)001:20858: sangs rgyas rnams kyi tshul gong nas gong du mang khyad zhugs par mthong ba yang /
NK115(re)001:20859: sangs rgyas kyi yul dang ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:20860: stong gsum gyi lha dang mi rnams ni ches nyung gis /
NK115(re)001:20861: phyi rol pa'i drang srong mngon par shes pa dang
NK115(re)001:20862: ldan pa gcig gis shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam gyi
NK115(re)001:20863: sa'i khyon la sems can mthong ba ni de bas
NK115(re)001:20864: ches mang ngo // de dag gis stong gsum du
NK115(re)001:20865: mthong ba bas ni nyan thos rnam par thar pa
NK115(re)001:20866: brgyad la bsam gtan pa'i gang zag gcig gis shing
NK115(re)001:20867: rta'i 'phang lo tsam gyi khyon la mthong ba ches
NK115(re)001:20868: ches mang ngo // mang ngo // de dag gis stong gsum du mthong ba bas ni /
NK115(re)001:20869: byang chub sems dpa' rnam par thar pa brgyad la
NK115(re)001:20870: bsam gtan pa gcig gis shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam
NK115(re)001:20871: la mthong ba ches mang ngo //
NK115(re)001:20872: de dag gis stong gsum du mthong ba bas ni /
NK115(re)001:20873: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan gyis shing rta'i 'phang lo
NK115(re)001:20874: tsam gyi sa'i khyon la gzigs pa ches mang ngo
NK115(re)001:20875: zhes so // de lta bu'i sems can tshad med
NK115(re)001:20876: pa de dag gi don ji ltar mdzad pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:20877: gdul ba rnam pa bzhi po de gang yin zhe
NK115(re)001:20878: zhes so // na / de yanga sku bsoda namas
NK115(re)001:20879: chena po'i stobs las byung ba'i mdzad pasa gdul bya
NK115(re)001:20881: sku yi rnam par 'phrul pa'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod kyang /
NK115(re)001:20882: gtso bo dga' ldan gyi gnas nas 'pho ba la
NK115(re)001:20883: sogs pa'i madzada pa chena po bcu gnyis sogs su
NK115(re)001:20884: ston pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa yin
NK115(re)001:20886: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bar /
NK115(re)001:20887: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK115(re)001:20888: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK115(re)001:20889: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK115(re)001:20890: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20891: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20892: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20893: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20894: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK115(re)001:20895: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK115(re)001:20896: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK115(re)001:20897: mya ngan 'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK115(re)001:20898: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK115(re)001:20899: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK115(re)001:20902: gsunga gi madzada pa gdul bya'i rna bar tshig sdeb sbyor legs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20903: tshangs pa'i dbyangs yan lag drug cu dang ldan par thos pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:20905: gsung ni tshig sbyor legs pa la //
NK115(re)001:20906: tshangs pa'i dbyangs ni yan lag drug /
NK115(re)001:20908: de lta bu'i gsung gis bstan pa'i theg pa'i rnam
NK115(re)001:20909: grangs ni nyan rang byang sems kyi thega pa gsuma
NK115(re)001:20910: mama / bla na med pa'i theg pa gciga ste
NK115(re)001:20911: sprul pa'i sku rnams kyis zhing la la na theg
NK115(re)001:20912: pa gsum gsang sngags dang bcas pa ston par mdzad
NK115(re)001:20913: mama / la / la la na mtshan nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:20914: theg pa gsum po ston la gsang sngags mi ston
NK115(re)001:20915: mama / la / pa dang / la la na theg pa chen po 'ba' zhig ston pa ste /
NK115(re)001:20916: gdul bya'i dbang gis tshul tha dad la /
NK115(re)001:20919: ji srid sems ni 'jig pa'i bar //
NK115(re)001:20920: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK115(re)001:20921: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK115(re)001:20922: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK115(re)001:20923: ces pa ltar gdul bya'i sems kyi 'jug pa yod
NK115(re)001:20924: pa de srid du ni de 'dul byed kyi theg
NK115(re)001:20925: pa'i grangs yang / gcig nas bcu drug gi bar dang /
NK115(re)001:20926: grangs med pa'i bar du yang dbyer yod la /
NK115(re)001:20927: sems kyi 'jug pa zhi ba na ni theg pa zhes pa'ang dmigs su med par gsungs so //
NK115(re)001:20928: de ltar bstan pa'i theg pa'i grangs dang chos kyi
NK115(re)001:20929: sgo ganga yanga gdul bya rnams kyi 'du shesa sna
NK115(re)001:20930: tshogs pa'i rjesa su 'gro ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:20931: semas cana gyi rgyud kyi nyona mongas dug gsum cha
NK115(re)001:20932: mnyam pa dang bcas pa re re la nyi khri
NK115(re)001:20933: chig stong rer phye ba'i grangs kyi gnyen pora dgongas
NK115(re)001:20935: sde snod gsum sngags dang bcas pa'i bzhi po re
NK115(re)001:20936: re la de snyed phye ba'i chosa kyi sgo 'aphara
NK115(re)001:20937: yang brgyad khri bzhi stong gi grangas su gsungas pa
NK115(re)001:20938: ltar snang yanga rnam par rtog pa'i kun slong gis
NK115(re)001:20939: bskyed pa'i lce mchus rtsol ba dang bcas pa las
NK115(re)001:20940: byung ba'i sgra tshiga ranga matshana pa ma yina par
NK115(re)001:20941: gdul bya'i semas cana gyi khamas la rgyal ba'i thugs
NK115(re)001:20942: rjes byina gyis barlabas pa'i mthusa so so'i rnama para
NK115(re)001:20943: riga pa nyid dang mthuna para shara ba yin te
NK115(re)001:20945: 'gro ba'i bsod nams las dag las //
NK115(re)001:20946: rgyal ba'i gsung dbyangs gcig snang ba //
NK115(re)001:20947: mos pa'i dbang gis so sor thos //
NK115(re)001:20950: thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK115(re)001:20951: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugas mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis
NK115(re)001:20952: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus dang 'dul byed kyi thabs
NK115(re)001:20953: sogs shes bya thams cad la mngon sum du dbang
NK115(re)001:20955: de yang dusa gsuma gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK115(re)001:20956: chags thogs med pa'i mkhyena cinga gzigas pa sngon gnas
NK115(re)001:20957: rjes dran gyi mngon shes dang /
NK115(re)001:20958: de ltar dusa gsum gyi dngos po thams cad ma
NK115(re)001:20959: 'dres pa gzigs kyang 'di ni 'das pa'i dus so
NK115(re)001:20960: zhes pa la sogs pa'i mtshan ma can du so
NK115(re)001:20962: dusa gsum skye ba meda pa'i dbyings su sgrib gnyis
NK115(re)001:20963: bag chags dang bcas pa zad pa'i dus bzhi mnyam
NK115(re)001:20964: pa nyid kyi ranga bzhina gdoda ma'i gansa skabsa kuna
NK115(re)001:20965: tu bazanga po'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan
NK115(re)001:20966: gyi 'khor lo spyod pa yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen
NK115(re)001:20967: pa zag zad mkhyen pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK115(re)001:20968: gazhana sems can mtha' yas pa kun gyi semas rnam par rtog pa'i rgyud dge ba dang /
NK115(re)001:20970: lung ma bstan pa la sogs pa'i rnam pa thams
NK115(re)001:20971: cad ma 'dres par dus gcig tu mkhyen pa gzhan
NK115(re)001:20972: sems mkhyen pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK115(re)001:20973: de bzhina du rdzu 'phrula chena po gang gis 'gro
NK115(re)001:20974: ba 'dul ba de ltar ston pa'i mngon shes kyis
NK115(re)001:20975: gdul bya'i mos pa dang mthun pa'i don spyod pa
NK115(re)001:20977: gzigs pa lha'i spyan gyis dag ma dag gi 'jig
NK115(re)001:20978: rten kun gyi sems can rnams 'di nas 'chi 'pho
NK115(re)001:20979: zhing 'dir skye'o zhes pa la sogs pa mkhyen pa
NK115(re)001:20980: lha'i mig gi mngon shes dang /
NK115(re)001:20981: gsan pa snyan gyi mngon shes kyis 'jig rten khams
NK115(re)001:20982: kyi sgra phra rags thams cad nye ring med par
NK115(re)001:20983: mkhyen pa lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes te drug dang
NK115(re)001:20984: / gzhan yang mkhyen pa'i stobs bcu la sogsa pa
NK115(re)001:20985: thugs kyi yon tan dpag tu med na'ang mdor bsdu
NK115(re)001:20986: na mngona par shesa pa druga po de rnams thugs
NK115(re)001:20987: kyi rjes su 'gro bas gdul bya rnams thabs gang
NK115(re)001:20988: gis dus nam 'dul ba'i dusa la bab pa na
NK115(re)001:20989: / / de lasa skad cig kyang yola ba med par don mdzad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:20990: phrina lasa bsam gyis mi khyab pas gdula bar mdzad pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:20991: gdul bya mtha' yas pa kuna tu sku mi zad
NK115(re)001:20992: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi
NK115(re)001:20993: khyab pa mtshan dang dpe byad du gsal ba dang
NK115(re)001:20994: / rang rang gi snang ba dang mthun pa'i gzugs tshangs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20996: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rnam par ston pa dang /
NK115(re)001:20997: zhing khams kyi bkod pa rnam snang gangs chen mtsho'i
NK115(re)001:20998: phyag gi pad+ma'i steng na zhing khams nyi shu rtsa
NK115(re)001:20999: lnga'i bkod pa yod par gsungs pa lta bu bkod
NK115(re)001:21000: pa'i bye brag mi 'dra ba mang po snang ba
NK115(re)001:21001: dang / kun tu thugsa kyi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:21002: mi khyab pa spangs pa dang rtogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:21005: ting nge 'dzin rgya mtsho'i rnam par rol pa mnga' brnyes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21006: de bzhina du sku gcig las kuna tu rang gi
NK115(re)001:21007: snang ba dang mthun par zhala gyi dkyil 'khor zhi
NK115(re)001:21008: ba dang khro bo la sogs pa'i rnam pa tha
NK115(re)001:21009: dad pa bstan nas de kho na la gzigs pa
NK115(re)001:21012: 'dzam bu'i gling gi sems can de dag gi bdag
NK115(re)001:21013: cag kho na'i mdun na bzhugs nas thugs brtse ba'i
NK115(re)001:21014: phyir chos ston to snyam mo //
NK115(re)001:21015: de bzhin du lus 'phags gling dang /
NK115(re)001:21016: ba lang spyod nas 'og min gyi bar du gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21019: res 'ga' gdon chen bgegs mdzad de //
NK115(re)001:21020: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK115(re)001:21023: gang gi rang bzhin chags sdang rnam bral yang //
NK115(re)001:21024: chags pa can la chags bcas ltar ston cing //
NK115(re)001:21025: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro la khror ston pa //
NK115(re)001:21026: thabs kyis rnam 'dren de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK115(re)001:21028: yang dus kuna tu gsunga gi gasnga ba bsam gyis
NK115(re)001:21029: mi khyab pa yan lag rgya mtshos 'gro drug so
NK115(re)001:21030: so'i skad kyis chos ston pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21031: brda'i gsung brda dang rnam 'gyur bstan pas don mdzad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21032: mdzad pa chen po'i gsung sems can gyi mos pa
NK115(re)001:21033: ltar gang la gang 'dul gyi chos kyi rnam grangs
NK115(re)001:21034: mang pos gdul bya'i rgyud 'grol bar mdzad pa'o //
NK115(re)001:21035: de ltar gdul ba bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa na /
NK115(re)001:21036: sku gsung thugas gsum gyis ni dngos su ste de
NK115(re)001:21037: yang thugs kyis gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs mkhyen pa
NK115(re)001:21038: bzhin sku mngon sum du bstan nas gsung gis de
NK115(re)001:21039: dang mtshams pa'i gdams ngag 'doms pas lam dang 'bras
NK115(re)001:21040: bu la dngosa su dgod pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i
NK115(re)001:21041: dona madzada la / phrina lasa kyis ni de ltar
NK115(re)001:21042: dngosa dang gzhan yang thabs tshul sna tshogs pas sgrib
NK115(re)001:21043: pa mdzad pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas lam gyi
NK115(re)001:21044: rten la 'god pa sogs brgyud nas kyang mdzad de
NK115(re)001:21045: dona madzada la / / mdor na dus kuna tu
NK115(re)001:21046: 'gro ba'i don la g.yel ba med par madzada pa
NK115(re)001:21047: lhun gyis grub cing rgyun mi 'chad par 'jug pa'o
NK115(re)001:21048: dona madzada la / / // de yang snga ma
NK115(re)001:21049: ni mi'i thub pa'i mdzad pa dang 'brel che la
NK115(re)001:21050: dona madzada la / / // / phyi ma ni
NK115(re)001:21051: lhag ma lnga po'i gdul ba gtso bor shes par
NK115(re)001:21053: ltar chos sku'i dbyingsa lasa gnam zla ltar snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:21054: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku las sprul pa'i sku mchoga
NK115(re)001:21055: chu zla ltar snang ba rnamas kyis /
NK115(re)001:21056: mkhyen bya chosa nyid la ltos nas ji lta ba'i
NK115(re)001:21057: ye shesa kyi zab mo don dam pa'i bden pa
NK115(re)001:21058: dang / chos can ji snyed pa la ltos nas
NK115(re)001:21059: rgya che ba gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rnam par bzhag
NK115(re)001:21060: pa la sogs pa kun rdzob kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:21061: ji snyed pa thams cad ma 'dres par so sor
NK115(re)001:21062: mkhyen pa yi ye shesa gnyis po de nyid kyis
NK115(re)001:21064: de yang brjod bya don dang ldan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21065: rjod byed ngag tshig dri ma med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21066: byed las nyon mongs nye bar spong ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21067: 'bras bu zhi ba'i phan yon ston pa ste khyad
NK115(re)001:21068: par bzhi dang ldan pas phyi rol pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:21069: pas bstan pa dang ma 'dresa shing thun mong du
NK115(re)001:21070: ma gyur pa'i chosa kyi tshula bzang po ston pa'i
NK115(re)001:21071: sgo nas te / rgyud bla ma las /
NK115(re)001:21072: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK115(re)001:21073: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs spong byed gsung //
NK115(re)001:21074: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par mdzad pa gang //
NK115(re)001:21075: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK115(re)001:21077: gnyis pa de las yang sprul gyi rnam grangs bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21078: 'gro 'dul gyi sprul pa de dag lasa yang sprul
NK115(re)001:21079: gyi rnama pa ni brjod kyis mi langa ba zhig
NK115(re)001:21080: yod de / 'gro ba'i khams kyi bye brag bsam
NK115(re)001:21081: gyis mi khyab pa ji snyed cig yod pa dang
NK115(re)001:21082: mnyam par sprul pa yang bsam gyis mi khyab bo
NK115(re)001:21083: yod de / // 'on kyang 'gro ba de thams
NK115(re)001:21084: cad rigs bsdu na gnas rigs druga tu 'du bas
NK115(re)001:21085: de dag gi gansa su rang rang gi rigas de
NK115(re)001:21086: snyed du rnam pa rang dang mthun par snang ba'i
NK115(re)001:21087: tshul rgyal chen rigs bzhi nas 'og min gyi bar
NK115(re)001:21088: lha rnamas 'dula bar byed pa'i sprul pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21091: bde 'byung ste khyab 'jug la sogas pa so so'i
NK115(re)001:21092: gnas rigs kyi gtso bos 'khor rnams kyi rgyud la
NK115(re)001:21093: sdig pa spong ba'i chos rang rang gi blo dang
NK115(re)001:21095: sdug bsngal sel bar byed la /
NK115(re)001:21096: de bzhin du mi rnams la snang tshul yang theg dman gyi rigs can rnams la nyan thos dang /
NK115(re)001:21098: theg chen gyi rigs can rnams la /
NK115(re)001:21100: dge bcu'i khrims kyis 'dul bar 'os pa'i dus su 'khora losa sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK115(re)001:21102: blon po la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21103: de bzhina du lha ma yin rnams la thagas bzang risa la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21104: bya rnams la shinga rta mo dang /
NK115(re)001:21105: rma bya'i rgyal po gser du snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21106: sreg pa la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21107: ri dwagas rnams kyi phyir du senga ge'i rgyal po yi dama brtan pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21110: mdora na dmyal ba dang yi dwagas kyi 'gro ba
NK115(re)001:21111: sogs sems can rnams ganga dang ganga gis 'dula bar
NK115(re)001:21112: byed pa de dang de 'dra ba'i gzugas su sprula
NK115(re)001:21113: nasa / semas can gyi dona mdzad pa la dus nama du yanga g.yela ba meda de /
NK115(re)001:21115: sangs rgyas rnams dang de yi sras //
NK115(re)001:21116: gang gis gdul bya de nyid la //
NK115(re)001:21117: de dang mthun pa'i gzugs ston to //
NK115(re)001:21119: de lta bu'i sprul pa'i rnam grangs 'di ni phyogs
NK115(re)001:21120: bcu'i 'jiga rten druga gi zhing rab 'byams rnamas su
NK115(re)001:21124: las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi dang yan lag gyi 'jig rten drug gi /
NK115(re)001:21125: zhes s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi sems can gnas pa'i snod kyi bye brag gru bzhi dang /
NK115(re)001:21130: steng g.yogs med pa ste drug go /
NK115(re)001:21131: s+n+rel gzhi sogs ni phal po che las /
NK115(re)001:21132: las kyi bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK115(re)001:21134: gshin rje'i 'jig rten s+n+rel gzhi ste //
NK115(re)001:21135: byol song lha min gyen du 'gro //
NK115(re)001:21137: de ltar 'jig rten drug gi 'gro ba de dag rang rang gis lasa bsags tshul dang /
NK115(re)001:21138: las des baga chagas bzhag pa smin tshul gyis ma nges pa sna tshogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21139: 'di ltar las gcig tu dge ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21140: gcig tu mi dge ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21141: dge sdiga 'dres ma dag byas pa'i rgyu las ni /
NK115(re)001:21142: 'brasa bu'i dus kyi gansa rigas kyang lha'i 'gro ba
NK115(re)001:21143: 'ga' zhig lta bu bde ba 'ba' zhig la spyod
NK115(re)001:21144: pa dang / dmyal ba'i sems can lta bu sduga bsngal kho na la spyod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21145: mi la sogs pa'i 'gro ba 'ga' zhig lta bu bde sdug 'dres ma la spyod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21146: gnas kyang lha mi sogs steng dang /
NK115(re)001:21147: ngan 'gro'i 'gro ba 'og ste mtho damna ltar med
NK115(re)001:21148: bzhin 'khrul ngor snanga ba'i gnas skabs na sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:21149: rnams kyi thugs rjes rnam par 'phrul pa yang tshad
NK115(re)001:21150: med par 'gro ba ranga rang gi snanga ba dang
NK115(re)001:21151: mthuna pa'i ston par bstan pasa so so'i dona madzada
NK115(re)001:21152: cinga rgyun mi 'chad pa sna tshogs su snang na'ang
NK115(re)001:21153: rang bzhin chos kyi sku las ma g.yos te /
NK115(re)001:21155: sangs rgyas bcom ldan bsam mi khyab //
NK115(re)001:21156: de bzhin gshegs pa rtag pa'i sku //
NK115(re)001:21157: sems can rnams la phan pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:21158: bkod pa rnam pa sna tshogs ston //
NK115(re)001:21160: de dag 'dul byed kyi thabs chosa kyanga ma ngesa
NK115(re)001:21161: pa sna tshogs su gdula bya'i blo rtoga ltar snang
NK115(re)001:21165: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' rnam pa gsum du yod cing /
NK115(re)001:21167: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa
NK115(re)001:21168: gsum du yod par gsungs pas mtshon ston pa po'ang
NK115(re)001:21169: ma nges te / bshad sbyar las /
NK115(re)001:21170: ston pa 'di yi byin rlabs kyis //
NK115(re)001:21172: pad+mo dag dang dpag bsam shing //
NK115(re)001:21173: rnga bo che las byung ba yang //
NK115(re)001:21174: rgyal bas byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyir //
NK115(re)001:21175: de dag bka' zhes bya bar 'dod //
NK115(re)001:21178: rgyal pa'i nyan thos gang dag ji snyed chos ston dang //
NK115(re)001:21179: 'chad dang rigs pa dag dang ldan par brjod pa dang //
NK115(re)001:21180: mchog 'phags bde ba byed dang de yi 'bras thob pa //
NK115(re)001:21181: de dag kun kyang de bzhin gshegs pa skyes bu'i mthu //
NK115(re)001:21182: ci'i phyir zhe na rgyal bas chos tshul gang bstan pa //
NK115(re)001:21183: de la mi mchog slob mar gyur pas mngon bslabs shing //
NK115(re)001:21184: mngon sum byas nas bslabs pa ji bzhin ston byed pa //
NK115(re)001:21185: sangs rgyas mthus byed rang gi stobs kyi mthus ma yin //
NK115(re)001:21187: ston tshul yang rnam pa kun tu sgra tshig tu grag par ma nges te /
NK115(re)001:21188: dper na spos kyi yongs gang brtsegs pa'i zhing khams na /
NK115(re)001:21189: byang chub sems dpa' rnams spos kyi shing chen po'i drung na gnas pa na /
NK115(re)001:21190: shing de'i dri tshor ba tsam gyis byang chub sems
NK115(re)001:21191: dpa'i rgyud la rnam par thar pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK115(re)001:21193: de bzhin du 'jig rten gyi khams la la na kha zas zos pas /
NK115(re)001:21194: la la na chos gos gyon pas /
NK115(re)001:21195: la la na sku la bltas pas /
NK115(re)001:21196: la la na rmi lam rmis pa la sogs pas
NK115(re)001:21197: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa nye bar bsgrub pa yod
NK115(re)001:21198: de bsam gyis mi khyab bo zhes dkon mchog brtsegs
NK115(re)001:21199: pa las byung ba'i bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:21200: don mdzad pa'i dusa kyang yun 'di tsam mo zhes dang /
NK115(re)001:21201: 'di'i dus su zhes mtha' gcig tu ma nges te
NK115(re)001:21202: gdul bya ranga ranga nam 'dul ba'i dus la bab
NK115(re)001:21204: de yang ji tsam snang ba'i skala ba yod pa
NK115(re)001:21205: de tsam du snang nas don mdzad pa yang de'i
NK115(re)001:21206: bsod nams kyi rjesa su 'gro ba yin la /
NK115(re)001:21207: don mdzad tshul yang lam gyi rten la 'god pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21209: 'bras bu la dgod pa sogs du ma ste ma
NK115(re)001:21210: daga pa'i zhing gi 'gro ba rnams la ni tshul
NK115(re)001:21211: de ltar snanga ba yin no //
NK115(re)001:21212: gsum pa de nyid sgyu ma ltar snang ba'i tshul bshad pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21213: de ltar gdul bya dang 'dul byed du snang ba
NK115(re)001:21214: de thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:21215: / gdul bya'i 'gro ba ganga zhiga bde gshegs snying
NK115(re)001:21216: po'i rang bzhin glo bur gyi dri mas bsgribs te
NK115(re)001:21217: yul don sems su bag chags nas gzung 'dzin gyi
NK115(re)001:21218: rtog pas bkod pa'i 'khor ba'i gnas rigs bde sdug
NK115(re)001:21219: sna tshogs su shar ba de yang med snang 'khrul
NK115(re)001:21221: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa las /
NK115(re)001:21222: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK115(re)001:21223: bde sdug nyid du snang ba ni //
NK115(re)001:21224: sems kyis sprul zhing sems kyis byas //
NK115(re)001:21225: sems las gzhan du cung zad med //
NK115(re)001:21226: dper na rmi lam ji bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:21228: der 'dul byed kyi sprul pa snang ba yang dri
NK115(re)001:21229: ma mtha' dag dang bral bas rang gi rang bzhin
NK115(re)001:21230: shes pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi byin rlabs dang /
NK115(re)001:21231: sems can so so'i smon lam dang dge ba'i las snang 'dzom pa las /
NK115(re)001:21232: nang gsal dbyings kyi sku gsum po'i thugs rje phyir
NK115(re)001:21233: gsal du shar ba ye shes dang phrin las dag
NK115(re)001:21235: khyad par so so'i skye bo la'ang mchog gi sprul
NK115(re)001:21236: sku rgyal ba sh+aakya seng ge la sogs par snang
NK115(re)001:21237: ba ni / 'ga' zhig gnyid du song ba'i rmi
NK115(re)001:21238: lam gyi nanga du sangsa rgyas mthonga ba ltar rang
NK115(re)001:21239: rang gi sems snang tsam yin la /
NK115(re)001:21240: rmi lam du mthong ba'i sangs rgyas des chos gsungs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21241: rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pa sna tshogs bstan pa na
NK115(re)001:21242: dad pa sogs dge blo du ma skye bar 'gyur
NK115(re)001:21243: ba'i rkyen byed pa lta bura /
NK115(re)001:21244: rang sems dag pa la snang ba'i sangs rgyas mchog
NK115(re)001:21245: gi sprula pa'i sku des chosa kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK115(re)001:21246: ba dang / cho 'phrul chen po bstana pa la
NK115(re)001:21247: sogs pas gdul bya rnams mngon par mtho ba dang
NK115(re)001:21248: nges par legs pa la dgod par mdzad na yanga
NK115(re)001:21249: ba dang / / ngo bo nyid meda de gdul
NK115(re)001:21250: bya'i sems snang tsam las phyi rol du sangs rgyas
NK115(re)001:21251: dang chos la sogs pa'i dngos po'i ranga bzhina gnyis
NK115(re)001:21253: gang la snang ba'i sems de yang rang bzhin gyis badga med cing 'od gsal ba'i phyir dang /
NK115(re)001:21254: gang zhig snang ba'i sangs rgyas de yang stong gzugs
NK115(re)001:21255: dag pa'i snang ba tsam yin pa'i phyir gdul bya
NK115(re)001:21256: 'dul byed kyi rten 'brel tshogs pa las snang yang
NK115(re)001:21257: bden pa med pas gsoga tu riga par bya'o zhesa
NK115(re)001:21258: zaba mo'i mdo sde daga lasa gsungas pa yin te
NK115(re)001:21259: // 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK115(re)001:21260: ngas ni rmi lam lta bu'i 'gro ba la //
NK115(re)001:21261: rmi lam lta bur sprul nas chos bstan yang //
NK115(re)001:21262: ngo bo med de rang bzhin gnyis su med //
NK115(re)001:21263: bdag med stong pa gsog tu rig par bya //
NK115(re)001:21265: de bas na bag la nyal shin tu zad pa'i
NK115(re)001:21266: sangs rgyas kyi rang snang la ma dag pa med
NK115(re)001:21267: kyang 'gro ba so so'i 'khrul snang thams cad thogs
NK115(re)001:21268: pa med par mkhyen pa'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:21269: dper na rin po che'i khang bu zhig gi nang
NK115(re)001:21270: du sprul pa dang mngon shes can gnyid du ma
NK115(re)001:21272: yon tan de dag med cing gnyid du song ba'i phal pa kha cig gnas pa las /
NK115(re)001:21273: gnyid du song ba rnams kyi rmi lam du bde sdug sna tshogs pa so sor snang ba na /
NK115(re)001:21274: ma song ba des de shes te sprul pa du ma bkye nas /
NK115(re)001:21275: kye 'di ltar chos thams cad ni ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21278: rang bzhin gyis dag pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21279: khyod ni gnyid kyi snang ba la zhen pa ste
NK115(re)001:21280: don la ni med do zhes brjod nas rim gyis
NK115(re)001:21281: sad pa'i thabs la sbyor ba ltar sangs rgyas kyis
NK115(re)001:21282: mkhyen gyi rang snang du min te de dag rin
NK115(re)001:21283: po che'i khang bu na gnas pa bzhin no //
NK115(re)001:21284: de ltar 'khor rang bzhin 'khrul snang gi bkod pas
NK115(re)001:21285: brdzun pa'i rang bzhin can 'dul byed mya ngan las
NK115(re)001:21286: 'das pa'i rang bzhin can sangs rgyas dang de'i bstan
NK115(re)001:21287: pa la sogs par snang ba yang sems can gyi
NK115(re)001:21288: 'khrul ngo tsam du de ltar ston pas gnyis ka'ang
NK115(re)001:21289: med bzhin snang ba rmi lam lta bu'i rola pa
NK115(re)001:21291: gdul bya la snanga ba'i sprul pa sangsa rgyas kyang
NK115(re)001:21292: ngo bo daga pa gnyis ldan chos kyi sku las
NK115(re)001:21293: ma g.yos na'ang sprul pa gdul bya rang nyid dang
NK115(re)001:21294: mthun par sdug bsngal gyi bden pas bsdus pa ltar
NK115(re)001:21295: snanga ba yin pa'i phyir na rang bzhin med de
NK115(re)001:21297: rab 'byor chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu /
NK115(re)001:21299: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK115(re)001:21301: de ltar ma daga pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi ngor
NK115(re)001:21302: tshad med thugas rjesa rola pa'i sprul pa snang ba
NK115(re)001:21303: yanga ji srida gdul bar bya ba'i 'khora ba yod
NK115(re)001:21304: pa de srid du de'i rjesa su 'gro zhing rgyun
NK115(re)001:21306: de ltar gdul bya 'dul byed gnyis kyang dbyings gcig
NK115(re)001:21307: las ma g.yos bzhin du dri ma dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:21309: dri ma las grol ba'i tshe mya ngan las 'das
NK115(re)001:21310: pa'i rnam 'gyur du shar ba'i gnas lugs gshis thog
NK115(re)001:21311: tu phebs pa la de kho na nyid mthong ba'i
NK115(re)001:21313: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK115(re)001:21314: sangs rgyas med cing chos dang dge 'dun med //
NK115(re)001:21315: de ltar sus shes de ni mkhas pa yin //
NK115(re)001:21316: sems can rang bzhin byang chub nyid du gsungs //
NK115(re)001:21317: byang chub rang bzhin sems can thams cad de //
NK115(re)001:21318: sems can rnams dang byang chub gnyis ma yin //
NK115(re)001:21319: de ltar sus shes skyes bu mchog tu 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:21321: gsum pa sna tshogs sprul pa bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:21322: sna tshogs sprul pa dngos bshad pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21323: gzugs sku'i snang ba bsdu tshul gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK115(re)001:21324: dang po sna tshogs sprul pa dngos bshad pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK115(re)001:21325: bem po ltar snang ba'i sprul pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21327: dang po bem po ltar snang ba'i sprul pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21328: de nyid nganga lasa zhes pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa
NK115(re)001:21329: de nyid kyi ngang zhes bshad kyang 'gal ba med
NK115(re)001:21330: de gcig las gcig 'phros pa lta bu ma yin
NK115(re)001:21331: na'ang / chos sku las sprul pa'i 'char gzhi rang snang gi gzugs sku rang snang ba las /
NK115(re)001:21332: rang bzhin sprul pa nas sna tshogs sprul pa'i bar
NK115(re)001:21333: chu zla ltar cig char du shar yang thams cad
NK115(re)001:21334: chos kyi sku'i ngo bor tha dad pa med pa'i
NK115(re)001:21335: phyir ro // de yang sems can gyi khams bsam
NK115(re)001:21336: gyis mi khyab pa'i 'khrul pa'i snang ba la sems
NK115(re)001:21337: med bem po dang sems dang ldan pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:21338: pa'i rnam pa gcig tu ma nges par sna tshogas
NK115(re)001:21340: yid kyis byed pa po dang chos su bya ba med bzhin du /
NK115(re)001:21341: ri brag dang yul ljongs la sogs par sku gsung
NK115(re)001:21342: thugs kyi rten ranga bzhina du byon par snang ba
NK115(re)001:21343: dang / yul nyer bzhi la sogs pa'i bkod pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21345: lha bzo sogs skyes bu rnams kyis rtsol bas 'du
NK115(re)001:21346: byed pa las byung ba yi de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK115(re)001:21347: sku gsung thugs kyi snang brnyan 'bura du byas pa
NK115(re)001:21348: dang / risa su brisa pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21349: thags su btag pa la sogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21351: sku gzugs rnam pa mang po der sprul te //
NK115(re)001:21352: 'gro ba dge la spyod pa'i don byed do //
NK115(re)001:21353: zhes gsungs pa ltar sku gsung thugs kyi rnam pa
NK115(re)001:21354: gang zhig mthong ba tsam gyis dad pa'i rnam 'gyur
NK115(re)001:21356: de'i rgyud kyi sgrib pa 'dzad cing /
NK115(re)001:21357: bsod nams su bya ba 'phel nas thar pa'i sa bon bskrun pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21358: khyad par du ston pa thugs rje can gyi zhal nas /
NK115(re)001:21359: lnga brgya'i tha mar gyur pa na //
NK115(re)001:21360: nga ni yi ge'i gzugs su snang //
NK115(re)001:21361: nga yin snyam du yid byos la //
NK115(re)001:21362: de tshe de la gus par gyis //
NK115(re)001:21364: gsung rab yi ge'i rnam par yod pa rnams bklags
NK115(re)001:21365: pa dang thos bsam byas pas sdig sgrib 'dzad cing
NK115(re)001:21367: dge sdig gi yon tan dang skyon shes nas blang dor byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21368: gnas lugs zab mo'i don bsgom zhing rgyud la skye
NK115(re)001:21369: ba'i lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen byed pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:21370: pa'i sgo nas sangs rgyas dngos su byon pa'i mdzad
NK115(re)001:21371: pa sgrub par byed pas na mchog gi sprul par
NK115(re)001:21373: gal te sku gzugs dang yi ge 'di dag ni rgyu 'di lta bu zhig la bzo bo dang /
NK115(re)001:21374: bris pa lta bu gang zag 'di dang 'dis byas
NK115(re)001:21375: pa yin pas sprul pa ji ltar yin snyam du
NK115(re)001:21376: sems na / de lta na sangs rgyas dang byang
NK115(re)001:21377: sems kyi sprul pa'i gang zag khyad par can thams
NK115(re)001:21378: cad kyang yab dang yum gyi rgyu rkyen la brten
NK115(re)001:21379: nas byung ba yin pas de kun kyang sprul pa
NK115(re)001:21380: ma yin par 'gyur dgos na de mi rigs pas
NK115(re)001:21381: de gnyis la khyad par cung zad tsam yang yod
NK115(re)001:21383: gzhan yang gan+d+ho la ste gtsug lag khang dang /
NK115(re)001:21386: mya ngama gyi thanga gnas khang dang nyer spyad sogs
NK115(re)001:21387: gang yang med par 'khyams pa rnams la sprula pa'i
NK115(re)001:21388: gronga khyer du snang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21391: yida bzhina gyi nora bu dang /
NK115(re)001:21395: zasa gosa la sogas pa semas meda bema po'i sprul
NK115(re)001:21396: pa sna tshogs pa'i tshula du snanga nas sems can
NK115(re)001:21398: 'jigs pa las skyob cing phan pa dang bde ba'i gzhir gyur pa dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK115(re)001:21399: gnyis pa skye ba sprul sku ni /
NK115(re)001:21401: sna tshogs sprul pa rgyun mi 'chad //
NK115(re)001:21402: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs par //
NK115(re)001:21403: bsgyur nas sems can don mdzad do //
NK115(re)001:21405: 'gro ba phal pa'i skye ba sna tshogs su sprul nas dngos sam brgyud nas phan 'dogs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21406: 'di ltar skye bo rnams mu ge'i sdug bsngal gyis
NK115(re)001:21407: gdung zhing nyam thag pa'i tshe na nya bo chera
NK115(re)001:21408: sprul nas rang gi shas tshim par byed pa dang
NK115(re)001:21409: / sman gyis gsor mi rung ba'i nada kyis gdunga
NK115(re)001:21410: ba'i skye bo mang po la sroga chags desa pa
NK115(re)001:21411: zhes bya bar sprul nas rang gi sha za ru
NK115(re)001:21412: bcug nas nad las grol bar byed pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21413: mi mang po srina mo'i glinga du tshud nas srog
NK115(re)001:21414: gi 'jigs pas mnar ba la canga shesa ba la
NK115(re)001:21415: hara sprul nas de las thar bar byed pa dang
NK115(re)001:21416: / mi gatsanga 'adma du skyes pa'i srin bu'i rigs
NK115(re)001:21417: rnams la gsera gyi bunga bar sprul nas bung ba'i
NK115(re)001:21418: skad kyis chos sgra bsgrags pas thams cad tshe 'phos
NK115(re)001:21419: te bde ba can du byang chub sems dpa' kha
NK115(re)001:21420: nas spos kyi dri ngad ldang ba zhes sha stag
NK115(re)001:21421: tu gyur ba la sogas pa'i sprul pa'i rol pa
NK115(re)001:21422: sna tshogas su snang nas rnama pa kuna tu phan
NK115(re)001:21423: pa dang bde ba'i gzhira gyur na yang /
NK115(re)001:21424: sprul pa'i gzhi spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes
NK115(re)001:21425: la ni sprul pa 'di lta bu'i sgo nas sems
NK115(re)001:21426: can gyi don byed do ba'i rtog pa med cinga
NK115(re)001:21427: byed rtsol gyi g.yo ba meda bzhin du /
NK115(re)001:21428: ji skad bshad pa de lta bu'i sprul pa'i rnam
NK115(re)001:21429: grangs dag gis sems can rnams kyi lus ngag yid
NK115(re)001:21430: gsum la phan pa rgya chen po bsgrub cing mthun
NK115(re)001:21431: pa dang ldan pa'i bde ba chen po ster ba
NK115(re)001:21432: dang / brgyud nas byang chub gsum gyi go 'phang
NK115(re)001:21433: la 'god pa la sogs pa'i dona chena gyis ni
NK115(re)001:21434: dapala du nye bar gansa te /
NK115(re)001:21435: de yang gzugs dang thabs gang gis gdul ba'i dus
NK115(re)001:21436: la bab pa na de dang der snang nas don
NK115(re)001:21437: mdzad pa la ni dus las yo ba med de
NK115(re)001:21439: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas kyi rlabs //
NK115(re)001:21440: dus las yo bar 'gyur srid kyi //
NK115(re)001:21441: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
NK115(re)001:21442: sangs rgyas dus las yo mi mnga' //
NK115(re)001:21444: gnyis pa gzugs sku'i snang ba bsdu tshul bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:21445: sprul sku longs skur thim tshul /
NK115(re)001:21446: longs sku chos skur thim tshul chos sku dbyings su 'khyil tshul lo //
NK115(re)001:21447: dang po sprul sku longs skur thim tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:21448: de lta bu'i phrin las de dang por yang dbyings
NK115(re)001:21449: las byung zhing mthar yang dbyings su spros pa nye
NK115(re)001:21451: gala te gdula bar bya ba'i dusa yola ba ste /
NK115(re)001:21452: gdul bya bye brag pa mchog gi sprul sku gcig
NK115(re)001:21453: gi gdul bya'i dbang du byas na rang gi sku
NK115(re)001:21454: dngos kyi gdul byar gyur pa thams cad kyi don
NK115(re)001:21455: mdzad zin nas / mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul
NK115(re)001:21456: ston par mdzad de skal pa dman pa rnams kyi
NK115(re)001:21457: don du re zhig mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK115(re)001:21458: des mtshon nas ma dag pa'i zhing gi 'gro ba
NK115(re)001:21459: rnams kyi ngor snang ba'i sprul pa thams cad mi
NK115(re)001:21460: snang bar 'gyur ba'i tshul shes par bya la /
NK115(re)001:21461: gdul bya sar gnas rnams ni thams cad skal pa
NK115(re)001:21462: mnyam zhing snang ba dag pas de dag gi ngor
NK115(re)001:21463: snang ba'i gzugs sku de mya ngan las 'da' ba'i
NK115(re)001:21464: tshul mi ston mod kyang byang sems rang rang ston
NK115(re)001:21465: pa dang dgongs klong dbyer med du gyur nas sangs
NK115(re)001:21466: rgyas pa'i tshe na sngar gdul bya dang 'dul byed
NK115(re)001:21467: kyi gnyis snang gi cha de dbyings su zhi bar
NK115(re)001:21468: 'gyur ro // 'o na gdul bar bya ba'i sems
NK115(re)001:21469: can gcig kyang med pa'i gnas skabs zhig yod dam
NK115(re)001:21470: 'gyur ro // zhe na / 'khor ba'i spyi'i mtha'
NK115(re)001:21471: 'dzad du yod par ni theg pa gong 'og gang
NK115(re)001:21472: na'ang ma gsungs pas de 'dra ba'i gnas skabs med
NK115(re)001:21473: 'gyur ro // zhe na / kyang / rdo rje
NK115(re)001:21474: 'chang gis bkod pa'i tshangs chen gyi bskal pa'i 'gro
NK115(re)001:21475: ba spyir snang ba thams cad gdod ma'i sar grol
NK115(re)001:21477: de'i tshe na sprul skus gdul ba'i gnas 'dzam bu'i
NK115(re)001:21478: gling 'dir chos sku'i bstan pa dngos rdzogs pa chen
NK115(re)001:21479: po'i byin rlabs las rang shar ba rin po che
NK115(re)001:21480: brgya rtsa gcig gi rgyu las rang 'khrungs pa'i rdo
NK115(re)001:21481: rje tshe lo dpag med nas da lta'i bar gyi
NK115(re)001:21482: mi rnams kyi phyag gang ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21483: longs sku'i bstan pa dngos rang byung bstan pa bu
NK115(re)001:21484: gcig gi byin rlabs las rang shar ba rin po
NK115(re)001:21485: che brgya rtsa gcig gi rgyu las rang 'khrungs pa'i
NK115(re)001:21486: yi ge glegs bam sor bzhi pa chos kyi rang
NK115(re)001:21488: sprul sku bcu gnyis pa'i byin rlabs las rang shar
NK115(re)001:21489: ba rin po che brgya rtsa gcig gi rgyu las
NK115(re)001:21490: sus kyang ma byas par 'khrungs pa'i sku gzugs 'gro
NK115(re)001:21491: ba'i lus bongs dang mnyam pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21492: bstan pa'i btsas gsum yang chos kyi dbyings su thim pa'i tshe na /
NK115(re)001:21493: gzugs sku'i bkod pa thams cad kyang dbyings su bsdu zhing /
NK115(re)001:21494: slar 'khrul pa mngon gyur du ldang ba'i gdul bya
NK115(re)001:21495: rnams 'byung ba na gzugs sku phrin las dang bcas
NK115(re)001:21496: pa rtsol med du snang ba ni 'chad ma rag
NK115(re)001:21497: pa ste / tshul de ni mdo rgyud 'og ma
NK115(re)001:21498: rnams na gab pa'i tshul du yod pa rdzogs pa
NK115(re)001:21499: chen po'i rgyud sde nas gsal bar bstan zhing /
NK115(re)001:21500: de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa'i man ngag rnams kyis kyang bkral ba yin pas /
NK115(re)001:21501: spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i grub pa'i mtha' la go
NK115(re)001:21502: ba gting phyin nas kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer
NK115(re)001:21503: gyi mdzod chen bdun la sogs pa la mos gus
NK115(re)001:21504: gyis mjal bar byas na yid ches shing theg pa
NK115(re)001:21505: thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'gal med du go bar
NK115(re)001:21506: 'gyur bas re zhig de tsam mo //
NK115(re)001:21507: de ltar shes par byas nas gdul bya spyi dang
NK115(re)001:21508: bye brag pa gang yang rung ba med pa'i gnas
NK115(re)001:21509: skabs na / de 'dula byed kyi gzugs sku dbyingsa
NK115(re)001:21510: su nub para 'gyur ba'i tshul de mtshona par byed
NK115(re)001:21511: pa'i dpe ni ji ltar na sa steng gi chu
NK115(re)001:21513: bye brag pa gang yang rung ba meda pa'i tshe
NK115(re)001:21514: na chu de dang de'i nang du shar ba'i zla
NK115(re)001:21516: sprula gzhi ste dang po rnam pa gtod par byed
NK115(re)001:21517: pa'i nam mkha'i zla ba nyid la thima pa zhes
NK115(re)001:21518: dngos po gcig cig shos la 'dres pa lta bu
NK115(re)001:21519: ma yin kyang de las gzhan du gar yang song
NK115(re)001:21520: ba med pas dbyer med du gyur pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:21521: dag ma dag gi gdula bya'i snang basa bsdusa pa'i
NK115(re)001:21522: sna tshogs sprula pa nas rang bzhin sprul pa'i bar
NK115(re)001:21523: rnamas ranga snanga longas spyod rdzogas pa'i dbyingas su thima
NK115(re)001:21524: pa ste de las gzhan du ma song zhing dbyer
NK115(re)001:21525: med du gyur nas thugs rje phyir gsal gdul bya
NK115(re)001:21526: snang ba'i cha de mi mngon no //
NK115(re)001:21527: gnyis pa longs sku chos skur thim tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:21528: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku de'ang chos skur thim pa'i tshul /
NK115(re)001:21529: dper na ganma stong gi dus su phyir gsal du
NK115(re)001:21530: yod pa'i zla ba gciga shosa nasa gciga tu thima
NK115(re)001:21531: pa'am gtan med du song ba meda kyang phyir gasla
NK115(re)001:21532: gyi gadngas nanga dbyingsa 'od snang phyir sprosa pa meda
NK115(re)001:21533: pa'i gting gsal gyi nganga du thima pa ltar /
NK115(re)001:21534: longas spyod rdzogas pa'i sku dang zhing khams ranga snanga
NK115(re)001:21535: du shar ba de yang nang dbyings spros pa med
NK115(re)001:21536: pa chosa kyi sku'i ye shesa chena pora 'khyila ba
NK115(re)001:21537: ste / sgron ma snang byed las /
NK115(re)001:21538: chos sku'i ye shes gzhi gnas te //
NK115(re)001:21539: shes pa'i cha ni gsal byed la //
NK115(re)001:21540: 'dzin pa rags pa'i rtog pa med //
NK115(re)001:21541: ngang ngam shugs kyi thugs rje'o //
NK115(re)001:21542: gsal zhing shes pa rig dang bcas //
NK115(re)001:21543: cha la 'dres pa med par gnas //
NK115(re)001:21545: de lta bu'i sku gsum gyi dgongs pa ro gcig
NK115(re)001:21546: tu gyur pa'i gnas skabs de nyid la dbu ma
NK115(re)001:21547: thal 'gyur ba rnamas ni sems dang sems byung yul
NK115(re)001:21548: la 'juga pa'i gnyis snang gi bag chags shin tu
NK115(re)001:21549: phra ba spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i chosa
NK115(re)001:21550: kyi dbyingsa su bud shing zad pa'i me bzhin zhi
NK115(re)001:21551: ba'i tshe na ni dman lam gyi dgra bcom thob
NK115(re)001:21552: pa lta bu bag chags phra ba ma zad pa'i
NK115(re)001:21553: 'goga pa nyi tshe ba tsam ma yin par myang
NK115(re)001:21554: 'das mthar thug 'gog pa dama pa zhesa rtag tu
NK115(re)001:21555: de la mnyam par bzhag bzhin sngon smon gyi dbang
NK115(re)001:21556: gis gdul bya'i yul la phrin las rtsol med du
NK115(re)001:21559: shes bya'i bud shing skam po ma lus pa //
NK115(re)001:21560: bsregs pas zhi de rgyal rnams chos sku ste //
NK115(re)001:21561: de tshe skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NK115(re)001:21562: sems 'gags pas de sku yis mngon du mdzad //
NK115(re)001:21564: gsum pa chos sku dbyings su 'khyil tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:21565: 'dira rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs su ni
NK115(re)001:21566: glo bur gyi dri ma tshogs brgyad dang bcas pa'i
NK115(re)001:21567: khams gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems dang sems byung thams
NK115(re)001:21568: cad 'gags kyang so so ranga riga pa'i ye shesa
NK115(re)001:21569: nyid ni 'gags pa ma yin te /
NK115(re)001:21570: de yang 'gags na mya ngan las 'das pa'i yon
NK115(re)001:21571: tan stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa shin
NK115(re)001:21572: tu rgyas pa'i cha dang ye shes kyi chos nyid
NK115(re)001:21573: nyi ma dang 'od zer ltar gnas pa'i 'char gzhi
NK115(re)001:21574: 'gag pa med pa'ang rgyun 'chad par 'gyur bas so
NK115(re)001:21575: // de bas na gzhi dus na'ang dbyings la lhun
NK115(re)001:21576: grub kyi rig cha'i yon tan ye ldan du yod
NK115(re)001:21577: kyang 'khrul bas bsgribs nas lkog tu gyur pa'i tshul
NK115(re)001:21579: gnam stong nub mo zla ba yongs rdzogs kyang //
NK115(re)001:21580: nyi ma'i stobs kyis mngon du mi snang bas //
NK115(re)001:21581: tshe gcig gong nas bco lngar rdzogs gyur te //
NK115(re)001:21582: de bas zla ba bskyed du med pa ltar //
NK115(re)001:21583: rin chen sbubs la 'du 'bral med kyis kyang //
NK115(re)001:21584: 'khrul pa'i stobs kyis mgon du gsal ma nus //
NK115(re)001:21586: slob pa'i lam gyis sgrib pa rim gyis bsal nas sangs rgyas pa'i tshe na /
NK115(re)001:21587: phra zhing rtogs dka' ba'i ye shesa nanga gasla chosa
NK115(re)001:21588: kyi dbyingsa dang 'dul 'bral med pa gzugs sku phyir
NK115(re)001:21589: gsal gyi cha thima la rang bzhin ma rmugsa pa
NK115(re)001:21590: gzhona nu buma pa'i sku yi dgongs pa ji lta
NK115(re)001:21591: ba bzhin mngon du gyur nas zla ba nya gang
NK115(re)001:21592: ba ltar spangs rtogs kyi yon tan thams cad mthar
NK115(re)001:21593: phyin nas de las gong du 'gror med pa ste
NK115(re)001:21595: dang po'i sa nas bco lngar yongs rdzogs te //
NK115(re)001:21596: de las yar gshegs gong la shul mi mnga' //
NK115(re)001:21598: de yang gnas dang dus ganga du gdula bya'i 'gro
NK115(re)001:21599: ba snanga ba na de'i moda nyid la 'agga pa
NK115(re)001:21600: meda pa'i thugas rje'i gdangs las ye shesa phyir gsal
NK115(re)001:21601: sku dang phrin las rgyun mi 'chad pa rtsol med
NK115(re)001:21602: du mcheda pa'i gzhi ru gyur pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21603: de lta bu'i bsam gyis mi khyab cing shina tu
NK115(re)001:21604: mnyam para bazhaga pa gnyis snang mtha' dag dbyings su
NK115(re)001:21606: 'brasa bu sangs rgyas kho na'i ma 'dres pa'i chos
NK115(re)001:21607: mnyam par ma bzhag pa med pa'i yon tan lhuna
NK115(re)001:21608: gruba chena po'i go 'aphanga yina la de yang dbyings
NK115(re)001:21609: nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang na /
NK115(re)001:21610: nyi ma dang 'od zer bzhin sku dang ye shes
NK115(re)001:21611: thams cad rtag tu bri gang dang 'pho 'gyur med
NK115(re)001:21612: par lhun gyis grub par bzhugs pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21613: kun mkhyen chen po'i gsang 'grel las /
NK115(re)001:21614: rgyud kyi mdzad pa rdzogs nas dgongs pa chos nyid du bzhugs pa'i tshul brjod pa'i skabs su /
NK115(re)001:21615: rgyud kyi don de skad ces brjod pas rang snang
NK115(re)001:21616: 'od gsal du bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK115(re)001:21617: lnga til gyi gong bu ltar ji snyed kyis nam
NK115(re)001:21618: mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' dbus khyab pa de dag thams
NK115(re)001:21619: cad gnyis su mi dmigs shing /
NK115(re)001:21620: ngo bo dbyer med par dgyes nas dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa'i ngang /
NK115(re)001:21621: gzhir rdzogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK115(re)001:21622: dus bzhi chos nyid kyi 'khor lo /
NK115(re)001:21623: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings mtha' dbus med pa'i zhing
NK115(re)001:21624: khams snang zhing bkod pa thams cad ston pa nyid
NK115(re)001:21625: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs mi zad pa rgyan
NK115(re)001:21626: gyi 'khor lo'i rang bzhin las lhun stug po bkod
NK115(re)001:21627: pa'i rgyan nyid du sngon ji lta bar phyis kyang
NK115(re)001:21629: nam mkha' bzhin du rang bzhin 'pho 'gyur dang 'phel 'grib med pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK115(re)001:21631: yona tana rina po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i chara zhesa bya ba lasa /
NK115(re)001:21632: mathara phyin 'brasa bu sku dang ye shesa bstan pa'i
NK115(re)001:21633: tshomas te le'u bcu gsuma pa'i 'grel pas gzhung don
NK115(re)001:21636: // spyi don gsum pa tha mar dge ba mjug gi don bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK115(re)001:21638: des thob pa'i dge ba bsngo ba /
NK115(re)001:21640: dang po bstan bcos rtsom pa'i rgyu ni /
NK115(re)001:21641: spyir rang gi shes rab kyi stobs kyis bka'i dgongs
NK115(re)001:21642: pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos zhig rtsom par byed pa
NK115(re)001:21643: la / bstan bcos rtsom pa'i rgyu gsum legs par tshang dgos pas /
NK115(re)001:21644: de ji ltar tshang ba'i tshul ni /
NK115(re)001:21645: gzhung 'di rtsom pa po badga gi rgyud slob ma
NK115(re)001:21646: bzang po'i mtshan nyid 'phags sa thob pa la sogs
NK115(re)001:21647: pa'i snoda kyi dpyad pa thams cad yongs su rdzogas
NK115(re)001:21648: pa ste ma tshang ba med par gyura la /
NK115(re)001:21649: de ltar na bstan bcos rtsom pa'i rgyu yang tshang ba yin te /
NK115(re)001:21650: rgya bod kyi mkhas grub rgyal ba'i sras sam slob
NK115(re)001:21651: mar gyur pa'i bstan bcos byed pa po thams cad
NK115(re)001:21652: la de lta bu'i yon tan legs par tshang nasa
NK115(re)001:21653: / rgyal tshab tu gyur pa'i slob ma'i bya ba
NK115(re)001:21654: bstan pa'i chos mdzod 'dzin zhing dgongs 'gre gyi bstan
NK115(re)001:21655: bcos kyang mang du mdzad pa bzhin 'dir yang chu
NK115(re)001:21656: dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar /
NK115(re)001:21657: bsam yas mchims phu'i brag dmar ke'u tshang gi sgrub
NK115(re)001:21658: gnas su sgrub pa la rtse gcig tu gzhol ba'i
NK115(re)001:21659: tshe / bde gshegs ri rab mar me'i rgyal mtshan
NK115(re)001:21660: du 'gyur ba'i 'jiga rten gsum gyi mgona po kun
NK115(re)001:21661: mkhyen dri meda 'oda zera gyi skus byin gyis brlabs
NK115(re)001:21662: te ye shes kyi sku'i zhala mngon sum du mthonga
NK115(re)001:21663: tshe / / gsung gis byin gyis brlabs te bstan bcos rtsom pa'i gnang ba byin /
NK115(re)001:21664: thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs te thugs yid dbyer med du 'dres pa ste /
NK115(re)001:21665: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs nas
NK115(re)001:21666: thugas rjesa dbugas 'byina par mdzad pas bstan bcos rtsom
NK115(re)001:21667: pa'i spobs pa skyes pa yin gyi /
NK115(re)001:21668: gal te de lta bu'i yon tan khyad par can ma thoba na /
NK115(re)001:21669: rnam grol gyi lam mina pa'i las sna tshogs pas
NK115(re)001:21670: 'khor ba'i gayanga sara rtag tu 'phyan par 'gyur bas
NK115(re)001:21671: na dala ba'i rtena bzang po lon pa yang stong
NK115(re)001:21672: lo byas par zad do zhes gsungs te /
NK115(re)001:21673: dam pa 'di ni thugs rje yas sprul gyi gang
NK115(re)001:21674: zag yin par tshad mas grub kyang gdul bya'i ngor
NK115(re)001:21675: lam la slob pa'i tshul bstan zhing rjes 'jug rnams
NK115(re)001:21676: la mi lus thob tshe dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi
NK115(re)001:21677: thugs mdzod lon par ma byas na stong log mkhan
NK115(re)001:21678: du 'gyur ro zhes shugs kyis gdams pa'ang yin no
NK115(re)001:21679: // gong du ji skad bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan de
NK115(re)001:21680: yi phyir na gzhung 'di la bstan bcos rtsom pa'i
NK115(re)001:21681: rgyu gsum legas para tshang bas bashada pa'i cha skyon
NK115(re)001:21682: med cing rnam par dag pa mchis pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21683: bla ma'i byina rlabas dang rang gi bsgomas byunga gi
NK115(re)001:21684: stobs kyis chos nyid kyi bden pa mngon sum du
NK115(re)001:21685: mthong zhing / de ltar mthong ba de la yi dam lhag pa'i lha yang 'du 'bral med cing /
NK115(re)001:21686: mngon sum la shes bya bden pa gnyis kyi sgo
NK115(re)001:21687: nas rnam par bzhag pa'i chos thams cad so sor
NK115(re)001:21688: 'byed pa'i shesa raba kyang ngang gis skye ba'i phyir
NK115(re)001:21689: / rgyu de rnams tshang ba lasa brtsams pa yin
NK115(re)001:21690: gyi don mngon sum du ma mthong bzhin rjes dpag
NK115(re)001:21691: thosa bsam gyi rtoga ge'i riga pasa rang phyogs la
NK115(re)001:21692: mchog tu 'dzin pa la sogs pas ma bskyed pasa
NK115(re)001:21693: / na / don la 'gal ba'i nyes pa yid kyis dogs nas bzod gsol mi dgos kyang /
NK115(re)001:21694: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis rtsom pa ni mkhas
NK115(re)001:21695: pas nga mi rgyal zhing rlom sems med la snying
NK115(re)001:21696: rjes byas pa'i bstan bcos yin pas /
NK115(re)001:21697: grub pa'i mtha' so sor 'dzin pa po rnams ranga
NK115(re)001:21698: ranga gis 'doda pa'i gzhunga gi phyogas dang 'agla ba
NK115(re)001:21699: ltar snang na 'achagas par byed kyis bzod par mdzod
NK115(re)001:21700: cig ces pa'o // de yang rgyal bas gdul bya
NK115(re)001:21701: rnams kyi mos pa dang 'tshams par bstan pa'i drang
NK115(re)001:21702: nges kyi chosa tshula rgya mtsho lta bu rgya che
NK115(re)001:21703: zhing gtinga dapaga daka'a ba'i dona ni /
NK115(re)001:21704: chos nyid rnal ma'i don la manyama para bazhaga pa
NK115(re)001:21705: kho na'i khyad chosa lasa de kho na nyid kyi
NK115(re)001:21706: don ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs shing /
NK115(re)001:21707: de'i rjes la thob pa ji snyed pa'i chos thams
NK115(re)001:21708: cad ma nor zhing ma 'dres par so sor mkhyen
NK115(re)001:21709: pa'i ye shesa kyis rtogs pa'i gansa yin gyi /
NK115(re)001:21710: de las gzhan du phyogs tsam las ji bzhin pa mi rtogs la /
NK115(re)001:21711: kho bos ni mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis po mngon
NK115(re)001:21712: du gyur bas gsung rab kyi dgongs don zab mo
NK115(re)001:21713: yanga dag par mthonga nas brtsams pa yin pas bstan
NK115(re)001:21714: bcos 'di la shes rab gsum gyis zhugs te nyams
NK115(re)001:21715: su blangs na dus nam du yang bslu ba med
NK115(re)001:21716: do zhes gdams par mdzad do //
NK115(re)001:21717: gnyis pa des thob pa'i dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK115(re)001:21718: de ltar bstan bcos legs par brtsams pa'i dge ba
NK115(re)001:21719: 'di yi mthu la brten nas rtsom pa po badga
NK115(re)001:21720: dang mtha' yas pa'i semas can rnamas /
NK115(re)001:21721: rgyala ba'i ringa lugas nora ba med pasa theg pa
NK115(re)001:21722: chen po'i mdo sngags kyi lam bzang po sgriba pa
NK115(re)001:21723: gnyis kyi rnyoga pa dwangas pa'i ste skyon gyis mi
NK115(re)001:21724: bardzi ba'i gzingas chen por zhugas nasa /
NK115(re)001:21725: 'bras bu mthar thug byang chub chen po'i go 'phang
NK115(re)001:21726: mtha' gnyis kyi dri ma nye bar zhi ba chos
NK115(re)001:21727: dang gzugs kyi sku'i yon tan rina chena gyi glinga
NK115(re)001:21728: dam pa der myur du phyin par shog cig /
NK115(re)001:21729: de ma thob kyi bar gnas skabs thams cad du'ang
NK115(re)001:21730: dam pa rnams kyis basngagasa shing chos dang mthun pa'i
NK115(re)001:21731: dben gnas phun sum tshogs pa /
NK115(re)001:21732: gangs khrod dang g.ya' khrod la sogs pa dang /
NK115(re)001:21733: nagas kyi mthongas nyams dga' ba ri dwagas sna tshogs
NK115(re)001:21734: phan tshun dkyu zhing brtse ba'i smana gyi ljongas yid
NK115(re)001:21736: dusa bzhi'i mngona rtogsa gsar du ngoma pa'i shing ljona pa rnams ni /
NK115(re)001:21737: de na gnas pa'i dranga sronga rnal 'byor pa rnamas
NK115(re)001:21738: la mi snyana pa'i gtam sgroga par mi byed la
NK115(re)001:21739: / snying la 'abba pa ste shin tu yid du
NK115(re)001:21740: 'ong bar smra ba'i bya yi tshogas dag gis kyang
NK115(re)001:21741: / / dug sbrul gduga pa 'khri zhing 'khyil ba'i
NK115(re)001:21742: shinga gi drung na 'dug pa lta bu'i 'khora ba
NK115(re)001:21743: / / yi gnas 'dira / snying nas skyo ba'i
NK115(re)001:21744: nges 'byung gi shinga rtas rnal 'byor ba'i yida thar
NK115(re)001:21746: skad snyan gyi ca co 'jam zhing shina tu zhi
NK115(re)001:21747: ba sgroga pa'i sgra thosa pa sogs nags tshal gyi
NK115(re)001:21749: dabnga po yul la g.yeng ba'i nyes pa nye bar
NK115(re)001:21750: zhi ba'i bsam gtan zhi lhag zung du 'jug pa'i
NK115(re)001:21751: dapala phun sum tshogs pa thoba par shoga cig /
NK115(re)001:21752: mdor na gnas lugs rtogs pa'i lta ba ni rtog
NK115(re)001:21753: ge'i yida byed mthar 'dzin gyi rlunga gisa ma dkrugas
NK115(re)001:21754: la / sgo gsum gyi spyod pa thams cad rgyal
NK115(re)001:21755: ba'i thugs kyi srasa po byang sems dama pa 'jig
NK115(re)001:21756: rten dbang phyug la sogs pa'i rjesa su 'gro bas
NK115(re)001:21757: la / / skye ba 'di nas bzung tshe rabs
NK115(re)001:21758: kun tu nama yanga sems can gazhana gyi ba spu'i
NK115(re)001:21759: khung bu gcig tsam la'ang gnod pa'i khura du mi
NK115(re)001:21760: la / / 'gro zhing / thabs la mkhas shing
NK115(re)001:21761: rlabas chena po'i phrin las kyis dngos brgyad gang yang
NK115(re)001:21762: rung bar mtha' yas pa'i 'gro ba ma lus pa'i
NK115(re)001:21763: phan bde bsgrub pa'i dapala du 'gyur bar shoga cig
NK115(re)001:21764: la / / 'gro zhing / ces pa'o // gsum pa mjug mdzad byang brjod pa ni /
NK115(re)001:21765: yona tan rina po che'i mdzoda dag'a ba'i chara zhesa bya ba /
NK115(re)001:21766: gtsang la stoda kyi chosa rje braga phuga pasa bskula ba'i ngora /
NK115(re)001:21767: dpal o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po sangas rgyas
NK115(re)001:21768: gnyisa pa pad+ma sam+b+ha wa'i zhabas rdula la spyi bosa
NK115(re)001:21770: chos sku'i dgongs pa ranga byunga don gyi rdo rje'i
NK115(re)001:21771: gnas lugs nam mkha' lta bu mngon du gyur nas
NK115(re)001:21772: / longs sku'i ye shes mkhyena brtse'i dkyil 'khor mchog tu rgyas shing /
NK115(re)001:21773: sprul sku'i mdzad pa gang 'dul phrin las kyi 'oda
NK115(re)001:21774: zera stong du 'phro bas yid can kun gyi lam
NK115(re)001:21775: ston du gyur pa de nyid la mtshan gzhan 7rig
NK115(re)001:21776: 'dzin 'dzigs med gling pa zhes yongs su grags pa'i
NK115(re)001:21777: rig sngags 'chang chen po klong chen nam mkha'i rnal
NK115(re)001:21778: 'byor gyis grub pa'i bsti gnas tshe ring ljongs su
NK115(re)001:21779: grags pa'i dben gnas 'od gsal gnyug ma'i pho brang
NK115(re)001:21780: dapala ldana pad+ma 'oda glinga du sbyar ba'o //
NK115(re)001:21783: gang zhig legs bshad bdud rtsi dngar po'i skyes //
NK115(re)001:21784: don gnyer snyim pas 'thung ba'i skal bzang gi //
NK115(re)001:21785: thos bsam sgom pa'i yi ge phye srid na //
NK115(re)001:21786: phul byung gtam 'di ro brgya'i bcud du dngar //
NK115(re)001:21787: thos pa'i mtha' rgya gcod pa'i blo gsal dang //
NK115(re)001:21788: bsam pa'i don bcud myong ba'i snying stobs dpal //
NK115(re)001:21789: gus dang rtag pa'i brtson 'grus mi dman pa'i //
NK115(re)001:21790: rnam dpyod ldan pa'i yid la dpyid dpal bzhin //
NK115(re)001:21791: blo grus g.yeng ba'i khol du rgyug dga' ba'i //
NK115(re)001:21792: rnam rig yal ga'i ri dwags bzhin rtsen la //
NK115(re)001:21793: don bzang ri mo bkra ba'i za 'og bkrag /
NK115(re)001:21794: bkram pa'i ltas mo ngom du su zhig spros //
NK115(re)001:21795: don gnyer dul ba'i ngang tshul las ring ba'i //
NK115(re)001:21796: sems rta na tshod gsar ba'i tsab tsub la //
NK115(re)001:21797: thos bsam khal chen 'gel ba'i shom ra 'di //
NK115(re)001:21798: 'bras med ngal khur rang gis len par zad //
NK115(re)001:21799: mtshan dpe'i byad las legs 'phos ri mo'i lha //
NK115(re)001:21800: re chen rgyal bar re ba'i gdung yus kyis //
NK115(re)001:21801: legs bshad ngag gi man+dala phul phul yang //
NK115(re)001:21802: thugs brtses bdag gir bzhes sam su yis shes //
NK115(re)001:21803: rang don snying po'i sgrub la blos btang nas //
NK115(re)001:21804: don med 'chad dang rtsom pa'i gzugs brnyan gyis //
NK115(re)001:21805: rnam g.yeng snying po re ba'i col chung 'di //
NK115(re)001:21806: shes med sh+r+ai hral po'i rang gshis lags //
NK115(re)001:21807: chos don zab par bshad kyang ngag gi khur //
NK115(re)001:21808: sna tshogs yi ger bris kyang shog bu'i gron //
NK115(re)001:21809: bdag dang bdag 'dra byis pa'i byed spyod 'di //
NK115(re)001:21810: rang dang gzhan bcas su yi don du 'gyur //
NK115(re)001:21811: da ni mi tshe'i lhag ma cung zad 'di //
NK115(re)001:21812: dben pa'i ri khrod mi med lung stong du //
NK115(re)001:21813: rnam g.yeng spangs pa'i rtse gcig nyams len gyis //
NK115(re)001:21814: tshe 'dir snying po'i don la 'dril bar shog /
NK115(re)001:21815: thugs rjes gzigs shig drin chen bla ma rje //
NK115(re)001:21816: byin gyis rlobs shig yi dam spyan ras gzigs //
NK115(re)001:21817: las ngan bdag gi blo sna la 'ur bstungs //
NK115(re)001:21818: gong ma'i rjes su snyegs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK115(re)001:21819: rgyal ba kun las rgyal ba'i mdzad pa can //
NK115(re)001:21820: sangs rgyas kun las bka' drin chen lhag pa //
NK115(re)001:21821: mgon med bdag gi skyabs gcig rin po che //
NK115(re)001:21822: yang dang yang du thugs rje'i spyan gyis gzigs //
NK115(re)001:21823: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod 'chad pa'i skabs su
NK115(re)001:21824: dka' gnas kha shas brjed thor byas pa'i zin bris
NK115(re)001:21825: 'di nyid grub dbang bla ma dam pa'i sku gsung
NK115(re)001:21826: thugs kyi sras mchog bde chen rig pa'i ral gri
NK115(re)001:21827: dpon slob kyi thugs gsos su mdo med dpal dge
NK115(re)001:21828: hral pos blo thog nas bris pa'o //
NK115(re)001:21829: zhes pa ni dka' 'grel gyi mjug rtsom dang mdzad byang ngo //
NK115(re)001:21831: // spyi don sa bcad dkyus kyi khog phub nas //
NK115(re)001:21832: tshig don ma 'khrul 'bru rnams chom par bshad //
NK115(re)001:21833: bsdus don ma nor gnad du dril shes pa'i //
NK115(re)001:21834: 'chad pa'i tshul 'di mkhas pa'i ring lugs yin //
NK115(re)001:21835: gzhung don tshig las phral nas spyi don steng //
NK115(re)001:21836: ma nyams me long gzugs bzhin 'dzin shes na //
NK115(re)001:21837: thos don bsam par 'char ba'i sngon 'gro ste //
NK115(re)001:21838: de phyir kun gyis 'di la nan tan mdzod //
NK115(re)001:21839: ces pa 'di sa bcad kyi gsham na'o //
NK115(re)001:21842: za ba dang rgya che'i tshig gi don //
NK115(re)001:21843: 'grel pa'i rang nus med na yang //
NK115(re)001:21844: dam pa'i gsung gi snang ba la //
NK115(re)001:21845: brten nas go sla gsal bar bkod //
NK115(re)001:21846: 'on kyang bdag blo rmongs pa'i dris //
NK115(re)001:21847: bslad nas nyes par bshad pa'i cha //
NK115(re)001:21848: rtsa gsum lha dang srung ma dang //
NK115(re)001:21849: chos kyi spyan ldan rnams la 'chags //
NK115(re)001:21850: rgyal bstan snyigs mar gyur pa la //
NK115(re)001:21851: phan pa'i lhag bsam dag pa yis //
NK115(re)001:21852: brtson pa'i dge ba ci mchis pa //
NK115(re)001:21853: sras bcas rgyal ba'i rjes su bsngo //
NK115(re)001:21854: rgyal bstan dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK115(re)001:21855: bstan 'dzin mchog rnams zhabs pad brtan //
NK115(re)001:21856: 'jig rten dus kyi rgud pa zhi //
NK115(re)001:21857: rdzogs ldan dpal la spyod par shog /
NK115(re)001:21858: bdag dang bskul ba'i gtsor byas kun //
NK115(re)001:21859: mtshungs med bla ma'i bka' 'khor du //
NK115(re)001:21860: lhan cig chos kyi dga' ston la //
NK115(re)001:21861: rol pa'i skal pa yod gyur cig /
NK115(re)001:21862: de tshe ma bcos gnyug ma'i don //
NK115(re)001:21863: dam pa'i drin gyis legs mthong nas //
NK115(re)001:21864: ye shes bla ma'i sa mchog der //
NK115(re)001:21865: tshom bu gcig tu grol bar shog /
NK115(re)001:21866: mchog gsum bden pa'i byin mthu yis //
NK115(re)001:21867: ji ltar smon bzhin 'grub pa dang //
NK115(re)001:21868: sa gsum phan bde'i dpal 'byor pa'i //
NK115(re)001:21869: bkra shis char gyis 'gengs gyur cig /
NK115(re)001:21870: de ltar yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi 'grel
NK115(re)001:21871: pa nyi zla'i sgron me zhes bya ba 'di nyid
NK115(re)001:21872: snga mo nas klu shul sprul pa'i sku 'jigs med
NK115(re)001:21873: yon tan dpal bzang pos gzhung 'di'i rang 'grel ni
NK115(re)001:21874: rgya che zhing 'bru mnan ma mdzad pas gsar bu
NK115(re)001:21876: 'grel pa gzhan rnams ha cang bsdus ches pas /
NK115(re)001:21877: 'di la 'bru 'grel go sla zhing bla ma'i gsung
NK115(re)001:21878: rgyun sems la yod pa rnams kyang skabs gang 'os
NK115(re)001:21879: su sbyar ba zhig dgos zhes nan cher mdzad kyang
NK115(re)001:21880: / rang nyid ni thos rgya chung zhing rgyud tshod
NK115(re)001:21881: dman pa nyams len gyis dbul bas rtsom pa lta
NK115(re)001:21882: / ci / 'chad pa'i yon tan tsam yang med pas /
NK115(re)001:21883: bla ma dang man ngag bzang po dang phrad pa'i
NK115(re)001:21884: dus 'dir rang rgyud la phan pa'i nyams len re
NK115(re)001:21885: la ci nus su brtson pa skabs su bab na
NK115(re)001:21886: yang / da lta rgyal bstan spyi dang rang lugs
NK115(re)001:21887: kyi gzhung rnams la bshad pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam yang
NK115(re)001:21889: rang gi bla ma dam pa rnams kyis bdag lta
NK115(re)001:21890: bu'i bshad pa'i gzugs brnyan las kyang yang brnyan rang
NK115(re)001:21891: don 'chor zhing gzhan don med pa 'di tsam la'ang
NK115(re)001:21892: dgyes tshor che che ltar mdzad 'dug pa la bsam
NK115(re)001:21893: nas mi tshe gang po de 'dra'i rnam g.yeng la
NK115(re)001:21894: zad du bcug pa la ma gtogs /
NK115(re)001:21895: de 'dra bri 'dod ni gtan nas ma skyes par lo cha shas song ba la /
NK115(re)001:21896: sprul sku khong rang nas lo gsum la bstud mar gzhung 'di'i rtsa ba dang /
NK115(re)001:21897: 'grel pa shing rta rnam gnyis la brtson 'grus bskyed nas gzigs shing /
NK115(re)001:21898: kun mkhyen rgyal ba klong chen pa yab sras kyi
NK115(re)001:21899: gzhung rnams la mos 'dun yang che bas slar yang
NK115(re)001:21900: bri gzhi'i shog bu dang bcas nan gyis gsungs pa
NK115(re)001:21901: dang / nye char rdo rje'i mched po rnams kyis
NK115(re)001:21902: kyang bskul ba'i gsung bzlog ma phod par bri dgos
NK115(re)001:21903: dang / byung la / bri ba'i tshe na ni
NK115(re)001:21904: bla ma rnams la snying nas gsol ba btab cing
NK115(re)001:21905: rgyal bstan snyigs mar gyur pa dang 'gro ba'i bde
NK115(re)001:21906: skyid zad pa'i dus tshod 'di lta bu la phan
NK115(re)001:21907: pa'i lhag bsam gyi 'dun pa yang yang bcos nas
NK115(re)001:21908: dang / byung la / / 'grel pa shing rta rnam gnyis la gzhi byas /
NK115(re)001:21909: kun mkhyen rgyal ba yab sras kyi gsung gzhan rnams dang /
NK115(re)001:21910: rang gi bla ma dam pa rnams kyi gsung rgyun spyi dang /
NK115(re)001:21911: khyad par chos rje bla ma bka' drin can 7'jigs
NK115(re)001:21912: med chos kyi dbang po'i zhal snga nas gsungs pa'i
NK115(re)001:21913: sa bcad 'bring po bsdus don du bzhag cing /
NK115(re)001:21914: dka' gnas rnams zur du 'grel pa skabs gang 'os
NK115(re)001:21915: su sbyar nas de gnyis mjug rtsom dang bcas kha
NK115(re)001:21917: rang nus ci yod kyis 'bru bsnan cing dka' gnas
NK115(re)001:21918: rnams blos dpogs tshod kyis dpyad pa dang bcas gsal
NK115(re)001:21919: bar bkod pa po ni dge mang skyabs rje rin
NK115(re)001:21920: po che'i dbon po bka' drin mtshungs pa med pa
NK115(re)001:21921: 7o rgyan bstan 'dzin nor bu'i zhabs rdul spyi bos
NK115(re)001:21922: reg cing dam pa de nyid kyi gcung rigs su
NK115(re)001:21923: gyur pa rmongs rtul sh+aakya'i dge slong gi ming tsam
NK115(re)001:21924: 'dzin pa 7yon tan rgya mtshor 'bod pas lhun grub
NK115(re)001:21925: bde chen gling gi gtsug lag khang bshad sgrub nor
NK115(re)001:21926: bu'i dga' tshal du grub par bgyis pa 'di yang
NK115(re)001:21927: rgyal bstan spyi dang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK115(re)001:21928: bstan pa phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du dar
NK115(re)001:21929: zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur
